(3, 1, 'SHIPPING &amp; RETURN', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;STANDARD SHIPPING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWe offer standard free shipping every day on U.S. orders over $99 when shipping to the lower 48 states. We don\'t ship to Alaska and Hawaii, P.O. Box or APO/FPO/DPO and International orders.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOur standard shipping method is ground shipping. We will ship your order via any of the major mail carriers, including UPS, FedEx, DHL and the United States Postal Service.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPlease note that delivery of orders with more than one item may ship on different dates according to stock availability.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;SHIPPING SERVICES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;delivery_page&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;table class=&quot;table table-bordered&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; width: 1068px; max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 17px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); line-height: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; line-height: 1.42857; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Carrier&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; line-height: 1.42857; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Location&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; line-height: 1.42857; vertical-align: mi