;box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17.1429px;&quot;&gt;5-7 business days&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px; line-height: 1.42857; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;$0.00&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PROCESSING TIME&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFor all orders, please allow 2 to 3 business days for order processing before shipping.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOrders placed over holidays and weekends will be processed the following business days.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nYour final shipping cost and estimated delivery timeframe will be available to you during checkout.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;about-page&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ORDER STATUS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTo view the full details of &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ankermart.com/index.php?route=account/track_order&quot;&gt;YOUR ORDER&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; as well as obtain tracking information, please enter your order number and your email address.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIf you do not receive the confirmation email, please check your Junk or Spam folders. Then select the confirmation message and click not junk, which will allow future messages to get through.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;1. COMPLETE: You successfully submitted your order to Ankermart.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. IN FULFILLMENT:&amp;nbsp; Your order is at a Ankermart warehouse and will usually ship in 2-3 business days.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. SHIPPED: Your order is on its way. You will receive an e-mail with tracking information.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. RETURN INITIATED: At your request, Ankermart set up a return for an order.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. RETURN COMPLETE: Ankermart warehouse received the returned item.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n6. CANCELED: Your order has been canceled.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n7. REFUNDED: Your payment has been refunded.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EASY RETURNS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;1. SUBMIT A REQUEST: Click &quot;submit a request&quot; button below and fill &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://ankermart.com/index.php?route=account/return/insert&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;out the form&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;2. RECEIVE RETURN AUTHORIZATION: Receive return authorization (RA) form with the exact return address and a shipping label (may take 24-72 hours)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;3. SHIP IT BACK: Print and attach the provided UPS/FedEx shipping label as well as the RA form to the outside of the box&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;4. RECEIVE REFUND OR REPLACEMENT: Once the merchandise is received your refund would be issued within 48 hours or a replacement shipped&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;center&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://ankermart.com/image/data/return-steps.png&quot; style=&quot;height: 115px; width: 880px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/center&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RETURN POLICY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;1. The Items must be returned within 15 days of receipt of the product. We apologize for any inconvenience. However, we cannot accept returns over 15 days. All items must be in brand new, unused condition and include all original packaging, components, manuals, and documentation. The products non-defective / non-damaged returns are responsible for the shipping cost of the order and a 20% restocking fee, and customer pay return shipping.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;2. The few exceptions for items that cannot be returned include:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px; margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;2.1. Items Marked &quot;Non-Returnable&quot; (clearly indicated on the product page before placing your order).&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2.2. Personalized Items (custom engraved or embroidered).&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2.3. Mattress, Wheels &amp;amp; Tires Packages,&amp;nbsp;Electronics Tool Kits.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;3. All products require a Return Authorization Number (RA #) before being returned. This number can be obtained by contacting us by&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ankermart.com/index.php?route=account/return/insert&quot;&gt;Returns Center&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;or email sale@ankermart.com.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;4. All products defective / damaged during shipping must be reported to us within 48 hours and your package must be returned or postmarked within five business days from receipt so that we may properly report a claim to our shipping carrier. We will gladly replace item/s damaged during shipping. However, we ask that you follow the above instructions provided.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;5. Customers who refuse delivery of an item that they ordered is responsible for the shipping cost of the order and a 20% restocking fee, and customer pay return shipping&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;6. Customers who provide an incorrect shipping address or are not available to receive a shipment are responsible for the shipping costs of the order. We will try our best to keep track of all orders and will notify customers of additional shipping information needed for delivery.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;REFUND POLICY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;1. We inspect all returned items when they arrive at our processing facility. If your return is a result of the defective product, we will refund the full cost of the merchandise and original shipping charges.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;2. If you return an item that was opened or shows signs of wear, we will issue a partial refund minus the original shipping charges and return shipping fees. Products decrease in value over time.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;3. You can expect your refund within 01&amp;nbsp;weeks from the date you return your package. In most cases, you will receive a refund sooner.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;4. Please allow 2-3 business days from the time of your request for refunds to appear on your Card/Paypal.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;5. All refunds are issued to the original method of payment. Once your return is processed, we will send you an email with your refund details.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n'),
(8, 1, 'FAQ', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;#Q WHAT IS THE CONDITION OF THIS ITEM?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;#A&lt;/strong&gt; All items are a brand-new, unused, unopened item in its original packaging, with all original packaging materials included. Original manufacturer\'s warranty.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HOW DO I MAKE PAYMENTS USING PAYPAL? HOW DOES IT WORK?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPaypal is the easiest way to make payments online. While checking out your order, you will be redirected to the Paypal website. Be sure to fill in correct details for fast &amp;amp; hassle-free payment processing. After a successful Paypal payment, a payment advice will be automatically generated to the ankermart.com system for your order. It\'s fast, easy &amp;amp; secure.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT PAYMENT METHODS DOES ANKERMART ACCEPT?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPayPal is currently the only payment method accepted.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CAN I PAY USING PAYPAL WITHOUT A PAYPAL ACCOUNT?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nYes! It is commonly misunderstood that a Paypal account is needed in order to make payments through Paypal. The truth is you DO NOT need one, although we strongly recommend you sign up to enjoy the added ease of use.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Without a Paypal account, all you need is any Debit/Credit card stated below that is supported by Paypal. By using Paypal, we can process &amp;amp; deliver your orders to you in a shorter time. Paypal is the easiest &amp;amp; most secure way to make payments online. No account needed.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFor more details, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.paypal.com/us/webapps/mpp/how-paypal-works/overview&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;click here&lt;/a&gt; to see how Paypal works for you.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CAN I CHANGE MY ORDER ONCE IT HAS BEEN SUBMITTED?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNo. Once an order has been submitted to the ANKERMART store, no further changes can be made to it.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HOW DO I CANCEL MY ORDERS?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOrders cannot be canceled after payment is made, if you wish to cancel the order, please do not complete checkout.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HOW LONG WILL IT TAKE FOR MY ORDER TO ARRIVE AFTER I MAKE PAYMENT?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPlease allow 3-4 business days for order processing prior to shipping, and it needs about 4-5 business days to deliver to your home. Orders placed over holidays and weekends will be processed the following business days.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY DO ITEM(S) HAVE A QUANTITY LIMIT RESTRICTION? WHEN CAN I ORDER MORE?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSome promotional or sales item(s) may have a quantity limit and will be mentioned in the item listing so more customers can take advantage of the sales.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOrders that exceed listed availability will automatically be voided without notice.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DOES ANKERMART OFFER ANY TECHNICAL SUPPORT OR ADVICE ON COMPONENT COMPATIBILITY?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nANKERMART does not offer any technical assistance or advice. Please contact the manufacturers for accurate answers to your technical questions and for insight on how different products interact together.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHERE CAN I ACQUIRE MORE INFORMATION ON THE PRODUCTS LISTED?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nANKERMART provides all the detail information available in the product description section. If additional information is needed, please contact the manufacturer.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY AM I BEING ASSESSED AN ADDITIONAL ELECTRONIC WASTE RECYCLING FEE BY THE STATE OF CALIFORNIA (EWRA E-WASTE)?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe primary objective of the Electronic Waste Recycling Act (&quot;Act&quot;) is to initiate a recycling program for computer products containing chemicals deemed hazardous to the environment. To fund this program, California requires retailers and e-tailers to collect, on the state\'s behalf, a fee for each product covered by this law.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHERE DO YOU SHIP FROM?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThis item ships from the United States.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DO SHIPPING COSTS DECREASE WHEN THERE ARE MULTIPLE ITEMS IN AN ORDER?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhen multiple items are ordered together, shipping cost is usually reduced according to weight and size, safety and insurance required. Simply place all items in the shopping cart, pick the state and method of shipping and apply the shipping calculator.&amp;nbsp;Please note that the delivery of orders with more than one item may ship on different dates according to stock availability.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HOW LONG DOES IT TAKE FOR ANKERMART TO PROCESS AN RMA?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;RMA processing time may vary depending on the product and reason for the return but generally, the processing time is 2-5 business days once the RMA is received and meet all of the required criteria.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CAN I OBTAIN AN RMA FOR A CONSUMABLE ITEM (INK/TONER CARTRIDGE, PAPER PRODUCT, BLANK CD/DVD MEDIA, BATTERIES, ETC.) USING ANKERMART\'S ONLINE RMA SYSTEM?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nConsumable items cannot be returned to ANKERMART unless the item is new and sealed in its original packaging.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HOW DO REFUNDS/CREDITS WORK? HOW IS A REFUND/CREDIT APPLIED?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe refund will be charged back to your PayPal account.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HOW LONG IS THE WAITING PERIOD BEFORE I AM ABLE TO FILE A CLAIM FOR A LOST, DAMAGED, MISDELIVERED OR TAMPERED PACKAGE?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIf an order was damaged, misdelivered or tampered with while in transit, please contact Customer Service within 2 business days of delivery. If your order was lost while in transit, please contact Customer Service within 7 business days of not receiving your order.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;APPROXIMATELY HOW LONG WILL IT BE BEFORE A REFUND/CREDIT ACTUALLY APPEARS ON MY PAYPAL ACCOUNT?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIt takes us approximately 24-48 hours to process a credit back to a PayPal Account. Please allow 2-3 business days for it to appear on the statement.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n');
