(104, 1, 'Kodak AZ251 Digital Camera with 16.15 Megapixels and 25x Optical Zoom', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;Discover the new collection of Kodak PIXPRO digital cameras and discover a world of creativity at your fingertips. The Kodak AZ251 Black Digital Camera is the perfect bridge camera to explore your love of photography. Ample megapixels, 25x optical mega zoom and a wider angle lens than traditional models, this camera could easily become your new best friend. Tell your story. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;Kodak Black AZ251 Digital Camera:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Kodak AZ251 Black Digital Camera 16.15 megapixel resolution with high-quality still images and video recordings&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	Featuring Auto, Indoor and Panorama Effects with 720p HD Movie Recording, Face Detection Technology, Optical Image Stabilization and Blink Detection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Kodak 4.3-107.5mm zoom lens with 25x optical/4x digital zoom&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	Equivalent to a 24-600mm lens on an analog camera with TTL Contrast, Single AF, Multi-AF, Glass Lens&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3.0&quot; TFT LCD screen with image editing features&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	Featuring Brightness Adjustment, Graphical User Interface, color TFT LCD screen&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Kodak Digital Camera with 16.15 Megapixels has built-in flash with Red-Eye Reduction, Forced Flash, Auto On/Off and Slow-Sync Flash&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;Additional Features:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;8MB built-in memory with 1 SD/SDHC memory card slot (memory card not included)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Powered by 4 AA alkaline batteries (included) or 4 AA NiMH batteries (not included) for up to 280 shots (alkaline) or 500 shots (NiMH)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ISO Modes: Auto, 3200, 1600, 800, 400, 200, 100, 80&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Kodak Digital Camera with 16.15 Megapixels File Formats Supported: EXIF, MOV&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The 25x Optical Zoom Digital Camera is 4.53&quot; x 2.93&quot; x 2.74&quot;; 12.5 oz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;Kodak AZ251 Black Digital Camera Compatibility and Warranty:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;This 25x Optical Zoom Digital Camera is compatible with PC or Mac&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1-year limited manufacturer warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;What\'s in the Box:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Kodak Black AZ251 Digital Camera&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery, charger and power cable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick Start Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CD with software and digital manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Kodak AZ251 Digital Camera with 16.15 Megapixels and 25x Optical Zoom', 'Kodak AZ251 Digital Camera with 16.15 Megapixels and 25x Optical Zoom', 'Kodak AZ251 Digital Camera with 16.15 Megapixels and 25x Optical Zoom'),
(105, 1, 'Beats Studio Over-Ear Headphones- Assorted Colors', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;The world\'s most famous headphones, Beats Studio Over-Ear Headphones, have been completely redesigned and re-imagined. The new Beats Studio headphones are lighter, stronger and more comfortable. They are designed with precision sound, Adaptive Noise Canceling (ANC), a 20-hour rechargeable battery and RemoteTalk capabilities. It has the energy and excitement you expect from Beats, plus a powerful re-engineered sound. The included USB 2.0 charging cable can be used in a computer or it can be used with a USB-lighter adapter for the car. You\'ll find that these noise cancelling over ear headphones are ideal for busy environments. Use them when on the go, or use them at home for private listening. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;Beats Studio Over-Ear Headphones:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Noise-cancelling over-ear headphones have Adaptive Noise Canceling (ACT) technology&amp;gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;20-hour rechargeable battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;RemoteTalk&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes USB 2.0 charging cable, power adapter, 3.5mm audio cable, RemoteTalk cable, hard shell carrying case and Beats cleaning cloth&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Blue&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Model No.: Beats 900-00149-01&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Shipping Weight (in pounds): 2.51 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Product in Inches (L x W x H): 9.13&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;6.85&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;5.28 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Ankermart&amp;nbsp;No.: 552260860&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Beats Studio Over-Ear Headphones- Assorted Colors', 'Beats Studio Over-Ear Headphones- Assorted Colors', 'Beats Studio Over-Ear Headphones, Beats Studio headphones,assorted colors, noise canceling over ear headphones'),
(106, 1, 'Beats by Dr. Dre Pro Over-Ear Headphones', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;These Beats By Dr. Dre Pro Headphones will transform the way you listen to music. Equipped with dual headphone ports, these headphones will let you share your crystal-clear, pulse-pounding music with any 3.5mm-equipped device. Their durable construction and foldable design make these Beats Pro Headphones reliable and easily portable. The plush leather ear cups provide comfortable listening and can be rotated so that you can find just the right headphone position. For soaring highs and deep bass, these Beats over-ear headphones are the premier choice. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Beats by Dr. Dre Pro Over-Ear Headphones:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wide frequency range for true studio sound&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Strong, durable construction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual ports to share what you\'re hearing on Beats over-ear headphones&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Plush leather ear cups rotate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Battery Type: Does Not Contain a Battery &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Primary Color: Black Model No.: 900-00034-01 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Shipping Weight (in pounds): 3.16 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Product in Inches (L x W x H): 9.13&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;6.85&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;5.28 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Ankermart No.: 551469555&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Beats by Dr. Dre Pro Over-Ear Headphones', 'Beats by Dr. Dre Pro Over-Ear Headphones', 'Beats by Dr. Dre Pro Headphones, Beats Over-Ear Headphones, Beats Pro Headphones'),
(116, 1, 'Andis 4-Cup Coffee Maker, 69045, Black/Stainless Steel', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;Have your morning coffee easily with this brewer by Andis. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;It holds four cups of coffee and has a sleek, black and stainless steel coloring to fit any kitchen. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;Andis 4-Cup Coffee Maker:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4-cup capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto shut off after 1 hour&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Non-stick warming plate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy-pour stainless steel carafe&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brewing instructions printed on side of coffee maker&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;90-day warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model# 69045&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Battery Type: Does Not Contain a Battery &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Primary Color: Black &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Multi Pack Indicator: No &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Model No.: 69045 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Shipping Weight (in pounds): 3.6 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Product in Inches (L x W x H): 10.8&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;10.8&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;7.8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Ankermart No.: 551857941&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Andis 4-Cup Coffee Maker, 69045, Black/Stainless Steel', 'Andis 4-Cup Coffee Maker, 69045, Black/Stainless St