(60, 1, 'Neato XV Signature Robotic Vacuum, 945-0079', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Robotic vacuums are not to be used as a primary vacuum. They\'re meant as supplemental cleaning between regular cleaning. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;It\'s a robot and a vacuum! The Neato Robotic Vacuum, 945-0079 is the smartest, most powerful robot vacuum. Its improved aerodynamic design hugs the floor for superior pickup on all floor types - the strongest suction available in a robot vacuum. The unique square front and low profile design keeps the Neato Robotic Vacuum, 945-0079 close to corners and walls for maximum pick-up of dirt, dust, debris and pet hair - all without sacrificing suction power! It automatically moves from one floor type to another, and even manages rugs with fringe. The Neato Automatic Vacuum comes with a high-performance filter which makes it a great choice for anyone with allergies or who is concerned about dust. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Neato XV Signature Robotic Vacuum, 945-0079:&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;dl&gt;\r\n&lt;/dl&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Neato Automatic Vacuum makes your life easier and your home cleaner&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Works on all types of floors&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Scans and systematically cleans your home&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Knows where it\'s been and where it\'s going&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatically moves from room to room&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Gets in corners and under furniture&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easily schedule daily cleanings or just push a button for spot clean or instant multi-room cleaning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High-performance filter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Robot software can be upgraded when new features become available&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Improved aerodynamic design picks up 50 percent more dust&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Large bagless dirt bin makes it easy to use and environmentally friendly&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1-year limited warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;XV Signature Neato Vacuum Model# 945-0079&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cleaning Path Width: 13 inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Primary Color: Black&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi Pack Indicator: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery Type: Nickel Metal Hydride&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model No.: XVSignature&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shipping Weight (in pounds): 15.85&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product in Inches (L x W x H): 12.5&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;13.0&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;4.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ankermart&amp;nbsp;No.: 551675303&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Neato XV Signature Robotic Vacuum, 945-0079', 'Neato XV Signature Robotic Vacuum, 945-0079', 'Neato Robotic Vacuum, 945-0079, Neato Automatic Vacuum, Neato Vacuum, XV Signature'),
(61, 1, 'Shark Rotator Professional Upright Vacuum, NV400', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;This lightweight, never-loses-suction Shark Rotator Professional Lightweight Upright Vacuum is ultra-maneuverable featuring enhanced swivel steering for better control to maneuver in and around furniture. This Shark upright vacuum also features ultra-quiet technology for operation anywhere, anytime. Plus, an anti-allergen complete seal traps over 99.99 percent of dust and allergens inside the vacuum. This ultra quiet vacuum includes extra-long cleaning reach wand, pet power brush and other premium tools such as a 24-inch flexible crevice tool and a three-in-one tool that ride on board for versatile cleaning throughout the home. The premium power nozzle of this Shark upright vacuum comes with headlights for illuminating dark spaces and the brush roll can be turned on or off, providing superior performance on both carpets and bare floors.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;Shark Rotator Professional Upright Vacuum, NV400:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rotator technology with enhanced swivel steering and better deep carpet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Anti-allergen complete seal technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Never loses suction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lightweight and ultra-quiet operation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extended above-floor reach and premium pet tools&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ergonomic handles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra-large capacity, bottom-empty dust cup&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;30\' power cord&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5-year warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model# NV400&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Multi Pack Indicator: No &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Battery Type: Does Not Contain a Battery &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r