(55, 1, 'Hoover Max Extract All-Terrain Carpet Washer, F7452900', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;Clean your carpets and floor to perfection at a moment\'s notice with the Hoover Max Extract All Terrain Carpet Cleaner, F7452900. This Hoover carpet cleaner is designed to deep clean the carpeted and hard floor surfaces in your home. Dual V Nozzle technology, heated cleaning, patented SpinScrub brushes and Auto Rinse technology combine to provide superb floor and carpet cleaning performance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Hoover Max Extract All-Terrain Carpet Washer:&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Designed to clean carpet, upholstery, sealed hardwood, tile, or vinyl flooring&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual V Nozzle technology provides equal suction across the full width of the nozzle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SpinScrub brushes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heated cleaning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic detergent mixing system provides the correct mix of detergent and water&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatically rinses carpet and hard floors&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3 scrubbing and spill pick up speeds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hard floor package includes hard floor squeegee, SpinScrub brushes for hard floors and large, soft wheels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;8-foot hose for above floor cleaning with simple attachments and SpinScrub hand tool&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;20-foot power cord&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cleaning solutions included: Floor-to-Floor and Ultra Detergents included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;13-inch cleaning path&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;12-amp motor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weighs 30 pounds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 gallon Capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1-year warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Finer Categorizations: Robotic Multi&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pack Indicator: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li