(103, 1, 'GE Black X550 Power PRO Digital Camera with 16 Megapixels, 27mm Wide-Angle Lens', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;Capture all the action like a pro with the General Electric Bridge Camera. All the power and performance you need is this best-selling bridge camera series. High megapixels, ample long zoom, electronic view finder and a 27mm wide-angle lens are just a few of the cutting edge features offered in this affordable bridge camera only from GE. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;GE Power Pro Series X550 Bridge Digital Camera with 16 Megapixels and 15x Optical Zoom:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;16 megapixel resolution with high-quality still images and video recordings&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	The General Electric Bridge Camera features Panorama, Auto Scene Selector, Face Detection Technology, Optical Image Stabilization and Smile and Blink Detection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4.9 - 73.5mm lens with 15x optical/6x digital zoom&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	Equivalent to a 27 - 405mm lens on an analog camera with Object Tracking, HDR+, Shutter and Aperture Priority modes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2.7&quot; LCD screen&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	Featuring auto brightness&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The GE Digital Camera 15X 2.7 has built-in flash with Auto, Red-Eye Reduction, Forced Flash, No Flash, Slow Synchro, Red-Eye Reduction + Slow Synchro&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;Additional Features:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;13MB built-in memory with 1 SD/SDHC memory card slot (memory card not included)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Powered by 4 x AA batteries for up to 300 shots&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;GE Digital Camera 15X 2.7 ISO Modes: Auto, 3200, 1600, 800, 400, 200, 100, 80&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;File Formats Supported: JPEG, MOV, G.711&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4.0&quot; x 2.9&quot; x 2.6&quot;; 15 oz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;Compatibility and Warranty:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;