(54, 1, '25&quot; GMC Denali 700c Men\'s Road Bike, Black', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;The GMC Denali 700c Men\'s Road Bike is built around a lightweight aluminum road bicycle frame. As its name suggests, it is meant for typical road usage, such as plain commuting or racing. It features a slim wheel and a smooth tire that reduces the friction between the road and the tire. This GMC Denali 21-Speed Road Bike is equipped with alloy calipers and brake levers to make stopping smooth and precise. The rims of the X-Large GMC Denali 700c Road Bike are made of high-profile alloy Vitesse and perform as good as they look. A better aerodynamic position is possible with the lower hand position. Shimano Revo shifters allow you to shift without taking your hands off the handle bars, providing safety and confidence. A Shimano derailleur completes the road cycle drive train for quick and smooth gear changes. This GMC Denali 21-Speed Road Bike is a good entry level bike and is well worth the price.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;25&quot; GMC Denali 700c Men\'s Road Bike, Black:&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fits riders 6\'2&quot;-6\'5&quot; with a stand over of 32&quot;-34&quot;.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Riding style: road bike.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Frame: Aluminum 7005 50cm.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Handlebar: Steel custom 2-piece.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Gearing: 21-speed.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;X-Large GMC Denali 700c Road Bike shifters: Shimano Revo SIS.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Front Derailleur: Shimano FD-TZ 31 Index.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rear Derailleur: Shimano RD-TZ30GS 7SPD.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bike Saddle: Cionlli Black.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Seat post: HL Aluminum Micro Adjust 27.2 X 300 mm.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brakes: Promax 501A Alloy Caliper Brake.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brake levers: Promax BL-250AP Aluminum.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bi