(10021, 1, 'Eureka 955A Complete Clean Bagless Canister Vacuum', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;The 955A Eureka Complete Clean Canister Vacuum is ideal for tidying up the whole home from floor to ceiling. Electronic on/off brushroll picks up dust and allergens from carpets and bare floors. The pet hair and dirt that has been picked up from the floor is kept in the included flip-bottom dust cup protecting you from them. Moreover, the 955A Eureka Complete Clean Canister Vacuum has a HEPA filtration system that captures 99.97 percent of dust and allergens for a tidier home. This bagless canister vacuum with motorized power nozzle can be used to clean carpets and rugs, as well as bare floors. Be sure to empty the dust container after each and every use to enhance its performance. You can also access unreachable areas using the extra-long telescopic wand. This Eureka canister vacuum comes with an impressive cyclonic technology that retains suction power for a longer duration.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;Once you are done with the day\'s cleaning, just lower the handle and neatly store it in a closet. The automatic cord rewind retracts effortlessly for quick and easy storage. Clean any place in a snap with this bagless canister vacuum with motorized power nozzle.\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Eureka Complete Clean Bagless Canister Vacuum, 955A:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1 Year Limited&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Eureka canister vacuum with On/Off Brushroll Switch: picks up dust and allergens from carpets and bare floors&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic Cord Rewind: rewinds cord effortlessly for quick and easy storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;955A Eureka Complete Clean Canister Vacuum with HEPA Filtration: captures 99.97% of dust and allergens for a cleaner home&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flip-Bottom Dust Cup: helps keep fine, allergy-causing dust away from you&lt;/