(72, 1, 'Neato XV-12 Robotics Automatic Bagless Vacuum', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Robotic vacuums are not to be used as a primary vacuum. They\'re meant as supplemental cleaning between regular cleaning.&lt;/strong&gt;The future of vacuuming. The Neato XV-12 will keep your floors clean with just the push of a button. Featuring the most powerful suction in a robot vacuum, the Neato will easily pick up dirt, debris and even pet hair. Its laser navigation system ensures that it never misses a spot. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Neato XV-12 Robotics Automatic Bagless Vacuum :&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;dl&gt;\r\n&lt;/dl&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The most powerful suction in a robot vacuum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easily picks up dirt, debris and even pet hair&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Laser navigation system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cleans in a methodical back and forth pattern&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bagless technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic cleaning system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1-year manufacturer defect warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model# XV-12&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Multi Pack Indicator: No Battery &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Type: Nickel Metal Hydride &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Model No.: NeatoXV-12Robot &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Shipping Weight (in pounds): 14.0 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Product in Inches (L x W x H): 13.0&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;13.0&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;4.0 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;An