(102, 1, 'Canon PowerShot SX170 IS 16MP 16x Optical Zoom Camera', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;Zoom in on images you\'re not likely to capture with a smartphone. The 16x optical zoom on the Canon Powershot 16MP Digital Camera, SX170 gets you up close to kids and wildlife, down on the field and up on the stage, while Canon\'s Optical Image Stabilizer keeps images steady and clear. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;Canon PowerShot SX170 IS 16MP 16x Optical Zoom Camera:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;16 megapixel resolution with high-quality still images and video recordings&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	The Canon Powershot 16MP Digital Camera, SX170 features Portrait, Face Self-timer, Low Light, Snow and Fireworks modes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5.0-80mm zoom lens with 16x optical/4x digital zoom&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	Equivalent to a 28-448mm lens on an analog camera with TTL Autofocus, Manual Focus, Glass Lens&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3&quot; TFT LCD screen with image editing features&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	Featuring Brightness Adjustment, Graphical User Interface, easy-to-read menu system, color TFT LCD screen&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Black Canon Powershot Camera has built-in flash with Auto, Flash On, Slow Synchro, Flash Off&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;Additional Features:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 SD/SDHC/SDXC memory card slot (memory card not included)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rechargeable Lithium-Ion battery for up to 440 shots&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ISO Modes: Auto, 1600, 800, 400, 200, 100, 80&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;File Formats Supported: JPEG, MOV&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Canon Powershot Digital Camera with 16x Optical Zoom is 4.25&quot; x 2.80&quot; x 1.73&quot;; 11.1 oz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;Compatibility and Warranty:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible with PC or Mac&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Canon Powershot Digital Camera with 16x Optical Zoom has a 1-year limited manufacturer warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;What\'s in the Box:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Canon Black PowerShot SX-170 IS Camera&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery, charger and power cable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick Start Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CD with software and digital manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Canon PowerShot SX170 IS 16MP 16x Optical Zoom Camera', 'Canon PowerShot SX170 IS 16MP 16x Optical Zoom Camera', 'Canon PowerShot SX170 IS 16MP 16x Optical Zoom Camera'),
(83, 1, 'Weber 508 sq. inch One Touch Gold Charcoal Grill, Black', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;Bring your taste buds to life and cook all your favorite barbeque dishes with the One Touch Gold Charcoal Grill from Weber. The Weber charcoal grill is spacious enough for you to grill a variety of delicious meats and vegetables at one time. This Weber 508 Sq Inch One Touch Gold Charcoal Grill features a stainless steel cooking grate that is easy to clean with a wire barbeque brush. It also includes a built-in thermometer that allows you to easily monitor the temperature of the grill. This stainless steel charcoal grill also has a tuck-away lid holder so you can move the lid to the side when you need to check the food or add more charcoal. Add this porcelain charcoal grill to your backyard or patio and invite your family and friends over for Weber charcoal grilling.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Weber 508 Sq Inch One Touch Gold Charcoal Grill:&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Porcelain enameled bowl and lid&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;26.5 inch cooking area = 508 square inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stainless steel hinged cooking grate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stainless steel one touch cleaning system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable high capacity ash catcher&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tuck away lid holder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No rust aluminum vent&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built in thermometer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Glass reinforced nylon handles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Crackproof all weather wheels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weber cookbook&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Limited Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Primary Color: Black &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Multi Pack Indicator: No &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&