(86, 1, 'Little Tikes Hide and Slide Climber', '&lt;p&gt;A great backyard climber that is the perfect jungle gym for toddlers! This rugged climber is built with our famous Little Tikes quality. Kids will love the sliding board, climbing platforms and places to crawl, climb and hide. Designed to promote healthy activity and imaginative play.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;As slides and outdoor playgrounds go, this rugged unit has a lot to offer. This easy-to-climb, outdoor playground gym is a great way for toddlers and preschoolers to burn some of their boundless energy! &amp;nbsp;A jungle gym that will last forever.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;• The wavy, gentle slide provides smooth rides and soft landings&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;• A secret play area underneath the playground platform for hide-and-seek games&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;• Wide, multi-level platforms make it easy for little ones to climb up to the slide landing&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;• Maximum number of kids: 3&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;• Weight limit up to 60lbs. per child&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;• Assembly Required&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;• Made in USA&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;• Age: 2 - 6 years&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dimension:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Size: 66.00\'\'L x 56.50\'\'W x 45.25\'\'H --- Weight: 41.50lbs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Box Size: 48.00\'\'L x 18.30\'\'W x 21.96\'\'H --- Weight: 41.50lbs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Slide height from ground to top of slide: 0.00\'\'L x 0.00\'\'W x 27.00\'\'H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Platform height from ground to top of platform: 0.00\'\'L x 0.00\'\'W x 25.00\'\'H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Slide : 39.00\'\'L x 0.00\'\'W x 0.00\'\'H&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note: The Little Tikes Hide &amp;amp; Slide Climber is intended to be used for home outside backyard use only.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Little Tikes Hide and Slide Climber', 'Little Tikes Hide and Slide Climber', 'Little Tikes Hide and Slide Climber'),
(87, 1, 'Little Tikes Pirate Ship Toddler Bed', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;Ahoy Matey! Children can sail the seas and bring the adventure and treasure right into their own bedroom with the Little Tikes Pirate Ship Toddler Bed. The bed features a built-in toy box, a ship wheel for &quot;steering&quot; the ship, a mast with a fabric sail and working night lights. The Pirate Ship Bed For Kids is sure to entice any little one to dream of action and adventure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Little Tikes Pirate Ship Toddler Bed:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes ship wheel, cannons, mast with fabric sail and crow\'s nest&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Features built-in toy box, cubby holes and working night lights&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Little Tikes Toddler Bed meets or exceeds all U.S. safety standards&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Recommended for children 15 months to 5 years and up to 50 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Primary Color: Brown &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Multi Pack Indicator: No &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Battery Type: Does Not Contain a Battery&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Model No.: 625954M &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Shipping Weight (in pounds): 90.0 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Product in Inches (L x W x H): 86.0&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;47.0&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;84.0 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Assembled in Country of Origin: USA &lt;/span&gt;&lt