(91, 1, 'Little Tikes Home and Garden Playhouse', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;Get the Little Tikes Home and Garden Playhouse for your kid to develop the do-it-yourself skills. This kids outdoor playhouse is an interactive and fun activity that will keep your kid busy for hours together. Also, it helps boost your kids mental ability. Your kid is sure to have a great time building the fence and hanging the flower box. Kids can even plant and grow real flowers in the flower box. For an imaginative play, this children play house comes with a kitchenette that features a pretend stove with clicker knobs and a faucet.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Little Tikes Home and Garden Playhouse:&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Working door, mailbox with flag, and multiple play areas&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Playhouse includes pounding bench and toolbox&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sand &amp;amp; water / planting play area&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flower box&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6 Fence pickets&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;16 Nails/bolts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Little Tikes Home and Garden Playhouse comes with hammer, screwdriver and wrench&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Little Tikes Home and Garden Playhouse requires some adult assembly with kid participation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Age End: &amp;nbsp;and up &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Age Start: 18 Months,1-1/2 Years &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Primary Color: Multi-Color &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Battery Type: Does Not Contain a Battery &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&