(10025, 1, 'Fiskars 6201 18-Inch Staysharp Max Push Reel Lawn Mower', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Patent pending InertiaDrive™ technology, combines a large diameter cutting reel and heavy blades to store energy (like a flywheel) until a burst of extra cutting power is needed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Twice the power to blast through small twigs, weeds and dense grass&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No steel-on-steel contact that dulls standard reel mower blades and peak performance can be maintained&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exclusive StaySharp™ cutting system is precision engineered to cut grass w/o the blades touching, greatly reducing friction and blade wear&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Patent pending VersaCut™design, utilizes a unique forward position cutting reel and a long wheel base to provide best in class cutting capabilities - with cut height settings from 1&quot; to 4&quot; and the closest side edging of any reel mower&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fiskars advanced technologies combine to reduce friction, provide optimal blade positioning and deliver extra cutting power to reduce push force by 30% in long grass&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fiskars ergonomics and best in class features further enhance the mowing experience&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unique forward reel position provides the closest side edging of any reel mower and mess-free forward grass discharge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Superior ergonomics include a simple one-touch cut height adjustment and a height-adjustable handle with a padded ergo grip for superior maneuverability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut Width (Inches): 18.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bagger Included: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Handle Style: Ergonomic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UL Safety Listing: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CSA Safety Listing: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ETL Safety Listing: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0