(10026, 1, 'Soda Stream 1019111015 Black Revolution Soda Maker Starter Kit', '&lt;p&gt;The Revolution is the first automatic SodaStream home soda maker, the Revolution offers breakthroughs in both function and design. Featuring One-touch activation providing a choice of carbonation levels (low, medium, high, turbo), an LED display indicating carbonation progress and CO2 usage status, and a Snap-lock mechanism for easy bottle insertion and removal. Turn water into sparkling water and soda in seconds with a Sodastream Revolution home soda maker.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One-touch activation lets you choose carbonation level.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LED display indicates carbonation progress and CO2 usage status.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Snap-lock bottle mechanism makes it easy to insert and remove bottle.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Reusable carbonator fizzes up to 60L of soda.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Custom flavors lets you create the drink you want.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy-to-clean drip tray adds convenience.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Slim, sleek design fits perfectly on most countertops.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Revolution soda maker, black with nickel accents&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 BPA-free reusable carbonating bottle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Reusable carbonator to fizz up to 60L of soda&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AC Adapter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sodamix Variety 6 pack&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;* Compatible with both 130L and 60L carbonators&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Product Construction &amp;amp; Care:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Plastic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Soda Maker: Wipe Clean&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bottles: Hand Wash&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt