(108, 1, 'Ionic Pro Combo Air Purifier with Bonus Car Air Purifier  90IP1RCMB1', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;The Ionic Pro Combo Air Purifier with Bonus Car Air Purifier 90IP1RCMB1 is ideal for cleaning the atmosphere in small rooms, offices and homes. The air purifier best suits rooms that are about 250 sq ft in area. An additional Car Ionizer comes along with this Ionic Pro air purifier. This bonus product is used to deliver clean fresh air in your car and helps you keep your vehicle free of dust. This ionic car air purifier is an excellent choice for people who wish to keep their rooms and cars filled with clean refreshing air.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;Operating on less than 12 watts, the Ionic Pro Combo Air Purifier with Bonus Car Air Purifier 90IP1RCMB1 saves on your energy costs. As the unit is inexpensive to operate and does not require expensive filter replacements, it is indeed one of the best home improvement appliances of today.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ionic Pro Combo Ionic Air Purifier:&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes bonus compact Ionic Pro and vehicle air purifier&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No costly filters to replace&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ionic Pro air purifier is inexpensive to operate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy efficient (operates on less than 12 watts)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vehicle air purifier is easy to clean (simply wipe the collection plates)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Recommended for rooms up to 250 sq ft&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with three steel collection blades&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stable base stand&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Multi Pack Indicator: No &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Shipping Weight (in po