(109, 1, 'Hoover WH10600 True HEPA Air Purifier, Black', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;If you are looking for an efficient and quiet True HEPA unit, then go for the Hoover WH10600 Air Purifier. It comes with a UV bulb, rinseable pre-filter and titanium dioxide coated screen that provides complete air purification. The UV bulb in this black air purifier removes germs and microorganisms to create a healthy living space. The titanium dioxide coated screen removes germs that may have passed under the UV light, ensuring complete germ cleanup. Larger particles, lint and pet hair are captured and removed by the pre filter present in this True HEPA air purifier. It also comes with an ionizer that releases negative ions into the air to ensure effective filtration. You can adjust the three-speed fan on the Hoover WH10600 Air Purifier according to your requirement. Operation is made easy by the included remote control. This black air purifier is a good choice for allergy and asthma sufferers, as well as for people who live in arid climates.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hoover WH10600 Air Purifier:&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;7 room air changes every 3 hours based on a 12\' x 12\' room size&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UV bulb in True HEPA air purifier helps remove airborne germs, bacteria and other microorganisms&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Titanium Dioxide coated screen helps remove 99.9% of germs that pass under UV light&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hoover WH10600 Air Purifier has a rinsable pre-filter that catches lint, pet hair and other large particles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;HEPA media filter traps 99.97% of dust and pollen down to 0.3 microns&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ionizer emits negative ions into the air that make filtration more effective&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-speed fan easily adjusts for multiple layers of cleaning power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Change filter LED indicator lets you know when the filter needs changed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AHAM Certified CADR (Clean Air Delivery Rate)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes remote control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Model No.: WH10600 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Shipping Weight (in pounds): 15.05&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Product in Inches (L x W x H): 13.2&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;9.8&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;28.7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Hoover WH10600 True HEPA Air Purifier, Black', 'Hoover WH10600 True HEPA Air Purifier, Black', 'Hoover WH10600 True HEPA Air Purifier, Black'),
(110, 1, 'Germ Guardian 3-in-1 Digital HEPA Air Purifier with 28&quot; Pet Pure Filter, Gray', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;More than an air filter, the Germ Guardian HEPA Air Purifier with 28&quot; Pet Pure Filter will help keep the air in your home clean and fresh. This unit includes a specially-treated, multi-layer, complete filter that captures allergens, controls odors and fungi on the surface of the filter. The Germ Guardian 3-in-1 Air Purifier can also help to remove common home odors like smoke and more. Meanwhile the UV-C light in kills viruses as they pass through the system, leaving the air in your home safer and free from harmful bacteria. The Germ Guardian Digital Air Purifier also captures around 99.97 percent of all airborne allergens in your home. The features in this 3-in-1 Air Purifier work together to help improve indoor air quality in your home. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;Germ Guardian 3-in-1 Digital HEPA Air Purifier with 28&quot; Pet Pure Filter, Gray:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;True HEPA filter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Captures 99.97 percent of airborne allergens&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Captures particles as small as .3 microns&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power of UV-C Technology kills bacteria and viruses&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removes common household odors and smoke particles from the air with activated carbon filter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Kills airborne mold spores and other allergens&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CADR rated 125+&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Processes the air in approximately 193 sq ft per hour&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quiet operation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Digital controls&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5-year limited warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 6.10&quot;L x 9.50&quot;W x 27.25&quot;H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model# AC5250PT&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Multi Pa