(113, 1, 'Bunn-O-Matic 10-cup Black Professional Coffee Brewer, GRX-B', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;Nothing brews like the Bunn-O-Matic 10-Cup Black Professional Coffee Brewer! Using coffee brewing technology perfected in over 40 years of service to the restaurant industry, Bunn has built the perfect home brewing system. It\'s the perfect choice for parties, family gatherings and more. This unique &quot;reservoir-style&quot; coffee brewer makes up to 10 cups of coffee in just three minutes, while keeping hot water available for tea or other uses. It comes with an internal stainless steel water tank and a durable glass decanter. The Bunn-O-Matic 10-Cup Black Professional Coffee Brewer has a 3-year limited warranty. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;Bunn-O-Matic 10-Cup Black Professional Coffee Brewer:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bunn-O-Matic features the Original Bunn home brewer design, which uses coffee brewing technology perfected in over 40 years of service to the restaurant industry&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Coffee brewer comes complete with an internal stainless steel water tank and a durable glass decanter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unique &quot;reservoir-style&quot; coffee brewer makes up to 10 cups of coffee in just three minutes, while keeping hot water available for tea or other uses&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Coffeemaker has a built-in warming plate that keeps brewed coffee at optimal serving temperature for hours&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bunn-O-Matic 10-Cup Black Professional Coffee Brewer has a 3-year limited warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Primary Color: Black &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Multi Pack Indicator: No &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Model No.: GR