(114, 1, 'Mr. Coffee 24-oz Single Serve Coffee Maker', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;The Mr.Coffee 24-oz Mr Coffee Single Serve features Keurig Brewed technology for coffee house quality at home. Choose from a variety of over 200 K-Cup packs from coffee and tea to hot cocoa. The 24-ounce removable reservoir holds multiple cups of water before refilling. The Mr.Coffee 24-oz Mr Coffee Single Serve features a serving size selector that allows you to choose between two cup sizes. Remove the drip tray to accommodate larger cups or travel mugs so you can take your coffee to go.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mr. Coffee 24-oz Single Serve Coffee Maker:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Mr.Coffee Coffee Maker is powered by Keurig Brewed technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Uses patented Keurig K-Cup packs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable 24-oz water reservoir for multiple brews without refilling&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6-oz and 10-oz brew size options&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable drip tray to accommodate larger cups or travel mugs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brews a 6-oz cup in under 2 minutes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;This single serve coffee maker is perfect for coffee, tea or hot cocoa&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes a 5-count variety pack of K-Cup packs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Note: Distilled or reverse osmosis water is not recommended as this may cause overfilling in the drip tray&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Primary Color: Black &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Multi Pack Indicator: No &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Model No.: BVMC-KG5-001 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1