(115, 1, 'KitchenAid 12-cup Glass Carafe Coffee Maker, Black', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;Make fresh, hot coffee easily with the KitchenAid Glass Carafe Coffee Maker. This programmable coffee maker allows you to program brewing times, pause brewing and even select your brewing strength. Make coffee how you want it, when you want it with the KitchenAid Glass Carafe Coffee Maker. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;KitchenAid 12-cup Glass Carafe Coffee Maker, Black:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;24-hour programmability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Variable brew strength selector&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pause and serve feature&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 to 4 cup feature&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Large digital LED display and clock&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dripless spout&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes replaceable charcoal filter and gold tone filter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 11&quot;W x 8.3&quot;D x 13.8&quot;H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model# KCM1110B&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Primary Color: Black&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Multi Pack Indicator: No &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Model No.: KCM111OB &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Shipping Weight (in pounds): 7.55 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Product in Inches (L x W x H): 11.0&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;8.3&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;13.8 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Ankermart No.: 552035950&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'KitchenAid 12-cup Glass Carafe Coffee Maker, Black', 