(118, 1, 'Hamilton Beach 2-Way Brewer Coffeemaker, Black/Stainless Steel', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;There\'s finally an affordable, low-maintenance coffeemaker that can brew a basic or premium roast coffee in a fraction of the time and cost as the coffeehouse: With stainless steel durability and twice the brewing options as other leading coffeemakers, this Hamilton Beach 2-Way Brewer Coffeemaker doubles as a compact single-serve coffeemaker and also includes a full 12-cup pot. This fully programmable two-way coffee maker unit lets you decide when to brew, 7:00 a.m. or a late-night indulgence. This two-for-the-price-of-one coffeemaker lets coffee drinkers decide the right size to start their day and enjoy the best convenience for their schedule.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIf simplifying the morning wake-up routine is top priority, then use the single-serve for a standard-size cup or travel mug-size cup. If more coffee is needed, simply switch to the carafe side and watch as the Hamilton Beach 2-Way Brewer Coffeemaker makes a full 12 cups. This two-way brewer provides gourmet options and gourmet appeal. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;Hamilton Beach 2-Way Brewer Coffeemaker, Black/Stainless Steel:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 ways to brew - single cup or full 12-cup glass carafe&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;14 oz stainless steel travel mug with lid and 12-cup glass carafe included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Standard-size &quot;single-serve side&quot; water reservoir for easy, one-time filling&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&quot;Carafe-side&quot; water reservoir with extra-large capacity and measurement markings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&quot;Single-serve side&quot; Brew Basket comes with a mesh filter to hold ground coffee or pre-packaged soft pods&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&quot;Single-serve side&quot; multilevel cup rest adjusts/stacks to fit all cup and mug sizes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pod holder snaps onto the single-serve brew basket to hold soft pods&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brew strength selector for brewing &quot;REGULAR&quot; or &quot;BOLD&quot; preferred flavor/strength&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control panel and display, with hour and minute buttons to program the brewing time up to 24 hours beforehand&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Equipped with programmable timer with 2-hour automatic shutoff&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic pause &amp;amp; serve feature for pouring a cup from carafe while still brewing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Nonstick, keep-hot warming plate on &quot;carafe side&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;12-cup coffeemaker measures: 15.00&quot;L x 10.00&quot;W x 12.50&quot;H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model# 49980&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Battery Type: Does Not Contain a Battery &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Multi Pack Indicator: No &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Model No.: 49980 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Shipping Weight (in pounds): 7.0 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Product in Inches (L x W x H): 15.0&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;10.0&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;12.5 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Ankermart No.: 001450650&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Hamilton Beach 2-Way Brewer Coffeemaker, Black/Stainless Steel', 'Hamilton Beach 2-Way Brewer Coffeemaker, Black/Stainless Steel', 'Hamilton Beach 2-Way Brewer Coffeemaker, Black/Stainless Steel'),
(119, 1, 'Weber 22.5&quot; Performer Gold Charcoal Grill, Multiple Colors', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;The Weber 22.5&quot; Performer Charcoal Grill has everything you need to make grilling over charcoal a pleasure. This Weber Gold Charcoal Grill is available in Multiple Colors, and it features a plated steel hinged cooking grate, a porcelain-enameled bowl and lid and a removable LCD cooking timer. In addition, the Weber Charcoal Grill offers you a 363-sq in cooking area with a 22-burger capacity. It also features an aluminized steel One-Touch cleaning system and a removable high-capacity aluminum ash catcher. Built for durability, the grill also features a rust-resistant aluminum damper, a glass-reinforced nylon handle, a weather-protected CharBin storage container and durable all-weather wheels with locking casters and full-wheel hubcaps.&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Weber 22.5&quot; Performer Gold Charcoal Grill, Multiple Colors:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;363-sq in cooking area&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;22-burger capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Plated steel, hinged cooking grate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Porcelain-enameled bowl and lid&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable LCD cooking timer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Aluminized steel One-Touch cleaning system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable, high-capacity aluminum ash catcher&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rust-resistant aluminum damper&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tuck-Away lid holder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 glass-reinforced nylon handle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 Char-Basket charcoal fuel holders&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Thermoset work table&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weather-protected CharBin storage container&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wire bottom shelf&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 durable all-weather wheels with full-wheel hubcaps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&