(120, 1, 'Ninja Ultima High-Speed Blender with Dual-Stage Technology', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;The Ultima High-Speed Blender is the next generation Ninja blender. It features a dual-blade assembly system that provides top puree and blending performance. This fruit blender contains eight blades for total crushing technology. It crushes fruit with the top blade, then purees with the bottom blades. It includes 1500/2HP ultimate technology, variable speeds for juicing and blending needs and a newly designed 72-oz pitcher with an ergonomic shape and handle. In addition, the 2HP blender with dual-stage technology comes with two 16-oz single-serve cups with Sip &amp;amp; Seal lids. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;Ultima High-Speed Blender with Dual-Stage Technology:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1500/2HP ultimate powerhouse&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual-stage technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Crush fruits with top blades and puree with bottom blades&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Total of 8 blades&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Total crushing technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Crush ice into snow, fruits and veggies into purees and nuts into butter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Newly designed 72-oz pitcher with ergonomic shape and handle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Variable speeds for all juicing and blending needs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two 16-oz single-serve cups with Sip &amp;amp; Seal lids&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2HP blender with dual-stage technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Battery Type: Does Not Contain a Battery &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Primary Color: Black &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Multi Pack Indicator: No &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Model No.: BL810 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Shipping Weight (in pounds): 15.43 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Product in Inches (L x W x H): 16.5&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;11.0&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;15.0 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Ankermart No.: 551763945&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Ninja Ultima High-Speed Blender with Dual-Stage Technology', 'Ninja Ultima High-Speed Blender with Dual-Stage Technology', 'Ninja Ultima High-Speed Blender with Dual-Stage Technology'),
(121, 1, 'Nutri Ninja Pro Blender, Silver/Black', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;Unlock all the natural benefits of fruits and veggies with the Nutri Ninja Pro Blender. It makes a wonderful addition to your kitchen. The high-performance blender breaks down fruits and vegetables for nutritious rich juices that you can enjoy on the go. The silver/black blender uses Ninja Pro extractor blades that are strong enough to crush through ice, seeds, skins and stems for a smooth, even consistency. Twist on the Sip and Seal Lids, and you can even take your drinks with you while you travel. All parts of the fruit and vegetable blender are BPA-free for added safety. It can even be cleaned in the dishwasher for simple maintenance. Accompanied by jars, a cord wrap and a 30-recipe inspiration guide, this blender is a great choice for eating healthy, no matter how busy you are.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;NutriNinja Pro Blender, Silver/Black:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Single serve blending&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;900W professional power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The fruit and vegetable blender provides powerful nutrient and vitamin extraction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sip and Seal Lids for healthy, personalized drinks on the go&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Frozen blending: crush through ice and frozen fruit in seconds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ninja Pro Extractor Blades crush through ice, seeds, skins and stems for a smooth, even consistency&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;18 oz jar and 24 oz jar&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher safe&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BPA-free&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cord wrap&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;30-recipe inspiration guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1-year warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model# BL450&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Battery Type: Does Not Contain a Battery &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;