(127, 1, 'Mainstays Contempo Futon Sofa Bed, Multiple Colors', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;TheMainstays Contempo Futon Sofa Bed Multiple Colors is ideal for anyone who values comfort. This item conveniently acts as both a sofa and as a bed, so you can use it as a regular piece of furniture, and when a guest comes over to visit, you can use it as a bed. This versatile piece of furniture is popular among people who might have limited space in their homes or apartments. This space-saving futon couch converts into a twin sleeper sofa quickly and easily. It utilizes Click-Clack technology that makes opening and closing it a hassle free experience. The conversion can be done by one person with no help. This Mainstays sofa bed has a micro-suede cover that is available in different colors, so you can choose the one that is right for your room. This microfiber sofa bed has a multi-position back that can be adjusted to your exact comfort preferences, which you can change easily and often. The sofa is suitable for sleeping, sitting and lounging. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;Mainstays Contempo Futon Sofa Bed, Multiple Colors:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microfiber futon sofa bed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Micro-suede cover&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Click-Clack technology makes this futon sleeper easy to open and close&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Contempo futon sleeper is ideal for sleeping, sitting and lounging&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folds into a twin sleeper sofa: 72&quot;L x 40&quot;W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi-position back and wings for optimal comfort&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Contempo futon sofa bed model #3155096W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Primary Color: Black Multi Pack Indicator: Yes&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Shipping