(10022, 1, 'Eureka Boss SmartVac Sealed HEPA Bagged Upright Vacuum, 4870MZ', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;Offering powerful performance for everyday household cleaning, the Eureka 4870MZ Boss Smart Vac Upright HEPA Vacuum is the solution for people who insist on having a truly clean home. The adjustable vacuum with Turbo Upholstery Tool provides superior suction. It also features an air-selector switch that lets you direct all suction either for deep cleaning. They can handle any cleaning challenge from frequent pet hair cleanups to reaching out of the way spots in your home. The Sealed HEPA vacuum cleaner has a 15&quot; cleaning path with brush-view window and furniture guard. Its HEPA filtration system eliminates 99.97 percent of dust, pollen, allergens, and bacteria, making your completely clean and tidy. A handy stretch hose extends to five times its original length, so you can easily clean around furniture. It also help you to remove cobwebs from ceiling.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Eureka 4870MZ Boss Smart Vac Upright HEPA Vacuum:&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 2 Year Limited&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ultra-quiet 12-amp motor provides superior suction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;15&quot; cleaning path with brush-view window and furniture guard&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;True HEPA filtration eliminates 100% of allergens in the air&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Motorized brush roll with on/off switch for cleaning bare floors and carpets&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes Power Paw Upholstery tool for removing pet hair and deep down dirt from upholstery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;7 height adjustments to clean everything from heavy carpet to bare floors&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Air-selector switch for focused suction and deep cleaning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5:1 ratio stretch hose and extension wand for maximum cleaning reach&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Anti-clog design and extended-life belt provide maintenance-free performance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;On-board tools&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;30-foot power cord&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Soft, rubberized wheels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Primary Color: Red &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Multi Pack Indicator: No &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Shipping Weight (in pounds): 26.0 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Product in Inches (L x W x H): 16.0&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;15.25&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;43.0 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Ankermart No.: 001586721&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Eureka Boss SmartVac Sealed HEPA Bagged Upright Vacuum, 4870MZ', ' Eureka 4870MZ Boss Smart Vac Upright HEPA Vacuum, Sealed HEPA Vacuum Cleaner, Adjustable Vacuum', ' Eureka 4870MZ Boss Smart Vac Upright HEPA Vacuum, Sealed HEPA Vacuum Cleaner, Adjustable Vacuum'),
(10023, 1, 'Eureka SuctionSeal Pet Bagless Upright Vacuum, AS1104A', '&lt;p&gt;The Eureka SuctionSeal bagless upright has concentrated suction for maximum cleaning on carpets and barefloors. Wide tubes that increase the amount of airflow for superior suction &amp;amp; cleaning. This unit picks up pet hair and liter from carpets and bare floors. This model maintains suction power as you vacuum your home.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deep Cleaning Power on All Floors.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nProven to Clean Carpets Better Than Dyson DC25 and DC41 For Less Than ½ The Price,* &amp;nbsp;the SuctionSeal PET bagless upright combines Eureka exclusive AirSpeed Technology with SuctionSeal Technology for deep cleaning power on all floor surfaces.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SuctionSeal Technology&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSuctionSeal Technology with All-Surface Suction Plates concentrates airflow for deep cleaning suction power. &amp;nbsp;As you move across carpet, hardwood or tile floors the plates raise and lower, creating a seal to maximize airflow for powerful cleaning performance. &amp;nbsp;Whether it’s surface dirt or debris hiding in crevices, it’s sucked up and away without any scattering.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AirSpeed Technology&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nUnlike other vacuums, AirSpeed Technology has two smooth tubes, featuring limited bends and turns. &amp;nbsp;This allows more air to pass through the vacuum. &amp;nbsp;The direct air path from floor to cup, decreases the distance for dirt to travel, which increases the amount of airflow for powerful suction.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Never Loses Suction&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEureka has engineered SuctionSeal to provide maximum suction power longer than other types of vacuums.** &amp;nbsp;Tested to strict industry standards, Eureka’s multicyclonic dust cup system never loses suction and maintains power as you vacuum your home.***&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tough Enough for Pet Owners&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDesigned to deep clean pet hair from carpets, bare floors, upholstery and more. &amp;nbsp;The SuctionSeal Pet features a Pet Upholstery Brush, a turbo driven PET Power Paw, and a 39 foot hose and wand to clean above the floors. &amp;nbsp;The on/off brushroll switch lets you clean carpets and bare floors. &amp;nbsp;This model includes an odor absorbing HEPA filter to eliminate pet odors and reduce allergens for a cleaner home.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;*Based on a comparison between (a) regular MSRP of Eureka SuctionSeal PET and Dyson DC25 and DC41 vacuums as of November 2011 (b) independent lab tests using industry standard ASTM F608 test, measuring embedded dirt removal from carpeting.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n**When compared to conventional bagged and single stage cyclonic vacuums having dirt cup filters.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n***Per IEC 60312-1 Edition 1.0 (2010). &amp;nbsp;Test results within accepted variability tolerance of 5%.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;content&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;productDescriptionWrapper&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;aplus&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;half-col&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power: 12 amps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cord Length: 27 ft.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cleaning Path Width: 14 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 20.7 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shipping Weight: 25.6 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cleaner Dimensions: 14.2&quot;W x 15.3&quot;L x 43.8&quot;H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tools/Accessories: PET Power Paw, Wand, Crevice Tool, Pet Upholsery Brush&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional Product Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n• All Surface Cleaning: Designed to deep clean carpets, bare floors, upholstery and more.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n• Automatic Cord Rewind: Rewinds cord effortlessly for quick and easy storage.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n• PET Power Paw Turbo Brush: Removes pet hair from carpet and upholstery. Plastic teeth loosen it, a rubber strip grabs it and bristles remove it.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n• Flip-Bottom Dust Cup: Allows you to empty the dust cup quickly and easily without touching the captured dust. Emptying the dust cup regularly, as needed, will help to maintain optimum cleaning performance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n• Washable Dust Cup Filter: Save money and lessen waste by washing and reusing the allergy-reducing filter.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n• Low Profile Cleaning Nozzle: Reaches under furniture and close to baseboards.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n• Foot Controlled, 7-Setting Height Adjustment: Easily adjust to clean most floor surfaces.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n• EZ Roll Soft Wheels: Wheels won’t scratch or nick hard floors.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Eureka SuctionSeal Pet Bagless Upright Vacuum, AS1104A', 'Eureka SuctionSeal Pet Bagless Upright Vacuum, AS1104A', 'Eureka SuctionSeal Pet Bagless Upright Vacuum, AS1104A'),
(10024, 1, 'Husqvarna 223L 25cc 2-Cycle 18-in Straight Shaft Gas String Trimmer', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Husqvarna 223L 25cc 2-Cycle 18-in Straight Shaft Gas String Trimmer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Versatile trimmer with straight shaft&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto return stop switch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy starting&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Long reach and loop handle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Series Name: N/A&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Best Use: Up to 2 acres&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engine Displacement (Cu. Centimeters): 25.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engine Type: 2-cycle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel Type: Gas/oil mix&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2-Cycle Fuel Mix Ratio: 50:1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Type: Straight&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cutting Swath (Inches): 18.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Recommended Line Diameter (Inches): 0.095&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Line Feed: Bump&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Single or Dual Line Feed: Dual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electric Start Capable&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Spring-Assist Starting: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Edger Capable: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Attachment Compatible: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight (lbs.): 9.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 2-year limited&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Package Contents: Unit, manual, oil, guard&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UL Safety Listing: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CSA Safety Listing: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ETL Safety Listing: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;pdf&quot; href=&quot;http://pdf.lowes.com/warrantyguides/705788502998_warranty.pdf&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 73, 144); font-weight: 700; outline: 0px; text-decoration: none;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Product Information: Warranty Guide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\