(138, 1, '25&quot; GMC Denali 700c Men\'s Road Bike, Black', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;The GMC Denali 700c Men\'s Road Bike is built around a lightweight aluminum road bicycle frame. As its name suggests, it is meant for typical road usage, such as plain commuting or racing. It features a slim wheel and a smooth tire that reduces the friction between the road and the tire. This GMC Denali 21-Speed Road Bike is equipped with alloy calipers and brake levers to make stopping smooth and precise. The rims of the X-Large GMC Denali 700c Road Bike are made of high-profile alloy Vitesse and perform as good as they look. A better aerodynamic position is possible with the lower hand position. Shimano Revo shifters allow you to shift without taking your hands off the handle bars, providing safety and confidence. A Shimano derailleur completes the road cycle drive train for quick and smooth gear changes. This GMC Denali 21-Speed Road Bike is a good entry level bike and is well worth the price.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;25&quot; GMC Denali 700c Men\'s Road Bike, Black:&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fits riders 6\'2&quot;-6\'5&quot; with a stand over of 32&quot;-34&quot;.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Riding style: road bike.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Frame: Aluminum 7005 50cm.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Handlebar: Steel custom 2-piece.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Gearing: 21-speed.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;X-Large GMC Denali 700c Road Bike shifters: Shimano Revo SIS.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Front Derailleur: Shimano FD-TZ 31 Index.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rear Derailleur: Shimano RD-TZ30GS 7SPD.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bike Saddle: Cionlli Black.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Seat post: HL Aluminum Micro Adjust 27.2 X 300 mm.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brakes: Promax 501A Alloy Caliper Brake.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brake levers: Promax BL-250AP Aluminum.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bicycle Tires: 700 x 32c tires for smooth ride and low-rolling resistance.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rims: Vitesse Alloy black 700CX14GX36H.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pedals: VP-990S plastic body with steel cage.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fork: GMC Series 7000 steel.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Chain: KMC Z 51.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Crankset: Alloy 335P6 28x38x48 170mm.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stem: Aluminum quill.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;GMC Denali 21-Speed Road Bike dimensions: 68&quot; x 18&quot; x 41&quot;H.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly required.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Warranty: lifetime warranty on frame, 1-year on parts.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Speeds: 21-Speed &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Bike Type: Road Bikes &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Age End: and up Age Start: 15 Years &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Battery Type: Does Not Contain a Battery &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Primary Color: Black Multi &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Pack Indicator: No &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Model No.: 52708 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Shipping Weight (in pounds): 38.0 Product in Inches (L x W x H): 68.0&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;18.0&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;41.0 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Ankermart&amp;nbsp;No.: 000798300&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Purchase the GMC Denali 700c Men\'s Road Bike at an always low price from ankermart.com. Save money. Live better.', 'GMC Denali 700c Men\'s Road Bike, GMC Denali 21-Speed Road Bike, GMC Denali 700c Road Bike, X-Large', 'GMC Denali 700c Men&amp;#039;s Road Bike, GMC Denali 21-Speed Road Bike, GMC Denali 700c Road Bike, X-Large'),
(10002, 1, 'Graco Blossom 4-in-1 Seating System High Chair, Vance', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;The Graco Blosson 4-In-1 Seating System High Chair has been designed to adjust to your child\'s seating needs. Ideal for children up to eight pounds, this Graco high chair transforms seamlessly from an extremely functional highchair to an infant feeding booster, a toddler booster, and finally a youth chair. It even features front wheels and locking rear casters that help in portability. The frame of this adjustable height high chair is sturdy and has a wipe clean finish. The 6-position height adjustment assures a front row seat for baby at any family table. Cleaning the removable tray after the meal is done is a breeze, given the fact that the pull-out tray is dishwasher-safe. Even the seat pad is removable and machine washable. The three-position removable footrest and three-position one-hand reclining seat will ensure your growing child stays comfortable at mealtime. The Graco high chair with wheels has a convertible three and five point harnesses that keeps your baby secured. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Graco Blosson 4-In-1 Seating System High Chair: &lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stage 1: Highchair&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stage 2: Infant Feeding Booster&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stage 3: Toddler Booster&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stage 4: Youth Chair&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;For a child up to 3 years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6 height positions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable tray with dishwasher-safe pull-out insert for quick, hassle-free cleanup&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable seat pad can be machine washed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Convertible 3- and 5-point harness keeps baby secured&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3 recline levels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-position adjustable footrest helps keep your child comfy as they grow&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Front wheels and locking rear casters help keep chair in place and offer greater portability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Weight Capacity: 50 lbs for Stage 1, 2 and 3; 80 lbs for Stage 4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wipeable frame with sturdy tubing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly required&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Age: 2 Years,Birth - 12 Months,12 - 24 Months,3 - 4 Years&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Age End: and up Age Start: 3 Years &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Collection: Graco Vance,Vance &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Battery Type: Does Not Contain a Battery &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Primary Color: Beige &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Multi Pack Indicator: No &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Model No.: &lt;/span&gt;1812897&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Shipping Weight (in pounds): 37.0 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Product in Inches (L x W x H): 22.5&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;29.0&amp;nbsp;x&amp;nbsp;41.0 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Ankermart&amp;nbsp;No.: 551126225&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Graco Blossom 4-In-1 Seating System High Chair - ankermart.com', 'Get the Graco Blossom 4-In-1 Seating System High Chair at an every day low price from ankermart.com', 'Graco Blossom 4-In-1 Seating System High Chair'),
(10001, 1, 'Graco Alano Classic Connect Travel System, Roman', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Stroller Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes the top rated Graco SnugRide&amp;nbsp;Classic Connect&amp;nbsp;Infant Car Seat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller holds child up to 50 lbs. for years of comfortable strolling&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One-hand, self-standing fold closes easily, no bending necessary&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Padded seat with multi-position recline keeps baby comfy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lockable front swivel wheels with suspension for superior maneuverability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra-large, drop-down storage basket lets you reach in without disturbing your reclined child&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Parent’s tray with storage and 2 cup deep holders for on-the-go convenience&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Child’s tray with cup holder pivots for no-fuss stroller entry&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Convertible 3 or 5-point harness grows with your child&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SnugRide&amp;nbsp;Classic Connect&amp;nbsp;Infant Car Seat Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Top rated by leading consumer magazines and publications&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rigorously crash test to meet or exceed U.S. safety standards&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EPS, energy absorbing foam liner&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5-point harness helps keep baby secure&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable infant head support cradles child’s head and neck&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nStylish and feature-friendly, our Alano Classic Connect Travel System is perfect for all of your adventures with baby. This system includes the innovative Alano Classic Connect Stroller, the top rated SnugRide Classic Connect Infant Car Seat and a stay-in-car base. This fashionable stroller is made with durable elliptical tubing to stand up to rough handling, and comes fully-loaded with convenience features like a one-hand, self-standing fold, a parent’s tray with two deep cup holders, and an easy access drop-down storage basket. And the lockable front swivel wheels with suspension make sure the ride is smooth for everyone. For your added convenience, it’s also compatible with the top rated Graco Classic Connect Infant Car Seats.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller weight: 19.6 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 30&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 23.5&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 41&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded Length: 41&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded Width: 23.5&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded Height: 17&quot;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight without base: 7.5 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight with base: 12.7 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions:&amp;nbsp;Depth: 26.7&quot;, Width: 17.5&quot;, Height: 24.2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Care and Maintenance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWash removable seat cushion in cold water on delicate cycle and line dry&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTo clean stroller frame, use only household soap and warm water&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNever use bleach&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIf wheels squeak, use a light oil&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Recommended Use&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nStroller: For child up to 50 lbs&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCar Seat: Rear-facing for infants 5 to 22 lbs &amp;amp; up to 29&quot;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instructions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul class=&quot;productInstructions&quot; style=&quot;padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10.909090995788574px; line-height: 18px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; height: 16px; list-style-type: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;pdf&quot; href=&quot;http://download.gracobaby.com/ProductInstructionManuals/PD224074A_PD261467A.pdf&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px 0px 0px 26px; margin: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(70, 173, 230); text-decoration: none; display: block; height: 16px; line-height: 16px; background: url(http://www.gracobaby.com/assets/images/icon-pdf.png) 0px 0px no-repeat;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Download product instructions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Graco Alano Classic Connect Travel System, Roman', 'Graco Alano Classic Connect Travel System, Roman', 'Graco Alano Classic Connect Travel System, Roman'),
(10003, 1, 'Graco Nautilus 3-in-1 Multi-Use Car Seat, Gavit', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-in-1 car seat helps protect your toddler, from 20-100 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Top rated by leading consumer magazines and publications&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rigorously crash tested to meet or exceed U.S. safety standards&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Side-impact tested* (*In addition to meeting or exceeding all applicable US safety standards, the Nautilus car seat has been side impact tested for occupant retention solely with the built-in 5 point harness system.)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EPS, energy absorbing foam for effective impact energy management&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steel-reinforced frame provides strength and durability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-position recline helps keep your growing child comfy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One-hand, adjustable headrest easily adapts to your growing toddler\'s needs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Online videos help ensure proper installation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Open-loop belt guides help you correctly position your vehicle’s seat belt&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Contoured armrests with cup holder and storage pockets&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFinally, the car seat that parents have been searching for is here! Our Nautilus 3-in-1 car seat helps keep your child secure from 20 to 100 lbs. Nautilus is a 3-in-1 car seat that converts from a harnessed booster to a high back belt-positioning booster and finally to a backless belt positioning booster. The harness booster can be used up to 65lbs, and as your little one continues to grow, the Nautilus does too, transitioning into a Highback belt positioning booster which can be used from 30 – 100lbs, and finally into a Backless belt positioning booster for a comfortable fit from 40 to 100 lbs. The seat is designed to help keep your child in a harness booster longer as well as to fit them up to 57&quot; tall. You can easily see Graco\'s commitment to safety as this seat is extensively crash tested to meet or exceed U.S safety standards, side-impact testing, and outfitted with reinforced steel for effective energy management. Nautilus has been thoughtfully designed with plush comfort features, an integrated cup holder and storage compartments, as well as a one-hand height adjustable headrest to help keep your growing child happy on even the longest rides! This 3-in-1 car seat is will last your little travel companion well into childhood.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 26 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 29H x 20W x 22D&quot; (head rest in lowest position)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Care and Maintenance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMachine-washable seat cushion.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To Unbuckle Harness:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nLift the lever and pull the shoulder harness straps to loosen the harness&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTilt the top of the buckle toward the child’s abdomen&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPress in at the top of the red button&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPull tongues out of the buckle&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Harness Buckle Cleaning Process:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTurn the restraint over and push the retainer through the harness strap slot to remove the buckle from the car seat. Place the buckle in a cup of warm water upside down and gently agitate the buckle, pressing the red button several times while it is in the water. Do not submerge the harness webbing and do not use soaps or lubricants, only rinse the harness buckle with warm water. Shake out the excess water and allow the harness buckle to air dry. Reattach the harness buckle into the same slot and re-check harness for correct installation according to the car seat manual before use.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Recommended Use&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith Built-In Harness:&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWeight: 20 to 65 lbs&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHeight: 27 to 52 inches&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Without Built-In Harness:&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWeight: 30 to 100 lbs&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHeight: 38 to 57 inches&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Without Built-In Harness and Back Support:&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWeight: 40 to 100 lbs&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHeight: 40 to 57 inches&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAs recommended by the American Academy of Pediatrics, children 4 feet 9 inches tall or under should ride in a belt-positioning booster seat.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instructions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul class=&quot;productInstructions&quot; style=&quot;padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10.909090995788574px; line-height: 18px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; height: 16px; list-style-type: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;pdf&quot; href=&quot;http://download.gracobaby.com/ProductInstructionManuals/PD265359C_PD265362C.pdf&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px 0px 0px 26px; margin: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(70, 173, 230); text-decoration: none; display: block; height: 16px; line-height: 16px; background: url(http://www.gracobaby.com/assets/images/icon-pdf.png) 0px 0px no-repeat;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Download product instructions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Graco Nautilus 3-in-1 Multi-Use Car Seat, Gavit', 'Graco Nautilus 3-in-1 Multi-Use Car Seat, Gavit', 'Graco Nautilus 3-in-1 Multi-Use Car Seat, Gavit'),
(10004, 1, 'Graco Nautilus 3-in-1 Multi-Use Car Seat, Matrix', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-in-1 car seat helps protect your toddler, from 20-100 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Top rated by leading consumer magazines and publications&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rigorously crash tested to meet or exceed U.S. safety standards&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Side-impact tested* (*In addition to meeting or exceeding all applicable US safety standards, the Nautilus car seat has been side impact tested for occupant retention solely with the built-in 5 point harness system.)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EPS, energy absorbing foam for effective impact energy management&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steel-reinforced frame provides strength and durability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-position recline helps keep your growing child comfy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One-hand, adjustable headrest easily adapts to your growing toddler\'s needs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Online videos help ensure proper installation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Open-loop belt guides help you correctly position your vehicle’s seat belt&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Contoured armrests with cup holder and storage pockets&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFinally, the car seat that parents have been searching for is here! Our Nautilus 3-in-1 car seat helps keep your child secure from 20 to 100 lbs. Nautilus is a 3-in-1 car seat that converts from a harnessed booster to a high back belt-positioning booster and finally to a backless belt positioning booster. The harness booster can be used up to 65lbs, and as your little one continues to grow, the Nautilus does too, transitioning into a Highback belt positioning booster which can be used from 30 – 100lbs, and finally into a Backless belt positioning booster for a comfortable fit from 40 to 100 lbs. The seat is designed to help keep your child in a harness booster longer as well as to fit them up to 57&quot; tall. You can easily see Graco\'s commitment to safety as this seat is extensively crash tested to meet or exceed U.S safety standards, side-impact testing, and outfitted with reinforced steel for effective energy management. Nautilus has been thoughtfully designed with plush comfort features, an integrated cup holder and storage compartments, as well as a one-hand height adjustable headrest to help keep your growing child happy on even the longest rides! This 3-in-1 car seat is will last your little travel companion well into childhood.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 26 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 29H x 20W x 22D&quot; (head rest in lowest position)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Care and Maintenance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMachine-washable seat cushion.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To Unbuckle Harness:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nLift the lever and pull the shoulder harness straps to loosen the harness&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTilt the top of the buckle toward the child’s abdomen&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPress in at the top of the red button&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPull tongues out of the buckle&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Harness Buckle Cleaning Process:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTurn the restraint over and push the retainer through the harness strap slot to remove the buckle from the car seat. Place the buckle in a cup of warm water upside down and gently agitate the buckle, pressing the red button several times while it is in the water. Do not submerge the harness webbing and do not use soaps or lubricants, only rinse the harness buckle with warm water. Shake out the excess water and allow the harness buckle to air dry. Reattach the harness buckle into the same slot and re-check harness for correct installation according to the car seat manual before use.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\