(10008, 1, 'Graco Ready2Grow LX Stand and Ride Double Stroller, Metropolis', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;Your kids will love getting out and about in the Graco Ready2Grow LX Stand and Ride Double Stroller. This versatile stroller gives you 12 riding options for two kids. It has a standing platform and a padded bench seat for your older child and a removable Face Time rear seat for some bonding time with your baby.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Graco - Ready2Grow LX Stand and Ride Double Stroller, Metropolis:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Front seat, bench seat and standing platform designed to hold a child up to 50 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rear seat designed to hold a child up to 40 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;12 riding options for 2 children&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi-position reclining front seat in the Graco Double Stroller lies flat for baby\'s comfort&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable rear seat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Front and back seats feature convertible 3-point or 5-point harness&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rear bench seat features 3-point harness&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable canopy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra-large storage basket in the Graco - Ready2Grow LX Stand and Ride Stroller&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Toddler bench seat lifts for easy basket access&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable child\'s tray with cup holders&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Parent\'s tray with pivoting cup holder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Ride Stroller accepts 2 Graco SnugRide infant car seats&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Plastic tires&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lockable front swivel wheels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Graco Double Stroller features 1-hand folding with storage latch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Metal frame&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Ride Stroller assembles in approximately 15 minutes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model#