nts for all rear facing only CRs. Graco now allows the use of the handle in any locked position on Graco Infant SafeSeat, SnugRide Classic Connect 22, SnugRide Classic Connect 30, SnugRide Classic Connect 32, SnugRide Classic Connect 35 and the new SnugRide Click Connect 35 and SnugRide Click Connect 40. This change does not apply in Canada, where the handle must always be used locked in the upright position.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instructions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul class=&quot;productInstructions&quot; style=&quot;padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10.909090995788574px; line-height: 18px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; height: 16px; list-style-type: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;pdf&quot; href=&quot;http://download.gracobaby.com/ProductInstructionManuals/PD261464A.pdf&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px 0px 0px 26px; margin: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(70, 173, 230); text-decoration: none; display: block; height: 16px; line-height: 16px; background: url(http://www.gracobaby.com/assets/images/icon-pdf.png) 0px 0px no-repeat;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Download product instructions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Graco SnugRide Classic Connect 35 Infant Car Seat, Vance', 'Graco SnugRide Classic Connect 35 Infant Car Seat, Vance', 'Graco SnugRide Classic Connect 35 Infant Car Seat, Vance'),
