 150BT 50.2cc 2-Cycle X-Torq Gas Powered Back Pack Blower', 'Husqvarna 150BT 50.2cc 2-Cycle X-Torq Gas Powered Back Pack Blower'),
(10017, 1, 'Le Creuset Signature Enameled Cast Iron 5.5 Qt. Round French Oven', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;Gather your family around the table to share a meal carefully prepared in the 5 1/2 qt. round French oven, Le Creuset’s signature piece that’s been well-loved for generations. The generous size is indispensable in any working kitchen, easily accommodating classic recipes like chicken soup or beouf bourguignon.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Also known as a Dutch oven, this updated kitchen classic enhances the cooking process by evenly distributing heat and locking in the optimal amount of moisture. With ergonomic handles and an advanced interior enamel that resists chipping and cleans easily, Le Creuset’s French ovens blend the best of the past with the latest innovations in comfort and functionality.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Colorful, long-lasting exterior enamel resists chipping and cracking; interior enamel is engineered to resist staining and dulling&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sand-colored interior enamel makes it easy to monitor food as it cooks, preventing burning and sticking&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oversized handles provide even weight distribution and a secure grip&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ergonomic composite knobs are heat resistant to 500°F&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in lid stabilizers provide a secure, no-slide fit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The lightest weight per quart of any premium cast iron cookware available&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;Specifications&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity: 5 1/2 qt.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Diameter: 10 3/4 Inch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 6 3/4 Inch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Piece Count: 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Cast Iron&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heat Source: Gas, Electric, Ceramic, Halogen, Induction, Oven &amp;amp; Outdoor Grill&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cleaning: Dishwasher-Safe&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Warranty: Limited Lifetime Warranty&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Country of Origin: France&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;content&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Le Creuset Signature Enameled Cast-Iron 5.5 Quart Round French Oven, Cherry', 'Le Creuset Signature Enameled Cast-Iron 5.5 Quart Round French Oven, Cherry', 'Le Creuset Signature Enameled Cast-Iron 5.5 Quart Round French Oven, Cherry'),
(10018, 1, 'Quirky GE Aros Smart Window Air Conditioner', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The World’s Smartest Air Conditioner&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ditch your dumb window A/C for Aros, because Aros is smart. It learns from your budget, location, schedule, and usage to automatically maintain the perfect temperature and maximize savings for your home. What\'s more, it can be controlled from anywhere using the Wink app on your mobile device.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cools 350 sq. ft. (~17\'x20\')&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fits double-hung windows 24.5&quot; to 40.5&quot; W x 13.5&quot; H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Three cooling modes + three fan speeds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;8000 BTU, 115 volt, 6.3 amps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;Smartphone savvy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOn the go? Don\'t want to get up off the couch? Aros has you covered either way. It connects via Wi-Fi and can be monitored, programmed, and controlled from anywhere with the easy-to-use Wink app.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Budget conscious&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAros keeps a constant eye on how much you’ve spent on cooling each month and offers suggested settings based on your budget and the upcoming weather report, so you can save on energy costs.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Intuitive scheduling&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAros learns from your patterns to cool when you need it, not when you don’t. It predicts the temperatures you like when you wake up, lounge on weekends, leave for work, or return home.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Anticipates your movements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAros responds to your smartphone\'s GPS settings (in a non-creepy way) to turn off when you leave and perfect the temperature by the time you get back. You’ll never come home to nasty, stuffy summer heat again.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. Game-changing design&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIts innovative design features upward airflow, which increases circulation. It also redirects noise so you can switch between its three cooling modes and three fan speeds discreetly.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6. Best looking A/C on the block&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAll this brain power is paired with unprecedented beauty. Aros features flat, touch-capacitive sensors, a sleek LED display, and retractable fabric wings that ensure the right fit in your window.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7. Bringing Aros to life&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIn this video, get a beautiful, behind-the-scenes look at the meticulous care that went into the making of Aros, and witness our very first smart air conditioning unit roll off the assembly line.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;8.&amp;nbsp;Garthen, meet Aros&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWe rolled out the red carpet when Aros inventor Garthen Leslie paid a visit to Quirky HQ. Watch his reaction to seeing Aros for the first time, and learn about what inspired him to invent the world’s smartest A/C.&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;​&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Quirky + GE Aros Smart Window Air Conditioner', 'Quirky + GE Aros Smart Window Air Conditioner', 'Quirky + GE Aros Smart Window Air Conditioner'),
(10019, 1, 'Weber 22.5 Inch One-Touch Gold Charcoal Grill, Black Color', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt;Get fired up with the Weber &lt;/span&gt;22.5 Inch&lt;span class=&quot;ql-details-short-desc&quot;&gt; One-Touch Gold Charcoal Grill. The intuitive features on this proven performer make charcoal grilling easier than you ever imagined. Weber\'s aluminized steel One-Touch cleaning system makes quick work of removing ashes from the bowl. Other convenient features include a plated steel, hinged cooking grate and a built-in lid thermometer. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;b&gt;Weber 22.5 Inch One-Touch Gold Charcoal Grill:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;363-sq in cooking area&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;22-burger capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Plated steel, hinged cooking grate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Porcelain-enameled bowl and lid&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Aluminized steel One-Touch cleaning system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable, high-capacity aluminum ash catcher&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rust-resistant aluminum damper&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 glass-reinforced nylon handles with tool hooks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Durable all-weather wheels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Angled lid hook inside grill lid&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in thermometer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Owners guide included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Battery Type: Does Not Contain a Battery &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Primary Color: Black &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Multi Pack Indicator: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;No Model No.: 1351001 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.