(10020, 1, 'Nest Learning Thermostat, 2nd Generation', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Learning Thermostat with Built-In Wifi -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 12.727272033691406px;&quot;&gt;Model&amp;nbsp;T200577&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Nest Learning Thermostat remembers what temperatures you like, turns itself down when you’re away and can be controlled from your smartphone, tablet or laptop&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto-Schedule creates a personalized schedule for your home by remembering when you adjust the temperature&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto-Away automatically turns Nest thermostat down when there’s nobody home so you don’t waste energy heating or cooling an empty house&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Remote control Nest thermostat over Wi-Fi from your smartphone, tablet or laptop&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy History shows you how much energy you\'ve used and what affects your energy use most&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Nest Leaf helps you save energy by guiding you to energy-efficient temperatures&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Airwave lowers your AC bills and keeps you cool by cutting AC runtime when humidity’s not too high&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatibility expanded so Nest thermostat works with most 24-volt heating and cooling systems, including humidification, dehumidification and dual-fuel, find out if Nest thermostat will work for you at &lt;a href=&quot;https://nest.com/thermostat/installation/#works/?mode=buy&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;https://nest.com/thermostat/installation/#works/?mode=buy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Installation takes most people 30 minutes or less&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Display &amp;amp; Wireless&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 28.0mm / 1.10&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mass: 254 g / 9.0 oz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Diameter: 83mm / 3.27&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wifi: 802.11b/g/n @ 2.4GHz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Nest Weave: 802.15.4 @ 2.4GHz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Package Contents:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Nest Learning Thermostat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Installation Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Welcome Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Screwdriver And Screws&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Trim Kit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible with Oil Fuel Types: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible with Gas Fuel Types: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible with Electric Fuel Types: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Supports Single-Stage Heating: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Supports Single-Stage Cooling: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Supports Multi-Stage Heating: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Supports Multi-Stage Cooling: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control Type: Dial&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery Type: Lithium ion (Li-ion)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto-Away Mode: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Proximity Sensor: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Outdoor Weather Sensor: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy History Indicator: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Iris Technology: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes Mounting Hardware: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes Remote Control: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ENERGY STAR Qualified: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UL Safety Listing: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish Family: Steel-Stainless&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 2-year limited&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible with 24V Heating: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible with 24V Cooling: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Program Type: Learning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Program Periods per Day: 24.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto System Change from Heat to Cool: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Temperature Displayed: Current and setpoint/desired temperature&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li