(10030, 1, 'GPI EZ-8 12 Volt 8 GPM Fuel Transfer Pump 137100-01', '&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;Universal Electric Fuel Transfer Pump (137100-01) by Dee Zee®, 8 Gallons Per Minute. This 12-volt electric motor pumps 8 gallons of liquid or medium weight oil per minute. Features 10 feet of .625” diameter nitrile butadiene rubber hose that is highly resistant to breaking down from oil, fuels and extreme temperatures. Features a built in anti-siphon valve and strainer along with a 3-piece suction pipe. Nozzle will fit standard unleaded fuel openings on motorized vehicles. UL certified to U.S. and Canadian safety standards.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;Pumps 8 gallons per minute&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;12-volt electric fuel pump comes with 15-foot power cord, or can be hardwired to your vehicle for power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;10 feet of .625” diameter nitrile butadiene rubber hose is resistant to breakdown from oil, fuels and extreme temperatures&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;Aluminum construction provides high strength, light weight and resistance to corrosion&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;Designed with smaller nozzle that will fit standard size vehicle unleaded fuel holes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;Features built-in strainer to prevent sediment and large impurities from being pumped out of your fuel transfer tank&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;Anti-siphon valve prevents theft of liquid in your tank&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;Duty cycle allows 15 minutes of use between 30 minute cool down cycles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;Motor features an internal, auxiliary temperature-limiting device, and handle is manual shutoff only&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;3-piece suction pipe allows a range of sizes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;Products have been certified to represent highest levels of safety and quality by Underwriters Laboratories (UL)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;Built by Great Plains Industries (GPI) under partnership with Dee Zee and backed with a 2-year warranty through GPI&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;Proudly manufactured in the United States&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;For those who prefer easy removal of liquid from your liquid transfer tank, Dee Zee has hand selected the best pumps that offer you quality construction, proper fit, easy operation, no-leak sealing, and the security of safety certification. The EZ-8 Electric Fuel Transfer Pump is designed with a 12-volt electric motor that can pump 8 gallons per minute – equivalent to the flow rate of most gasoline service stations. Lightweight, all-aluminum construction provides the versatility of easy handling, and the motor is designed for gasoline with ethanol blends up to 15%, diesel fuel with biodiesel blends up to 20%, and kerosene. A built-in strainer catches any sediments or impurities that may end up in your tank, and an anti-siphon valve prevents theft.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nA 10-foot hose allows the range you need to easily reach equipment parked behind your truck, or off to either side. Nitrile butadiene rubber hose construction is of the highest durability to ensure resistance to breaking down after repeated exposure to caustic oil, fuels, and even extreme cold or hot temperatures. A 3-piece suction pipe can even be trimmed easily to the length you need or the diameter of piping you prefer. Under a partnership with Dee Zee, the 8gpm Electric Fuel Transfer Pump is manufactured by fuel pump specialists Great Plains Industries (GPI) and warrantied by them for a 2-year period. The 8gpm Electric Fuel Transfer Pump has been certified by Underwriters Laboratories (UL) that all components fully comply with government regulations and meet or exceed all safety guidelines in effect at the time of productio&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'GPI EZ-8 12 Volt 8 GPM Fuel Transfer Pump 137100-01', 'GPI EZ-8 12 Volt 8 GPM Fuel Transfer Pump 137100-01', 'GPI EZ-8 12 Volt 8 GPM Fuel Transfer Pump 137100-01'),
(10031, 1, 'Aprilaire 8800 Touchscreen Communicating Thermostat', '&lt;p&gt;Take controlling your heating and air conditioning system to a whole new level with Aprilaire\'s 8800 Communicating Thermostat. This thermostat can be integrated into a home automation system or controlled right from your home\'s PC*. If you have 1 thermostat or multiple thermostats, you can control the temperature of each from any web-enabled device, whether you\'re at home, at work or on vacation. If you\'re building a new home with complete home automation in mind or if you\'re simply upgrading your current home to a smart home, the Aprilaire 8800 Communicating Thermostat promises you total convenience and control 24-7.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Aprilaire 8800 is a simple, yet technologically advanced system that gives you total remote control of your home\'s HVAC system. It also has a Message Center display that opens up new possibilities for enhancing your systems. The Message Center simplifies set up and addressing while it can also display custom messages. It\'s not total home automation without HVAC control and the Model 8800 Communicating Touchscreen Thermostat is the choice of professional integrators and the DIY type alike, making your home control easier and more convenient.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Front battery door access for fast, easy replacement&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Programmable fan control with fan circulation mode&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy to use temperature control can override program schedule at any time&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Progressive recovery ensures proper temperature at the start of a program event&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built in compressor protection prevents damage to your equipment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;RS485 communications ready&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Universal system compatibility&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Configurable to control a humidifier and dehumidifier&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tools Needed&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Small flat head screwdriver for terminal screws (1/8&quot; wide tip)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Medium size flat/Phillips head screwdriver for component mounting screws&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Volt/ohm meter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Computer with available com port (RS-232) and terminal emulator (for system checkout)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wire strippers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Small level (use to mount components level, required for appearance only)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi-conductor thermostat cable (18-20 gauge)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Category 5 communication wire (4 pair twisted cable)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;table border=&quot;2&quot; cellpadding=&quot;2&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid black; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; font-size: 12.7272720336914px; color: black; width: 857.272705078125px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica; line-height: 15.9545440673828px;&quot; width=&quot;600&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;td colspan=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 2px; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid black;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;Specifications&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 2px; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid black;&quot;&gt;Manufacturer&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 2px; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid black;&quot;&gt;Aprilaire&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 2px; vertical-align: top;