(10032, 1, 'Stadler Form O-009A - Otto Fan Bamboo', '&lt;p&gt;This Stadler Form O-009A Otto bamboo fan provides superior airflow in a durable and reliable design.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Comfort&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIf you are in need of additional relief from heat or room stuffiness, this unit is for you. Enhance your comfort efficiently and inexpensively.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Durability&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMetal components and bamboo casing provide extraordinary durability to ensure proper operation for prolonged periods of time.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stability&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThis unit features a wide base to minimize shaking, wobbling, and instability. The leveling legs can be adjusted to ensure secure placement on any tabletop surface.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Top Quality Performer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nQuality construction means that this unit is a reliable choice. Outperforming any other of its kind, this fan provides superior room ventilation and helps control the ambient temperature.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model: O-009A&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UPC: 802322002430&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Type: Bamboo Fan&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Dimensions: L: 13.50&quot; x W: 7.20&quot; x H: 14.60&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight: 9.77 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Color: Bamboo&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Type: Electric Fan&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oscillation: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Watts: 45 watts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Usage: Indoor , Outdoor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Certified for Commercial Use: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy Star Certified: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fan Style: Floor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Construction: Aluminum , Steel , Wood&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Remote Control: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Timer: