(10037, 1, 'Stadler Form O-001 - Otto Fan African Saeple', '&lt;p&gt;The Stadler Form O-001 Otto wooden fan features a functional design with decorative style. &amp;nbsp;This fan allows you to enjoy a cool breeze in any room in your home with its portable design. &amp;nbsp;It also boasts an elegant, modern look that\'s made of steel and natural wood. &amp;nbsp;It\'s the perfect fan to cool your home office, family room or other indoor living spaces during the summer.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bamboo Construction&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEnjoy a unique look with the Stadler Form Otto fan that\'s enhanced by the bamboo finish. &amp;nbsp;Plus, you don\'t have to worry about harming the environment because it is made of eco-friendly materials, like bamboo.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Three Fan Speeds&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Stadler Form O-001 portable fan conveniently comes with three fan speeds for you to choose from. &amp;nbsp;With these different speeds you can choose a soft breeze of a powerful wind to cool your living space. &amp;nbsp;Also, the fan is designed to be very quiet for your convenience.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Solid Construction&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThis electric fan boasts a durable construction. &amp;nbsp;It features a high grade steel frame and components. &amp;nbsp;For your convenience, this fan also comes with a one year manufacturer\'s warranty.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Adjustable&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Stadler Form O-001 wooden fan comes with height-adjustable feet. &amp;nbsp;These feet allow you to raise or lower the fan. &amp;nbsp;This allows you to adjust the fan and enjoy the perfect air circulation.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model: O-001&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UPC: 802322001501&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Type: Otto Wooden Electric Table Fan&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Dimensions: L: 13.50&quot; x W: 7.20&quot; x H: 14.60&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight: 9.77 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Color: Brown&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Application: Perfect for providing a cool breeze in your living room, home office or other indoor living spaces. It features a clean, contemporary design that\'s perfect for any modern home.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Warranty: 1 year limited manufacturer\'s warranty&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Type: Electric Fan&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage: 120 volts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oscillation: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Watts: 45 watts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Frequency: 60 Hz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Noise Level: 48.2 dB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Certifications: ETL&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fan Style: Floor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Construction: Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable Tilt: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable Height: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Speeds: 3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;RPM: 1045&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Remote Control: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control Type: Box at the rear of the fan&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Timer: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-In Air Purification System: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Commercial/Industrial Use: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Stadler Form O-001 - Otto Fan African Saeple', 'Stadler Form O-001 - Otto Fan African Saeple', 'Stadler Form O-001 - Otto Fan African Saeple'),
(10038, 1, 'ISY-994i Insteon Compatible Automation Controller with Dual-Band PLM', '&lt;p&gt;Easy-to-Use Central Controller Configures and Programs INSTEON® Devices&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Kit Comes Complete with ISY-994i Controller and INSTEON Dual-Band PLM (PowerLinc Modem)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extends the capabilities of ISY99i Series&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Remotely Accessible from any Standard Web Browser&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Does Not Require a PC to Operate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Supports 256 Devices/ Scenes and controls up to 300 Programs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Apple and Android apps available&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The ISY994i is one of the most advanced INSTEON controllers on the market and has numerous features to satisfy the most advanced DIY\'er or seasoned home control enthusiast. If you need unbridled control, the ISY994i is your controller.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The ISY994i supports up to 256 devices and scenes, and a maximum of 300 programs. The ISY994i controller is able to configure and program INSTEON devices using INSTEON native protocols and specifications. This allows it to directly write to INSTEON devices internally instead of just in the controller, creating a more robust network. You can set up timer events and custom event triggers, as well as monitor and control all the INSTEON-compatible devices in your home from any web-browser anywhere in the world. Now you can check if the lights in your house were left on and remotely control them from your computer at the office.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;INSTEON Control&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThis kit includes an INSTEON Dual-Band PLM Serial Interface, allowing for direct communication with your existing INSTEON network from the ISY-99i controller. The PLM features built-in dual-band technology that sends and receives INSTEON signals via powerline and radio frequency (RF), so it doubles as an Access Point. This makes it ideal for new INSTEON installs if you have or plan to use an RF-only INSTEON-compatible devices like a remote, thermostat, motion sensor or contact sensor.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nControl other network-enabled devices using an optional Network Module (RS-232 devices can be controlled using an ELK IP232 or Global Cache GC-100 and more)&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCan be field upgraded to IR platform&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Extends the capabilities of the ISY99i Series&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAn expansion slot which could be utilized to install and support other protocols such as a Zigbee&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIncreased code memory to support additional communications drivers&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNative support for Open ADR out of the box&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please Note:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe ISY994i does not require a power supply when used with a PLM which supplies power via the RJ-45 port (for example, PLM model #2412S). ISY994i does provide a port for an optional AC adapter for instances where the PLM does not supply power, or the user prefers to supply power independent of the PLM (for example, PLM model #2413S).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Using any Java-enabled web browser, the ISY-994i gives you the ability to control, monitor, and configure all INSTEON-compatible devices from any web-browser anywhere in the world. Best of all, no software is needed to gain access to your INSTEON network. Simply bring up a browser and type in the URL of your Home Automation Controller.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer: Universal Devices&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No. of Timers Supported: 1000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No. of Triggers Supported: 300&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Input : 110-120VAC, 50-60Hz, 0.15A&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1x - ISY994i INSTEON Compatible Automation Controller&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1x - 2413S INSTEON Dual-Band PLM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2x - 3 Foot Eternet Cable (RJ-45)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1x - Power Supply&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1x - Quick Start Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MobiLinc and MobiLinc Lite&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nUsing Wi-Fi or Cellular communication, MobiLinc supports control and real-time monitoring of up to 256 INSTEON or X10 devices, 256 scenes, and 300 programs on your iPhone or iPod touch anywhere in the world. With MobiLinc Pro and your iPhone or iPod touch, control all of your lights, thermostats, devices, programs and irrigation system while on vacation or away from home. With MobiLinc and the many INSTEON devices available, home automation from the palm of your hand has never been easier.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMobiLinc Pro works with any ISY-99i central controller (requiring the PowerLinc Modem), the SmartLinc - INSTEON Central Controller, or the INSTEON PowerLinc Controller (PLC).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Automatic Find and Sync with ISY on Local Wi-Fi&lt;br /&gt;\r\nReal Time INSTEON Device Status&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCommand Your Devices Anywhere with Wi-Fi, 3G, or EDGE&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSupports up to 256 INSTEON Devices, 256 Scenes, and 300 Programs&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSupports the Brultech Energy Monitor to display real-time energy consumption&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSupports Smart eMeters&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSupports Weather&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSupports X10 Devices&lt;br /&gt;\r\nKeep Your Favorite Devices, Scenes, and Programs on a dedicated page&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSupports a virtual unlimited number of ISY-99x controllers&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCustomize your devices, scenes, and programs with icons, custom command names, and custom status names&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSecurely access your ISY anywhere using MobiLinc Connect for your ISY-99x series controller. No complex networking required. It just works. See www.mobilinc.com for more information.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'ISY-994i Insteon Compatible Automation Controller with Dual-Band PLM', 'ISY-994i Insteon Compatible Automation Controller with Dual-Band PLM', 'ISY-994i Insteon Compatible Automation Controller with Dual-Band PLM'),
(10042, 1, 'Troy-Bilt 32cc 4-Cycle Heavy-Duty Gas Backpack Leaf Blower - TB4BP EC', '&lt;p&gt;JumpStart™ capable - electric start adaptor eliminates pull starting (sold separately)&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFully-tensioned multi-material suspension system distributes weight evenly and comfortably between shoulders and hips&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBackpack design and padded hip belt for reduced operator fatigue; fits the shape of your hips and reduces pressure points&lt;br /&gt;\r\nErgonomic tube-mounted throttle lever for easy operation&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPowerful 32cc, 4-cycle engine eliminates the need to mix gas and oil and features a smooth-operating full-crank design with outboard starter&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engine Displacement (Cu. Centimeters): 32.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engine Type: 4-cycle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Air Velocity (MPH): 150.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Volume of Air Moved (CFM): 500.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 2-year limited&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Decibel Rating (Decibels): 72.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Starting Type: Push&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;California Air Resources Board Compliant: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Recommended 4-Cycle Engine Oil Type: 30W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4-Cycle Oil Capacity: 3.2 oz.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2-Cycle Fuel Mix Ratio: N/A (2-cycle)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vacuum Kit Included: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Press2Start Compatible: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Interchangeable Tips: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembled Weight (lbs.): 21.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Red&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color Family: Red/Pink&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UL Safety Listing: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CSA Safety Listing: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ETL Safety Listing: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Package Contents:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Gas backpack blower&lt;/li&