(10045, 1, 'Honeywell TrueEASE 18 Gallon Basic Fan Powered Humidifier - HE300A1005', '&lt;p&gt;The Honeywell HE300A1005 Fan Powered humidifier with a basic humidistat control humidifies a tight indoor coverage area of up to 2700 square feet. The Honeywell TrueEase HE300A1005 humidifier combines user-friendly with eco-friendly. TrueEase is loaded with homeowner-friendly features that set it apart from all other humidifiers. The HE300A1005 replaces Honeywell models: HE365B1004, HE365DG115, HE365H8908, HE365VPIAQ.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Honeywell TrueEase HE300A1005 delivers up to 18 gallons of humidity into your home. The TrueEase will keep your home at the perfect humidity level!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Maintaining perfect humidity in your home helps you to turn down your thermostat and save energy. The Honeywell TrueEase humidifier also prevents damage to your woodwork and hardwood floors as well as eliminating dry nasal passages, dry skin and static electricity.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Honeywell TrueEase HE300A1005 humidifier pad is AGION coated to avoid the growth of microorganisms and is tested as per ARI standard 610.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDiscountFurnaceFilter.com is the most reputed online source of the Honeywell HE300A1005 TrueEase humidifier models at unbeatable prices. We also provide truly secured fast shipping and we have thousands of satisfied and happy customers across the United States. Contact us now to acquire your selected model at unmatched prices.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Features&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Up to 50% Water Savings on Advanced Fan-Powered Models&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy to Install - All Plumbing is Connected in a Single Step&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quietest Residential Fan Humidifier - Allowing You to Enjoy to Humidity Without the Noise&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Integrated Wiring Eliminating Time and Money Spend on Separate Relay Switches.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Installs in the Same Space as Existing Bypass Humidifiers for Easy Upgrades&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy Slide Out Design Pad Access for Easy Maintenance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Actual Gallons Per Day: 18&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control: Automatic Digital&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Drain Required: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Equipment Type: Whole House Humidifier&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Gallons Per Day: 15 - 20&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Square Footage: 3000 - 4000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;OEM: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: Honeywell&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Amps:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;3,000 FT2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electrical:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;120 V. 1 Phase. 60 Hz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;HE300A1005&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;10 3/8&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;16 3/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Length:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;15 1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Ship Weight:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;24 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UPC:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;085267845892&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty Terms - Parts: 5 Years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manuals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.acwholesalers.com/hvac/pdf/honeywell/honeywell-humidifier/HE150-250-300-wr.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Honeywell Wiring&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Honeywell TrueEASE 18 Gallon Basic Fan Powered Humidifier - HE300A1005', 'Honeywell TrueEASE 18 Gallon Basic Fan Powered Humidifier - HE300A1005', 'Honeywell TrueEASE 18 Gallon Basic Fan Powered Humidifier - HE300A1005'),
(10044, 1, 'Aprilaire 700 Power Fan Humidifier Automatic Digital Control', '&lt;p&gt;The Aprilaire Model 700 Humidifier is a large-capacity powered unit with big humidification performance to match the biggest of homes. The Model 700:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Has an evaporation capacity of 0.75 gallons per hour—among the highest capacity humidifiers sold&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Humidifies tightly constructed homes up to 4,200 square foot in size&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Features truly automatic control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Aprilaire 700 Whole-House Humidifier features the new #60 truly automatic control, plus a built-in bypass damper, which means fewer parts to install. The bypass damper is conveniently labeled for both summer and winter settings, allowing you to set it for the entire season with no guesswork involved.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Aprilaire 700 Humidifier is one of eight updated humidifier models from Aprilaire. The Aprilaire 700 Humidifier is the top-of-the-line choice, and features truly automatic control with the new, #60 upgraded digital humidity control (included).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Aprilaire 700 humidifier is a direct dimensional replacement for the Aprilaire 760 humidifier!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Aprilaire 700 Humidifiers includes the option to install an outdoor temperature sensor (also included) to properly monitor and adjust relative humidity settings in the home. In addition, the Aprilaire 700 humidifier can be installed in automatic OR manual mode and can humidify a tightly-constructed home of up to 4,200 square feet.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Aprilaire 700 comes complete with the new Aprilaire digital humidity control, first Aprilaire water panel, outdoor temperature sensor, saddle valve, 24V transformer and installation instructions from Aprilaire!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Delivers optimum levels of humidity control with the Automatic Digital Humidifier Control. You never have to monitor your settings or wait until you feel uncomfortable.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Provides vital service, temperature and relative humidity indicators in manual mode as well.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Performs quietly with simple annual maintenance.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Actual Gallons Per Day: 18&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control: Automatic Digital&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Drain Required: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Equipment Type: Whole House Humidifier&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Gallons Per Day: 15 - 20&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Amps: 0.8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: Aprilaire&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;OEM: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity: 4,200 FT2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electrical:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;120 V. 1 Phase. 60 Hz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model: 700&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;10 11/32&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;18&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Length: 15 29/32&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight: 16 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty Terms - Parts: 5 Years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manuals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.aprilaire.com/docs/default-source/product-owners-manuals/humidifier/aprilaire-humidifier-model-700-owners-manual.pdf?Status=Master&amp;amp;sfvrsn=6&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Aprilaire Humidifier Model 700 Owners Manual&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.aprilaire.com/docs/default-source/product-owners-manuals/humidifier/aprilaire-humidifier-model-700m-owners-manual.pdf?Status=Master&amp;amp;sfvrsn=6&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Aprilaire Humidifier Model 700M Owners Manual&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Aprilaire 700 Power Fan Humidifier Automatic Digital Control', 'Aprilaire 700 Power Fan Humidifier Automatic Digital Control', 'Aprilaire 700 Power Fan Humidifier Automatic Digital Control'),
(10048, 1, 'Lincoln Industrial PowerLuber Cordless Grease Gun 14 Volts 7500 PSI', '&lt;p&gt;This Lincoln Industrial PowerLuber is a professional-grade, heavy-duty cordless grease gun that lets you do your lubrication tasks at a fraction of the time of a manual grease gun, delivering up to 7,500 PSI and up to 8 grease cartridges with a single charge. Featuring a 14.4V high-torque motor combined with a 14.4V high-capacity NiCd battery for superior performance and run time, this PowerLuber grease gun allows for faster lubrication with much less fatigue.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cordless grease gun (1)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;30in.L hose (1)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery (1)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charger (1)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Case (1)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.northerntool.com/images/product/features/40394.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 782px; height: 394px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;14.4 Volts of Powerful Performance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nYou\'ll quickly appreciate the exceptional performance of this high-torque 14.4V motor teamed with an 14.4V high-capacity NiCd battery. The pair tackles the heaviest of heavy-duty greasing jobs with ease and extends run times to a level you\'ll have to experience to believe.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Accurately Measure Grease Output&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nLincoln\'s patented stroke indicator finally offers an accurate way to check how much grease you\'ve expended BEFORE the cartridge runs dry. Just place your thumb on the indicator during use to count each stroke; output is measured at 0.20 oz. of grease every 10 strokes.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stacked with Safety Components&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFrom the built-in circuit breaker to the handy manual reset button, right down to the reliable pressure relief valve, no motor safety feature was overlooked. This grease gun is truly designed to last.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Versatile Two-Speed Design&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIt\'s easy to match the tool to the task when you\'re presented with the right options! The two-speed transmission allows you to choose between high volume output to get the job done quickly, or high pressure output (up to 7,500 PSI) for those more demanding jobs.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cartridge or Bulk Flexibility&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe plated steel barrel is equipped with a premium grease follower that accepts either grease cartridges or bulk grease, giving you the option of how you choose to fill your PowerLuber.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reach Those Hard-to-Reach Spots&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGet that little extra out of your grease gun when you add on the high-quality 30in. long flexible hose that\'s included with this PowerLuber. Reach back to those hard-to-access fittings and use the spring guards and retaining clip to hold the hose in place, turning difficult into much easier!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deliver Grease, Not Air&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhen it comes to efficiency, it\'s hard to beat the PowerLuber\'s combination valve. This valve purges trapped air from the gun, allowing for a smoother, more efficient grease delivery.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specification&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ship Weight: 14.0 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Volts: 14.4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operating PSI: 7,500&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cordless: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hose Length (in.): 30&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Application: Auto, trucking, agriculture industry&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions L x W x H (in.): &amp;nbsp;23 x 15 x 4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Speeds (qty.): Two-speed design delivers unsurpassed output and pressure at the flip of a switch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery Included: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charger Included: Yes &quot;Smart Charger&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Case Included: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes: Built-in hose/coupler holder, hook for shoulder strap&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Lincoln Industrial PowerLuber Cordless Grease Gun 14.4 Volts 7500 PSI', 'Lincoln Industrial PowerLuber Cordless Grease Gun 14.4 Volts 7500 PSI', 'Lincoln Industrial PowerLuber Cordless Grease Gun 14.4 Volts 7500 PSI'),
(10039, 1, 'Onsite Pro FS3/4H-90 Washing Machine Valve Shutoff Kit', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stop Washing Machine Leaks From Becoming a Disaster!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Prevent avoidable water damage to your home or belongings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatically shuts off water to washing machine when leak is detected&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Installs in minutes - no professional plumber is needed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two output contact wires make is easy to integrate with INSTEON&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Don\'t risk your floors, carpets and other personal belongings to costly and ruinous water damage! Prevent flood damage and avoid costly repairs with the easy-to-install Washing Machine Valve Shutoff Kit. This system not only detects leaks early, but it automatically shuts your water off in the event of a leak, alerting you with the control panel\'s alarm. Incorporate the Flood Stop into your INSTEON or X10 network - the control unit has two output contact wires and plugs with 6&quot; leads. The Washing Machine FloodStop with 90 Degree Valves is also available with Straight Valves, sold separately.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;When using the AC/DC adaptor, the 4 AA batteries will serve as a battery backup in case of a power outage. These FloodStop valves screw onto your pre-existing hose-bibbs, just like screwing on a hose. The non-intrusive devices can be installed in as little as 10 minutes; no professional plumbers are required. This kit includes everything you need to protect your property from costly water-leak damage: valves installed on your hot and cold water inlets, a water sensor to be placed on the floor, and the control unit, which is mounted to your wall with the included screws.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This kit includes everything you need to protect your property from costly water-leak damage: valves installed on your hot and cold water inlets, a water sensor to be placed on the floor, and the control unit, which is mounted to your wall with the included screws. An AC/DC power supply is included; you can also install four AA batteries, (sold separately) for backup power. You can even add multiple water sensors for different areas around your washing machine. The Washing Machine FloodStop with Straight Valves is also available with 90 Degree Valves, sold separately.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Designed for both residential and commercial dwellings, the Washing Machine Valve Shutoff Kit uses a pair of 3/4-inch threaded motorized ball valves powered by an AC/DC power adaptor (or 4 AA batteries) to shut off the water supply whenever your washing machine leaks.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer: OnSite Pro&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Product No.:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; FS3/4H90&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UPC:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 815361000114&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: Sensor: 1.25&quot; x 7.5&quot; double-sided; 3/4&quot; hose fitting&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Alarm: Beeping with mute button&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Lead-Free brass&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;PSI Rating: Rated 0-180 psi; max. 250 psi&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Signal Outputs:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;From 1 normally closed &amp;amp; 1 normally open to 1 Normally Open&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Valve: Motorized Ball Valves&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Motorized Ball Valves: CNC machined with 90-degree downward outlet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operation: Motors operate at 6VDC&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operating Temperature: 32°F to 212° F&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power: AC/DC and 4 AA batteries for backup power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compliance: UL-listed class 2 wall adapter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Warranty: 1 Year, limited&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2x - Automatic 90 Degree Ball Valves&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1x - Water sensor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1x - FloodStop control unit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1x - AC/DC Adaptor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2x - Output Contact Wire&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mounting hardware and Velcro Pad&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Instructions Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Onsite Pro FS3/4H-90 Washing Machine Valve Shutoff Kit', 'Onsite Pro FS3/4H-90 Washing Machine Valve Shutoff Kit', 'Onsite Pro FS3/4H-90 Washing Machine Valve Shutoff Kit'),
(10050, 1, 'Warn 885000 PullzAll Handheld Electric Pulling Tool - Red, 120 Volt', '&lt;p&gt;The Warn PullzAll is an electric pulling tool that replaces come-a-longs and chain falls. Now you can get the job done faster, with more control and without the manual labor. With its 1,000-lb. working load capacity, the PullzAll has endless applications for the professional tradesman and do-it-yourselfer, including construction, pipe fitting, iron work, equipment and plant maintenance, farm and ranch use, auto shops, garages, machine shops, home improvement, hunting, camping and more.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;PullzAll pulling tool (1)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;15-ft. wire rope (1)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features + Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.northerntool.com/images/product/features/147026.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 782px; height: 394px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operates on 120V AC power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1000lb. lifting/pulling capacity handles heavy-duty jobs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lightweight portable tool to help tradesman lift or move heavy objects&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Combines power of winch or hoist with compact style of handheld power tool&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wire rope tension plate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electronic load limiter with LED indicator protects against overload&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy-grip handle with built-in trigger for variable speed control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Convenient forward/reverse switch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes 15ft. of 7/32in. wire rope with industrial-grade hook&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Swivel anchor hook adds versatility&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Note: Do not spool the wire rope out past the red paint, which is visible at 13 ft. Doing so can cause the wire rope to spool on the drum in the wrong direction, which can damage the wire rope and fairlead.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specification&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ship Weight: 20.0 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Volts: 120&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Line Pull (lbs.): 1,000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Run Time: 1 min.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cooling: 30 min.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Line Speed (FPM): 13.8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Clutch: None&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Braking: Dynamic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Switching Method: Variable speed trigger w/forward/reverse&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rope Type&amp;nbsp;: Galvanized aircraft grade wire&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rope Size L x dia. (ft. x in.): 15 total (13 usable) x 7/32&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fairlead Type: Hawse&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Cord (ft.)&amp;nbsp;: 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mounting Hardware Included: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions L x W x H (in.): 12 x 8 x 8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Warn 885000 PullzAll Handheld Electric Pulling Tool - Red, 120 Volt', 'Warn 885000 PullzAll Handheld Electric Pulling Tool - Red, 120 Volt', 'Warn 885000 PullzAll Handheld Electric Pulling Tool - Red, 120 Volt'),
