(10072, 1, 'KitchenAid Classic Series 4.5 Qt. Stand Mixer', '&lt;p&gt;Whip up batter in a jiffy using the KitchenAid Classic Series 4.5 Qt. Stand Mixer. This stand mixer comes along with a bowl, splashguard, whisk, mixing paddle, and dough hook. This stand mixer includes recipes.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This stand mixer is sturdy and durable owing to its construction out of premium quality metal. The stainless steel mixing bowl is detachable allowing easy storage and cleaning. It has a capacity of 4.5 quarts, and has a handle making it easy to carry. The Classic Series 4.5 Qt. Stand Mixer by KitchenAid has a tilt head allowing flexibility in the mixer’s movement. It has 10 speed settings and multiple attachments making it versatile in its use. The locking head helps it stay firmly in the position it is placed in. The splash guard and pouring shield can help in preventing a mess caused from batter splattering. The 250-watt stand mixer sports a silver finish that gives it a sterling look.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This stand mixer requires minimal effort for cleaning and can be wiped clean with a soft, dry cloth, while the beaters can be rinsed with water after use. Made in the United States of America, this stand mixer is reliable.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tilt-head design allows clear access to the beater and bowl&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&quot;C&quot; dough hook kneads yeast dough for bread and pizza recipes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;10-speed slide control ranges from a very fast whip to a very slow stir&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Made in the USA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fits any kitchen aid stand mixer, regardless of the series the mixer is from&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Details&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Beaters: 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Locking Head: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Splash Guard: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wattage: 250 Watts (W)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Speeds: 10&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Warranty: 1 year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bowl or Mixing Cup Included&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bowl or Cup Capacity: 4.5 Quarts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Multiple Attachments&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Attachments Included: Metal whisk; Dough hook; Pouring shield&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Weights &amp;amp; Dimensions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall: 13.9&quot; H x 8.75&quot; W x 14.13&quot; D&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall Product Weight: 25 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'KitchenAid Classic Series 4.5 Qt. Stand Mixer', 'KitchenAid Classic Series 4.5 Qt. Stand Mixer', 'KitchenAid Classic Series 4.5 Qt. Stand Mixer'),
(10073, 1, 'Weber Q 2200 LP Gas Grill', '&lt;p&gt;Grill up your favorites on the Weber Q 2200 LP Gas Grill and get perfect results every time. Its built-in thermometer and precise temperature control with the turn of a knob means this grill gives you total control over your cooking experience. The porcelain-enameled, cast-iron cooking grates provide 280 square inches of grilling surface and clean-up is a snap. At the push of a button this propane grill ignites to belt out 12,000 BTUs per hour.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;About Weber Grills&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWeber-Stephen Products Co., headquartered in Palatine, Ill., is the premier manufacturer of charcoal and gas grills, grilling accessories, and other outdoor room products. A family-owned business for more than 50 years, Weber has grown to be a leading seller of outdoor grills worldwide.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dimensions &amp;amp; Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;# of Burners: 1 burner&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: Weber&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cooking Power: 12000&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 51.4W x 24.3D x 26H in.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Finish: Silver&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel Type: Liquid Propane&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Cast Aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Surface Size: 280&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 42 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manufacturer Warranty&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAlum castings &amp;amp; thermoplastic 5 years, 2 years paint and all remaining parts&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included: &lt;/strong&gt;Grill Only with side shelves&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Weber Q 2200 LP Gas Grill', 'Weber Q 2200 LP Gas Grill', 'Weber Q 2200 LP Gas Grill'),
(10086, 1, 'Sizzix 656250 Big Shot Pro Die Cutting Machine', '&lt;p&gt;If you\'re tired of the same old pre-designed greeting cards, holiday and special event decorations, and scrapbooking materials, then the Big Shot Pro die-cutting machine from Sizzix is just what you need to reinvigorate the artist inside. In addition to the cutting machine, the Big Shot Pro contains a sliding tray, cutting and crease pads and much more to get you started right away.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Black&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: ABS plastic, POM plastic, thermoplastic rubber, rubber, steel, aluminum, metal alloy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible with all Sizzix and Ellison designs (not included)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Any shape-cutting or embossing product thinner than a Bigz Die requires the Big Shot Pro Solo Platform, shim and wafer-thin die adapter (sold separately)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 24.25 inches high x 15 inches wide x 7.5 inches deep&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Imported&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 5 year Limited Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model No: 656250&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: Sizzix&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Package includes:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One (1) Big Shot Pro&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One (1) standard sliding tray&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One (1) standard cutting pad&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One (1) premium crease pad&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two (2) 0.1-mm Mylar shims&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One (1) standard adapter pad&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One (1) die pick&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Dies sold Separately&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;#13793915 Sizzix Big Die-Star, 5 Point 3-D&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;#13621551 Sizzix Big XL Die-Box&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;#13054503 Sizzix Big XL Die-Gift Card Holder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;#13054504 Sizzix Big XL Die-Card, Ornate Tri-Fold&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Sizzix 656250 Big Shot Pro Die Cutting Machine', 'Sizzix 656250 Big Shot Pro Die Cutting Machine', 'Sizzix 656250 Big Shot Pro Die Cutting Machine'),
(10108, 1, 'H-100 Bic Acoustech Cinema Series Powered Subwoofer', '&lt;p&gt;The Bic Acoustech subwoofer fills the room with clean bass that enhances music or movies The Cinema Series speakers\' deep rumbling bass creates a more exciting home theater sound.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Subwoofer features a sleek cabinet in black, laquered wood&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Long-throw 12-inch woofer features vented enclosures&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power: 150 watts RMS, 500 watts peak&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Output: 115dB SPL&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Frequency response: 24Hz to 200Hz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Crossover frequency: 40Hz to 150Hz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measures 17 inches high x 15 inches wide x 18.25 inches deep&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 17.0x15.0x18.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 2 year Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: Wood, black laquer finish&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model No: H-100&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: BIC&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;This item cannot be shipped to Alaska or Hawaii.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Bic Acoustech H100 Cinema Series Powered Subwoofer', 'Bic Acoustech H100 Cinema Series Powered Subwoofer', 'Bic Acoustech H100 Cinema Series Powered Subwoofer');
