(10077, 1, 'Brother LB6800PRW Project Runway Sewing and Embroidery Machine', '&lt;p&gt;This Brother Project Runway computerized embroidery machine features 120 frame pattern combinations and 5 embroidery lettering fonts for endless creative options. The on-screen editing and backlit LCD touchscreen ensures sewing precision.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;70 Built-in embroidery patterns&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;67 true sewing stitches with 98 stitch functions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4 x 4 Field of Embroidery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;120 frame pattern combination and five embroidery lettering fonts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Simple letter selection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in embroidery card slot&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4x4 field of embroidery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Seven styles of one- step automatic buttonholes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;USB port to connect to PC to download patterns from the Internet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Backlit LCD touchscreen design memory&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;On-screen editing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick-Set drop-in bobbin and automatic needle threader&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Speed of 710 stitches a minute and can embroider at 400 stitches a minute&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Variable stitch speed slider&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Precise tension wheel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Free arm capability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;F.A.S.T. Bobbin Winding System&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in stitches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 38.4 pounds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 21.5 inches high x 16 inches deep x 22 inches long&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Included Accessories​:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 limited edition Project Runway rolling carrying case&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 seam ripper&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multiple bobbins&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 needle set&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 twin needle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 cleaning brush&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 eyelet punch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 screwdriver&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 pair of scissors&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 embroidery hoop and spool net&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Included Accessory Feet​:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Buttonhole foot&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overcasting foot&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;USB port on machine to attach the machine to a computer and download patterns&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Monogramming foot&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Zipper foot&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Zig-zag foot&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blind hem and embroidery foot&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 21.5 in. H x 16 in. D x 22 in. L&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: 25 year Limited Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: Plastic / Metal&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model Number: LB6800PRW&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Metal Plastic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Type: Computerized&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Brother LB6800PRW Project Runway Sewing and Embroidery Machine', 'Brother LB6800PRW Project Runway Sewing and Embroidery Machine', 'Brother LB6800PRW Project Runway Sewing and Embroidery Machine'),
(10076, 1, 'Brother SE-400 Computerized Sewing and Embroidery Machine', '&lt;p&gt;The computerized SE-400 combination embroidery and sewing machine is designed to help &amp;nbsp;you give your projects a customized, high-end look—all while being priced to fit your budget! &amp;nbsp;Featuring 70 built-in embroidery designs, 67 built-in sewing stitches, 120 frame pattern combinations and 5 embroidery lettering fonts, the SE-400 is the perfect machine for all your&amp;nbsp;sewing, embroidery, crafting and home décor projects. Computer connectivity allows you to&amp;nbsp;easily import embroidery designs directly from your computer. Features like the automatic&amp;nbsp;needle threading system and backlit touch screen LCD make working on the machine easy&amp;nbsp;on your eyes, while the Quick-SetTM drop-in top bobbin, easy bobbin-winding system and&amp;nbsp;built-in push-button thread cutter add a new level of convenience to your sewing and&amp;nbsp;embroidery crafting. With an impressive assortment of included accessories, the SE-400 is&amp;nbsp;truly an affordable, feature-rich choice for the budding fashion designer.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SE-400 Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Computer Connectivity with Update Capability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;70 built-in embroidery designs, 5 monogramming&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;fonts and 120 frame pattern combinations&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;67 built-in sewing stitches with 98 stitch functions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy-to-view back-lit, touch screen LCD display&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;On-screen reference guide in 16 languages&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick-Set™ drop-in bobbin and automatic needle&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;threader&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in push button thread cutter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Large 4” x 4” embroidery area&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brightly lit LED work area&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fast, automatic bobbin winding&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One-touch start/stop/reverse operations&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operates with or without foot control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Full Assortment of Accessories&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electronic Variable Sewing Speed Control allows&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;you to choose the most comfortable sewing speed&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;for your project&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Free arm/flatbed convertible sewing surface&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick change presser feet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stitch width and length control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable thread tension control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Safety power and light switch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lightweight with built-in handle for portability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Instruction booklet in English and Spanish&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 20.7999992370605px;&quot;&gt;SE-400&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 15.0x9.0x13.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: 25 year Limited Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: plastic and metal&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model Number: SE-400&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Metal Plastic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Type: Computerized&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;What In the box: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;1. Brother SE400 Computerized Sewing and Embroidery Machine&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Included Accessory Feet:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nButtonhole foot, Overcasting foot, Monogramming foot, Zipper foot, Blind Stitch foot, Button Fitting foot, Embroidery foot&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Included Accessories:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEmbroidery arm, accessory bag with seam ripper, needle set, twin needle, cleaning brush, eyelet punch, screwdrivers (3), touch pen, spool caps (3), Extra Spool Pin, Scissors, Embroidery Bobbin Thread, Instruction CD, language setting sheet, felt with stabilizer, USB cable, power cord and Operation Manual&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Included Embroidery Hoops:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1 (4&quot; x 4&quot;) Additional hoops may be available, please see Optional Accessories&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;row ratings-container&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: -15px; margin-right: -15px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11.8181819915771px; line-height: 20px;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-6&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; float: left; width: 247.5px;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;ratings&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.2em;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Brother SE-400 Computerized Sewing and Embroidery Machine', 'Brother SE-400 Computerized Sewing and Embroidery Machine', 'Brother SE-400 Computerized Sewing and Embroidery Machine'),
(10107, 1, 'Singer Special Edition 90s Computerized Sewing Machine', '&lt;p&gt;More than a stunning sewing machine to look at, this machine features 231 built in stitches, extra-large sewing space and a SwiftSmart threading system. The heavy-duty metal frame and abundant accessories mean that you\'ll be having fun crafting fun gifts for a long time.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Machine type: Computerized&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of feet: 16&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Type of feet: All-purpose, zipper, buttonhole, blind hem, satin stitch, beading, braiding, chenille stitching, cording, darning/freehand embroidery, edge joining, fancy, fringe, invisible zipper, open toe, roller&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Buttonhole options: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;USB port: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LCD screen: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Free arm capability: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic threading: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stitch width and length control: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer: Singer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model: 230075912&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 24 pounds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: Plastic, metal&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 19 inches high x 13 inches wide x 19 inches long&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly required.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 25-year limited warranty by manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Set includes: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Pack of needles, four (4) class 15J bobbins (3 + 1 in machine), three (3) thread spool caps, auxiliary spool pin, spool pin felt, needle plate screwdriver, seam ripper/lint brush, soft-sided dust cover, foot control, power cord, instruction manual with stitch guide, quick-start guide, wing (hemstitch) needle, presser foot shank, value-added instructions.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Singer Special Edition 90s Computerized Sewing Machine', 'Singer Special Edition 90s Computerized Sewing Machine', 'Singer Special Edition 90s Computerized Sewing Machine'),
