(10111, 1, 'Brother MFC-9460CDN Laser Multifunction Printer - Color - Plain Paper', '&lt;p&gt;Network-ready MFC9460CDN Color Laser Printer offers auto duplexing for printing, copying, faxing and scanning. Connect to your PC or install on a network. Print 25 pages per minute in color and black/white with up to 2400 x 600 dpi and generate 25 copies per minute. Install the printer on a wired or wireless network via Ethernet or connect locally to a single computer via USB. 33.6Kbps fax modem transmits a page in 2.5 seconds, stores up to 500 pages and features 316 dial locations, 366 broadcast locations, and fax forwarding. 48-bit scanner offers black/white and color scanning, optical scan resolution of 1200 x 2400 dpi, and interpolated scan resolution of 19,200 dpi. The 250-sheet input tray adjusts for letter-size or legal-size paper. Printer also offers an expandable 128MB memory, USB 2.0 direct interface, a 50-sheet multipurpose tray for envelopes or other types of media, 25 to 400 percent copy scaling, and 35-page automatic document feeder. Energy Star qualified.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer: Brother Industries, Ltd&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Part Number: MFC-9460CDN&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Website Address: http://www.brother-usa.com&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand Name: Brother&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Series: MFC&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Model: MFC-9460CDN&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Name: MFC-9460CDN Multifunction Printer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Type: Laser Multifunction Printer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multifunction Devices: Copier/Fax/Printer/Scanner&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Recommended Use: Plain Paper Print&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Print Color: Color&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Mono Print Speed (ppm): 25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Color Print Speed (ppm): 25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Print Resolution: 2400 x 600 dpi&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Duplex Printing: Automatic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Standard Memory: 128 MB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;USB: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ethernet: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ethernet Technology: Fast Ethernet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Display Screen Type: LCD&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Scanner Type: Flatbed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Scan Color: Color&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Optical Resolution: 1200 dpi&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Interpolated Resolution: 19200 x 19200 dpi&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color Depth: 48-bit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Copier Type: Flatbed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Copy Color: Color&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Copy Resolution: 1200 x 600 dpi&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Mono Copy Speed (cpm): 25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Color Copy Speed (cpm): 25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Copies: 99&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fax Color: Color&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Modem Speed: 33.60 Kbps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Transmission Speed: 3 sec/page&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Media Type: Glossy Paper&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Media Size: B6 - 4.92&quot; x 6.93&quot;, A4 - 8.27&quot; x 11.69&quot;, Letter - 8.50&quot; x 10.98&quot;, A5 - 5.83&quot; x 8.27&quot;, Custom Size, Executive - 10.51&quot; x 7.24&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Input/Multipurpose Trays Installed: 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Input Trays Supported: 3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Standard Input Media Capacity: 300 sheets&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Input Media Capacity: 800 sheets&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Duty Cycle: 40000 pages per month&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Form Factor: Desktop&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Gray&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 19.4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 16.1&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth: 19.8&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight (Approximate): 58.40 lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Platform Supported: PC&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Recycled: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Recycled Content: 0%&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Post-consumer-waste%: 0%&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly Required: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Green Compliant: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Green Compliance Certificate/Authority: ENERGY STAR&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Country of Origin: China&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Package Contents:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;MFC-9460CDN Multifunction Printer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Black Toner Cartridge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Cyan Toner Cartridge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Magenta Toner Cartridge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Yellow Toner Cartridge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Drum Unit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Installation and Documentation CD-ROMs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AC Power Cord&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick Setup Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Basic User\'s Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Brother MFC-9460CDN Laser Multifunction Printer - Color - Plain Paper', 'Brother MFC-9460CDN Laser Multifunction Printer - Color - Plain Paper', 'Brother MFC-9460CDN Laser Multifunction Printer - Color - Plain Paper'),
(10112, 1, 'NeatConnect Cloud Scanner and Digital Filing System for PC and Mac', '&lt;p&gt;Our smartest way to get organized! NeatConnect transforms paper into digital files and sends them straight to the cloud — without a computer. At home or at the office, the wireless NeatConnect sends your files straight to Neat, email, cloud services, and wherever else they need to be. Includes free Neat desktop software for PC or Mac.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wireless -&amp;nbsp;Scan Straight to Neat (Premium Subscription Included)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSend items directly to Neat, where your information becomes secure, useful, and usable. Create reports, edit data, and share files from anywhere, with Neat and the Neat mobile app.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOrganize Everything : Add e-receipts, forward emails, and import PDFs and image files into Neat.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFind Anything: Neat extracts key data from everything you scan, making it easy to find, use, and share.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAccess Anywhere: Securely sync your Neat files – access them on your desktop, mobile device, or online.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSave Time: Create spending, tax and expense reports, share folders, and comment on shared items&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Computerless&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;​ -&amp;nbsp;A Touch of Organization&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nYou don’t need a computer to use NeatConnect, because everything is driven by the easy, intuitive touchscreen interface. From any room in your house, or any spot in the office, scanning is as simple as loading your paper, swiping through to your destination, and tapping Scan.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nScan Settings: Select one- or two-sided scanning, save each page separately or combined, and scan anything exactly the way you want it.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nScan Directly to Email: Send scanned items as attachments in one easy step – right from NeatConnect. It’s the fast, simple way to share files with anyone!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Paperless -&amp;nbsp;Your Life, Neat.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNeatConnect and the Neat Smart Organization System transform your information, making it easy to find, use, and share. It’s the simple, easy way to take control of your files and declare independence from paper.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFreedom from Clutter: Don’t let paper pile up in your home or office. With NeatConnect, it’s easy to stay on top of things, transforming paper into digital files and keeping your space neatly organized.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTake Back Your Time: Tracking expenses, getting ready for taxes, or finding a file when you need it – Neat makes dealing with paper faster and easier than ever before. Spend less time messing with paper, and more time doing what matters to you.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOrganize Everything: You’ll always know where to find an important document when you have Neat. Organized, searchable, and backed up to Neat, your files have never been in a better place.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NeatConnect​&amp;nbsp;Scanner Specs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wireless: Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n compatible WLAN (required)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Supported wireless bands: WEP, WPA/WPA2-Personal&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic Document Feeder (ADF) Scanner&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1- and 2-sided scanning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;24 PPM color, grayscale, B&amp;amp;W (300 dpi, A4 size)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum resolution: 600 dpi&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Supported paper sizes: 1.5″ x 2″ to 8.5″ x 30″&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max scan area: 8.5″ x 11″ (up to 30″ long for 300dpi)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity with paper tray: 15 business cards + 15 receipts + 15 letter-size documents&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity without paper tray: 50 letter-size documents&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;TWAIN, WIA, and Image Capture support for scanning into other imaging applications&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 SD card slot for saving scanned images (32 GB max)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 USB Port for scanning directly to PC or Mac&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Scanner Dimensions: 11″W x 8.7″D x 7.5″H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 5.3 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Neat Software Specs /&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;&quot;&gt;For&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 20.7999992370605px;&quot;&gt;Windows:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Images can be saved in JPEG, PDF, and other popular formats&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Data can be sent to Excel®, Outlook®, Quicken®, QuickBooks®, TurboTax®, and more&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Reads U.S. and Canadian receipts and business cards&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Neat Software Specs&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;&quot;&gt;/&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;&quot;&gt;For Mac:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Images can be saved in JPEG, PDF, and other popular formats®&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Data can be exported to Excel®, Quicken®, TurboTax® and Mac Address Book&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Reads U.S. and Canadian receipts and business cards&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;System Requirements /&amp;nbsp;For&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;&quot;&gt;Windows:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microsoft® Windows® 7 (32- and 64-bit) or Windows 8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pentium® IV 2.0+ GHz or faster (Dual Core recommended)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 GB RAM; 2 GB highly recommended&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 GB of available hard disk space to installation, 1 GB recommended for user data&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CD-ROM drive or DVD drive required for installation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Available USB port&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;&quot;&gt;System Requirements /&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For Mac:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mac OS X v10.7 or later&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mac computer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 GB of RAM; 4 GB recommended&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;650 MB of available disk space for installation, 1 GB recommended for user data&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CD-ROM or DVD drive required for installation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Available USB port&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'NeatConnect Cloud Scanner and Digital Filing System for PC and Mac', 'NeatConnect Cloud Scanner and Digital Filing System for PC and Mac', 'NeatConnect Cloud Scanner and Digital Filing System for PC and Mac');
