(10113, 1, 'NeatDesk Desktop Scanner and Digital Filing System for PC and Mac', '&lt;p&gt;NeatDesk is a high-speed, duplex desktop scanner and smart organization system. Scan receipts, business cards and documents in one batch while the software identifies, extracts, and organizes key information. Includes free Neat desktop software for PC or Mac.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lose the Paper. Keep the Information&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNeat brings scanned documents to life, using InDocument Identification (ID2) technology to read and understand key information, then automatically organizing what it sees. The resulting digital files are useful and usable – easy to find, easy to access, and easy to share.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Make quick work of your paper clutter&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNeatDesk will scan in your receipts, business cards, or documents at a speedy 24 pages per minute. Scan up to 50 pages at once – 1 or 2-sided, color or B&amp;amp;W, single or multi-page.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;From paper piles to organized digital files&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNeat reads and extracts the information from whatever you scan. Receipts become digital records with vendors and amounts, business cards become digital contacts, and documents become fully keyword searchable.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Information you can use (and find)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCreate tax or expense reports with your receipt data, or export to Excel®, Quicken®, or TurboTax®. Sync your contacts with Outlook® or Address Book. Find what you need with a keyword, and organize it however you like.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Digital Filing System – to go&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNeatDesk comes with a free trial version of Neat’s cloud service, which allows you to sync and back up your Neat files, and access them anywhere with your browser or mobile device.*&lt;br /&gt;\r\n*Available for iOS devices and Android phones.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NeatDesk Scanner Specs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic Document Feeder (ADF) Scanner&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Scans in color, grayscale, or B&amp;amp;W CIS&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Scans simplex (1-sided) or duplex (2-sided)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;600 dpi maximum resolution&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Optical Character Recognition (OCR) + Intelligent Text Recognition (ITR)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Up to 24 PPM Color, Grayscale, B&amp;amp;W (300dpi, A4 size, simplex)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Up to 24 PPM Grayscale, B&amp;amp;W (300dpi, A4 size duplex)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity with paper tray: &amp;nbsp;15 business cards + 15 receipts + 15 letter-size documents&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity without paper tray: &amp;nbsp;50 letter-size documents&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Scan Area: &amp;nbsp; 8.5” x 11″ (up to 30” long for 300dpi)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Scanner Dimensions: &amp;nbsp;10.8”W x 7.5”D x 7.3”H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: &amp;nbsp;4.4 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AC Power Adapter Included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Factory calibrated&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Image capture support for scanning into other imaging applications&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Neat Software Specs / For Windows:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Images can be saved in JPEG, PDF, and other popular formats&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Data can be sent to Excel®, Outlook®, Quicken®, QuickBooks®, TurboTax®, and more&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Reads U.S. and Canadian receipts and business cards&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Neat Software Specs / For Mac:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Images can be saved in JPEG, PDF, and other popular formats&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Data can be exported to Excel®, Quicken®, &amp;nbsp;TurboTax® and Mac Address Book&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Reads U.S. and Canadian receipts and business cards&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;System Requirements / For Windows:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microsoft® Windows® 7 (32- and 64-bit) or Windows 8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pentium® IV 2.0+ GHz or faster (Dual Core recommended)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 GB RAM; 2 GB highly recommended&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 GB of available hard disk space to installation, 1 GB recommended for user data&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CD-ROM drive or DVD drive required for installation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Available USB port&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;System Requirements / For Mac:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mac OS X v10.7 or later&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mac computer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 GB of RAM; 4 GB recommended&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;650 MB of available disk space for installation, 1 GB recommended for user data&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CD-ROM or DVD drive required for installation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Available USB port&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'NeatDesk Desktop Scanner and Digital Filing System for PC and Mac', 'NeatDesk Desktop Scanner and Digital Filing System for PC and Mac', 'NeatDesk Desktop Scanner and Digital Filing System for PC and Mac'),
(10114, 1, 'AAXA Technologies P4X Pico Pocket Projector 125 Lumens - 90min Battery', '&lt;p&gt;The P4-X Pico Projector from AAXA Technologies combines ultra-compact, long lasting LED projection technology, a built-in media player, and a plethora of multimedia ports to act as a mobile projection power house. It\'s a real working projector that weighs under a half pound (0.2kg), and features a dazzling 125 lumens. The LED light source is rated to last 15,000 hours. You\'ll probably never change the lamp in this projector. The P4-X comes with a li-ion rechargeable battery that\'s good for 90+ minutes on a charge. You can recharge it using the included AC wall charger adapter or directly from a USB port. Of course you can always run it on AC power if there\'s a socket nearby and save your battery power for when you really need it. With its vivid 2000:1 contrast ratio you can project on a screen or just about anywhere.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer: AAXA Technologies, Inc&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Manufacturer Website Address: http://www.aaxatech.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand Name: AAXA Technologies&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Model: P4-X&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Name: AAXA P4X Pico Projector&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Type: DLP Projector&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Projection Method: Front&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Lamps: 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lamp Type: LED&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Normal Mode Lamp Life: 15000 Hour&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Standard Mode Brightness: 125 lm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Native Resolution: 720x480&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Graphic Mode: WVGA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Resolution: 1280 x 768&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Minimum Diagonal Image Size: 80&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Diagonal Image Size: 6.67 ft&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Contrast Ratio: 2,000:1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Video Signal Standard: HDTV&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Input Scan Format: 720p&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Output Scan Format: 720p&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;HDMI: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;USB: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;VGA In: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Audio Line Out: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Composite Video: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in Devices: Media Player&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Memory Card Supported: microSD&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operating Power Consumption: 12.5 W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Black&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 141mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 71mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth: 31mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 22.0 x 10.0 x 9.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model No: KP500-02&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: AAXA Technologies&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'AAXA Technologies P4X Pico Pocket Projector 125 Lumens, 90min Battery', 'AAXA Technologies P4X Pico Pocket Projector 125 Lumens, 90min Battery', 'AAXA Technologies P4X Pico Pocket Projector 125 Lumens, 90min Battery'),
(10115, 1, 'Sea Eagle SE370 Pro Inflatable Kayak White', '&lt;p&gt;Enjoy a day out on the water with this SE370 deluxe inflatable two-person kayak. With its included paddles and 8-minute inflate time, this is the perfect grab-and-go boat. This lightweight, 32-pound kayak lets you enjoy the wild outdoors without straining your back. This piece of equipment can hold up to 650 pounds, so larger individuals can have a great time, or parents can bring a child along for the ride. A repair kit is included to ensure you\'re never left stranded due to small punctures or scrapes.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Self bailing drain valve&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lashed down inflatable spray skirts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;I-beam construction floor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two skegs on the bottom for better tracking and speed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bow and stern grab line&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Chambers: Three (port, starboard and floor)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: 38 mil PolyKrylor (K80 PVC)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Seam: High frequency welded&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Floor: Inflatable I-beam construction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Air valves: Three deluxe one way&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Inflation and assembly time: 8 minutes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Interior: 10 feet 8 inches long x 1 foot 1 inch wide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exterior: 12 feet 6 inches long x 2 feet 10 inches wide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Deflated: 31 inches long x 19 inches wide x 8 inches thick&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tube diameter: 9 inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity: 3 Persons or 650 pounds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 32 pounds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: 3 year Limited Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: PVC&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model Number:&amp;nbsp;SE370K-Pro&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Type: Kayak&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Includes:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SE370 Hull&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two AB30 Paddles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two inflatable DKS Seats&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Storage Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Foot Pump&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Repair Kit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Sea Eagle SE370 Pro Inflatable Kayak White', 'Sea Eagle SE370 Pro Inflatable Kayak White', 'Sea Eagle SE370 Pro Inflatable Kayak White'),
(10116, 1, 'Exerpeutic 440XL Fitness Walking Electric Treadmill', '&lt;p&gt;Walking on the Exerpeutic 440XL is one of the easiest and most effective ways to achieve a regimen of regular exercise. Unlike outdoor walking, treadmill fitness walking has the benefits of shock absorption and the convenience of exercising in your own home, in front of a TV or just listening to your favorite music. Fitness walking can help you lose body fat, tone muscles and is a great way to stay in shape. Studies show that a 2 mile walk everyday achieves the same results as an intense exercise of any technique. It can take the punishment. The Exerpeutic 440XL has been tested up to 400 lbs user weight capacity allowing you to walk your way to fitness at any age and body size.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with a 1.5 Horse Power High Torque Motor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Utilizes \'Quite Drive\' which reduces any noise when walking&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Speed adjusts in increments of 1/10\'s mph up to a maximum of 4mph&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Belt has been widened to a fitness club size of 20 inches for safety and security&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra long 18-inch safety handles that are 2x the standard length&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Frame has been reinforced to accommodate a high weight capacity capability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Speed control buttons and on/off buttons are on the handle bars for convenience&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folds up easily for storage and can be wheeled around&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LCD display window features elapsed time, distance walked, calories burned, speed and pulse monitoring&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 51.2 inches long x 32 inches wide x 63 inches high&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: 5 year Limited Distributor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: Plastic, Steel, Mesh&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model Number: 1020&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly: Assembled&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Console Display Type: LCD&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folding Treadmill: Folding&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heart Rate Monitoring: Pulse Grips Only&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Portability: Portable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stride Adjustability: Non-Adjustible Stride&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tread Cushioning: Standard&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Treadmill Running Surface Length: 50 to 60 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight Capacity: 351 - 400 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Exerpeutic 440XL Fitness Walking Electric Treadmill', 'Exerpeutic 440XL Fitness Walking Electric Treadmill', 'Exerpeutic 440XL Fitness Walking Electric Treadmill'),
(10117, 1, 'Exerpeutic 350 Fitness Walking Electric Treadmill', '&lt;p&gt;Improve your health and endurance with this Paradigm Fitness electric walking treadmill. This heavy-duty treadmill supports up to 350 pounds, has a ground level surface, and a speed range of 0.4 to four miles-per-hour. The extra-long handles serve as a safety measure to cut down on the chances of you falling during your workout. The treadmill weighs only 110 pounds, making it easy to move when not in use. This treadmill is ideal if you\'re just starting a workout regiment because this workout device allows you to start at a slow speed and work your way up to a faster setting as your strength improves.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sports equipment is designed for fitness walking and supports a higher weight capacity, up to 350 pounds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Treadmill features extra-long safety handles for walking security and balance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Features a heavy-duty frame to support additional weight capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ground level walking surface and wide side rails for easy on and off&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Powered by a 1.5-horsepower motor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Speed range of 0.4 to 4 mph&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Excellent for vigorous fitness walking&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 47 inches long x 29 inches wide x 51 inches high&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product weight: 110 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 47 inches long x 29 inches wide x 51 inches high&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: 5 year Limited Distributor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: Steel and Plastic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model Number: 1010&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly: Assembled&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Console Display Type: LCD&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Portability: Stationary&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stride Adjustability: Non-Adjustible Stride&lt