(10135, 1, 'NewAir AC-12000H 12,000 BTU Portable Conditioner with Heat 115V', '&lt;p&gt;This NewAir portable AC lets you heat and cool rooms up to 425 sq. ft. With the convenience of 4 appliances in one, you get complete control of your indoor environment - heat, cool, dehumidify, and circulate the air at a fraction of the cost. It features an energy-efficient auto-evaportive cooling system plus a powerful heat pump for spot heating. Offering adjustable louvers, 2 fan speeds, a convenient remote control, and a go-anywhere portable design, this AC is effective and efficient.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LCD control panel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fan only option&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dehumidifying capabilities&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AC, heater, and fan&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;64-90 degrees F cooling temperature&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;425 sq. ft. coverage area&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;24 hour timer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 fan speeds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Our SKU number(s): NewAir AC-12000H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The manufacturer model number(s): NewAir AC-12000H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications for the Newair AC-12000H:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Amps: 11&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: Newair&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cooling BTU: 12000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electrical: 115 V&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model: AC-12000H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;15 5/9&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;29 1/3&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Length:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;14 37/100&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Ship Weight: 71.45 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UPC:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;854001004129&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty Terms - Parts: 1 Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wattage:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;1166&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt