(10134, 1, 'Bissell 86T3 Big Green Deep Cleaner', '&lt;p&gt;Get your home cleaned up with this Bissell professional-grade carpet cleaner that will get high-quality results. This Big Green Deep Cleaner features a tough stain tool for the hard-to-clean spots and will bring professional quality into your hands. Get your floors cleaner than ever before with the Bissell professional-grade carpet cleaner. Whether you are freshening up a little-used room in preparation for guests, or need to deep clean a high traffic area, the powerful carpet cleaner will provide the results you and your family need to comfortably enjoy your home.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: Plastic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 20 inches long x 11 inches wide x 42 inches high&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;9-foot hose and tough stain tool&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cord reach: 25 feet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 25 pounds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cleans in forward and reverse&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Large capacity removable tanks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flow indicator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy to clean brush roll&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ergonomically designed and adjustable handles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes: One (1) deep cleaning formula, One (1) long reach hose, One (1) tough stain tool&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1 year Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: Plastic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model Number: 86T3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly: Assembled&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Bissell 86T3 Big Green Deep Cleaner', 'Bissell 86T3 Big Green Deep Cleaner', 'Bissell 86T3 Big Green Deep Cleaner'),
(10120, 1, 'Ironman ATIS 4000 Inversion Table', '&lt;p&gt;Intensify your workout routine the smart way with this Ironman ATIS 4000 inversion table. Simple, sleek design features an adjustable seat, adjustable height, and a max holding weight of over 300 pounds. The Ironman ATIS is serious about helping you work your abs while reducing the risk of back pain.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Improve your fitness and athletic performance with this Ironman ATIS 4000 inversion table&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;With the benefits of inversion training, this is the perfect core exercise machine&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exercise machine will help reduce back stress, strengthen your abs, stimulate blood flow and more&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Inversion table will also increase flexibility and improve sport performance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Abdominal muscles are trained more effectively with the ATIS 4000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Features:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable user height from 147 cm to 198 cm (4.83 feet to 6.5 feet)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Supports up to 145.1 kg (320 pounds)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Patented \'smartgear\' locking system has 10 different inversion positions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ratchet ankle lock system with comforter ankle pads&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra large foot platform&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6.35 cm (2.5 inches) of memory foam backrest&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Foam covered steel safety handles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions:&amp;nbsp;62 in. H x 35 in. W x 58 in. L&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials:&amp;nbsp;Memory foam back, steel frame&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model Number:&amp;nbsp;5903&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shape:&amp;nbsp;Oval&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly:&amp;nbsp;Assembly Required&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fitness Machine Weight Capacity Range:&amp;nbsp;301 - 350 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Portability:&amp;nbsp;Portable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight Capacity:&amp;nbsp;301 - 350 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Ironman ATIS 4000 Inversion Table', 'Ironman ATIS 4000 Inversion Table', 'Ironman ATIS 4000 Inversion Table'),
(10121, 1, 'Intel Core i7 4820K Quad-Core 3.70 GHz Processor - Socket LGA2011', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;An entirely new platform!&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nProcessor integration and manufacturing take huge leaps forward in the latest Intel® microarchitecture (codename Haswell). As the first new microarchitecture on the 22nm manufacturing process, it marks the arrival of a new 4th gen Intel® Core™ platform, which comprises 4th gen Intel Core processors and the Intel® 8 Series chipset family (codename Lynx Point).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Information:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Processor Manufacturer: Intel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Processor Core: Quad-core (4 Core)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Clock Speed: 3.70 GHz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overclocking Speed: 3.90 GHz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Direct Media Interface: 5 GT/s&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;L1 Cache: 256 KB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;L2 Cache: 1 MB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;L3 Cache: 10 MB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;64-bit Processing: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Process Technology: 22 nm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Processor Technology: Enhanced SpeedStep Technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Processor Socket: Socket R LGA-2011&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;General Information:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer: Intel Corporation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Part Number: BX80633I74820K&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Website Address: http://www.intel.com&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand Name: Intel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Line: Core i7&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Series: i7-4800&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Model: i7-4820K&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Name: Core i7 Quad-core i7-4820K 3.7GHz Desktop Processor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Package Type: Retail&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Type: Processor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Power Descrip