(10127, 1, 'Safavieh Hand-woven Weaves Natural-colored Fine Sisal Rug 9 x12 ft.', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Complete your home decor with a hand-woven area rug&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Casual rug features rich shades of beige&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rug is constructed of 100-percent natural jute&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Innately soft and durable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Will add a warm accent to any decor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fringeless borders give a clean, elegant look and feel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Professional cleaning recommended&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pile measures 1/4 inch high&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Primary color: Beige&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pattern: Solid&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specs:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 9 ft. x 12 ft.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: Jute&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model Number: NF447A-9&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Brown Natural&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Style: Casual Contemporary Southwestern&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Jute&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pattern: Border Geometric Solid&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weave Type: Hand-Woven&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shape: Rectangle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rug Type: Indoor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tip: We recommend the use of a non-skid pad to keep the rug in place on smooth surfaces.&lt;/b&gt; Feel the hand-crafted quality every time you step on this woven rug by Safavieh. Crafted with a tight weave of fine natural sisal, this rug adds texture and style to any casual room. The quality of the design and materials ensure durability and beauty that last for years to come.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;i&gt;All rug sizes are approximate. Due to the difference of monitor colors, some rug colors may vary slightly. O.co tries to represent all rug colors accurately. Please refer to the text above for a description of the colors shown in the photo.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Saf