(10128, 1, 'Body Solid GCAB-360 Cam Series AB and Back Machine', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unique dual-function machine allows you to exercise both the stomach and the back&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Innovative plate-load design is based on health club single stationary machines&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exercise equipment features commercial grade steel frame&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Full-range cam design has an easy-to-use pop pin that allows an additional 26 adjustments to increase and control your range-of-motion&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Break-through technology lets you tighten abdominal muscles, strengthen your lower back and increase flexibility&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight plate post is 1-inch diameter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specs:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model Number: GCAB360&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Type: Home Gyms&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Equipment: Core Benches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly: Assembled&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Elliptical Resistance: Eddy-Current&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fitness Machine Weight Capacity Range: 301 - 350 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hand Weight: 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Incline: 13 to 15 percent&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: 1 year Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Body Solid GCAB-360 Cam Series AB and Back Machine', 'Body Solid GCAB-360 Cam Series AB and Back Machine', 'Body Solid GCAB-360 Cam Series AB and Back Machine'),
(10129, 1, 'SPT UF-304SS Stainless Steel Upright Freezer', '&lt;p&gt;Add some much needed freezer space to your home, or keep some cold beverages closer with this compact and versatile freezer. Offering three cubic feet of space, this freezer adds just the right amount of cold storage. This freezer has an energy saving feature to help lower your energy bill. The freezer has two bins for separation and storage, and there is a key to lock the unit. The freezer is constructed of stainless steel for durability, and you can easily adjust the temperature at any time.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: SPT&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Included items: Two (2) wire baskets, key&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Type: Upright freezer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Finish: Stainless steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color options: Stainless steel door with black cabinet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Style: Traditional&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Settings: Adjustable thermostat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Display: None&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy saver&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wattage: 126-watts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity: 3 cubic feet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Dimensions: 19.375 inches wide x 21.125 inches deep x 33.75 inches high&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: 1 year Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model Number: UF-304SS&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Black Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Style: Upright&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cord Length: More than 1 ft.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Features: Energy Star Compliant Variable Temperature Control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'SPT UF-304SS Stainless Steel Upright Freezer', 'SPT UF-304SS Stainless Steel Upright Freezer', 'SPT UF-304SS Stainless Steel Upright Freezer'),
(10130, 1, 'Brondell S900-EW Swash 900 Bidet Seat - Elongated, White', '&lt;p&gt;This heated bidet toilet seat is eco-friendly with a remote control for easy adjustment. This bidet features a heated wash system that cleans all areas while being easy to use.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Available in round and elongated&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 23 inches long x 20 inches wide x 8 inches high&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: Plastic, electronics&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of boxes this will ship in: One&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Posterior and feminine warm-water washes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Eco-friendly instant ceramic heating system for unlimited warm water&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Twin adjustable stainless steel nozzles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Water and seat temperature settings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Water pressure controls&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Aerated wash spray with width adjustment (three levels)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Intelligent body sensor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wireless remote control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stylish design and comfortable seat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\'Quick release\' for easy seat removal and cleaning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Gentle-closing seat and lid&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic power-save mode&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Reduce resources wasted on toilet paper&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Make conservation an effortless habit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic eco-mode conserves energy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy to install and use&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easily replaces existing toilet seats&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fits most toilets&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Intuitive wireless remote controls&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Refreshing and hygienic warm water washes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual stainless steel wands for front and rear cleansing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Eliminate hand contact with bacteria&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Provides independence for seniors and children&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Model Options:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;S900-EW /Elongated&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;S900-RW / Round&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 20.0 x 15.0 x 6.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: 1 year Limited Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: Plastic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Style: Solid&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Plastic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly: Assembled&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Features: &amp;nbsp;Includes Hardware&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Toilet Seat Shape: &amp;nbsp;Elongated/Round&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Once opened this item cannot be returned.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Brondell S900-EW Swash 900 Bidet Seat - White', 'Brondell S900-EW Swash 900 Bidet Seat - White', 'Brondell S900-EW Swash 900 Bidet Seat - White'),
(10131, 1, 'Breville BOV800XL Toaster Oven with Element IQ', '&lt;p&gt;Make mornings easy with this handy toaster oven. Toast up to six pieces of bread at one time, and feed your entire family quickly. This toaster oven cooks everything from pizza to cookies without you preheating your conventional oven. The nine preset programs let you cook numerous foods with just the touch of a button. This toaster oven\'s non-stick interior means you can spend more time cooking delicious food than cleaning up afterwards. This convenient countertop toaster oven takes up as little space as possible, making it ideal for small apartments or office kitchens. Toast your bagel, reheat your lunch or even bake some cookies with this clever toaster oven.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Breville Toaster Oven puts the power where it\'s needed most and delivers the right power at the right time&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smart oven can cook up to six (6) slices of toast&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Appliance has an element IQ&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Nine (9) preset programs, toast, bagel, bake, roast, broil, pizza, cookies, reheat and warm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Non-stick interior&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measures 22.5 inches wide x 17.3 inches deep x 14.625 inches high&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Dimensions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;: &lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt; 18.5 x 16.2 x 11.2 inches ; 30 pounds&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specs:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: Stainless Steel &amp;amp; Nonstick Interior&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model Number: BOV800XL&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Silver&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity: 6-Slice&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly: Assembled&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cord Length: More than 1 ft.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Features: Variable Temperature Control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Breville BOV800XL Toaster Oven with Element IQ', 'Breville BOV800XL Toaster Oven with Element IQ', 'Breville BOV800XL Toaster Oven with Element IQ');
