(10132, 1, 'GE JVM7195SFSS 1.9 Cu. ft. Stainless Steel Over the Range Microwave', '&lt;p&gt;This GE Over the Range Sensor Microwave oven is easy to use. The built-in sensor controls take all the guesswork out of microwave cooking by automatically adjusting time and power settings. This microwave even helps plan meals with a feature called the USDA MyPlate menu that provides healthy pre-programmed food options and recipes. Pop a few vegetables in the microwave, and use the steam cook button for steamed vegetables or your other favorite steamed dish. The recessed turntable with on and off controls allows food to cook evenly every time. Large quantities fit easily in the microwave when the oven rack is removed. Fourteen one-touch settings make it easy to create a perfectly cooked dish.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sensor cooking controls automatically adjust time and power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steam cook button lets you perfectly prepare your steamed favorites&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: GE&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Included items: One (1) over the range microwave&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Type: Microwave&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Finish: Stainless steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color options: Stainless steel, white, black, bisque, slate, stainless steel with black case&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Style: Modern&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-speed 300-CFM venting system removes smoke, steam and odors&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Recessed turntable with on/off controls turntable operation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable oven rack to cook large quantities&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Child lock&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Defrost&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extend cook&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum cooking time&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;14 one-touch settings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 30 inches long x 15 inches wide x 16 inches high&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1 year Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: metal&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model Number: JVM7195SFSS&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Stainless Steel with Black Case&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity: 1.6 - 2.0 cf&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Features: Clock Display Variable Temperature Control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wattage: 1000-1500 Watts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'GE JVM7195SFSS 1.9 Cu. ft. Stainless Steel Over the Range Microwave', 'GE JVM7195SFSS 1.9 Cu. ft. Stainless Steel Over the Range Microwave', 'GE JVM7195SFSS 1.9 Cu. ft. Stainless Steel Over the Range Microwave'),
(10133, 1, 'Bradley BTDS76P 4-rack Digital Smoker', '&lt;p&gt;Perfect for entertaining, creating gourmet foods in your own home, or just enjoying the flavor that smoking brings, this Bradley 4-rack Digital Smoker offers an easier and better way to automatically roast, smoke and barbecue in the outdoors. Create your own mouth-watering foods easily with this smoker. An upgrade from the original Bradley Smoker, this unit now uses digital technology that allows you to monitor temperature, time and smoke precisely, giving you complete control over how your food turns out. Constructed of a powder-epoxy steel exterior and a polished stainless-steel interior, this smoker is built to last for many years to come.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4-rack Digital Smoker includes all the features of the Original Bradley Smoker&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Now with the benefits of digital technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Temperature, time, and smoke are now completely controllable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;You can decide how much smoke you want, how long your food is going to be smoked for, and at what temperature&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: Bradley&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Powder epoxy steel exterior/polished stainless steel interior&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity: 520 square inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 14 inches wide x 17 inches deep x 31 inches high&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1 year Limited Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: epoxy steel, stainless steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model Number: BTDS76P&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Type: Cookware Accessories Smokers Specialty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly: Assembled&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Bradley BTDS76P 4-rack Digital Smoker', 'Bradley BTDS76P 4-rack Digital Smoker', 'Bradley BTDS76P 4-rack Digital Smoker'),
(10136, 1, 'Saeco RI9367/47 Via Venezia Stainless Steel Manual Espresso Machine', '&lt;p&gt;The Via Venezia manual espresso machine from Saeco gives you the enjoyment of crafting your favorite espresso beverages right from your home. With a cup warmer and simple brew and steam functions, this espresso maker will become an essential part of your daily routine.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cup warmer function&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Filter holder: Pressurized for rich layered crema&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hot water/ steam nozzle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Interface: Direct buttons&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ESE pod adapter suitable for pre-packaged shots&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pannarello: Plastic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Simultaneous brewing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Silvertone&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials and finishing: Stainless steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Technical specifications&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Boiler material: Inox&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Technical data&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power: 950-watt&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pump Pressure: 15 bar&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product dimensions: 10.6 inches long x 14.7 inches deep x 13.5 inches high&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 18 pounds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Water tank capacity: 2-9 liters&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;&quot;&gt;Material:&amp;nbsp;Stainless Steel&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;&quot;&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: O&lt;/span&gt;ne-year limited warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Saeco RI9367/47 Via Venezia Stainless Steel Manual Espresso Machine', 'Saeco RI9367/47 Via Venezia Stainless Steel Manual Espresso Machine', 'Saeco RI9367/47 Via Venezia Stainless Steel Manual Espresso Machine'),
(10137, 1, 'Abu Garcia Ambassadeur Morrum ZX', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;10 stainless steel HPCR™ bearings + 1 roller bearing provides increased corrosion protection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Machined aluminum frame and sideplates provides strength without excess weight&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Carbon Matrix™ drag system provides smooth, consistent drag pressure across the entire drag range&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Infinitely Variable Centrifugal Brake (IVCB-IV™) gives very precise brake adjustments allowing anglers to easily cast a wide variety of baits&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Infini II™ spool design for extended castability and extreme loads&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Not just any reel has what it takes to bear the Mörrum name - introducing the new Mörrum ZX. From its machined aluminum frame and sideplates to bent carbon handle and flat EVA knobs, no detail was spared in designing the ultimate round reel. Compact design coupled with the renowned Infinitely Variable Centrifugal Brake (IVCB-IV™ ) system enables anglers to cast ultra-lightweight lures with precision accuracy and control.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Made in Sweden.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Abu Garcia Ambassadeur Morrum Zx', 'Abu Garcia Ambassadeur Morrum Zx', 'Abu Garcia Ambassadeur Morrum Zx'),
(10138, 1, 'Abu Garcia Revo Beast', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;X-Cräftic™ alloy frame and sideplates for increased corrosion resistance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;7 stainless steel HPCR™ bearings + 1 roller bearing provides increased corrosion protection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Titanium coated sideplates provide increased scratch resistance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extended bent handle for increased cranking power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Round EVA knob provides improved grip for improved cranking power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Carbon Matrix™ drag system provides smooth, consistent drag pressure across the entire drag range&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Duragear™ brass gear for extended gear life&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Infini™ brake system allows almost limitless adjustability to handle any fishing situation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ti coated line guide reduces friction and improves durability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Infini II™ spool design for extended castability and extreme loads&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;D2 Gear Design™ provides a more efficient gear system while improving gear durability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Corrosion resistant instant anti reverse bearing provides greater protection&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Made in Sweden.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&quot;The Revo® Beast raises the bar when it comes to high performance and durability in a low profile design. Engineered for strength from the ground up, the Beast features titanium coated sideplates, 7 stainless steel HPCR™ bearings + 1 roller bearing as well as an X-Cräftic™ alloy frame for increased durability and corrosion resistance. A max drag rating of 22lbs along with the dependable Duragear™ brass main gear and the tried-and-true Carbon Matrix™ drag deliver impressive power and durability in a surprisingly compact package. &amp;nbsp;Get the upper hand on hard fighting fish with the extended bent handle and round EVA power knob. The Infini casting brake incorporates the use of both an internal centrifugal brake as well as an externally adjustable magnetic brake to give anglers almost limitless adjustability. &quot;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Abu Garcia Revo Beast', 'Abu Garcia Revo Beast', 'Abu Garcia Revo Beast'),
(10139, 1, 'Abu Garcia Revo Rocket Low Profile', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;10 stainless steel HPCR™ bearings + 1 roller bearing provides increased corrosion protection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rocket gear ratio provides superfast line retrieve for picking up line quickly&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;X-Cräftic™ alloy frame and sideplates for increased corrosion resistance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Carbon MatrixTM drag system provides smooth, consistent drag pressure across the entire drag range&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;D2 Gear Design™ provides a more efficient gear system while improving gear durability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Infini™ brake system allows almost limitless adjustability to handle any fishing situation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Infini II™ spool design for extended castability and extreme loads&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;You have never experienced speed like this before - rocket fast retrieve with smooth performance. An impressive 37 inches of line retrieve per turn of the crank handle makes the new Rocket the fastest low profile in the Revo lineup. Whether you are walking-the-dog with topwater lures or burning up spinnerbaits, buzzbaits or crankbaits, the Revo Rocket delivers the ultimate package for techniques requiring a quick retrieve.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Made in Sweden.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Abu Garcia Revo Rocket Low Profile', 'Abu Garcia Revo Rocket Low Profile', 'Abu Garcia Revo Rocket Low Profile'),
(10140, 1, 'GreenWorks 24322 DigiPro G-MAX 40V Cordless 185MPH Blower/Vacuum', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features &amp;amp; Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High Performance G-MAX 40V Lithium-Ion Battery delivers fade-free power with no memory loss after charging&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Powerful DigiPro brushless motor offers greater performance without the hassle of gas and carbon emission&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Variable speed dial along with a turbo button delivers on-demand power for up to 185 MPH of wind speed, which makes clearing your yard, driveway and patio effortless&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Up to 340 CFM of air flow makes blowing through dry/wet leaves and debris a breeze&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick and easy tool-less transition from blowing to vacuuming when the need arises leaves your yard looking pristine&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electric motor gets you started within seconds and eliminates the hassle of gas pull cords and hazardous fumes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lightweight at only 7.8 lbs with battery providing all the power with none of the fatigue&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible only with GreenWorks G-MAX 40V Battery Models 29462, 29472 and Charger 29482&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s in the Box?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;G-MAX 40V Cordless Digipro Blower/Vacuum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blower Tube&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Concentrator Tip&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vac Tube&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Collection Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4Ah battery (1)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Owner\'s Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specification:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model: 24322&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Source: G-MAX 40-Volt Lithium-Ion Battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Motor Type: Brushless&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Housing Material: Plastic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Certification(s): CSA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Collecting Bag Capacity : 1.2 Bushel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Speeds: Variable Dial&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;MPH: 185 MPH&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CFM: 340 CFM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vac Kit Included: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Impeller Material: Nylon&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Total Length/Width/Height: 32.5” x 8.75” x 11.75”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'GreenWorks 24322 DigiPro G-MAX 40V Cordless 185MPH Blower/Vacuum', 'GreenWorks 24322 DigiPro G-MAX 40V Cordless 185MPH Blower/Vacuum', 'GreenWorks 24322 DigiPro G-MAX 40V Cordless 185MPH Blower/Vacuum'),
(10141, 1, 'GreenWorks 25302 G-MAX 40V 20-Inch Twin Force Lawn Mower, Dual Blade', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Powerful G-MAX 40V Li-Ion Systems delivers greater efficiency with up to 70 minutes of run time with included: 40V Li-Ion 2Ah and 40V Li-Ion 4Ah battery along with compatible charger.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Innovative SMART CUT technology adjust for power or runtime based on the thickness of your grass&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual blades offer better cut quality, superior mulching and bagging capabilities&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic battery switchover pulls power from the second battery once the first is depleted to eliminate downtime&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5 position single lever height adjuster allows for a cutting height range of 1-3/8&quot; to 3-3/8&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2-in-1 feature offer versatile use with mulching and rear bagging capabilities&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Air flow tab on rear bag indicates when the bag is full and needs to be emptied&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy Fold System for storage or compact transportation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;10&quot; rear wheels and 7&quot; front wheels make it easy to maneuver through any range of terrain&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes two 40V batteries and a charger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Use with (2) G-MAX 40V 4 AH Li-Ion battery for up to 90 minutes of runtime&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible Only with GreenWorks G-MAX 40V Battery Models 29462, 29472 and Charger 29482&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s in the Box?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;G-MAX 40V 20-Inch Twin Force Mower&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rear Discharge Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mulch Plug&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Isolator Key&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) 4Ah Battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) 2Ah Battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Owner\'s Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;