(10157, 1, 'Haier HPN14XHM 14,000 BTU Portable Air Conditioner with Heat 115V', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;This 14,000 BTU portable air conditioner is ideal for spot cooling larger rooms up to 500 Sq. Ft. in the summer and providing supplemental heat in colder months. With 3 cool settings, 3 fan settings, 3 heat settings, a 24 hr on/off timer, and dehumidify mode, this single-hose model is equipped to meet your interior climate needs. A Quick-Install Window Kit is included for exhausting the unit through any horizontal or vertical opening window, and fully-directional casters provide mobility. Maintenance is minimal with a slide-out washable mesh filter, and Auto Evaporation technology makes manual draining unnecessary.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electronic with Full-function Remote Control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dehumidification Function&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3 Cooling and 3 Fan Speeds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extended Window Exhaust Kit Included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Our SKU number(s): Haier HPN14XHM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The manufacturer model number(s): Haier HPN14XHM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications for the Haier HPN14XHM:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Amps: 10.8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: Haier&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cooling BTU: 14,000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electrical:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;115 V. 1 Phase 60 Hz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heating BTU: 11,000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hose Type: Single&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model: HPN14XHM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth: 16 5/8&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height: 33 1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Length:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;20&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Ship Weight: 105 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UPC:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;688057403441&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty Terms - Parts: 1 Year&lt;/l