(10163, 1, 'Friedrich Dehumidifier with 70 Pint Capacity Removal - D70BP', '&lt;p&gt;Have a room or area that needs powerful dehumidification Friedrich has a line of ENERGY STAR qualified models that can extract 25, 50 or 70 pints of moisture every 24 hours. Larger capacity models D50AP and D70BP have built-in drain pumps that can pump condensation vertically or horizontally up to a combined distance of 15 feet. All three models provide continuous-drainage operation and can be set to precise humidity levels from 30% to 90%. Precise humidity control is so important that the EPA\'s proposed ENERGY STAR Version 2.1 Dehumidifier specification may require a digital humidity readout or dial.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in casters for easy mobility&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in drain pump can pump condensation vertically or horizontally up to a combined distance of 15 feet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;24-hour ON/OFF timer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Washable, slide-out filter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ENERGY STAR qualified&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic defrost cycle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Displays temperature in Fahrenheit or Celsius&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Displays room temperature and humidity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Top-mount, digital touch controls&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low ambient operation down to 41 Degrees Fahrenheit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2-speed fan&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Set humidity level from 30% to 90% RH&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable condensate bucket with carry handle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Continuous-drainage operation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Our SKU number(s): Friedrich D70BP&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The manufacturer model number(s): Friedrich D70BP&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications for the Friedrich D70BP:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: Friedrich&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity: 16.2 Pints&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electrical: 110/115 V. 1 Phase