(10164, 1, 'Broan QP3 series 42-inch Under Cabinet Range Hood - Stainless Steel', '&lt;p&gt;The EVOLUTION Series of QP Range Hoods has a contemporary style and sleek appearance that will complement any kitchen design. Easy to clean, brilliant lighting and quiet operation result in the perfect marriage of functionality.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Enclosed non-stick bottom pan ensures quick clean-up to make your work fast and easy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Choice of 3-1/4&quot; rectangular or 7&quot; round ducting ensures reliable discharge without repositioning the blower.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Optional remote control (BCR1 sold separately) has a magnetic base which allows you to position it wherever it is most convenient.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Enables operation of blower speed, lighting and delay-off features from across the room, so range hood operation is always at your fingertips.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Advanced Heat Sentry detects excessive heat and turns blower to high, prolonging product life and ensuring your confidence in range hood performance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Optional non-ducted installation requires CleanSense charcoal filters (BPPF sold separately), providing you the right choice of installation for your kitchen&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ultra quiet at less than 0.3 sones at Normal speed and only 5.0 sones at High speed, allows you to clear out cooking smoke and unwanted smells without disturbing the peace in your kitchen&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible with optional Broan-NuTone Make-up Air Dampers (MD6T or MD8T, sold separately) to fit 6&quot; or 8&quot; ducting and help to balance the air pressure when the range hood is in use, keeping your environment comfortable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Full filter design has an antimicrobial coating to inhibit the formation of odor-producing bacteria. Aluminum micro-mesh filters are dishwasher-safe to give you the confidence your kitchen will always smell fresh&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li