(10171, 1, 'August Bluetooth Smart Lock', '&lt;p&gt;The August Smart Lock gives you an intelligent, secure way to control access to your home from an app on your iPhone, iPod, or iPod touch. There\'s no longer a need for keys and codes; just tap on your iOS device to select who enters and who doesn\'t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Durable and reliable&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHoused in a stylish yet strong aluminum body, the August Smart Lock is powered by standard AA batteries that last a year and alert you when they’re low. So if your Wi-Fi, power, or cable goes down, you can still control and use the lock thanks to built-in Bluetooth Smart Ready technology.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security first&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAugust relies on the same, safe communications technology used by financial institutions. This advanced system lets you easily issue keys and specify who receives access to your home and for how long. For example, you can issue a key for a family member to allow anytime access or one for your housecleaner that is active for only a couple of hours a week. The app also shows you a full list of individuals who have access and when they enter or exit. Any changes you make take effect immediately.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Discreet installation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAugust mounts on the interior side of your door. Once it\'s installed, you can continue to unlock your current deadbolt with the original keys or start using the August app on your iOS device—whichever you prefer. The outside of the door remains unchanged.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Highlights:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Encrypted locking technology is safer than keys that can get lost or door codes that can be copied&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Replaces the interior portion of compatible deadbolts in about ten minutes; exterior door hardware is unchanged&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No wiring or electrical connections required&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Powered by four AA batteries, so it\'s always on—even if your power, Wi-Fi, or cable goes down&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;App alerts you when the battery gets low&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Complete control over who has access to your home and how long it lasts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Instantly invite family, friends, or services from your contacts lists and issue them keys in seconds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EverLock technology automatically locks your door behind you&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto-Unlock senses your approach and unlocks the door without you having to reach for your iOS device&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Share more than your keys; write thank you notes, leave instructions, and read comments from your virtual guestbook&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Did you notice?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bluetooth connectivity ensures that you can control the lock even if your power or Wi-Fi goes down.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s in the Box?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;August Smart Lock&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Baseplates and adapters for a single-cylinder deadbolt&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Four AA batteries&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Installation guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tech Specs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Source: Battery Power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 2.21 in./5.61 cm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 3.26 in./8.28 cm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 14 oz./396.89 g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Warranty:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One year limited warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'August Bluetooth Smart Lock', 'August Bluetooth Smart Lock', 'August Bluetooth Smart Lock'),
(10172, 1, 'Okidokeys Access-pack Bluetooth 4.0 Smart Lock System', '&lt;p&gt;OKIDOKEYS Access-Pack allows you to unlock your home door not only with Bluetooth 4.0-enabled smartphones, but also using any smartphones, cell phones and OKIDOKEYS RFID Smart-Tags (included). Share Smart-Tags with your family or friends, use them every day!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;More Info:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Enhance your existing lock with the world leading mobile key technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lock and unlock your home door with all authorized mobile phones (including non-smartphones) and OKIDOKEYS Smart-Tags&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Create, send and cancel mobile keys for family, friends and guests from anywhere, at anytime&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Authorize and cancel Smart-Tags for family, friends and guests&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Define specific time date appropriate access adapted to each user&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Receive notifications when your guests unlock your door&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Select between different opening rules for easier use&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unlock your door when you’re nearby with the hands free mode&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatically re-lock your door when closing it&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes a wireless doorbell (included in the Smart-Reader)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy to install: no drilling, no wiring&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Use OKIDOKEYS app and web portal with &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.okidokeys.com/content/18-okidokeys-licences&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;free Homekeys license&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The OKIDOKEYS Access-Pack includes:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Smart-Lock + user guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3 Smart-Lock covers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 metal plate + protective rubber gasket&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 sensor kit (confirms door open/close status)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Smart-Reader (white) + user guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 RFID Smart-Tag wallet size card&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 RFID Smart-Tag wristband&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 RFID Smart-Tag key-chain&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4 screws + screwdrivers kit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;7 AAA batteries&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Homekeys license&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Download:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.okidokeys.com/index.php?controller=attachment&amp;amp;id_attachment=1&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Smart-Reader Installation Guide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.okidokeys.com/index.php?controller=attachment&amp;amp;id_attachment=2&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Smart-Lock Installation Guide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.okidokeys.com/index.php?controller=attachment&amp;amp;id_attachment=3&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Smart-Lock Usage Guide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Okidokeys Access-pack Bluetooth 4.0 Smart Lock System', 'Okidokeys Access-pack Bluetooth 4.0 Smart Lock System', 'Okidokeys Access-pack Bluetooth 4.0 Smart Lock System'),
(10173, 1, 'Polar CS500+cad Cycling Monitor Black', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Measures distance traveled, elapsed time, speed, heart rate and more&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSo you can optimize each ride. Heart-rate-based target zones with alarms let you know when you\'re within an ideal range.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3 speed modes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEnable you to track your actual speed, overall average speed and maximum speed. The cadence tracker helps you evaluate your pace against speed and incline data, and the altimeter records elevation changes.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Power output sensor&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMeasures the force of every pedal stroke, so you know how much power your legs are producing.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Oversize, aerodynamic display&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nProvides clear, highly visible information in a variety of conditions.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dual-lock bike mount&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPlus rocker-switch operation gives you precise control, even at high speeds. The wireless design enables simple attachment to your bike\'s handlebars or stem.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty Terms - Parts: 1 year &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty Terms - Labor: 1 year &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 3 inches &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 2 inches &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth: 0.5 inches &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 0.5 pounds &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color Category: Black &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Body Metrics Measured: Speed|Distance traveled|Heart rate &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Clock Displ