.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Polar Dual Lock Bike Mount&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CS500 Getting Started Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CS speed sensor W.I.N.D. User Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CS cadence sensor W.I.N.D. User Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Polar CS500+cad Cycling Monitor Black', 'Polar CS500+cad Cycling Monitor Black', 'Polar CS500+cad Cycling Monitor Black'),
