(10184, 1, 'Anova Sous Vide Immersion Circulator - 120V Circulator Cooker - Black', '&lt;p&gt;Anova is the award-winning sous vide immersion circulator for the home chef. It features a 360° directional pump for maximum circulation, an easy-to-use touch screen display, and stainless steel parts. It is easy to disassemble and has a dishwasher-safe steel skirt.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Versatile and secure&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAnova was designed to give the home chef the flexibility needed to use it with a wide array of cooking equipment and the confidence to know that it will stay secure for hours.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Sturdy and secure clamp design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;1.25” max opening&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;3.5” of room between the minimum and maximum fill line&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Auto-shutdown and wet sensors for safety&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Built to last&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n“This thing feels solid as a rock. It\'s heavy, sturdy, and just a really tight feeling piece of hardware. It\'s made by a company with a long history of high-quality products, which shows in its no-nonsense, solid design.” Kenji Lopez, Serious Eats&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Stainless steel with removable wetted parts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Dishwasher safe steel skirt&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;System disassembly for easy cleaning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Simple and intuitive&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAnova’s LCD touchscreen display makes getting started as easy as 1-2-3. Set the temperature, set the timer, and press start.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;F &amp;amp; C programmable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Timer shut off&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Variable status displays for easy read-out&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Accurate, powerful and reliable&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAnova is packed with 1KW of power and a 360° directional pump for max circulation, giving you the ability to cook superbly even and perfectly consistent meals for a small get-together or a large dinner party.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Accurate to within a tenth of a degree&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Capacity of up to 22L&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Vectoring pump manages overcrowding bags&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Silenceometer for perfectly quiet operation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Temperature Range: 25°C to 99°C ± 0.01°C&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pump Speed: 12L/min Directional&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tank Capacity: Up to 22 Litres (5-6 Gallons)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Timer: 99 hours with auto shut off&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Safety: water level sensor for auto shut off&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 2.75&quot; x 2.75&quot; x 15.5&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max Clamp Opening: 1.25”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heating Power: 1kW&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Input: 115-120 VAC (220V-240V available Oct. 2013)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Limited Warranty: 1 year parts &amp;amp; labour&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Inside The Box: Anova immersion circulator; power cord and operating manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Anova Sous Vide Immersion Circulator - 120V Circulator Cooker - Black', 'Anova Sous Vide Immersion Circulator - 120V Circulator Cooker - Black', 'Anova Sous Vide Immersion Circulator - 120V Circulator Cooker - Black'),
