&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model: CP12G10A&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Plug Type:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;5-5P&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;21 3/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;15&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Length:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;23 5/8&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Ship Weight:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;93 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UPC:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;724587430325&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty Terms - Parts: 5 Years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wattage:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;1,060&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Friedrich CP12G10A&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Owners Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Info and Guides for the Friedrich CP12G10A:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.7999992370605px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://ankermart.com/image/guides/Friedrich-Window-Ac-Br.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Friedrich Brochure&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Friedrich CP12G10A 12,000 BTU 11.3 EER Chill Window Air Conditioner\r\n', 'Friedrich CP12G10A 12,000 BTU 11.3 EER Chill Window Air Conditioner\r\n', 'Friedrich CP12G10A 12,000 BTU 11.3 EER Chill Window Air Conditioner'),
(10190, 1, 'Samsung SB-330 Level Box Bluetooth Wireless Speaker - White', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://ankermart.com/Samsung-SB-330-Level-Box-Bluetooth-Wireless-Speaker-Black&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Also available in Black color!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wireless Speaker&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIntroducing the new Samsung Level Box wireless speaker. Stream your favorite music, podcasts or audio books from your Samsung Galaxy phone, tablet or any other Bluetooth compatible device, directly to the speaker for crystal-clear wireless sound.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No Cables, No Problem&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Level Box streams audio from any Bluetooth-compatible device for high quality playback on the go without the inconvenience of cables. Utilizing the advanced APT-X audio codec, the Samsung Level Box allows for real time streaming of the highest quality stereo audio over a Bluetooth connection. (To maximize the performance of the Level Box wireless speaker the source device must also incorporate the APT-X audio codec.)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Easy Pairing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nJust place a Near-Field Communications (NFC) enabled smartphone near the Level Box to quickly and easily make a connection. Devices without NFC capabilities can still be effortlessly connected through the speaker\'s one touch Bluetooth pairing system.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Exceptional Battery Life&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe built-in rechargeable battery boasts over 15 hours of playback on a single charge, ensuring your music is always ready when you are.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Built-In Speakerphone&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Level Box features advanced HD speakerphone functionality for streaming voice calls directly from your smartphone for hands free operation, making it great for conference calls or chatting with friends when your smartphone\'s speakerphone doesn\'t cut it.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Small Package&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSpeaker measures just 6 1/2” wide.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Battery Type: Up to 15 hrs. of playback&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatibility: Bluetooth and 3.5mm devices&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Package Contents:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Samsung SB-330 Bluetooth Speaker&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Travel Charger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3.5mm Aux. Cable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;User Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Samsung SB-330 Level Box Bluetooth Wireless Speaker - White', 'Samsung SB-330 Level Box Bluetooth Wireless Speaker - White', 'Samsung SB-330 Level Box Bluetooth Wireless Speaker - White'),
(10191, 1, 'Samsung Level On OG-900 Premium On-Ear Headphones - White/Black', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Premium On-Ear Headphones&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIntroducing the new Samsung Level On premium stereo headphones. The exceptional sound and classic design of these headphones make them the perfect companion to any device, including your Samsung tablet or Galaxy smartphone.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Balanced Sound&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDual diaphragm design with large 40mm drivers provides exceptionally clear sound with full dynamic range and powerful bass at any volume.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Designed for Comfort&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDesigned to maximize listening comfort, the Level On is great for long flights or an evening of music. The ultra-soft ear cushions and padded headband work with the lightly-tensioned frame for a fatigue-free listening experience.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In-Line Control&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAdjust the volume, pause/play, advance to the next track and control phone functionality from the convenient in-line, multi-function remote. S Voice enabled for easy touch and talk phone operation.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Carrying Case&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIncludes custom zippered carrying case.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Audio Out Port: 40mm Dual Diaphragm Speaker&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: White/Black&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Earbud Type: On-Ear Headphones&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Impedance: Impedance 32 ohms&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Package Contents:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;On-Ear Headphones&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Premium Carrying Case&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Detachable 3.5pi Cable with Integrated Remote and Airplane Adapte&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Samsung Level On OG-900 Premium On-Ear Headphones - White/Black', 'Samsung Level On OG-900 Premium On-Ear Headphones - White/Black', 'Samsung Level On OG-900 Premium On-Ear Headphones - White/Black'),
(10189, 1, 'Samsung SB-330 Level Box Bluetooth Wireless Speaker - Black', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://ankermart.com/Samsung-SB-330-Level-Box-Bluetooth-Wireless-Speaker-White&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;Also available in White color!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wireless Speaker&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIntroducing the new Samsung Level Box wireless speaker. Stream your favorite music, podcasts or audio books from your Samsung Galaxy phone, tablet or any other Bluetooth compatible device, directly to the speaker for crystal-clear wireless sound.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No Cables, No Problem&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Level Box streams audio from any Bluetooth-compatible device for high quality playback on the go without the inconvenience of cables. Utilizing the advanced APT-X audio codec, the Samsung Level Box allows for real time streaming of the highest quality stereo audio over a Bluetooth connection. (To maximize the performance of the Level Box wireless speaker the source device must also incorporate the APT-X audio codec.)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Easy Pairing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nJust place a Near-Field Communications (NFC) enabled smartphone near the Level Box to quickly and easily make a connection. Devices without NFC capabilities can still be effortlessly connected through the speaker\'s one touch Bluetooth pairing system.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Exceptional Battery Life&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe built-in rechargeable battery boasts over 15 hours of playback on a single charge, ensuring your music is always ready when you are.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Built-In Speakerphone&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Level Box features advanced HD speakerphone functionality for streaming voice calls directly from your smartphone for hands free operation, making it great for conference calls or chatting with friends when your smartphone\'s speakerphone doesn\'t cut it.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Small Package&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSpeaker measures just 6 1/2” wide.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Battery Type: Up to 15 hrs. of playback&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Black&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatibility: Bluetooth and 3.5mm devices&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Package Contents:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Samsung SB-330 Bluetooth Speaker&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Travel Charger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3.5mm Aux. Cable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;User Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Samsung SB-330 Level Box Bluetooth Wireless Speaker - Black', 'Samsung SB-330 Level Box Bluetooth Wireless Speaker - Black', 'Samsung SB-330 Level Box Bluetooth Wireless Speaker - Black');
