(10192, 1, 'Canary Wireless High-definition All-in-one Home Security System', '&lt;p&gt;Canary is a complete home security system packed into a single device—a modern approach to security that lets you protect the people and places you care about most.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SEE AND HEAR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nStream real-time video of your home with Canary’s 1080p HD camera, 147° wide-angle lens, night vision, and high-quality audio.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MORE THAN A CAMERA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nProtect your home with Canary’s 90+ dB siren, motion-activated recording, auto-arm/disarm, and optional professional monitoring.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HOMEHEALTH TECHNOLOGYTM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMonitor air quality, temperature, and humidity to help understand how your home might affect your health.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;INTELLIGENT NOTIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nReceive instant video alerts on your iOS or Android device. Easy options allow you to respond to incidents before they turn into emergencies.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NO INSTALLATION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSet up in minutes. Download the free iPhone or Android app, put Canary on a shelf or table, plug it in, connect to the internet, and you’re ready to go.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FREE CLOUD RECORDING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCanary works right out of the box and includes free cloud storage of recent events.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFind out about additional storage and call center options here:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://canary.is/plans&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://canary.is/plans&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Camera:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1080p HD Camera&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;147° Wide-angle lens&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic night vision&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Motion detection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sensors:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-axis accelerometer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ambient light&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacitive touch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HomeHealth Technology:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Temperature&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Humidity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Air quality&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Audio &amp;amp; Siren:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High-quality microphone&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in speaker&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;90+ dB siren&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Connectivity:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2.4GHz Wi-Fi (802.11 b/g/n)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wired Ethernet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Size/Weight &amp;amp; Power:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 6 in (152.4 mm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Diameter: 3 in (76.2 mm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 0.87 lb (396 g)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;100-240v power supply&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In the box:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One Canary device&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Secure setup cable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AC power adapter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Micro-USB cable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick Start guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements for Setup:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Broadband internet connection (1 Mbps upload recommended)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wi-Fi or Ethernet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Available power outlet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;iPhone 4s or newer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Android 4.0 or newer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Canary Wireless High-definition All-in-one Home Security System', 'Canary Wireless High-definition All-in-one Home Security System', 'Canary Wireless High-definition All-in-one Home Security System'),
(10194, 1, 'Schlage FE599CAM619ACC Keypad Lock With Lever Handle, Satin Nickel', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Schlage FE599CAM619ACC Keypad Lock With Lever Handle, Satin Nickel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Receive text or email alert when your family uses their codes, so you know who\'s home&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Grant access to your home when you can\'t be there with a scheduled code to let someone&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Add, delete or change user codes remotely&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Run the most important systems in your home-thermostats, locks, lights and cameras from anywhere with Z-Wave technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;This Z-Wave enabled product allows for wireless communication to other Z-Wave products in your home&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Details&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Item model number: FE599CAM619ACC&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Item Weight: 5.2 pounds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Dimensions: 3.1 x 3.1 x 8.1 inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Batteries:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;3 AA batteries required. (included)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Satin Nickel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Style: Traditional&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Finish: Satin Nickel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Batteries Included: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Batteries Required: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Average Battery Life: 17520 hours&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: Limited lifetime mechanical and finish warranty, 1 year electronics warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Includes&lt;/strong&gt;: Schlage FE599CAM619ACC keypad lever; two keys; operating and installation instructions&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Schlage FE599CAM619ACC Keypad Lock With Lever Handle, Satin Nickel', 'Schlage FE599CAM619ACC Keypad Lock With Lever Handle, Satin Nickel', 'Schlage FE599CAM619ACC Keypad Lock With Lever Handle, Satin Nickel'),
(10195, 1, 'Kwikset Kevo SmartKey Single-Cylinder Entry Door Deadbolt w Bluetooth', '&lt;p&gt;Kevo SmartKey Venetian Bronze Single-Cylinder Motorized Electronic Entry Door Deadbolt with Bluetooth&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Your smartphone is now your key&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Touch to open convenience&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Send eKeys via your smartphone&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Receive notifications and manage lock and eKeys through Kevo mobile app&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SmartKey deadbolt cylinder for superior security and backup traditional key&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy to install, no power or internet required&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Kevo app is available for iPhone 4s, 5, 5C, 5S, 6 &amp;amp; 6 plus and 5th generation iPod touch, 3rd generation or higher iPad/iPad mini&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Kevo is now available on iOS and select Android 5.0, Lollipop devices&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Color Option:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model: 925 KEVO DB L03 &amp;nbsp;/ Polished Brass&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model: 925 KEVO DB 15 &amp;nbsp; / Satin Nickel&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model: 925 KEVO DB 11P / Venetian Bronze&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Collection Name: Kevo&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Cylinders: 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Re-Key Technology: SmartKey&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Keyway: K&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Solid Brass&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Commercial / Residential: Residential&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Backset Size: Adjustable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fits Door Thickness: 1-3/8-in to 1-3/4-in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Projection (Inches): 1.3125&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bolt Type: Motorized&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Keypad Included&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of User C