(10208, 1, 'Gtech AirRam High-power Cordless Vacuum Cleaner', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Introducing the Ultra Lightweight AirRam, The Perfect Vacuum.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe AirRam weighs less than a gallon of orange juice, half the weight of most vacuums. Find out what effortless cleaning really means. No attachments or adjustments needed to move from carpet, to rugs, to hard floors. Discover how the AirRam’s low profile and swivel steering makes for easy cleaning under the sofa and bed.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The innovative Gtech AirRam will change the way you vacuum your home forever, making cleaning faster, easier and more convenient.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High performance and versatile cleaning on carpet, hard floors and tiled floors and it weighs only 7.7 pounds.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Clean the average home on one 4 hour charge with up to 40 minutes of run time with 22V Lithium-ion technology.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The AirRam is bag-less with lifetime washable filters. No expensive replacements required.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Powerful rotating brush bars make it ideal for pet hair.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AirRam for powerful all surface floor cleaning.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe AirRam is incredibly light weight, but cleaning power is what really matters. Whether it’s ground in dirt on the carpet, pet hair in the rug, paper clips on the office floor or moist pea &amp;amp; corn nibbles in the kitchen. The AirRam has the power to devour mess while grooming your carpets.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AirRam high performance, ultra-lightweight vacuum&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;22v Lithium-Ion battery (up to 40 minutes runtime)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Premium Filter&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AC Charger&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Swivel Steering&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dust Bin&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2-year warranty by Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AirRam - How It Works: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aYv3vxML4PA&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aYv3vxML4PA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAirRam - See It In Action: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UBBRWsv8PYI&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UBBRWsv8PYI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Gtech AirRam High-power Cordless Vacuum Cleaner', 'Gtech AirRam High-power Cordless Vacuum Cleaner', 'Gtech AirRam High-power Cordless Vacuum Cleaner'),
(10209, 1, 'Gtech AirRam Upright Vacuum and Multi Handheld Cleaning System', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Introducing the Ultra Lightweight AirRam, The Perfect Vacuum.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe AirRam weighs less than a gallon of orange juice, half the weight of most vacuums. Find out what effortless cleaning really means. No attachments or adjustments needed to move from carpet, to rugs, to hard floors. Discover how the AirRam’s low profile and swivel steering makes for easy cleaning under the sofa and bed.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The innovative Gtech AirRam will change the way you vacuum your home forever, making cleaning faster, easier and more convenient.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High performance and versatile cleaning on carpet, hard floors and tiled floors and it weighs only 7.7 pounds.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Clean the average home on one 4 hour charge with up to 40 minutes of run time with 22V Lithium-ion technology.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The AirRam is bag-less with lifetime washable filters. No expensive replacements required.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Powerful rotating brush bars make it ideal for pet hair.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AirRam for powerful all surface floor cleaning.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe AirRam is incredibly light weight, but cleaning power is what really matters. Whether it’s ground in dirt on the carpet, pet hair in the rug, paper clips on the office floor or moist pea &amp;amp; corn nibbles in the kitchen. The AirRam has the power to devour mess while grooming your carpets.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The perfect vacuum system: Introducing the ultra-lightweight AirRam, plus Multi.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe AirRam weighs less than a gallon of orange juice, half the weight of most vacuums. Find out what effortless cleaning really means. The Multi is a powerful, compact canister vacuum designed as a handheld. The Multi’s built in retractable suction hose gets you into tight, hard to reach spaces that conventional handhelds simply can’t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Multi for floor to ceiling cleaning and everywhere in between.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMulti has on board, performance-based cleaning tools that you will use instead of lose.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Multi has not one, but two built in high-beam cleaning lights. See what you are doing in dimly lit areas. Perfect for vacuuming the interior of your car, in cabinets and between the cushions of your furniture. Second is the built in high performance dusting brush that is simply impossible to lose. Third is the on board crevice tool to clean baseboard, mouldings and hard to get to places. Lastly, is our specially designed upholstery brush that flexes to the contours of your sofa and chairs.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Best of all the AirRam &amp;amp; Multi are powered by Advance Cordless!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n“Advance Cordless” is the latest technology that is used to power full size electric cars that travel over 200 hundred miles on a single charge. No more plugging and unplugging the vacuum as you move room to room. No more cord getting caught on a corner or piece of furniture. No more cord winding. The AirRam can clean a 2000 square foot house on a single charge. “Advance Cordless” technology also means that Multi charges fully in just 4-hours and lasts for up to 30 minutes from a single charge.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AirRam high performance, ultra-lightweight vacuum&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;22v Lithium-Ion battery (up to 40 minutes runtime)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Premium Filter&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AC Charger&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Swivel Steering&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dust Bin&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2-year warranty by Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi high-performance handheld vacuum&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;14&quot; Multi extension tube&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;AirRam &amp;nbsp;- How It Works: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aYv3vxML4PA&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aYv3vxML4PA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAirRam - See It In Action: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UBBRWsv8PYI&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UBBRWsv8PYI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gtech Multi - How It Works: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VOp_QERpbFc&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VOp_QERpbFc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGtech Multi - See the Multi in Action: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fSQymSuPX4Y&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fSQymSuPX4Y&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Gtech AirRam Upright Vacuum and Multi Handheld Cleaning System', 'Gtech AirRam Upright Vacuum and Multi Handheld Cleaning System', 'Gtech AirRam Upright Vacuum and Multi Handheld Cleaning System'),
(10214, 1, 'Weslo Cadence G 5.9 Treadmill', '&lt;p&gt;Get more results in less time with the Weslo Cadence G 5.9 treadmill. Featuring 6 Personal Trainer Workouts, a 2-position manual incline and Comfort Cell™ Cushioning, this treadmill is the perfect tool for losing weight or increasing performance. Each workout is designed by a Certified Personal Trainer so you can maximize your time and get a great workout! The incline is easy to change and will increase the intensity of your workout. And, with the addition of Comfort Cell™ Cushioning, you\'ll stay comfortable throughout each stride. The Weslo Cadence G 5.9 is right for you!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Easy Pulse™ Heart Rate Monitor&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGet an accurate heart rate reading by simply placing your thumb on the Easy Pulse™ sensor that is built right into the console.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Blue-Tinted LCD with Priority Display&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTrack your workout results with this easy-to-read blue-tinted LCD with Priority Display. This display tracks your speed, time, distance and calories burned so you can monitor your progress throughout your workout.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Comfort Cell ™ Cushioning&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nReduce stress on your joints and increase workout comfort with this unique treadmill deck, designed with a layer of cushioning for maximum stride impact absorption.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Warranty&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Weslo Cadence G 5.9 is protected with a 1-Year Motor Warranty and 90 Days Parts &amp;amp; Labor.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6 Personal Trainer Workouts&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBurn fat, lose weight and stay motivated with Personal Trainer Workouts. These programs take the guesswork out of your workout by automatically adjusting the speed and incline of the treadmill for increased intensity.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model: WLTL29609&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Motor: 2.25 HP Impulse™ Motor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Incline: 2-Position Manual Incline&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Treadbelt: 16&quot; x 50&quot; Treadbelt&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;QuickSpeed™ Control: 0–10 MPH QuickSpeed™ Control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight Capacity: 250 lb. Weight Capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Footprint: 64.5&quot;-L X 29&quot;-W X 55.5&quot;-H&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Weslo Cadence G 5.9 Treadmill', 'Weslo Cadence G 5.9 Treadmill', 'Weslo Cadence G 5.9 Treadmill'),
(10215, 1, 'Weider Ultimate Body works Home Gym &amp; Cable and Pulley', '&lt;p&gt;Designed for a total body workout, the new and improved Weider® Ultimate Body Works is perfect for both upper and lower body workouts. It strengthens muscles and enhances flexibility. The Weider Home Gym features an incline bench with wheels that can be adjusted to the desired position with the help of pulleys on both sides. By adjusting this bench, you can increase or decrease the weight resistance suitable to your body weight. The Weider home gym features a compact space-saving design that makes it the perfect full body workout equipment for home use.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Adjustable Incline Bench&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAdjustable incline bench on wheels with a pulley on each side. Adjust the bench to a steeper incline to increase the amount of weight resistance.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Resistance Bands&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nProvides the option to increase weight resistance up to 50-pounds with the addition of the four resistance bands.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cable &amp;amp; Pulley System&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAllow for greater versatility and greater range of motion. Resistance bands increase weight resistance beyond the users own body weight.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Exercise Chart&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWeider® Ultimate Body Works conveniently folds for easy storage.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Full-body home-gym exercise system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Targets upper and lower body&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable incline bench&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Increase or decrease weight resistance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Resistance bands increase weight up to 50lb.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cable-and-pulley system allows for greater range of motion&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exercise chart&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compact, space-saving design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 71”x26.5”x49.5”; 75lb.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Weider Ultimate Body works Home Gym &amp; Cable and Pulley', 'Weider Ultimate Body works Home Gym &amp; Cable and Pulley', 'Weider Ultimate Body works Home Gym &amp; Cable and Pulley'),
(10216, 1, 'HP F800x Full HD Wi-Fi GPS Car Dashboard Video Recorder Camera &amp; KIT', '&lt;p&gt;Enhance the capabilities of your vehicle with the HP f800x Full HD Wi-Fi GPS Car Dashboard Video Recorder Camera. This premium full HD 1080p camcorder offers an ultra-wide angle lens, numerous Advanced Driver Assistance System (ADAS) features and now is Wi-Fi ready. The built-in GPS allows for real time tracking of speed and heading using the 4-quadrant display.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhen you are ready to playback your video on the PC, the SuperCar application (included) will enhance your experience with Digital Map position tracking as well as speed, heading and G-force sensor information.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KIT Includes 6 Items with all Manufacturer-supplied Accessories + Full USA Warranties:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;HP f800x Full HD Wi-Fi GPS Car Dashboard Video Recorder Camera&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Transcend 32GB microSDHC 300x UHS- Class 10 Memory Card with Adapter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Kodak Gear Small Neoprene Case (70790 - Grey)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Precision Design SD/SDHC + MicroSD HC Card Reader&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Precision Design 8 SD / 2 MicroSD Memory Card Case&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microfiber Cleaning Cloth&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wireless Capable:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe built-in 2.4Ghz model allows you to stream live video, basic camcorder control and copy files from the f800x to your smartphone or tablet. Install the free HP Pixi Cam app to fully utilize the Wi-Fi capability of the f800x. Advanced Driver&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Assistance System (ADAS):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe f800x comes loaded with ADAS features such as Lane Departure Warning System (LWDS), Front Collision Warning System (FCWS), Front Vehicle Go, and Headlight Warning. It will be important to review the User Manual for further details on how to enable and utilize these features. It is important to note that these features are for reference only and will not control your vehicle to prevent accidents&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GPS Capability:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe built-in GPS capability records the locations you have been as well as tracking your speed, compass heading and speed camera locations as you mark them&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Built-in, 3-Axis G-Force and Motion Sensor:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNo one expects to get into a driving accident, but when it happens, the built-in G-force sensor can detect these events and trigger Emergency Video Recording mode. These emergency recordings are date and time-stamped as well as protected from loop recording overwrites.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Easy to Install and Use:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nUse the enclosed bracket to install to many windshields in seconds. The car power adapter has a generous 11.4 feet (3.5 meter) cord that accommodates easy routing in almost any vehicle. Once installed, the f800x automatically begins recording when the vehicle starts and powers down when the vehicle is turned off. The camcorder also offers many easy to use options such as motion detection&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Loop Recording:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe f800x records video clips of 3 or 5 minute lengths (customer selectable) on to the installed microSDHC memory card. The standard loop recording technology prevents storage overload by erasing the oldest previously recorded file and replacing it with the new one.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'HP F800x Full HD Wi-Fi GPS Car Dashboard Video Recorder Camera &amp; KIT', 'HP F800x Full HD Wi-Fi GPS Car Dashboard Video Recorder Camera &amp; KIT', 'HP F800x Full HD Wi-Fi GPS Car Dashboard Video Recorder Camera &amp; KIT');
