(10235, 1, 'Bowflex SelectTech 552 Adjustable Dumbbell - Pair', '&lt;p&gt;Get the most out of your workout with the Bowflex® SelectTech® 552 Adjustable Dumbbell Set. Great for shrugs, lunges, curls, raises and more, these dumbbells feature easy-to-use selection dials that enable you to adjust your resistance from 5 lb. to 52.5 lb. The metal plates with molding ensure quiet workouts and dependable construction. &quot;Secrets of the 4 Step Rep&quot; DVD included.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features and Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Durable molding around the metal plates for smooth liftoff and quiet workouts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Each dumbbell is adjustable from 5 lb. to 52.5 lb. (2.5 lb. increments for the first 25 lb.)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy-to-use selection dials enable quick adjustments&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&quot;Secrets of the 4 Step Rep&quot; DVD includes more than 30 exercises with more than 80 variations&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes 2 dumbbells&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s in the Box&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bowflex® SelectTech® 552 Adjustable Dumbbell Set (Pair)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Workout DVD&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Owner\'s manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty - General: 2 years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty - Parts: 2 years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty - Labor: 1 year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (Lb.): 106&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Bowflex SelectTech 552 Adjustable Dumbbell - Pair', 'Bowflex SelectTech 552 Adjustable Dumbbell - Pair', 'Bowflex SelectTech 552 Adjustable Dumbbell - Pair'),
(10236, 1, 'Ronco ST5250BUGEN EZ Store Rotisserie Oven', '&lt;p&gt;The original Ronco Showtime Rotisserie revolutionized cooking forever. Now you and your family can savor all the incredible and natural flavors of Rotisserie cooking with the new Ronco EZ-Store Rotisserie. This easy-to-store, compact version of the Ronco classic makes delicious appetizers, entrées, even desserts! The push-button digital display takes out all the guesswork as it cooks with the precision of a commercial kitchen rotisserie. With the same cooking capacity as our standard rotisserie models, you can cook a turkey up to 15 lbs!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Seals In Natural Juices&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Evenly Browns&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic Timer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compact Design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher Safe Components&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lighted Oven&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy Efficient&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cook a variety of healthy, delicious meals with less fat and grease&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cooks up to a 15 lb turkey&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Top and parts nest inside, folding down to only 7.75 inches tall for easy storing in most kitchen cabinets&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Digital display with easy-to-use, push-button operation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Self-basting rotation locks in the flavor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;On-trend design comes in popular colors&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lid, Drip Tray and Heat Shield easily remove for cleaning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto shut-off safety feature when legs aren\'t extended or drip tray is removed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Accessories are dishwasher safe&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One-year limited warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n