(10237, 1, 'Mobo Triton Ultimate Three Wheeled Cruiser - Youth', '&lt;p&gt;The Ultimate Three-Wheeled Cruiser. The Mobo Triton is anything but rudimentary. With its ultra-maneuverability and way cool design, it is unparalleled as a three-wheeled cruiser for big kids. A simple steering mechanism and low-to-the-ground chassis makes the Mobo Triton the perfect companion for a brisk work out resulting in increased cardiovascular health and hand-eye coordination. Looking for a bike to fit your growing adolescent? Caliper handbrakes, a front free-wheel mechanism, and ergonomic seating are just a few of the many features. But don\'t just take our word come and get your ride on!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Safety flag included for optimal visibility&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tricycle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ergonomically designed cruiser&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Innovative steering system with no balance needed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sturdy adjustable frame that fits riders up to 5\'5&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low-to-the-ground frame for optimal stability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Enhances hand-eye coordination and increases arm and leg muscle strength&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Free-wheel without chain&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Durable high quality luxury with rugged, yet sleek lines&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comfortable cushioned seat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Caliper handbrake&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Recumbent-style design reduces shoulder and arm stress&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stylish look with appealing graphics&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length adjustment: 8 slot adjustments in 13 increments&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Single speed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steering mechanism: Rear steering handlebars&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hub: Free-wheel mechanism&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cushioned seat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Inflatable rubber tires&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Recommended for use on flat and