(10270, 1, 'Swingline GBC Thermal Laminator, Fusion 5000L, 12 Inch, 1703077', '&lt;p&gt;Super fast with Intelligent Pouch Thickness Detection, this 4 roller laminator does a lot of work for you and delivers spectacular results. It is easy to achieve high productivity with a one minute warm-up time and 39&quot; per minute laminating speed. Visual ready alert and audible ready alert clearly indicate when laminator is set. Automatically able to detect pouch thickness and determine the best settings, this laminator always delivers high quality results. Alternatively, you can also choose settings manually using the interactive user display. The Included Intelligent Jam Alert and Auto Reverse automatically clears jammed pouches barely any user assistance. The 5000L is compatible with 3, 5, 7, or 10 mil pouches and laminates documents up to 12&quot; wide. This laminator also includes a cold setting for smooth lamination results with pressure sensitive pouches. Intelligent Power Off activates after 30 minutes of idling. Limited 1-year warranty.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warms up in 1 minute&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Laminating speed of 39&quot; per minute for super fast laminating&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Intelligent™ Pouch Thickness Detection feature automatically determines optimal laminator settings based on thickness of pouch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Interactive user display with color LCD screen provides intuitive menu selection for Manual Settings along with a Help Menu, Job Counter, and a Countdown to Ready Timer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Laminates documents up to 12&quot; wide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Use with 3, 5, 7, and 10 mil thermal pouches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Intelligent™ Jam Alert beeps until button is pressed to release jammed pouch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4 roller system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Green ready light and audible alert beep indicates laminator has finished warming up&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Intelligent™ Power Off feature shuts down the laminator after 30 minuates of inactivity to conserve energy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;22 5/8&quot; L x 7 3/8&quot; W x 5 1/8&quot; H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Limited 1-year warranty by Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Details&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Format: Thermal/Pressure Sensitive&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Page Size: 12 inch&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Style: Thermal Lamination&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Swingline GBC Thermal Laminator, Fusion 5000L, 12 Inch, 1703077', 'Swingline GBC Thermal Laminator, Fusion 5000L, 12 Inch, 1703077', 'Swingline GBC Thermal Laminator, Fusion 5000L, 12 Inch, 1703077'),
(10271, 1, 'SKLZ Hurricane Category 4 Batting Trainer', '&lt;p&gt;The Hurricane™ Category 4 maintains the snap-back action of the original Hurricane with a sleeker design, additional power band (4 total) for fast-back action, and a high visibility impact head. Designed for baseball or softball swing training, the Hurricane™ Category 4 allows batters to develop swing power, technique and speed with a stationary or moving target.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hurricane Category 4 Introduction&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe SKLZ Hurricane Category 4 solo baseball swing trainer allows batters to work on their swing mechanics, hand-eye coordination and ball contact through repetition training. Adjust positioning and tension to practic…&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hurricane™ Category 4 Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Turns two-man target training into an advanced solo trainer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Can be used for static tee practice or as a dynamic moving target&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable height for virtually any player or ball position&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi-twist mechanics provide feedback on bat speed and power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy setup and storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No tools needed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'SKLZ Hurricane Category 4 Batting Trainer', 'SKLZ Hurricane Category 4 Batting Trainer', 'SKLZ Hurricane Category 4 Batting Trainer'),
(10272, 1, 'SKLZ Quickster Baseball Combo Net System, 7x7 Feet', '&lt;p&gt;With one frame and two nets, switch between a practice net with a ball collection skirt and a return net with removable strike zone target quickly and easily. Taking only 90 seconds to fully assemble, and even less to take down, the net spans a full 7\' x 7\'. The larger coverage area means more confidence while training. Practice anywhere with this lightweight net that fits into a convenient carry-bag.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quickster® 7x7 Baseball Combo System Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Switch between a practice net and a return net quickly and easily&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;7 feet wide and 7 feet tall&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ultra-durable design for high-intensity training for youth and elite players&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Utilizes Tension-Tite™ Frame Technology with heavy duty corner constructions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lightweight, easy to pack, carry, and store&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes removable target, 4 ground stakes, and carry bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'SKLZ Quickster Baseball Combo Net System, 7x7 Feet', 'SKLZ Quickster Baseball Combo Net System, 7x7 Feet', 'SKLZ Quickster Baseball Combo Net System, 7x7 Feet'),
(10273, 1, 'SKLZ Pro Training Goal', '&lt;p&gt;Unlike other training goals, the Pro Training Goal offers a more authentic visual. Built to stand up to the most powerful shots, the goal combines an authentic white net, crossbar and posts with an easy set up and lightweight design, giving you the look and feel of an authentic goal without the weight and hassle.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Pro Training Goal - 8\' x 5\' Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Portable goal built to withstand powerful shots&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Works on grass and turf using the Pro Training Utility Weight&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Authentic goal look with white net, cross bar and posts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Fast and easy set up and break down&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Measures 8\' wide by 5\' tall&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Includes a soft carry bag with a shoulder strap&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Pro Training Goal - 12\' x 6\' Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Portable goal built to withstand powerful shots&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Works on grass and turf using the Pro Training Utility Weight&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Authentic goal look with white net, cross bar and posts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Fast and easy set up and break down&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Measures 12\' wide by 6\' tall&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Includes a soft carry bag with a shoulder strap&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pro Training Goal - 18\' x 7.5\' Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Portable goal built to withstand powerful shots&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Works on grass and turf using the Pro Training Utility Weight&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Authentic goal look with white net, cross bar and posts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fast and easy set up and break down&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measures 18\' wide by 7.5\' tall&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes a rolling hard carry bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'SKLZ Pro Training Goal', 'SKLZ Pro Training Goal', 'SKLZ Pro Training Goal'),
(10274, 1, 'SKLZ Quickster Soccer Goal, 12x6 Feet', '&lt;p&gt;Get your practice going in under 2 minutes. The Quickster® is easy to set up and ultra-portable, yet durable and stable for youth and elite players alike. The unique Tension-Tite poles create a sturdy frame, while the easy velcro net attachments and steel ground stakes ensure the net will stay put. Carry bag is included for easy, compact storage.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quickster® 12x6 Goal Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sets up and breaks down in under 2 minutes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ultra-durable design for high-intensity training&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Equipped with strong 2-ply netting, heavy gauge tarpaulin facing and easy connection click-lock tubing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Utilizes Tension-Tite™ Frame Technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lightweight and portable for quick and easy setup&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;12 feet long and 6 feet tall&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'SKLZ Quickster Soccer Goal, 12x6 Feet', 'SKLZ Quickster Soccer Goal, 12x6 Feet', 'SKLZ Quickster Soccer Goal, 12x6 Feet'),
(10275, 1, 'Aerocart 8-in-1 All-Purpose, Wheelbarrow / Yard Cart / Dolly', '&lt;p&gt;It\'s an 8-in-1 all-purpose wheelbarrow, yard cart &amp;amp; dolly that lightens every load. Two oversized, balanced wheels make a back-breaking 200lb load feel more like 17lbs. The Aerocart also converts into a powerful dolly using a fulcrum to easily move large potted plants, boulders and even a trailer!*&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Turbo Lift design makes a 200 lb wheelbarrow load feel like 17 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Highly versatile 8-in-1 lifting and moving work system that instantly converts between a wheelbarrow, yard cart, bag holder, dolly, extended dolly, cylinder carrier, rock/plant mover &amp;amp; trailer tote&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Patented two-wheel design adjusts center of gravity for a balanced and easy-to-manage load&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flat free tires never need inflating&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes flower pot strap and cylinder, bag &amp;amp; rock holder strap&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3 Year Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Convenient Dolly&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDo you have to move a heavy object? Don\'t worry - the Aerocart has a heavy duty dolly flap that allows you to lift up to 300 lbs! So go ahead, move that dishwasher or refrigerator - the Aerocart can handle it.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Plant &amp;amp; Rock Mover&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThose heavy flower pots can be really annoying and back-breaking to move around.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIt often takes two or more people to move just one plant. Not anymore! With the flower pot moving strap and the Aerocart\'s patented extended arms, you can easily do it by yourself&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Extended Dolly&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Aerocart\'s extended dolly is ideal for bulky items such as mulch, straw bales and even furniture.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bag Holder&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe bag holder is great for leaves, debris or trash. The frame and elastic band hold the bag in place firmly. Store your Aerocart with a bag in place and it\'s a trash can for your garage or shop while it\'s parked.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cylinder Carrier&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBuckets, tanks and water jugs won\'t roll off the sides of the Aerocart.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features &amp;amp; Specs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wheelbarrow weight capacity: 300 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wheelbarrow volume capacity: ~3ft3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dolly load capacity: 300 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cart weight: 41 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 3 years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Aerocart 8-in-1 All-Purpose Yard Cart&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cylinder Holder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bag Holder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Plant Mover Strap&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rock Mover Mesh&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Trailer Tote*&lt;br /&gt;\r\nRoll ATV, motorcycle or boat trailers wherever you want them with the Aerocart!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Aerocart 8-in-1 All-Purpose, Wheelbarrow / Yard Cart / Dolly', 'Aerocart 8-in-1 All-Purpose, Wheelbarrow / Yard Cart / Dolly', 'Aerocart 8-in-1 All-Purpose, Wheelbarrow / Yard Cart / Dolly'),
(10276, 1, 'ProForm Hybrid Trainer', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hybrid Design, Fitness Technology&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEnjoy fitness motivation like never before when you access all your favorite benefits of the Hybrid Trainer. Engage your core, upper body, and lower body with the elliptical. Then tap into a great cardio workout with the recumbent bike. And now, for the first time ever, iFit® technology is available on the Hybrid Trainer allowing you to select a route anywhere in the world—and then go. Powered by Google Maps™, you can work out somewhere new every day (subscription required). Plus, you can explore unlimited iFit® workouts featuring top TV trainers like Chris and Heidi Powell. No matter your goal, you’ll find programs created just for you. The tablet holder keeps all your favorite fitness tools close by and secure. The ProForm® Hybrid Trainer is the ultimate in fitness technology.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 Machines in 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;iFit® Bluetooth® Smart Enabled&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tablet Holder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;15&quot; Stride&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Delivering More Options at a Better Price - Two Machines in One&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nProForm® partnered with TV Trainers and Transformation Specialists Chris and Heidi Powell to help you transform your home fitness routine with the ProForm® Hybrid Trainer. Now you can access the benefits of two machines in one.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIn two quick steps the Hybrid Trainer evolves from an elliptical to a recumbent bike. Simply adjust the pedals and console. And with the latest in fitness technology at your fingertips, you can enjoy daily motivation like never before with workouts designed to get you started and keep you motivated.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Recumbent Bike&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Elliptical&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transformation Technology - iFit® Bluetooth® Smart Enabled&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;It’s time to get started on your fitness transformation. When you purchase an iFit® membership, you get VIP access to the best in fitness technology.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Top features include Google Maps™ workouts that take you anywhere in the world. Whether you choose a route from our vast collection of pre-drawn trails or draw your own course, iFit® sends the route straight to your Hybrid Trainer for a unique, fun, and completely personalized experience.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;iFit® also sends you a brand new workout every day, designed by certified personal trainers, making it so you’ll never get bored. And with automatic tracking, you can keep a close eye on your fitness evolution.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;iFit® Bluetooth® Smart Enabled&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Large LCD Window&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SMR™ Silent Magnetic Resistance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Integrated Tablet Holder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;16 Digital Resistance Levels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;16 Workout Apps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;iPod® Compatible&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Soft Grips Upper-Body Workout Arms&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;15” Elliptical Stride&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Watts Power Meter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable, Cushioned Seat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oversized, Adjustable Pedals&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Water Bottle Holder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Transport Wheels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EKG™ Grip Pulse&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;350 Lb. Weight Capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The ProForm® Hybrid Trainer is protected with a &lt;strong&gt;5-Year Frame Warranty&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'ProForm Hybrid Trainer', 'ProForm Hybrid Trainer', 'ProForm Hybrid Trainer'),
(10277, 1, 'XYZprinting Da Vinci 1.0 3D Printer, Blue', '&lt;p&gt;Choose from one of XYZprinting’s many vivid filaments to print your next project! All filaments have been tested for distortion in color or form to ensure perfect prints every time.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Big&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith its robust build size of 7.8 x 7.8 x 7.8 inch (20x20x20cm), the da Vinci 1.0 is on average 69％ bigger than all competing 3D printers for a fraction of the cost!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Easy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe da Vinci 1.0 is ready-to-go right out of the box. This plug-and-play 3D printer features easy-to-Install filament cartridges for quick refills and filament swaps.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Safe&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCE certified, the da Vinci 1.0 3D printer features a fully-enclosed design which protects the users from the high temperatures required to print, and ensures that no external filament movement occurs.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thoughtful&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nXYZprinting’s online resources ensure that you have support at every step of your 3D printing process. Join our awesome online 3D design community, 3D Design Hub and Artist Collection, which features hundreds of easy-to-print, downloadable designs from all around the world! Register your product online to receive all the latest software upgrades and technical support.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dimensions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Dimension (WxHxD)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;18.4 x 20 x 22 inch&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(46.8 x 51 x 55.8 cm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Package&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Package Dimension&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;22.1 x 23.3 x 27.6 inch&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(56 x 59 x 70 cm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Package Gross Weight&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;26kg (57.3 lb)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technology&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;FFF (Fused Filament Fabrication)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Build Volume (WxHxD)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;7.8W x 7.8H x 7.8D inch (20x20x20cm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Resolution&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fine 0.1 mm (100 microns)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Standard 0.2 mm (200 microns)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Speed 0.3 mm (300 microns)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ultra Fast 0.4 mm (400 microns)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Display&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Panel Type&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2.6” FSTN LCM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Software&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;(XYZWare)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;File Types&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;.stl , XYZ Format&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OS Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Windows XP ( .Net 4.0 required) and Windows 7 above (for PC)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mac OSX 10.8 above-bit (for Mac)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Note: Stardard VGA driver on operating system, or a graphics card doesn\'t support OpenGL 2.1, may cause unknown error in XYZware&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hardware&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hardware Requirements (for PC/Mac)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;X86 32/64-bit compatible PCs with 4GB+ DRAM (for PC)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;X86 64-bit compatible Macs with 4GB+ DRAM (for Mac)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;More&amp;nbsp;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Print Head: Single Nozzle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Nozzle Diameter: 0.4 mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Filament Diameter: 1.75 mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Filament Material: ABS&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Language: Multi Language&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Connectivity: USB 2.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'XYZprinting Da Vinci 1.0 3D Printer, Blue', 'XYZprinting Da Vinci 1.0 3D Printer, Blue', 'XYZprinting Da Vinci 1.0 3D Printer, Blue'),
(10278, 1, 'Slendertone Connect Abdominal Muscle Toner', '&lt;p&gt;Slendertone Connect Abs belt combines the power of Slendertone\'s abdominal strengthening system and the versatility of smartphones / iOS tablets, this product revolutionizes the concept of muscular work at home. And, what could be better than a personal coach for your daily workout?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nApp driven abdominal toning belt, control your workout from your iPhone or iPad (required and sold seperately).&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThis smart device tones and tracks your progresses, motivates you with programmes tailored to your goal.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n30 minutes is like doing 202 sit-ups.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe highly-ergonomic Slendertone Connect Abs belt is designed to be used by anyone, anywhere, anytime. Super slim and extremely discreet, you can wear it under your clothes, activate it at home, on-the-go, in work and even when practising sport for much greater results.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Slendertone Connect Abs, the brand-new muscle toning belt, comes with an iOS app that bears the same name and connects using Bluetooth Smart technology. With the app, you can create your profile, fix your goals and real-time monitor your progress day-by-day. A tailored programme is generated for you based on the goals you want to reach.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;You just need to register your Connect controller on your smartphone or iOS tablet to access our fully-interactive environment. Needs-specific workout programmes, weekly targets and a monitoring tool that encourages you to go that extra mile help you constantly improve your results.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Slendertone Connect app has 5 unique 6 week programmes for different needs: increasing your physical performances, getting back into shape after pregnancy, staying in shape, toning muscles even more…&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This product fits the following sizes:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWaist: 24” - 42”&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s in the box:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Slendertone Connect Abs unisex toning belt.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rechargeable controller.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 USB charging cable.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Set of replacement gel pads.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Instruction manual.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Storage pouch.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;*This app requires the Slendertone Connect Abs toning belt and an Apple iPhone 4S or newer, an Apple iPad 4th generation or newer or Apple iPod Touch&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Slendertone Connect Abdominal Muscle Toner', 'Slendertone Connect Abdominal Muscle Toner', 'Slendertone Connect Abdominal Muscle Toner'),
(10279, 1, 'TRX Training Home Suspension Training (No)', '&lt;p&gt;The all-in-one, total-body workout system you can set up in less than 60 seconds at home or anywhere you go. Get stronger, build muscle, lose weight and improve flexibility fast - no weights required.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;The TRX Home Gym includes two anchoring options, a workout guide, and six digital workout videos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Workout Anywhere&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe TRX® Home Gym weighs less than two lbs. You can set it up virtually anywhere in less than a minute. Work out anywhere on your own schedule.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Burn Fat, Build Lean Muscle&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith 300+ exercises, the TRX® Home Gym will give you TOTAL BODY results, helping burn unwanted fat and build lean – not bulky – muscle.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Get A Stronger Core&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nA stronger core supports your WHOLE body. Research shows that Suspension Training is one of the MOST effective tools for stimulating and conditioning the core.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Perfect Full Body Workout&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOn the TRX® Suspension Trainer, you\'re in control. Use your bodyweight and gravity to perform over 300 exercises that you can make easier or harder. The straps allow you to increase or decrease the exercise difficulty based on your body\'s position.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Progress any exercise using only your bodyweight&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Get lean muscle and burn fat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Be stronger from your core out&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Build greater flexibility, mobility and stability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Increase your body’s durability and endurance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What’s in the Box?​&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Trx® Home Suspension Trainer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Anchor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Suspension Anchor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Content + App&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mesh Carry Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Getting Started Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty by Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'TRX Training - Home Suspension Training Kit', 'TRX Training - Home Suspension Training Kit', 'TRX Training - Home Suspension Training Kit'),
(65, 1, 'Razor E300 Electric Scooter, Gray', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Let your child explore the neighborhood with the Razor E300 Electric Scooter Gray. It is an electronic scooter with a rechargeable battery that helps it in its operation. This scooter is made from a premium-quality material, which makes it sturdy and durable. It has a stunning black finish that adds an alluring look. This E300 Electric Scooter Gray from Razor has a high-torque motor that is capable of generating a speed of 15 mph. It has a twist grip accelerator and a hand-operated rear brake to control the speed. The scooter has a foldable handlebar which height can also be adjusted according to your child’s height.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UL approved battery charger and tools included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ideal for ages 12 and up&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Super sized deck and frame&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Twist grip acceleration control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rechargeable battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hand operated rear brake&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable handlebar height&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Handlebar folding mechanism&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Decorations may vary&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High torque motor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Variable speed chain drive&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra wide 10 inch pneumatic tires&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High performance motor with variable speeds up to 15 mph&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum rider weight 220 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Runtime of the scooter is 40 min.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;24V (two 12V) sealed lead acid rechargeable battery system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wide pneumatic tires&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Retractable kickstand&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall: 42&quot; H x 17&quot; W x 41&quot; D&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall Product Weight: 46 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Type: Electric scooter&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Black&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wheels Included: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Wheels: 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Age Group: 11 to 12 Years; 13+ Years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Razor E300 Electric Scooter, Gray', 'Razor E300 Electric Scooter, Gray', 'Razor E300 Electric Scooter, Razor E300 Scooter, Multiple Colors, Razor Electric Scooter'),
(10280, 1, 'Worx WG775 24-Volt Cordless 14-inch Lawn Mower', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Can cut up to 6,000 square feet in a single charge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-in-1 mower: mulch, bag, or rear-discharge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Collapsible handle for space-saving storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable, replaceable 24V PowerTank™ battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Finer mulching performance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe WORX 24V 14&quot; cordless lawn mower features exclusive mulching fins in the mower deck, which chop up the grass blades 40% more finely than conventional mowers. Finely mulched grass clippings promote quicker decomposition and and a healthier lawn.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Versatility and more options&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe WORX 24V 14&quot; cordless mower provides 3 different cutting operations in one, compact machine. Now you may choose between bagging, mulching or a rear-discharge - giving you the opportunity to cater to your lawn\'s needs.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Space-saving storage&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe collapsible handle provides quick, easy and compact storage - freeing up additional space. And at a mere 32-lbs, this cordless mower can go anywhere it is needed.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Removable PowerTank™ battery&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNo garage, no problem. The WORX PowerTank™ series battery easily lifts out so that you may charge it where you want, when you want. And because it\'s removable, you can keep a spare&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Simplified operation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPull-cord gas lawn mowers are a thing of the past thanks to our WORX cordless lawn mowers. This 24V 14&quot; cordless mower starts the first time, with just a right or left side lever pull. The lightweight and compact design enables the cordless mower to give professional results in all of the areas that a larger mower cannot access. Now there is a mower that will give you the results you want on all parts of your lawn; especially along the edges!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 3 Year by&amp;nbsp;Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max. Cutting Area Per Charge:6,000 Ft²&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery: 24V&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Deck Width: 14&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut Height Range: 2&quot;-3.5&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Grass Bag Capacity: 0.85 Bushels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charging Time: 4-5hr (approx.)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Machine Weight: 32lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s in the Box&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;WG775&amp;nbsp;Cordless Intellicut Lawn Mower&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable 24-Volt Battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Battery&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Charger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Grass Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;User\'s Manual.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Worx WG775 24-Volt Cordless 14-inch Lawn Mower', 'Worx WG775 24-Volt Cordless 14-inch Lawn Mower', 'Worx WG775 24-Volt Cordless 14-inch Lawn Mower'),
(10281, 1, 'Worx WG782 24-Volt Cordless 14-inch Lawn Mower with IntelliCut', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;IntelliCut technology ensures torque is there when you need it&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-in-1 mower: mulch, bag or rear-discharge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cuts up to 10,000 square feet per charge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable, replaceable battery 24V PowerTank™ battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-position, simple mowing height adjustment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Intellicut™ technology&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPatented IntelliCut™ technology ensures that torque is there when you need it. No more bogging down in tough conditions when mowing tall grass or mulching leaves. Simply set the dial to POWER when cutting through the tough stuff, or just switch the dial to QUIET to powerfully and efficiently mow in everyday conditions without disturbing the neighbors.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Power when you need it&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIntelligent Power-on-Demand technology provides a boost when the grass is tall and thick. When the going gets tough, our mowers get going so you get a great finish.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Space-saving storage&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe fully collapsible handle provides quick, easy and compact storage - freeing up additional space. And at a mere 32-lbs, &amp;nbsp;the WORX mowers are the lightest on the market.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Removable PowerTank™ battery&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNo garage, no problem. The WORX PowerTank™ series battery easily lifts out so that you may charge it where you want, when you want. And because it\'s removable, you can keep a spare&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Simplified operation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPull-cord gas lawn mowers are a thing of the past thanks to our WORX cordless lawn mowers. The 24V 14&quot; IntelliCut™ mower starts the first time, with just a right or left side lever pull. The lightweight and compact design enables the IntelliCut™ cordless mower to give professional results in all of the areas that a larger mower cannot access. Now there is a mower that will give you the results you want on all parts of your lawn; especially along the edges!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 3 Year by&amp;nbsp;Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max. Cutting Area Per Charge:10,000 Ft²&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery: 24V&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Deck Width: 14&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut Height Range: 2&quot;-3.5&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Grass Bag Capacity: 0.85 Bushels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charging Time: 4-5hr (approx.)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Machine Weight: 32lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s in the Box&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;WG782 Cordless Intellicut Lawn Mower&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable 24-Volt Battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Battery&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Charger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mulch Insert&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Grass Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;User\'s Manual.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Worx WG782 24-Volt Cordless 14-inch Lawn Mower with IntelliCut', 'Worx WG782 24-Volt Cordless 14-inch Lawn Mower with IntelliCut', 'Worx WG782 24-Volt Cordless 14-inch Lawn Mower with IntelliCut'),
(10282, 1, 'Worx WG320 20-Volt MaxLithium Cordless 6-inch JawSaw Chainsaw', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Powerful and lightweight 2.0 Amp MaxLithium battery delivers long-lasting performance without self-discharge or memory effect&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut or trim materials up to 4-inches in diameter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Innovative auto-tension feature guarantees optimum tension at all times&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Features an automatic chain oiler with oil level indicator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blade housing allows for safe cuts directly on the groundg&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Scissor cut action limits dangerous kickback for safer operation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes a 3 Year Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No More Heavy Lifting / No More Sore Back and Muscles&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nForget having to lift heavy limbs off of the ground to cut, the JawSaw is the only chainsaw designed to operate directly on the ground or pavement.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cordless Convenience&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPowered by a commanding 20V MaxLithium battery, the WORX JawSaw has gone mobile - making it the lightweight, portable and safe way to work.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Patented Auto-Tension System&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe JawSaw\'s patented system automatically sets the proper tension, ensuring that your JawSaw is functioning at the optimum level.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Forget Ladders&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith the 5ft. pole extension accessory, you will &amp;nbsp;be able to cut even hard-to-reach branches.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cleanup After the Storm&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDowned logs and branches? The 20V MaxLithium Cordless JawSaw is the easiest way to cleanup the mess.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe auxiliary handle provides added stability &amp;amp; control, while the scissor-cut action limits dangerous kickback.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rated Voltage: 20V MAX*&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No-Load Speed: 1350/min&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Guide Bar Length: 6&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oil Tank Capacity: 30 ml&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Chain Pitch: 1/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Chain Gauge:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;0.05&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Chain Links: 42&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charging Time: 3 hours (approx.)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Machine Weight: 7.9 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: &amp;nbsp;3 Years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;*Voltage measured without workload. Initial battery voltage reaches maximum of 20 volts. Nominal voltage is 18 volts.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;20V Cordless JawSaw&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;20V MaxLithium Battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;20V Battery Charger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Chainsaw Chain&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Chainsaw Bar&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bar &amp;amp; Chain Oil&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oil Bottle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Spanner Wrench&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Worx WG320 20-Volt MaxLithium Cordless 6-inch JawSaw Chainsaw', 'Worx WG320 20-Volt MaxLithium Cordless 6-inch JawSaw Chainsaw', 'Worx WG320 20-Volt MaxLithium Cordless 6-inch JawSaw Chainsaw'),
(10283, 1, 'EGO 110 MPH 530 CFM Variable-Speed Turbo 56V Cordless Electric Blower', '&lt;p&gt;The EGO Power+ 530 CFM Blower is the next, big step up in power and convenience for cordless blowers. Turbine fan engineering, inspired by advanced aeronautics technology, performs better than many premium gas-powered models. The light-weight, compact, high-efficiency brushless motor delivers longer run time, low vibrations and an extended motor life. The advanced EGO Power+ 56-Volt battery uses industry-leading Arc-Lithium technology to deliver Power Beyond Belief and is compatible with all EGO Power+ products.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2.5Ah power+ battery is compatible with all EGO power+ products and chargers&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High efficiency brushless motor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Turbo boost function delivers 530 CFM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Variable-speed: from 250 CFM to 530 CFM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Up to 75-minute run time on low setting with included battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;50 minute charge time with included battery and charger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weather-resistant construction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ergonomic design for superb balance and user comfort&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5-year limited warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembled Depth (in.) : 35.9 in&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembled Width (in.) : 6.7 in&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembled Height (in.) : 10.9 in&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Antivibration: Yes&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum air speed (mph): 110&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly Required: &amp;nbsp;No&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Noise rating (dB): &amp;nbsp;64&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Batteries Included: Yes&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Batteries Required: 1&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery Type Required: 56V Li-ion&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 9.8 lb&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blower Type: Handheld Blower&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Reconditioned: No&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charger Included: Yes&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Start Type: Electric&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engine Cycles: Electric Motor&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Variable speeds: Yes&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Interchangeable nozzle connections: Yes&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage (volts): 56&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Air Volume (CFM): 530&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'EGO 110 MPH 530 CFM Variable-Speed Turbo 56V Cordless Electric Blower', 'EGO 110 MPH 530 CFM Variable-Speed Turbo 56V Cordless Electric Blower', 'EGO 110 MPH 530 CFM Variable-Speed Turbo 56V Cordless Electric Blower'),
(10284, 1, 'RYOBI 40 Volt 155MPH Jet Fan Blower Kit, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TYPES OF PRODUCTS WE CARRY:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSAVE UP TO 90% OFF with our Factory Blemished or Certified Pre-Owned.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://ankermart.com/image/data/TYPE-PRO.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The RYOBI 40-Volt Jet Fan Blower features Gas-Like Power without the hassle of gas and oil. The unique jet fan design of the RYOBI Cordless 40 Volt Lithium-Ion Blower optimizes air flow to produce 155 MPH and 300CFM of power. The Jet Fan Blower powers through wet and dry leaves and debris, making it ideal for lawns and hard surfaces. Featuring a variable speed trigger for air speed control and an overall sleek design with a soft grip handle for user comfort, the RYOBI 40-Volt Jet Fan Blower will tackle any clearing job with ease.The entire RYOBI 40-Volt family runs off of the same 40 Volt lithium-ion battery platform.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Jet Fan Design for Gas-Like Power 155 MPH / 300 CFM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Variable Speed Trigger For Adjustable Clearing Power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Soft Grip Handle For User Comfort&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;40 Volt Lithium-Ion high capacity battery and 90 min. charger included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Motor: 40 Volt Lithium-Ion Battery Air Velocity: 155MPH/300CFM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Trigger: Variable Speed Trigger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 8.85 lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S INCLUDED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blower&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blower Tube&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;40 Volt Lithium Battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;40 Volt Charger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operator’s Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MORE INFORMATION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: RYOBI&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power: Battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage: 40V&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery Type: Lithium-Ion&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Condition: Certified Pre-Owned&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1-Year Reconditioned Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Batteries: 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Batteries Included: Batteries Included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blowout: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'RYOBI 40 Volt 155MPH Jet Fan Blower Kit, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', 'RYOBI 40 Volt 155MPH Jet Fan Blower Kit, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', 'RYOBI 40 Volt 155MPH Jet Fan Blower Kit, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED'),
(10286, 1, 'Rockwell RK1807K2 20V Brushless Drill/Impact Driver Combo Kit, 2-Piece', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Kit includes a 20V Brushless Drill/Driver &amp;amp; 20V Brushless Impact Driver&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brushless motor increases runtime up to 50% more per charge over a standard brushed motor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Computer-controlled power distribution improves efficiency and durability by reducing heat, friction and wear&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;20V MaxLithium technology provides longer runtimes, higher working efficiency, more charge cycles &amp;amp; minimal self-discharge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;On-board battery fuel gauge tracks charge status anytime&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes a 20 Year Warranty + Free Batteries for 20 Years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x 20V Brushless Drill / Driver (RK2852K2)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x 20V Brushless Impact Driver (RK2860K2)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 x 20V MaxLithium Battery ( RW9351)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x 20V Battery Charger ( RW9420)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Rockwell Carrying Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 x Rockwell Belt Clip&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 x Rockwell Double Ended Bit (PH2/SL5.5)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications - RK2852K2&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Chuck: 1/2”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No-Load Speed: 0-600 / 0-2000/min&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage: 20V MAX*&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max Torque: 531 in/lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Torque Settings: 18 + 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charge Time: 60 min&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery Capacity: 1 x 2.0 Ah&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Machine Weight: 3.9 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications - RK2860K2&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Chuck: 1/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No-Load Speed: 0-2900/min&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage: 20V MAX*&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max Torque: 1550 in/lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Torque Settings: 20 + 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charge Time: 60 min.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery Capacity: 1 x 2.0 Ah&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Machine Weight: 3.20 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Rockwell RK1807K2 20V Brushless Drill/Impact Driver Combo Kit, 2-Piece', 'Rockwell RK1807K2 20V Brushless Drill/Impact Driver Combo Kit, 2-Piece', 'Rockwell RK1807K2 20V Brushless Drill/Impact Driver Combo Kit, 2-Piece');
INSERT INTO `oc_product_description` (`product_id`, `language_id`, `name`, `description`, `meta_description`, `meta_keyword`, `tag`) VALUES
(10287, 1, 'Stokke Tripp Trapp High Chair', '&lt;p&gt;Be together. Grow together. TRIPP TRAPP - The Chair that grows with the child. Tripp Trapp is a sturdy children\'s chair that grows with your child. It lifts them up so they can be included in activities around the table. Children love interacting with the family. In today\'s hectic lifestyle, it is more important than ever to encourage these special moments of togetherness. The dining table is more than a place for mealtime. It\'s for playing, homework or simply just talking, enjoying quality time together. A child sitting at the same height as an adult at a table stimulates the development of confidence. We believe that life around the table is incredibly important. As an adult, we have the luxury of being able to rest our feet on the floor, allowing us to move freely to get comfortable. For your child, there is no such luxury. Tripp Trapp therefore features a unique, adjustable footrest that brings the floor up to your child. This creates better balance and comfort, as your child can easily shift their weight. By sitting with the feet supported and elbows at table height, your child can move easily and naturally, and use their body without strain. It\'s all about support, balance and movement.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brings your baby to the dining table and closer to the family&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Baby set and cushion accessories provide comfort for your baby&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Highly adjustable seat and footplate positions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Available in a variety of colors for your baby boy or girl&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Classic Scandinavian design by Peter Opsvik&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://ankermart.com/image/data/Stokke-Tripp/GROW_TrippTrapp.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height: 230px; width: 736px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The iconic Tripp Trapp® chair was the first high chair of its kind when designed by Peter Opsvik in 1972. Made of solid European beech wood, its intelligent design grows with your child, providing a comfortable, ergonomic seat at any age. It has been made to fit right up to your dining table to bring your baby into the heart of your family, allowing your little boy or girl to eat, learn, play and develop alongside you.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product info&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product weight in kg/lbs: 7 / 15,4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product dimensions (length x height x width) in cm/in: 49x79x46 / 19,3&quot;x31,1&quot;x18,1&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Suitable for age in months: &amp;gt;36&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: Wood&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Your child can comfortably sit at the dining table and enjoy mealtimes with the rest of family.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Comfort &amp;amp; Design&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Classic, iconic design will never go out of style.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unique adjustability of seat and footplate to ensure both back and feet support for any age.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stable footrest that supports your child and provides comfort.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Solid construction and European beech wood can hold up to a 300 lb adult.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Array of color choices match any décor.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Safety&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5-point harness included with chair for extra safety.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Arrives with guide for positioning of seat and footplate related to age of child.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Optional extended gliders provide increased backward stability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy to clean spills with dampened cloth.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extended 7-year warranty available on wooden components.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Water-based, non-toxic paint.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No harmful substances/free from bisphenol and phtalates.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Certified by JPMA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Stokke Tripp Trapp High Chair', 'Stokke Tripp Trapp High Chair', 'Stokke Tripp Trapp High Chair'),
(10288, 1, 'Blink Wireless Home Security &amp; Video Monitoring System - 3 Cameras', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Also Available:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ankermart.com/Blink/Blink-Wireless-Home-Security-Video-Monitoring-System-5-Cameras&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;Blink Wireless Home Security &amp;amp; Video Monitoring System - 5 Cameras&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Meet Blink, the one-of-a-kind, battery-powered home monitoring system that\'s simple to set up and equally perfect for renters or homeowners. Its stylish, totally wire-free design houses innovative HD video technology, plus motion and temperature sensors, to deliver instant home insight through the Blink app for your iOS or Android device.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cameras are totally wire-free; powered by 2 AA Lithium batteries (included) which deliver more than a full year of battery life&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;HD video capture and built-in motion detector; when motion detector is triggered, receive a short (5-10 second) video clip of the event&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Check in anytime with streaming Live View feature&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy, DIY set-up; mounting kit included; control and access quickly and easily through free apps for iOS 8.0 and Android 4.4 KitKat or higher&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No monthly fees or service contract required&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Place it Anywhere&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBlink is battery-powered and truly wire-free, so it\'s simple to place and move within any indoor environment. Create a system that covers your entryways and windows, monitors the garage, or keeps a watchful eye over the kids\' rooms (or even the cookie jar). Unique technology which delivers more than a full year of battery life for extended, no-hassle peace of mind.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Visual Verification&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong