gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Fellowes AeraMax™ 290 Air Purifier uses a four-stage purification system to remove airborne particles.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. The carbon filter removes odors and captures large airborne particulates&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. The True HEPA filter safely removes 99.97 percent of airborne particles as small as 0.3 microns, including pollen, ragweed and other allergens, viruses, germs, dust mites, mold spores, pet dander and cigarette smoke&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. The AeraSafe antimicrobial treatment provides built-in protection from the growth of odor-causing bacteria, mildew, and fungi on the True HEPA filter&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. PlasmaTRUE technology creates an ionized field to help safely remove airborne pollutants&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Certifications&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCertified asthma &amp;amp; allergy friendly™&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Fellowes® AeraMax™ Air Purifiers are certified by the Asthma and Allergy Foundation of America (AAFA). This certification is only awarded to air cleaning products that have scientifically demonstrated their contribution to the goals of allergen reduction. AAFA and Allergy Standard Limited (ASL) utilize stringent standards to identify only best-in-class products that are more suitable for those with asthma and allergies.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AHAM Certified - Association of Home Appliance Manufacturers&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFellowes® AeraMax™ Air Purifiers have been certified by the Association of Home Appliance Manufacturers (AHAM) with three&lt;br /&gt;\r\nClean Air Delivery Rate (CADR) numbers which indicate the volume of filtered air delivered by the air purifiers (measured in ft3/min).&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThere are three CADR ratings: one for smoke, one for pollen and one for dust. The higher the number, the faster the air purifier filters the air.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Energy Star Certified&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Fellowes® AeraMax™ 290 Air Purifier is Energy Star-qualified. Energy Star-qualified air purifiers are 40% more energy-efficient than non-qualifying models&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;UL Listed&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Fellowes AeraMax™ Air Purifiers are all UL certified for your safety. UL is a world leader for over 100 years in product safety testing and certification&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AeraSmart Sensor™: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Change Filter Light Indicator: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Filter Change Type&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;: Side Drawer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Filter Type: Carbon/ True HEPA with AeraSafe™ Antimicrobial Treatment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Item H x W x D (inches): 25.50 x 16.00 x 8.13&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Item weight (lbs): 13.52&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;PlasmaTrue™ Technology: PlasmaTrue™ Technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Room Size (Sq Ft): 300-600&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Room Size: Large Room&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UPC Code: 043859660117&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 3 Years Limited by Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Fellowes AeraMax DX95 True HEPA Portable Air Purifier, White', 'Fellowes AeraMax DX95 True HEPA Portable Air Purifier, White', 'Fellowes AeraMax DX95 True HEPA Portable Air Purifier, White'),
(10304, 1, 'iWalk 2.0 Hands Free Crutch', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why would you use an ARM crutch (or scooter) when a LEG CRUTCH works so much better?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Before you buy let\'s make sure iWALK2.0 will work for you:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe iWALK2.0 will work for most people, but not everyone.&amp;nbsp; For your safety and satisfaction, before you buy, make sure you read and understand the sizing and user qualification guidelines.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Basic Physical Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nRegardless of age, if you can pass these two physical ability tests, you should be capable of using the iWALK 2.0.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;If you cannot do these things, then iWALK probably will not work for you.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;If you can do these two things, continue and read the rest of this page.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Stair Test&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBefore your injury, could you easily walk up and down stairs at a normal pace, without using a hand rail?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Balance Test&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCan you balance on one foot for a full 30 seconds?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you can do these two things, continue reading to ensure that iWALK 2.0 will work for you:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Before your injury, could you walk without difficulty?&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Could you go up or down stairs without using a hand rail for balance or support?&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. Is your injury to one leg only?&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. Is your injury below the knee?&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. Can you bend your injured leg 90 degrees at the knee?&lt;br /&gt;\r\n6. Do you have full, unrestricted use of your uninjured leg?&lt;br /&gt;\r\n7. Are you between 4\'10&quot; and 6\'6&quot;? (see sizing limitations below)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n8. Are you under 275 pounds?&lt;br /&gt;\r\n9. Is your upper thigh circumference (measured at the highest point of your thigh) 27&quot; or less?&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIf you answered yes to all, then read on, and get ready to ditch your crutches.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;iWALK2.0 is the hands free, pain free alternative to conventional crutches and knee scooters. Think of all the things you can’t do when using conventional crutches; preparing a meal, walking your dog, carrying a cup of coffee, pushing a shopping cart. You no longer need to have your life interrupted – the iWALK2.0 sets you free to resume your day to day routine and enjoy pain free, functional mobility.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Stop sitting on the sidelines of your own life because a lower leg injury is impeding your mobility. The iWALK2.0 allows you continue your daily routine with little to no interruption, all while safely letting your lower leg injury heal.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The iWALK2.0 is a crutch alternative for non-weight bearing lower leg injuries that frees the user from the limitations of conventional crutches. No more pain, nerve damage, or using your arms to support your weight, because the iWALK2.0 enables the user to walk normally without using your upper body to provide support. If you need to be non-weight bearing for any length of time and do not want give up your traditional daily routine, the iWALK2.0 is for you!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Walking on the iWALK2.0 feels natural and easy.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features and Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Patented FDA and CE Registered Class 1 Medical Device&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Regain your independence&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tool free, intuitive adjustments&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One size fits from 4\'10&quot; to 6\'6&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Take on or off in seconds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Converts for Left or Right leg use in seconds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Independent upper and lower leg adjustments&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable length straps with comfort pads.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comfortable for long term use&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Keeps your injury partially elevated&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured in the USA from the highest quality materials&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with a 1 Year Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comfortable hypoallergenic foam padding&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Clinically proven&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Not suited for:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Injuries of the knee or above&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Those with impaired strength or balance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;People with injuries or limitations in both legs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Those over 275 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Thigh circumference greater than 28&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Inability to bend knee 90 degrees on your injured leg&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Age Limits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIf you\'re over 60, pay careful attention - iWALK2.0&amp;nbsp; might not be for you.&amp;nbsp; It\'s difficult to put an age limit on the iWALK2.0 because physical condition and abilities vary considerably from individual to individual, especially in the elderly.&amp;nbsp; iWALK2.0 has been used successfully by people in their 70\'s and beyond, but we\'ve also seen people in their early 60\'s who could not adapt.&amp;nbsp; You do not need to be an elite athlet to use the iWALK2.0 but you do need average strength and balance.&amp;nbsp; Personal assessment and sound judgement are your best tools to determine if an elderly person will succeed on the iWALK2.0.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nRule of Thumb - If you can briskly walk up and down stair without using a hand rail, then you possess the physical abilities to use the iWALK2.0.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sizing Information&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nLeg length is the most important factor in determining if the iWALK2.0 will fit, however, since most people don\'t know their leg length, we use height as a starting point.&amp;nbsp; In general, the iWALK2.0 will fit you if you are between 4\'10&quot; to 6\'6&quot; tall, however, there are exceptions.&amp;nbsp; If you are between 4\'10&quot; and 5\'1&quot;, there is a 95% chance that the it will fit.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Similarly, if you are between 6\'2&quot; and 6\'6&quot; there is also a 95% chance it will fit.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Training&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nProper fit is easy to achieve, and essential to success.&amp;nbsp; For your satisfaction and safety, view our instructions entirely BEFORE you try the device.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'iWalk 2.0 Hands Free Crutch', 'iWalk 2.0 Hands Free Crutch', 'iWalk 2.0 Hands Free Crutch'),
(10305, 1, 'Hyper Vest Pro Weight Vest', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hyper Vest Pro is currently out of stock for Small, Large and X-Large. Please check back on 5/31!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Hyper Vest PRO weighted vest will take your training to the next level. Whether you are looking for sports performance training, cross training or general fitness, weight loss or rehab, the Hyper Vest PRO is simply the best weight vest on the market.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unisex patented design for exceptional comfort&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unique breathable, odor resistant, wicking fabric&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Open side panels provide superior ventilation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Thin profile allows for full range of motion&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flexible side lacing for highly-adjustable fit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes pre-loaded with 10 lbs of steel weights&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hand washable.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One year limited warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wash in sink with weights in, towel off, hang dry.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Hyper Vest® PRO is a revolutionary type of weighted vest that features a unique control system and fabric. The PRO vest\'s innovative design allows the user complete range of motion, since the weights are held comfortably and firmly to the core, even during vigorous, multi-plane movement. Even better, the Hyper Vest PRO is flexible around the chest in the horizontal plane. This horizontal stretch allows full chest expansion and contraction for breathing while the weights stay in place. A breathable, wicking fabric and generous open side panels make the vest exceptionally comfortable. This weighted vest is so thin you can wear it under a shirt and no one would know (weights are only ¼ inch thick).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Small through XL vests are available, and every vest comes pre-loaded with 10 lbs. Additional 5 pounds booster packs of weight can be purchased to increase the load of the vest. &amp;nbsp;Max weight capacities: Small - 22lbs. Medium - 24lbs. Large - 34lbs. XL - 48lbs.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://ankermart.com/image/data/Hyper-Vest/size.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 700px; height: 147px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits and Uses:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Hyper Vest PRO creates the effect of mass evenly distributed over the body’s core to create resistance. By adding weight to the core, you can engage in any movement with the additional resistance of the weights. This is body weight training at its best. Use the vest for sports performance training, tactical training for fire, police, and military, general fitness, and overall health, weight loss, and prevention of osteoporosis.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Research:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nResearch and practical application have proven that weight loading via weighted garments can produce positive results during the rigorous activities of various sports, as well as rehabilitation. Recent studies have also discovered some other interesting findings. Wearing weighted garments during daily activities, for extended periods of time, when used correctly, can increase functional body strength, overall fitness level, and athletic performance.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Hyper Vest Pro Weight Vest', 'Hyper Vest Pro Weight Vest', 'Hyper Vest Pro Weight Vest'),
(10306, 1, 'Teton Sports Outfitter XXL Camp Cot', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Outfitter XXL Camp Cot&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWell-built steel-frame cot, seven feet long and over three feet wide. Comfortable and durable. Quick setup. This will be the best cot you_ve ever owned. Count on a sound sleep every night with the Outfitter XXL Cot. The sleeping area is bigger than a twin size mattress and supports up to 600 pounds easily. Rubber feet have been redesigned to provide better protection for tent floor and the whole cot folds into a sturdy drawstring bag for carrying or stowing. Comfortable enough to use as a guest bed, especially when paired with the Outfitter XXL Camp Pad.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions (setup): 85&quot; x 40&quot; x 19&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions (stored): 42&quot; x 12&quot; x 7&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pack Weight: 26 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bed: Heavy-duty 600D Poly Canvas&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Frame:Extruded Aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Legs: Reinforced Steel S-Leg Assembly&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Black&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Storage: 600D Canvas Carry Bag with Drawstring Closure&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Patented steel leg design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oversized sleeping area that supports up to 600 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible with Outfitter XXL camp pad, Outfitter XXL Quick tent, gun sleeve, and organizer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cot folds up to a compact 42&quot; x 12&quot; x 7&quot; for easy transport&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One person setup and take down is quick and easy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Durable canvas fabric suspends your weight from the frame for a more comfortable night\'s sleep&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Channeled aluminum support bars at top and bottom add stability which means you don\'t have to readjust every time you use the cot.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Limited Lifetime Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gear Video&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b8M4gn1bvlk&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b8M4gn1bvlk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Teton Sports Outfitter XXL Camp Cot', 'Teton Sports Outfitter XXL Camp Cot', 'Teton Sports Outfitter XXL Camp Cot'),
(10307, 1, 'Louisville Slugger 2016 Select 716 Bbcor (-3) Baseball Bat', '&lt;p&gt;Extreme POWER. &amp;nbsp;Crafted to be the next generation of hybrid power, the SELECT 716 combines an AC21 alloy barrel and a 100% composite handle to deliver powerful performance. &amp;nbsp;The TRU3 Dynamic Socket Connection allows for slight movement between the barrel and handle to maximize the barrel trampoline effect and eliminate negative vibration. &amp;nbsp; The SELECT 716 has a massive sweet spot, true feel and is one of the lightest swing weights among all hybrid bats.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;100% composite handle/AC21 alloy barrel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;TRU3 - featuring Dynamic Socket Connection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-piece bat construction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flex Band barrel technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lizard Skins Grip&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 5/8 inch barrel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;31/32 inch tapered handle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product SKU(s): WTLBBS7163-31, WTLBBS7163-32, WTLBBS7163-33, WTLBBS7163-34&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Barrel Diameter: 2 5/8 Inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Barrel Material: Composite&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Certification: BBCOR&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight Drop: Adult -3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1 Year by Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Louisville Slugger 2016 Select 716 Bbcor (-3) Baseball Bat', 'Louisville Slugger 2016 Select 716 Bbcor (-3) Baseball Bat', 'Louisville Slugger 2016 Select 716 Bbcor (-3) Baseball Bat'),
(10308, 1, 'BabyPlus Prenatal Education System', '&lt;p&gt;Build a strong bond with your baby during pregnancy with the BabyPlus Prenatal Education System. Studies have shown that the brain is most receptive during the prenatal period. So, by creating the right kind of environment, you can help develop your baby\'s emotional, creative, social, and intellectual capabilities. Use this 16-week baby educational system between the 18th and 32nd weeks of your pregnancy. It has a series of 16 naturally derived sounds that are similar to a mother\'s heartbeat. These prenatal education tracks soothe and relax the mom and child. This system comes with a belt clip so you can carry it with you wherever you go. It requires 4 AA batteries.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Features: Automatic Shut-Off, Low Battery Indicator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes: Instruction Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Not Included: Batteries&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Baby Monitor Type video monitors&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Source: Battery-powered&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Channels: 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wireless Frequency Band: 49 megahertz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Radio Range: Does Not Apply&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 5.500 H x 3.000 W x 2.000 D&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: .800&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 180 Day Limited Manufacturer Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery required, not included: 4 AA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly Details: no assembly required&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'BabyPlus Prenatal Education System', 'BabyPlus Prenatal Education System', 'BabyPlus Prenatal Education System'),
(10309, 1, 'Clicgear Model 3.5+ Golf Push Cart - 2016 Lime', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Also Available:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ankermart.com/Clicgear-USA/Clicgear-Model-3-5-Plus-Golf-Push-Cart-2016-Orange&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;Clicgear Model 3.5+ Golf Push Cart - 2016 Orange&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Model 3.5+ is the latest version of our original push cart.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCompact &amp;amp; durable, Model 3.5+ offers &lt;strong&gt;5 main upgrades&lt;/strong&gt;;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;80% larger storage net&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Larger cup holder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;New bag strap system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Improved Umbrella Holder bracket&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Improved brake system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Standard features include:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded measurement of just 13” x 15” x 24”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oversized Console (incl scorecard, golf ball, pencil &amp;amp; tee holders)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Independent Handle Adjustment (while maintaining overall width)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-In Accessory Mounts (for Clicgear cart accessories)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable Bag Saddle System (accommodates all bag sizes)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-In Umbrella Mount&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Comes with 3 Year Warranty on the frame (1 Year Warranty on all parts).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Clicgear Model 3.5+ Golf Push Cart - 2016 Lime', 'Clicgear Model 3.5+ Golf Push Cart - 2016 Lime', 'Clicgear Model 3.5+ Golf Push Cart - 2016 Lime'),
(10310, 1, 'Clicgear Model 3.5+ Golf Push Cart - 2016 Orange', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Also Available:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ankermart.com/Clicgear-USA/Clicgear-Model-3-5-Plus-Golf-Push-Cart-2016-Lime&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;Clicgear Model 3.5+ Golf Push Cart - 2016 Lime&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Model 3.5+ is the latest version of our original push cart.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCompact &amp;amp; durable, Model 3.5+ offers &lt;strong&gt;5 main upgrades&lt;/strong&gt;;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;80% larger storage net&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Larger cup holder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;New bag strap system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Improved Umbrella Holder bracket&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Improved brake system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Standard features include:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded measurement of just 13” x 15” x 24”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oversized Console (incl scorecard, golf ball, pencil &amp;amp; tee holders)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Independent Handle Adjustment (while maintaining overall width)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-In Accessory Mounts (for Clicgear cart accessories)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable Bag Saddle System (accommodates all bag sizes)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-In Umbrella Mount&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Comes with 3 Year Warranty on the frame (1 Year Warranty on all parts).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Clicgear Model 3.5+ Golf Push Cart - 2016 Orange', 'Clicgear Model 3.5+ Golf Push Cart - 2016 Orange', 'Clicgear Model 3.5+ Golf Push Cart - 2016 Orange'),
(10311, 1, 'Pado Pure-Wave CM7 Body &amp; Facial Massager, Black/White', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Pure-Wave CM7 features a dual motor cordless design with percussion and vibration motors. &amp;nbsp;Both percussion and vibration motors can be specifically adjusted to your desired intensity. &amp;nbsp;The CM7 model includes 6 different massage sticks to address different areas of the body and unique styles of massage. Soft, Medium or Firm. &amp;nbsp;For percussion mode light is solid green. For vibration light is blinking green. Weight: 1.75 lbs.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Air-Cushion Stick&lt;/strong&gt; - This patented air-cushioned massage head is very versatile and designed to fit many users and body areas. &amp;nbsp;This tip is ideal for users who prefer a softer massage pressure. &amp;nbsp;It is also perfect for massaging between sensitive joint areas such as scapula, knees, shoulder joints and ankles. &amp;nbsp;This tip will also provide great relief to loved ones who suffer from bed sores due to hospitalization. &amp;nbsp;The patented air-cushion stick allows you to massage areas that most massagers wouldn\'t, such as elbows, knees, hands and feet. Use Pure Wave to shorten muscle recovery time and increase well being.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Point Stick&lt;/strong&gt; - Do you enjoy a deep tissue massage or firm acupressure technique? &amp;nbsp;Some may find this a little painful, but if you find pleasure in a therapist\'s elbow digging into your muscles, this tip is for you. &amp;nbsp;The combination of pin-point acupressure tip and the Pure-Wave\'s powerful percussion motor will allow you to drill into those stubborn knots. &amp;nbsp;If you suffer from stiff neck, using this tip in the trapezius area will help relieve the stiffness.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;6-Head Stick&lt;/strong&gt; - If you enjoy deep tissue sports massage, this tip is for you. &amp;nbsp;The firmness of this massage head is great for hitting bigger muscle areas. &amp;nbsp;Use it to loosen up those tight hamstrings, cramping calves, sore lower back and stiff hips. This massage head will help prevent sports injury and also speed up muscle recovery time. This tip is very popular for people with diabetes to help relieve cramping legs and improve circulation in the feet and calves.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Body Massage Oil Stick (Available with CM7 Only) &lt;/strong&gt;- Wouldn\'t it be great if you can apply your favorite massage oil or pain relieving cream to those hard to reach areas like your middle and upper back. Wouldn\'t it be even better if you can massage those areas at the same time by yourself. Pure-Wave\'s Body Massage Oil stick is your solution. This tip although designed originally to slip over the percussion side threads (snugly) can be used with both the percussion and vibration motor modes along with your favorite cream. &amp;nbsp;In addition, give your spouse or partner an awesome massage with Body Massage Oil Stick. They will think they are visiting their favorite spa.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scalp Massage Stick (Available with CM7 Only)&lt;/strong&gt; - Close your eyes, take a deep breath, relax and run Pure-Wave\'s Scalp Massage Stick through your hair and scalp. You will feel like you are getting your hair washed and scalp massaged at a 5 star hair salon. This unique scalp massage tip is a great way to relieve tension and headache. Use the scalp massager after a long day at work to relax and wind down. This tip is a favorite amongst our customers and also a great way to massage in hair regrowth formulas as well. Designed originally to slip over the percussion side threads (snugly) can be used with both the percussion and vibration motor modes/sides.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Facial Massage Stick &amp;nbsp;(Available with CM7 Only)&lt;/strong&gt; - Want to revitalize your face to feel young and healthy? &amp;nbsp;You may already spend time taking care of your face with various cleansers, toners, creams and moisturizers. With Pure-Wave CM7 you have the ability to work in a facial massage to your evening moisturizing treatments. The facial massage stick will promote deeper penetration of facial moisturizers. Simply attach the facial massage stick to the vibration massage tip at the end of the handle and turn on the vibration mode. Massage with smooth motions to work moisturizer into your skin with the massage stick. In short time, your face will feel more refreshed and relaxed.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pure-Wave CM7 Massager&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6 massage sticks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UL approved charger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pure-Wave Stand&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;User manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tech Specs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;&gt;Battery: 7.2 V Lithium-Ion 2200ma 18650 X 2 Cell&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charge Time: (1) One Hour&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charge Duration: 180 Min Continuous / 1 Week @ 20-30 Min Use/day&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Percussion Motor: 7.2v, Dc, 3700 Rpm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Percussion Speed: Variable Speed (1,500 Rpm - 3,700 Rpm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Facial Vibration Motor (Cm7 Only): 7.2 V, Dc&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Facial Vibration Speed (Cm7 Only): Up To 11,000 Rpm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charger Input Voltage: 100v-240v, 50/60hz, 0.4 A Max&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charger Output Voltage: 8.5v, Dc, 1A Max&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Pado Pure-Wave CM7 Body &amp; Facial Massager, Black/White', 'Pado Pure-Wave CM7 Body &amp; Facial Massager, Black/White', 'Pado Pure-Wave CM7 Body &amp; Facial Massager, Black/White'),
(10314, 1, 'SoClean 2 CPAP Cleaner and Sanitizer', '&lt;p&gt;Automated cleaning and sanitizing that kills 99.9% of CPAP germs and bacteria in your mask, hose and reservoir with no disassembly, no water, and no harsh or messy chemicals.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The SoClean 2 is an automated CPAP equipment cleaner and sanitizer. With the SoClean 2, you can sanitize and disinfect your CPAP mask, hose and reservoir without needing to take any pieces apart every day. The machine does not require water or any messy chemicals. Your equipment remains completely dry.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Included with your SoClean purchase is:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Small Bottle Pre-Wash (prior to first use)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cartridge Filter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Check Valve Assembly&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Slot Plug&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AC Power Adapter.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SoClean 2 Features:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;New sleek design&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smaller footprint&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Front display&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Indicator lights throughout the cycle&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Left or right hose insertion option&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy filter cartridge system&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Year Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SoClean Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Destroys 99.9% of bacteria, viruses, and mold*&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Peace-of-mind sanitizing&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Completely automated&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No need to take CPAP equipment apart&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No water or messy chemicals required&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Same sanitizing process used in water purification, hospitals, and produce handling&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'SoClean 2 CPAP Cleaner and Sanitizer', 'SoClean 2 CPAP Cleaner and Sanitizer', 'SoClean 2 CPAP Cleaner and Sanitizer'),
(10312, 1, 'Kraus New Virtus Single Lever Vessel Faucet, Chrome/Brushed Nickel', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Made by Kraus&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBased in New York, Kraus combines substance and style in their products, which are handcrafted and designed by a team of professionals with an unparalleled enthusiasm for making great kitchen and bathroom products. Their diverse assortment of fixtures and accessories guarantees that you can find what you\'re looking for no matter what your lifestyle and budget are.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Modern style meets unwavering functionality in the Virtus Single Lever Vessel Faucet. Made from solid brass for a lifetime of durability and crafted from high-quality components, like the Neoperl aerator, which reduces water waste without sacrificing pressure, and the Kerox ceramic cartridge, which creates a reliable drip-free experience, this faucet is the ideal choice for any bathroom in need of an upgrade. The clean lines and clear aesthetics ensure this product will seamlessly blend with any established motif. Available in either Chrome or Brushed Nickel.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Solid brass construction for maximum durability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Single lever design for effortless flow control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Kerox ceramic cartridge (tested with 500,000 cycles)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High performance / low flow soft-touch Neoperl aerator resists calcium build-up&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lead-free&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Coordinates with any vessel sink&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Limited lifetime warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Installation hardware included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Drain not included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flow rate: 1.5 GPM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Complies with the following standards/codes:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;cUPC&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AB 1953&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;NSF 61&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;NSF 372&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EPA WaterSense&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;DOE&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CEC&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;MASS&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CAL Green&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dimensions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall Height: 12.875&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall Width: 1.625&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall Depth: 8.5&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Spout Height: 10.25&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Spout Reach: 7.25&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max Deck Thickness: 1.25&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Material &amp;amp; Model&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material(s): Solid brass&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Item Number: KRA-KEF-15500&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model:&amp;nbsp;KEF-15500CH (Chrome)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Model:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;KEF-15500BN (Brushed Nickel)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Kraus New Virtus Single Lever Vessel Faucet, Chrome/Brushed Nickel', 'Kraus New Virtus Single Lever Vessel Faucet, Chrome/Brushed Nickel', 'Kraus New Virtus Single Lever Vessel Faucet, Chrome/Brushed Nickel'),
(10313, 1, 'MyPurMist Personal Steam Inhaler for Cold &amp; Congestion Relief', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MyPurMist Handheld Steam Inhaler / Steam Vaporizer / Personal Steam Inhaler&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The steady red light is an indicator for water out or when the timer has run a full cycle. At times a red light may come on prematurely. In such cases the water level may need to be adjusted (fill to the top of the spout) or the device needs to be reset. Distilled water should not be refrigerated.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Doctor Recommended: Steam therapy is widely recommended by leading medical institutions such as the Mayo Clinic, Harvard Medical School, and Kaiser Permanente.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Soothing Steam on Demand. No preparation, no waiting, no cleanup&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Portable and Handheld: Easily use MyPurMist at home, at work or when traveling.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Natural Germ-Free Decongestant: MyPurMist Hand-Held Steam Inhaler delivers germ-free steam.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Steam?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSteam is the recommended approach for natural respiratory relief by doctors and healthcare professionals. Steam is proven to help with the discomfort associated with sinusitis, allergies, cough, colds, flu, and other respiratory conditions&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Steam provides sore and dry passages with moisture, while excess pollen and environmental pollutants are cleansed. Soothing vapor eases nasal congestion and sinus pressure by relieving inflammation. A natural mucolytic, steam helps to thin sticky mucus allowing easy clearance of the airways.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;MyPurMist has re-invented steam delivery by providing germ free steam instantly without the presence of any boiling water. The instant fine mist penetrates deep into your sinuses, nose, and throat for superb relief. MyPurMist\'s soothing mist provides effective symptomatic relief of allergies, sinusitis, colds/flu, cough, laryngitis, parched throat, and discomfort from sore throat.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Instant fine mist penetrates deep into your sinuses, nose, and throat - Provides superb relief&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;100% natural &amp;amp; 100% drug-free&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Handheld, portable, and lightweight&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;99.9999% germ-free warm mist&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microprocessor controls multiple safety features and regulates temperature within 100-1150F&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Instant steam for fast relief - No waiting&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic drying cycle - No cleanup&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No boiling water - No scalding risk&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Great for the whole family (for ages above 12 years)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Handheld Steam Inhaler&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Adult Mask&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;9.5 Oz of MyPurFill&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Storage Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Year Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'MyPurMist Personal Steam Inhaler for Cold &amp; Congestion Relief', 'MyPurMist Personal Steam Inhaler for Cold &amp; Congestion Relief', 'MyPurMist Personal Steam Inhaler for Cold &amp; Congestion Relief'),
(10315, 1, '360 Fly - 4K Panoramic 360 HD Video Camera - Black', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Also Available:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ankermart.com/360-Fly-Panoramic-360-HD-Video-Camera-Black&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;360 Fly - Panoramic 360 HD Video Camera - Black&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;At the heart of the 360fly 4K is a powerful new 16-megapixel image sensor that increases resolution to 2880x2880 pixels - with no seaming or stitching. 360fly 4K is water resistant to 1 ATM, dustproof, shockproof and has a non-slip/soft-touch coating. New features include Motion/Audio Activate, Time-Lapse Mode, First-Person POV Mode, built-in gyroscope, non-assisted GPS, 64 GB internal memory, and full 360° Live Stream via the free Livit mobile app.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The full picture and package.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEverything you need to start capturing and sharing life in 360° 4K video comes with your 360fly 4K camera. Just charge it up, connect it with your iOS or Android mobile device using the 360fly app and hit record.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your 360fly 4K includes:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;360fly 4K Camera&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;USB 2.0 Cable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Cradle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ACA (Action Camera Adapter)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Carrying Pouch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quickstart Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty Card&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Share life in the same 360° you live it.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIt’s a social media world. And 360fly gives you one of the world’s simplest and most seamless ways to share videos and VR experiences with family, friends and fans. All it takes is a push of a button in the 360fly app to share immersive, interactive 360° edits directly to Facebook and YouTube. For social media channels that aren’t yet 360° compatible, the app has everything you need to create and share standard 16:9 edits and panoramic stills.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '360 Fly - 4K Panoramic 360 HD Video Camera - Black', '360 Fly - 4K Panoramic 360 HD Video Camera - Black', '360 Fly - 4K Panoramic 360 HD Video Camera - Black'),
(10316, 1, 'GearWrench 1/2 in. Drive 12-Point Socket Set, 49-Piece', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;84 Tooth Full Polish Chrome Thin Profile Ratchet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Knurled Full Polish Chrome Extensions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sockets Feature Surface Drive® Technology To Reduce Fastener Rounding&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes Storage Case&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Full Polish Chrome Sockets With Large Hard Stamp Size Markings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Meets or Exceeds ASME B107.1, B107.5M, B107.10&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UPC: 099575807015&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Foreign Trade Code: 82042000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Set Piece Count: 49&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Set Included Storage: Blow Mold Case&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Set Size Range Min: 7/16&quot;, 10mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Set Size Range Max: 15/16&quot;, 24mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SAE/Metric/Torx: SAE/Metric&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ASME Specification&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;: B107.1, B107.5M, B1007.10&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Drive Type: 12 Point&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Drive Tang Size: 1/2 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length Format: Standard/Deep&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Finish: Full Polish Chrome&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Set: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'GearWrench 1/2 in. Drive 12-Point Socket Set, 49-Piece', 'GearWrench 1/2 in. Drive 12-Point Socket Set, 49-Piece', 'GearWrench  1/2 in. Drive 12-Point Socket Set, 49-Piece'),
(10317, 1, 'Wonder Core Smart Total Core Workout - Extreme Package', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Resistance level settings&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Sit-ups/Crunches&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Push-ups&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. Bridge&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. Scissor Kicks&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. Forearm/Biceps&lt;br /&gt;\r\n6. Triceps&lt;br /&gt;\r\n7. Ab Tucks&lt;br /&gt;\r\n8. Bicycling&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Includes (Extreme Package)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wonder Core® Smart&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Workout DVD&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;User Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exercise &amp;amp; Nutrition Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Twister Seat and Non-Slip Mat.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Wonder Core Smart Total Core Workout - Extreme Package', 'Wonder Core Smart Total Core Workout - Extreme Package', 'Wonder Core Smart Total Core Workout - Extreme Package'),
(10318, 1, 'Finis Duo Underwater MP3 Player', '&lt;p&gt;The Duo™ is an MP3 player designed for swimmers that offers the highest quality sound without the use of ear buds.&amp;nbsp; The Duo™ utilizes a sleek, two-piece design and Bone Conduction audio transmission to deliver crystal clear audio through cheekbones to the inner ear.&amp;nbsp; An integrated clip design secures the Duo™ to goggle straps to rest on the cheekbones for a comfortable and streamlined fit.&amp;nbsp; A simplified interface offers four buttons to easily navigate between songs, podcasts, audiobooks and other supported audio files.&amp;nbsp; The Duo™ supports unprotected MP3 and WMA files.&amp;nbsp; The included USB magnetic dock allows for universal data transfers and charging.&amp;nbsp; The device offers 4GB of flash memory and a Lithium-Ion rechargeable battery life of up to 7 hours.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BONE CONDUCTION AUDIO TRANSMISSION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAmazingly clear sound in the water without the use of ear buds&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SUPPORTS MP3 &amp;amp; WMA AUDIO FORMATS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCompatible with iTunes®; listen to music, audiobooks, podcasts and more&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4GB OF STORAGE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nStores approximately up to 1000 songs or 60 hours of playback&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;INTEGRATED CLIP DESIGN&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSecures the device to goggle straps to rest on the cheekbones for a comfortable and streamlined fit&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RECHARGEABLE LITHIUM-ION BATTERY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nUp to 7 hours of battery life&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WATERPROOF IPX8&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTested to perform at a depth of 3 meters (10 feet) for 30 minutes. If immersion at 3 meters (10 feet), or deeper, occurs for longer than 30 minutes, damage may occur.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;INTERNATIONALLY PATENTED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;USA – 7.310.427 B2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Europe – 03766986.8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Australia – 2003257031&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;COMES WITH 1 MANUFACTURER WARRANTY.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Finis Duo Underwater MP3 Player', 'Finis Duo Underwater MP3 Player', 'Finis Duo Underwater MP3 Player'),
(10319, 1, 'SteriShoe+ UV Germ + Odor Eliminator / Ultraviolet Shoe Sanitizer', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features &amp;amp; Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The only shoe sanitizer awarded the Seal of Acceptance from the American Podiatric Medical Association.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Clinically-proven to kill up to 99.9% of harmful fungus and bacteria in shoes. Treats the entire shoe from toe to heel with UV light.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Works in just 15 minutes and is 100% ozone free. Ozone hurts the environment and according to the EPA can &quot;potentially cause harmful health consequences.&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dries shoes with a built in fan, active deodorization system with scent pouches, and meets UL\'s stringent safety standards.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Only the SteriShoe+ is built with a rugged steel frame (and not just plastic) for years of funk-free shoes (one year warranty).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your complete SteriShoe kit includes everything you need to sanitize two shoes at once:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 SteriShoe+ Shoe Sanitizers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 5-Watt Ultraviolet Lamps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;8 Scent Pouches ($10 Vaue)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 Shoe Bags&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One-Touch Controller&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Integrated Shoe Dryer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'SteriShoe+ UV Germ + Odor Eliminator / Ultraviolet Shoe Sanitizer', 'SteriShoe+ UV Germ + Odor Eliminator / Ultraviolet Shoe Sanitizer', 'SteriShoe+ UV Germ + Odor Eliminator / Ultraviolet Shoe Sanitizer');
