(10320, 1, 'iHealth Core Wireless Body Composition Scale for Apple and Android', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;iHealth Core Body Composition Scale&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nYou can’t change what you don’t measure. Take control of your health with a complete assessment of your body composition. The iHealth Core meets rigorous accuracy standards in both the US and Europe. Measure and track nine aspects of your overall health including weight, BMI, and muscle mass. The iHealth app lets you set goals, view readings, and share results right from your touchscreen. Measurements are stored on your secure iHealth account, presented in easy to read charts, and weight and BMI are graphed with past readings to view your progress at a glance.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s in the Box?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe iHealth Body Composition Scale comes complete with (1) Wireless body composition scale, (1) User manual, (1) Quick start guide, (4) AA batteries.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Apple iOS and Android Compatiblity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nVisit our support page for a list of compatible devices.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measurements evaluated and interpreted using Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation, and Treatment of High Blood Pressure guidelines&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;FDA approved for accurate systolic/diastolic blood pressure and heart rate results&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wireless, lightweight, blood pressure monitor and easy to use interactive app&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One touch saving and data sharing on secure iHealth Cloud to track results and trends&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technology You Will Love&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOur design works with smart technology to store every reading in your secure iHealth account, so not only do you get precise measurements, but the iHealth app logs your readings, tracks your trends, and allows you to share results instantly. Automatic software updates ensure your device is always on the technological forefront.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Results You Can Use&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMeasurements are presented in easy to read charts, and weight and BMI are graphed with past readings to track progress towards your goals. Share your triumphs with your trainer or friends right from your touchscreen.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quality You Can Trust&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe iHealth Core meets rigorous accuracy standards in both the US and Europe. With long-standing expertise creating and manufacturing medical grade devices, iHealth products are proven reliable and effective.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How it Works&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\niHealth Core uses bioimpedence sensors and a set of proprietary algorithms to measure nine aspects of your body composition. Stand barefoot on the sensors to view your data, use Wi-Fi to automatically sync to the iHealth app on your tablet or smartphone. Measure offline and store up to 200 readings to sync with the app at your convenience.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About iHealth&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\niHealth Lab’s line of products include blood pressure monitors, blood glucose monitors, body analysis scales, pulse oximeters and activity trackers. All products sync directly with a free mobile app to make measuring, tracking, and sharing your health data virtually effortless. Our family of top quality devices are integrated with the latest technology to give you a full picture of your overall health. iHealth: smart for life.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'iHealth Core Wireless Body Composition Scale for Apple and Android', 'iHealth Core Wireless Body Composition Scale for Apple and Android', 'iHealth Core Wireless Body Composition Scale for Apple and Android'),
(10321, 1, 'Magical Butter (PBC) Machine MB2E - Latest Version', '&lt;p&gt;Welcome to a new generation of Health and Happiness®! Now, at the touch of a button, enjoy great-tasting, healthy foods or make natural skin-care products at home with the MB2e Botanical Extractor™.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;MagicalButter has succeeded in transforming a once-confusing, complicated process into a consistent, user-friendly experience, making it easy to integrate botanicals into your healthy lifestyle. The creative possibilities with the MB2E are truly endless.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Completely unique in the kitchen appliance universe, our exclusive microprocessor technology ensures pinpoint accuracy and thorough, even heating at any elevation, in any climate. The MB2e provides a practical solution to extracting nutrients from roots, fruits, and herbs and infusing them directly into butters, oils, tinctures, salves, lotions, and more—right on your countertop! Let your imagination run wild!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NEW MB2E Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No Heat setting for non-activated tinctures, cold soups and beverages, and other goodies&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;130°F/54°C temperature setting for optimized extraction at high altitude or in dry climates&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tips&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Each button runs a preset, microprocessor-controlled cycle—heating, grinding, extracting, and stirring.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;You can extend a cooking cycle by simply selecting a longer duration. The easy self-cleaning function completes the process.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;MagicalButter Makes Herbal Butters, Oils, Tinctures, Soups, Sauces, Salad Dressings, Skin Care Products, Pet Medicines, and more.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight is 8 Pounds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width 10 Inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height 14 Inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth 10 Inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity 2-5 Cups of Liquids&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LoveGlove, PurifyFilter and 110V power cord are included with each machine.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Magical Butter (PBC) Machine MB2E - Latest Version', 'Magical Butter (PBC) Machine MB2E - Latest Version', 'Magical Butter (PBC) Machine MB2E - Latest Version'),
(10322, 1, 'Corentium Home 223 Radon Detector, Radon Gas Detector', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Corentium Radon Monitor&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nA state-of-the-art measuring instrument that combines ease of use and performance.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Corentium monitor allows you to take a reading of the radon levels and its LCD screen displays the average daily, weekly and long term concentrations. Powered by 3 standard AAA batteries, the monitor makes it easy to take measurements from one room to another in order to get an overview of the concentrations of radon in a home, workplace, school, a daycare centre or any other location. The Corentium monitor is also an essential tool to use when performing property inspections or when checking the operation of a radon mitigation system.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The internal architecture of the Corentium monitor comes from advanced technology normally reserved for commercial-type detectors. Particular attention has been paid to the quality and protection of the internal components, allowing the use of algorithms for signal analysis that are more sophisticated. The Corentium monitor quickly adapts to its environment and eliminates inaccuracies related to external factors, allowing it to obtain the best accuracy in its niche.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Corentium monitor is guaranteed for one year and in normal home use, it requires no annual calibrations throughout its useful life, estimated at over 10 years.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;When accuracy matters&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCorentium Home adapts to its environment and eliminates inaccuracies. That is why it is the most accurate radon level test in its category.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Battery life marvel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDesigned for durability and efficiency, the batteries will keep Corentium Home monitoring for two years monitoring the air and protecting your health.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extremely accurate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LCD display, short term from one to seven days, and long term one year average.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;USA version in pCi/L&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Designed in Europe, and tested in Japan&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unaffected by humidity, electromagnetic interference and dust&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2-year battery life powered by 3AAA batteries&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Corentium Home 223 Radon Detector, Radon Gas Detector', 'Corentium Home 223 Radon Detector, Radon Gas Detector', 'Corentium Home 223 Radon Detector, Radon Gas Detector'),
(10323, 1, 'Cassia Hub Connected Home Kit', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Product&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The first Bluetooth router and winner of the Best of CES 2016 Award for Connected Home Product&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Patent pending Smart Antenna technology extends your Bluetooth range to anywhere in your home&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control multiple Bluetooth devices at once, like LED bulbs or smart plugs, individually or in groups&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Specialized audio support lets you stream music to multiple Bluetooth speakers in any room ·&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bluetooth speaker, one Bluetooth multi-color LED, and oneBluetooth Smart Plug, controlled by the HUB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Cassia Hub Connected Home Kit which includes a Cassia Hub, Bluetooth Speaker, Multi-Color LED, and Smart Plug is the ideal solution for streaming high quality audio, controlling lights and appliances with unparalleled range throughout your home and beyond.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Cassia Hub offers first of it’s kind Bluetooth Routing technology and an elegant design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Cassia Hub easily connects and controls up to 22-compatible Bluetooth enabled devices. No longer are customers limited to 2-devices (e.g. 1-Smart Phone and 1-Speaker).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Consumer Bluetooth devices typically only have a range around 30 feet (10 meters). Now with the Cassia Hub, the same devices have open air communication up to 1000+ feet (300+ meters) or the ability to penetrate 3-interior walls (on average).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;360 degree sound, Bluetooth Speaker is included:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stereo 2.1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual bass radiator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built in Microphone&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Aux In&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Up to 10-hours of playback time on rechargeable battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;NFC easy connect and disconnect&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Water resistant enclosure&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bluetooth Multi-color LED is included&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;RGBW 4-color light&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ability to turn on / off via Cassia App&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ability to adjust brightness and color&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ability to turn lights on when you are not at home for improved security&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Create mood lighting and/or party scene&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;25,000 hour life expectancy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy savings over traditional light sources ≥ 80%&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Environmental friendly. No mercury harmful substances, no radiation, no UV and no flash.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Smart Plug is included&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Supports both 110v and 220v&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ability to turn on / off via Cassia App&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi-plug input support&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Works with household and office appliances&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;25,000 hour life expectancy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;For indoor use only; not waterproof&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Environmental friendly. No mercury harmful substances, no radiation, and no UV.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What is included in the box:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) Cassia Hub / Power Adapter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) Bluetooth Speaker&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(3) Multi-color Bluetooth LED\'s&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) Smart plug&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Service &amp;amp; Support = One-year limited warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Cassia Hub Connected Home Kit', 'Cassia Hub Connected Home Kit', 'Cassia Hub Connected Home Kit'),
(10324, 1, 'Runtastic Moment Elite - Activity Tracker', '&lt;p&gt;Active folks with a feeling for fashion &amp;amp; style will love the quality and classic look of Moment Elite. The watch combines high wearing comfort, attractive design and a unique set of features. Just like any other activity tracker, Elite tracks your steps, active minutes, calories burned, as well as your sleep. The integrated alarm function wakes you with gentle vibrations on your wrist, while the progress indicator shows you at just one glance and anytime how far you are from reaching your daily goal (like 10,000 steps, for instance).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Monitor your daily habits, set personal goals and reach them with this stylish accessory on your wrist. There’s more: Unlike other activity trackers, Moment needs no charging. The lithium battery lasts for up to six months and is easy to exchange. In combination with the Runtastic Me app, you can tap the full potential of your Runtastic Moment. The app provides a detailed overview of all your tracked values and stats. Plus, Moment always shows the correct local time! Forget about daylight saving time or time zone changes when travelling - Moment will sync automatically. You can even display the distance covered during fitness activities on your Moment when connected with your Runtastic app.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features &amp;amp; Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;24/7 timekeeping &amp;amp; activity tracking&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Provides information on daily steps, distance, calories burned, sleep duration &amp;amp; cycles, etc.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High quality, classic design &amp;amp; innovative technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Reach your goals &amp;amp; monitor your daily progress directly on your watch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No charging necessary: long-lasting lithium battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Waterproof up to 300 ft / 100m&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Supported Devices:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;iPhone: iPhone 4s and newer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Android: Bluetooth® Smart Ready devices running Android 4.3 or higher&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Windows Phone: Bluetooth® Smart Ready smartphones running WP 8.1 or higher&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compatible Apps:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Runtastic Me&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Runtastic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Package Contents:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Runtastic Moment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x lithium battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Screwdriver for battery change&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4 x spare screws&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Quick Instructions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(Comes with Manufacturer Warranty)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Weight (incl. packaging):&lt;/strong&gt; 242g&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Material:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stainless steel case (ø 1.81in / 46mm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Scratch-proof mineral glass&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Textile &amp;amp; leather strap (upper side textile, bottom side leather)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Runtastic Moment Elite - Activity Tracker', 'Runtastic Moment Elite - Activity Tracker', 'Runtastic Moment Elite - Activity Tracker'),
(10325, 1, 'Livescribe 3 Smartpen Pro Edition for Android and iOS', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Everything from paper, pulled into a mobile app&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHandwritten notes instantly appear on your smartphone and tablet.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nRecords audio that’s synchronized with your written notes using the mics on your smartphone or tablet.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIn the Livescribe+ mobile app, notes become useful when they are tagged, searchable or converted to text.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEasily integrate your notes with the rest of your mobile life - create tasks, reminders, calendar events, contacts and more with just a few taps of your finger.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compatibility:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Livescribe+ for Android: Requires Android v4.4.2 (KitKat) or newer and Bluetooth Smart support&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Livescribe+ for iOS: Bluetooth Smart Ready device running iOS 8 or newer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Livescribe 3 smartpen - Black &amp;amp; Dark Chrome&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Livescribe+ Mobile App (free download from the App Store and Google Play)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Leather Smartpen Portfolio&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One-Year Subscription to Evernote Premium (download)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;100 sheet Dot Paper Journal&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Micro USB Charging Cable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Integrated Stylus (covers charging port)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 Tungsten-Carbide Ink Cartridges - Black Medium&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Livescribe 3 smartpen Basics Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Livescribe 3 Smartpen Pro Edition Specs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Connectivity- Bluetooth Smart (Bluetooth 4.0)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery- Rechargeable lithium (non-removable)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charging- Connects to your computer wtih micro-USB cable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Processor- ARM 9&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Camera- High speed infrared camera&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Audio- Recording and play back of audio is handled by your companion device&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color- Livescribe 3 Pro Edition: Black &amp;amp; Dark Chrome&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 162.0 mm (6.38 in.)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 14.9 mm (0.59 in.)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 34 grams (1.2 oz.)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ink Cartridge Tungsten carbide ballpoint ink cartridge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;67 mm length x 2.5 mm diameter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;NOTE: ink cartridges used for Sky™/Echo™/Pulse™ smartpens will not fit the Livescribe 3 smartpen&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How It Works&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Livescribe 3 smartpen is designed with the meticulous attention-to-detail that a premium writing instrument deserves. From the integrated stylus cap, down to the Swiss-made tungsten-carbide ballpoint ink cartridge, we\'ve paid close attention to deliver an experience that is worthy of the title of your new favorite pen. But it is the amazing amount of technology packed inside the Livescribe 3 that really delivers the magic. The infrared camera in the tip of the pen captures your handwriting, storing it on the built-in memory. When it\'s paired to your tablet or smartphone, all your notes are synced to the Livescribe+ mobile app.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bluetooth Smart — Quicker Pairing, Longer Battery Life&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nLivescribe 3 smartpen uses Bluetooth Smart technology to pair with compatible mobile devices to support over 14 hours of continuous use between charges. Pairing is also made much easier – just turn on the Livescribe 3 and accept the pairing request on your mobile device with a single tap. After that, your smartpen will pair automatically each time you launch the app.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Livescribe+ Mobile App&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAvailable on iOS and Android, Livescribe+ is the companion to the Livescribe 3 smartpen that’s designed to quickly make your notes more useful. Livescribe+ makes it easy to integrate your notes with the rest of your mobile life:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Find what you need quickly with incredibly accurate handwriting search&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Convert your handwritten notes to text and use them in any doc or app&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Create contacts, appointments and more from your handwritten notes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Use easy sharing options to send notes to a variety of apps and services&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Record audio that syncs to your handwriting&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Livescribe 3 Smartpen Pro Edition for Android and iOS', 'Livescribe 3 Smartpen Pro Edition for Android and iOS', 'Livescribe 3 Smartpen Pro Edition for Android and iOS'),
