ons&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Metal Steam Head: 6 in / 15.2 cm wide metal steam head&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Carton Dimension: 18 in x 12 in x 17 in / 45.7 cm x 30.4 cm x 43.1 cm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembled Dimension: 15 in x 10 in x 64 in / 38.1 cm x 24.4 cm x 162.5 cm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Carton Weight: 18 lbs / 8.16 kg (metal head)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electrical Certifications: UL, cUL, TUV/GS, CE, NOM and ANCE Listed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steam Time per Filling: 90 minutes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Water Capacity: 3/4 gal / 2.84 L&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage: 120V&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wattage: 1300W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cord Plug: NEMA 5-15&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Jiffy Personal Clothing Steamer, Metal Head with Hose, J-2000M', 'Jiffy Personal Clothing Steamer, Metal Head with Hose, J-2000M', 'Jiffy Personal Clothing Steamer, Metal Head with Hose, J-2000M'),
(10332, 1, 'Chair Gym Total Body Workout , Blue', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features &amp;amp; Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Over 50 different exercises&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Improves strength, flexibility, and energy levels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3 levels of resistance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Supports over 350lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Safely supports the back while exercising.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy to set up!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folds &amp;amp; rolls away for fast easy storage.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Easy &amp;amp; Convenient&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTotal body workout in just minutes!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No More Bulky Weights&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3 Smooth adjustable resistant bands.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Back Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDouble seat roll bars for extra support.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Portable Design&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFolds &amp;amp; rolls away for fast easy storage&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6 Free Video Workouts in 1&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;20 min TOTAL BODY EXPRESS workout DVD&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Total Body Conditioning DVD&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Upper Body Strength &amp;amp; Flexibility DVD&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lower Body Strength &amp;amp; Flexibility DVD&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Core Balance &amp;amp; Stability DVD&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pilates Flow and Stretch DVD&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Chair Gym Total Body Workout , Blue', 'Chair Gym Total Body Workout , Blue', 'Chair Gym Total Body Workout , Blue'),
(10333, 1, 'Thync, The First Wearable For Relaxation And Energy', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THYNC KIT - The Thync system has three simple components &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Module: sits comfortably on your forehead&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Strips: placed on the back of your neck&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;App: control your calm or energy Vibes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features &amp;amp; Specs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The first wearable technology that enhances calm and energy, without alcohol or pills&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Consistent Thync use (3-5 sessions/week) has been clinically proven to improve sleep, balance stress and manage energy levels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Effectiveness and safety tested over five years of development and 5,500 sessions by our team of neurobiologists and neuroscientists&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible with iOS 8+ (iPhone, iPod) and Android OS Lollipop and Marshmallow (Samsung S5 &amp;amp; S6, Nexus5 and 5X, Motorola Nexus 6 and Huawei Nexus 6)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thync: How Good feels&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nUse Thync to sleep better, release stress, or motivate yourself. Thync is unlike any other wearable technology - not a tracker or monitor. Thync acts on your own natural ability to relax or energize by stimulating nerves on your head and neck - all without drinks or pills! If you are motivated to learn and regularly use an entirely new way to relax and energize, then Thync is for you.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How Thync Works&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThync delivers low-energy waveforms to safelty and comfortably stimulate nerves on your head and face, allowing your body to relax or energize. We call these waveforms “Vibes.” Our Vibes were developed by our neuroscientists and engineers after 4 years of proven clinical studies, with thousands of participants. Calm Vibes feel similar to the relaxing sensation of a massage, whereas Energy Vibes deliver a refreshing feeling of a splash of cold water. Thync is simple and safe lifestyle product that has been exempted by the FDA.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Better Sleep&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThync Calm Vibes help you settle down and overcome anxious moments, on-demand. Take the edge off. Beat stress. Unwind after a long day. Relax before bed.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;De-Stress&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThync Calm Vibes help you settle down and overcome anxious moments. Take the edge off. Beat stress. Unwind after a long day. Relax before bed.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Energize&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThync Energy Vibes invigorate you for peak performance. Get motivated. Power through. Boost your workout. Kickstart your day.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s in the Box&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Thync Module&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pack of Calm Strips&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pack of Energy Strips&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charging Cable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How It Works:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;http://www.thync.com/how-it-works&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aVdm_wV9pzg&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Thync, The First Wearable For Relaxation And Energy', 'Thync, The First Wearable For Relaxation And Energy', 'Thync, The First Wearable For Relaxation And Energy'),
(10334, 1, 'JumpSport Fitness Trampoline New Model 200, Black', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Model 200 Fitness Trampoline Overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe JumpSport Model 200 Fitness Trampoline offers an affordable option for anyone looking at introducing a fitness routine that is not only fun, but easier on the body and joints. The cords are the key feature on this Fitness Trampoline that allows for a gentle, stress free workout. The 200 Fitness Trampoline is very easy to assemble with its six straight screw-on legs. In no time, you can be working out and enjoying the benefits of rebounding. Improved balance, lymphatic circulation, bone and joint health and of course a great cardio workout that will burn the calories and help you with your weight management.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;An affordable option to stress-free rebounding&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Straight screw-on legs for ease of assembly&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Enjoy the wonderfully smooth, cushioned bounce&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Benefit from improved lymphatic circulation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fitness that’s fun for everyone!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fast, High Calorie Burn – Trim fat and tone your whole body&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Excellent Cardio Routines&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Great Core Exercises&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Detox / Body Cleansing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Improve your balance &amp;amp; spatial awareness&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Physical Rehab&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low Impact Workout with a wide variety of exercises&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exercise at your own convenience&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Better than a Steel Spring Rebounder&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Virtually Silent FlexBounce System vs. Steel springs &amp;amp; frame become squeaky&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No Stress, Gentle, Smooth Bounce vs. Jarring, unpleasant bounce&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lifetime Frame Warranty vs. 2 year warranty!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Elegant Arched Legs = Super Stable vs. Straight legs are unstable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Over 45% Larger Jumping Area vs. Constricted jumping area&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Model 200 Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;39” black frame with 32.5” skirted mat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6 straight screw-on legs for easy assembly&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;30 EnduroLast 2 elastic cords (Not Adjustable) – tested to millions of bounces!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;FlexBounce Ready offers the ability to upgrade to EnduroLast 3 and 7 adjustable tension setting cords.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes our “Basics” workout DVD for both beginners and beyond&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wide range of fitness accessories available&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight capacity is 250 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;All models come with our Basic Workout DVD that provides viewers with a total-body workout routine. This video meets you where you are at with beginner, intermediate and advanced levels demonstrated during the workout.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;All models (except the 220 and 250) come with 3 additional workouts: Cardio, Core, and Strength.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Warranty:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steel Frame &amp;amp; Legs – Lifetime&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mat – 5 years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EnduroLast 2 Elastic Cords – 2 Years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EnduroLast 3 Elastic Cords – 3 Years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EnduroLast 4 Elastic Cords – 4 Years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EnduroLast XF Elastic Cords – 4 Years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;All other components – 1 year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'JumpSport Fitness Trampoline New Model 200, Black', 'JumpSport Fitness Trampoline New Model 200, Black', 'JumpSport Fitness Trampoline New Model 200, Black');
