(10340, 1, 'NutriBullet LEAN System - Get 2 Free Tubs LEAN Boost', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HOW IT WORKS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNutriBullet LEAN is the world\'s first Precision Nutrient Extractor and&lt;br /&gt;\r\n7-Day Transformation Plan that unlocks the Weight Loss Code in everyday foods, so you can drop pounds and inches faster than you ever thought possible!*&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;UNLOCK THE WEIGHT LOSS CODE FOUND IN EVERYDAY FOODS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOver time, eating the wrong foods in the wrong amounts can send the wrong message to your body, telling it to convert the food you eat into excess body fat. But eating the right foods, in the right amounts and combinations, can create and entirely different code — the &quot;Weight Loss Code.&quot; NutriBullet LEAN uses Precision Nutrient Extraction to unlock the Weight Loss Code found in everyday foods.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE 7-DAY TRANSFORMATION PLAN&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe 7-Day Transformation Plan teaches you how easy it is to unlock the Weight Loss Code and become the leanest, healthiest you possible! You learn how to make perfect, delicious MacroBlasts and Portion Perfect Meals. You\'ll find the recipes, shopping lists, tips, and tricks you need for success. Plus, you\'ll get exclusive access to the NutriBullet LEAN app which makes following the plan and generating your shopping lists a breeze!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU GET&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;1. NutriBullet LEAN Power Base&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNutriBullet LEAN uses 1200 Watts of pure extraction power and distinctive MacroBlast Mode technology to transform ordinary foods into extraordinary nutrition - extracting whole fruits, vegetables, nuts, seeds, and other superfoods into silky-smooth drinkable form.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. NutriBullet LEAN 7-Day Transformation Plan&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nLearn how to eat exactly the right foods, in the right portions at the right times. This program also includes instructions on how to operate your NutriBullet LEAN to make perfect, delicious MacroBlasts and Portion Perfect Meals. Plus, you’ll find the recipes, shopping lists, tips, and tricks you need to become the leanest, healthiest you possible!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. An $80 Value Yours Free! 2 x Tubs NutriBullet LEAN Boost™&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNutriBullet LEAN Boost — a premium blend of protein, fiber, and prebiotics is designed to optimize your weight loss potential. This flavorful formula features ingredients that promote satiety and regularity, and naturally support optimum metabolic functioning.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. The Portion Perfect Set&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 Measured 32-oz MacroBlast Cups&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Measured Short Cup&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Portion Perfect Plate Divider&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Healthy Fats Measuring Spoon&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Boosts &amp;amp; Freebies Measuring Spoon&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. Core Accessories&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extractor Blade&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comfort Lip Ring&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flip Top To-Go Lid&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 Stay-Fresh Resealable Lids&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6. Support Tools&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;NutriBullet LEAN App&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;24/7 Access to NutriLiving.com&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'NutriBullet LEAN System - Get 2 Free Tubs LEAN Boost', 'NutriBullet LEAN System - Get 2 Free Tubs LEAN Boost', 'NutriBullet LEAN System - Get 2 Free Tubs LEAN Boost'),
(10341, 1, 'Rachael Ray Cucina Hard-Anodized 12-Piece Cookware Set, Red Handles', '&lt;p&gt;Grace the stovetop and the kitchen with the inviting pots and pans in the Rachael Ray Cucina Hard-Anodized Nonstick 12-Piece Cookware Set.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Enhance the cooking experience with the durable, artisan-styled pots and pans in the Rachael Ray Cucina Hard-Anodized Nonstick 12-Piece Cookware Set. Sturdily crafted from hard-anodized aluminum, the attractive rustic, modern cookware provides fast, even heating, helping to reduce hot spots that can burn foods. The appealing espresso-colored nonstick is PFOA-free and long-lasting to provide easy food release and cleanup. Offering a comfortable grasp, the rustically designed cookware’s silicone-over-stainless-steel handles are dual riveted for added strength and boast an earthy, modern hue for a dash of color. The saucepans, stockpot and sauté feature shatter-resistant glass lids with wide stainless steel rims and allow simmering soups and sauces to be monitored without losing heat or moisture. Including two skillets, the cookware set also offers a sturdy yet flexible slotted nylon turner and spoon that match the handles’ color. Oven safe to 400°F, the pots and pans are suitable for all stovetops, except induction. Dishwasher safe for convenience, this cookware set makes a handsome addition to serveware, dinnerware and other cookware pieces in the beautiful Rachael Ray Cucina collection.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Crafted from sturdy hard-anodized aluminum for fast, even heating, and to help reduce hot spots that can burn foods.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The appealing espresso-colored nonstick is PFOA-free and long-lasting to provide easy food release and cleanup.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Offering a comfortable grasp, the silicone-over-stainless-steel handles are dual riveted for added strength and boast an earthy, modern color.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shatter-resistant glass lids feature wide stainless steel rims and allow cooking to be monitored without losing heat or moisture.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes a sturdy yet flexible slotted nylon turner and spoon that match the handles’ stylish color.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oven Safe to 400°F&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lifetime Limited Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;More Info&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Clean and Care: Dishwasher Safe&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes: 1-Quart &amp;amp; 2-Quart Covered Saucepans, 6-Quart Covered Stockpot, 8-1/2-Inch &amp;amp; 10-Inch Skillets, 3-Quart Covered Saute, Slotted Nylon Turner &amp;amp; Spoon&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Made In: Thailand&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Made Of: Hard Anodized&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: Limited Lifetime Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 17.5 lb.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Gray&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Rachael Ray Cucina Hard-Anodized 12-Piece Cookware Set, Red Handles', 'Rachael Ray Cucina Hard-Anodized 12-Piece Cookware Set, Red Handles', 'Rachael Ray Cucina Hard-Anodized 12-Piece Cookware Set, Red Handles'),
(10342, 1, 'Trigger Point Performance Kit, Total Body Deep Tissue Self-Massage', '&lt;p&gt;The Performance Kit from Trigger Point provides users with premium equipment and how-to instructions designed to guide any user through the complexity of biomechanics and the proper self-massage techniques used to increase mobility and achieve optimal performance. Easy to follow step-by-step instructions focus on key areas that commonly cause problems and limit physical performance. With access to Trigger Point\'s video, you\'ll become a master on how to manage your own therapeutic self-care at home, on the road, or at the gym. You don\'t have to be a professional athlete or have a kinesiology degree to perform at new higher levels; all you need is the Trigger Point Performance Collection to start feeling better and moving more freely through daily deep tissue massage.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performance Kit Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Six (6) premium Trigger Point performance tools for deep tissue massage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Total Body E-Book and Ultimate 6 E-book illustrated instructional guides&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy step-by-step instruction guide through Trigger Point\'s Video Portal&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Safe and efficient way to help alleviate muscle tension and restore healthy biomechanics&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Empowering programming designed for self-care application&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Durable, premium equipment is travel friendly&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Kit Includes:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;TP Massage Ball (2)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;TP 2-Ball Sleeve (1)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;FootBaller (1)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;QuadBaller (1)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Baller Block (1)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Trigger Point Performance Kit, Total Body Deep Tissue Self-Massage', 'Trigger Point Performance Kit, Total Body Deep Tissue Self-Massage', 'Trigger Point Performance Kit, Total Body Deep Tissue Self-Massage'),
(10550, 1, 'Briggs &amp; Stratton Powerbuilt OHV Vertical Engine 500cc, Electric Start', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BRIGGS &amp;amp; STRATTON POWERBUILT OHV VERTICAL ENGINE — 500CC, 1IN. X 3 5/32IN. SHAFT, ELECTRIC START, MODEL# 31R907-0007-G1&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dura-Bore™ cast iron cylinder sleeve for extended life&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maintenance-free Magnetron® electronic ignition and float carburetor for consistent, easy starts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual-Clean™ dual-element air cleaner for maximum protection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Patented balancing system for smoother performance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Gear-driven DuraLube™ splash lubrication bathes all internal engine parts with oil&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT SUMMARY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;The Briggs &amp;amp; Stratton Powerbuilt™ 500cc Engine features 12V electric start, rewind backup and a 9 Amp DC alternator. The exhaust manifold and muffler are included but fuel tank is omitted. For use on riding lawn mowers, wide area walk-behind mowers and trail mowers. Emission-compliant engine is for sale in all 50 states.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S INCLUDED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;(1) Engine with electric start&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES + BENEFITS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dura-Bore™ cast iron cylinder sleeve for extended life&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maintenance-free Magnetron® electronic ignition and float carburetor for consistent, easy starts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual-Clean™ dual-element air cleaner for maximum protection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Patented balancing system for smoother performance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Gear-driven DuraLube™ splash lubrication bathes all internal engine parts with oil&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tool-less air filter cover for easy access&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy-duty Teflon sleeve bearing withstands load and reduces wear&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automotive dipstick makes checking oil levels easy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KEY SPECS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: Briggs &amp;amp; Stratton&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer\'s Warranty: 2 years consumer use / 1 year commercial use&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ship Weight: 81.0 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engine Displacement (cc): 500&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Start Type: Electric&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Application: Riding mower, lawn tractor, trail mower&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engine Type: Intek&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Output: Vertical&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Crankshaft&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;: 1 x 3 5/32&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Diameter (in.): 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Length (in.): 3 5/32&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Keyway (in.): 1/4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft End Tapped (Diameter (in.)/Threads per inch): 7/16-20&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Rotation (From PTO Shaft Side): CCW&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Gear Reduction: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bearing Type: Plain&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cylinders (qty.): 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cylinder Bore: Cast iron&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bore x Stroke (in.): 3.56 x 3.06&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compression Ratio: 8.5:1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cooling System:&amp;nbsp; cooled&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Air Cleaner Type: Dual element&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel Tank: Not included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel Type: Gasoline&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel Pump: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel Filter: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oil Capacity (qt.): 1 1/2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lubrication System: Splash&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low Oil Alert: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low Oil Shutdown: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ignition System: Electronic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Governor System: Mechanical&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Carburetor: Float&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Throttle Control: Remote&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Choke Control: Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max. RPM: 3,300&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charging System Amps: 9&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Muffler Included: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flywheel Brake: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto Compression Release&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bolt Circle (in.)&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions L x W x H (in.): 19 x 16 x 13&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EPA/CARB Approval (California Air Resource Board): Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Briggs &amp; Stratton Powerbuilt OHV Vertical Engine 500cc, Electric Start', 'Briggs &amp; Stratton Powerbuilt OHV Vertical Engine 500cc, Electric Start', 'Briggs &amp; Stratton Powerbuilt OHV Vertical Engine 500cc, Electric Start'),
(10344, 1, 'Lebert Fitness Pro Pack', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bundle All 3 Products:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lebert Equalizer®&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lebert Buddy System™&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lebert Stretch Strap™&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Simplify your exercise routine, and conquer your fitness goals with the LEBERT EQUALIZER Total Body Strengthener. The Lebert Equalizer is a simple, portable, yet multi-purpose and versatile piece of strength training equipment that works arms, chest, back and core muscles like no other can, using your own body weight as resistance. Created by personal trainer and Taekwondo Black Belt, Marc Lebert, the Equalizer is now being used by athletes of all levels and ages, in bootcamps, group fitness, sports conditioning classes, martial arts clubs and home gyms everywhere.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Lebert Fitness Pro Pack', 'Lebert Fitness Pro Pack', 'Lebert Fitness Pro Pack'),
(10346, 1, 'Fuzion Z300 Pro Scooter, All New Design - 2017 Version', '&lt;p&gt;The Fuzion Z300 Pro Scooter has been revamped for the 2017 campaign. Color combinations and deck graphics have been updated to make the already solid Z300 a standout in a deep entry level/ intermediate scooter market. The Z300 has been engineered to handle any street or park obstacle. The Z300 is built around Fuzion’s renowned Dog Bone deck and now features a brand new tapered deck neck design. Wider and longer deck&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Dog Bone deck design allows for the landing forces to be distributed evenly across the decks outer surface making this one tough lightweight deck. Fuzion’s Z300 delivers the best “complete” in the market.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The deck has a 3 degree top and bottom concavity making it ideal for grinds and stable landings and an 82.5 degree head tube angle. The entire neck tube is internally reinforced for added strength.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Fuzion Z300 comes fully equipped with an HIC compression system, Fuzion integrated and sealed headset bearings, Light weight one piece alloy steel fork, Chromoly T bars. Aluminum alloy staggered triple bolt clamp, 110 mm cast 88 a PU and aluminum core wheels with lightning fast ABEC 9 bearings and a bolt on easy to adjust steel flex brake.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This scooter is competition ready right out of the box. It weighs just less than 8 pounds and is designed for high speed, high impact riding. The Fuzion Z300 can handle any skate park or street obstacle and will surely help you conquer your best tricks!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6061 T6 Aluminum Deck &amp;amp; Neck 82.5 angle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dog-bone Deck 20.5″ L x 4.50″ W (520 mm X 114 mm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fully Sealed and Integrated Headset Bearings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;HIC Compression System&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One Piece High Tensile Steel Threadless Fork&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4130 Chromoly T Bars 22″ H x 21” W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;60 MM Alloy Triple Bolt Staggered Headset Clamp&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;110mm Cast 88 a PU with Aluminum Core Wheels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual Bolt Flex Style bolt on Rattle Free Steel Break&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuzion Rib Pattern Supper Control TPR Grips with Nylon Bar Ends&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Die Cut Full Deck Edge to Edge Fuzion Grip Tape&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Age: 8+&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max Weight: 220 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Skill Level: Intermediate to Advance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight: 7.9 lbs. (3.58 Kg.)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Dimensions: 26.77” x 30.71” x 4.25”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Box Dimensions: 25.5” x 18” x 4.75”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Fuzion Z300 Pro Scooter, All New Design - 2017 Version', 'Fuzion Z300 Pro Scooter, All New Design - 2017 Version', 'Fuzion Z300 Pro Scooter, All New Design - 2017 Version'),
(10347, 1, 'Fuzion Z350 Pro Scooter, All New Design - 2017 Version', '&lt;p&gt;For the 2017 Campaign we’ve made needed changed to the Z350. The Z350 was redesigned to meet the demand of riders that want to go big and go hard. With a brand new wider and longer deck&lt;br /&gt;\r\nand “Z” neck cut out, the Z350 comes equipped with an HIC compression system, NECO sealed and integrated head set all built around Fuzion’s Signature Dog Bone design deck.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Fuzion’s unique Dog Bone deck and neck design, crafted from aircraft grade 6061 T6 aluminum, evenly distributes impact forces across the deck’s outer surface, making this one of the toughest and lightest decks around. Our 3 degree top and bottom concavity deck design delivers added stability when landing and makes for super smooth grinds. The Dog-Bone designed side deck rails also allows for easier grab tricks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6061 T6 Aluminum Deck &amp;amp; Neck 82.5 angle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dog-bone Deck 20.5″ L x 4.50″ W (520 mm X 114 mm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;HIC Compression System&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;NECO Fully Sealed and Integrated Headset Bearings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CNC Aluminum Fork&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuzion 23″ H x 21″ W 4130 Chromoly Bars&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;40 MM Fuzion “Strangler” Alloy Headset Clamp&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;110mm Cast 88 a PU &amp;amp; Aluminum Core Wheels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual Bolt Flex Style bolt on Rattle Free Steel Break&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuzion Rib Pattern Supper Control TPR Grips with Nylon Bar Ends&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Die Cut Full Deck Edge to Edge Fuzion Grip Tape&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Specifications:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Age: 8 +&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max Weight: 220 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Skill Level: Intermediate to Advance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight: 7.9 lbs. (3.58 Kg.)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Dimensions: 26.77” x 30.71” x 4.25”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Box Dimensions: 26.8” X 5.3” X 20.1”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Fuzion Z350 Pro Scooter, All New Design - 2017 Version', 'Fuzion Z350 Pro Scooter, All New Design - 2017 Version', 'Fuzion Z350 Pro Scooter, All New Design - 2017 Version'),
(10345, 1, 'Fuzion Z375 Pro Scooter Signature - Limited Edition by Michael Luzzi', '&lt;p&gt;The Z375 is built for performance. Wider longer deck, CNC head tube cut out together with Fuzion’s CNC forged aluminum fork the Z375 comes with NECO Integrated and Sealed Headset Bearings. The Z375 comes fully loaded to meet the demand of the most serious advance rider. If you are a technical rider looking to shred every rail and ledge you come across the Z375 is the Scooter for you.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With the Fuzion’s unique Dog Bone deck and neck design impact forces are evenly distributed around the decks outer surface making this one of the toughest and lightest decks around. Our 3 degree top and bottom concave deck design delivers added landing stability and makes for super smooth grinds. Fuzion’s neck tube uses the same Dog Bone extrusion design plus it is internally reinforced for added strength and the Dog-Bone designed deck side rails allows for easier grab tricks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Z375 components list consists of a light and tough CNC forged aluminum fork, oversized Fuzion Chromoly T bars, 3 Bolt Fuzion’s only “Strangler” clamp. 110mm cast 88 a PU aluminum core wheels with ABEC 9 bearings offering speed, grip and a great bounce together with long wear.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Z375 is the “complete” for the rider who knows exactly which components make up a great scooter. This is a truly custom scooter for the price of a complete.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6061 T6 Aluminum Deck &amp;amp; Neck 82.5 angle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dog-bone Deck 20.5″ L x 4.50″ W (520 mm X 114 mm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;HIC Compression System&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;NECO Fully Sealed and Integrated Headset Bearings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CNC Aluminum Fork&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuzion Chromoly Bars (22” H x 21″ W)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;76 MM Aluminum “Strangler” Headset Clamp&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;110mm Cast 88a PU Aluminum Core Wheels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual Bolt Flex Style bolt on Rattle Free Steel Break&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuzion Rib Pattern Supper Control TPR Grips with Nylon Bar Ends&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Die Cut Full Deck Edge to Edge Fuzion Grip Tape&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Age: 8 +&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max Weight: 220 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Skill Level: Advance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight: 7.9 lbs. (3.58 Kg.)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Dimensions: 26.77” x 30.71” x 4.25”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Box Dimensions: 25.5” x 18” x 4.75”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Container 40′: 1450&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Container 40′ HQ: 1700&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Fuzion Z375 Pro Scooter Signature - Limited Edition by Michael Luzzi', 'Fuzion Z375 Pro Scooter Signature - Limited Edition by Michael Luzzi', 'Fuzion Z375 Pro Scooter Signature - Limited Edition by Michael Luzzi'),
