t;110mm Cast 88a PU Aluminum Core Wheels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual Bolt Flex Style bolt on Rattle Free Steel Break&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuzion Rib Pattern Supper Control TPR Grips with Nylon Bar Ends&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Die Cut Full Deck Edge to Edge Fuzion Grip Tape&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Age: 8 +&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max Weight: 220 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Skill Level: Advance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight: 7.9 lbs. (3.58 Kg.)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Dimensions: 26.77” x 30.71” x 4.25”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Box Dimensions: 25.5” x 18” x 4.75”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Container 40′: 1450&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Container 40′ HQ: 1700&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Fuzion Z375 Pro Scooter Palldium Silver', 'Fuzion Z375 Pro Scooter Palldium Silver', 'Fuzion Z375 Pro Scooter Palldium Silver'),
(10349, 1, 'Globber Adult One Kick Folding Scooter', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This new addition to the Globber family allows use of a full size scooter for both every day commuters and weekend travelers, the easy to transport One Kick Folding mechanism allows for storage in even the tightest of spaces.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;You no longer have to carry it thanks to its trolley mode feature easy parking-storage option (with brake) thanks to its wheel locking feature, it can be stored vertically.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The rigidity of extruded aluminum creates a solid base for riders new and advanced. Wide and low to the ground to resist against wear from intensive daily use. Adjustable Handlebar adapted to different body types, this can be adjusted to three heights.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;A wide, curved handlebar (48 cm) adapted for daily use provides real comfort.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flexible, dual-injection material for more comfort and resistance.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rear Brake with lever on the handlebar. A reassuring brake lever that’s easy to use for getting around an urban setting. Large 180 mm wheels made of HR &amp;amp; HQ PU (high rebound, high quality polyurethane), with nylon cores, mounted on ABEC 7 bearing. Reinforced Double Clamp Mudguards to protect against splashes.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Globber Adult One Kick Folding Scooter', 'Globber Adult One Kick Folding Scooter', 'Globber Adult One Kick Folding Scooter');
