fi - Green Juice Super Food Supplement, Six Bottles', 'Organifi - Green Juice Super Food Supplement, Six Bottles'),
(10353, 1, 'Micro Suspension Scooter', '&lt;p&gt;Not just for kids to enjoy, Micro Scooter extends its handy design for adults who want the ultimate commuting tool. This adult suspension scooter features big 200mm wheels, ensuring a robust and reliable experience, while the 360 degree steering means you can take total control. Contemporary and cool, this two-wheel scooter is an essential when whizzing around busy streets as it folds away with ease, making it a convenient choice when transporting and storing. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Micro Scooter adult scooter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fold-up design, branded print, two wheels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max weight of adult 95kg&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight of scooter 6.4kg&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Suspension&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Foldable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable handlebar height 84-106cm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steers like a bike&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;360 Steering&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wheel diameter 200mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Micro Suspension Scooter', 'Micro Suspension Scooter', 'Micro Suspension Scooter'),
(10355, 1, 'Osmo Wonder Kit', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Meet Osmo&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOsmo is an award-winning game system that will change the way your child interacts with the iPad by opening it up to hands-on play.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Now you can play with your hands&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPut your iPad in the Osmo base with the red reflector over the camera – and now it can see what’s in front of it.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Coding Game&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOsmo Coding uses hands-on physical blocks to control Awbie, a playful character who loves delicious strawberries. Each block is a coding command that directs Awbie on a wondrous tree-shaking, strawberry-munching adventure.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Tangram Game&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nArrange wooden puzzle pieces to match on-screen shapes. Animals, objects, humans and more. Play with a friend or challenge yourself to increasingly more difficult levels as your handiwork lights up with each victory.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;3. Words Game&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGuess and spell the on-screen image. Team up or compete in-person with friends or family to see who will get their letter in first! Download free content like trivia, geography or upload your own like family names. The possibilities are endless!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Newton Game&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNewton works with any object or drawing – Mom’s keys, hand-drawn basket, even toys you already own. Simply place the object/drawing in front of the screen and manipulate it to guide the falling balls into the target zones.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6. Masterpiece Game&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nUnleash your inner artist! Pick an image from the camera, web or curated gallery and Masterpiece will transform it into easy-to-follow lines, helping you create beautiful drawings.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6. Numbers Game&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAdd, count and multiply the tiles to match the numbers on the bubbles. Popping enough bubbles will free the fish and unleash a storm of lightning and thunder! Big or small, even or odd, will you become the Numbers Master?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Osmo Game Systems: Base &amp;amp; Reflector x1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Osmo Games:&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;Numbers &amp;amp; Numbers Tiles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;Coding &amp;amp; Coding Blocks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;Tangram &amp;amp; Tangram Pieces&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;Words &amp;amp; Words Tiles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;Newton&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;Masterpiece&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Osmo Wonder Kit', 'Osmo The Complete Kit', 'Osmo Wonder Kit'),
(10354, 1, 'Osmo The Complete Kit', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Meet Osmo&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOsmo is an award-winning game system that will change the way your child interacts with the iPad by opening it up to hands-on play.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Now you can play with your hands&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPut your iPad in the Osmo base with the red reflector over the camera – and now it can see what’s in front of it.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Monster Game&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBring your drawings to life! Each item you draw for Mo will be magically pulled into his world. Together create animated activities to share with family and friends.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coding Game&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOsmo Coding uses hands-on physical blocks to control Awbie, a playful character who loves delicious strawberries. Each block is a coding command that directs Awbie on a wondrous tree-shaking, strawberry-munching adventure.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tangram Game&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nArrange wooden puzzle pieces to match on-screen shapes. Animals, objects, humans and more. Play with a friend or challenge yourself to increasingly more difficult levels as your handiwork lights up with each victory.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Words Game&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGuess and spell the on-screen image. Team up or compete in-person with friends or family to see who will get their letter in first! Download free content like trivia, geography or upload your own like family names. The possibilities are endless!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Newton Game&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNewton works with any object or drawing – Mom’s keys, hand-drawn basket, even toys you already own. Simply place the object/drawing in front of the screen and manipulate it to guide the falling balls into the target zones.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Masterpiece Game&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nUnleash your inner artist! Pick an image from the camera, web or curated gallery and Masterpiece will transform it into easy-to-follow lines, helping you create beautiful drawings.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Numbers Game&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAdd, count and multiply the tiles to match the numbers on the bubbles. Popping enough bubbles will free the fish and unleash a storm of lightning and thunder! Big or small, even or odd, will you become the Numbers Master?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Osmo Game Systems: Base &amp;amp; Reflector x2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Osmo Games:&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;Numbers &amp;amp; Numbers Tiles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;Coding &amp;amp; Coding Blocks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;Tangram &amp;amp; Tangram Pieces&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;Words &amp;amp; Words Tiles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;Newton&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;Masterpiece&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;Monster&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Osmo Accessories:&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;Creative Board&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;Fuzzy Pouch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;Dry Erase Markers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Osmo The Complete Kit', 'Osmo The Complete Kit', 'Osmo The Complete Kit'),
(10356, 1, 'Miele Swing H1 Quickstep Vacuum Cleaner', '&lt;p&gt;Miele Swing H1 Quickstep is a powerful corded stick vacuum cleaner offering versatile cleaning performance without compromise. Lightweight and easy to use, the H1 Quickstep has a modular design that allows it to transform to reach cobwebs high up in ceiling corners or dust bunnies deep under furniture. Its filtration surpasses the competition featuring Miele’s exclusive AirClean System. Replace the AirClean filter with Miele’s HEPA filter for maximum filtration performance. The Swing H1 Quickstep comes packaged with a newly design combination floor tool but can be used with any of Miele’s power brushes or floor tools if desired. Additional floor tools available for purchase separately.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Miele Swing H1 Quickstep Vacuum Cleaner are ideal for someone who...&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wants a handy companion to their canister or full-size upright vacuum for quick pickups and small cleaning jobs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wants a lightweight vacuum for apartments, loft spaces, yachts, RVs and campers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Would like a vacuum that is versatile and has multiple configurations to fit the job that needs to be done&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features of Miele Swing H1 Quickstep Vacuum Cleaner&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Powerful, 1000-watt Miele-made Vortex Motor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max/Min speed control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AirClean Sealed System™&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AirClean filter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;IntensiveClean Plus filter bags, type K, 2.6 qt capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Upholstery nozzle and crevice tool with VariClip holder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;FiberTeQ combination floor tool SBD 470-3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electric connection to accommodate a power brush&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Modular design for multiple configurations&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ergonomic handle with anti-slip stopper&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stainless steel telescopic wand&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cord-wrap system with quick-release clip&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;28 ft. cleaning radius&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lightweight – only 9 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: mango red&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Good Housekeeping seal of approval&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer warranty (Includes 7 year motor warranty)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Miele?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quality - Miele vacuums are tested to last 20 years, each day delivering the same great performance as day one&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Performance - A robust Vortex Motor System provides powerful suction and precise adjustment – no matter the surface being cleaned&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Filtration - Miele’s unique AirClean filtration system captures and retains over 99.9 percent of all lung damaging particles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Convenience - Exceptionally nimble and remarkably intuitive, Miele effortlessly adapts to the cleaning task at hand – ensuring complete floor-to-ceiling care&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Craftsmanship of: &lt;/strong&gt;Parts are made in Germany, assembled in China&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Miele Swing H1 Quickstep Vacuum Cleaner', 'Miele Swing H1 Quickstep Vacuum Cleaner', 'Miele Swing H1 Quickstep Vacuum Cleaner'),
(10357, 1, 'Oransi Finn HEPA UV Air Purifier', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Finn HEPA Air Purifier is designed for small to medium sized rooms like a bedroom or office - up to 400 sq ft (20\' x 20\'). You get high-end air purifier performance and a shrewd buy that works with your budget in mind. Optimized to remove airborne dust, pollen, pet dander, mold, and other solid airborne particles. Also features a carbon pre-filter to help with light odors.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSimple to use, low cost to operate and recognized as one of the quietest HEPA air purifiers in its class. With its tower design it can be placed near a wall so is a perfect air purifier for a bedroom or office.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Small Footprint and Modern Design:&lt;/strong&gt; With its tower design the Oransi Finn HEPA air purifier fits nicely in any room. We invested heavily in design to bring you a HEPA air purifier you are proud to show off and not hide behind the couch. In addition, we have removed wasted space to make it more compact and powerful than other tower air purifiers. Attractive neutral color and cool contemporary design that will match any décor. A conversation piece that blends nicely with your room.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;V-Lock/V-Seal: &lt;/strong&gt;No air by-pass so all of the air is filtered. This is a huge feature and is one reason we have superior air filtration performance. This is due to the v-lock system that creates a seal around the air filter and locks the filter cover in place.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2 Stage HEPA Filtration + UV:&lt;/strong&gt; Pre-filter and HEPA filter with mini-pleats. UV Sterilizes HEPA filter and can turn on/off&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Replacement Filter Indicator: Electronic display alerts you when it is time to check the filters.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quiet Operation:&lt;/strong&gt; 3 fan speeds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Easy to Use:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Simple, intuitive controls with easy filter access.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Ready to use out of the box.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Don\'t need a manual to operate the unit.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Effective&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Best Filters: Rated best in independent study by Clemson University&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Relieves Allergies, Pollen, Dust, Mold, Pet Dander and Light Odors&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Removes 98%+ of airborne allergens &amp;amp; particulates&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Great Value&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Comes with 2 extra replacement pre-filters for free (included in box).&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- The included v-hepa air purifier filter will last for 1 to 2 years. This provides up to 2 years of air cleaning and an average savings of $202 compared to other similar models in just the first two years!&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Big savings when 2 or more are ordered plus free shipping&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Low cost to operate, low power usage&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Have confidence with 10 year warranty&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Safe&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Certified Ozone Safe by the State of California Air Resources Board&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- ETL certified safe&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Room Coverage: up to 400 sq feet (20\' x 20\')&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Noise Level: 40dB - 60dB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Air Flow: 140 (speed 3 CADR)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Filter: Cleanable pre-filter and v-hepa filter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;v-HEPA filter efficiency: 99%&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Filter life: up to 2 years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fan speeds: 3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Controls: Electronic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Filter Replace/Clean Indicator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Negative ion&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UV lamp&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 7&quot; x 10&quot; x 22&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 10 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power: 55 watts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 10 years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What’s in the Box&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Finn Air Purifier&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UV lamp, pre-filter, HEPA filter (inside air purifier)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 extra pre-filters&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;User’s Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Oransi Finn HEPA UV Air Purifier', 'Oransi Finn HEPA UV Air Purifier', 'Oransi Finn HEPA UV Air Purifier'),
(10358, 1, 'Green Air Purifiers Green Air Encore HEPA and Carbon Filter', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Three-stage advanced purifier system with True HEPA and Granulated Carbon filter technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;IonCluster Technology to attack airborne microbes, purify the air, and aggressively kill bacteria&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Air quality color changing light ring and automatic air filter change indicator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Four operating modes (AUTO, FAN, NIGHT, SILENT)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy Efficient, Whisper Quiet Operation, Covers up to 1000 sq. ft.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Green Air Encore features a three-stage air filter system, along with IonCluster technology that will attack airborne microbes, purify your air, and aggressively kill bacteria. The certified True HEPA filter removes 99.97 pecent of particulates and allergens less than 0.3 microns while the granulated activated carbon filter effectively reduces smoke, foul odors, and harmful off gassing VOCs including Formaldehyde and Benzene.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Green Air Encore is fully adjustable to your needs, and features a worry free AUTO mode to keep your indoor air as clean as possible.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith its three-stage advanced purifier system, Green Air Encore eliminates allergens such as dust, smoke, pollen (including tree, grass, and ragweed), pet dander, mold, odor, and harmful VOCs.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFeatures four distinct operating modes (AUTO, NIGHT, FAN, SILENT), and includes an air quality color changing light indicator which automatically adjusts the unit to match the air quality in the room. Covers up to 1000 sq. ft.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Three-Stage Advanced Filter Technology:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mesh Pre-Filter - washable micron mesh filters 99.9% of particulate matter larger than 0.28mm improving the lifespan of the other two filters.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Activated Carbon Filter - granulated carbon formula that effectively reduces smoke, odor and harmful off gassing VOCs including Formaldehyde and Benzene.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;True HEPA Filter - removes 99.97 percent of particulates and allergens including dust, smoke, pet dander, mold spores and pollen less than 0.3 microns.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Green Air Purifiers Green Air Encore HEPA and Carbon Filter', 'Green Air Purifiers Green Air Encore HEPA and Carbon Filter', 'Green Air Purifiers Green Air Encore HEPA and Carbon Filter'),
(10360, 1, 'Shed &amp; Storage Shed-In-A-Box Roundtop 10 x 10 x 8 Ft.', '&lt;p&gt;The ShelterLogic Shed-in-a-Box has a small footprint and big value when space is at a premium. Great for storing garden tools, mowers, snow blowers, snowmobiles, ATVs, pool items, or anything you need to store out of sight. Shed-in-a-Box is designed for use in every season and can protect your equipment from sunlight, rain, tree sap and more. Win back garage space with an affordable storage solution.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features &amp;amp; Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1-3/8 in. / 3,1 cm all-steel frame, bonded with thermoset premium powder-coated finish prevents chipping, peeling, rust and corrosion&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Advanced engineered triple-layer ripstop polyethylene cover is waterproof, UV-treated inside and out with added fade blockers, anti-aging, antifungal agents resulting in a fabric cover that withstands the elements&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ratchet Tite cover tensioning system ensures a drum tight cover and door-panel connection to shelter frame. Quality ratchet and web strap components keep cover tight and neat looking.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy Slide Cross Rail system locks down and squares up frames for initial and continuous frame to fabric fit.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Patented ShelterLock® stabilizers ensure rock solid stability, delivers a stable, more durable shelter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High profile white interior provides enhanced illumination&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Structure requires no building permits in most cases. Check local ordinances before installation.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SKU: 70435&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly Manual: &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://s7d2.scene7.com/is/content/ShelterLogic/manuals/05_70435_70437.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Download (PDF)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Size: 10 X 10 X 8 Ft&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Style: Round&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 10&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 10&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fabric Material: Polyethylene 7.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fabric Color: Gray&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Valance: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Waterproof: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Water-Resistant: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fire Rated: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1 Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Storage Bag: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hardware Kit: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Shed &amp; Storage Shed-In-A-Box Roundtop 10 X 10 X 8 Ft.', 'Shed &amp; Storage Shed-In-A-Box Roundtop 10 X 10 X 8 Ft.', 'Shed &amp; Storage Shed-In-A-Box Roundtop 10 X 10 X 8 Ft.'),
(10361, 1, 'Weber Harley-Davidson Q1200 Gas Grill', '&lt;p&gt;The Weber® Q® 1200™ Harley-Davidson® edition is the grill for you. This grill is designed with a large capacity porcelain-enameled, cast-iron cooking grate measuring a whopping 189 square inches. So go ahead, pack it full of ribs, chicken, steaks, veggies, pizza...whatever your guests’ hunger requires. A built-in lid thermometer, stainless steel burner and an infinite control burner valve mean plenty of consistent heat across the grate to cook practically anything with perfect results every time. This grill is made with ease in mind. It has an electronic ignition and stainless steel burner that can pump out up to 8,500 BTU-per-hour. The cast aluminum lid and body has a glass-reinforced nylon frame with two folding work tables to keep all your tools nearby.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Owners Guide and Grilling Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Limited warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cooking System&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stainless steel burner(s): 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Main burners: BTU-per-hour input: 8,500&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Infinite control burner valve(s)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electronic ignition system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Total cooking area (square inches): 189&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Construction&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cast aluminum lid and body&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Glass-reinforced nylon frame&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two folding work tables&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable catch pan&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in lid thermometer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Porcelain-enameled, cast-iron cooking grate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fuel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;14.1 or 16.4 oz. LP cylinder (sold separately)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Color/Item&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Painted, cast aluminum lid finish&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dimensions (Lid Open, Tables Out)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height (inches): 24.6&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width (inches): 40.9&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth (inches): 20.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Weber Harley-Davidson Q1200 Gas Grill', 'Weber Harley-Davidson Q1200 Gas Grill', 'Weber Harley-Davidson Q1200 Gas Grill'),
(10365, 1, 'AIRMEGA 300S The Smarter WIFI App Enabled Air Purifier (1256 sq. ft.)', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;ONLY 1 LEFT!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The 300S is equipped with Wi-Fi,* so that you can control your Airmega anywhere and at any time through the Airmega mobile app. With Smart Mode (Auto, Sleep, Eco) and real-time air quality monitoring, you can rest assured you’ll have clean air at all times.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAt 1,256 square foot coverage, the 300 model is perfect for small- to medium-sized rooms.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAll Airmega models comes with two Pre-filters and two Max2 Filters.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;*In order to connect your smartphone to the 300S, your Wi-Fi router should use two frequency bands commonly used for Wi-Fi communication: 2.4 and 5GHz. Many modern routers support both bands. If your dual band router is set to broadcast only 5GHz, please set your router to broadcast both bands or only 2.4GHz. Your Wi-Fi security should be set to one of the following options: Open, WEP, WPA, WPAAES, WPA2AES, WPA2TKIP, WPA2.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Real-time Air Quality Monitoring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAirmega’s air quality sensor tells you the quality of the air in the room in real time. The brightly colored LED ring lets you know if your air is fresh or unhealthy every minute of the day.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Smart Mode&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith Smart Mode, Airmega adapts to you. It allows Airmega to automatically adjust its fan speed based on the room’s air quality and room condition.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Smart (Auto) Mode&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAirmega’s Smart Mode automatically adjusts the air filtration speed according to the room’s current air quality.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Smart (Eco) Mode&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhen the air quality remains good for 10 minutes or more, Airmega conserves energy by shutting down the fan. If the sensor detects pollution in the air, the fan will restart automatically.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Smart (Sleep) Mode&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhen set on Smart Mode, Airmega’s light sensor detects when it’s dark and the air purifier automatically reduces its fan speed so it runs much quieter.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Powerful Performance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCompact, efficient and powerful. With its dual suction capability and advanced filters, Airmega can handle a room up to 1,256 square feet in size and remove from the air pollutants as small as one micron in size.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mobile App&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Airmega mobile app, available for the 400S and 300S, gives you the ability to monitor the air quality inside your home, see the status of the filters, schedule the timer, and even receive real-time outdoor air quality updates.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Filter Levels&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAirmega tells you when it’s time to replace the filter—so you never have to think about the age of the filter.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two air changes/hour*: 1,256 ft2 (117 m2)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Four air changes/hour**: 628 ft2 (58 m2)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mobile App: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto Mode: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Eco Mode: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sleep Mode: Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Filter: Washable pre-filter + Max2 filter set (Activated carbon + Green True HEPA)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Real-Time Monitoring: Good, Moderate, Unhealthy, Very Unhealthy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Filter Life Time Indicator: Wash, Change&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fan Speed: Sleep, Low, Medium, High&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Timer: Airmega application (1, 2, 4, 8 hours)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Scheduler: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Size (H x W x D):&amp;nbsp; 21.2 x 13.6 x 13.6 in (53.8 x 34.5 x 34.5 cm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 21.4 lb (9.7 kg)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Noise Level: 22~52 dB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Consumption: 57 W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The coverage area of the Airmega reflects the size of the area in which the Airmega can make two air changes per hour (ACPH). “One air change per hour” reflects how many times the Airmega can clean an area, assuming the height of the ceiling to be 8 feet, in one hour. *The Airmega can clean the area once every 30 minutes. **The Airmega can clean the area once every 15 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'AIRMEGA 300S The Smarter WIFI App Enabled Air Purifier (1256 sq. ft.)', 'AIRMEGA 300S The Smarter WIFI App Enabled Air Purifier (1256 sq. ft.)', 'AIRMEGA 300S The Smarter WIFI App Enabled Air Purifier (1256 sq. ft.)'),
(10363, 1, 'Weber Q1200 Chicago Cubs', '&lt;p&gt;The ultra-portable, ultra capable Weber® Q® 1200™ gas grill - Cubs Edition&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Want to grill with Cubs pride? Represent the Cubs with the new Weber® Cubs Edition Q® 1200™ gas grill. This grill has all the power of standard models with 189 sq inches of cooking area, built-in thermometer and folding side tables; but with some Cubs flare.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Owners Guide and Grilling Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Limited warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cooking System&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stainless steel burner(s): 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Main burners: BTU-per-hour input: 8,500&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Infinite control burner valve(s)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electronic ignition system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Total cooking area (square inches): 189&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Construction&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cast aluminum lid and body&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Glass-reinforced nylon frame&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two folding work tables&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable catch pan&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in lid thermometer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Porcelain-enameled, cast-iron cooking grate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fuel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;14.1 or 16.4 oz. LP cylinder (sold separately)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Color/Item&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Painted, cast aluminum lid finish&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dimensions (Lid Open, Tables Out)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height (inches): 24.6&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width (inches): 40.9&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth (inches): 20.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Weber Harley-Davidson Q1200 Gas Grill', 'Weber Harley-Davidson Q1200 Gas Grill', 'Weber Harley-Davidson Q1200 Gas Grill'),
(10362, 1, 'Weber Q1200 College Edition Grills', '&lt;p&gt;The large capacity porcelain-enameled, cast-iron cooking grates can be packed full of ribs, chicken, steaks, veggies, pizza and more to accommodate any size gathering. A built-in lid thermometer, stainless steel burner and an infinite control burner valve allow for plenty of consistent heat across the grates to grill practically anything with perfect results every time.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. WEBER® Q® 1200™ AUBURN UNIVERSITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGrill with Tiger pride with the Weber® Q® 1200™ gas grill, Auburn University edition.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. WEBER® Q® 1200™ FLORIDA STATE UNIVERSITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGrill with Seminole pride with the Weber® Q® 1200™ gas grill, Florida State University edition.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. WEBER® Q® 1200™ UNIVERSITY OF MICHIGAN&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGrill with Wolverine pride with the Weber® Q® 1200™ gas grill, University of Michigan edition.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. WEBER® Q® 1200™ UNIVERSITY OF WISCONSIN&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGrill with Badger pride with the Weber® Q® 1200™ gas grill, University of Wisconsin edition.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. WEBER® Q® 1200™ UNIVERSITY OF NEBRASKA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGrill with Husker pride with the Weber® Q® 1200™ gas grill, University of Nebraska edition.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6. WEBER® Q® 1200™ UNIVERSITY OF NOTRE DAME&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGrill with Fighting Irish pride with the Weber® Q® 1200™ gas grill, University of Notre Dame edition.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7. WEBER® Q® 1200™ THE UNIVERSITY OF TEXAS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGrill with Longhorn pride with the Weber® Q® 1200™ gas grill, The University of Texas edition.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Owners Guide and Grilling Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Limited warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cooking System&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stainless steel burner(s): 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Main burners: BTU-per-hour input: 8,500&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Infinite control burner valve(s)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electronic ignition system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Total cooking area (square inches): 189&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Construction&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cast aluminum lid and body&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Glass-reinforced nylon frame&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two folding work tables&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable catch pan&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in lid thermometer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Porcelain-enameled, cast-iron cooking grate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fuel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;14.1 or 16.4 oz. LP cylinder (sold separately)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Color/Item&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Painted, cast aluminum lid finish&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dimensions (Lid Open, Tables Out)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height (inches): 24.6&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width (inches): 40.9&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth (inches): 20.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Weber Q1200 College Edition Grills', 'Weber Q1200 College Edition Grills', 'Weber Q1200 College Edition Grills'),
(10364, 1, 'Withings Body Cardio - Heart Health and Body Composition Wi-Fi Scale', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall cardiovascular health with Heart Rate and Pulse Wave Velocity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Full body composition - Track weight, BMI, total body fat and water percentage plus bone and muscle mass&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Best-in-class accuracy via Position Control™ technology, a patented body position detector&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic WiFi or Bluetooth synchronization with your smartphone&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full Body Composition&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGet a holistic picture of your health and fitness. The scale displays your weight, body fat and water percentage, as well as bone and muscle mass. It also displays a graph with your last 8 weigh-ins to help you understand your weight trend.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Home heart health check-up&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDoctors regard Pulse Wave Velocity as a key indicator of your risk for developing hypertension or cardiovascular disease. Body Cardio is the first scale to bring this important measurement home. Heart rate readings complete the picture to give you a better idea of your overall fitness.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Personalized coaching&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAll data syncs to the Withings Health Mate app, automatically, via WiFi or Bluetooth. Set goals, get rewards, and view detailed graphs to assess your progress.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Best-in-class accuracy by design&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAt only 0.7 inches thick Body Cardio is the thinnest scale available, but it\'s incredibly strong and stable thanks to its tempered glass and solid aluminum base. There are no feet to adjust, it\'s accurate on any surface, and patented Position Control™ technology includes on-screen indicators that guide you to a perfect stance.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Designed for life&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBody Cardio can automatically recognize and record data from up to 8 users. Lasts up to 12 months and charges one night via micro USB (included).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;100+ Partners: Pick an app, any app...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCompare progress to calorie intake with Weight Watchers, Lose It! or MyFitnessPal. Or train for a race with Runkeeper, MapMyRun or Runtastic. These are just a few of the more than 100 top health &amp;amp; fitness apps that easily pair with Body Cardio to help you understand how efforts impact what you see on the scale.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CONNECTIVITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;iOS compatibility (iOS 8 and higher)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- iPhone (4S and above)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- iPod touch (5th generation or higher)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Android compatibility (2.3.3 and higher)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Requires Internet access (mobile data or Wi-Fi)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wireless Sync&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- WiFi 802.11 b/g/n, compatible with WEP/WPA/WPA2-personal networks&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Bluetooth connectivity (Bluetooth Smart Ready)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;METRICS TRACKED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Weight&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Four weight sensors&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Patent-pending body position detector&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Highly accurate weighing&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Body Composition&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Bioelectrical Impedance Analysis&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Athlete and non-athlete mode&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Unit: body fat %, total body water %, muscle mass kg or lb, bone mass kg or lb&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Heart rate&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Patented heart rate measurement technology&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Unit: bpm (beats per minute)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pulse Wave Velocity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Patent-pending measurement technology&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Unit: m/s&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Normality range&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Automatic user recognition&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Up to 8 different users&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SENSORS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Four weight sensors&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Weighing range: 5 -&amp;gt; 180kg&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- (9 -&amp;gt; 396lb)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- 100g (0.2lb) graduation&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Units: kg, lb, st lb&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Patented body position detector&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Highly-accurate weighing via Position ControlTM technology&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IN THE BOX&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Scale&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Body Cardio&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- USB Cable for charging&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Installation guide&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- FR/EN/DE/ES/IT&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Free Health Mate app&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- To set up the alarm clock and fine tune daily activity/sleep objectives&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- To track up to 5 dimensions of your health - Activity, Sleep, Weight, Heart, Environment&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Free Withings account&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- To securely store your data and make it readily available&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Download your data at any time, free of charge&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Withings Body Cardio - Heart Health and Body Composition Wi-Fi Scale', 'Withings Body Cardio - Heart Health and Body Composition Wi-Fi Scale', 'Withings Body Cardio - Heart Health and Body Composition Wi-Fi Scale');
