(10366, 1, 'DR Trimmer Mower 6.75 Premier', '&lt;p&gt;At just 57 lbs., the PREMIER is the lightest weight, easiest-rolling Trimmer/Mower in the industry. Incredibly nimble, yet with its 6.75 Briggs &amp;amp; Stratton engine, the PREMIER has plenty of power for all your trimming and mowing jobs. Manual- and Electric-Start available.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Cut Above the Competition&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOur Premier model offers vastly more power than any handheld trimmer and will power through any trimming task and handle light to moderate mowing jobs with ease. At just 57 lbs it is light enough to maneuver in tight quarters, rolling easily on big 14&quot; resin wheels. The Premier features a 22&quot; cut and has five adjustable height settings, from 1.5 to 3.5 inches.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The 6.75 series Briggs &amp;amp; Stratton engine is available with either an easy-pull manual start, or an electric start for maximum convenience. Each DR Trimmer/Mower is backed by a 2-year warranty for residential use (90 days for commercial use). Briggs &amp;amp; Stratton engines are performance engineered, ensuring that you get the most out of your DR Trimmer/Mower!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;An offset frame design allows the Premier to trim right up against foundations, fence lines and other obstacles with precise control. The front is fortified with a cast aluminum nose plate that protects the machine against damage from collisions.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5X the power of handheld trimmers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6.75 ft/lb Briggs &amp;amp; Stratton engine&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;22&quot; Cutting Width&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5 Cutting Heights: 1.5&quot; to 3.5&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Accepts optional DuraBlades and Beaver Blade&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Accepts 175 mil cord—the thickest, longest-lasting cord available.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Warranty Coverage&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engine: 2 years residential&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Machine: 2 years residential&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Briggs &amp;amp; Stratton Engine&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe legendary power, performance and durability of Briggs &amp;amp; Stratton® engines make them the only ones we use on our Trimmer/Mowers. They are easy to start, comfortable to use, and feature a debris management system that protects the engine from whatever you kick up while you’re cutting&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Super-duty Cutting Cords&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAll DR Trimmer/Mowers accept super-thick 175 mil cutting cords—the thickest, longest-lasting in the industry (so you spend more time mowing and less time changing cords).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cast Aluminum Nose Plate&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe DR Trimmer/Mower\'s cast aluminum nose plate protects it against damage from collisions. Bumps and scrapes are inevitable when you\'re working, but you can ensure that they don\'t damage your&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optional DuraBlades for 3/8&quot; Thick Brush&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith our optional DR DuraBlades you can quickly swap out your cutting cords with metal blades, embedded in a high-tech polymer, that slice through woody material up to 3/8&quot; thick&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Patented Cord Attachment System&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAttach new cords in seconds, without tools! Choose from one of five cutting heights (1.5&quot; to 3.5&quot;) when you attach new cords. And the DR wide-body design prevents vegetation from wrapping and tangling around the trimmer head, even in tall grass.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optional Beaver Blade for the big stuff&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe optional Beaver Blade turns your trimmer into a chainsaw on wheels. Cuts trees up to 3&quot; in diameter quickly and easily. It\'s the perfect way to take down stands of &quot;weed trees&quot; without bending over or dropping to your knees like you have to with a normal chainsaw.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optional Quick-Lock Trimmer Head&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAllows you to change your trimmer cord in just seconds—completely hassle-free! Cord is simply inserted into the head and is anchored in place by the unique gripping mechanism! Perfect for quick cord changes in the field, and for those who often trim dense thickets of weeds.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cutting Width: 22&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cutting Height: 1 1/2&quot; - 3 1/2&quot; (adjustable)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Make: Briggs &amp;amp; Stratton&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model: 675 Series&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Starting Type: Manual or Electric&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ft Lbs Torque: 6.75&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Displacement: 163cc Manual Start / 190cc Electric Start&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number Of Cylinder: 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Air Filter: Paper filter and prefilter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oil Capacity: 20oz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lubrication: Splash&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oil Typet: 30W HD&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Tires: 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 14&quot; Resin&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tread: Diamond&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 21 1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 57 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shipping Dimensions: 35&quot;L x 22.25&quot;W x 24&quot;H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Handlebar Height: 31&quot; - 49&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shipping Weight: 66 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel Capacity: 1 qt&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Frame: 14 ga steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'DR Trimmer Mower 6.75 Premier', 'DR Trimmer Mower 6.75 Premier', 'DR Trimmer Mower 6.75 Premier'),
(10367, 1, 'As Seen On TV 10 Qt. Electric Power Pressure Cooker XL Stainless Steel', '&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;Prepare your favorite slow-cooked recipes 70% faster and make one-pot meals with a touch of a button with the Electric Power Pressure Cooker XL. Features flavor infusion technology to lock in flavor and nutrients for delicious and healthier results.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;As Seen On TV&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electric Power Pressure Cooker XL allows you to cook delicious, flavorful and healthier meals up to 70% faster than conventional cookware and is also suitable for canning fruits, vegetables, and more&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Intelligent one touch preset options allow you to perfectly cook meat, fish, vegetables, beans, rice, soup or stews with just a press of a button&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flavor infusion technology traps super heated steam inside the pot to force liquid and moisture into your food, locking in intense flavor and nutrients&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Push-button control panel with digital display&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Slow cooker function easily and perfectly makes your favorite slow-cooked recipes 10x faster&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Safe lock lid with manual steam release&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manual pressure and cooking time adjustments&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic keep warm mode&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Large and sturdy lid arm handle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One-Touch Preset Buttons&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Non-Stick Inner Pot&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Safe Lock Lid With&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steam Release&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Digital Display Panel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic Keep Warm Mode&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Slow Cooker Option&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flavor Infusion Technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-In Safety Features&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;10 Qt Capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher Safe&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ideal For Canning, Families &amp;amp; Holidays&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Replaces Seven Common Devices: Slow Cooker, Canner, Soup Maker, Steamer, Cookware &amp;amp; Rice Cooker&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Pressure Cooker XL - 10 QT&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Copper Chef Frying Pan ($20 Bonus)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Chopper&amp;nbsp; ($12.99 Bonus)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6 Year Warranty ($30.00 Bonus)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4 Piece Utensil Set ($19.95 Bonus)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Eric\'s Power Pressure Cooking Cookbook ($29.97 Bonus)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'As Seen On TV 10 Qt. Electric Power Pressure Cooker XL Stainless Steel', 'As Seen On TV 10 Qt. Electric Power Pressure Cooker XL Stainless Steel', 'As Seen On TV 10 Qt. Electric Power Pressure Cooker XL Stainless Steel'),
(10368, 1, 'USA Map Value PLUS Rug - Rectangle - 6x9', '&lt;p&gt;USA Map Value PLUS Rug - Rectangle - 6\' x 9\' by Carpets for Kids. Our KID$ Value PLUS line was created to include our high quality KIDply Backing and edge yarn for long-lasting carpets that stay looking great. Created to stimulate a child’s imagination through a variety of design themes &amp;amp; ideal for small groups, circle time and classroom organization. You can be assured that our products are safe for your room &amp;amp; constructed with attention to detail and quality!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Origin: 100% North American Made.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mfg Warranty: 5 Year Abrasive Wear Warranty &amp;amp; Includes No-Fault Serge Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Backing Material: High Quality KidPly Backing.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Surface Material: Made with Recyclable Nylon Fiber.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Anti-stain Treatment: Soil &amp;amp; Stain Resistant.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Certifications: Passes CPSC FF1-70, Standard for the Surface Flammability of Carpets and Rugs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MANUFACTURER INFO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCarpets for Kids® (CFK) is the industry leader in high quality, educational area rugs. CFK is a major supplier of children\'s educational rugs for daycares and schools and homes across the country. Our bright colors, innovative designs and passion for education make CFK the first choice for quality children’s rugs. CFK is a member of the National Headstart Association (NHSA), the National School Supply &amp;amp; Equipment Association (NSSEA), and an annual exhibitor at the National Association for the Education of Young Children NAEYC) conference.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;History&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCarpets for Kids® was founded in 1991 and is corporately located in Portland, Oregon with manufacturing at our Georgia facility. We are a family owned company that strives to produce the highest quality product for your children as well as keeping our product safe and long lasting.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Purpose&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAt Carpets for Kids® our goal is to provide teachers, parents, pastors and more with a quality tool to enhance learning for young children. We strive to have the best designed and highest quality products out on the market.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Not only are we here to provide the educational and home markets with a great product, but we also want to be good stewards with what we\'ve been given. We are thankful for this great planet that we live on, and aim to do as much as we can to keep our home green. Giving back to the community is key for us and we encourage our employees to serve with their giftings in their local communities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Caring for the Environment&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCarpets For Kids® helps keep our planet green by reducing landfill waste. We send our unused production scraps and damaged goods from our Georgia facility to a nearby recycling center. Carpets For Kids® uses renewable power from PGE: Green Source. 100% of our monthly usage in our corporate office is offset with renewable resources. Our power comes from approximately 50% new wind, 40% geothermal and 10% biomass (wood waste) power.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Made in the USA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAll Carpets for Kids® products are 100% made in the USA and proud of it. From the raw materials turned into carpeting, to the printing and finishing process of our product; all of it is done in the USA. Our large facility in West Point, Georgia not only provides US jobs to a struggling economy, but it ensures the safest quality product for your children. All of our products are 100% lead free and contain only materials that are safe for children\'s environments.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'USA Map Value PLUS Rug - Rectangle - 6x9', 'USA Map Value PLUS Rug - Rectangle - 6x9', 'USA Map Value PLUS Rug - Rectangle - 6x9'),
(10369, 1, 'Inmovement Standing Desk', '&lt;p&gt;Switch from sitting to standing in seconds with the most popular InMovement Standing Desk, the Elevate DeskTop DT2. It comes fully assembled and has ten different adjustable height settings. Simply place the InMovement Standing Desk on top of your existing desktop, grasp the handles, and adjust the product to your desired standing height.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BENEFITS &amp;amp; FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Retractable Keyboard Tray:&lt;/strong&gt; A retractable keyboard tray keeps your keyboard and mouse at the ideal ergonomic height&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Executive Sized Desk:&lt;/strong&gt; At 41&quot; across, the DT2 allows for a fully functional workstation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Choice Of Styling: &lt;/strong&gt;The DT2 is available in three high-end finishes to complement any workstation. Choose from a contemporary light grain, rich dark grain or modern white finish&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stay Charged:&lt;/strong&gt; Professionals report increased energy by alternating between sitting and standing throughout the day&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: White | Light Wood | Dark Wood&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Work Surface: &amp;nbsp;41&quot; x 26.2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual Monitor: &amp;nbsp;Dual Monitor Compatible&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Keyboard Tray Dimensions: &amp;nbsp;25&quot; X 10.5&quot;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ergonomic Keyboard Tray: &amp;nbsp;Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vertical Travel: &amp;nbsp;14&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built in Monitor Mount: &amp;nbsp;No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mounting Standard: &amp;nbsp;N/A&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multiple Finishes: &amp;nbsp;Yes&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max Weight Capacity: &amp;nbsp;35 lbs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cable Management: &amp;nbsp;No&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: &amp;nbsp;58 lbs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electricity Required: &amp;nbsp;No&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Installation Options: &amp;nbsp;N/A&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Desk Thickness Compatibility: &amp;nbsp;N/A&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Desk Depth Compatibility: &amp;nbsp;26&quot;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: &amp;nbsp;1 year by Manufacturer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Inmovement Standing Desk', 'Inmovement Standing Desk', 'Inmovement Standing Desk'),
(10370, 1, 'AcuRite 01075RM 5-in-1 Weather Station, Color Display, Multi Sensor', '&lt;p&gt;​&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The 5-in-1 Weather Station, Display, &amp;amp; 2-Sensor Temperature and Humidity Weather Environment System with My AcuRite includes a smartHUB, a PRO+ 5-in-1 weather sensor, a color weather station display for 5-in-1 sensor data, and two (2) indoor or outdoor temperature and humidity sensors.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Monitor temperature, humidity, rain, wind speed and wind direction remotely for any location, track historical records and customize email and text alerts to know when conditions change. View your sensors from virtually anywhere on a smartphone, tablet or computer with the My AcuRite app or website, or easily publish your weather reports on Weather Underground.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One-year limited warranty. It\'s more than accurate, it\'s AcuRite.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWeather Environment System Includes: Smarthub, Color Display For 5-In-1 Sensor Data, Pro+ 5-In-1 Weather Sensor, (2) Temperature And Humidity Sensors, Tabletop Stand, Mounting Bracket, Mounting Hardware, Ethernet Cable, Power Adapters, Quick Start Guide, Instruction Manual,&amp;nbsp;Limited One-Year Warranty.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Precision Weather Instruments&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Measure rainfall, wind speed, wind direction, temperature, humidity, and barometric pressure.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Complimentary My AcuRite App&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith My AcuRite you can view sensor data, conditions, history, trends, forecasts, and more on your mobile devices or computer.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Create Alerts to Take Action&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nReal-time email and phone notifications of changes in your home and outdoor environments.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Create Alerts to Take Action&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nReal-time email and phone notifications of changes in your home and outdoor environments.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sharable Weather Information&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nLet friends and family access your current conditions, plus broadcast to communities like Weather Underground.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;History, Trends, plus High &amp;amp; Low Records&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAnalyze or download data to help guide decisions for a more efficient, healthy home.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expandable&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTrack up to ten sensors with one smartHUB. Add smartHUBs to track even more sensors, or monitor additional locations.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Illuminated Color Display&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSee all of your 5-in-1 sensor data, the weather forecast, plus indoor temperature and humidity—all at-a-glance on a digital display screen.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Free, US-based Technical Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTalk to friendly, knowledgeable people for setup and operation assistance.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;My AcuRite App&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;View your sensors on any iPhone, Android smartphone, computer or tablet with the complimentary My AcuRite App.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Create email and phone alerts to notify you when conditions change or your presets are reached.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Alerts can be triggered by events like rainfall, potential flood conditions, high wind speed, high or low temperature and humidity conditions, and more.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy-to-read, comprehensive trend observation with graphic charts and historical data.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sensor data can be monitored privately, shared with others, or be reported to online weather communities like Weather Underground.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRO+ 5-in-1 Weather Sensor&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measures temperature, humidity, wind speed, wind direction and rain&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two solar panels power the internal fan to maximize ambient temperature accuracy at all hours of the day (standard 5-in-1 includes only one solar panel)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Strong wireless range up to 330 feet (100 meters)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Transmits data every 18 to 36 seconds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic self-emptying rain collection cup&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 year battery life&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Durable, all-weather construction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;smartHUB&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Provides access AcuRite sensor data using the My AcuRite app&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Reports data for up to 10 compatible AcuRite sensors simultaneously (additional sensors sold separately)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy setup: Ethernet cable plugs into your internet router&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Weather Environment System includes:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nsmartHUB, Color Display for 5-in-1 Sensor Data, PRO+ 5-in-1 Weather Sensor, mounting bracket, mounting hardware, Ethernet cable, power adapters, tabletop stand, quick start guide, instruction manual.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Color Display for 5-in-1 Sensor&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Illuminated color display with auto-dimming brightness&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;12 to 24 hour weather forecast&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Patented Self-Calibrating Forecasting pulls data from a sensor in your backyard to give you the most accurate forecast for your exact location&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weather Ticker™ streams real-time information and alerts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rain accumulation data recorded for today, over all-time, by year, by month, and by rainfall event; tracks days with rain this month, and days since last rain&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wind speed: current, peak, and average (MPH or KPH)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wind direction with 16 point wind rose&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Indoor and outdoor temperature (degrees Fahrenheit and Celsius) with trend arrow&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Indoor and outdoor humidity (%RH) with trend arrow&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heat index, wind chill, dew point and &quot;feels like&quot; calculations&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weekly, monthly, and all-time high and low records&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Barometric pressure with trend arrow and manual calibration option&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Time and date (month/day)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tabletop or wall-mountable design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Indicator for wireless sensor signal strength&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'AcuRite 01075RM 5-in-1 Weather Station, Color Display, 2-Sensor Temperature and Humidity Weather Environment System with My AcuRite Remote Monitoring App', 'AcuRite 01075RM 5-in-1 Weather Station, Color Display, 2-Sensor Temperature and Humidity Weather Environment System with My AcuRite Remote Monitoring App', 'AcuRite 01075RM 5-in-1 Weather Station, Color Display, 2-Sensor Temperature and Humidity Weather Environment System with My AcuRite Remote Monitoring App'),
(10371, 1, 'AcuRite 01078M 5-in-1 Weather Station with Dual Display, Wind and Rain', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The AcuRite Pro 5-in-1 Weather Station includes a 5-in-1 weather sensor, and two (2) color weather station displays for 5-in-1 sensor data.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measure temperature, humidity, rain, wind speed and wind direction right in your own backyard. Dual digital displays allow you to observe your weather data in multiple rooms.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The illuminated color displays feature three different lighting settings, ensuring you can easily read the information you want at a glance. Select a lighting preference manually, or choose auto dim mode. In auto dim mode, the display automatically adjusts its brightness based on time of day and year. The high-precision 5-in-1 weather sensor accurately measures five different conditions, including rainfall, wind speed and wind direction, outdoor temperature and humidity, giving you comprehensive data about the elements surrounding your home. One-year limited warranty. It\'s more than accurate, it\'s AcuRite.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Color Display for 5-in-1 Sensor&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Illuminated color display with auto-dimming brightness&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;12 to 24 hour weather forecast&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Patented Self-Calibrating Forecasting pulls data from a sensor in your backyard to give you the most accurate forecast for your exact location&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weather Ticker™ streams real-time information and alerts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rain accumulation data recorded for today, over all-time, by year, by month, and by rainfall event; tracks days with rain this month, and days since last rain&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wind speed: current, peak, and average (MPH or KPH)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wind direction with 16 point wind rose&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Indoor and outdoor temperature (degrees Fahrenheit and Celsius) with trend arrow&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Indoor and outdoor humidity (%RH) with trend arrow&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heat index, wind chill, dew point and &quot;feels like&quot; calculations&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weekly, monthly, and all-time high and low records&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Barometric pressure with trend arrow and manual calibration option&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Time and date (month/day)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tabletop or wall-mountable design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Indicator for wireless sensor signal strength&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5-in-1 Weather Sensor&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5-in-1 Sensor measures temperature, humidity, wind speed, wind direction and rain&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Strong wireless range up to 330 feet (100 meters)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Transmits data every 18 to 36 seconds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic self-emptying rain collection cup&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 year battery life&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Durable, all-weather construction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy installation includes mounting hardware&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n(2) Color Displays For 5-In-1 Sensor Data, 5-In-1 Weather Sensor, Mounting Bracket, Debris Filter, Tabletop Stand, Mounting Hardware, Ac Power Adapter, Instruction Manual, Limited 1 Year Warranty&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'AcuRite 01078M Pro Color Weather Station with Two Displays and Rain/Wind/Count Temperature/Humidity\r\n', 'AcuRite 01078M Pro Color Weather Station with Two Displays and Rain/Wind/Count Temperature/Humidity\r\n', 'AcuRite 01078M Pro Color Weather Station with Two Displays and Rain/Wind/Count Temperature/Humidity'),
(10372, 1, 'Jugs Small-Ball Pitching Machine, M7000', '&lt;p&gt;It\'s been said that the toughest thing to do in sports is hit a round ball with a round bat. Now you can hone your skills even further with the Jugs Small-Ball pitching machine, which tests your mettle with a ball half the size. By practicing against a 5-inch Jugs polyurethane foam ball, hitters learn to track the ball better from the release point to the impact zone, while simultaneously sharpening their mental focus. In addition, the Small-Ball machine helps hitters improve depth perception by forcing them to keep their head still and eyes level. And young hitters can learn the fundamentals of hitting without the fear of getting whacked by a real baseball.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Small-Ball pitching machine is built of heavy-duty steel, with adjustable legs that help simulate a realistic delivery height for both baseballs and softballs. More significantly, the machine throws fastballs or overhand curves with uncanny accuracy, with simulated speeds of up to 75 mils per hour. Just load up the 25-ball feeder--which offers both manual and automatic feeds--and the mechanism will release a ball every five seconds. Plus, when it\'s time for fielding practice, you can adjust the machine to instead shoot fly balls and ground balls. Safe to use anywhere, including backyards, garages, or your chosen practice field, the Small-Ball pitching machine is popular among backyard players, youth leagues, high schools, and colleges.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Jugs Small-Ball pitching machine operates on standard 110-volt AC power, but can also function on a separately sold battery pack. Other details include a free brook describing hitting drills, a portable design that weighs only 23 pounds, and a one-year warranty.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Throws the JUGS polyurethane-foam 5-in./0.5-oz. Small-Ball.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Simulates speeds up to 75 mph.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Portable and light-weight, weighs only 23 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy-duty steel construction.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable legs for realistic delivery height for baseball and softball.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manual or automatic feed: 25-ball feeder releases ball every 5 seconds.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Throws fastballs or overhand curves with uncanny accuracy.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Great for ground balls and fly balls.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Safe to use anywhere, including backyards garages or your chosen practice field.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Balls can be picked up using the plexi extension tube.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Runs on 110-volt AC, 1000-watt Yamaha EF1000iS generator , Rechargeable Battery Pack or the NEW Complete Practice Battery Pack.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Recommended age: 5 to adult&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Speed range: Simulated up to 75 miles per hour&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Speed adjustments: Dial&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rechargeable battery pack: Sold separately&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power source: 110-volt AC or battery pack&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Types of pitches thrown: Fastballs and curveballs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;360-degree swivel: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cover: Yes, optional&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manual and automatic feed: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Video demonstration available: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 23 pounds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1 year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Jugs Small-Ball Pitching Machine, M7000', 'Jugs Small-Ball Pitching Machine, M7000', 'Jugs Small-Ball Pitching Machine, M7000'),
(10373, 1, 'GoSun Sport: Easy, Delicious, and Versatile Portable Solar Cooker', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;ONLY 1 LEFT IN STOCK!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BENEFITS&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy: &amp;nbsp;Load food and relax. It\'s that simple!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fast: &amp;nbsp;Cooks a meal in as little as 20 minutes, reaching temperatures up to 550°F (290°C)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cooks Through Clouds: &amp;nbsp;You don\'t have to see the Sun to cook! The GoSun Sport is so effective at capturing ultraviolet light that if you can see a defined shadow, you can cook!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Portable: &amp;nbsp;Set-up in seconds and clamshells into a slim package. GoSun Anywhere!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel-Free: &amp;nbsp;No mess, no flames, no hauling fuel and no cost.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Versatile: &amp;nbsp;Bake, steam, roast and fry. Cooks from 360° retaining your food\'s flavor and richness.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Safe to Touch: &amp;nbsp;Vacuum Insulation keeps exterior surface cool&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two Year Warranty: &amp;nbsp;Durable, made of borosilicate glass (like Pyrex®)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HOW IT WORKS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGoSun’s compound parabolic reflectors and tubular design converts nearly 80% of all sunlight entering it’s reflectors into useable heat.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe GoSun Sport includes a durable borosilicate, vacuum tube oven, two anodized aluminum, parabolic reflectors that fold to protect the tube, a stainless steel cooking tray, a scrubby cleaning tool and stainless steel carrying handles.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0789/1333/files/How_it_Works_Exports-03_grande.png?12935288119796061648&quot; style=&quot;width: 600px; height: 385px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;A miracle of science, the evacuated glass tube of the GoSun Cooking Technology is a near perfect insulator, allowing one to solar cook in even the most challenging conditions. By effectively capturing light from a broad range of angles, the GoSun does not require frequent readjustment, making it the lowest maintenance fuel-free cooking device yet.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dry Weight: 7 lbs (3.18kg)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oven Volume: 40oz (1.2L) fluid or up to 3 lbs (1.4kg) of food&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oven Dimensions: 2.7” (7.0cm) outside diameter, 2.1” (5.4cm) inside diameter , 24” (61cm) length&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unit Open Size: 24” (61cm) long x 16” (41cm) tall x 12” (30cm) wide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unit Closed Size: 24” (61cm) long x 8” (20cm) tall x 5” (13cm) wide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Estimated Power Output: 200 Watts in full sunlight&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Temperature: 550°F (288°C)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Working Temperature: 200°F (93°C) – 450°F (232°C)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cooking Time: As fast as 10 minutes, see infographic below&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WARRANTY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGoSun is proud to offer all purchases being backed by with a Two-Year Warranty on the vacuum tube, as well as a One-Year Limited Warranty on the Parts and Labor.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'GoSun Sport: Easy, Delicious, and Versatile Portable Solar Cooker', 'GoSun Sport: Easy, Delicious, and Versatile Portable Solar Cooker', 'GoSun Sport: Easy, Delicious, and Versatile Portable Solar Cooker'),
(10374, 1, 'New Speed and Agility Training Kit with Free Carry Bag and DVD', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brand New Speed and Agility kit&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Our goal is to help provide you the tools you need to practice correct technique and get faster. &amp;nbsp;So, for about the cost of attending a speed clinic you can train yourself over and again using this Speed and Agility equipment and instructional DVD.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIt’s been said that unless you’re born with speed you’ll never be fast enough. &amp;nbsp;We are here to show you that’s a myth. &amp;nbsp;Year after year we help athletes become faster and stronger. The most common pitfall we see in slower athletes is the lack of proper technique. &amp;nbsp;So, the question is how do you acquire the correct technique?&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHaving a personal trainer is great! &amp;nbsp;However, often times you may not have the resources to pay a trainer or may not be able to train with one. &amp;nbsp;That’s where we can help you.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhatever your sport, this instructional series will teach you and re-teach you until you ultimately begin forming the correct habits you need to maximize your SPEED. &amp;nbsp;As you practice these exercises, you will begin to strengthen the muscles that are essential in building speed.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Agility Ballistic Response Ladder&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHeavy duty, team grade, and round rung designed. &amp;nbsp;The round rung design requires the runner to stay on the balls of their feet. &amp;nbsp;If the runner cheats and runs flat footed, they will feel the rungs hit their heals. &amp;nbsp;This round rung design helps promote good form and technique. It stretches out (12′) twelve feet, has (10) ten rungs that are spaced (16″) inches apart, and has (9) nine stepping spaces. It is the most popular piece of training equipment we sell. &amp;nbsp;Just roll it out and go!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Adjustable 8″ to 12” Performance Hurdles are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBest for teaching proper knee lift, generating force with the leg, explosive plyometrics, with variable degrees of adjustable difficulty.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Speed Parachute&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAn XL 54”and creates the drag necessary to force athletes to push themselves harder to achieve speed. The easy step-in belt was added based on athlete feedback, allowing you to get right to your workout without stopping to adjust buckles.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Speed Harness&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nResistance training at its finest! It maximizes your force application, power, running mechanics &amp;amp; acceleration. All the things that make you a powerhouse. Hook it to a sled, tire, or other weighted object for use alone, or have a partner provide varying degrees or resistance for more sport-specific applications.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reaction Ball&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nA unique 6-sided design is the liveliest and most erratic ball available! The random bouncing helps the athlete focus on moving with their opponents and reacting to unpredictable variables.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lateral Resistor Power Ankle Resistance Band&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHelps develop a strong first-step quickness and targets the hard to isolate inner and outer twitch thigh muscles. The extra long padded ankle cuffs are accommodated with quick change velcro connectors.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Agility Cones&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHelp improve acceleration, deceleration and change direction. &amp;nbsp;They build precise timing and body control ideal for agility training drills. &amp;nbsp;They are durable and will not break when stepped on. &amp;nbsp;Use them to mark your distance and direction.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;What\'s Included In This Kit:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) Instructional Training DVD&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) Six Sided Reaction Ball &amp;amp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) Lateral Resistor Ankle Resistance Stepper&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) 12 Foot Round Rung HD Team Grade Agility Ladder &amp;amp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) Resistance Harness&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(5) 8″ to 12″ Adjustable Speed Hurdles &amp;amp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(10) Agility Disc Cones&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) Speed Resistance Training Parachute &amp;amp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) Heavy Duty All In One Carrying Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'New Speed and Agility Training Kit with Free Carry Bag and DVD', 'New Speed and Agility Training Kit with Free Carry Bag and DVD', 'New Speed and Agility Training Kit with Free Carry Bag and DVD'),
(10375, 1, 'GoSun Sport Pro Pack - Stainless Steel', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ONLY 1 LEFT IN STOCK!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EVERYTHING YOU NEED TO COOK LIKE A PRO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe GoSun Sport Pro Pack contains a GoSun Sport and everything you need to make full use of it, including a padded Carrying Case for secure travel, an extra Cooking Tray for prepping your next dish and non-stick silicone baking pans. GoSun anywhere!\\&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THIS PACKAGE INCLUDES:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;GoSun Sport Solar Oven: &amp;nbsp;The next evolution in fuel-free cooking&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Reusable Silicone Mini Baking Pans: Perfect for cooking different foods, baking, and easy clean up too!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Carrying Case: A perfect companion to the GoSun Sport, this durable, padded Nylon bag is built to take a beating, with the capacity to hold a kitchen on the go.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Custom Fit Padded Interior Pocket: Protects the stove from impact and scratches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy-Clean Tray Pocket: Clean up any mess with a few wipes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ergonomic Shoulder Strap: Easy to carry heavy loads&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra Cooking Tray: Great for serving one dish while cooking another - first savory, then sweet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BENEFITS:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fast: &amp;nbsp;Cooks a meal in as little as 20 minutes, reaching temperatures up to 550°F (290°C)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cooks When Cloudy: &amp;nbsp;You don\'t have to see the Sun to cook! The GoSun is so effective, almost no day is off limits!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Portable: &amp;nbsp;Set-up in seconds and folds into a slim package. GoSun anywhere!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel-Free and Clean: &amp;nbsp;No mess. No flames. No cost. Always prepared for delicious!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Versatile: &amp;nbsp;Bake, Boil, Steam or Fry. Cook Anything&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Safe to Touch: &amp;nbsp;Vacuum insulation keeps exterior surface cool&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two Year Warranty: &amp;nbsp;Durable, made of borosilicate glass (like Pyrex®)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;International Shipping Available: Simply enter your shipping address to check shipping costs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HOW IT WORKS&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;GoSun’s compound parabolic reflectors and tubular design converts nearly 80% of all sunlight entering it’s reflectors into useable heat.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The GoSun Sport includes a durable borosilicate, vacuum tube oven, two anodized aluminum, parabolic reflectors that fold to protect the tube, a stainless steel cooking tray, a scrubby cleaning tool and stainless steel carrying handles.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0789/1333/files/How_it_Works_Exports-03_grande.png?12935288119796061648&quot; style=&quot;width: 600px; height: 385px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;A miracle of science, the evacuated glass tube of the GoSun Cooking Technology is a near perfect insulator, allowing one to solar cook in even the most challenging conditions. By effectively capturing light from a broad range of angles, the GoSun does not require frequent readjustment, making it the lowest maintenance fuel free cooking device yet.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dry Weight: 7 lbs (3.18kg)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oven Volume: 40oz (1.2L) fluid or up to 3 lbs (1.4kg) of food&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oven Dimensions: 2.7” (7.0cm) outside diameter, 2.1” (5.4cm) inside diameter , 24” (61cm) length&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unit Open Size: 24” (61cm) long x 16” (41cm) tall x 12” (30cm) wide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unit Closed Size: 24” (61cm) long x 8” (20cm) tall x 5” (13cm) wide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Estimated Power Output: 200 Watts in full sunlight&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Temperature: 550°F (288°C)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Working Temperature: 200°F (93°C) – 450°F (232°C)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cooking Time: As fast as 10 minutes, see infographic below&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0789/1333/files/Cooktimes_ForWeb-02.png?8094397530195484926&quot; style=&quot;width: 655px; height: 332px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'GoSun Sport Pro Pack - Stainless Steel', 'GoSun Sport Pro Pack - Stainless Steel', 'GoSun Sport Pro Pack - Stainless Steel'),
(10359, 1, 'AIRMEGA 300 The Smarter Air Purifier (Covers 1256 sq. ft.)', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ONLY 1 LEFT!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The 300 model is &lt;strong&gt;NOT WI-FI / MOBILE APP&lt;/strong&gt;-enabled. With Smart Mode (Auto, Sleep, Eco) and real-time air quality monitoring, you can rest assured you’ll have clean air at all times.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;At 1,256 square foot coverage, the 300 model is perfect for small- to medium-sized rooms.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;All Airmega models come with two Pre-filters and two Max2 Filters.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Real-time Air Quality Monitoring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAirmega’s air quality sensor tells you the quality of the air in the room in real time. The brightly colored LED ring lets you know if your air is fresh or unhealthy every minute of the day.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Smart Mode&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith Smart Mode, Airmega adapts to you. It allows Airmega to automatically adjust its fan speed based on the room’s air quality and room condition.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Smart (Auto) Mode&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAirmega’s Smart Mode automatically adjusts the air filtration speed according to the room’s current air quality.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Smart (Eco) Mode&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhen the air quality remains good for 10 minutes or more, Airmega conserves energy by shutting down the fan. If the sensor detects pollution in the air, the fan will restart automatically.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Smart (Sleep) Mode&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhen set on Smart Mode, Airmega’s light sensor detects when it’s dark and the air purifier automatically reduces its fan speed so it runs much quieter.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Powerful Performance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCompact, efficient and powerful. With its dual suction capability and advanced filters, Airmega can handle a room up to 1,256 square feet in size and remove from the air pollutants as small as one micron in size.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Filter Levels&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAirmega tells you when it’s time to replace the filter—so you never have to think about the age of the filter.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two air changes/hour*: 1,256 ft2 (117 m2)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Four air changes/hour**: 628 ft2 (58 m2)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mobile App: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto Mode: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Eco Mode: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sleep Mode: Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Filter: Washable pre-filter + Max2 filter set (Activated carbon + Green True HEPA)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Real-Time Monitoring: Good, Moderate, Unhealthy, Very Unhealthy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Filter Life Time Indicator: Wash, Change&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fan Speed: Sleep, Low, Medium, High&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Timer: Product (1, 4, 8 hours)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Scheduler: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Size (H x W x D): 21.2 x 13.6 x 13.6 in (53.8 x 34.5 x 34.5 cm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 21.4 lb (9.7 kg)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Noise Level: 22~52 dB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Consumption: 57 W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The coverage area of the Airmega reflects the size of the area in which the Airmega can make two air changes per hour (ACPH). “One air change per hour” reflects how many times the Airmega can clean an area, assuming the height of the ceiling to be 8 feet, in one hour. *The Airmega can clean the area once every 30 minutes. **The Airmega can clean the area once every 15 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'AIRMEGA 300 The Smarter Air Purifier (Covers 1256 sq. ft.)', 'AIRMEGA 300 The Smarter Air Purifier (Covers 1256 sq. ft.)', 'AIRMEGA 300 The Smarter Air Purifier (Covers 1256 sq. ft.)');
