(10376, 1, '48-Inch Crank Adjustable Two-tier Standing Desk with Steel Frame', '&lt;p&gt;Get the health benefits of an adjustable height stand up desk with this two tier shelf design that puts your monitor at the proper viewing height and the keyboard and mouse at the proper working height. Easily move from sitting to standing with the desk’s crank, which allows for on-the-fly adjustments from top to bottom in just 60 seconds. Our stand up desk comes with 3-inch casters to support easy movement at home or in collaborative office environments.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The two-tier shelf design improves your posture by keeping your screen at the ideal height&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Crank adjusts from 28.875” to 42.625” (lower surface) and 33.5” to 47.25” (upper surface)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;47” wide work surface—14” deep top shelf; 16” deep lower shelf&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two-tier shelf design, 3.75” separation between shelves&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Silver gray powder coat paint finish&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The 3&quot; casters, two with locking brakes, support easy mobility&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall dimension: 47” W x 28.5” D x 33.5” – 47.5” H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Everything needed for assembly is included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;This standing desk is BIFMA certified and has a maximum table load of 154 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Download:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://standupdeskstore.com/media/wysiwyg/SUDCR48_instruct.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;48&quot; Crank Adjustable Height Sit to Stand Up Desk Assembly Instructions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://standupdeskstore.com/media/wysiwyg/pdfs/SUDC48FT_Dimensions.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;48&quot; Crank Adjustable Height Sit to Stand Up Desk Dimensions&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', '48-Inch Crank Adjustable Two-tier Standing Desk with Steel Frame', '48-Inch Crank Adjustable Two-tier Standing Desk with Steel Frame', '48-Inch Crank Adjustable Two-tier Standing Desk with Steel Frame'),
(10377, 1, '60-Inch Crank Adjustable Sit to Stand Two-tier Desk with Steel Frame', '&lt;p&gt;The innovative 60&quot; Crank Adjustable Sit to Stand Desk helps enhance your health by giving you movement and flexibility through the workday. Easily move from sitting to standing with the desk’s crank, which allows for effortless on-the-fly adjustment. Improve your focus, productivity, posture, and all-around health immediately with the 60&quot; Crank Adjustable Sit to Stand Desk.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Crank adjusts from 28.875&quot; to 42.625&quot; (lower surface) and 33.5&quot; to 47.25&quot; (upper surface)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;59” wide work surface—14” deep top shelf; 16” deep lower shelf&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two-tier shelf design, 4.625” separation between shelves&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Silver gray powder coat paint finish&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3&quot; furniture casters with two locking brakes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall dimensions: 59” W x 28.5” D x 33.5 – 47.25” H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Everything needed for assembly is included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;This standing desk is BIFMA certified and has a maximum table load of 154 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Download:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.standupdeskstore.com/media/wysiwyg/SUDC60_instruct.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;60&quot; Crank Adjustable Sit to Stand Up Desk w/ Heavy Duty Steel Frame Assembly Guide&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://http://www.standupdeskstore.com/media/wysiwyg/pdfs/SUDC60_Dimensions_0615.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;60&quot; Crank Adjustable Sit to Stand Up Desk w/ Heavy Duty Steel Frame Dimensions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', '60-Inch Crank Adjustable Sit to Stand Two-tier Desk with Steel Frame', '60-Inch Crank Adjustable Sit to Stand Two-tier Desk with Steel Frame', '60-Inch Crank Adjustable Sit to Stand Two-tier Desk with Steel Frame'),
(10379, 1, 'Predator Engines 13 HP 420cc OHV Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA/CARB', '&lt;p&gt;This Predator 420cc gasoline engine has gas-saving overhead valves for cooler, cleaner performance and longer life. The horizontal shaft is ball-bearing mounted, making this gas engine an ideal replacement for most standard engine configurations. The powerful gas engine features a durable cast iron cylinder making it the perfect replacement engine for a lawn mower, log-splitter and dozens of other machines.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Upgraded engineering and construction for improved lifespan&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Durable cast iron cylinder withstands wear and abuse&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;User-friendly controls for easy starting and operation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low oil sensor shuts down engine when oil reaches a level that is too low for safe operation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel shut off for safe transport&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;For use on: pressure washers, compressors, log splitters, vacuums, tillers, water pumps, chipper/shredders, blowers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manufacturer Warranty Detail&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWe guarantee the emissions control system on your engine will be free from defects in material and workmanship for two (2) years, provided there has been no improper maintenance, misuse, or abuse of your engine. We guarantee this product to be free from defects in materials and workmanship for 90 days from the date of purchase. Limitations apply.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Manual&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://manuals.harborfreight.com/manuals/69000-69999/69736.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Download the Manual for the 69736 420 cc OHV Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine - Certified for California&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://manuals.harborfreight.com/manuals/69000-69999/Q69736.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Download Quick Start Guide for the 69736 420 cc OHV Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine - Certified for California&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Name: 13 HP (420cc) OHV Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA/CARB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: Predator Engines&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Application: pressure washers, compressors, log splitters, vacuums, tillers, water pumps, chipper/shredders, blowers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Certification: EPA &amp;amp; CARB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engine displacement (cc): 420cc&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Horsepower (hp): 13&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum speed (rpm): 3600 RPM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Torque (ft. - lbs.): 18.4 ft. lbs. @ 2500 RPM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mounting pattern: 195.5mm L x 86.0mm W - 103.0mm W (7.7 in. L x 3.4 in. W - 4.1 in. W )&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mounting type: Horizontal&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft rotation direction: Counter clockwise&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sound rating (dB): 108 dB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Start type: Electric start with recoil backup&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height: 17.1 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Length: 18.9 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This item can only be shipped within the 48 contiguous states via Standard Ground Shipping. In order to return this item for a refund or replacement, all fuel must first be drained.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Predator Engines 13 HP 420cc OHV Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA/CARB', 'Predator Engines 13 HP 420cc OHV Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA/CARB', 'Predator Engines 13 HP 420cc OHV Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA/CARB'),
(10385, 1, 'Strider - 12 Pro Balance Bike, Ages 18 Months to 5 Years, All-Aluminum', '&lt;p&gt;The lightweight aluminum frame makes the 12 Pro the lightest production Strider® toddler bike available and a perfect way for STRIDER Riders to take the next step with their riding. Whether it’s onto the playground or the dirt track. &amp;nbsp;If you are looking for the lightest, most advanced balance bike for toddlers on the market, the STRIDER 12 Pro is for you.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;All-Aluminum, High-End Model&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The lightest STRIDER Bike in the World!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ages 18 months - 5 years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ultra-Lightweight design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Same specs as 12 Sport Model, PLUS:&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Aluminum materials for ultra lightweight&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stylish number plate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Available in silver&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Strider?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThrough ten years of development, manufacturing improvements, riding, observation, testing and even racing, Strider Bikes has created a bike that allows for an easy and more successful transition to a pedal bike. Strider specializes specifically in Balance Bikes and in the process the company has developed enhanced features, including the lowest seat in the industry. With Strider’s Four Learn-to-Ride steps, children can jump on a bike and get moving as soon as the bike is set up. As lovers of riding bikes, Strider loves inspiring children to ride. Strider’s mission is to build lightweight, efficient, all-terrain bikes that develop two-wheeled balance, coordination, and confidence. With 1 million sold worldwide, Strider hopes to continue to reach families around the world.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Balance Bikes?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe balance bike is a simple design to teach young children how to steer and balance on two wheels without training wheels. Since the bike has no pedals or other complicated forms of propulsion, most children come to find that riding a balance bike is as easy as walking. Children do not have to fear when they are on a balance bike because they can place their feet solidly on the ground. As the child progresses at his or her pace, they can change to a traditional bicycle whenever they are ready.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;About the Strider 12 Sport&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Feature-Rich, Mid-Level Model offers every feature a child (or parent) could want with custom grips, padded saddle, handlebar pad, and quick release clamps (no-tool adjustment). It is the perfect balance of performance, options, and value. More than eight years of design evolution and manufacturing improvements all packaged into one model. And with a bonus second, taller seat post for the 3-5 year old child, it is the only balance bike a toddler/preschooler will ever need.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Handlebar&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nUnique 12.7mm swaged-aluminum handlebar is 43% smaller than standard to allow better control with tiny hands. Custom logo mini-grips are soft urethane with protective ends. Machined-aluminum quick release allows “No Tools” height adjustment from 46-56cm (18-22”).&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe included number plate features custom Pro graphics for that hi-performance look.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wheel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nStrider-exclusive, ultralight one-piece wheels sport a raised-letter, five-spoke design with 10 bearing support gussets for maximum strength at the lightest weight possible.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTop-quality sealed cartridge bearings roll smooth and never need adjustment.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tires&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEVA polymer (industrial foam) tires are super light and durable yet offer a smooth ride. Best of all, they never need air and will never go flat.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Seats&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe durable, all-weather mini-saddle is designed specifically for beginning riders and their tiny hips. Smaller, narrower, and lighter than a typical saddle, this seat allows for proper riding position and posture. ** The Pro model also includes a padded XL saddle and long seatpost to fit kids over 3 years and allows seat height adjustments up to 48cm (19”).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bar and seat clamps&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMachined aluminum quick release allows “No Tools” saddle height adjustment from 28-41cm (11-16”) for the perfect fit for your child.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Footrest&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nUnique, frame-integrated footrests are properly positioned directly below the saddle for natural bike balance. This position also fosters the advanced ability to stand while gliding as well as pumping and jumping the bike&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brake mount&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nStrider-exclusive rear brake mount allows the addition of a foot-operated brake once the kids are proficiently gliding with feet on the footrests. Brake sold separately.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Strider - 12 Pro Balance Bike, Ages 18 Months to 5 Years', 'Strider - 12 Pro Balance Bike, Ages 18 Months to 5 Years', 'Strider - 12 Pro Balance Bike, Ages 18 Months to 5 Years'),
(10381, 1, 'Stark Power JumpBox V8 Pro 1000', '&lt;p&gt;The JUMPBOX V8 Pro 1000 is the ultimate jump starter device for your CARS, SUVs, TRUCKS, ATVs, UTVs, MOTORCYCLES, PWCs, BOATS and RVs. Its 1000 Amp design makes it 2.5 times more powerful than any lithium-ion starter on the market and allows it to excel in colder conditions. It directly connects to your existing lead-acid starter battery and jumps your battery in 1-2 seconds. Not only does it contain the most powerful lithium chemistry, it also has an internal microprocessor controlled cell balancer for added performance and longevity. No more worries about dead batteries with the JUMPBOX V8 Pro 1000 in your vehicle.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Jump starts most gasoline engines up to 7.2L V8, diesels up to 4.0L and all power sport models.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The JumpBox V8 Pro 1000 comes with mobile phone connectors, computer charging connectors and has two (2) 5V USB ports for rapidly charging any Smartphone, laptop, camera or other mobile electronic device you may have.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;StarkPower’s internal microprocessor is a controlled cell balancer for added performance and longevity.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Jump starts most gasoline engines up to 7.2L V8, diesels up to 4.0L and all power sport models.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The JumpBox V8 Pro 1000 comes with mobile phone connectors, computer charging connectors and has two (2) 5V USB ports for rapidly charging any Smartphone, laptop, camera or other mobile electronic device you may have.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;StarkPower’s internal microprocessor is a controlled cell balancer for added performance and longevity.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WORLD CLASS SAFETY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nStarkPower prides themselves on being at the forefront of safety innovations in the portable power category.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;StarkPower Smart Cables have a built in sensor that protects them from overheating and sparking by reversing the polarity.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;battery-icons&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;StarkPower’s internal microprocessor regulates internal temperatures and controls cell balancing for added safety.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;thermometer-icons&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The JumpBox functions in a wider range of temperatures than any other jump starter (from -4˚F to +140˚F.)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe JumpBox V8 Pro 1000 is smaller, more powerful and lasts longer than any other jump starter on the market.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;At 6.9”(L) x 3.4”(W) x 1.4”(H) and weighing only 1.25 lb., the JumpBox V8 Pro 1000 has the best size to power ratio of any lithium-ion jump starter on the market.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;power-icons&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Its 54,000mWh power bank ensures longer lasting power for when you need it most.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;battery-icons&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The JumpBox has an expected battery life of 8-10 years as opposed to the industry average of 3 years.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ultra light weight (Up to 80% less weight than lead acid)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;500% smaller than conventional lead acid jump boxes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lasts 300-400% longer than lead acid&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Internal cell balancing circuit for longer life and added starting performance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wall charger and cigarette charger included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charge smart phones with 4-in-1 mobile micro connectors&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;FAST charge electronic devices (laptop, tablets, cameras PSP etc) with use of 7-in1 adaptor fittings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Choose voltage at 19V,16V or 12V for optimum charging&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Environmentally friendly: No explosive gasses during charging, no lead, no heavy metals, no acid spills&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;54,000 mWh power bank for long lasting power supply&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery charge lasts for multiple years unattended- Self discharge rate (2% vs 10% lead acid / month)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built in LED flash light (3 modes-high, strobe and SOS)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;USB Port – 5V/2.1A&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built in LED charge indicator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Over 20 starts with fully charged battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic Power-Off when not in use&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Expect 8-10 years of battery life&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easily fits in a glove box for emergency power source&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Stark Power JumpBox V8 Pro 1000', 'Stark Power JumpBox V8 Pro 1000', 'Stark Power JumpBox V8 Pro 1000'),
