(10388, 1, 'Central Machinery 5 ton Log Splitter, 1.8 HP, 12 Amp 6 inch Wheels', '&lt;p&gt;This log splitter delivers up to 5 ton of splitting force to split logs as thick as 10 in. in diameter. Features include a wheel kit for easy transport and a 1.8 HP electric motor for reliable power. Split heavy logs quickly and safely with this 5 ton log splitter.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Split 10 in. diameter logs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6 in. wheels for easy transport&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compact size for convenient storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy grip handle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Name: 5 ton Log Splitter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SKU: 61373&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: Central Machinery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Amperage (amps): 12&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Horsepower (hp)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;: 1.8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Diameter: 10 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quantity: 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Length: 38 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width: 11 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shipping Weight: 110.80 lb.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tire size (in.):&amp;nbsp; 6 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Travel length (in.):&amp;nbsp; 0-17 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Product Manual&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://manuals.harborfreight.com/manuals/61000-61999/61373.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Click here to Download the Manual for the 61373 5 ton Log Splitter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Central Machinery 5 ton Log Splitter, 1.8 HP, 12 Amp 6 inch Wheels', 'Central Machinery 5 ton Log Splitter, 1.8 HP, 12 Amp 6 inch Wheels', 'Central Machinery 5 ton Log Splitter, 1.8 HP, 12 Amp 6 inch Wheels'),
(10389, 1, 'Chicago Electric 2.5 Horsepower 10&quot; Industrial Tile/Brick Saw', '&lt;p&gt;The two-position cutting head on this professional tile saw lets you adjust blade for a variety of tiles or bricks. Includes built-in 3 gallon per minute water pump, removable easy-to-clean high-impact ABS water tub.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable cutting head lets you adjust blade for standard tiles or bricks up to 3-1/2 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;24 in. cutting capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Head pivots to allow 22.5° and 45° bevel cuts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Powerful dual capacitor motor with sealed bearings and thermal overload protection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy duty cast alloy column and cutting head for reduced vibration&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oversized steel frame with precision linear bar system for smooth operation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Name: 10 in. 2.5 HP Tile/Brick Saw&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SKU: 69275&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: Chicago Electric Power Tools&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Amperage (amps): 15&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cutting angles (deg): 0-45°&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Horsepower (hp): 2.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum cutting thickness (in.): 3-1/2 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum speed (rpm): 3800 RPM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Arbor size: 5/8 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blade size : 10 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth of cut (in.): 3-1/2 in. @ 0°, 1-1/2 in. @ 45°&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height: 22-1/2 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Length: 35 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight: 90 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width: 24 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shipping Weight: 79.05 lb.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Table dimensions: 17 in. x 19-3/4 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Accessories Included: Pump, water tub, miter gauge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Diagonal cut size (in.) : 18 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Manual&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://manuals.harborfreight.com/manuals/69000-69999/69275.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Click here to Download the Manual for the 69275 10 in. 2.5 HP Tile/Brick Saw&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Stand sold separately. Diamond blade shown, sold separately.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Chicago Electric 2.5 Horsepower 10&quot; Industrial Tile/Brick Saw', 'Chicago Electric 2.5 Horsepower 10&quot; Industrial Tile/Brick Saw', 'Chicago Electric 2.5 Horsepower 10&quot; Industrial Tile/Brick Saw'),
(10390, 1, 'Predator Engines 22 HP 708cc V-Twin Vertical Shaft Gas Engine EPA', '&lt;p&gt;This Predator 708cc V-twin 4-stroke gasoline engine delivers more power in less space than similar displacement standard twins. The vertical shaft is ball-bearing mounted, making this gas engine an ideal replacement for most standard engine configurations. The powerful v-twin gas engine features a durable cast iron cylinder making it the perfect replacement engine for: mowers, water pumps, high pressure washers and dozens of other machines.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compact v-twin design for more power in a smaller footprint&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Durable cast iron cylinder withstands wear and abuse&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electric start&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel shut off for safe transport&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;For use on: mowers, water pumps, high pressure washers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Name: 22 HP (708cc) V-Twin Vertical Shaft Gas Engine EPA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SKU: 62879&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Application: mowers, water pumps, high pressure washers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engine displacement (cc): 708cc&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel type: 85 octane or higher unleaded&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Horsepower (hp): 22&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low oil shutdown: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum speed (rpm): 3000+/-100 RPM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Torque (ft. - lbs.)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;: 32.5 ft. lbs. torque at 2500 RPM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mounting type: Vertical&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft rotation direction: CCW&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Start type: Electric&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height: 14 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Length: 18-3/8 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight: 92.6 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width: 18-9/10 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Keyway: 0.25 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shipping Weight: 117.35 lb.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroke length (in.): 76 mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Diameter: 1 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Manual&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://manuals.harborfreight.com/manuals/62000-62999/62879.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Click here to Download the Manual for the 62879 22 HP (708cc) V-Twin Vertical Shaft Gas Engine EPA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Not for sale in California. In order to return this item for a refund or replacement, all fuel must first be drained. Battery sold separately. Fuel tank not included.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Predator Engines 22 HP 708cc V-Twin Vertical Shaft Gas Engine EPA', 'Predator Engines 22 HP 708cc V-Twin Vertical Shaft Gas Engine EPA', 'Predator Engines 22 HP 708cc V-Twin Vertical Shaft Gas Engine EPA'),
(10378, 1, 'Predator Engines 8 HP (301cc) OHV Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA', '&lt;p&gt;This Predator 301cc gasoline engine has gas-saving overhead valves for cooler, cleaner performance and longer life. The horizontal shaft is ball-bearing mounted, making this gas engine an ideal replacement for most standard engine configurations. The powerful gas engine features a durable cast iron cylinder making it the perfect replacement engine for a lawn mower, log-splitter and dozens of other machines.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Upgraded engineering and construction for improved lifespan&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Durable cast iron cylinder withstands wear and abuse&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;User-friendly controls for easy starting and operation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low oil sensor shuts down engine when oil reaches a level that is too low for safe operation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel shut off for safe transport&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;For use on: pressure washers, compressors, log splitters, vacuums, tillers, water pumps, chipper/shredders, blowers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manufacturer Warranty Detail&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWe guarantee the emissions control system on your engine will be free from defects in material and workmanship for two (2) years, provided there has been no improper maintenance, misuse, or abuse of your engine. We guarantee this product to be free from defects in materials and workmanship for 90 days from the date of purchase. Limitations apply.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Manual&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;http://manuals.harborfreight.com/manuals/62000-62999/62554.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Click here to Download the Manual for the 62554 8 HP (301cc) OHV Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Name: 8 HP (301cc) OHV Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SKU: 62554&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: Predator Engines&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Application: pressure washers, compressors, log splitters, vacuums, tillers, water pumps, chipper/shredders, blowers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Certification: EPA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engine displacement (cc): 301cc&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Horsepower (hp): 8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum speed (rpm): 3600 RPM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Torque (ft. - lbs.)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;: 14.9 ft. lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mounting pattern: 195.5 mm L x 82.5 mm W - 96mm W (7.7 in. L x 3.25 in. W - 3.78 in. W)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft rotation direction: Counter clockwise&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Start type: Recoil&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height: 17.25 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Length: 15 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight: 54 lb. / 24.5 kg.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width: 17 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft length (in.): 3.48 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Keyway: 0.25 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shipping Weight&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;: 63.60 lb.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroke length (in.): 60 mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Diameter: 1 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Manual&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://manuals.harborfreight.com/manuals/62000-62999/62554.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Click here to Download the Manual for the 62554 8 HP (301cc) OHV Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Item for sale outside California only – please refer to item 61415 for California compliant model. This item can only be shipped within the 48 contiguous states via Standard Ground Shipping. In order to return this item for a refund or replacement, all fuel must first be drained.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Predator Engines 8 HP (301cc) OHV Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA', 'Predator Engines 8 HP (301cc) OHV Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA', 'Predator Engines 8 HP (301cc) OHV Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA');
