(10391, 1, 'Predator Engines 22 HP 670cc V-Twin Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA', '&lt;p&gt;This Predator 670cc V-twin 4-stroke gasoline engine delivers more power in less space than similar displacement standard twins. The horizontal shaft is ball-bearing mounted, making this gas engine an ideal replacement for most standard engine configurations. The powerful v-twin gas engine features a durable cast iron cylinder making it the perfect replacement engine for: Mowers, water pumps, high pressure washers and dozens of other machines.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compact v-twin design for more power in a smaller footprint&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Durable cast iron cylinder withstands wear and abuse&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electric start&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel shut off for safe transport&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;For use on: Mowers, water pumps, high pressure washers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Name: 22 HP (670cc) V-Twin Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SKU: 61614&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: Predator Engines&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Application: Mowers, water pumps, high pressure washers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Certification: EPA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engine displacement (cc): 670cc&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel type: 87+ octane unleaded gasoline&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Horsepower (hp)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;: 22&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum speed (rpm): 4000 RPM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Torque (ft. - lbs.): 45 NM @ 2500 RPM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mounting pattern: 7.7 in. x 4 in. - 3.4 in. (195.5mm x 101.5mm - 86mm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft rotation direction: Counter clockwise&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sound rating (dB): 88 dB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Start type: Electric&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height: 16.9 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Length: 23.6 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight: 106 lb.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width: 19.2 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft length (in.): 2.84 in/72.2 mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Keyway: 1/4 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shipping Weight&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;: 127.40 lb.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroke length (in.): 70 mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Diameter: 1 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Manual&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://manuals.harborfreight.com/manuals/61000-61999/61614.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Click here to Download the Manual for the 61614 22 HP (670cc) V-Twin Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Predator Engines 22 HP 670cc V-Twin Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA', 'Predator Engines 22 HP 670cc V-Twin Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA', 'Predator Engines 22 HP 670cc V-Twin Horizontal Shaft Gas Engine EPA'),
(10392, 1, 'Husqvarna 455 Rancher Gas Chainsaw 56cc Engine, 18-Inch', '&lt;p&gt;For the heaviest cutting jobs, the Husqvarna 455 Rancher has you covered. This model combines the X-Torq® engine and Smart Start® technologies of earlier models with a uniquely heavy-duty and ergonomic design.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAmong Husqvarna\'s most powerful chainsaws, the Husqvarna 455 Rancher combines a heavy-duty design with a 56cc X-Torq® engine and countless safety and ease-of-use features. Smart Start® technology ensures that the engine starts easily every time, even in the cold. Thanks to the innovative centrifugal air cleaning system, dust and debris are removed before they hit the air filter, making the engine is incredibly long-lasting. LowVib® technology and the ergonomically designed 7&quot; offset handle reduce vibration and fatigue, allowing for hours of comfortable use. Powerful and ergonomic, the Husqvarna 455 Rancher is packed with quality features for your comfort and safety.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;56cc X-Torq® engine&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Centrifugal air cleaning system reduces air filter cleanings and improves engine life&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smart Start® technology ensures an easy start every time&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Combined choke and stop control allows for easier starting and reduces the risk of engine flooding&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Side-mounted chain tensioner allows for easy chain tensioning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LowVib® system reduces vibration to the operator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Inertia-activated chain brake reduces the likelihood of injury due to kickback&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick-release air filter makes cleaning and changing the air filter easy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Forged three-piece crankshaft for maximum durability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Husqvarna 455 Rancher Gas Chainsaw 56cc Engine, 18-Inch', 'Husqvarna 455 Rancher Gas Chainsaw 56cc Engine, 18-Inch', 'Husqvarna 455 Rancher Gas Chainsaw 56cc Engine, 18-Inch'),
(10393, 1, 'Husqvarna 445 Gas Chainsaw 46cc Engine, 16-Inch', '&lt;p&gt;Powerful X-Torq® engine and Smart Start® technology ensure this chainsaw starts easily every time and always gets the job done. Tree pruning, cutting firewood, and maintaining a property have never been so easy!&lt;br /&gt;\r\nA fantastic all-around chainsaw, the Husqvarna 445 has all the quality features of a professional-grade machine. The 46cc X-Torq® engine delivers low fuel consumption and exhaust emissions, making it a powerful as well as environmentally friendly choice. The LowVib® system minimizes hand and arm vibration, cutting down on operator fatigue and allowing for hours of comfortable use. Smart Start® technology ensures that the engine starts easily every time, even in the cold. Thanks to the innovative centrifugal air cleaning system, dust and debris are removed before they hit the air filter, making the engine is incredibly long-lasting. Powerful and ergonomic, the Husqvarna 445 is packed with quality features for your comfort and safety.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;46cc X-Torq® engine&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Centrifugal air cleaning system reduces air filter cleanings and improves engine life&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smart Start® technology ensures an easy start every time&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Combined choke and stop control allows for easier starting and reduces the risk of engine flooding&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Side-mounted chain tensioner allows for easy chain tensioning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LowVib® system reduces vibration to the operator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Inertia-activated chain brake reduces the likelihood of injury due to kickback&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick-release air filter makes cleaning and changing the air filter easy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Husqvarna 445 Gas Chainsaw 46cc Engine, 16-Inch', 'Husqvarna 445 Gas Chainsaw 46cc Engine, 16-Inch', 'Husqvarna 445 Gas Chainsaw 46cc Engine, 16-Inch'),
(10394, 1, 'Husqvarna 240 Gas Chainsaw 38cc Engine, 16-Inch', '&lt;p&gt;This powerful Husqvarna chainsaw won\'t let you down. Ergonomic design, powerful X-Torq® engine, Smart Start® technology, and a low emissions rating make it ideal for tree pruning, cutting firewood, and keeping your property looking its best.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;For lighter cutting jobs, the Husqvarna 240 chainsaw is the quality piece of machinery you\'ve been looking for. The 38cc X-Torq® engine delivers low fuel consumption and exhaust emissions, making it a powerful as well as environmentally friendly choice. The LowVib® system minimizes hand and arm vibration, cutting down on operator fatigue and allowing for hours of comfortable use. The engine starts easily and is incredibly long-lasting, thanks to the innovative centrifugal air cleaning system, which removes dust and debris before they hit the air filter. Powerful and ergonomic, the Husqvarna 240 is packed with quality features for your comfort and safety.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;38cc X-Torq® engine&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Centrifugal air cleaning system reduces air filter cleanings and improves engine life&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Combined choke and stop control allows for easier starting and reduces the risk of engine flooding&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Side-mounted chain tensioner allows for easy chain tensioning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LowVib® system reduces vibration to the operator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Inertia-activated chain brake reduces the likelihood of injury due to kickback&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Comes with Manufacturer Warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Husqvarna 240 Gas Chainsaw 38cc Engine, 16-Inch', 'Husqvarna 240 Gas Chainsaw 38cc Engine, 16-Inch', 'Husqvarna 240 Gas Chainsaw 38cc Engine, 16-Inch'),
(10395, 1, 'DR Trimmer/Mower 7.25 Pro, Manual Start', '&lt;p&gt;For heavier mowing, the PRO model features a premium 7.25 FPT Briggs &amp;amp; Stratton engine. The PRO also has bigger wheels (16&quot;) for easier maneuvering.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Power for Tougher Mowing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe PRO model features a premium Briggs &amp;amp; Stratton engine with 7.25 foot-pounds of torque. The frame is mounted with extra high 16&quot; wheels for easier maneuvering. The PRO cuts a 22&quot; swath, has 5 adjustable mowing heights (1.5&quot; to 3.5&quot;), and offers ergonomic handlebars for stress free mowing.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;An offset frame design allows the PRO to trim right up against foundations, fence lines and other obstacles with precise control. The front is fortified with a cast aluminum nose plate that protects the machine against damage from collisions.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5X the power of handheld trimmers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;7.25 ft/lb Briggs &amp;amp; Stratton engine&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ergonomic handlebars with padded grips&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;22&quot; Cutting Width&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5 Cutting Heights: 1.5&quot; to 3.5&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Accepts optional DuraBlades and Beaver Blade&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Accepts 175 mil cord—the thickest, longest-lasting cord available.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Warranty Coverage:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engine: 2 years residential&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Machine: 2 years residential&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Briggs &amp;amp; Stratton Engine&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe legendary power, performance and durability of Briggs &amp;amp; Stratton® engines make them the only ones we use on our Trimmer/Mowers. They are easy to start, comfortable to use, and feature a debris management system that protects the engine from whatever you kick up while you’re cutting.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Super-duty Cutting Cords&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAll DR Trimmer/Mowers accept super-thick 175 mil cutting cords—the thickest, longest-lasting in the industry (so you spend more time mowing and less time changing cords).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Engineered to Perform&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAmerica\'s #1 selling trimmer on wheels, backed by over 25 years of innovation, and tested for thousands of hours. Every detail is designed to deliver rock soild reliability and unbeatable performance.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optional DuraBlades for 3/8&quot; Thick Brush&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith our optional DR DuraBlades you can quickly swap out your cutting cords with metal blades, embedded in a high-tech polymer, that slice through woody material up to 3/8&quot; thick!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No Wrapping&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nUnlike most trimmers, the DR wide-body design prevents vegetation from wrapping and tangling around the trimmer head (which tends to stall the engine. Even in tall grass, the DR Trimmer Mower keeps on keeping on.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optional Beaver Blade for the big stuff&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe optional Beaver Blade turns your trimmer into a chainsaw on wheels. Cuts trees up to 3&quot; in diameter quickly and easily. It\'s the perfect way to take down stands of &quot;weed trees&quot; without bending over or dropping to your knees like you have to with a normal chainsaw.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Patented Cord Attachment System&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCords go on in seconds, no tools required. Choose from 5 different cutting height adjustments (1.5&quot; to 3.5&quot;) at the same time you attach your cords. No tools and no extra time required. Set the cutting height low for trimming, or set it high for off-lawn mowing of tall grass and weeds.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optional Quick-Lock Trimmer Head&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAllows you to change your trimmer cord in just seconds—completely hassle-free! Cord is simply inserted into the head and is anchored in place by the unique gripping mechanism! Perfect for quick cord changes in the field, and for those who often trim dense thickets of weeds.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cutting Width: 22&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cutting Height: 1 1/2&quot; - 3 1/2&quot; (adjustable)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engine Make: Briggs &amp;amp; Stratton&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model: 725 Series&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ft Lbs Torque: 7.25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Displacement: 163cc Manual Start&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number Of Cylinders: 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Air Filter: Paper filter and prefilter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oil Capacity: 20oz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lubrication: Splash&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Oil Type: 30W HD&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Tires: 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 16&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel Capacity: 1 qt&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Resin Tread: Diamond&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 62 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material Frame: 14 ga steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'DR Trimmer/Mower 7.25 Pro, Manual Start', 'DR Trimmer/Mower 7.25 Pro, Manual Start', 'DR Trimmer/Mower 7.25 Pro, Manual Start'),
(10396, 1, '60-Inch Crank Adjustable Height Sit to Stand Up Desk', '&lt;p&gt;Efficiency meets affordability with our best selling 60” Crank Adjustable Standing Desk. With a hand crank that can be placed on either side of the desk, you have flexibility to sit or stand and easily adjust from one to the other in less than sixty seconds. Increase focus, burn calories, and counteract the health effects of a sedentary life throughout your workday. With the added mobility of rolling casters, the height adjustable stand up desk is mobile and suited for any environment. A generous and sturdy desktop gives space for multiple monitors and office accessories.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Crank adjusts from 29.5” to 45.25” high&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;59&quot; wide x 29.5&quot; deep shelf&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Desktop and frame available in a variety of color options&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Powder coat painted frame&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3&quot; furniture casters, with two locking brakes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall dimensions: 59&quot; W x 29.5&quot; D x 29.5”—45.25”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Everything needed for assembly is included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;This standing desk is BIFMA certified and has a maximum table load of 154 pounds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Desk Frame / Desk Top Color:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Black Frame / Gloss Black Top&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;White Frame / Gloss White Top&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Black Frame / Teak Top&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charcoal Frame / Gloss White Top&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charcoal Frame / Natural Walnut Top&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Black Frame / Black Oak Top&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charcoal Frame / White Oak Top&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Download:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.standupdeskstore.com/media/wysiwyg/SUDC60FT_instruct.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;60&quot; Crank Adjustable Height Sit to Stand Up Desk Assembly Guide &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.standupdeskstore.com/media/wysiwyg/pdfs/SUDC60FT_Dimensions.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;60&quot; Crank Adjustable Height Sit to Stand Up Desk Dimensions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', '60&quot; Crank Adjustable Height Sit to Stand Up Desk', '60&quot; Crank Adjustable Height Sit to Stand Up Desk', '60&quot; Crank Adjustable Height Sit to Stand Up Desk'),
(10397, 1, '60-Inch Electric Stand Up Desk', '&lt;p&gt;Welcome to the new era of sit to stand desks: the Electric Standing Desk from Stand Up Desk Store. Easily transition from sitting to standing in just 20 seconds—all at the touch of a button. The power-lifting mechanism features a quiet motor, giving you the liberty to change your desk\'s height throughout the day. Constructed from a solid steel frame, our electric stand up desk is BIFMA certified and has a maximum table load of 154 lbs. Achieve long-lasting health benefits, including boosted productivity, improved posture, and reduced risk of heart disease, with the effortless mobility of an electric standing desk.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electric push button control adjusts desk from 29-1/2”-45-1/4” in 20 seconds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Spacious 59” W x 29-1/2”D work surface, available in various color options&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Durable powder coat painted frame&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3&quot; furniture casters, with two locking brakes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall dimensions: 59” W x 28-1/2” D x 29-1/2 - 45-1/4” H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Desk Frame / Desk Top Color:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Black Frame / Gloss Black Top&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Black Frame / Teak Top&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charcoal Frame / Gloss White Top&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;White Frame / Gloss White Top&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charcoal Frame / Natural Walnut Top&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Black Frame / Black Oak Top&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charcoal Frame / White Oak Top&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Download:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.standupdeskstore.com/media/wysiwyg/pdfs/SUDE60FT_Dimensions.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;60&quot; Electric Stand Up Desk Dimensions&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.standupdeskstor