(10398, 1, '60-Inch Two Tier Electric Stand Up Desk', '&lt;p&gt;The Two Tier Electric Stand Up Desk puts even the most boring moments of your workday to GREAT use, improving your health while you work. Feel like sitting? Standing? Whichever it is, simply click the button and adjust the height of your power desk to sit or stand in less than 20 seconds.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With a second tier for your monitors and office supplies, the two shelved desk will make good posture easier by keeping your screens closer to eye level. A sixty-inch wide desktop is more than enough room for two monitors, a phone, an array of papers, and even a picture or two of your favorite cat or dog—use it as you see fit.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Also available as a &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ankermart.com/48-Two-Tier-Electric-Stand-Up-Desk&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;48&quot; Two Tier Electric Stand Up Desk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quickly and easily adjust from anywhere between 28.87” and 42.62”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Four casters let you move the desk easily, while locking brakes keep it stationary when it’s time to work&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;A steel frame and powder coat finish give a durable, clean aesthetic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;59” wide work surface, 14” deep top shelf, 16” deep lower shelf&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;This product meets ANSI/BIFMA standards&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Desk Color&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Black Shelves&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dark Walnut Shelves&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Download:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.standupdeskstore.com/media/wysiwyg/pdfs/60_Electric_Split_Top_Desk_Adjustments.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;60&quot; Split Top Electric Stand Up Desk Dimensions &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.st