(10422, 1, 'Predator 2500 PSI, 2.4 GPM, 4 HP (160cc) Pressure Washer EPA/CARB', '&lt;p&gt;Here\'s a powerful pressure washer for tough jobs, with 2500 PSI and 2.4 GPM of cleaning power. The pressure washer has a long-reach high pressure hose so you can clean wider areas. Two heavy duty pneumatic tires make transport easy. This is a great pressure cleaner for any auto garage or shop that wants to clean larger items spic-n-span!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;160cc Predator engine with low oil sensor and recoil start for optimal performance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Commercial-grade axial pump for tough jobs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Five quick-connect tips and 25 ft. high pressure hose for easy cleaning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2500 PSI water pressure provides the cleaning power for almost any job&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2.4 GPM flow rate helps ensure efficient cleaning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Chemical/detergent injector on pump&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EPA/CARB certified engine&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Name: 2500 PSI, 2.4 GPM, 4 HP (160cc) Pressure Washer EPA/CARB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SKU:&amp;nbsp; 62201&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: Predator Outdoor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Certification: EPA/CARB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engine displacement (cc): 160cc&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel type: 86+ Octane Unleaded Gasoline&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Horsepower (hp): &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low oil shutdown: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum pressure (PSI): 2500 PSI&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Nozzle angle (deg): 0°, 15°, 25°, 40°, Soap nozzle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Start type: Recoil&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Thermal Overload Protection (y/n): Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hose Length: 25 ft.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shipping Weight&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;: 70.50 lb.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tire size (in.): 12 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Accessories Included&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;: High pressure hose, gun assembly&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Predator 2500 PSI, 2.4 GPM, 4 HP (160cc) Pressure Washer EPA/CARB', 'Predator 2500 PSI, 2.4 GPM, 4 HP (160cc) Pressure Washer EPA/CARB', 'Predator 2500 PSI, 2.4 GPM, 4 HP (160cc) Pressure Washer EPA/CARB'),
(10424, 1, 'Toucan Surveillance Kit, Security Camera with Alarm, Motion Detection', '&lt;p&gt;With no live wires or batteries, the Toucan connects effortlessly via USB so you can turn your outdoor lights into your homes smart security defense. The kit includes a Smart Security Camera, Smart Socket adaptor, and is Powered by Kuna. Detect activity outside of your home (even at night) and receive instant mobile alerts when people are approaching so you can safely take action using your HD live-feed, two-way intercom, prerecorded deterrent messages, 100+ decibel siren, and light(s).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Free Shipping&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;1-Year Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Free 2-Hour Look Back&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Voice Control with Alexa&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;TECHNICAL SPECS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Full-color HD video for accurate recordings and playback, even at night.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;720p HD camera with 116° diagonal field of view.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;100 dB siren &amp;amp; high-fidelity speaker for clear.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microphone for high-quality two-way audio capture.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Advanced sensors to detect rapid change in motion instantly.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dusk-to-dawn light control and timer light mode.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Motion activated + dusk-to-dawn + turn on/off from your phone&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smart Socket&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Type: E26. Input: AC120V, 60Hz. USB Output: DC5V, 1A&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Security Camera&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Input Voltage: DC: 5V/1.0A&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weatherproof&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;IP44 Rating | Tested in -40F (-40C) and 131F (55C)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;REQUIREMENTS: (US &amp;amp; Canada ONLY)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wi-Fi and Bluetooth 4.0 for easy setup with iOS or Android devices.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Security Camera: DC:5V/1.0A&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smart Socket: AC120V, 60Hz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;iOS devices running iOS7 and above (iPhone 4S and above and iPads enabled with Bluetooth 4 capability)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Android devices supporting Bluetooth LE: 4.4 (Kit Kat) and above&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Internet connection required for both mobile device and location where Kuna Powered device is installed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Best performance with 2 Mbps upload and download speed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Kuna Powered devices run on 2.4GHz only&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible with any LED, CFL, or incandescent bulb up to 75W (not included)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;*(Light fixtures with compact-sized sockets are not supported)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EASY INSTALLATION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Install the Smart Socket&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIf you can change a lightbulb, you can install a Toucan Surveillance Kit! Connect camera to USB adaptor, just replace your old light fixture with Kuna.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Connect Camera to Smart Socket via USB&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nToucan efficiently uses live power from your house, allowing us to provide you with advanced features not previously possible when relying on existing powered devices.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Download App &amp;amp; Pair&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nUse the free Kuna app to connect the Smart Socket and Camera via Bluetooth and WI-FI. It’s that easy.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Toucan Surveillance Kit, Security Camera with Alarm, Motion Detection', 'Toucan Surveillance Kit, Security Camera with Alarm, Motion Detection', 'Toucan Surveillance Kit, Security Camera with Alarm, Motion Detection'),
(10426, 1, 'Rawlings Pro Preferred 11.25 in Infield Glove', '&lt;p&gt;This Pro Preferred 11 1/4” baseball glove from Rawlings features the PRO I Web pattern, which is desired by infielders and positions that require players to use two hands to scoop the ball. The Pro Preferred Series is made with soft, durable Kipskin Leather for easy break-in, laces pretested to 100lb tensile strength and deerskin lining that provides comfort, fit, and durability. The Conventional back on this pattern is designed with an additional break point which allows it to be squeezed easier. This is the same pattern worn by Jose Reyes.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DETAILS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Age: Adult&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Map: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sport: Baseball&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Size: 11.25 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Camel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hand: Right&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Back: Conventional&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Player Break-In: 70&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fit: Pro&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Level: Adult&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lining: Pittards Sheep Skin&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Padding: 100% Wool Blend&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pattern: Pro&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Position: Infield&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Series: Pro Preferred&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shell: Kip Leather&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Type: Baseball&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Web: Pro I&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Rawlings Pro Preferred 11.25 in Infield Glove', 'Pro Preferred 11.25 in Infield Glove', 'Rawlings Pro Preferred 11.25 in Infield Glove'),
(10425, 1, 'Rawlings Heart of the Hide Blem 11.25 in Infield Glove', '&lt;p&gt;This Jose Reyes Game Day Heart of the Hide baseball glove features the PRO I Web pattern, which is a single post reinforced bottom web that conforms to a smaller lighter web pattern desired by infielders, this allows you to better shape the pocket. With its 11 1/4&quot; pattern, this glove features a flat, shallow pocket which allows fielders to get the ball out of the glove quickly. It works best for 2nd Base or Shortstop positions. Handcrafted from the top 5% of steer hides and the best pro grade lace, the Heart of the Hide gloves durability remains unmatched. This glove is made to the exact specifications of the game day glove worn by Gold Glove Award Winner Jose Reyes. B Grade Glove&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DETAILS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Age: Adult&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Map: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sport: Baseball&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Size: 11.25 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Black&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hand: Right&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Back: Conventional&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Player Break-In: 70&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fit: Pro&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Level: Adult&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lining: Deer-Tanned Cowhide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Padding: Moldable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pattern: Pro&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Position: Infield&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shell: Steer Hide Leather&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Type: Baseball&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Web: Pro I&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Worn By: Jose Reyes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Rawlings Heart of the Hide Blem 11.25 in Infield Glove', 'Rawlings Heart of the Hide Blem 11.25 in Infield Glove', 'Rawlings Heart of the Hide Blem 11.25 in Infield Glove'),
(10427, 1, 'Rawlings Pro Preferred Blem 11.25 in Infield Glove', '&lt;p&gt;This Blem Pro Preferred 11 1/4” baseball glove features the PRO I Web pattern, which is desired by infielders and positions that require players to use two hands to scoop the ball. Utilizing the best patterns from the best pro players, Pro Preferred™ gloves feature impeccable kip skin leather that breaks in to specific playing preferences, forming the perfect pocket. The high-performance sheepskin lining wicks moisture away, keeping the hand dry for better control when players need it most.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DETAILS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Age: Adult&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Map: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sport: Baseball&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Size: 11.25 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Black&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hand: Right&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Back: Conventional&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Player Break-In: 70&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fit: Pro&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Level: Adult&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lining: Pittards Sheep Skin&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pattern: Pro&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Position: Infield&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Series: Pro Preferred&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shell: Kip Leather&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Type: Baseball&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Web: Pro I&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Rawlings Pro Preferred Blem 11.25 in Infield Glove', 'Rawlings Pro Preferred Blem 11.25 in Infield Glove', 'Rawlings Pro Preferred Blem 11.25 in Infield Glove'),
(10428, 1, 'ALLie 360 Degree Camera with 24/7 Live Streaming, Monitoring, Cloud', '&lt;p&gt;The ALLie camera is a dual lens 360-degree camera that allows you to navigate across and around your home in immersive video without blind spots or ever missing a thing. You can even tell what\'s going on when the room is dark, thanks to ALLie\'s 10 built-in infrared LEDs.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The ALLie camera connects to your Wi-Fi network to let you monitor live or recorded video from anywhere, using your smartphone or tablet. Zoom and pan using the ALLie mobile app to look around your room, even when you\'re at work or away on business. You can navigate around the image by swiping your finger across the screen. If your device has gyroscopic motion sensors, you can just tilt and move the screen around to change what you\'re seeing. A built-in microphone and speaker allow two-way talk. A variety of cloud-based storage plans are available if you want to increase the amount of video you save.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S INCLUDED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ALLie 360 Degree Camera with 24/7 Live Streaming, Monitoring, Cloud Recording&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;9v (1Amp) PSU with 10ft lead&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;USB Cable for Setup Purposes on PC or Mac&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Printed Instruction Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mounting Hardware&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Field of View: 360x360, no blind spots&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Optical Configuration: 2 x fisheye lens, back-to-back, reliable, no moving parts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Each Lens: All glass, FOV=200 degrees, F#=2.8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Image Sensor: 2 x OV10823 Type 1/2.6’’, 10.5Megapixel, CMOS Effective Pixels 4320x2432&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Resolution &amp;amp; FPS in Away Mode (cloud): 2048x2048@20fps per sensor (8MP total)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Resolution &amp;amp; FPS in Home Mode: 2448x2448@20fps per sensor (12MP total)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Image Signal Processing: Auto White Balance, Auto Gain, Noise Reduction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Platform/Processor: Qualcomm Snapdragon 800&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Video Compression: H.264&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bitrate: 2-4 Mbit/s for Away Mode (cloud) and 3-8 Mbit/s for Home Mode&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Equalrectangular Resolution: 4096x2048&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;IR Illumination: 10 x IR LEDs internal&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microphone: Built-in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Audio Compression: 16-64Kbps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;WiFi: 802.11ac/n/b/g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bluetooth: BLE, used for set-up of camera&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Local Storage: Recordings stored on your mobile device&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cloud Recording: 24 hrs: $6.95 (FREE for the first year), 48hrs: $9.95, 72hrs: $12.95&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Custom plans are available&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Supply: 9VDC&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Consumption: Max 7.5W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mount: Wall or ceiling mount ring&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Size: Approximately 3”x3”x3.5”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 10 oz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Working Environment: For indoor use only&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;*Power supply for all purchases comes with Type A plug top (e.g. 2 x Blade design).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'ALLie 360 Degree Camera with 24/7 Live Streaming, Monitoring, Cloud', 'ALLie 360 Degree Camera with 24/7 Live Streaming, Monitoring, Cloud', 'ALLie 360 Degree Camera with 24/7 Live Streaming, Monitoring, Cloud'),
(10429, 1, 'Sonos PLAY:1 Compact Wireless Smart Speaker for Streaming Music', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PLEASE NOTE: WE DON\'T SHIP TO CALIFORNIA&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;ALASKA AND HAWAII, P.O. BOX OR APO/FPO/DPO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SONOS PLAY:1. MINI SPEAKER. MIGHTY SOUND.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe most compact Sonos speaker. A perfect fit for bookshelves, counters, and other snug places. PLAY:1 lets you enjoy great-sounding music wherever you want to listen.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Surprisingly Powerful: PLAY:1 sounds a lot bigger than it looks, thanks to two Class-D amplifiers and custom-built drivers, all meticulously tuned to the speaker’s unique acoustic architecture.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Trueplay Speaker Tuning: This exclusive Sonos feature fine-tunes your PLAY:1 to make sure you get the very best sound in any room, no matter where you place it.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Humidity Resistant: Enjoy your favorite songs in music-starved places like bathrooms and outdoor patios.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stereo Pair With Another PLAY:1: Turn each speaker into separate left and right channels for wider, bigger and deeper stereo sound.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Home Theater Rears: Add a pair or PLAY:1 speakers to PLAYBAR and SUB for an epic surround sound experience.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Simple setup. Better over time.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPut your speaker wherever you want. Plug it in. Tap the free Sonos app – it connects to your home WiFi and you’re ready to rock.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nRegular, ongoing software updates bring new features and services to your PLAY:1. So the longer you own it, the better it gets.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WiFi, not Bluetooth&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith Sonos, the songs stream from your WiFi network (not your phone), so there\'s never any of the dropouts, delays or interruptions associated with Bluetooth.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Multi-room music&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOne room of streaming music is great. But a house full is even better. Fill more rooms with music by simply adding more Sonos speakers. They all work together seamlessly so you can play different songs in different rooms or the same song everywhere.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rekindle your love for music&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSonos makes it easy to bring music back into your life. Enjoy old favorites or discover something new. With Sonos, music wakes you in the morning, surrounds you all day, and fills every moment with the full body joy of listening out loud.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;All the music on earth&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSonos plays everything - the most popular streaming services, on-demand Internet radio, your favorite podcasts and audiobooks, your go-to collection of downloads - whatever you love to listen to. Access all the music on earth through the Sonos app, or control Sonos directly from the Spotify app.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;One app. Complete music control.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nChoose what to play, where to play it, and how loud. In one room or all over your home. Track down songs across all your music services with a single search. Create playlists in an instant. The Sonos app does it all.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAudio&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two Class-D digital amplifiers perfectly tuned to match the speaker drivers and acoustic architecture.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One tweeter creates a crisp and clear high-frequency response.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One mid-woofer ensures you’ll hear the faithful playback of mid-range vocal frequencies plus deep, rich bass.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable bass and treble controls let you customize your sound by individual room or groups of rooms.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Physical&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions - H x W x D: 6.36 x 4.69 x 4.69 in. (161.45 x 119.7 x 119.7 mm).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 4.08 lbs. (1.85 kg).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product finish: White with light metallic grille; black with graphite grille.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Top-panel buttons &amp;amp; lights: Volume and Play/Pause buttons. LED indicates Sonos component status and mute status.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Threaded mount: 1/4 in. (6.35 mm) / 20-threaded mounting socket. Works with standard wall mounts and speaker stands.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Sonos PLAY:1 Compact Wireless Smart Speaker for Streaming Music', 'Sonos PLAY:1 Compact Wireless Smart Speaker for Streaming Music', ''),
(10431, 1, 'Kamp-Rite Double Kwik-Cot', '&lt;p&gt;The Kamp-Rite® Double Kwik Cot is the two-person version in Kamp-Rite® ’s line of compact, convenient and comfortable cots. The unique design offers sturdy support, delivering a comfortable night’s sleep within minutes. Extremely versatile, the Kamp-Rite® Double Kwik Cot serves double duty as both an indoor and outdoor sleeping cot. The compact size requires minimal storage space and the quick, easy set up offers an ideal solution to overnight guests when a “spare bed” is needed at a moment’s notice anywhere, anytime.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy duty, powder-coated frame&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy duty 600 D fabric base&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mesh storage hammock underneath cot&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Padded head section&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Setup: 85″L x 55″W x 19″H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bed: 85″L x 55″W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 33 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity: 500 lbs (total)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded: 42″L x 11″W x 11″H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shipping: 42″L x 11″W x 11″H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;STANDARD INCLUSIONS:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy Duty 600 D Carry Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MEDIA:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Instructions: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=3&amp;amp;v=whFnbh6JfBM&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=3&amp;amp;v=whFnbh6JfBM&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Kamp-Rite: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1RnRM5YXPcWaYoNju79sRQ&quot;&gt;https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1RnRM5YXPcWaYoNju79sRQ&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Kamp-Rite Double Kwik-Cot', 'Kamp-Rite Double Kwik-Cot', 'Kamp-Rite Double Kwik-Cot'),
(10430, 1, 'Air Oasis 1000 G3 - Small Tower Air Purifier', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AIR OASIS 1000 G3 - SMALL TOWER AIR PURIFIER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Perfect for the home or office, the Air Oasis 1000 G3 is a compact and powerful photocatalytic air purifier that can quietly reduce carbon-based contaminants. You and your loved ones can breathe easier without having to deal with clunky design, constant noise, or expensive air filter replacement.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Low Maintenance, High Performance: &lt;/strong&gt;This easy-to-use filtration system simply turns on or off: There are no complicated settings to learn, filters to change, or maintenance tasks to perform. An audible alarm will indicate when the AHPCO (advanced hydrated photocatalytic oxidation) cell needs to be replaced (about once every three years). Originally developed by NASA, AHPCO technology has revolutionized the air filtration industry. In many cases, it performs better and more efficiently than a HEPA system, and you won’t need to regularly replace expensive filters. The audible alarm beeps when the lamp completely burns out, but the AHPCO cell should be replaced every two years for optimal performance, since it drops below 80% output after two years.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cutting-Edge Technologies: &lt;/strong&gt;In addition to using Bi-Polar® Ionization and an AHPCO catalyst, the Air Oasis 1000 G3 also includes our LongLife™ technology. Because of this specialty coating on our UVC lamps, the output of our lamps is far higher than the industry standard. Many lamps maintain 65% of their output at 9,000 hours, whereas ours will maintain up to 80% of their output at 16,000 hours. At only 14 inches high, this small air purifier has&lt;br /&gt;\r\na coverage area of up to 1,000 square feet.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Improved Indoor Air Quality:&lt;/strong&gt; The whisper-quiet operation of this tower air purifier can eliminate odors from smoke, food, cleaning chemicals, mold, and pets and reduce carbon-based contaminants. Common carbon-based contaminants include bacteria, viruses, and molds. In addition, the photocatalytic air purifier can also reduce smoke, odor-causing volatile organic compounds (or VOCs), and other allergens.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Durable Design:&lt;/strong&gt; Perfect for bedrooms, bathrooms, nurseries, living rooms, and offices, this five-pound tower air purifier can be placed on any desk, dresser, or counter. The Air Oasis 1000 G3 has internal metal components, a thick brushed-metal housing (not a faux finish), and a three-year warranty. Meeting domestic and international standards, this durable product also comes with a 12-volt DC wall adapter and a six-foot cord. It’s entirely made within the U.S.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional Benefits: &lt;/strong&gt;Whether you’re looking to buy the Air Oasis 1000 G3 for commercial or residential purposes, know that the system, in addition to being powerful, is also energy-efficient. Competing purifiers often use 100 watts of energy or more, whereas the Air Oasis 1000 G3 uses less energy than a 45-watt light bulb. You can both breathe easier and go green!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How It Works:&lt;/strong&gt; Without high-powered fans or thick filters, this non filtration system uses a lamp that destroys germs with UV light. That light is reflected with the AHPCO catalyst, which produces catalytic molecules, which then, in turn, seek out and destroy carbon-based molecules. This powerful small air purifier cleans the air quickly, efficiently, and without using too much energy. We added our Bi-Polar® technology to further enhance the effectiveness of our countertop purifiers.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Simple Operation:&lt;/strong&gt; The Air Oasis 1000 G3 is simple to operate. The device turns on with the flip of a single switch. There are no complicated multiple settings to learn.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Durable Construction:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1/8″ thick brushed metal housing, not a faux finish&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Internal metal components ensure long term use&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Virtually Maintenance Free:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No routine maintenance to perform&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No filters to change or clean&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Audible alarm indicates when it’s time to replace the AHPCO Cell&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(AHPCO Cell only needs replacing every three years)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Power Source:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;12VDC wall adapter (can be used overseas)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Meets domestic and international standards&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electrical: 12VDC 15 Watts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cord: 6 foot cord, Meets domestic and international standards.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Airflow: 11 CFM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ozone Levels: Less than .04 ppm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Positive &amp;amp; Negative ion concentration: 20,000,000/cm³&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Coverage: 1000 sq. ft.* (* Multiple units may be needed in areas of higher contamination)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Settings: ON/OFF&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Materials: Aluminum and polymers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Working Temp: 0°F – 122°F&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 3 year limited warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Country of Origin: &lt;strong&gt;Made in the USA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Dimensions: 19″ x 7″ x 5″&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 6 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Air Oasis 1000 G3 - Small Tower Air Purifier', 'Air Oasis 1000 G3 - Small Tower Air Purifier', 'Air Oasis 1000 G3 - Small Tower Air Purifier'),
(10432, 1, 'Kamp-Rite Oversize Tent Cot', '&lt;p&gt;The Kamp-Rite® Oversize Tent Cot stands 11” above the ground and brings additional comfort with its expanded sleeping area. The Oversize Tent Cot is wider and longer than the Original Tent Cot and adds a domed top to create more head room and interior space. This off-the-ground sleep shelter ensures superior protection from the elements and delivers a level of comfort and convenience not usually found in traditional, old style camping gear.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The sturdy cot base includes two additional support legs located at each end of the Tent Cot for extra stability. Extremely versatile, the unique hinge design enables the Oversize Tent Cot to be converted to a lounge chair for daytime relaxation or a standard style cot for sleeping under the stars.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Oversize Tent Cot sets up in mere minutes and comes complete with a waterproof Kamp-Rite® Rain Fly and a convenient Carry Bag.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy duty 190T Nylon&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No-See-Um Mesh on all windows and doors&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Elevated cot base for off-the-ground comfort&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy duty, powder-coated aluminum steel frame&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy use, corrosion-resistant zippers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unique multi-function hinge design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Converts to a lounge chair or cot&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Superior quality clips and buckles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Interior storage pouches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick, easy set up&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight rating recommendation of 350 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT SPECIFICATIONS:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Setup: 90″L x 32″W x 47″H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bed: 90″L x 32″W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tent: 90″L x 32″W x 36″H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 32 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity: 350 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded: 36″L x 34″W x 7″H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shipping: 36″L x 36″W x 7″H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;STANDARD INCLUSIONS:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy Duty 600D Carry Bag [CB401]&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fitted Waterproof Rain Fly [RF402]&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Kamp-Rite Oversize Tent Cot', 'Kamp-Rite Oversize Tent Cot', 'Kamp-Rite Oversize Tent Cot'),
(10433, 1, 'Kamp-Rite Double Tent Cot', '&lt;p&gt;Kamp-Rite®’s Double Tent Cot is the two-person version in the line of Tent Cot products. The sturdy aluminum frame keeps you 11” above the ground to provide comfort and protection from insects, rocks and dampness.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The fully enclosed Double Tent Cot creates a private sleep shelter and brings a level of convenience to outdoor outings not typically found with old style camping gear. The quick, easy set up can be done alone without the help of an extra pair of hands, making it the ideal solution to get out and enjoy the Great Outdoors more often and more comfortably.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Double Tent Cot’s unique hinge design creates great versatility and function—it can be easily converted into a lounge chair or a standard style cot for use in larger, family-style tents.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy duty 190T Nylon&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No-See-Um Mesh on all windows and doors&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Elevated cot base for off-the-ground comfort&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy duty powder-coated aluminum frame&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy use, corrosion-resistant zippers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unique, multi-function hinge design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Converts to a lounge chair or cot&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Superior quality clips and buckles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Interior storage pouches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick, easy set up&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT SPECIFICATIONS:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Setup: 84″L x 53″W x 51″H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bed: 84″L x 53″W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tent: 84″L x 53″W x 40″H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 51 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity: 500 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded: 56″L x 34″W x 8″H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shipping: 56″L x 34″W x 8″H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n