(10435, 1, 'SOEKS 2-in-1 Radiation Detector and Nitrate Tester for Food ECOTESTER', '&lt;p&gt;Accurate, down to micro-Sieverts (uSv) personal radiation meters usually very expensive but we offer Personal Radiation and Food Testing Meter that offers high accuracy at a more affordable price Ecotester 2-in-1 Radiation Detector &amp;amp; Nitrate Food Tester. For a concerned consumer it is the most reliable and easy way to monitor radiation exposure as well as the useful tool that help to eliminate foods that contain elevated levels of chemical contamination from your diet.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;EcoTester SOEKS measures Radiation Exposure and provides real-time readings of Gamma and Beta ionized Radiation - the kind of radiation which is harmful to humans health, damages DNA and causes cancer.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Device can be run 24/7 through USB cable and work as Geiger Counter early warning device, monitoring radiation background and alerting you via audio and visual alarms about increasing levels of radiation in environment. To help you verify quality of the foods.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;EcoTester has an application of a Nitrate Tester. The metal probe can be inserted in produce, fruit and meats as well as in processed meat to check on Nitrates and Sodium Nitrate levels or Potassium Nitrates and Nitrites, which food companies put in cured meat to preserve its color, preventing fats from going rancid and avert bacteria from growing. Foods that were exposed to synthetic pesticides, chemical preservatives or rodent poisons will show very high nitrate levels, indicating you might want to avoid them. Organically grown products potentially will show the decreased level of Nitrates (depending on the grower) Babies are extremely vulnerable to Nitrate exposure which can be a cause of Blue Baby Syndrome. Vegan, Vegetarians, Raw foodists alike and individuals with wide variety of medical conditions, including food allergies, asthma, hepatitis, and gallstones, low stomach acid also can be highly sensitive to the effects of nitrate.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ecotester 2-in-1 Radiation Detector &amp;amp; Nitrate Food Tester has a list of&amp;nbsp; food items commonly consumed and alerts you via visual and audio messages about exceeded levels of Nitrates so you can make an informed decision whether to consume the product or not.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;127 points of measurement&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Geiger Muller Tube&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measures Gamma Beta X Ray ionized Radiation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Range of indicated Nitrate content, mg/kg from 20 to 5000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Range of indicated background radiation level, mcSv/h from 0,03 to 1 000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Range of Indicated Background Radiation mcR/h from 3 to 100 000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Registered Gamma Radiation Energy from 0,1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Readings up to 20 seconds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The numerical and graphic form of representation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bright, informative color TFT the display 128x160&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charging and delivery of energy for continuous&amp;nbsp; running via mini-usb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Simple management&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measuring error no more than 30%&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Continuous work for 10 hours&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Visual and Audible Alarms&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product size: 5&quot; 5/8 x 1&quot; 7/8 x 3/4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product weight: 2.5 oz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S INCLUDED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EcoTester 2 in 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manual with Warranty Certificate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 AAA Alkaline Batteries&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 Year Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'SOEKS 2-in-1 Radiation Detector and Nitrate Tester for Food ECOTESTER', 'SOEKS 2-in-1 Radiation Detector and Nitrate Tester for Food ECOTESTER', 'SOEKS 2-in-1 Radiation Detector and Nitrate Tester for Food ECOTESTER'),
(10436, 1, 'SOEKS Professional Radiation Detector Dosimeter QUANTUM', '&lt;p&gt;Geiger Counter Quantum by SOEKS is intended to accumulate, store, alert and display cumulative dose of the radiation exposure.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Quantum is the highly reliable personal radiation dosimeter and radiation detector for precise dose and dose rate measurement. This pocket size Geiger Counter is able to run continuously, up to 700 hours, monitor the radiation environment and store cumulative dose of up to 999 days.&amp;nbsp; Easy to use device has Radiation Dose and Dose Rate thresholds and whenever thresholds are triggered Geiger Counter will produce an Audio, Visual and Text alarm message.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Geiger Counter Quantum is designed to work in the wide range of radiation safety applications and can be used successfully to&amp;nbsp; determine radioactive contamination and radioactive sources of Gamma and Beta and X-Ray Radiation by security service and customs, control services, first responders, personnel who\'s&amp;nbsp; solving problems of local radiation sources or single objects contaminated by ionized radiation (for example, to check on radioactive contamination of scrap, banknotes, stones, antiques, etc.)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;To access historical data (up to 999 days) of the radiation exposure, readings can be uploaded to SOEKS Device Manager Software via included USB.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Distinctive features of the device - the quick and reliable identification of any source of ionized radiation, accumulation of data and display of cumulative dose, make Quantum by SOEKS a complete multifunctional tool able to address concerns and solve problems of radiation awareness and control and ensure radiation safety.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;General public, radiation safety and security specialists, health physicists are among common users.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&