(10461, 1, 'Graco Nautilus 65 LX 3-in-1 Car Seat', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NAUTILUS™ 65 LX 3-IN-1 CAR SEAT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-in-1 harness booster helps protect your child, from toddler to youth&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Harness Booster (22 – 65 lb), highback booster (30 – 100 lb), and backless booster (40 – 120 lb)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Simply Safe Adjust™ Harness System headrest and harness adjust together&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Be sure to check your local and state laws, as well as AAP and NHTSA recommendations, for car seat usage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engineered &amp;amp; crash tested to meet or exceed US standard FMVSS 213&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DETAILS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGraco’s top-rated Nautilus™ 65 LX 3-in-1 harness booster goes the distance, from toddler to youth, to help keep your growing child safe. It secures your child in a 5-point harness from 22-65 lb, converts to a belt-positioning booster from 30-100 lb, and becomes a backless booster seat from 40-120 lb. Its Simply Safe Adjust™ Harness System allows you to adjust the harness and headrest together, with no rethreading. You’ll appreciate the ease of the fuss-free harness, for easy in and out, while your travel partner enjoys the comfy body insert, personal cup holder and storage compartment.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-in-1 harness booster helps protect your child, from toddler to youth&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Harness Booster (22 – 65 lb), highback booster (30 – 100 lb), and backless booster (40 – 120 lb)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Simply Safe Adjust™ Harness System headrest and harness adjust together&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Be sure to check your local and state laws, as well as AAP and NHTSA recommendations, for car seat usage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engineered &amp;amp; crash tested to meet or exceed US standard FMVSS 213&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Keeps your child in a booster longer - up to 120 lb.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuss Free harness storage to get baby in and out easily&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable body support helps keep your child comfy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steel-reinforced frame provides strength and durability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-position recline helps keep your growing child comfy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rigorously crash tested to meet or exceed U.S. safety standards&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Side Impact Tested* *In addition to meeting or exceeding all applicable US safety standards, the Nautilus™ 65 has been side impact tested for occupant retention solely with the built-in 5-point harness system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One-hand, 5-position adjustable headrest easily adapts for your growing child&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EPS, energy absorbing foam for effective impact management&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Depth: 18 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Width Outside: 20 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Height: 28 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Weight Without Base: 20.52 lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Limited Warranty: One year by Graco®&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CARE AND MAINTENANCE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Machine-washable seat cushion&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Metal and plastic parts may be cleaned with mild soap and cool water&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Buckle may be cleaned with a damp cloth&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Harness straps may be spot cleaned&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://s7d2.scene7.com/is/content/Newellsync/116438&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DOWNLOAD PRODUCT INSTRUCTIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Graco Nautilus 65 LX 3-in-1 Car Seat', 'Graco Nautilus 65 LX 3-in-1 Car Seat', 'Graco Nautilus 65 LX 3-in-1 Car Seat'),
(10462, 1, 'Graco Aire3 Click Connect Travel System', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AIRE3™ CLICK CONNECT™ TRAVEL SYSTEM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes the Graco SnugRide Click Connect 35 Infant Car Seat and base&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One-second, one-hand fold &amp;amp; carrying strap for convenience&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto-lock &amp;amp; self-standing fold for easy storage &amp;amp; portability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ultra-light stroller weighs less than 21 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi-position seat reclines flat to create an infant carriage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DETAILS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGraco\'s Aire3 Click Connect Travel System is designed to make it extra-easy for you to explore with baby. The sleek, lightweight stroller weighs less than 21 lbs. so its easy to lift. and carry, and the 3-wheel design is easy to maneuver. It folds with one hand and automatically stands for simple storage. The multi-position, flat-reclining seat is comfortable as your child grows. A parents tray with zippered storage and two cup holders, and an extra-large storage basket makes strolling more convenient for mom. It also includes the best-selling Graco SnugRide Click Connect 35 Infant Car Seat and base.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Parent\'s tray with storage &amp;amp; extra-large storage basket&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable armrest bar with cup holder for easy in &amp;amp; out&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-wheel design with locking front-swivel for added maneuverability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Holds a child up to 50 lbs. for longevity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra-large canopy with zippered extension panel provides maximum coverage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Convertible 3- or 5-point harness grows with your child&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Weight With Base: 13.82 lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Depth: 30.67 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Width Outside: 18.66 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Height: 15.59 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Depth: 17 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Weight: 21 lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Width: 34.5 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Height: 41 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Rear Wheel Size: 9.5 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Front Wheel Size: 6.25 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Weight Without Base: 7.5 lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Width Inside: 11.75 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DOWNLOAD: &lt;a href=&quot;http://s7d2.scene7.com/is/content/Newellsync/108081&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;PRODUCT INSTRUCTIONS &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CARE AND MAINTENANCE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ICS: Wash removable seat cushion in cold water on delicate cycle and line dry&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller: To clean stroller frame and seat pad, spot clean using mild soap and warm water&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Never use bleach&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Use light oil if wheels squeak&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RECOMMENDED USE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller: Holds a child up to 50 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Infant Car Seat: Rear facing only from 4-35 lbs., up to 32&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WARRANTY:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOne year by Graco®. This limited warranty does not cover claims resulting from misuse, failure to follow the instructions on installation, maintenance and use, abuse, alteration, involvement in an accident, and normal wear and tear.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Graco Aire3 Click Connect Travel System', 'Graco Aire3™ Click Connect™ Travel System', 'Graco Aire3™ Click Connect™ Travel System'),
(10463, 1, 'Graco FastAction Fold Sport Click Connect Travel System', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FASTACTION™ FOLD SPORT CLICK CONNECT™ TRAVEL SYSTEM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes the Graco SnugRide® Click Connect™ 35 Infant Car Seat and base&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One-second fold&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lightweight, sturdy frame&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller holds child up to 50 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi-position reclining seat for baby\'s comfort&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DETAILS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nExperience Graco\'s new three-wheel travel system featuring a unique, one-second fold. This lightweight stroller not only features a fast fold, but it also has a multi-position reclining seat, expandable canopy and an extra-large, expandable storage basket. It also includes the SnugRide Click Connect 35 Infant Car Seat and base, one of America\'s #1 selling infant car seats&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Three-wheel design with a locking front swivel for added maneuverability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra-large, expandable canopy with peek-a-boo window keeps your child shaded&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra-large storage basket with expandable rear-pouch to hold all your travel essentials&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Parent’s tray with storage &amp;amp; 2 deep cup holders for on-the-go convenience&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Child’s tray with cup holder pivots or removes for no-fuss stroller entry&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Convertible 3 or 5-point harness grows with your child&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Weight With Base: 13.82 lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Depth: 30.67 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Width Outside: 18.66 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Height: 15.59 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Depth: 40 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Weight: 21.38 lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Width: 25 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Height: 42 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Rear Wheel Size: 8.5 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Front Wheel Size: 7.5 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded Depth: 16 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded Height: 28 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded Width: 25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Weight Without Base: 7.5 lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Width Inside: 11.75 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DOWNLOAD:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://s7d2.scene7.com/is/content/Newellsync/116837&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;PRODUCT INSTRUCTIONS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CARE AND MAINTENANCE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nICS: Wash removable seat cushion in cold water on delicate cycle and line dry&lt;br /&gt;\r\nStroller: To clean stroller frame and seat pad, spot clean using mild soap and warm water&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNever Use Bleach. Use light oil if wheels squeak&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RECOMMENDED USE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nStroller: For child up to 50 lbs. Infant Car Seat: The FastAction™ Fold Sport Click Connect™ Travel System comes with either a SnugRide® Click Connect™ 30 or SnugRide® Click Connect™ 35 Infant Car Seat, depending on model. Check product features to determine which car seat is included. If Travel System includes a SnugRide Click Connect 30 Infant Car Seat, these are the car seat usage recommendations: Rear-facing for infants from 4 - 30 lbs. and up to 30&quot; If Travel System includes a SnugRide Click Connect 35 Infant Car Seat, these are the car seat usage recommendations: Rear-facing for infants from 4 – 35 lbs. and up to 32&quot;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WARRANTY:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOne year by Graco®. This limited warranty does not cover claims resulting from misuse, failure to follow the instructions on installation, maintenance and use, abuse, alteration, involvement in an accident, and normal wear and tear.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Graco FastAction Fold Sport Click Connect Travel System', 'Graco FastAction Fold Sport Click Connect Travel System', 'Graco FastAction Fold Sport Click Connect Travel System'),
(10460, 1, 'Graco FastAction Fold Jogger Click Connect Travel System', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FASTACTION™ FOLD JOGGER CLICK CONNECT™ TRAVEL SYSTEM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes the Graco SnugRide Click Connect 35 Infant Car Seat and base, rear facing for infants from 4-35lbs. and up to 32&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One-second, one-hand fold has an automatic storage lock and is self-standing when folded&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Air-filled rubber tires offer suspension&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Locking front swivel wheel provides an easy transition from daily strolling to jogging&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi-position reclining seat for baby\'s comfort&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DETAILS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGraco\'s first jogger is the ultimate crossover stroller, combining all the comfort &amp;amp; convenience features of a traditional stroller with the performance &amp;amp; maneuverability of an all-terrain jogger. This stroller is loaded with innovative features like the one-second, one-hand FastAction fold bringing the ultimate in convenience to a jogger. Click Connect technology allows for a one-step, secure connection of infant car seat to stroller.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Deluxe parent\'s tray features a unique smartphone cradle for your phone or MP3 player, 2 deep cup holders and a covered storage compartment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra-large, expandable canopy with peek-a-boo window keeps your child shaded&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra-large storage basket to hold all your essentials&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Reflectors for added low-light visibility&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Child\'s tray with cup holder pivots or removes for no-fuss stroller entry&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Convertible 3 or 5-point harness grows with your child&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Weight With Base: 14.17 lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Depth: 30.67 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Width Outside: 18.66 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Height: 15.59 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Depth: 40 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Weight: 31.99 lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Seat Width: 12 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Seat Depth: 14 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Width: 24 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Height: 42 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Seat Height: 21 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Rear Wheel Size: 16.0 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller Front Wheel Size: 11.0 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Weight Without Base: 7.5 lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Width Inside: 11.75 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Limited Warranty: One year by Graco®&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CARE AND MAINTENANCE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ICS: Wash removable seat cushion in cold water on delicate cycle and line dry&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroller: To clean stroller frame and seat pad, spot clean using mild soap and warm water&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Never Use Bleach. Use light oil if wheels squeak&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RECOMMENDED USE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nStroller: For child up to 50 lbs. Car Seat: Rear-facing for infants from 4 – 35 lbs. and up to 32&quot;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WARRANTY:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOne year by Graco®. This limited warranty does not cover claims resulting from misuse, failure to follow the instructions on installation, maintenance and use, abuse, alteration, involvement in an accident, and normal wear and tear.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;DOWNLOAD:&lt;a href=&quot;http://s7d2.scene7.com/is/content/Newellsync/116410&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;PRODUCT INSTRUCTIONS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Graco FastAction™ Fold Jogger Click Connect™ Travel System', 'Graco FastAction™ Fold Jogger Click Connect™ Travel System', 'Graco FastAction™ Fold Jogger Click Connect™ Travel System'),
(10464, 1, 'Graco Milestone All-in-1 Car Seat', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MILESTONE™ ALL-IN-1 CAR SEAT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-in-1 seat grows with your child from 5-100 lbs., rear- to forward-facing and becomes a belt-positioning booster&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Simply Safe Adjust™ Harness System is safe &amp;amp; simple.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4-position recline helps keep your growing child comfy, in rear- and forward-facing modes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;InRight™ LATCH system for an easy, one-second LATCH attachment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Side-impact tested* *In addition to meeting or exceeding all applicable US safety standards, the Milestone car seat has been side impact tested for occupant retention solely with the built-in 5-point harness system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DETAILS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGraco\'s® Milestone™ All-in-1 Car Seat grows with your child. It’s three seats in one, for comfort at every stage! It’s a rear-facing (5–40 lbs.) and a forward-facing (22–65 lbs.) car seat, and belt-positioning booster (30-100 lbs.). Thanks to the Simply Safe Adjust™ Harness System, you’ll adjust the harness and headrest together, for an always-right fit. The 4-position recline keeps your child comfortable, while the InRight™ LATCH system makes installation easy with a one-second attachment. The seat is side-impact tested and SafeSeat Engineered, giving you peace of mind. With loads of safety features, Milestone is an obvious car seat choice!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engineered &amp;amp; crash tested to meet or exceed US standard FMVSS 213&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Washable seat cover is easy to access without removing the harness&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steel-reinforced frame provides strength and durability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Integrated harness storage compartment holds unused harness straps while in the belt positioning booster mode&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Plush inserts keep your child comfortable and are removable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EPS, energy absorbing foam for effective impact energy management&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;A removable cupholder keeps your child\'s drink close at hand&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Weight With Base: 19.4 lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Depth: 24 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Width Outside: 17 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Car Seat Height: 18.88 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DOWNLOAD&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;a href=&quot;http://s7d2.scene7.com/is/content/Newellsync/116517&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;PRODUCT INSTRUCTIONS &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CARE AND MAINTENANCE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Machine-washable seat cushion&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Metal and plastic parts may be cleaned with mild soap &amp;amp; cool water&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Buckle may be cleaned with a damp cloth&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Harness straps may be spot cleaned&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RECOMMENDED USE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Rear-facing Harness Mode&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Weight: 5-40 lb&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Height: head must be at least 1&quot; below handle&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Forward-facing Harness Mode&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Weight: 20-65 lb&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Height: 27-49 inches&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. Highback Booster Mode&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Weight: 30-100 lb&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Height: 38-57 inches&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. STOP using this child restraint or base and throw it away 10 years after the date of manufacture. The American Academy of Pediatricians (AAP) and National Highway Safety Administration (NHTSA) recommend that children ride rear facing until the age of 2 or until they reach the maximum rear-facing height or weight rating for their seat, and when forward-facing, children should use the built-in harness system for as long as possible until they reach the maximum forward-facing weight or height for their car seat. After reaching the maximum forward-facing weight and height, they also recommend that children 4 feet 9 inches tall or under should ride in a belt-positioning booster seat. *Always remember to check your local or state laws regarding car seat usage.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WARRANTY:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOne year by Graco®. This limited warranty does not cover claims resulting from misuse, failure to follow the instructions on installation, maintenance and use, abuse, alteration, involvement in an accident, and normal wear and tear.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Graco Milestone All-in-1 Car Seat', 'Graco Milestone All-in-1 Car Seat', 'Graco Milestone All-in-1 Car Seat'),
(10467, 1, 'RIDGID 13 in. Thickness Corded Planer, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TYPES OF PRODUCTS WE CARRY:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSAVE UP TO 90% OFF WITH OUR FACTORY BLEMISHED OR CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://ankermart.com/image/data/TYPE-PRO.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 800px; height: 400px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The RIDGID 13 in. Corded Planer has a 120-Volt, 15 Amp motor that delivers 9000 RPM for maximum power and continuous operation. It features a 3-blade cutter head with quick-changing, dual-edge blades that are reversible and self-aligning for a smooth surface with minimal blemishes. The multiple depth features help you achieve your desired depth, and the 13 in. wide feed capacity is great for planing large stock.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Chip impeller dust removal system to effectively pull wood chips from the workpiece for improved cuts and a cleaner work area&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sure-cut carriage lock to lock the cutter head to help minimize snipe at the end of the workpiece&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Large infeed/outfeed table extensions for extra workpiece support to help eliminate snipe&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steel top with glides for extra wide area to easily stage your material for its next cut&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy-to-reach, adjustable, top-mounted handle with 1/16 in. per revolution precision&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sof-touch controls for improved comfort and grip&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ind-I-cut depth gauge for instantly measuring the cutting depth before each pass&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;8 adjustable repeat-a-cut depth stops to precisely plane multiple workpieces to consistent, desired thickness for repetitive tasks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum cut depth (in.) .125&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.) 25.7&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.) 20.9&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.) 15.6&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S INCLUDED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;R4330 Thickness planer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hex key&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Magnetic blade tool&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blade/tool storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth adjustment handwheel and knob&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dust hood&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dust hood knobs (2)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operator’s manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MORE INFORMATION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: RIDGID&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power: Corded&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Condition: Certified Pre-Owned&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1-Year Reconditioned Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Batteries Included: Batteries not Included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blowout: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'RIDGID 13 in. Thickness Corded Planer, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', 'RIDGID 13 in. Thickness Corded Planer, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', 'RIDGID 13 in. Thickness Corded Planer, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED'),
(10466, 1, 'RIDGID 15 Amp 10 in. Heavy-Duty Portable Table, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TYPES OF PRODUCTS WE CARRY:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSAVE UP TO 90% OFF WITH OUR FACTORY BLEMISHED OR CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://ankermart.com/image/data/TYPE-PRO.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 800px; height: 400px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This RIDGID 15 Amp 10 in. Heavy Duty Portable Table Saw with Stand is equipped with a 4000 RPM motor. It features an updated table saw utility vehicle that provides single-point release for simple 1-step setup and great job site portability. You can easily complete jobs with this saw\'s user-friendly onboard storage for your miter gauge, extra blades, rip fence and other accessories.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Durable for heavy duty projects&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;10 in. blade&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ability to rip through 4 in. x 4 in. material in a single pass for fast, accurate cuts.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Front and back clamping fence which features integrated T-slots that give ability to hold select accessories&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum cut depth of 2-1/4 in. at 45 Degrees and 3-1/2 in. at 90 Degrees for a variety of useful cuts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blade Diameter 10 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.) 29.93 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Cut Depth @ 90 Deg. 3.5 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Table Length (in.) 30.25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.) 50.2 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Table Width (in.) 21&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.) 23.15 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S INCLUDED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Table Saw&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stand Included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MORE INFORMATION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: RIDGID&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power: Corded&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Condition: Certified Pre-Owned&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1-Year Reconditioned Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Batteries Included: Batteries not Included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blowout: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'RIDGID 15 Amp 10 in. Heavy-Duty Portable Table, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', 'RIDGID 15 Amp 10 in. Heavy-Duty Portable Table, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', 'RIDGID 15 Amp 10 in. Heavy-Duty Portable Table, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED');
