(10465, 1, 'RIDGID GEN5X 18 Volt 5-Piece Combo Kit, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TYPES OF PRODUCTS WE CARRY:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSAVE UP TO 90% OFF WITH OUR FACTORY BLEMISHED OR CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://ankermart.com/image/data/TYPE-PRO.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 800px; height: 400px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;RIDGID GEN5X permanent magnet motors have been engineered to provide best-in-class power, performance and runtime, giving you the advantage on any jobsite. This recondition kit is powered by 4.0 hyper Lithium-Ion batteries that have 4X run time compared to standard Lithium-Ion batteries and an arsenal of features such as; two times longer life, triple protection electronics, best-in-class extreme weather performance and fuel gauge.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;GEN5X permanent magnet motors have been engineered to provide best-in-class power, performance and runtime&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;GEN5X hammer drill produces 780 in. lbs. of torque for demanding drilling and driving applications, unobstructed chuck light shines directly out of the chuck to eliminate shadows around the bit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;GEN5X impact driver drives various fasteners easily with an open frame motor that provides 2,000 in. lbs. of high end torque, 3-speed settings provide adjustable power and speed for the most demanding job as well as precision work&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;GEN5X circular saw powers through the cut every time with a best-in-class open frame motor for corded like performance and a 7-1/4 in. blade for maximum depth&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;GEN5X reciprocating saw delivers optimal cutting speed with 1-1/8 in. stroke length at 3,000 strokes per minute, on/off orbital action for wood demolition and metal cutting&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;GEN5X LED flashlight has a lifetime LED bulb, no need to change the bulb for the life of the flashlight&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;HAMMER DRILL&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Torque:&amp;nbsp; 780 in.-lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No Load Speeds:&amp;nbsp; 0-450/0-1,600 RPM; 0-7,200/0-25,600 BPM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Chuck:&amp;nbsp; 1/2 in. carbide locking jaws&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IMPACT DRIVER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Torque:&amp;nbsp; 2,000 in.-lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No Load Speeds:&amp;nbsp; 0-2,750 RPM; 0-3,200 IPM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CIRCULAR SAW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blade Size:&amp;nbsp; 7-1/4 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No Load Speed:&amp;nbsp; 3,700 RPM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RECIPROCATING SAW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stroke Length:&amp;nbsp; 1-1/8 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No Load Speed:&amp;nbsp; 0-3,000 SPM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LED FLASHLIGHT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity:&amp;nbsp; 4.0 Ah&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage:&amp;nbsp; 18V&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Features:&amp;nbsp; Up to 4X the runtime; Up to 4X longer life; Operates down to -4⁰F and up to 120⁰F&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CHARGER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatibility:&amp;nbsp; 9.6V - 18V&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Input:&amp;nbsp; 120V&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S INCLUDED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;RIDGID R8611503 Hammer Drill&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;R86035 Impact Driver&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;R8652 Circular Saw&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;R8642 Reciprocating Saw&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;R8693 LED Flashlight&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;R840095 Charger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(2) Lithium Batteries&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auxiliary Handle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(2) Bits&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Circular Saw Blade&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blade Wrench&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Reciprocating Saw Blade&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(3) Belt Hooks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operator\'s Manuals&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MORE INFORMATION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: RIDGID&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Type : Combo kit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power: Battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage: 18V&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery Type: Lithium-Ion&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Condition: Certified Pre-Owned&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1-Year Reconditioned Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Batteries: 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Batteries Included: Batteries Included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blowout: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'RIDGID GEN5X 18 Volt 5-Piece Combo Kit, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', 'RIDGID GEN5X 18 Volt 5-Piece Combo Kit, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', 'RIDGID GEN5X 18 Volt 5-Piece Combo Kit, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED'),
(10468, 1, 'RIDGID GEN5X 18 Volt Driver/Impact Driver Kit, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TYPES OF PRODUCTS WE CARRY:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSAVE UP TO 90% OFF with our Factory Blemished or Certified Pre-Owned.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://ankermart.com/image/data/TYPE-PRO.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;RIDGID introduces their next generation of cordless tool with the GEN5X Brushless 18-Volt Compact Hammer Drill/Driver and 3-Speed Impact Driver Combo Kit. The 18-Volt Brushless 2-Piece kit has best-in-class torque for the most demanding applications. RIDGID brushless has up to 50% more run time and longer motor life. Powered by 4.0Ah Hyper Lithium Technology, an innovative battery technology built for high performance.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hammer drill: best-in-class torque with a powerful 700 in. lbs. of torque in a compact hammer drill&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hammer drill: compact size and lightweight design for a fully powered hammer drill in a compact size&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hammer drill mode selector quickly transition between driving, drilling or hammer modes without changing the micro-clutch setting&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Impact Driver: best-in-class torque with a crushing industry leading 2,250 in. lbs. of torque&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Impact Driver: 3 speed settings provide adjustable power and speed for the most demanding jobs as well as precision work&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Impact Driver: tri-beam 3 LED lights around the front housing to eliminate shadows&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Grip light engages light independently of trigger to illuminate work space&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hex grip enhanced micro-texture for secure grip and maximum user comfort&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4.0 HYPER lithium-ion batteries have triple-protection electronics, best-in-class extreme weather performance and on-battery fuel gauges&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;GEN5X brushless motors technology deliver up to 50% more run time and longer motor life&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth 9.06 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width 11.81 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height 9.29 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S INCLUDED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;R86116 hammer drill&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;R86037 impact driver&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(2) R840087 4.0Ah hyper lithium-ion batteries&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;R840095 charger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(2) belt hooks with screws&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;auxiliary handle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(2) bits&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operator\'s Manuals&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MORE INFORMATION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: RIDGID&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Type: Combo kit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power: Battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage: 18V&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery Type: Lithium-Ion&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Condition: Certified Pre-Owned&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1-Year Reconditioned Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Batteries: 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Batteries Included: Batteries Included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blowout: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'RIDGID GEN5X 18 Volt Driver/Impact Driver Kit, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', 'RIDGID GEN5X 18 Volt Driver/Impact Driver Kit, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', 'RIDGID GEN5X 18 Volt Driver/Impact Driver Kit, CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED'),
(10469, 1, 'RYOBI 40 Volt 16 In. Cordless Lawn Mower Kit CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TYPES OF PRODUCTS WE CARRY:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSAVE UP TO 90% OFF with our Factory Blemished or Certified Pre-Owned.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://ankermart.com/image/data/TYPE-PRO.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;RYOBI takes cordless to the next level with the 40-Volt Lithium-ion Mower. This convenient mower works with the 40-Volt Lithium-ion Battery to deliver fade-free power, and quick 90 minute recharge. With a 16 in. cutting deck and single-lever height adjustment, this instant-starting, whisper quiet mower is the perfect solution for small yards and close neighbors.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2-in-1 mowing system for mulching and bagging&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;16 in. cutting deck&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Single lever height adjustment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick charger fully charges your battery in 90 minutes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 20.5 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 28.5 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth: 16 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 40 lb.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S INCLUDED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) 16 in. 40-Volt Cordless Walk-Behind Lawn Mower&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(2) 40 Volt Lithium Battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) 40 Volt Lithium Charger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) Grass Catcher Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) Switch Key&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) Mulch Plug&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operator’s Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MORE INFORMATION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: RYOBI&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power: Battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage: 40V&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery Type: Lithium-Ion&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Condition: Certified Pre-Owned&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1-Year Reconditioned Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Batteries: 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Batteries Included: Batteries Included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blowout: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'RYOBI 40 Volt 16 In. Cordless Lawn Mower Kit CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', 'RYOBI 40 Volt 16 In. Cordless Lawn Mower Kit CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED', 'RYOBI 40 Volt 16 In. Cordless Lawn Mower Kit CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED'),
(10470, 1, 'Ubiquiti UniFi AC HD', '&lt;p&gt;Build your Wi-Fi network with the UniFi® AC HD Access Point, part of the Ubiquiti Networks® UniFi Enterprise Wi-Fi System. The UAP-AC-HD, is an indoor/outdoor, high-performance, 802.11AC Wave 2 dual-band access point, capable of throughput speeds of up to 2533 Mbps and a maximum range of up to 122 meters. &amp;nbsp;Engineered from the ground up to take advantage of 802.11AC Wave 2, the UAP-AC-HD provides unparalleled multi-user support.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manage Your Networks from a Single Control Plane&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Intuitive and Robust Configuration, Control and Monitoring&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Remote Firmware Upgrade&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Users and Guests&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Guest Portal/Hotspot Support&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT SPECIFICATION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 220 x 220 x 48.1 mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: &amp;nbsp;700 g (24.7 oz), 830 g (29.3 oz) with Mounting Kits&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Networking Interface: (2) 10/100/1000 Ethernet Ports&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ports: (2) Ethernet RJ45, (1) USB Type C&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Buttons: Reset&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Antennas: (2) 2.4G internal single band antennas, dual polarity (2) 5G internal single band antennas, dual polarity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wi-Fi Standards: 802.11a/b/g/n/ac/ac-wave2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Method: PoE 802.3at&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Supply: PoE Injector 48VDC -0.5A Gigabit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Power Consumption: 17W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max TX Power: 25 dBm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BSSID: 4 Per Radio&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Save: Supported&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wireless Security: WEP, WPA-PSK, WPA-Enterprise (WPA/WPA2, TKIP/AES)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Certifications: CE, FCC, IC&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mounting: Wall/Ceiling (Kits Included)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operating Temperature: -10 to 70° C (14 to 158° F)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operating Humidity: 5 to 95% Noncondensing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ADVANCED TRAFFIC MANAGEMENT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;VLAN: 802.1Q&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Advanced QoS: Per-User Rate Limiting&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Guest Traffic Isolation: Supported&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;WMM: Supported&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Concurrent Clients: 500+&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SUPPORTED DATA RATES (MBPS)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;802.11a: 6, 9, 12, 18, 24, 36, 48, 54 Mbps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;802.11n: 6.5 Mbps to 450 Mbps (MCS0 - MCS23, HT 20/40)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;802.11ac: 6.5 Mbps to 1.7Gbps (MCS0 - MCS9 NSS1/2/3/4, VHT 20/40/80)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;802.11b: 1, 2, 5.5, 11 Mbps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;802.11g: 6, 9, 12, 18, 24, 36, 48, 54 Mbps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Ubiquiti Unifi UAP-AC-HD PoE+ Access Point - 2.4/5 GHz - 1.733 Gbps', 'Ubiquiti Unifi UAP-AC-HD PoE+ Access Point - 2.4/5 GHz - 1.733 Gbps', 'Ubiquiti Unifi UAP-AC-HD PoE+ Access Point - 2.4/5 GHz - 1.733 Gbps'),
(10471, 1, 'Ubiquiti UniFi AP Pro', '&lt;p&gt;The UniFi UAP-PRO supports 802.11a/b/g/n with speeds of up to 300 Mbps in the 5 GHz radio band and up to 450 Mbps in the 2.4 GHz radio band. The UAP-PRO offers simultaneous dual-band operation with 2x2 and 3x3 MIMO technology. It has a range of up to 122 m (400 ft) and two Gigabit Ethernet ports. Aesthetic industrial design with unique front LED provisioning ring Sleek wall-mountable and ceiling tile mountable design (all accessories included).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SCALABLE AND UNIFIED ENTERPRISE WIFI MANAGEMENT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe UniFi Enterprise WiFi System is a scalable enterprise access point solution designed to be easily deployed and managed.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The UniFi Enterprise WiFi System includes the UniFi Controller software which can be easily accessed through any standard web browser. The software installs on any Windows, Mac, or Linux PC and can be run on-premise, in your private cloud or in a public cloud service. Using the UniFi Controller software, an Enterprise WiFi network can be quickly configured and administered without any special training. Real-time status, automatic UAP device detection, map loading, guest/hot-spot management, mobile roaming and advanced security options are all seamlessly integrated.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The UniFi controller software is included with each access point. There are no additional software license or subscription costs required to use the UniFi controller.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manage Your Networks from a Single Control Plane&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Intuitive and Robust Configuration, Control and Monitoring&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Remote Firmware Upgrade&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Users and Guests&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Guest Portal/Hotspot Support&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT SPECIFICATION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 200 x 200 x 36.5 mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 298 g (358 g with Mounting Kits)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Networking Interface: (2) 10/100/1000 Ethernet Ports&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Buttons: Reset&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wi-Fi Standards: 802.11 a/b/g/n&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Method: Passive Power over Ethernet (48V), 802.3af Supported&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Supply: 48V, 0.5A PoE Adapter (Included)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Power Consumption: 12 W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BSSID: Up to Four Per Radio&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Save: Supported&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wireless Security: WEP, WPA-PSK, WPA-TKIP, WPA2 AES, 802.11i&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Certifications: CE, FCC, IC&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mounting: Wall/Ceiling (Kits Included)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operating Temperature: -10 to 70°C&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operating Humidity: 5 - 80% Condensing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ANTENNAS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2.4 GHz: 3 Integrated (Supports 3x3 MIMO with Spatial Diversity)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5 GHz: 2 Integrated (Supports 2x2 MIMO with Spatial Diversity)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MAX TX POWER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2.4 GHz: 30 dBm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5 Ghz: 22 dBm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ADVANCED TRAFFIC MANAGEMENT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;VLAN: 802.1Q&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Advanced QoS: Per-User Rate Limiting&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Guest Traffic Isolation: Supported&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;WMM: Voice, Video, Best Effort, and Background&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Concurrent Clients: 200+&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SUPPORTED DATA RATES (MBPS)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;802.11a: 6, 9, 12, 18, 24, 36, 48, 54 Mbps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;802.11n (5 GHz 2x2): 6.5 Mbps to 450 Mbps (MCS0 - MCS23, HT 20/40)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;802.11n (2.4 GHz 3x3): 6.5 Mbps to 300 Mbps (MCS0 - MCS15, HT 20/40)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;802.11b: 1, 2, 5.5, 11 Mbps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;802.11g: 6, 9, 12, 18, 24, 36, 48, 54 Mbps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Ubiquiti Unifi UAP-Pro PoE Access Point - 5 GHz - 750 Mbps - Wi-Fi\r\n', 'Ubiquiti Unifi UAP-Pro PoE Access Point - 5 GHz - 750 Mbps - Wi-Fi\r\n', 'Ubiquiti Unifi UAP-Pro PoE Access Point - 5 GHz - 750 Mbps - Wi-Fi'),
(10473, 1, 'CatEye Volt 1600 HL-EL1010RC', '&lt;p&gt;From road to gravel to trail, the USB rechargeable Volt 1600 handles them all with ease by pumping out 1600 lumens through 2 ultra-bright LED. With 5 modes that allow for runtimes from 2 to 100 hours and a powerful wide beam pattern, there’s no commute, training ride, or singletrack session it can’t handle. If you’re looking for one light to do it all, look no further than the Volt 1600.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S INCLUDED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIncludes quick-change cartridge battery, micro USB charging cable, and H-34 FlexTightTM handlebar mount&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DIMENSIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;9 x 59.6 x 44.2 mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight：260 grams (light unit and battery)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1600 lumens&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High intensity white LED X2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery： Li-ion rechargeable battery (3.6V-6800mAh)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low battery indicator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lighting mode memory function.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OPTIONAL PARTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Helmet Mount (5341831N)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Center Fork Bracket (5342440)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MODES/RUN TIME&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High: Approx 2 Hours (1600 lumens)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Middle: Approx 5 Hours (500 lumens)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low: Approx 15 Hours (200 lumens)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hyper Constant: Approx 12 Hours (1600/200 lumens)： 12hrs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flashing: Approx 100 Hours (200 lumens)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Recharge time: Approx 9-16hrs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Recharge/discharge number of times： about 300 times（until the rated capacity drops to 70%)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;* Design and specifications are subject to change without notice.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'CatEye Volt 1600 HL-EL1010RC', 'CatEye Volt 1600 HL-EL1010RC', 'CatEye Volt 1600 HL-EL1010RCCatEye Volt 1600 HL-EL1010RC'),
(10474, 1, 'CatEye Padrone Smart Triple SPD/CDC/HR CC-PA500B', '&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PLEASE CHECK TO SEE IF YOUR SMARTPHONE MODEL IS COMPATIBLE.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.cateye.com/data/resources/cc_compatible_device.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Cateye Cycling Recommended Device/Email Program List&amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Smart technology meets our most popular display, the Padrone. Download the free CatEye Cycling app, stash your smartphone away safely in your jersey pocket or saddlebag and hit the road. Use Mirror Mode to get GPS-powered ride data, SMS (Text), call and email alerts from your phone displayed on the Padrone Smart’s screen while your phone is kept safe from the elements in sleep mode, preserving the battery. When carrying a phone isn’t ideal, use Sensor Direct Mode to get speed, cadence, heart rate and power data directly from Bluetooth® Smart wireless sensors. After use in either mode, seamlessly upload ride data to CatEyeAtlasTM, StravaTM or TrainingPeaksTM.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S INCLUDED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIncludes the ISC-12 bluetooth speed and cadence sensor , the HR-12 bluetooth heart rate sensor kit plus a FlexTightTMhandlebar mounting bracket, wheel magnet, cadence magnet, zip ties, and &amp;nbsp;3 CR2032 batteries.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;* For power data you will need a &lt;a href=&quot;http://cateyeamerica.com/Power-Meters&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Bluetooth Power Meter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Current speed： &amp;nbsp;0.0(4.0)～105.9km/h&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Total distance： 0.0～9999.9/10000-99999km&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Trip distance 1： 0.00～999.99km&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Trip distance 2： 0.00～999.99/1000.0～9999.9km&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Elapsed time： 0:00\'00&quot;～9:59\'59&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Average speed： 0.0～105.9km/h&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum speed： 0.0(4.0)～105.9km/h&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wireless transmission： Bluetooth® Smart&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Clock： 0:00\'～23:59\' [1:00\'～12:59\']&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pace arrow： Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto power saving： Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto mode： Yes (Auto/Manual start/stop)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual tire size： Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tire size: 100mm～3999mm (default：2096mm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible sensors： CatEye brand ISC-12 Speed/Cadence sensor / HR-12 Heart Rate sensor (* Also works with other brand Speed, Cadence, Heart Rate, and/or Power sensors conforming to Bluetooth4.0 CSCP/HRP/CPP)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery： CR2032 X1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery life：&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Approx 4 months&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimension： 67.5 X43.0 X15.6 mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight： 30 grams&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;※&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;The factory-loaded battery life might be shorter than the specification above.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n※&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Design and specifications are subject to change without notice.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'CatEye Padrone Smart Triple SPD/CDC/HR CC-PA500B', 'CatEye Padrone Smart Triple SPD/CDC/HR CC-PA500B', 'CatEye Padrone Smart Triple SPD/CDC/HR CC-PA500B'),
(10475, 1, 'Ubiquiti UniFi AC Pro', '&lt;p&gt;The UniFi AC Pro AP features the latest Wi-Fi 802.11ac, 3x3 MIMO technology in a refined industrial design and is ideal for deployment of maximum‑performance wireless networks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manage Your Networks from a Single Control Plane&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Intuitive and Robust Configuration, Control and Monitoring&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Remote Firmware Upgrade&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Users and Guests&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Guest Portal/Hotspot Support&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT SPECIFICATION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 196.7 x 196.7 x 35 mm (7.74 x 7.74 x 1.38&quot;)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 350 g (12.4 oz), 450 g (15.9 oz) with Mounting Kits&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Networking Interface: (2) 10/100/1000 Ethernet Ports&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ports : (1) USB 2.0 Port&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Buttons: Reset&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Antennas: (3) Dual-Band Antennas, 2.4 GHz: 3 dBi, 5 GHz: 6 dBi&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wi-Fi Standards: 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Method: Passive Power over Ethernet (48V), 802.3af/803.2at Supported (Supported Voltage Range: 44 to 57VDC)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Supply: 48V, 0.5A PoE Gigabit Adapter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Power Consumption: 9W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max TX Power: 22 dBm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BSSID: Up to Four per Radio&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Save: Supported&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wireless Security: WEP, WPA-PSK, WPA-Enterprise (WPA/WPA2, TKIP/AES)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Certifications: CE, FCC, IC&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mounting: Wall/Ceiling (Kits Included)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operating Temperature: -10 to 70° C (14 to 158° F)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operating Humidity: 5 to 95% Noncondensing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ADVANCED TRAFFIC MANAGEMENT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;VLAN: 802.1Q&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Advanced QoS: Per-User Rate Limiting&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Guest Traffic Isolation: Supported&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;WMM: Voice, Video, Best Effort, and Background&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Concurrent Clients: 200+&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SUPPORTED DATA RATES (MBPS)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;802.11a: 6, 9, 12, 18, 24, 36, 48, 54 Mbps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;802.11n: 6.5 Mbps to 450 Mbps (MCS0 - MCS23, HT 20/40)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;802.11ac: 6.5 Mbps to 1300 Mbps (MCS0 - MCS9 NSS1/2/3, VHT 20/40/80)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;802.11b: 1, 2, 5.5, 11 Mbps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;802.11g: 6, 9, 12, 18, 24, 36, 48, 54 Mbps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Ubiquiti UniFi AC Pro', 'Ubiquiti UniFi AC Pro', 'Ubiquiti UniFi AC Pro'),
(10478, 1, 'Philips Hue White Wireless Dimming Kit E26', '&lt;p&gt;Get started with Philips Hue wireless dimming kit and enjoy smooth wireless dimming. Control the bulb with the included dimmer switch, or connect everything to a Philips Hue bridge for control from your smart device.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WIRELESS DIMMING works out of the box&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x E26 bulb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimmer switch included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warm white light (2700K)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;INSTALLATION FREE DIMMING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nInstallation free dimming Experience guaranteed smooth dimming with Philips Hue. Not too bright. Not too dark. Just right. No need for wires, an electrician or installation&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPlace the switch anywherePlace the switch anywhere The Philips Hue dimmer switch works as a normal wall switch and dimmer. You can place it anywhere you want, using screws or the adhesive tape on the back plate of the switch&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;USE AS A REMOTE CONTROL&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nUse as a remote control Pick up the remote and use it wherever you want for your comfort. The control unit of the switch is magnetic and can be removed from the base plate.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CONTROL UP TO 10 PHILIPS HUE LIGHTS SIMULTANEOUSLY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nControl up to 10 Philips Hue lights simultaneously You can connect up to 10 Philips Hue lights to your Philips Hue dimmer switch and control them simultaneously.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FULL CONTROL FROM SMART DEVICE WITH HUE BRIDGE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFull control from smart device with Hue bridge Connect your Philips Hue lights with the bridge to unlock the endless possibilites of the system.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS THE BULB&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fitting: E26 screw base fitting&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Form factor: A19&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lifetime: 25000&amp;nbsp; hour(s)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wattage: 9.5&amp;nbsp; W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Light output: High quality white light / Dimmable via smart device only / Beam angle 180° / &amp;gt;80 CRI&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lumen output: 800 lm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Software upgradable: when connected to Hue bridge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Start up: Instant 100% light output&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 4.2&amp;nbsp; inch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 2.4&amp;nbsp; inch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color temperature: 2700K (warm white)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS THE SWITCH&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Batteries included: 1 x CR2450&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Frequency band: 2400 – 2483.5 MHz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lifetime: 50000 clicks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max. lights per switch: 10 if not linked to Hue bridge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Minimal battery lifetime: 3&amp;nbsp; year(s)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Minimal range indoor: 500&amp;nbsp; inch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Software upgradeable: when connected to Hue bridge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Switch depth: 0.43&amp;nbsp; inch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Switch height: 3.6&amp;nbsp; inch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Switch width: 1.38&amp;nbsp; inch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight of switch: 37&amp;nbsp; g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wall plate depth: 0.55&amp;nbsp; inch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wall plate height: 2.76&amp;nbsp; inch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wall plate width: 4.5&amp;nbsp; inch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight including wall plate: 67&amp;nbsp; g&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Zigbee Light link: protocol IEEE 802.15.4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S IN THE BOX&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hue dimmer switch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hue white bulbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Guarantee: 2 years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Philips Hue White Wireless Dimming Kit E26', 'Philips Hue White Wireless Dimming Kit E26', 'Philips Hue White Wireless Dimming Kit E26'),
(10488, 1, 'Bose QuietComfort 35 Wireless Headphones, Noise Cancelling - Black', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE BEST FROM BOSE JUST GOT WIRELESS.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBose put years of research into QuietComfort 35 wireless headphones so you could get more out of them. They\'re engineered with world-class noise cancellation that makes quiet sound quieter and music sound better. Experience world class performance and superior comfort without any wires in your way.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Engineered with superior noise cancellation, QuietComfort® 35 wireless headphones by Bose make quiet sound quieter and music sound better. Bluetooth and NFC pairing enable easy connection to your wireless devices. Up to 20 hours* of playtime on a single charge means you can get lost in your music - or the silence - without giving battery life a second thought.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EXCLUSIVE NOISE-CANCELLING TECHNOLOGY FOR CLEAR SOUND AND MORE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHear what you want to hear and block out the rest, like cabin noise inside an airplane or a busy office. The headphones\' advanced noise cancelling ensures you hear your favorite tunes the way the artist intended. Volume-optimized EQ provides balanced audio performance no matter what the volume. A built-in, noise-rejecting dual-microphone system makes sure both parties are heard loud and clear when making or taking calls on your smartphone.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NO-HASSLE, COMFORTABLE WIRE-FREE LISTENING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nConnect to your wireless devices via Bluetooth and NFC pairing. Then, experience unencumbered audio enjoyment as you jog around the track or jaunt around town. Constructed from premium materials, the QuietComfort 35 headphones are lightweight and comfortable for enjoyable all-day listening.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KEEP THE MUSIC PLAYING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhether you\'re commuting to work or just settling in for some private listening time, the built-in a lithium-ion battery will keep the music playing for up to 20 hours per charge*. The included audio-only cable allows user to continue to listen to their source even if the battery power is depleted.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EASY CALL AND MUSIC MANAGEMENT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nVoice prompts and intuitive controls make communicating and controlling your music hassle free. Manage music and calls on multiple Bluetooth devices, personalize your settings and more with the Bose Connect app.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S IN THE BOX&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOne Bose QuietComfort 35 wireless headphones, audio-only cable, USB cable, Airline adapter&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;*Battery power consumption depends on factors such as network configuration, carrier network and signal strength.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Bose QuietComfort 35 Wireless Headphones, Noise Cancelling - Black', 'Bose QuietComfort 35 Wireless Headphones, Noise Cancelling - Black', 'Bose QuietComfort 35 Wireless Headphones, Noise Cancelling - Black'),
(10489, 1, 'Bose QuietComfort 35 Wireless Headphones, Noise Cancelling - Silver', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE BEST FROM BOSE JUST GOT WIRELESS.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBose put years of research into QuietComfort 35 wireless headphones so you could get more out of them. They\'re engineered with world-class noise cancellation that makes quiet sound quieter and music sound better. Experience world class performance and superior comfort without any wires in your way.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Engineered with superior noise cancellation, QuietComfort® 35 wireless headphones by Bose make quiet sound quieter and music sound better. Bluetooth and NFC pairing enable easy connection to your wireless devices. Up to 20 hours* of playtime on a single charge means you can get lost in your music - or the silence - without giving battery life a second thought.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EXCLUSIVE NOISE-CANCELLING TECHNOLOGY FOR CLEAR SOUND AND MORE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHear what you want to hear and block out the rest, like cabin noise inside an airplane or a busy office. The headphones\' advanced noise cancelling ensures you hear your favorite tunes the way the artist intended. Volume-optimized EQ provides balanced audio performance no matter what the volume. A built-in, noise-rejecting dual-microphone system makes sure both parties are heard loud and clear when making or taking calls on your smartphone.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NO-HASSLE, COMFORTABLE WIRE-FREE LISTENING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nConnect to your wireless devices via Bluetooth and NFC pairing. Then, experience unencumbered audio enjoyment as you jog around the track or jaunt around town. Constructed from premium materials, the QuietComfort 35 headphones are lightweight and comfortable for enjoyable all-day listening.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KEEP THE MUSIC PLAYING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhether you\'re commuting to work or just settling in for some private listening time, the built-in a lithium-ion battery will keep the music playing for up to 20 hours per charge*. The included audio-only cable allows user to continue to listen to their source even if the battery power is depleted.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EASY CALL AND MUSIC MANAGEMENT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nVoice prompts and intuitive controls make communicating and controlling your music hassle free. Manage music and calls on multiple Bluetooth devices, personalize your settings and more with the Bose Connect app.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S IN THE BOX&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOne Bose QuietComfort 35 wireless headphones, audio-only cable, USB cable, Airline adapter&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;*Battery power consumption depends on factors such as network configuration, carrier network and signal strength.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Bose QuietComfort 35 Wireless Headphones, Noise Cancelling - Silver', 'Bose QuietComfort 35 Wireless Headphones, Noise Cancelling - Silver', 'Bose QuietComfort 35 Wireless Headphones, Noise Cancelling - Silver'),
(10491, 1, 'Ooma Telo Free Home Phone Service with HD2 Handset', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OOMA TELO FREE HOME PHONE SERVICE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Crystal clear nationwide calling for free and low international rates. Pay only monthly applicable taxes and fees.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;#1 rated for overall satisfaction and value by a leading consumer research publication.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;PureVoice HD delivers superior voice quality for a consistently great calling experience&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Works with your high-speed Internet and any home phone; installs in minutes.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes nationwide calling, voicemail, caller-ID, call-waiting, 911 emergency service, and Ooma mobile app&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Backed by 30-day money-back guarantee and extendable 1-year warranty with 24/7 customer support&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OOMA HD2 HANDSET&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two-Inch Color Screen and Picture Caller-ID&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cutting-Edge HD Voice Clarity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Superior Security and Range&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ooma Telo and HD2 Handset Bundle | Free home phone service VoIP phone and device&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The smartest home phone is the one that gives you exactly what you want with the greatest savings. That\'s Ooma.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Get crystal-clear nationwide calling for free. You pay only applicable taxes and fees. Connect Ooma to your high-speed Internet and activate online. It\'s that easy.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;REQUIREMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High-speed fixed-line Internet connection (cable, DSL, fiber-optic)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Min 180 Kbps upstream network speed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Corded or cordless home phone, or optional Ooma HD2 Handset&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Intended for residential use only&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES INCLUDED WITH OOMA BASIC SERVICE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Free U.S. calling&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Caller-ID and call-waiting&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low international rates&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;911 Alerts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Online call log&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One touch voicemail access&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fax mode&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The utmost voice clarity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Remote voicemail retrieval&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Online preferences&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Live customer support&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Free Ooma-to-Ooma calling&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Online Voicemail Playback&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Area Code Selection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Encrypted calls&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Call Return&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Online phonebook&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S IN THE BOX&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ooma Telo device + HD2 Handset (May ship separately)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ethernet cable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AC adapter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick start guide.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OOMA WORKS WITH NEST&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ooma Telo works with your Nest devices to allow your house to keep an eye on things while you’re away.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Now Ooma can automatically forward your home phone calls when you’re away and even call to alert you of important events in your home. With Ooma and Nest you get added convenience and peace of mind. Requires Ooma Premier service.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Ooma Telo Free Home Phone Service with HD2 Handset', 'Ooma Telo Free Home Phone Service with HD2 Handset', 'Ooma Telo Free Home Phone Service with HD2 Handset'),
(10496, 1, 'Callaway Strata 11-Piece Women’s Set', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CALLAWAY STRATA 11-PIECE WOMEN’S SET&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Gender: Ladies&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hand: Right or Left&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Origin: Factory Installed - Stock&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Material: Graphite&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Manufacturer: Callaway Golf&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Type: Callaway Graphite&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Flex: Ladies&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Set Composition: Driver, 5 Wood, 5 Hybrid, 7iron, 9iron, SW, Putter, Stand Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Callaway Strata 11-Piece Women’s Set', 'Callaway Strata 11-Piece Women’s Set', 'Callaway Strata 11-Piece Women’s Set'),
(10492, 1, 'Callaway Boys XJ Hot Junior Kids Golf Club Set, 9-12 Years Old', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CALLAWAY BOYS XJ HOT JUNIOR KIDS GOLF CLUB SET, 9-12 YEARS OLD&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Gender: Mens&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hand: Right or Left&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Origin: Factory Installed - Stock&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Material: Graphite&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Manufacturer: Callaway Golf&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Type: Callaway Junior Graphite&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Flex: Regular&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Set Composition: Driver, 3 Wood, 5H, 7i, 9i, SW, Putter, Stand Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DESIGNED FOR JUNIORS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe lengths, weights, and lofts are designed specifically for juniors to help them. The increased hosel offset helps square the face at impact for improved distance and accuracy.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DISTANCE MADE EASY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEvery club in the set is configured to generate more power for more distance. The center of gravity and perimeter weighting are strategically placed to help get the ball up in the air quickly and easily, something every young player wants to see.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;COMPLETE COURSE COVERAGE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe all-in-one set is designed to give juniors everything they need to play well. The clubs are engineered to improve distance control, with high ball flights out of a variety of lies to give them confidence on each shot.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Callaway Boys XJ Hot Junior Kids Golf Club Set, 9-12 Years Old', 'Callaway Boys XJ Hot Junior Kids Golf Club Set, 9-12 Years Old', 'Callaway Boys XJ Hot Junior Kids Golf Club Set, 9-12 Years Old'),
(10493, 1, 'Callaway Fusion 14 Stand Bag', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CALLAWAY FUSION 14 STAND BAG&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nShowcasing multiple pockets, quick release shoulder straps and a 14-way top normally found in cart bags, the Fusion 14 Stand Bag is the perfect blend of function and style.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES &amp;amp; DETAILS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nShowcasing multiple pockets, quick release shoulder straps and a 14-way top normally found in cart bags, the Fusion 14 Stand Bag is the perfect blend of function and style.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;14-way Top with Individual Full Length Club Dividers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;10 Pockets, including a Water-resistant, Velour-lined Valuables Pocket&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Improved Quick-release Comfort Tech Strap System&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Integrated Alignment Stick Holder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Black Satin Finished Towel Hook/Bottle Opener&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 5.4 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Custom Logo: Ball Pocket, Right and Left Side Pockets&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Callaway Fusion 14 Stand Bag', 'Callaway Fusion 14 Stand Bag', 'Callaway Fusion 14 Stand Bag'),
(10494, 1, 'Callaway Strata Plus 14-Piece Women’s Set', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CALLAWAY STRATA PLUS WOMEN\'S COMPLETE 14-PIECE SET&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Gender: Ladies&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hand: Right&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Origin: Factory Installed - Stock&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Material: Graphite&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Manufacturer: Callaway Golf&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Type: Callaway Graphite&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Flex: Ladies&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Set Composition: Driver, Fairway, 5 Hybrid, 6-9 Iron, PW, SW, Putter, Stand Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DRIVER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n460cc clubhead with a forgiving sweet spot and a graphite shaft for more distance off the tee. (Headcover included)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FAIRWAY WOODS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nStainless steel clubhead and graphite composite shaft promote faster swing speeds and long shots. (Headcover included)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HYBRIDS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDesigned for versatility and forgiveness on shots where you would usually hit a difficult long iron. (Headcover included)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IRONS/WEDGES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPerimeter weighting and progressive sole width technology for improved control.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PUTTER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMallet with T-Style alignment to help give you incredible accuracy.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;STAND BAG&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe lightweight, durable stand bag comes with five convenient pockets, an additional cooler pocket, a rain hood and a backpack strap system.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Callaway Strata Plus 14-Piece Women’s Set', 'Callaway Strata Plus 14-Piece Women’s Set', 'Callaway Strata Plus 14-Piece Women’s Set'),
(10495, 1, 'Callaway Strata 12-Piece Men’s Set', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CALLAWAY MEN\'S STRATA COMPLETE GOLF CLUB SET WITH BAG (12-PIECE)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Gender: Men\'s&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hand: Left or Right&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Origin: Factory Installed - Stock&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Material: Graphite/Steel Combo&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Manufacturer: Callaway Golf&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Type: Callaway Graphite&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shaft Flex: Regular&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Set Composition: Driver, 3 Wood, 5H, 6i-9i, PW, Putter, Stand Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DRIVER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n460cc forged driver has a large sweet spot and provides more forgiveness to help you rip it off the tee. (Headcover included)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FAIRWAY WOODS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThis 3-wood is very forgiving and has a more aerodynamic head shape for long, high flying shots. (Headcover included)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HYBRIDS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nA great alternative to difficult long irons, allowing for more confidence on a variety of shots.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IRONS/WEDGES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThese stainless steel irons offer a great combination of forgiveness and control&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PUTTER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMallet with T-Style alignment to help give you incredible accuracy.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;STAND BAG&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe lightweight, durable stand bag comes with five convenient pockets, an additional cooler pocket, a rain hood and a backpack strap system.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Callaway Strata 12-Piece Men’s Set', 'Callaway Strata 12-Piece Men’s Set', 'Callaway Strata 12-Piece Men’s Set');
