 frequencies for stricter consistency than the competition, often by an order of magnitude&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5+ Years of Comfort R&amp;amp;D - Ergonomic headband based and patent-pending hexagon shape minimizes force on your head, ears and gap for the best fit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WIRELESS FREEDOM + WIRED 0-LATENCY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hybrid Wireless + Wired - Enjoy the best of 2 worlds: virtually identical sound in wireless for freedom, wired when you run out of juice&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wired Hi-Res Audio Zero Latency - No powered EQ, artificial processing or colored sound that pollutes the audio and causes unacceptable latency for videos, gaming and DJ/music performance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto Analog Switch - Plug a cable in the jack to automatically switch off all battery and electronics to turn your Bluetooth headphones into a “zero latency” weapon for the win&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Go the Distance - Pair your Bluetooth device and enjoy your headphones up to 30 feet (10 meters)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Simultaneous Device Pairing - Multitasking users can pair the headphones with two sources at a time, such as a smartphone and laptop for work or a smartphone and smartwatch for working out&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;15% Longer Battery - Bigger battery provides up to 14+ hours of music, unlimited hours in wired analog mode&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CLIQFOLD PORTABILITY AND EXOSKELETON CASE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&quot;Folds to the smallest size of any over-the-ear headphone I\'ve ever reviewed.&quot; -Techhive&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Patented CliqFold Hinge - Luxury lighter-like hinge mechanism precisely folds the headphones into impossibly small exoskeleton case (patent pending)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;V-PORT Vents - New ventilation system for air circulation after use on stage or working out&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exoskeleton V-STRAP - Organize cables (including the V-Micro USB cable) via the V-STRAP system with extra room for your USB Drive &amp;amp; Faders earplugs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Carabiner Clip - Secure your case on the outside of your bag for quick access&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'V-MODA Crossfade 2 Wireless Over-Ear Headphone Matte White', 'V-MODA Crossfade 2 Wireless Over-Ear Headphone Matte White', 'V-MODA Crossfade 2 Wireless Over-Ear Headphone Matte White'),
(10506, 1, 'V-MODA Crossfade M-100 Over-Ear Noise-Isolating Metal Headphone Silver', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;V-MODA CROSSFADE M-100 OVER-EAR NOISE-ISOLATING METAL HEADPHONE MATTE BLACK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Base Color : &lt;strong&gt;WHITE SILVER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra Shields (Laser Engraved Aluminum): &lt;strong&gt;PLEASE CHOOSE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra Screws: &lt;strong&gt;BLACK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Design: &lt;strong&gt;STANDARD NO DESIGN&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&quot;No other headphone can touch the M-100\'s combination of features, build quality, and sound for the money&quot; -CNET&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;OVER-EAR . CLIQFOLD . 3D HEADPHONES&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWHY THE CROSSFADE M-100?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;#1 Trusted Sound&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3D Printed Metal + Fiber Personalization&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Military-level Durability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Six Star Service&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;#1 TRUSTED SOUND &amp;amp; COMFORT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nImmersive 3D Soundstage - Live performance experiences&lt;br /&gt;\r\nClean Deep Bass - Feel and hear precise vibrations of your music without bloated boom or muddy mids&lt;br /&gt;\r\nUltra Wide Clarity &amp;amp; Vivid Midrange - Lifelike vocals, crystal clear cymbals and crispy hi-hats&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCrossfade M-100\'s award-winning sound and comfort are created by:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;50mm Dual-Diaphragm Driver (Patent Pending) - Inner and outer rings separate the bass from bleeding into the mids and highs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Master Crafted Materials - More expensive driver and components than peer headphones at this price range&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Analog Noise Isolation - Naturally cut out the distractions of jet engines, crying babies and crowd noise&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No Batteries or Artificial Processing - Powerful, pure sound without the pollution of two extra digital-to-analog conversions of battery powered headphones&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Minimal sound leakage - Immersive sound for you without bothering others view details&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Consistent Driver Quality - Quality tested at 6 frequencies to maintain stricter consistency than the competition, often by an order of magnitude&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4+ Years of Comfort R&amp;amp;D - Ergonomic headband and hexagon shape that minimizes the force on your head, ears and gap&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BLISS Memory Foam Cushions - Naturally forms to your ears to provide supreme comfort and noise isolation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VERSATILITY AND STYLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&quot;You can wear cookie cutter headphones and look like everyone else, or you can wear V-MODA.&quot; -Morgan Page&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mind the Gap - Patented sleek design frames the natural lines of your facial features and minimizes unsightly gap&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Optional Custom Shield Kits - 3D Print or laser engrave your logo, change your shield material and color&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cable &amp;amp; Cushion Ecosystem - Extend your functionality with the BoomPro Mic for gaming and communication, XL Memory Cushions, CoilPro extended and a variety of cables&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;DURABILITY: BUILT to LAST&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&quot;There’s nothing I’d recommend more&quot; -Popular Science&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Virtually Indestructible STEELFLEX Headband&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steel Frame&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exoskeleton Form-Fitting Case&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tested Beyond Military-Level Quality MIL-STD-810G Test Standards&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Durable Cable/Plug Bend - Cables and 45-degree plug can bend over 1 million times (100x industry standard)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Headband Bend - Steelflex can bend 10+ times flat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Environmental - High and low temperatures, humidity, salt spray and UV exposure&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PORTABLE EXOSKELETON CASE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&quot;First full-size, audiophile-friendly headphone we\'ve seen that you can really take anywhere&quot; -Sound &amp;amp; Vision&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CliqFold™ Hinge - Luxury lighter-like hinge mechanism precisely folds the headphones into impossibly small exoskeleton case (patent pending)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exoskeleton V-STRAP - Organize cables and 1/4&quot; adapter via the V-STRAP system with extra room for your USB Drive &amp;amp; Faders VIP earplugs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Carabiner Clip - Secure your case on the outside of your bag for quick access&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DETACHABLE CABLES: MAKE the CALL . SHARE the VIBE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual Inputs &amp;amp; V-CORK - Mix two sources at the same time or daisy chain headphones with your friends; the included V-CORK seals &amp;amp; protects the unused input&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SpeakEasy™ Mic Cable - Specially tuned for voice recognition and calls in the noisiest environments, the button control universally works with all 3.5mm smartphones and tablets including Apple, Android, Samsung, Windows, Kindle and Blackberry&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SharePlay™ Audio Cable - Share your music on a ride or DJ tandem without adapters&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'V-MODA Crossfade M-100 Over-Ear Noise-Isolating Metal Headphone Silver', 'V-MODA Crossfade M-100 Over-Ear Noise-Isolating Metal Headphone Silver', 'V-MODA Crossfade M-100 Over-Ear Noise-Isolating Metal Headphone Silver'),
(10507, 1, 'Lomo\'Instant Sanremo + 3 Lenses', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LOMO\'INSTANT SANREMO + 3 LENSES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDiscover the flexibility of the Lomo\'Instant Sanremo. Shoot enchanting photos with this retro-chic instant camera and share them with your friends in just a snap.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Lomo\'Instant Sanremo is the perfectly sized instant camera to take wherever you go! The camera has a classy, retro brown design and it’s the most creative way to shoot marvelous photos which you can share anywhere and with everyone in an instant.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3 SHOOTING MODES TO COVER EVERY KIND OF INSTANT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Lomo\'Instant has an auto flash shooting mode so you can easily shoot fantastic instant photos with flash in the touch of a button. You can also switch to the two manual shooting modes to open up all kinds of experimental shooting possibilities.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flash-On Auto Mode: Using this mode, a sensor on the flash detects the brightness, and the light meter automatically gives off the right amount of flash. The default aperture value is f/16 and the exposure compensation dial can be adjusted. It’s perfect to use anywhere when you’re on the go.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flash-On Manual Mode: This mode is great for shooting indoors. The flash is on and you can switch between N for normal daytime shots and B shutter for long exposures.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flash-Off Manual Mode: This mode is great for long exposures at night. The flash is switched off and you can switch between N for normal daytime shots and B shutter for long exposures at night.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AN ULTRA-ADVANCED LENS SYSTEM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe camera has a built-in wide-angle lens and is compatible with multiple lens attachments that can be screwed onto the Lomo’Instant for tons of creative and experimental photography options.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wide-Angle Lens (built-in): This 27mm equivalent wide-angle captures more than your eyes can see and allows you to shoot up-close-and-personal shots with its 0.4m closest focusing distance.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fisheye Lens Attachment: The Fisheye lens attachment lets you take 170° snapshots. Get hooked, lined and shamelessly sinkered for wonderful circular instants with the 170° Fisheye Lens Attachment.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Portrait Lens Attachment: This versatile 35mm equivalent lens attachment is suitable for shooting both indoors and out. It\'s great for portraits as well as street photography and landscape shots.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Close-up Lens: This lens allows a 10-15cm closest focusing distance for striking close-ups.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SH-O-O-O-O-T L-O-O-O-O-O-NG EXPOSURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Lomo\'Instant’s B setting lets you create light-streaked photos by holding the shutter open for as long as you like. Try it out for night-time or light painting photoshoots.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SHOOT UNLIMITED MULTIPLE EXPOSURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Lomo\'Instant is the only modern Instant camera which allows you to shoot unlimited multiple exposure instants. This means you can combine numerous shots in one frame for show-stopping effects!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;COLOR GELS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nChoose from blue, red, purple and yellow! By adding the filters over your flash, you can play around with cool and warm tones, and give an artistic flair to your instants!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SHOOT BRIGHTER SHOTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith its maximum aperture of f/8, the Lomo\'Instant lets you shoot brighter shots.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE PERFECT INSTANT PHOTO FORMAT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe camera creates credit card-sized snapshots using high quality and widely available Fuji Instax Mini film, renowned for its bright colors and clear images.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MIRROR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Lomo\'Instant Camera has a tiny mirror to the left of the lens. Combined with the wide-angle lens, the Lomo’Instant mirror lets you take picture-perfect selfies.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;INTRODUCING THE LOMO’INSTANT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;https://vimeo.com/99014472&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PACKAGE INCLUDES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lomo’Instant Camera&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lomo\'Instant Fisheye Lens Attachment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lomo\'Instant Portrait Lens Attachment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lomo\'Instant Close-Up Lens Attachment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lens Caps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Colored Gel Filters&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shooting Technique Cards&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Instruction Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Film Format: Fujifilm Instax Mini Film&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exposure Area: 42mm x 64mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shutter Speed: 1/125s / Bulb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exposure Compensation: +2/-2 Exposure Values&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ejection Mechanism: Motorized&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multiple Exposures: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in Flash Guide Number: 9(m)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic Flash Output: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery Supply: 6V (4x AAA batteries)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tripod mount: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cable Release Mount: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Aperture: f/8, f/11, f/16, f/22, f/32&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Lomo\'Instant Sanremo + 3 Lenses', 'Lomo\'Instant Sanremo + 3 Lenses', 'Lomo\'Instant Sanremo + 3 Lenses'),
(10508, 1, 'Lomo\'Instant Wide Victoria Peak', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LOMO\'INSTANT WIDE VICTORIA PEAK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMake your instant photography skills sparkle and shine with the Lomo\'Instant Wide Victoria Peak camera.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Inspired by the vibrant scene at the top of the highest mountain on Hong Kong Island and famous spectacular panoramic views over the city, this statement camera will add a sparkle to all your creative photography escapades. The Lomo’Instant Wide Victoria Peak edition is a mixture of shiny glitter silver faux leather and glitter black linen. Available in both single and combo package.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Lomo’Instant Wide features not only manual exposure settings for the free-thinkers out there, but also comes equipped with a Fully Programmatic Shutter that lets you lean back and enjoy the ease of the instant. Long exposures, multiple exposures and color-flashed exposures—this camera gives you everything you need to explore your creativity.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PACKAGE INCLUDES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lomo’Instant Wide Camera Victoria Peak&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Colored Gel Filters&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Remote Control Lens Cap&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shooting Technique Cards&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Instruction Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Film Format: Fujifilm Instax Wide Film&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exposure Area: 64mm x 99mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lens Focal Length: 90mm (35mm equivalent)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto exposure type: Programmed Automatic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Aperture: f/8, f/22&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shutter Speed range: Bulb (Bulb Mode), 8s-1/250 (Auto Shooting Mode), 1/30 (Fixed Shutter Speed Mode)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exposure Compensation: +1/-1 Exposure Values (Ambient)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ejection Mechanism: Motorized&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multiple Exposures: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in Flash Guide Number: 13 (m)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in Flash: Automatic Electronic Flash &amp;amp; Flash Off Mode&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Closest Focusing Distance: 0.6m (0.1m with the Close-Up Lens)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Zone Focusing Setting: 0.6m / 1-2m / infinite&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tripod Mount: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Remote control transmission: Infrared&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery Supply: 4 x AA batteries (4 x 1.5V)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Remote control battery Supply: 1 x 2025 batteries (3V)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Filter Thread: 49mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fully Automatic &amp;amp; Creative Shooting Modes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhether you’re relaxing at a pool party in the hills of Hollywood, sipping tea on the sofa while your dog does backflips, biking through Chilean vineyards or enjoying Sunday brunch with friends—simply select your preferred shooting mode and you’ll be on your way!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fully Programmatic Shutter&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEngage auto mode and take advantage of its fully programmatic shutter. For every image you snap, the shutter will automatically determine how much light is necessary for perfect exposure—a totally hassle-free instant experience.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Remote Control Lens Cap&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nClose your eyes and imagine being able to snap an instant photo of yourself and your friends without having to push the shutter button. Now open your eyes—with the Lomo’Instant Wide, you can do just that. Remotely operate the shutter release with the lens cap of the Lomo’Instant Wide to take great group and party photos.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Take a Ride on the Wide Side&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nConjuring the spirit of shooting large film format Polaroids of yesteryear, the Lomo’Instant Wide uses Fuji Instax Wide film, which is twice as wide as Instax Mini film.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PC Sync Socket&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith the PC Sync Socket on the Lomo’Instant Wide, you can approach every lighting situation with ease—perfect for everything from single flashes to studio flash kits.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Built-In Premium 90mm Lens&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBeing a 35mm equivalent, the built in lens on the Lomo’Instant Wide means wide format instant versatility like never before. Take gorgeous portraits using the closest focusing distance (0.6m), keep your distance with the 1-2m setting, or simply switch infinity for everything else!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Large Format Long Exposures&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFor stunning long exposure photographs, engage Bulb Mode on your Lomo’Instant Wide. Experiment with insane light paintings just by holding the shutter open manually for as long as you need.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;When One is Just Not Enough: Unlimited Multiple Exposures&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNext to the Lomo’Instant, the Lomo’Instant Wide is the only other instant camera capable of unlimited multiple exposures! With the flick of the MX switch, you can create awe-inspiring multiple exposure classics in an instant.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Color Gels&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAdd artistic style to your shots and experiment with cool and crazy results—4 brightly colored flash gels let paint your Lomo’Instant Wide shots with a smack of color.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flash On and Off&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPerfect for those times you want to shoot the entire scene and not just your subject with a blacked-out background, this feature allows you to control exactly when and where the flash is enabled. With the help of the Fully Programmatic Shutter, you get well exposed shots without the flash.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Exposure Compensation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEasily shoot lighter or darker photos using the exposure compensation control.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fast Focusing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith three different zone focusing areas, it’s super-fast and easy to adjust to every focusing distance desired.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Lomo\'Instant Wide Victoria Peak', 'Lomo\'Instant Wide Victoria Peak', 'Lomo\'Instant Wide Victoria Peak'),
(10510, 1, 'PureSteam Duo Iron &amp; Pressurized Garment Steamer', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PURESTEAM DUO IRON &amp;amp; PRESSURIZED GARMENT STEAMER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPureSteam Duo combines the power of a high-pressure steamer and high-temperature iron into one powerful household unit that penetrates deep into fabrics to easily release wrinkles and freshen clothes in seconds.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Safe and effective for use on:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Clothing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Coats&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Curtains &amp;amp; Drapes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Table Linens&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Upholstered Furniture&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2-in-1 Iron &amp;amp; Steamer: Conveniently switch between steaming and ironing any garment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable Temperature Dial: User-friendly fabric settings like synthetics, silk, wool, and cotton take the guesswork out of selecting the perfect ironing temperature&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy-Fold Ironing Board: Folds up and down to allow for both vertical and horizontal ironing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Garment Hanger with Clips: Securely holds garments in place while steaming&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Liter Water Tank: Heats in 3 minutes or less to provide up to 30 minutes of continuous steaming per tank filling&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Burn Prevention Safety Cap: Prevents opening the water tank when there is hot steam or water inside that can cause skin burns&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Long 6-ft Cord: Makes it easy to plug in the unit from any room in your home without the need of an extension cord&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power: AC 120V, 60Hz, 1600W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Water Tank Capacity: 1L&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steam Time: Up to 30 minutes per tank refill&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Cord Length: 6ft&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT’S IN THE BOX&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 – Hanger Hook&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 – Clothes Hanger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3 – Connecting Rod&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4 – Telescopic Poles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5 – Iron Holder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6 – Iron/Steamer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;7 – Ironing Board&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;8 – Ironing Board Cover&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;9 – Fabric Brush&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;10 – Measuring Cup&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;11 – Funnel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;12 – Unit Body with Water Tank&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT WARRANTY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPureSteam Duo is backed by Pure Enrichment’s industry-leading 5 Year Warranty so your satisfaction is guaranteed.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'PureSteam Duo Iron &amp; Pressurized Garment Steamer', 'PureSteam Duo Iron &amp; Pressurized Garment Steamer', 'PureSteam Duo Iron &amp; Pressurized Garment Steamer'),
(10511, 1, 'Totem 58 Recycler Waste Separation and Recycling Unit 15-gallon Graphite', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TOTEM 58 RECYCLER WASTE SEPARATION &amp;amp; RECYCLING UNIT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Totem 58 is the perfect solution for households that need flexibility to split out their various types of recycling and waste while still keeping it all housed in one stylish unit.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES &amp;amp; BENEFITS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Totem range is the ultimate in home recycling and waste disposal, letting you house all your bags and bins in one stylish unit. From food waste to paper, glass, plastic or whatever you want to recycle there are plenty of handy drawers and compartments to keep it all separate. The range includes a variety of sizes and colors each with varying features, so you can find the best fit for your home and all come with a 10-year guarantee.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The versatile Totem 58 recycling separation bin offers several options for those who recycle, at the top there\'s space for two different recycling compartments with removable inner buckets and the bottom drawer comes with a divider so you can separate your recycling even further if required.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Each compartment is removable with liner-retaining holes and breather vents plus each takes custom-fit liners or standard bin liners.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Like other Totem products in the range, it also has a fingerprint-proof stainless-steel lid with an odor filter and a powder-coated steel body.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Total capacity: 58L (15.3 US Gallons).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Food waste caddy available separately&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Totem 58 Recycler Waste Separation &amp; Recycling Unit, 15-gallon, Graphite', 'Totem 58 Recycler Waste Separation &amp; Recycling Unit, 15-gallon, Graphite', 'Totem 58 Recycler Waste Separation &amp; Recycling Unit, 15-gallon, Graphite'),
(10512, 1, 'Totem 60 Recycler Waste Separation &amp; Recycling Unit, 16-gallon, Silver', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JOSEPH JOSEPH INTELLIGENT WASTE TOTEM KITCHEN TRASH CAN AND RECYCLE BIN UNIT WITH COMPOST BIN STAINLESS STEEL, 16-GALLON, SILVER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Totem 60 is the perfect solution for households wanting to combine their waste and recycling in one place, including a food caddy, a 36 liter (9.5 US gallon) general waste compartment and a multi-purpose recycling drawer.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES &amp;amp; BENEFITS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Totem range is the ultimate in home recycling and waste disposal, letting you house all your bags and bins in one stylish unit. From food waste to paper, glass, plastic or whatever you want to recycle there are plenty of handy drawers and compartments to keep it all separate. The range includes a variety of sizes and colors each with varying features, so you can find the best fit for your home and all come with a 10-year guarantee.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The highly flexible Totem 60 recycling separation bin features a removable food caddy for all your food waste, a 36 litre (9.5 US gallon) general waste compartment at the top which has a removable inner bucket and a multi-purpose drawer with a removable divider- so you can choose exactly how you want to separate your waste and recycling.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The inner bucket is removable, takes custom-fit liners and features liner-retaining holes, breather vents, and carrier bag hooks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The versatile food caddy can be stored on the kitchen counter, in the general waste compartment or in the multi-purpose drawer.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;It also has a fingerprint-proof stainless steel lid with odor filter and a powder-coated steel body.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KEY FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Food waste caddy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in odor filter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removeable drawer bucket&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removeable inner bucket&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Breather holes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Carrier bag hooks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CARE AND USE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 80 x 40 x 30 cm (31¼ x 15¾ x 11¾ inches)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 10.85 Kg&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Finger Print Proof: Stainless steel lid&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Designed By: Pearson Lloyd&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Totem 60 Recycler Waste Separation &amp; Recycling Unit, 16-gallon, Silver', 'Totem 60 Recycler Waste Separation &amp; Recycling Unit, 16-gallon, Silver', 'Totem 60 Recycler Waste Separation &amp; Recycling Unit, 16-gallon, Silver'),
(10513, 1, 'EarlySense Percept - Contact-Free, Clinically-Proven Fertility Tracker', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EARLYSENSE PERCEPT - CONTACT-FREE, CLINICALLY-PROVEN FERTILITY TRACKER&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTRACKS OVULATION, MENSTRUAL CYCLE, SLEEP PATTERNS AND RELAXATION LEVELS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CONTACT-FREE DEVICE: Earlysense Percept is the first contact-free fertility monitor that accurately pinpoints your dates of ovulation, fertility window, and period by monitoring physiological signals including heart rate and breathing. FDA registered.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;FERTILITY TRACKING: Receive an accurate 6-day fertility window. The Percept sensor detects your body\'s natural, physical signals using clinically-proven technology which is translated into fertility data and instantly sent to the app via Bluetooth.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;PERIOD AND OVULATION: Percept predicts your next period start date and ovulation date so you and your partner can plan ahead. Real-time adjustments based on your body\'s changing signals allow for prediction accuracy over time.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SLEEP, STRESS &amp;amp; VITALS MONITORING: This fertility monitor listens to what your body is saying by monitoring and analyzing sleep quality, stress level, heart rate and breathing levels to help predict your upcoming period and ovulation.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;DAILY TIPS: Receive valuable daily tips on fertility, health, sex and more to help you conceive faster. Percept allows you to understand your body without disrupting your day to day life.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT’S IN THE BOX:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Contact-Free Sensor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AC Power Supply&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick Setup Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Limited Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Including 2 year warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;*Note: Phone is not included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MEET PERCEPT&lt;br /&gt;\r\nClinically proven accuracy.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPercept monitors vital signs while you sleep in order to predict your ovulation, period, sleep quality, and relaxation levels. Using a technology originally developed for hospitals, Percept is clinically proven to predict ovulation more accurately than most standard methods.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Non-wearable, stress-free fertility tracking.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWho wants to pee on a stick or constantly take their temperature? When it comes to fertility tracking, the easier the better. Let EarlySense Percept take the hassle out of fertility tracking with an under-the-mattress sensor that captures your body\'s signals without interrupting your day to day life. Percept listens to what your body is saying - the language it speaks in, the signals that it sends - and then delivers simple and valuable information to the app, in real time. Percept allows you to understand your body in order to conceive faster.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What makes Percept different?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPercept is the world’s first contact-free, clinically-proven fertility tracker. Because heart rate is directly related with temperature during a woman\'s cycle, Percept can accurately predict ovulation dates by monitoring heart rate and other body signals while you sleep. Most period tracking apps are based only on your cycle history. Percept monitors your body\'s most subtle signals in real time in order to aid conception.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Seamless Fertility Tracking&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nLet Percept track your fertility with nothing to wear and no tasks to remember. The sensor pinpoints your next period, ovulation dates, and 6-day fertility window based on your body\'s signals including heart rate and breathing.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Accurate Period Prediction&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nYour body is constantly changing and Percept changes with it. It predicts your period start date with real-time adjustments based on your body\'s signals, to learn your natural cycle. Percept allows you to plan ahead with accurate menstrual cycle predictions for up to 3 months and maintains cycle history for up to 12 months.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stress, &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sleep&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; and Vitals Monitoring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPercept monitors and analyzes your sleep quality, stress level, heart rate and breathing rate in real-time. Understanding and taking control of your sleep and stress is critical to your general health and fertility.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Daily Tips&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nReceive valuable tips on fertility, health, sex and more. These daily tips help give you an understanding of your body which is key to being in control of your fertility and conceiving faster.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HOW PERCEPT WORKS&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Slide Under Mattress&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe sleek, contact-free design is small, thin and unnoticeable when placed under a mattress. The sensor recognizes your body\'s natural signals all while you soundly sleep - out of sight, out of mind.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Connect to Percept App&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe sensor detects your body\'s signals while you sleep and uses that to accurately predict your next period and fertility window. The signals are sent to the Percept App via Bluetooth.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;3. Start &lt;strong&gt;Tracking&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nYour period and fertility window predictions become more accurate every night with Percept\'s artificial intelligence algorithms.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Take Control of Your Fertility and Conceive Faster&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPercept provides the data you need at your fingertips, when you need it, without disrupting your life. No more peeing, patches or temperature-taking needed.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'EarlySense Percept - Contact-Free, Clinically-Proven Fertility Tracker', 'EarlySense Percept - Contact-Free, Clinically-Proven Fertility Tracker', 'EarlySense Percept - Contact-Free, Clinically-Proven Fertility Tracker'),
(10515, 1, 'TomTom Spark 3 Cardio GPS Fitness Watch with Heart Rate and Music', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TOMTOM SPARK 3 CARDIO + MUSIC BLACK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTrain with over 500 songs and your heart rate on your wrist&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;24/7 activity tracking&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;GPS tracking&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multisport mode&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Route exploration&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fitness Age&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Personalized Workouts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in heart rate monitor*&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Over 500 songs of music storage**&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bluetooth headphones included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery lifetime: Activity tracking: up to 3 weeks, GPS: up to 11 hours, GPS + Heart Rate + Music: up to 5 hours&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Waterproofing: 40 m / 130 feet (5 ATM)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Display size: .87 x .98 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Activity Measurements: Steps, active minutes, distance, calories burned and sleep&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Storage: 3 GB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IN THE BOX&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;TomTom Spark 3 Cardio + Music - Black&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;TomTom Sports Bluetooth Headphones&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;TomTom Watch Charging Cable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;User Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Multisport Modes: Track all your workouts. Run. Bike. Swim. Treadmill. Gym. Indoor Cycling and more.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in Heart Rate Monitor: See your heart rate on your wrist with the built-in heart rate monitor. No chest strap needed.*&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Over 500 Songs of Music Storage (3 GB): Work out with music, not with your phone.**&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;GPS Tracking: Time. Distance. Speed. Pace. Routes. Live stats, on the go.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;24/7 Activity Tracking: Capture your heart rate, steps, active minutes, and calories burned throughout the day. &lt;em&gt;(1)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Route Exploration: Find your way back to the start and explore new routes. &lt;em&gt;(2)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Indoor Training Mode: Track your performance on the treadmill or in the gym.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Perfect Fit: Select large or small watch straps to ensure the perfect fit for your wrist.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Customizable Straps: Switch watch straps to match your outfit or fit your mood.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wireless Syncing: Sync your watch wirelessly with your favorite workout apps.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Water Resistant to 40 m (5 ATM): Get wet. Dive in the pool and work out in all weather conditions.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Race Mode: Select one of your past workouts to race against.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Interval Training: Improve speed and fitness with custom work-rest sessions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ultra-Slim Design: Notice your watch only when you want to.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Social sharing: Celebrate your success with friends. Share your workouts online.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;QuickGPS: Get started faster with quicker GPS reception.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One-Button Control: Navigate easily through menus with a single button.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Long Battery Life: Get up to 11 hours of battery lifetime when using GPS. &lt;em&gt;(3)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic sleep tracking: Track your sleep patterns and know if you\'re getting the sleep you need.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5 Heart Rate Training Zones: Training in 5 different heart rate zones helps you see results faster.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Audio Performance Feedback: Push yourself with audio feedback on your performance.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;1. Heart rate is captured at regular intervals and is not measured continuously.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Be confident that you will find your way back home. Upload trails to your watch to discover new routes.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. Battery life can be impacted by using the heart rate monitoring or the music player.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'TomTom Spark 3 Cardio GPS Fitness Watch with Heart Rate and Music', 'TomTom Spark 3 Cardio GPS Fitness Watch with Heart Rate and Music', 'TomTom Spark 3 Cardio GPS Fitness Watch with Heart Rate and Music');
