(10517, 1, 'TomTom GO 620 GPS Navigator with Wifi-Connectivity', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TOMTOM GO 620 - SMARTER AND FASTER THAN EVER.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMeet the TomTom GO 620 - the smarter, faster, better connected GPS. Wi-Fi® connectivity lets you update without a computer. Voice controlled hands-free calling and smartphone messages offer connectivity with safety. With TomTom MyDrive, plan routes on your phone and the GPS is ready when you get in the car. Free lifetime maps*, traffic, and safety camera updates are all included - even get alerts for average speed zones. 6 inch screen size.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lifetime Maps (World)*&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;MyDrive Cloud App&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lifetime TomTom Trafffic via Smartphone&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Advanced Lane Guidance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hands-free calling&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Updates via Wi-Fi&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smartphone messages&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible with Siri and Google Now™&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Active magnetic mount&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IN THE BOX&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;GO 620&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Active magnetic mount&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;USB Cable &amp;amp; Car Charger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Documentation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery lifetime: Up to 1 hour&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vehicle mount: Active magnetic mount&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smartphone Connected: Connect to TomTom Services via Bluetooth® on your smartphone&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Internal memory: 16 GB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in Wi-Fi: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Updates via Wi-Fi:&lt;/strong&gt; Get the latest maps and software for your TomTom GO via built-in Wi-Fi. No computer needed. Your GPS device will notify you when new updates are available - simply connect to your preferred Wi-Fi network and choose what to install from the menu.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Smartphone Messages:&lt;/strong&gt; Hear text messages from your smartphone safely, with your hands on the wheel and your eyes on the road. Let your TomTom GO read them out for you or simply call contacts who message you via hands-free calling. All while the phone stays in your pocket.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compatible with Siri and Google Now:&lt;/strong&gt; Activate and talk to Siri or Google Now™ by tapping a button on your TomTom GO and using its built-in microphone. Get full access to your personal assistant with your phone safely tucked away in your bag or pocket saving battery life.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Destination Prediction:&lt;/strong&gt; TomTom GO learns your driving habits and predicts when you\'re likely to drive to frequent destinations saved in My Places. Thanks to smart learning, the more you drive with it the more accurate its predictions will become.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hands-free calling:&lt;/strong&gt; Your TomTom GO\'s speaker and microphone are designed for high-quality, hands-free calls in the car. Simply connect your phone via Bluetooth. You\'ll clearly see who\'s calling on your GPS device\'s screen. Your phone stays safely away saving battery.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performance Upgraded:&lt;/strong&gt; Start-up, destinations searches, route calculation - it\'s all faster with TomTom GO\'s upgraded processor. Each tap, swipe, or voice command will be registered instantly so you can enjoy all the navigation you need with zero hassle.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lifetime TomTom Traffic: &lt;/strong&gt;Insanely accurate traffic information enables your TomTom GO to intelligently plan routes around traffic. With real-time updates from millions of drivers, it\'s like having a huge network of friends helping you choose the best route to take.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lifetime World Maps:&lt;/strong&gt; Download and update maps from around the world at no extra cost for the life of your TomTom GO. Choose the best map for your trip from North America, through Europe and Africa, all the way to Australia and New Zealand. We\'ve got you covered.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lifetime Safety Cameras:&lt;/strong&gt; Advance warnings on your TomTom GO will let you know whenever you\'re approaching a fixed, mobile or average speed camera, and remind you of the speed limit. You can receive updated safety camera locations free of charge for the lifetime of your device.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;TomTom MyDrive: Plan routes, check live traffic, and save favorites – anytime, anywhere – from your smartphone, tablet, or PC. Your TomTom GO will pick up any destinations or favorites set on MyDrive as soon as it powers on in the car and connects to your smartphone.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Active Magnetic Mount: &lt;/strong&gt;The unique magnetic mount makes it easy to install your TomTom GO every time you drive. You can dock or undock your GPS device in a second with one hand. Find the perfect spot in your car by adjusting the mount for either windshield or dashboard use.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Voice Control: &lt;/strong&gt;Control your TomTom GO with the power of your voice. Say &quot;Hello TomTom&quot; to activate voice control and quickly set your next destination, get an alternate route, or adjust settings. Focus on driving while your TomTom GO takes care of the rest.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TomTom Services via Smartphone: &lt;/strong&gt;Activate live services like traffic by connecting to your smartphone via the TomTom MyDrive app. Your TomTom GO uses your smartphone\'s data connection to provide you with real-time traffic, safety camera updates, and MyDrive content. On average, less than 10 MB of data per month is used.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'TomTom GO 620 GPS Navigator with Wifi-Connectivity', 'TomTom GO 620 GPS Navigator with Wifi-Connectivity', 'TomTom GO 620 GPS Navigator with Wifi-Connectivity'),
(10516, 1, 'TomTom Spark 3 Cardio GPS Fitness Watch with Heart Rate', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TOMTOM SPARK 3 CARDIO BLACK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTrain to the beat of your heart on your wrist&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;24/7 activity tracking&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;GPS tracking&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multisport mode&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Route exploration&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fitness Age&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Personalized Workouts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in heart rate monitor*&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IN THE BOX&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;TomTom Spark 3 Cardio - Black&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;TomTom Watch Charging Cable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;User Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery lifetime: Activity tracking: up to 3 weeks, GPS: up to 11 hours, GPS + Heart Rate: up to 9 hours&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Waterproofing: 40 m / 130 feet (5 ATM)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Display size: .87 x .98 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Activity Measurements: Steps, active minutes, distance, calories burned and sleep&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Running: Tracks heart rate, speed, pace, distance, calories burnt, duration, breadcrumb trail, and preloaded trails&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Multisport Modes: Track all your workouts. Run. Bike. Swim. Treadmill. Gym. Indoor Cycling and more.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in Heart Rate Monitor: See your heart rate on your wrist with the built-in heart rate monitor. No chest strap needed.*&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;GPS Tracking: Time. Distance. Speed. Pace. Routes. Live stats, on the go.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;24/7 Activity Tracking: Capture your heart rate, steps, active minutes, and calories burned throughout the day.&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;(1)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Route Exploration: Find your way back to the start and explore new routes. &lt;em&gt;(2)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Indoor Training Mode: Track your performance on the treadmill or in the gym.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Perfect Fit: Select large or small watch straps to ensure the perfect fit for your wrist.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Customizable Straps: Switch watch straps to match your outfit or fit your mood.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wireless Syncing: Sync your watch wirelessly with your favorite workout apps.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Water Resistant to 40 m (5 ATM): Get wet. Dive in the pool and work out in all weather conditions.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Race Mode: Select one of your past workouts to race against.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Interval Training: Improve speed and fitness with custom work-rest sessions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ultra-Slim Design: Notice your watch only when you want to.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Social sharing: Celebrate your success with friends. Share your workouts online.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;QuickGPS: Get started faster with quicker GPS reception.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One-Button Control: Navigate easily through menus with a single button.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Long Battery Life: Get up to 11 hours of battery lifetime when using GPS. &lt;em&gt;(3)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic sleep tracking: Track your sleep patterns and know if you\'re getting the sleep you need.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5 Heart Rate Training Zones: Training in 5 different heart rate zones helps you see results faster.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;----&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------&lt;/span&gt;----&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;1. Heart rate is captured at regular intervals and is not measured continuously.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Be confident that you will find your way back home. Upload trails to your watch to discover new routes.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. Battery life can be impacted by using the heart rate monitoring or the music player.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'TomTom Spark 3 Cardio GPS Fitness Watch with Heart Rate', 'TomTom Spark 3 Cardio GPS Fitness Watch with Heart Rate', 'TomTom Spark 3 Multi Sport GPS Fitness Watch with Heart Rate'),
(10254, 1, 'TRX Suspension Trainer TRX HOME-2 (BEST SELLER)', '&lt;p&gt;Personalize your training. Using our newest TRX Suspension Trainer, your own body weight, and our personalized training app, TRX is ready to stay with you every step of the way. Choose from a wide variety of workouts from world-class coaches and get the results you want.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy setup in less than 60 seconds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Progress any exercise using only your bodyweight&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Get lean muscle and burn fat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Be stronger from the core out&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Build greater flexibility, mobility and stability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Increase your body\'s durability and endurance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OUR NEWEST SUSPENSION TRAINER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFeaturing upgraded webbing and adjusters, as well as new adjustable foot cradles, padding, and handles for a more versatile and comfortable experience.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PERSONALIZED TRAINING APP&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nChoose from dozens of workouts specific to your goals and lifestyle and listen or view on-screen as we coach you every step of the way. You can even schedule workouts and track your progress over time.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ALL CORE ALL THE TIME&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nStabilizing your body weight with TRX Suspension Training constantly challenges your core while engaging a broad range of muscle groups all at once, including your heart.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S INCLUDED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWorkout anywhere - home or outdoors - with these included anchors and accessories.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Comes with the following equipment:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;NEW TRX HOME2 SUSPENSION TRAINER&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;FREE ONE-YEAR SUBSCRIPTION TO THE TRX APP&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;DOOR ANCHOR&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SUSPENSION ANCHOR&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;MESH CARRY BAG&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PREMIUM CONSTRUCTION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Barrel lock adjusters for quick transitions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Padded handle straps for comfort&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Soft, but durable foam handles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable foot cradles for diverse workouts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EXCLUSIVE AT TRX&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTRXtraining.com is the only place for our latest products, a free one-year app subscription with signature product purchase, risk-free trial and more.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;TRX CONCIERGE&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;FREE ONE-YEAR APP SUBSCRIPTION&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5 YEAR WARRANTY&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'TRX Suspension Trainer TRX HOME-2, BEST SELLER', 'TRX Suspension Trainer TRX HOME-2, BEST SELLER', 'TRX Suspension Trainer TRX HOME-2, BEST SELLER'),
(10518, 1, 'Frigidaire 30 in. 1.6 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Stainless Steel', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FRIGIDAIRE 30 IN. 1.6 CU. FT. OVER THE RANGE MICROWAVE IN STAINLESS STEEL&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cooktop LED lighting gives you a clear view of your cooktop&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Features easy-to-use one-touch buttons&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra-large microwave will hold almost any size dish&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This extra-large and sleek Frigidaire 1.6 cu. ft. Over-the-Range Stainless Steel Microwave oven features Auto-Reheat and One-Touch options so you can warm up any meal with a single touch. The Fits-More capacity allows it to hold almost any dish. The ventilation with Auto-Start Heat Sensor Fan features includes 2 fan speeds that move up to 300 cu. ft. of air per minute and removable dishwasher-safe filters.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1.6 cu. ft. Extra-Large capacity microwave provides ample cooking space and will hold almost any dish - even a 13 in. x 9 in. baking dish&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1,000-Watt of cooking power and 9 power levels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The built in 2-Speed 105/220 CFM ventilating system doubles as a convertible hood to remove smoke, steam and odors&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ready-Select Controls allow you to easily select options with the touch of a button&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwaves feature easy-to-use one-touch buttons so you can cook baked potatoes, popcorn or even add 30 seconds with the touch of a button&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi-Stage Cooking option allows you to program power levels and cooking times in advance, so you can program the microwave all at once to defrost, cook and keep a meal warm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra-Large 13-1/2 in. Dia Glass Turntable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LED interior microwave light stays on while your dish cooks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 Speed Ventilation Over-The-Range microwave doubles as a hood with Auto-start Heat Sensor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher-Safe vent filter and charcoal vent filters (ductless, recirculating Installation) remove grease and impurities from the air&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Limited 1-Year Warranty nationwide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity of Microwave (cu. ft.): 1.6&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Front to Back Depth (in.): 14&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Height (in.): 17&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Left to Right Width (in.): 30&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth With Door(s) Open 90 Degrees (In.): 25.25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 15.25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 16.40&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 29.875&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Appliance Type: Over the Range Microwave&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish: Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish Family: Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Controls Location: Side Controls&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Swing/Style: Right to Left Swing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust Fan Speeds: 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust Maximum CFM: 220&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Light Source: LED&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Door Release: Pull&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Features: Charcoal Filter,Clock,Cooking Light,Cooktop Lighting,Interior Light,Nightlight,Removable Filter,Timer,Turntable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Settings: Defrost&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Size: Medium&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of One-Touch Settings: 13&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Power Levels: 9&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 52.6lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Returnable: Non-Returnable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vent Fan Location: Back&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vent Type: Convertible&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wattage (watts): 1000 W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Frigidaire 30 in. 1.6 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Stainless Steel', 'Frigidaire 30 in. 1.6 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Stainless Steel', 'Frigidaire 30 in. 1.6 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Stainless Steel'),
(10519, 1, 'Samsung 30 in. W 1.8 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Stainless Steel with Sensor Cooking', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SAMSUNG 30 IN. W 1.8 CU. FT. OVER THE RANGE MICROWAVE IN STAINLESS STEEL WITH SENSOR COOKING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1,000 watts of cooking power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sensor cook gives optimal heated results every time&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Digital, blue LED display complements any kitchen décor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Samsung over-the-range microwave with sensor cooking makes it easy to heat and is simple to clean. The Ceramic Enamel Interior lets you effortlessly remove grease and oil and is more scratch resistant than stainless steel. Plus, 4 speeds, 9 cooking presets, and more.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSimple Clean Filter – Is easy to eject and helps you remember to clean the filter&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1.8 cu. ft. Capacity – Accommodates an assortment of plates, bowls, mugs and pans&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1000 Watts of Power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;400 CFM Ventilation System – Quickly and quietly eliminates steam, fumes and odors from the kitchen&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;10 Power Levels – Helps deliver more precise cooking&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two-Stage Programmable Cooking&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto Defrost/Sensor Reheat – Preset to specific times and temperatures for various foods&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto Cook&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Chrome Rack&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Clock (12 hr/24 hr) – Has daylight savings time adjustment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Kitchen Timer – Built in so you can keep track of your cooking progress&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;End Signal – Alerts you again if your food is ready and you haven\'t opened the door yet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Interior Light – Halogen (1)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cooktop Lighting – Halogen: High, Low, Off&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color Options – Also available in Black Stainless, White, and Black&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity of Microwave (cu. ft.): 1.8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Front to Back Depth (in.): 18&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Height (in.): 17&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Left to Right Width (in.): 30&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth With Door(s) Open 90 Degrees (In.): 17&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 17.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 16.9&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 29.9&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Appliance Type: Over the Range Microwave&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish: Stainless&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish Family: Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Controls Location: Side Controls&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Swing/Style: Right to Left Swing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust Fan Speeds: 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust Maximum CFM: 400&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Light Source: Halogen&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Door Release: Pull&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Features: Charcoal Filter,Clock,Cooking Light,Cooktop Lighting,Interior Light,Nightlight,One Touch Cooking,Removable Filter,Safety Lock,Turntable,Turntable On/Off Option&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Settings: Defrost,Sensor Cook&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Size: Medium&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of One-Touch Settings: 12&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Power Levels: 10&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 56lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Returnable: Non-Returnable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vent Fan Location: Back&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vent Type: Convertible&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wattage (watts): 1000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Samsung 30 in. W 1.8 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Stainless Steel with Sensor Cooking', 'Samsung 30 in. W 1.8 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Stainless Steel with Sensor Cooking', 'Samsung 30 in. W 1.8 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Stainless Steel with Sensor Cooking'),
(10520, 1, 'Whirlpool 30 in. W 1.9 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave with Sensor Cooking', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHIRLPOOL 30 IN. W 1.9 CU. FT. OVER THE RANGE MICROWAVE IN FINGERPRINT RESISTANT STAINLESS STEEL WITH SENSOR COOKING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quickly clean up spills with our CLEANRELEASE non-stick interior&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Clear up cooktop space with steam cooking in the microwave&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Get automatically adjusted cook times with sensor cooking&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This microwave has convenient features that are easy to use no matter who\'s doing the cooking. Our sensor cooking microwave automatically adjusts cooking times so there\'s no need to guess. Free up cooktop space by steaming foods in the microwave and get quick cleanup with a CLEANRELEASE non-stick interior. From sides to snacks, fit cooking into any schedule.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCalifornia residents: see&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Proposition 65 information&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Spacious 1.9 cu. ft. capacity provides the room you need for reheating&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1000-Watt of cooking power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;300 CFM motor class matches the right amount of ventilation to the dish being prepared and quickly get rid of cooking odors with 3 different fan speed settings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Navigate through cooking modes and options with electronic touch controls that are as easy to use as they are to clean&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sensor Cooking automatically tracks the cooking progress of your food and adjusts the cook time as needed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steam Cooking option clears up cooktop space by steaming foods like rice, vegetables and fish right in the microwave (steam accessory available to purchase separately)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CLEANRELEASE non-stick interior lets you quickly clean up spills with a damp wipe, no special cleaning solutions required&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Choose whether the turntable rotates or not to accommodate a wide range of dish sizes with the Turntable On/Off Option&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher-safe turntable plate to you can clean up spills on the turntable by simply putting it in the dishwasher&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Keep an eye on what\'s cooking below the microwave or keep a nightlight on in the kitchen with adjustable cooktop lighting&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hidden Vent provides a clean look&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cooking Rack accommodates multiple dishes at once for reheating&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quickly set the microwave timer to 30 seconds or add it to already in-progress cooking time with the touch of a button&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Get just the right amount of heat and time, whether you\'re cooking or defrosting, with specific microwave preset options&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Resist fingerprints and smudges with steel that easily wipes clean. Available in Black Stainless and Stainless Steel colors&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity of Microwave (cu. ft.): 1.9&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Front to Back Depth (in.): 14&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Height (in.): 17.13&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Left to Right Width (in.): 30&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth With Door(s) Open 90 Degrees (In.): 39.38&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 15.94 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 17.13 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 29.94 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Appliance Type: Over the Range Microwave&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish: Fingerprint Resistant Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish Family: Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Controls Location: Side Controls&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Swing/Style: Right to Left Swing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust Fan Speeds: 3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust Maximum CFM: 300&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Light Source: Incandescent&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Door Release: Pull&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Features: Clock,Nightlight,Timer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Settings: Control Lock,Cook/Start,Defrost,Fresh Vegetable,Frozen Entree,Keep Warm,Popcorn,Potato,Reheat,Steam Cook&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Size: Medium&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of One-Touch Settings: 12&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Power Levels: 10&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 63 lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Returnable: Non-Returnable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vent Fan Location: Back&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vent Type: Convertible&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wattage (watts): 1000 W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Whirlpool 30 in. W 1.9 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave with Sensor Cooking', 'Whirlpool 30 in. W 1.9 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave with Sensor Cooking', 'Whirlpool 30 in. W 1.9 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave with Sensor Cooking'),
(10521, 1, 'GE 1.9 cu. ft. Over-the-Range Sensor Microwave Oven in Stainless Steel', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GE 1.9 CU. FT. OVER-THE-RANGE SENSOR MICROWAVE OVEN IN STAINLESS STEEL&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1.9 cu. ft. capacity - 1000 Watts (IEC-705 test procedure)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy clean enamel interior - Makes cleaning spills a snap&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Melt feature - Worry-free melting of butter, chocolate and cheese&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Your GE 1.9 cu. ft. Over the Range Sensor Microwave Oven in Stainless Steel has 1000-Watt of power. Four-speed with boost 400-CFM venting fan system quickly removes smoke, steam and odors from the cooktop to keep kitchen air fresh and clean. Weight and time defrost lets you simply enter the weight of the food, and the oven automatically sets the optimal defrosting time and power level or set your desired time for defrosting. Easy clean with steam lets you clean messes inside the microwave and is easy to wipe away after steam loosens food grime. GE appliances provide up-to-date technology and exceptional quality to simplify the way you live. With a timeless appearance, this family of appliances is ideal for your family. And, coming from one of the most trusted names in America, you know that this entire selection of appliances is as advanced as it is practical.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1.9 cu. ft. capacity accommodates small casserole dishes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1,000-Watt of cooking power and 10 cooking levels for boiling, reheating and defrosting&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The built-in 4-speed, 400 CFM venting system helps enhance kitchen air quality by removing smoke, steam and odors from your cooktop&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electronic controls with graphic display make this microwave oven easy to use&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sensor cooking automatically sets the optimal time and power level&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy Clean enamel interior for easier cleanup of spills&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Turntable on/off is ideal for even cooking results or for accommodating oversized dishes that may not fully rotate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cooktop lighting provides illumination above the range with 2 brightness settings, including a night-light option&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4 fan-speed settings let you choose the right amount of ventilation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave comes with a 1 year limited warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Click Here for details on the services included with Delivery &amp;amp; Basic Hook-up and Installation options for this product&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity of Microwave (cu. ft.): 1.9&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Front to Back Depth (in.): 12&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Height (in.): 16.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Left to Right Width (in.): 29.75&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth With Door(s) Open 90 Degrees (In.): 15.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 15.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 16.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 29.75&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Appliance Type: Over the Range Microwave&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish: Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish Family: Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Controls Location: Side Controls&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Swing/Style: Right to Left Swing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust Fan Speeds: 4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust Maximum CFM: 400&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Light Source: Incandescent&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Door Release: Pull&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Features: Clock,Cooking Light,Cooktop Lighting,Interior Light,Turntable On/Off Option&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Settings: Defrost,Sensor Cook&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Size: Medium&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of One-Touch Settings: 9&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Power Levels: 10&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 62lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Returnable: Non-Returnable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vent Fan Location: Back&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vent Type: External&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wattage (watts): 1000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'GE 1.9 cu. ft. Over-the-Range Sensor Microwave Oven in Stainless Steel', 'GE 1.9 cu. ft. Over-the-Range Sensor Microwave Oven in Stainless Steel', 'GE 1.9 cu. ft. Over-the-Range Sensor Microwave Oven in Stainless Steel'),
(10522, 1, 'KitchenAid 30 in. 2.0 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Stainless Steel with Sensor Cooking', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KITCHENAID 30 IN. 2.0 CU. FT. OVER THE RANGE MICROWAVE IN STAINLESS STEEL WITH SENSOR COOKING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sensor functions automatically adjust time and power needed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cookshield finish makes it easy to clean inside without chemicals&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cook favorites quickly and thoroughly with high 1000W power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This high power, 1000-Watt microwave oven features 4 sensor functions to assist you in the kitchen by automatically adjusting the time needed to cook, reheat or defrost without guesswork about power levels or cooking times. The interior\'s CookShield Finish wipes clean without harsh chemicals so it looks brighter longer while the exterior is a bold blend of professionally-inspired styling with sleek touches for the home.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCalifornia residents: see&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Proposition 65 information&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2.0 Cu. Ft. Capacity is large enough to comfortably fit different containers and work as a complement to your conventional oven&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sensor Functions automatically adjust the time needed to cook, reheat or defrost for deliciously even cooking without guesswork about power levels or cooking times&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-speed, 300 CFM venting system with charcoal odor filter helps keep excessive steam and cooking smells out of your kitchen&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electronic touch controls with vacuum fluorescent display (VFD) make it simple to interact with and control the microwave&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sensor Steam/Simmer Cook Cycle allows for precise steaming or simmering based on the food type and doneness level selected&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Keep Warm function operates at 10% cooking power to keep cooked foods warm until they\'re ready to be served&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cookshield Finish makes it easy to wipe the interior of the microwave clean so it looks clean and bright longer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stoppable Turntable cooks food evenly by continually rotating throughout the cooking cycle. The turntable can be stopped if, for example, the shape of the cooking dish blocks its rotation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cook your favorite foods quickly and thoroughly with high 1000-Watt power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;A bold blend of professionally-inspired styling with sleek touches for the home, this stunning microwave oven features Satin Textured Handles, Precision Touch Controls, the KitchenAid Brand Badge and KitchenAid Brand Medallion&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity of Microwave (cu. ft.): 2.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Front to Back Depth (in.): 12&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Height (in.): 17.13&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Left to Right Width (in.): 30&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth With Door(s) Open 90 Degrees (In.): 40.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 16.25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 17.25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 30&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Appliance Type: Over the Range Microwave&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish: Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish Family: Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Controls Location: Side Controls&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Swing/Style: Right to Left Swing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust Fan Speeds: 3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust Maximum CFM: 300&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Light Source: Halogen&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Door Release: Pull&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Features: Charcoal Filter,Clock,Cooking Light,Microwave Rack,Nightlight,One Touch Cooking,Removable Filter,Turntable,Turntable On/Off Option&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Settings: Defrost,Sensor Cook,Steam Cook&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Size: Large&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of One-Touch Settings: 9&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Power Levels: 10&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 67.1lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Returnable: Non-Returnable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vent Fan Location: Back&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vent Type: Convertible&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wattage (watts): 1000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: Limited 1-year /10-year limited parts warranty on select components&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'KitchenAid 30 in. 2.0 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Stainless Steel with Sensor Cooking', 'KitchenAid 30 in. 2.0 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Stainless Steel with Sensor Cooking', 'KitchenAid 30 in. 2.0 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Stainless Steel with Sensor Cooking'),
(10523, 1, 'Whirlpool 30 in. W 1.7 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave Electronic Touch Controls', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHIRLPOOL 30 IN. W 1.7 CU. FT. OVER THE RANGE MICROWAVE IN STAINLESS STEEL WITH ELECTRONIC TOUCH CONTROLS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThis microwave has convenient features that are easy to use no matter who\'s doing the cooking. Our microwave with a turntable accommodates various dish sizes while microwave presets deliver the right amount of time and heat. Plus, electronic touch controls are easy to use and clean. From sides to snacks, enjoy the flexibility of fitting cooking into any schedule.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Spacious 1.7 cu. ft. capacity provides the room you need for reheating&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1000-Watt of cooking power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;300 CFM motor class matches the right amount of ventilation to the dish being prepared and quickly get rid of cooking odors with 2 different fan speed settings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Navigate through cooking modes and options with electronic touch controls that are as easy to use as they are to clean&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Get just the right amount of heat and time, whether you\'re cooking or defrosting, with specific microwave preset options&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quickly set the microwave timer to 30 seconds or add it to already in-progress cooking time with the touch of a button&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher-safe turntable plate to you can clean up spills on the turntable by simply putting it in the dishwasher&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Keep an eye on what\'s cooking below the microwave or keep a nightlight on in the kitchen with adjustable cooktop lighting&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charcoal odor removing filter helps keep cooking smells from overpowering your kitchen&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Resist fingerprints and smudges with steel that easily wipes clean. Available in Black Stainless and Stainless Steel colors&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity of Microwave (cu. ft.): 1.7&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Front to Back Depth (in.): 14&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Height (in.): 17.13&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Left to Right Width (in.): 30&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth With Door(s) Open 90 Degrees (In.): 39.38&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 15.56 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 17.13 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 29.94 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Appliance Type: Over the Range Microwave&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish: Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish Family: Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Controls Location: Side Controls&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Swing/Style: Right to Left Swing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust Fan Speeds: 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust Maximum CFM: 300&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Light Source: Incandescent&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Door Release: Pull&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Features&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Clock,Interior Light,Nightlight,Timer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Settings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Add 30 Seconds,Control Lock,Cook Power,Cook Time,Cook/Start,Defrost,Pizza,Popcorn,Potato,Reheat,Soften/Melt&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Size: Medium&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of One-Touch Settings: 6&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Power Levels: 10&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 55.9 lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Returnable: Non-Returnable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vent Fan Location: Back&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vent Type: Convertible&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wattage (watts): 1000 W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: 1 year limited warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Whirlpool 30 in. W 1.7 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Stainless Steel with Electronic Touch Controls', 'Whirlpool 30 in. W 1.7 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Stainless Steel with Electronic Touch Controls', 'Whirlpool 30 in. W 1.7 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave Electronic Touch Controls'),
(10524, 1, 'Magic Chef 9.9 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Black', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MAGIC CHEF 9.9 CU. FT. TOP FREEZER REFRIGERATOR IN BLACK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;9.9 cu. ft. capacity is great for smaller places&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 glass fridge shelves and 1 slide-out freezer shelf&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Separate freezer compartment for all your frozen favorites&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Magic Chef 9.9 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator is the perfect in-between cooling machine -- more spacious than a mini but more compact than a regular household unit. It is a suitable appliance for smaller kitchens, breakrooms, office kitchenettes or anywhere with space constraints. It occupies a small footprint but offers numerous cold-storage options for foods and beverages, including a glass-covered crisper to keep produce fresh. It\'s equipped with two adjustable-height glass shelves in the refrigerator and one slide-out wire shelf in the freezer, with several other storage options built into the reversible doors.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable analog temperature control system offers different temperature settings, giving you great control over the interior temperature&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Glass refrigerator shelves provide for easy storage and easy cleaning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Clear produce crisper lets you easily identify contents&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;In-door can holder allows you to grab beverage cans with ease&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Clear door bins and bottle rack keep your condiments and larger bottles easily accessible&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Offers 2.6 cu. ft. of freezer space and 7.3 cu. ft. of fridge space&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Separate top freezer compartment for convenient frozen food storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic defrost for added convenience&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 reversible doors allow you to place the unit according to your space requirements&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fresh food section has an interior incandescent light&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty is 1 year parts and labor, 5 years compressor (part only)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;This item does not qualify for the Major Appliance Delivery &amp;amp; Haul Away or Installation Services&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth (Excluding Handles): 26.1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth (Including Handles): 26.1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth (Less Door): 22.98&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth With Door Open 90 Degrees (In): 50.98&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height to Top of Door Hinge: 59.8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height to Top of Refrigerator (in.): 59.8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 26.1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 59.8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 24&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Refrigerator Width (In.): 24&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Appliance Type: Top Freezer Refrigerator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity (cu. Ft.) - Freezer: 2.62&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity (cu. Ft.) - Fresh Food: 7.28&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity (cu. ft.) - Refrigerators: 9.9&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity (cu. ft.) - Total: 9.9&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color - Appliance Cabinet: Black&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color - Door Handle(s): Black&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish: Black&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish Family: Black&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Counter Depth (Yes/No): No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Defrost Type: Auto / Cycle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Finish: Smooth&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy Consumption (kWh/year): 329&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy Efficiency Tier Rating: Not CEE rated&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Freezer Door Type: Swing Door&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Freezer Features: Adjustable Leveling Legs,Adjustable Temperature Control,In-door Storage,Incandescent Light Type,Incandescent Light Type&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;General Features: Flat-back Design,Incandescent Light Type,Refrigerator Light,Two Door Design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ice Maker: None&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ice Maker Features: No Ice Maker&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ice/Water Dispenser: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Doors: 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Freezer Baskets/Bins: 0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Freezer Shelves: 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Fresh Food Shelves: 3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operational Features: Adjustable Temperature Control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 119.1lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Refrigeration Dispenser Features: No Dispenser&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Refrigerator Type: Freestanding&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Returnable: 90-Day&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shelf Material - Freezer: Wire&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shelf Material - Refrigerator: Glass&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Storage Features: Can Dispenser,Removable Shelves&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Temperature Control Type: Internal analog&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Water Filter Replacement Model#: No Water Filter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: 1 Year Parts and Labor 5 Years Compressor (Part Only)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Magic Chef 9.9 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Black', 'Magic Chef 9.9 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Black', 'Magic Chef 9.9 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Black');
