(10525, 1, 'Frigidaire Front Control Dishwasher in Stainless Steel', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FRIGIDAIRE FRONT CONTROL DISHWASHER IN STAINLESS STEEL&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ready-Select electronic controls allow for easy selection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UltraQuiet sound package (60 dBA) keeps the noise to a minimum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tall tub design with large capacity fits up to 14 place settings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This Frigidaire 24 in. Front Control Dishwasher features a large capacity, tall tub design with 14 place settings, allowing you to wash a large array of dishes at once. The three wash cycle options provide flexibility to select the type of cleaning that best suits your load, so you don\'t have to waste water and energy when washing smaller loads. Additionally, this quiet dishwasher operates at just 60 dBA and offers a no-heat dry option to help further conserve energy.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ready-Select electronic controls on front panel allow you to easily select options with the touch of a button&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UltraQuiet sound package (60 dBA) keeps noise to a minimum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Large capacity, tall tub design holds up to 14 place settings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Three wash cycles (heavy, light and normal) with two additional options (high heat wash and high heat/no heat dry) ensure your dishes are thoroughly cleaned&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy-saving, no heat dry option doesn\'t use heat so you can keep your energy bill low&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;White plastic interior offers a clean, classic look&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Detergent dispenser and rinse aid dispenser located in an easy-to-access compartment in the door&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;8 in. upper rack accommodates standard dishware and glasses&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flexible 10-5/8 in. lower rack accommodates large dishes and bowls in a single load&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Silverware basket is easy to remove and unload&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5-level wash system thoroughly washes all items with wash water filtered through plastic filter, removable small-items trap and stainless steel disposer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low rinse aid indicator light alerts you when it\'s time to refill the rinse aid dispenser&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2, 4, and 6-hour delayed start options&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Front to Back Width (in.): 24 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Height (in.): 34&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Left to Right Length (in.): 24 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth - Door Shut (with Handle) (in.): 25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth - Door Shut (without Handle) (in.): 25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth With Door Open 90 Degrees (In): 49.25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher Size: 24 In.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height - Maximum (in): 35&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height - Minimum (in): 33.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 35&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 23.75&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Amperage (amps): 10&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Appliance Type: Dishwasher&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish: Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish Family: Stainless&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control Type: Electronic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Custom Door Panel Ready: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Decibel (Sound) Rating: 60 dBA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Decibel Rating: 60 dBA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Delay Start Option: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher Cycles: Standard Wash Only&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher Features: Automatic Temperature Control,Delay Start Option,Filtered Water,Hard Food Disposer,Heated Dry,High Temperature Wash Option,Self-Cleaning Filter,Sound Reduction System&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher Rack Configuration: Lower Rack- Silverware Basket,Removable Silverware Basket&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Style: Front Control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy Consumption (kWh/year): 269&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy Efficiency Tier Rating: Not CEE rated&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Estimated Yearly Operating Cost ($): 29&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hard Food Disposer or Filtration&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hard Food Disposer &amp;amp; Filtration&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Cycles: 3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Place Settings: 14&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 60lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rack Material: PVC&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Returnable: Non-Returnable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Silverware Basket Location: In Rack&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sound Rating Range (Decibels): Quiet 56-60 dBA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steam Function: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tall Tub: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tub Material: Plastic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage (volts): 120&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: One year limited warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Frigidaire Front Control Dishwasher in Stainless Steel', 'Frigidaire Front Control Dishwasher in Stainless Steel', 'Frigidaire Front Control Dishwasher in Stainless Steel'),
(10526, 1, 'Whirlpool 7.0 cu. ft. Electric Dryer in White', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHIRLPOOL 7.0 CU. FT. ELECTRIC DRYER IN WHITE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AUTODRY drying system senses when to stop the cycle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The WRINKLE SHIELD option helps prevent wrinkles from setting in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy Duty cycle thoroughly dries heavy weight items&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Put a simple spin on laundry day even when the loads are heavy with this 7.0 cu. ft. capacity dryer. With the AutoDry drying system and plenty of room to easily handle large loads and bulky items, this high capacity dryer helps to keep your style solid. The Heavy Duty cycle manages those bulky items like towels and comforters with a high temperature to help ensure overall dryness. And, for those days when clothes in the dryer are an afterthought, the Wrinkle Shield option intermittently tumbles for up to 90 minutes after the cycle ends to help keep wrinkles from setting into your clothes while they\'re in your front dryer.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra Large 7.0 cu. ft. capacity easily handles large and bulky items&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;14 cycles include: Timed dry, air dry, energy preferred auto dry, heavy duty, less dry, more dry and very dry cycles to provide you drying choices to handle a variety of fabrics&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dryer drum\'s powder-coat finish resists chipping and abrasion to help protect clothes from damage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rear panel controls provide convenient access to all cycle and option selections&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4 temperature settings to handle variety of fabrics from delicate synthetics to heavyweight cotton&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The AutoDry drying system helps keep your style solid by automatically sensing when clothes have reached the right temperature and stopping the cycle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wrinkle shield option intermittently tumbles for up to 90 minutes after the dryer cycle ends helping to keep wrinkles from setting into your clean clothes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;End-of-Cycle signal alerts you when the drying cycle has completed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy Duty cycle sets the dryer to a high temperature to thoroughly dry heavyweight items&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dryer Duct and electrical cords are required for installation and will be offered separately during appliance checkout&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembled Depth (in.): 28.2 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembled Height (in.): 43 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembled Width (in.): 29 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth With Door Open 90 Degrees (In): 51&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Opening Height (In.): 18&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Opening Width (In.): 22.75&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 27.75&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 43.38&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 29&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Amperage (amps): 30&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Appliance Type: Electric Dryer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity - Dryer (cu. ft.): 7.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish: White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish Family: White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control Type: Electro-Mechanical&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Shape: Square Door&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Style: Reversible&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dry Cycles: Auto Dry,Cool Down,Extra Dry,Heavy Duty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dryer Drum Material: Powder-Coated Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dryer Features: Automatic Temperature Control,End-Of-Cycle Signal,Lint Filter,Sensor Dry,Timed Dry&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust Vent Location: Rear&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Included: No Additional Items Included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lint Filter Location: Top&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Matching Washer Type: Top Load&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Drying Cycles: 14&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Drying Temperatures: 4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pedestal Model#: None&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 109lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Returnable: Non-Returnable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stackable: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stacking Kit Model#: None&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steam Function: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage (volts): 240&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: Limited 1-year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Whirlpool 7.0 cu. ft. Electric Dryer in White', 'Whirlpool 7.0 cu. ft. Electric Dryer in White', 'Whirlpool 7.0 cu. ft. Electric Dryer in White'),
(10527, 1, 'Frigidaire Front Control Dishwasher in Stainless Steel, ENERGY STAR', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FRIGIDAIRE FRONT CONTROL DISHWASHER IN STAINLESS STEEL, ENERGY STAR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sanitize cycle removes up to 99.9% of household bacteria&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Runs at a quiet 55 dBA noise level&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Save money on your power bill with the ENERGY SAVER certification&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Frigidaire 24 in. built-in dishwasher features a large capacity tall tub design with 14 place settings that allow you to wash more at once. New attractive slim-console with Ready-Select controls lets you select options with the touch of a button. 5 versatile wash cycle options can handle all of your loads, from small plates to large pots and pans. The sanitize cycle helps remove 99.9% of household bacteria, ensuring your dishes are as good as new.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ready-Select electronic controls on a slim front panel allow you to easily select options with the touch of a button&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UltraQuiet III sound package (55 dBA) keeps the noise from your dishwasher to a minimum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tall-Tub design with large capacity fits up to 14 place settings so you can wash more at once&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;DishSense Technology automatically adjusts the cycle time based on your cleaning needs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5 easy-to-use wash cycle options meet all of your cleaning needs, including Energy Saver, Pots and Pans, Rinse Only, and Light wash&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Additional options include NSF Certified Sanitize, High Temperature Wash and High Heat/No Heat Dry to ensure your dishes are thoroughly cleaned at the end of your wash cycle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5 level wash system thoroughly washes all items using water filtered through a self-cleaning plastic filter, removable small items trap and stainless steel disposer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ENERGY STAR certified to maximize your savings and keep your energy bill low&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;White polymer interior supports the drying process so your dishes are dry the first time&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Detergent and rinse aid dispensers are located in an easy-to-access compartment in the door&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low rinse aid indicator light alerts you when it\'s time to refill the dispenser&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;8 in. upper rack accommodates all of your standard dishware and glasses&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi-compartment Silverware Basket has a place for all of your silverware and is easily removable for loading and unloading&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual spray arm system gives you a thorough clean every time&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;NSF Certified Sanitize cycle removes 99.9% of common household bacteria to ensure the cleanliness of your dishes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Delay Start options allow you to set your dishwasher to run 2, 4, or 6 hours in advance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Front to Back Width (in.): 24&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Height (in.): 35.25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Left to Right Length (in.): 24&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth - Door Shut (with Handle) (in.): 25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth - Door Shut (without Handle) (in.): 25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth With Door Open 90 Degrees (In): 49.25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher Size: 24 In.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height - Maximum (in): 35&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height - Minimum (in): 33.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 35&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 23.75&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Amperage (amps): 10&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Appliance Type: Dishwasher&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish: Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish Family: Stainless&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control Type: Electronic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Custom Door Panel Ready: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Decibel (Sound) Rating: 55 dBA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Decibel Rating: 55 dBA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Delay Start Option: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher Cycles: Pots and Pans,Rinse and Hold,Sanitize&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher Features: Delay Start Option,Filtered Water,Hard Food Disposer,Hard Food Filter,Heated Dry,High Temperature Wash Option,Self-Cleaning Filter,Sound Reduction System&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher Rack Configuration: Cup Shelf,Lower Rack- Silverware Basket,Removable Silverware Basket,Stemware Holder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Style: Front Control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy Consumption (kWh/year): 269&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy Efficiency Tier Rating: Not CEE rated&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Cycles: 5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Place Settings: 14&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 60lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rack Material: PVC&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Returnable: Non-Returnable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Silverware Basket Location: In Rack&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sound Rating Range (Decibels): Quieter 51-55 dBA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steam Function: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tall Tub: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tub Material: Plastic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage (volts): 120&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One Year Limited Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Frigidaire Front Control Dishwasher in Stainless Steel, ENERGY STAR', 'Frigidaire Front Control Dishwasher in Stainless Steel, ENERGY STAR', 'Frigidaire Front Control Dishwasher in Stainless Steel Energy Star'),
(10528, 1, 'Amana 6.5 cu. ft. Electric Dryer in White, NED4655EW', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AMANA 6.5 CU. FT. ELECTRIC DRYER IN WHITE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sensors monitor temperature &amp;amp; control time to prevent overdrying&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wrinkle Prevent option tumbles clothes intermittently&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6.5 cu. ft. capacity offers plenty of space for large loads&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Use only the energy you need with this 6.5 cu. ft. Electric Dryer in white. Equipped with Automatic Dryness Control, it uses sensors that stop the cycle when clothes are dry to help prevent overdrying. Its generous 6.5 cu. ft. capacity means there\'s plenty of room to dry your loads. When you can\'t unload right away, the wrinkle prevent option will intermittently tumble your clothes to help keep wrinkles from forming. And drying clothes on your schedule is easy thanks to Timed Dry cycles with up to 60 minutes of operation.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;California residents: see Proposition 65 information&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Generous 6.5 cu. ft. capacity means there\'s plenty of room to dry large loads&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;With 11 dryer cycles to choose from, you can provide the optimal environment for drying all your clothes.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dryer drum\'s powder-coat finish resists chipping and abrasion to help protect clothes from damage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Front panel controls provide convenient access to all cycle and option selections&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Save energy and help prevent overdrying by matching the temperature setting to the load being dried&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic Dryness Control uses sensors to end the cycle at the right time to help prevent overdrying&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wrinkle Prevent Option tumbles clothes intermittently without heat to help prevent creases and crinkles from settling in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Cool Down cycle gives clothes time to cool off, which helps prevent wrinkles when clothes are left in the dryer after the cycle ends&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Reversible side-swing door can be conveniently installed to open from the right or left side depending on your preference&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Choose from 11 dry cycles to accommodate the needs of every load&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lint screen is located on top of the dryer for easy access and quick cleaning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Timed Dry Cycle up to 60 minutes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dryer duct and electrical cord are required for installation and will be offered separately during appliance checkout&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth With Door Open 90 Degrees (In) 51&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Opening Height (In.): 16.8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Opening Width (In.): 22.75&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 27.75&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 43.38&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 29&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Amperage (amps): 30&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Appliance Type: Electric Dryer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity - Dryer (cu. ft.): 6.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish: White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish Family: White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control Type: Electro-Mechanical&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Shape: Square Door&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Style: Reversible&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dry Cycles: Auto Dry,Cool Down,Extra Dry,Wrinkle Free&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dryer Drum Material: Powder-Coated Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dryer Features: Lint Filter,Sensor Dry,Timed Dry&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust Vent Location: Rear&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lint Filter Location: Top&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Matching Washer Type: Top Load&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Drying Cycles: 11&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Drying Temperatures: 3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 109lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Returnable: Non-Returnable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stackable: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stacking Kit Model#: None&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steam Function: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage (volts): 240&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: Limited 1-year&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Amana 6.5 cu. ft. Electric Dryer in White, NED4655EW', 'Amana 6.5 cu. ft. Electric Dryer in White, NED4655EW', 'Amana 6.5 cu. ft. Electric Dryer in White, NED4655EW'),
(10529, 1, 'Amana Front Control Built-In Tall Tub Dishwasher in Stainless Steel', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AMANA FRONT CONTROL BUILT-IN TALL TUB DISHWASHER IN STAINLESS STEEL&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Triple Filter Wash System lets you skip the pre-rinse&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1-Hour Wash Cycle cleans light loads fast&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tall tub lets you fit more dishes in every load&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Featuring a slate gray plastic tub, this Amana dishwasher helps you clear off every crumb, thanks to the Triple Filter Wash System. A combination of three wash filters removes even tiny food particles from the wash water. The Heated Dry Option uses an internal heater to accelerate the drying process, so you can leave the dishtowel on the hook.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCalifornia residents: see&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Proposition 65 information&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Slim front console design features easy to use push button controls&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;When it\'s your turn to do the dishes, a 12-place setting capacity gives the space you need for every load&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Triple filter wash system helps you skip the pre-rinse so you can spend less time scrubbing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;A heater boosts the water temperature during the wash cycle with the high-temperature wash option, plus, an extra rinse is added to help get those dishes sparkling clean&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy star certified to help you conserve energy and pay less for utilities&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Slate gray plastic tub adds a touch of style to the interior&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rinse-aid dispenser automatically adds a measured amount of rinse-aid to help reduce potential for spots on dishes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Spacious upper rack accommodates items like glasses, bowls and cups&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lower rack provides room for larger items like pots and pans&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable silverware basket with handle is convenient for loading and unloading&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heated Dry Option uses an internal heater to accelerate the drying process, removing excess moisture so you can leave the dishtowel on the hook&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 wash-arms deliver complete cleaning coverage, even when the dishwasher is fully loaded&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Star K compliant as Kosher Consumer Friendly&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;New dishwasher connection kit is required for installation and will be offered during appliance checkout&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Front to Back Width (in.): 24 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Height (in.): 34 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Left to Right Length (in.): 24 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth - Door Shut (with Handle) (in.): 25.3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth - Door Shut (without Handle) (in.): 24.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth With Door Open 90 Degrees (In): 49.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher Size: 24 In.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height - Maximum (in): 34.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height - Minimum (in): 33.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 24.5 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 34.5 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 23.88 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Amperage (amps): 10 A&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Appliance Type: Dishwasher&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish: Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish Family: Stainless&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control Type: Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Custom Door Panel Ready: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Decibel (Sound) Rating: 63 dBA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Decibel Rating: 63 dBA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Delay Start Option: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher Cycles: Pots and Pans,Quick Wash&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher Features: Automatic Temperature Control,Cycle Status Lights,Heated Dry,High Temperature Wash Option&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dishwasher Rack Configuration: Removable Silverware Basket,Standard Rack Only&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Style: Front Control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy Consumption (kWh/year): 270&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy Efficiency Tier Rating: Not CEE rated&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hard Food Disposer or Filtration: Filtration&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Cycles: 3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Place Settings: 12&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 56 lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rack Material: Vinyl&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Returnable: Non-Returnable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Silverware Basket Location: In Rack&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sound Rating Range (Decibels): Average 61 dBA and Up&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steam Function: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tall Tub: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tub Material: Plastic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage (volts): 120&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: 1 year Limited Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Amana Front Control Built-In Tall Tub Dishwasher in Stainless Steel', 'Amana Front Control Built-In Tall Tub Dishwasher in Stainless Steel', 'Amana Front Control Built-In Tall Tub Dishwasher in Stainless Steel'),
(10530, 1, 'Amana 6.5 cu. ft. Gas Dryer in White', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AMANA 6.5 CU. FT. GAS DRYER IN WHITE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic Dryness Control uses sensors to end the cycle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wrinkle Prevent Option tumbles clothes intermittently&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6.5 cu. ft. Capacity can help take a load off your mind&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Use only the energy you need with this gas dryer. Equipped with Automatic Dryness Control, it uses sensors that stop the cycle when clothes are dry to help prevent overdrying. Generous 6.5 cu. ft. capacity means there\'s plenty of room to dry your loads. When you can\'t unload right away, the Wrinkle Prevent option will intermittently tumble your clothes to help prevent wrinkles from settling in. And drying clothes on your schedule is easy thanks to Timed Dry cycles.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCalifornia residents: see&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Proposition 65 information&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6.5 cu. ft. Capacity can help take a load off your mind.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;With 11 dryer cycles to choose from, with high heat, low heat and no heat options, whatever you put in the dryer comes out ready to wear&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dryer drum\'s powder-coat finish resists chipping and abrasion to help protect clothes from damage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Front panel controls provide convenient access to all cycle and option selections&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Save energy and help prevent overdrying by matching the temperature setting to the load being dried.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic Dryness Control uses sensors to end the cycle at the right time to help prevent overdrying, so favorite items like comfy sweatpants get just the perfect dry.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;When you can\'t fold right away, use the Wrinkle Prevent Option. It tumbles clothes intermittently without heat to help prevent creases and crinkles from settling in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Cool Down cycle gives clothes time to cool off, which helps prevent wrinkles when clothes are left in the dryer after the cycle ends&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Reversible side-swing door can be conveniently installed to open from the right or left side depending on your preference&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Choose from 11 Dry Cycles to accommodate the needs of every load.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lint screen is located on top of the dryer for easy access and quick cleaning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Timed Dry Cycle up to 60 minutes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dryer duct is required for installation and will be offered separately during appliance checkout&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth With Door Open 90 Degrees (In): 51&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Opening Height (In.): 16.8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Opening Width (In.): 22.75&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 27.75&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 43.38&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 29&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Appliance Type: Gas Dryer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity - Dryer (cu. ft.): 6.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish: White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish Family: White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control Type: Electro-Mechanical&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Shape: Square Door&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Style: Reversible&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dry Cycles: Auto Dry,Cool Down,Extra Dry,Wrinkle Free&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dryer Drum Material: Powder-Coated Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dryer Features: Lint Filter,Sensor Dry,Timed Dry&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust Vent Location: Rear&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Included: Power Cord&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lint Filter Location: Top&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Matching Washer Type: Top Load&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Drying Cycles: 11&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Drying Temperatures: 3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pedestal Model#: None&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 113lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Propane (LP) Conversion Kit Included: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Returnable: Non-Returnable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stackable: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stacking Kit Model#: None&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steam Function: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage (volts): 120&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: Limited 1-year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Amana 6.5 cu. ft. Gas Dryer in White', 'Amana 6.5 cu. ft. Gas Dryer in White', 'Amana 6.5 cu. ft. Gas Dryer in White'),
(10531, 1, 'Amana 3.5 cu. ft. Top Load Washer in White', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AMANA 3.5 CU. FT. TOP LOAD WASHER IN WHITE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual-action agitator delivers a thorough but gentle clean&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Porcelain tub helps protect fabrics, so favorites stay snag-free&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Deep Water Wash option provides more water for a confident clean&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This 3.5 cu. ft. Amana Top-Load Washer delivers a thorough, even clean with a Dual Action Agitator, which rolls clothes through the bottom of the wash basket. Its durable Porcelain Tub helps protect your favorites from snags, while the Deep Water Wash Option adds more water during the rinse cycle for added confidence.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCalifornia residents: see&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Proposition 65 information&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Now you can wash more in a single load with our large capacity top load washer, at 3.5 cu. ft., helping you save money and resources; this means fewer loads every week and fewer loads mean fewer resources&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Our durable Porcelain Tub helps protect fabrics, so socks and sweaters can stay snag-free&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;8 wash cycles, including Bulky/Sheets, Casual, Clean Washer with afresh, Deep Water Wash, Delicates, Drain and Spin, Normal, Rinse and Spin&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rear panel controls provide convenient access to all cycle and option selections&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic Load Size Sensing Technology helps takes the guesswork out of laundry by using the right amount of water for the cycle and soil level selected&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The 2 pieces of this agitator move independently to roll clothing through the bottom of the wash basket for a thorough, even cleaning&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Late Lid Lock gives you extra time to throw in any missed items before the Spin Cycle starts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Deep Water Wash Option fills the tub with more water during the wash and rinse cycle when you need it, so you can clean with confidence&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Uses a slower spin speed and a gentle wash motion to clean delicate items&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6 Temperature Settings help make sure the wash water is just the right temperature for every load&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Feedback-Status Indicators give you a variety of feedback including Done, Fill, Rinse, Sensing, Spin, Wash&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Washer requires use of only high-efficiency detergent, typically two tablespoons per load&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity - Washer (cu. ft.): 3.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height With Lid Open 90 Degrees (In): 51.2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 27&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 42&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 27.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Agitator/Impeller Type: Two-Piece Agitator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Amperage (amps): 20 A&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Appliance Type: Top Load Washer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish: White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish Family: White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control Type: Digital&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cycle - Allergen: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy Consumption (kWh/year): 206&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy Efficiency Tier Rating: Not CEE rated&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High Efficiency Washer: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High-Efficiency Detergent Required: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Included: Power Cord&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Spin Speed (RPM): 700&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Rinse Cycles: 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Rinse Temperatures: 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Wash Cycles: 8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Wash Speeds: 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Wash Temperatures: 5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 133lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Returnable: Non-Returnable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steam Function: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage (volts): 120&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wash Cycles: Bulky Items,Clean Washer,Deep Water Wash,Delicates,Drain &amp;amp; Spin,Rinse &amp;amp; Spin&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Washer Dispensers: Bleach&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Washer Features: Cycle Time Remaining Display,End-Of-Cycle Signal&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Washer Interior Light: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Washer Tub/Drum Material: Porcelain&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Amana 3.5 cu. ft. Top Load Washer in White', 'Amana 3.5 cu. ft. Top Load Washer in White', 'Amana 3.5 cu. ft. Top Load Washer in White'),
(10532, 1, 'Maytag 2.0 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Fingerprint Resistant with Sensor Cooking', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MAYTAG 2.0 CU. FT. OVER THE RANGE MICROWAVE IN FINGERPRINT RESISTANT STAINLESS STEEL WITH SENSOR COOKING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy-to-clean fingerprint resistant stainless steel exterior&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sensor cooking adjusts to your dinner with ideal settings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi-speed exhaust fan helps remove smoke and odors as you cook&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Our reliable over-the-range microwave, available in fingerprint resistant stainless steel, helps you get delicious to the table fast. Sensor reheat adjusts to whatever you\'re cooking with ideal time and power settings to help prevent overcooking. And when you need to heat more than one dish at once, 2.0 cu. ft. capacity and an interior cooking rack provide plenty of room. Plus, the multiple speed exhaust fan, mesh grease filter and charcoal odor filter work together in this hidden vent microwave to combat cooking odors and smoke. And with a 10-year limited parts warranty, you\'ve got an over-the-range microwave made to last in any kitchen.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2.0 cu. ft. extra-large capacity accommodates dinner plates and casserole dishes with ease&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1000-Watt of cooking power and 10 cooking levels make cooking and reheating a snap&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;400 CFM venting system whisks smoke, steam and odors away from the cooktop to keep your kitchen air clear&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electronic touch controls on this microwave oven are easy to use and keep clean and provide access to setting such as the Fan Timer, Light Timer, as well as programmed and sensor cooking cycles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sensor cooking adjusts to your dinner with ideal time and microwave power settings for everything from large casseroles to pasta&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Our interior cooking rack gives you the space you need to cook your whole meal at one time. The second surface lets you stack your side dishes on top of your main dish&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The multiple speed exhaust fan helps remove smoke and odors as you cook on your range&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Take the trouble out of scrubbing up after dinner with a mesh grease filter that helps prevent the mess&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Help prevent cooking smells from overwhelming your meals with a charcoal odor filter that removes high airflow odors and steam&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The stainless steel microwave cavity is designed to resist the splatter from any messy meal&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy-to-clean, fingerprint resistant stainless steel finish keeps your microwave looking as good on the outside as it works on the inside&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity of Microwave (cu. ft.): 2.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Front to Back Depth (in.): 12&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Height (in.): 17.13&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cut-Out Left to Right Width (in.): 30&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Depth With Door(s) Open 90 Degrees (In.): 42&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 17.75&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 17.13&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 30&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Appliance Type: Over the Range Microwave&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish: Fingerprint Resistant Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color/Finish Family: Stainless Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Controls Location: Side Controls&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Door Swing/Style: Right to Left Swing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust Fan Speeds: 3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust Maximum CFM: 400&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Light Source: Incandescent&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Door Release: Pull&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Features: Charcoal Filter,Clock,Cooktop Lighting,Fingerprint Resistant,Interior Light,Microwave Rack,One Touch Cooking,Removable Filter,Timer,Turntable,Turntable On/Off Option&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Settings: Add 30 Seconds,Control Lock,Cook Power,Cook Time,Defrost,Pizza,Popcorn,Potato,Reheat,Sensor Cook,Soften/Melt&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Microwave Size: Large&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of One-Touch Settings: 3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Power Levels: 10&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 54.1 lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Returnable: Non-Returnable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vent Fan Location: Back&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vent Type: Recirculating&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wattage (watts): 1000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Maytag 2.0 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Fingerprint Resistant Stainless Steel with Sensor Cooking', 'Maytag 2.0 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Fingerprint Resistant Stainless Steel with Sensor Cooking', 'Maytag 2.0 cu. ft. Over the Range Microwave in Fingerprint Resistant Stainless Steel with Sensor Cooking'),
(10533, 1, 'Maxiclimber The Original Patented Vertical Climber As Seen On TV', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SAFE AND EFFECTIVE. ..ALL IN ONE-SIMPLE WORKOUT!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMaxiClimber utilizes the same muscles used in rock climbing, and imitates the body’s natural movement of climbing –– giving you an intense workout from head to toe!&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMaxiClimber is Safe, utilizing only your bodyweight, with no added stress on the lower joints of the body.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Leaner legs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Beautiful Booty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Toned, shapely arms&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rock-hard abs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Slimmer, healthier body!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LIGHTWEIGHT AND DURABLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMaxiClimber is a vertical climber for integral fitness, made with the best materials. It’s light, and yet so durable that it’s guaranteed for life.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRE-ASSEMBLED ON DELIVERY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMaxiClimber is easy to set up and use as soon as you receive it. It comes pre-assembled and requires no additional parts.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SUPER-EASY STORAGE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhen you’re not using it, MaxiClimber stores in any corner or closet, without taking up space.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE MAXICLIMBER SYSTEM IS THE AFFORDABLE, CALORIE-BLASTING, BODY-SCULPTING WORK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMaxiClimber is the affordable, calorie-blasting, body sculpting workout that enables you to perform both cardio and muscle toning all in the comfort of your own home. MaxiClimber works your lower body, core and upper body muscle groups at the same time, maximizing your time&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Maxiclimber The Original Patented Vertical Climber As Seen On TV', 'Maxiclimber The Original Patented Vertical Climber As Seen On TV', 'Maxiclimber The Original Patented Vertical Climber As Seen On TV'),
(10534, 1, 'ChefSteps Joule Sous Vide, 1100 Watts, White Body, Stainless Steel Cap &amp; Base', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CHEFSTEPS JOULE SOUS VIDE, 1100 WATTS, WHITE BODY, STAINLESS STEEL CAP &amp;amp; BASE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smallest, sleekest sous vide tool available at just 11 inches tall and 1.3 pounds, with streamlined white body and solid stainless steel cap &amp;amp; base.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SAVES SPACE: Half the size of other sous vide machines, it’s small enough to slip into a top drawer.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;HEATS UP FAST: 1100 watts of power for hyper-fast water heating.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;PERFECT RESULTS: Visual Doneness (TM) feature in the Joule app displays exactly how food cooks. Dinner comes out predictably perfect, every time.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;WIFI AND BLUETOOTH READY: Works with iPhone or Android—connect with Bluetooth alone, or cook from anywhere with WiFi.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage warning: Works with 120 V outlets only. Due to our precise heating technology, voltage transformers and converters can damage your Joule, and use outside of North America voids the warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DURABLE STAINLESS STEEL CAP &amp;amp; BASE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe top and base are cold-forged from solid stainless steel for maximum durability and corrosion resistance.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SAVES SPACE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHalf the size of other sous vide machines, it fits in your silverware drawer.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VISUAL DONENESS &amp;amp; CHEF-TESTED RECIPES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nExclusive Visual Doneness feature feature in the Joule app shows exactly how food turns out—before you start cooking! Also includes more than 100 cooking guides, custom developed for the Joule community by our in-house chefs.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BLUETOOTH AND WIFI READY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCook with Bluetooth alone, or control Joule remotely with WiFi.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NO SPECIAL EQUIPMENT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nYour trusty phone, a favorite pot, a ziplock-style bag, and water. That\'s all you need to get cooking. With a magnetic base and a versatile clip, Joule can attach to almost any container, from a small saucepan to a cooler.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FAST AND PRECISE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith 1100 watts of power, heats water faster than most sous vide machines. Precise to 0.2°F / 0.1°C.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WORKS WITH AMAZON ALEXA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nControl Joule with your voice using the custom Joule Alexa skill.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WE WANT YOU TO LOVE YOUR JOULE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIf you\'re not delighted with your Joule, contact ChefSteps directly within 90 days, and we’ll make it right or give you a full refund. Issues or questions? Just contact our full-service support team.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'ChefSteps Joule Sous Vide, 1100 Watts, White Body, Stainless Steel Cap &amp; Base', 'ChefSteps Joule Sous Vide, 1100 Watts, White Body, Stainless Steel Cap &amp; Base', 'ChefSteps Joule Sous Vide, 1100 Watts, White Body, Stainless Steel Cap &amp; Base');
