(10542, 1, 'Keurig K150 Commercial Brewing System', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KEURIG® K150 COMMERCIAL BREWING SYSTEM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The K150 Commercial Brewing System is a fully programmable brewer with an interactive touch-screen that allows for customizable brew temperature, language settings, and a choice of 5 cup sizes. This brewer has a 90 ounce water reservoir or direct line plumbing option for continuous use. It is also NSF certified for use in foodservice outlets.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;First cup. Fourth cup - with Keurig®, it\'s always a fresh cup. The Keurig® K150 Commercial Brewing System brews a perfect cup of coffee, tea or hot cocoa as well as iced beverages in under one minute at the touch of a button. Now everyone can brew what they love. This fully programmable brewer has an interactive touch-screen that allows you to program the brew temperature, to set Auto On/Off, and to set your language preference to English, Spanish, or French. The K150 brewer offers a choice of five cup sizes, a removable drip tray to accommodate travel mugs, and a drainable internal hot water tank for transport or storage. This brewer is certified by the National Sanitation Foundation (NSF) for use in foodservice outlets. The K150 Brewing System is only available through a Keurig Authorized Distributor.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Experience an amazing variety of beverages from some of America’s most-loved brands.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HIGHLIGHTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy-Saving&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mode Automatic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;On/Off Function&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brewer Speed: Brews in under 3 minutes.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quiet Brew Technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Programmable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable Temperature&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multilingual Brewer Instructions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;NSF Certified&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Usage: Usage: Commercial and household&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power: 1,400 watts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage: 120VAC&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 18 lbs. empty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 13.9&quot;H x 14.0&quot;D x 10.4&quot;W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Keurig K150 Commercial Brewing System', 'Keurig K150 Commercial Brewing System', 'Keurig K150 Commercial Brewing System'),
