(10545, 1, 'Truck Pac 12/24 Volt Jump Starter 3000 Peak Amps', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TRUCK PAC 12/24 VOLT JUMP STARTER — 3000 PEAK AMPS, MODEL# ES1224&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Delivers 3,000 Peak Amps and 750 Cranking Amps (in 12V mode) to start a wide variety of vehicles, including cars, pickups, SUVs, light and medium duty trucks, buses, RVs, boats, agricultural equipment and off-road equipment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes exclusive ES Series batteries which are specifically designed for vehicle jumpstarting and deliver exceptional starting power, extended cranking duration and long service life&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The flexibility of 12 Volt and 24 Volt starting in a single unit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easily converted from 12V to 24V operation with the turn of a knob for quick adjustment for your starting needs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flexible, #2 AWG welding cable leads and Hit Jaw industrial grade clamps provide efficient power transfer from the ES1224 to the disabled vehicle\'s starting system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT SUMMARY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;Truck Pac® 3,200/1,600 Peak Amp industrial-grade 12/24 Volt jump starter and power source. Flip switch to select 12 Volt or 24 Volt power. Dual high-performance ES Series AGM batteries and extra-long 60in. cold-weather rated #2 AWG cables with industrial-grade Hot Jaw™ clamps. Features AWS (Advanced Warning System) with a buzzer alert if battery connections are reversed or improper voltage conditions occur. Automatic charging circuitry protects against overcharging. 12 Volt outlet for on-the-go power. Includes wall charger and 12 Volt vehicle charging cord.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES + BENEFITS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Delivers 3,000 Peak Amps and 750 Cranking Amps 