(10547, 1, 'Ironton Breaker Hammer Kit', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IRONTON BREAKER HAMMER KIT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;110V; 2050 Watt motor for high-demand, high-intensity work&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 1/8in. hex chuck bit system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1030 BPM to tackle the most demanding jobs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Super-durable percussion construction provides higher performance and stability for heavy-duty work in extreme environments&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Optimized gear driving chain provides longer life&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT SUMMARY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe robust 2050 Watt motor in this Ironton® Demolition-Breaker Hammer delivers the power to satisfy the most demanding and intense jobs. Convenient 1 1/8in. hex chuck bit system provides users with more choices. Incredibly durable percussion construction provides higher performance and stability to deliver heavy-duty productivity even in extreme environments. Comes with mobile cart for easy transport.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S INCLUDED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n(1) Breaker hammer(1) Pointed chisel(1) Flat chisel(1) Mobile cart&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES + BENEFITS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://www.northerntool.com/images/product/features/45998.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 782px; height: 394px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;110V; 2050 Watt motor for high-demand, high-intensity work&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 1/8in. hex chuck bit system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1030 BPM to tackle the most demanding jobs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Super-durable percussion construction provides higher performance and stability for heavy-duty work in extreme environments&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Optimized gear driving chain provides longer life&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shock-mounted handles reduce vibration and fatigue&lt