(10554, 1, 'Roughneck Hydraulic Lift Table Cart 2,200-Lb. Capacity', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ROUGHNECK HYDRAULIC LIFT TABLE CART — 2,200-LB. CAPACITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lift or lower the scissor lift tabletop with the handy foot pedal control featuring a nonslip rubber cover&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;40in.L x 20 1/4in.W platform&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra-tough all-steel construction with durable powder-coat finish is easy to clean and easy to operate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rolls on heavy-duty cast iron polyurethane casters; 2 swivel casters with brake and 2 fixed casters&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;53in.L x 24 3/4in.W x 39 3/8in.H overall size&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT SUMMARY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;This Roughneck® Hydraulic Lift Table Cart with foot pedal control allows you to quickly and easily lift and lower up to 2,200 lbs. Ideal for lifting, positioning and transporting heavy materials around the shop, factory, warehouse or office. 15in.–39 3/8in. lift range.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S INCLUDED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) Lift table cart&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES + BENEFITS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lift or lower the scissor lift tabletop with the handy foot pedal control featuring a nonslip rubber cover&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;40in.L x 20 1/4in.W platform&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra-tough all-steel construction with durable powder-coat finish is easy to clean and easy to operate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rolls on heavy-duty cast iron polyurethane casters; 2 swivel casters with brake and 2 fixed casters&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;53in.L x 24 3/4in.W x 39 3/8in.H overall size&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&am