(10244, 1, 'Coravin Model Two Plus Pack - BONUS Coravin Carry Case', '&lt;p&gt;The Coravin™ Model Two is Coravin’s most intuitive wine system that gives you the freedom to pour and enjoy a glass of wine from any bottle at any time. Model Two is the best-in-class tool that protects your wine from oxidation using Coravin’s proprietary technology that leaves the cork in place while the wine flows.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;New Thin Wall Needle pours 20% faster than the original needle, and locks into place.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;New Properfit Clamp is easy to open and close, and provides a secure hold on the bottle.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Coravin Capsule Load Cell Technology Makes installing gas easier, ensuring a perfect seal every time.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Proprietary Coravin Capsules contain more than 99.99% pure argon gas to protect the remaining wine from oxidation.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://images.wineenthusiast.com/products/Model2_Features_Desc_Feat.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 777px; height: 478px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Size and Weight&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 8.25 &quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 5.5 &quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 2.5 &quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: .98 lbs (with capsule installed)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Materials&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Device: Stainless steel, zinc, black ABS plastic, mixed polycarbonate, fiberglass reinforced nylon&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capsules: Capsule - recyclable steel; Seal - synthetic rubber; Cap - fiberglass reinforced nylon&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Needle: Needle - Teflon® coated, stainless steel; Grip - ABS plastic; &amp;nbsp;Seal - synthetic rubber&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Base: ABS plastic, silicone rubber&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Capsule Life&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Each Coravin Capsule will allow you to pour up to fifteen 5 ounce glasses of wine.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pour Speed&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;On average, a 5 ounce pour of wine with a standard needle will take 25 to 29 seconds.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S IN THE BOX:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Coravin Model Two Plus (New faster pouring Standard Needle included)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two (2) Coravin Capsules (pressurized argon gas)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Coravin Wine Bottle Sleeve&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Spray Mat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Needle Clearing Tool&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Carrying Case&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Coravin Model Two Plus Pack - BONUS Coravin Carry Case', 'Coravin Model Two Plus Pack - BONUS Coravin Carry Case', 'Coravin Model Two Plus - BONUS Coravin Carry Case'),
(10569, 1, 'Sun Joe Pressure Joe 2,030 psi 1.76-GPM 14.5 Amp Electric Pressure Washer with Hose Reel', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SUN JOE PRESSURE JOE 2,030 PSI 1.76-GPM 14.5 AMP ELECTRIC PRESSURE WASHER WITH HOSE REEL&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Eco friendly: no gas, oil or toxic carbon emissions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;34-inch spray wand extends reach&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easily connect or disconnect your garden hose adaptor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Count on power and performance under Pressure, and tackle your toughest home, outdoor and auto cleaning projects with ease. Packed with a powerful 1,800-Watt/14.5 Amp motor, this Pressure Joe generates up to 2,030 psi of water Pressure and 1.76-GPM of water flow to remove road tar, tree sap and bird splats from cars, grease deposits from concrete, heavy mildew, oil and rust stains, caked on mud, and other stubborn yard and garden gunk and grime. It comes equipped with an extra-large 40.6 ft. oz. (1.2 L) onboard detergent tank, perfect for blasting dirt and debris off your windows, cars, RVs, boats, ATVs, trailers, siding, barbecues and more. Its 34 in. extension spray wand and rear wheels provide maximum maneuverability and easy access to tight spaces such as beneath decks, behind grills, gutters and patio furniture as well as the undersides of automotive vehicles and heavy gardening equipment.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5 quick-connect spray tips (0 Degree , 15 Degree , 25 Degree , 40 Degree and soap) tackle light, medium and heavy duty cleaning tasks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Powerful 14.5 amp/1800-watt motor generates up to 2030 psi/1.76 GPM for maximum cleaning power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Onboard reel keeps 20 ft. (6 m) high-pressure hose organized for quick and easy clean-up and storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra-large 40.6 fl. oz. (1.2 L) onboard detergent tank&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;TSS (total stop system) automatically shuts off the pump when trigger is not engaged to save energy and prolong pump life&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in holder securely stores trigger gun and wand&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Other features include 34 in. extension wand, 20 ft. high pressure hose, 35 ft. power cord with GFCI protection, garden hose adaptor and needle clean-out tool&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CSA approved&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Full 2-year warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Choose the best nozzle that fits your pressure washer needs:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://inlinecontent.homedepot-static.com/28P/All%20Pressure%20Washers/NozzleSelectionGuide.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 654px; height: 478px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembled Depth (in.): 14.4 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembled Height (in.): 33.5 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembled Width (in.): 16.5 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hose Diameter (In.): 0.6&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hose length (in.): 240&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wheel Diameter (in.): 8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Amperage (amps): 14.5 A&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly Required: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Commercial: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Connection Type: Other&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cord Length (ft.): 35&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Features: Quick connect tips&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;GPM: 1.76&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hose Material: Other&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Included: Detergent tank,Onboard cord storage,Wheels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Pressure (PSI): 2030.000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Nozzle Type: Adjustable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of tips included: 5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pressure Washer Power Type: Electric&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 32lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pump Brand: Other&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pump Type: Axial&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Refurbished: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Start Type: Electric&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Water capability: Cold&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Sun Joe Pressure Joe 2,030 psi 1.76-GPM 14.5 Amp Electric Pressure Washer with Hose Reel', 'Sun Joe Pressure Joe 2,030 psi 1.76-GPM 14.5 Amp Electric Pressure Washer with Hose Reel', 'Sun Joe Pressure Joe 2,030 psi 1.76-GPM 14.5 Amp Electric Pressure Washer with Hose Reel'),
(10570, 1, 'Ryobi RY14122 1,700-PSI 1.2-GPM Electric Pressure Washer', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RYOBI 1,700-PSI 1.2-GPM ELECTRIC PRESSURE WASHER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes Turbo Nozzle for up to 50% More Cleaning Power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Features On-Board Detergent Tank for Easy Soap Application&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Performance Tested and Rated in Accordance with PWMA Standards&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Ryobi 1700 psi Pressure Washer is engineered to handle even your toughest jobs. With a powerful 13 Amp Electric Motor, this Ryobi Pressure Washer delivers 1700 PSI of force for quick cleaning of driveways, decks, windows and other areas around the house. Featuring a durable and compact roll-cage frame design this pressure washer is designed for easy transport. The On-Board Detergent Tank offers hassle-free cleaning by eliminating the need to drag a bucket and hose behind you. For added convenience, the Ryobi 1700 psi Pressure Washer is equipped with on-board accessory storage and a bonus Turbo Nozzle for up to 50% more cleaning power. The Ryobi 1700 PSI Electric Pressure Washer is backed with the Ryobi 3-year limited warranty and is guaranteed to deliver results for years to come.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Performance Tested and Rated in Accordance with PWMA Standard PW101&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1,700-PSI 1.2-GPM for efficient cleaning of residential areas&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;On-board detergent tank for easy soap application&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick connect capable for easy use of nozzles and additional attachments&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rugged roll-cage frame design protects the motor housing and stays upright; no tipping&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;25 ft. non-marring high pressure hose will not leave scuffs on the job&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3 nozzles included (15°soap and turbo) for cleaning a variety of surfaces&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Included turbo nozzle provides up to 50% more cleaning power with a cone-shaped spray pattern&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maintenance free aluminum pump for easy pump upkeep&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;On-board accessory storage for quickly and conveniently stowing trigger handle, hose and nozzles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-year warranty for guaranteed performance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembled Depth (in.): 17.125 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembled Height (in.): 18.500 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembled Width (in.): 17.750 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hose Diameter (In.): .25 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hose length (in.): 300&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wheel Diameter (in.): 7&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Amperage (amps): 13&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly Required: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Commercial: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Connection Type: M22 Universal Threaded Twist On Hose &amp;amp; Trigger Handle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cord Length (ft.): 35&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Features: Chemical/detergent injection,Cord Lock,Quick connect tips&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;GPM: 1.2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hose Material: Rubber&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Included: Detergent tank,GFIC plug,Onboard cord storage,Wheels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Pressure (PSI): 1700&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Nozzle Type: Turbo Nozzle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of tips included: 3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pressure Washer Power Type: Electric&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 32lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pump Brand: Other&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pump Type: Axial&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Refurbished: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Start Type: Electric&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Water capability: Cold&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Ryobi 1,700-PSI 1.2-GPM Electric Pressure Washer', 'Ryobi 1,700-PSI 1.2-GPM Electric Pressure Washer', 'Ryobi 1,700-PSI 1.2-GPM Electric Pressure Washer'),
(10571, 1, 'Lincoln Electric 88 Amp Handy MIG Wire Feed Welder with Gun, MIG and Flux-Cored Wire', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LINCOLN ELECTRIC 88 AMP HANDY MIG WIRE FEED WELDER WITH GUN, MIG AND FLUX-CORED WIRE, HAND SHIELD, GAS REGULATOR AND HOSE, 115V&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Plugs into household 115V outlet, 35-88 Amp welding output range&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Welds up to 1/8 in. mild steel both MIG and flux-cored&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compact, portable, lightweight and easy to use&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Lincoln Electric Handy MIG Welder is a user-friendly, compact portable and lightweight wire-feed welder that plugs into a 115-Volt, 20 Amp outlet. Four voltage settings and a continuous wire-feed speed adjustment allow you to weld mild steel from 24-Gauge to 1/8 in. thick. This handy welder includes gun and cable assembly, work cable and clamp, gas nozzle, gas regulator and hose, spool of solid wire, contact tips and a hand shield with filter plate and lens.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Welds both MIG (shielding gas sold separately) and flux-cored&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Welds up to 1/8 in. mild steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Plugs into a household 115-Volt 20 Amp outlet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes gun and cable assembly, work cable and clamp, gas nozzle, gas regulator and hose, spool of solid wire, contact tips and hand shield with filter plate and lens (shielding gas not included)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Also includes a spool of self-shielded, flux-cored wire, contact tips and chipping hammer/brush so you can weld with gasless flux-cored wire&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4 heat settings and infinite wire speed control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 18&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 16.75&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 10.31&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Engine Power: Electric (AC)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Input Power (Volts): 115&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum amperage output (amps): 88&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Minimum amperage output (amps): 35&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rated Output (Volts): 17&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tools Product Type: Power Tool&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Torch included: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Welder Type: MIG&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Lincoln Electric 88 Amp Handy MIG Wire Feed Welder with Gun, MIG and Flux-Cored Wire', 'Lincoln Electric 88 Amp Handy MIG Wire Feed Welder with Gun, MIG and Flux-Cored Wire', 'Lincoln Electric 88 Amp Handy MIG Wire Feed Welder with Gun, MIG and Flux-Cored Wire'),
(10591, 1, 'La Crosse Technology Professional Remote Monitoring WiFi Weather Station', '&lt;p&gt;New Professional Remote Monitoring Weather Station features wind, rain, indoor and outdoor temperature and humidity data, daily high and low temperature records, dynamic forecast icons, and a new Wi-Fi connected option, which will allow you to see all of your sensor data in our new La Crosse View app.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TEMPERATURE AND HUMIDITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Indoor/Outdoor Temperature and Humidity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Outdoor Trend Indicators&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Daily High/Low Outdoor Temperature Records&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Feels Like and Dew Point&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High and Low Records with Time Stamp&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WIND SPEED DATA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Current and Top Speed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wind Direction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;History Records with Time Stamp&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RAINFALL DATA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Time Frame Selectable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;History Records&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TIME AND DATE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;12/24 Hour Setting&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Displays Day of the Week, Month, Date &amp;amp; Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Perpetual Calendar: Date, Month, &amp;amp; Full Day&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ADDITIONAL FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Guided Settings Menu&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low Battery Indicator for Each Included Sensor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5 Settings LCD Brightness&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sensor Connection Indicator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wifi Connection Indicator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bonus Indoor Temperature Display&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brushed Metal Finish&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wall Hanging or Adjustable Kickstand for Free Standing Option&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WIFI CONNECTABLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nYour weather station can function as a standalone weather station OR you can download the free La Crosse View™ App for enhanced features.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DISPLAY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Indoor temperature range:&amp;nbsp; +32°F to +122°F (0°C to 50°C)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Indoor humidity range: 10% RH to 99%RH&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;INCLUDED LTV-TH2 WIRELESS OUTDOOR TEMP/HUMIDITY SENSOR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Outdoor temperature range: -40°F to 140°F (-40°C to 60°C)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Outdoor humidity range: 10% RH to 99%RH&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Transmission range: Up to 400 feet (121 meters) in open air&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Transmission frequency: 915 MHz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;POWER REQUIREMENTS:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Display: 5.0 Volt 600mA power cord included (Required); Optional 3 &quot;AA&quot; Alkaline batteries backup&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LTV-TH2 Sensor: 2 &quot;AA&quot; Alkaline batteries&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LTV-W1 Sensor: 2 &quot;C&quot; Alkaline batteries&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LTV-R2 Sensor: 2 &quot;AA&quot; Alkaline batteries&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DIMENSIONS&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Display: 8.98&quot; L x 1.00&quot; W x 5.43&quot; H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LTV-TH2: 1.97&quot; L x 0.75&quot; W x 5.73&quot; H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LTV-W1: 7.10&quot; L x 7.10&quot; W x 18.57&quot; H (with mounting bracket/pole)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LTV-R2: 7.14&quot; L x 3.43&quot; W x 4.94&quot; H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'La Crosse Technology Professional Remote Monitoring WiFi Weather Station C84428\r\n', 'La Crosse Technology Professional Remote Monitoring WiFi Weather Station C84428\r\n', 'La Crosse Technology Professional Remote Monitoring WiFi Weather Station C84428'),
(10578, 1, 'RIDGID WD1956 16 gal. 6.5-Peak HP Stainless Steel Wet Dry Vac', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RIDGID 16 GAL. 6.5-PEAK HP STAINLESS STEEL WET DRY VAC, MODEL # WD1956&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Durable stainless steel construction, built for the Pro&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cart &amp;amp; large rear wheels makes easy maneuvering &amp;amp; accessibility&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Features the RIDGID lifetime warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This RIDGID 16 Gal. stainless steel wet dry vac is designed to deliver the powerful suction, large capacity, rugged construction, unique features and excellent mobility that pro\'s demand for jobsite or shop. The powerful 6.5 peak horsepower motor easily handles the toughest jobsite clean-up tasks. A 3-layer fine dust filter, VF5000 captures drywall dust. Moving up and down steps or across rough terrain is a snap with the large fixed rear wheels and cart handle. The top handle doubles as a cord wrap, and an accessory storage bag keeps vac attachments close at hand. The cart handle includes a quick release design which allows easy emptying. This stainless steel construction shop vac also features RIDGID\'s patented Scroll Noise Reduction for quiet operation.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6.5 peak HP motor provides powerful suction for heavy-duty cleanups&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Blowing port provides for blowing leaves from walkways and decks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;20 ft. cord provides extensive reach&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in drain for easy emptying of liquids&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Accessory storage space gives you quick access to attachments&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes 2 wands, a utility nozzle, a car nozzle, a wet nozzle and a crevice tool&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stainless-steel construction for durability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Peak Horsepower represents a level at or below the maximum horsepower output of an electric motor tested in a laboratory using a dynamometer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Gallons indicated reflect drum volume, not necessarily collection capacity; actual capacity dependent upon type of debris collected, condition of filter, and other factors&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Limited lifetime warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ACCESSORIES/PARTS INCLUDED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIncludes a 2-1/2&quot; x 7\' Dual-Flex Locking Hose, 2 Extension Wands, Utility Nozzle, Car Nozzle, Wet Nozzle, Crevice Tool and Fine Dust Cartridge Filter VF5000&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DIMENSIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hose Diameter (In.): 2.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hose Length (ft.): 7&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 19.8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 28.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 19.8&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Air Volume (CFM): 203&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Amperage (amps): 12&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color Family: Oranges/Peaches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cord Length (ft.): 20&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Filter Type: Paper&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Floor Care Features: Blower Port,Built-In Accessory Storage,Built-In Drain,Casters&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Peak Horsepower: 6.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 40 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Safe For Use On: Auto Interior,Bare Floor,Carpet,Concrete,Laminate,Leather,Stairs,Tile,Upholstery,Vinyl,Wood&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Vacuum Capacity (Gallons): 16&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage (volts): 120&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'RIDGID WD1956 16 gal. 6.5-Peak HP Stainless Steel Wet Dry Vac', 'RIDGID WD1956 16 gal. 6.5-Peak HP Stainless Steel Wet Dry Vac', 'RIDGID WD1956 16 gal. 6.5-Peak HP Stainless Steel Wet Dry Vac'),
(10579, 1, 'Dyna-Glo Pro 80K BTU Forced Air Kerosene Portable Heater', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DYNA-GLO PRO 80K BTU FORCED AIR KEROSENE PORTABLE HEATER, MODEL # KFA80H&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Provides 80,000 BTUs, heating 1,900 sq. ft. for up to 9 hours&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Thermostat, run-time fuel gauge, cord wrap, and flameout sensor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;For Outdoor/Indoor Construction Use&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Dyna-Glo Pro 80,000 BTU Portable Forced-Air Kerosene Heater can help you stay warm and comfortable on the chilliest days. The continuous-spark ignition helps ensure a quick start, and the automatic shutoff and non-slip base help provide safe use. The heater features a handle and wrap cord to offer portability and easy transport. All Dyna-Glo Pro Kerosene Forced Air Heaters are CSA certified for multi-fuel use with these fuel types: K1 Kerosene, Diesel #1, Diesel #2, Fuel Oil #1, Fuel Oil #2, Jet A and JP-8. However, K1 Kerosene is the manufacturer’s recommended fuel for optimal, cleaner burns and long lasting product life.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Can produce up to 80,000 BTU/hr to help keep you warm and comfortable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;For use in outdoor or indoor construction or commercial environments with proper ventilation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Convenient 5 Gal. fuel capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Continuous-spark ignition helps ensure a fast start&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic shutoff and non-slip base help provide safety and peace of mind&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in fuel-gauge helps you monitor the fuel supply&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in thermostat allows you to choose and maintain the temperature you desire&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in air pressure-gauge and a dual-source power cord are included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy-lift carrying handle and cord wrap help provide portability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Note: product may vary by store&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DIMENSIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 11.69&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 16.69&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 32.01&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Area Heated (Sq. Ft.): 1900.000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Orange&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color Family: Oranges/Peaches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel Tank Capacity (gallons): 5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fuel rate (gallons/hour): .6&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heat rating (BTU/hour): 80000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heater Controls: Thermostat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heater Type: Forced Air&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heating Product Type: Kerosene Heater&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heating Technology Type: Forced Air&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ignition Type: Electrical&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Indoor/Outdoor: Outdoor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Metal&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Heat Settings: 1 Heat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Portable Heater Features: Automatic Shutoff,Fuel Gauge,Thermostat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power/Fuel Type: Multiple&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 26.9lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Run time (hours): 9&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Certifications and Listings: 1-UL Listed,CSA Listed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: 1 Year Limited&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Dyna-Glo Pro 80K BTU Forced Air Kerosene Portable Heater', 'Dyna-Glo Pro 80K BTU Forced Air Kerosene Portable Heater', 'Dyna-Glo Pro 80K BTU Forced Air Kerosene Portable Heater'),
(10580, 1, 'Whynter 70-Pint Portable Dehumidifier With Pump Energy Star', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHYNTER 70-PINT PORTABLE DEHUMIDIFIER WITH PUMP, ENERGY STAR, MODEL # RPD-702WP&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Whynter Energy Star 70-Pint portable dehumidifier is a high capacity unit with exceptional low-temperature operability. As an Energy Star-rated dehumidifier, the Whynter RPD-702WP provides cost-effective and energy-efficient operation, without sacrificing design and performance. Featuring an internal condensate pump, this unit is specifically designed for high volume usage without having to worry about interrupted operation. This dehumidifier can be continuously operated with 3 drainage options; manual drain, gravity drain and condensate pump drain. The condensate pump can pump out (and up) condensation water through the included 16.5 ft. drain for continuous water removal with approximately 15 ft. of vertical lift. This high capacity unit is ideal for the basement, attic or any heavy humidity spaces. To maintain a steady, comfortable humidity level, this Whynter dehumidifier comes standard with an auto-restart and auto-shutoff options for the compressor that activate based on your selected humidity level. Built for high capacity usage, this unit is suited for enclosed areas as large 3800 sq. ft.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Energy star certified 70-Pint (33 l) capacity dehumidifier&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;18-Pint (8.5 l) removable water bucket&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Condensate pump that pushes water up or over a longer distance; 16.5 ft. drain hose included for condensate pump drain&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Direct drain option for continuous operation; 3 ft. drain hose included for gravity drainage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto-restart and auto-shutoff functions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable humidity range of 30 - 90% relative humidity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low temperature operation (minimum ambient temperature low 40°F)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto-defrosting capability to prevent frost build-up inside unit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual fan speeds and 24 timer function&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Washable pre-filter included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Handles and caster wheels for portability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Non ozone-depleting refrigerant: R410a&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Air flow (at high speed): 187 m3/h/110CFM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power consumption: 950-Watt/7.5 Amp&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DIMENSIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 11.25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 23.25&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Width (in.): 14.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable Humidistat: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Air Treatment Product Type: Dehumidifier&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic defrost control: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic shutoff: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bucket Full Indicator: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bucket Location: Front&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bucket Storage or Bucketless: Bucket Storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bucket capacity (pints): 18&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Casters: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color Family: Whites&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Continuous Run: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control Type: Digital&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Drain Hose Included: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Drain hose connection: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LCD display: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Minimum operating temperature (F): 40&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Moisture removal capacity (pints/day): 70&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Fan Speeds: 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Weight (lb.): 45lb&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pump: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Remote Control: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Timer: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage (volts): 115&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Certifications and Listings: 1-UL Listed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: One year limited warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Whynter 70-Pint Portable Dehumidifier With Pump Energy Star', 'Whynter 70-Pint Portable Dehumidifier With Pump Energy Star', 'Whynter 70-Pint Portable Dehumidifier With Pump Energy Star'),
(10581, 1, 'Honeywell RCHT8610WF Lyric T5 Wi-Fi Thermostat', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HONEYWELL LYRIC T5 WI-FI THERMOSTAT, MODEL # RCHT8610WF&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control from anywhere via smartphone or tablet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Learns your heating/cooling cycles to maintain the optimal temp&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible with Apple HomeKit and other Lyric products&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Manage your home comfort anywhere, anytime or let it manage your comfort and savings automatically with the Lyric T5 Wi-Fi Thermostat. Choose from two different ways to control to fit your schedule or spur-of-the moment activities: 7-day scheduling or location based temperature control. With smart alerts, you will receive push notifications to remind you of filter changes and warn of extreme indoor temperatures. Intelligent comfort control maintains comfort by considering indoor and outdoor temperature and humidity. Plus, the Lyric T5 is fully compatible with Apple HomeKit so all your home comforts are taken care of - the simple, intuitive way. Honeywell Lyric is a Wi-Fi connected platform that simplifies home comfort, security and awareness by controlling all of your connected home products with a single application. Individually, each product performs brilliantly. Together, they\'re a way to orchestrate life.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wi-Fi enabled - control from anywhere&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Your choice of comfort control: 7-day scheduling or location based temperature control using geo-fence technology to make you comfortable by using your smartphone\'s location to know when you\'re away and when you return&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ecosystem integration - works with Apple HomeKit for a greater connected home experience&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy setup - installation through the Lyric app&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smart alerts - send push notifications to remind you to change your filter and warn you of extreme indoor temperatures&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Auto change from heat to cool - automatically determines if your home needs heating or cooling to provide maximum comfort&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smart response learns your home\'s heating and cooling cycle times to deliver the optimal temperature at the right time&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Connected by the Lyric app&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Works perfectly with Honeywell\'s Lyric family of products&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;App is compatible with Android and iOS smartphones and tablets&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DIMENSIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Display height (in.): 3.5 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Display width (in.): 3.5 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 1.0625 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 4.0625 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery Power Type: Hardwired&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery Size: Hardwired&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color Family: Blacks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Features: Automatic Heating/Cooling Changeover,Backlit Display,Built-in Wi-Fi,Daylight Savings Time Ready,Filter Monitor,Touch Screen,Vacation Mode&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Included: Thermostat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Periods per Programmable Day: 4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shape: Square&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smart Technology: Smart Home Hub Compatible&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Thermostat Product Type: Programmable Thermostat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Thermostat Type: Heating and Cooling&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage (volts): 24&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Certifications and Listings: No Certifications or Listings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty: 2 Year Limited Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Honeywell RCHT8610WF Lyric T5 Wi-Fi Thermostat', 'Honeywell RCHT8610WF Lyric T5 Wi-Fi Thermostat', 'Honeywell RCHT8610WF Lyric T5 Wi-Fi Thermostat'),
(10582, 1, 'Ecobee3 Lite 7 Day Programmable Smart Thermostat with Touchscreen', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ECOBEE3 LITE - 7 DAY PROGRAMMABLE SMART THERMOSTAT WITH TOUCHSCREEN&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Save money on your monthly energy bills&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control from anywhere with your iOS or Android device&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Now works with room sensors. Sold separately&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With its beautiful design, easy-to-use touchscreen display, and up to 23% annual savings on heating and cooling costs, the ecobee3 lite is the smarter thermostat that helps you live better and save more. It also now pairs with room sensors to help manage hot or cold spots in the home, delivering comfort to the rooms that matter most. And because they track occupancy, they make your home even smarter about saving energy when you’re away. ecobee3 lite pairs with up to 32 sensors. Works with Amazon Echo, Google Assistant, Apple HomeKit, Samsung SmartThings, Wink and IFTTT. We want you to love our products as much as we do, so your ecobee comes backed by a 3-year warranty. Learn more at ecobee.com/savings.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pays you back in savings: By conserving energy, your ecobee3 lite pays for itself in savings—and keeps it up, year after year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control from anywhere: Control your ecobee from your iOS (including Apple Watch) or Android devices anywhere, anytime&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wireless room sensors: Sensors work with your ecobee3 lite to deliver comfort in the rooms that matter most. And because they track occupancy, they’re smarter about saving energy when you’re away&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smarter comfort: Your ecobee3 lite works with your local weather, schedule, and desired comfort settings. That’s how we ensure comfort when you’re home, and savings when you’re not&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Integration: Integrates with your favorite platforms like Amazon Alexa, Google Assistant, Apple HomeKit, Samsung SmartThings, IFTTT and Wink&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fast, easy installation: We’ve designed the ecobee3 lite so that everything you need is in the box. The step-by-step guide on our app and free expert support make it easy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible with most: ecobee3 lite is designed to be compatible with most residential heating and cooling systems. Learn more at ecobee.com/compatibility&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smart home/away: Set up your schedule to ensure comfort when you’re home, and savings when you’re not. Your ecobee3 lite, when paired with room sensors, can sense if you’re home during a scheduled Away period (and vice versa) to automatically override your schedule&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smart recovery: ecobee3 lite learns how long it takes for your equipment to heat and cool your home combining that information with the local weather, it will use the least amount of time to pre-heat or pre-cool your home for the next scheduled temperature change to ensure your comfort&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DIMENSIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Display height (in.): 4.05 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Display width (in.): 4.05 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Depth (in.): 2.12 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Height (in.): 4.05 in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery Power Type: Lithium Coin&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery Size: CR2025&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color Family: Blacks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Features: Automatic Heating/Cooling Changeover,Built-in Wi-Fi,Daylight Savings Time Ready,Filter Monitor,Touch Screen,Vacation Mode&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hub Required: Samsung SmartThings Hub,Wink Hub&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Included: Batteries,Display Base,Dry Wall Plugs,Mounting Hardware,Power Extender Kit,Thermostat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Periods per Programmable Day: 24&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Options: C-wire,Plug-in&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Remote Access: Remote Access&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Requires Hub?: Requires Smart Hub&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shape: Specialty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smart Home: Smart Home Enabled&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smart Home Protocol: Wi-Fi&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smart Technology: Smart Phone/Android App Compatible&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Thermostat Product Type: Smart/Wi-Fi&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Thermostat Type: Heating and Cooling&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voice Control Hub Required: Siri via Apple HomeKit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage (volts): 3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Works With: Universal&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Works With: Apple HomeKit, Samsung SmartThings, Siri, Wink&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Ecobee3 Lite 7 Day Programmable Smart Thermostat with Touchscreen', 'Ecobee3 Lite 7 Day Programmable Smart Thermostat with Touchscreen', 'Ecobee3 Lite 7 Day Programmable Smart Thermostat with Touchscreen'),
(10217, 1, 'InSinkErator Evolution Compact 3/4 HP Household Garbage Disposer', '&lt;p&gt;The space-saving Evolution Compact includes two grind stages and is 40% quieter than a standard disposer. It\'s perfect for small households or restricted cabinet space. With an InSinkErator food waste disposer in your kitchen, chicken bones, fruit rinds, coffee grounds and more can go right in the sink -- where they\'re virtually liquefied to safely flow into your sewage system or septic tank. You\'ll enjoy a cleaner food preparation area, and less bagged garbage cluttering your home. What\'s more, if you\'ve never owned a food waste disposer, you\'re in for a pleasant surprise. InSinkErator disposers are economical to operate: in fact, they\'re among the least expensive installed kitchen appliances.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;MultiGrind two grind stages let you quickly grind difficult food waste you wouldn\'t put in a standard disposer, like celery and potato peels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SoundSeal makes the Evolution Compact at least 40% quieter than standard disposers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;34.6-Ounce stainless steel grind chamber and grind component handles more volume than standard disposers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Continuous feed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick lock sink mount&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Evolution Series collection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3/4 Horsepower Dura-Drive induction motor gives you more horsepower than standard disposers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Full 4 year parts and in-home service warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT DETAILS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Horsepower: 3/4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage: 120 Volts (V)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Cord Included: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Country of Manufacture: United States&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Warranty: 4 Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall: 12.13&quot; H x 8&quot; W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Horsepower: 3/4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage: 120 Volts (V)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power Cord Included: No&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Country of Manufacture: United States&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product Type: Garbage disposal&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Grind Chamber Capacity: 34.6 Ounces&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Noise Insulated: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Feed Type: Continuous&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible Power Cord: CRD-00&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DOCUMENTS (PDF FILES):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ankermart.com/image/data/B000G837TW/Installation-Assembly.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Installation&amp;nbsp;Assembly&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ankermart.com/image/data/B000G837TW/Installation-Instructions.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Installation Instructions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ankermart.com/image/data/B000G837TW/Warranty-Information.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.8px;&quot;&gt;Warranty&amp;nbsp;Information&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'InSinkErator Evolution Compact 3/4 HP Household Garbage Disposer', 'InSinkErator Evolution Compact 3/4 HP Household Garbage Disposer', 'InSinkErator Evolution Compact 3/4 HP Household Garbage Disposer');
