(10602, 1, 'Toro PowerPlex 40V Max 14 Inch Brushless String Trimmer, 51482', '&lt;p&gt;Designed for homeowners with more work to do than time to get it done; homeowners who appreciate the century of innovation and durability established by time-tested Toro products. Toro’s new family of cordless 40V PowerPlex® Lithium Ion yard tools give you more power and save you more time with an interchangeable T90 battery that provides up to 40 minutes of run time** and this battery charges in approximately 60 minutes in the quick charger. Three of the five products in the PowerPlex line carry a Brushless Motor, providing a more powerful, more efficient, and longer life than their brushed motor counter-parts. Featuring a 3 Year Full Warranty, Toro’s PowerPlex products are backed by one of the best yard tool warranties in the industry, keeping you running season after season.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;*Battery manufacturer rating = 40V maximum &amp;amp; 36V nominal. Actual voltage varies with load.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n**Based on low speed, free run laboratory testing of product.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brushless DC Motor: Get more power, more runtime and longer life than brushed motor.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;0.08&quot; Dual Line with Bump Feed: Durable, productive line control.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Variable Speed: Lower Speed = Longer Run Time / Higher Speed = More Power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cast-Aluminum Head: For long-lasting durability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Straight, Foldable Shaft: For easy storage and transport.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;T90 Battery: T90 battery (90 watt-hours) provides up to 40 minutes run time from a full charge.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick Charger: Table top or wall mount options. Charges T90 in 60 minutes, T180 in 120 minutes. Comes standard with the PowerPlex complete tools.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brushless Motor - Powerful, efficient and longer life&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;0.08&quot; (2.03 mm) Dual Line With Bump Feed - Durable, productive line control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cast-Aluminum Head - For long-lasting durability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Variable Speed -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lower Speed = Longer Run Time&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Higher Speed = More Power&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Disclaimer: *Battery manufacturer rating = 40V maximum &amp;amp; 36V nominal. Actual voltage varies with load.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 3-Year Full on Tools, 1-Year Full on Batteries***&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 9.2 lbs (4.2 kg) with battery / 7.0 lbs (3.2 kg) without battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Charger: Quick Charger (Model 88542) - Fully charges in 60 minutes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cutting Width: 14&quot; (35.56 cm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Handle Design: Straight, foldable shaft&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Line Feed: Bump&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Line Type: Dual (.08”) (2.03 mm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Replacement Spool: 88546 (3-Pack), Use only .08 inch (2.03 mm) diameter monofilament string. Use original manufacturer’s replacement string for best performance.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BATTERY POWER:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;T90 Battery* (Model 88540 - Included)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;40-Volt Max, 2.5 Amp-Hour, 90 Watt-Hour&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;T180 Battery* (Model 88541 - Compatible)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;40-Volt Max, 5.0 Amp-Hour, 180 Watt-Hour&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'PowerPlex 40V Max 14 Inch Brushless String Trimmer, 51482', 'PowerPlex 40V Max 14 Inch Brushless String Trimmer, 51482', 'PowerPlex 40V Max 14 Inch Brushless String Trimmer, 51482'),
(10605, 1, 'Joseph Joseph 30030 Intelligent Waste Titan Trash Can Compactor', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JOSEPH JOSEPH® TITAN COMPACTING WASTE CAN IN STAINLESS STEEL&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nJoseph Joseph packs 90 liters of trash into the 30 liter Titan Compacting Waste Can. Its patented compacting plate doesn\'t directly contact trash and won\'t tear your liners. A built-in filter controls odors.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;COMPACT YOUR WASTE. MAXIMISE SPACE.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTitan\'s patented compaction system enables it to hold up to three times more waste than a similar-sized household waste can.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HYGENIC &amp;amp; MESS-FREE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTitan\'s patented design ensures only the inside of the plastic liner touches the trash while compacting, leaving you with clean hands and a clean can&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WON\'T TEAR YOUR LINERS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTitan\'s anti-tear design won\'t stretch, pinch or tear the liner. Custom-fit liners avaliable. Also compatible with standard plastic liners.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;INTEGRATED ODOR FILTER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTitan features an integrated odor filter compartment inside its lid which holds replaceable filters, available seperately&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions : 31¼ x 15¾ x 11¾ inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight : 17.4 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Care &amp;amp; Use Guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;10-Year Garantee&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Against manufacturing defects&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Good Housekeeping: Institute Approved&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fingerprint-proof: Stainless steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Joseph Joseph 30030 Intelligent Waste Titan Trash Can Compactor', 'Joseph Joseph 30030 Intelligent Waste Titan Trash Can Compactor', 'Joseph Joseph 30030 Intelligent Waste Titan Trash Can Compactor'),
(10606, 1, 'Antigravity XP-10-HD Micro-Start Heavy Duty', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NEW MODEL! MICRO-START XP-10-HD HEAVY DUTY (HD) JUMP STARTER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;Our best-selling and #1 rated jump starter in the USA has just gotten better! The NEW XP-10-HD kit is perfect for mechanics and commercial or daily use. It includes the HEAVY DUTY Smart Clamps featuring a larger, stronger jaw and unbreakable All-Copper construction.&amp;nbsp; The Micro-Start XP-10 is unrivaled for performance &amp;amp; quality in the mini jump-start segment. This is our MOST POWERFUL and TOP RATED Micro-Start PPS (personal power supply). Small enough to fit in your hand yet has the amazing power to Jump-Start DIESEL vehicles up to 7.3L, as well as gas engines. Charge &amp;amp; Power most any electronics: 19V Laptops, 12V Devices, two USB 5V Devices!&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;The new Heavy Duty model of XP-10 Micro-Start has more power and includes the much larger, unbreakable all-copper Smart Clamps. Built for mechanics and commercial or daily use, this is the go-to Jump-Starter Kit for those who will most often use their XP-10 with cars, trucks, boats, or other larger vehicles. Now with some internal upgrades and using the Heavy Duty Smart Clamps, the XP-10-HD can put out an additional 50 Amps of cranking power over the original XP-10 model.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;The larger wires and jaw of the Heavy Duty Smart Clamps allow a much better connection to the vehicle’s battery terminals. They have a stronger clamping force and transfer the electrical current much better. Additionally these clamps have 5 built-in safety protections like our other clamps including reverse polarity protection, back-charge protection, short-circuit protection and more.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;POWER: 300 Amps / 650A Peak&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CAPACITY: 18,000 mAh&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;PORTS: 19V + 12V + Two USB 5V&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;FLASHLIGHT: 110-Lumen LED&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JUMP-START&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;DIESELS up to 7.3L, and Gas Engine vehicles: Cars, Trucks, Motorcycles, ATVs, UTVs, Snowmobiles, other Powersports Vehicles, Boats, other Watercraft.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;300 Amps starting current – 650A Peak!&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CHARGE &amp;amp; POWER&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;19V Laptops (not compatible with Apple 16V laptops)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;12V Devices: GPS, Mobile DVD Players, Small Fans, LED lighting and more.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;USB Devices: all Cell / SmartPhones, Tablets, Kindles, iReaders, GoPros, other Cameras, PSPs / Handheld Games, MP3 / Music Players, Bluetooth devices, etc.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;18,000 mAh capacity.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MORE FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LED Flashlight built-in with 3 beam modes (steady, strobe, SOS beacon).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lighted capacity indicator. Press a button to see level of battery capacity remaining in the Micro-Start.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic power-off when not in use; you do not need to turn it off.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in protections for over-charge &amp;amp; over-discharge. Long battery life.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rechargeable lithium battery. Recharge the XP-10-HD itself via wall outlet or vehicle cig lighter port.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Top Quality design, build-quality and safety features. UL listed battery cells.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KIT CONTENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;The Micro-Start XP-10-HD model comes with everything you need in a convenient carrying case.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Leatherette Carry Case that holds all parts neatly organized.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Micro-Start XP-10-HD (Heavy Duty) PPS.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Set of SMART Mini Jumper Clamps with Multiple Safety Protections built-in (prevents reverse polarity connection, over-charge, over-discharge, short-circuit, back-charge).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 universal DC Cable (black) for all 12V Accessories &amp;amp; use with…&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;8 detachable Laptop Tips (Fits many but not every Laptop charging port. Fits: Apple, Acer, Dell, HP, Asus, more).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 universal 4-into-1 USB Cable (white). Tips: Mini USB, Micro USB, Apple 8-pin, and type-C.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Mobile Charger (plugs into cigarette lighter socket).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Home Charger (plugs into wall outlet).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Instruction Manual.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Antigravity XP-10-HD Micro-Start Heavy Duty', 'Antigravity XP-10-HD Micro-Start Heavy Duty', 'Antigravity XP-10-HD Micro-Start Heavy Duty'),
(10607, 1, 'Antigravity XP-10 Micro-Start', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MICRO-START XP-10 TOP RATED JUMP STARTER!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Micro-Start XP-10 is unrivaled for performance &amp;amp; quality in the mini jump-start segment. This is our Best Selling and TOP RATED Micro-Start PPS (personal power supply). Small enough to fit in your hand yet has the amazing power to Jump-Start DIESEL vehicles up to 7.3L, as well as gas engines. Charge &amp;amp; Power most any electronics: 19V Laptops, 12V Devices, two USB 5V Devices!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The XP-10 is unrivaled for performance and quality in the mini jump-start segment. It was rated the #1 BEST JUMP STARTER. That says a tremendous amount about the quality and abilities of Antigravity Batteries products. See how Consumer Reports stacks us up against the competition. The Micro-Start XP-10 Portable Power Supply (PPS) has proven to be the go-to device for professional mechanics as well as everyday riders and travelers.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;POWER: 300 Amps / 600A Peak&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CAPACITY: 18,000 mAh&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;PORTS: 19V + 12V + Two USB 5V&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;FLASHLIGHT: 110-Lumen LED&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JUMP-START&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDIESELS up to 7.3L, and Gas Engine vehicles: Cars, Trucks, Motorcycles, ATVs, UTVs, Snowmobiles, other Powersports Vehicles, Boats, other Watercraft.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n300 Amps starting current – 600A Peak!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CHARGE &amp;amp; POWER&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;19V Laptops (not compatible with Apple 16V laptops)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;12V Devices: GPS, Mobile DVD Players, Small Fans, LED lighting and more.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;USB Devices: all Cell / SmartPhones, Tablets, Kindles, iReaders, GoPros, other Cameras, PSPs / Handheld Games, MP3 / Music Players, Bluetooth devices, etc.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;18,000 mAh capacity.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MORE FEATURES&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LED Flashlight built-in with 3 beam modes (steady, strobe, SOS beacon).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lighted capacity indicator. Press a button to see level of battery capacity remaining in the Micro-Start.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Automatic power-off when not in use; you do not need to turn it off.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in protections for over-charge &amp;amp; over-discharge. Long battery life.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rechargeable lithium battery. Recharge the XP-10 itself via wall outlet or vehicle cig lighter port.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Top Quality design, build-quality and safety features. UL listed battery cells.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KIT CONTENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;The Micro-Start XP-10 model comes with everything you need in a convenient carrying case.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Leatherette Carry Case that holds all parts neatly organized*.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Micro-Start XP-10 PPS.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Set of SMART Mini Jumper Clamps with Multiple Safety Protections built-in (prevents reverse polarity connection, over-charge, over-discharge, short-circuit, back-charge).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 universal DC Cable (black) for all 12V Accessories &amp;amp; use with…&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;8 detachable Laptop Tips (Fits many but not every Laptop charging port. Fits: Apple, Acer, Dell, HP, Asus, more).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 universal 4-into-1 USB Cable (white). (Tips: Mini USB, Micro USB, Apple 8-pin, Apple 30-pin).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Mobile Charger (plugs into cigarette lighter socket).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Home Charger (plugs into wall outlet).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Instruction Manual.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;* Note: internal organization of carry case differs from photo and is now upgraded, featuring mesh pockets to hold parts more securely.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Antigravity XP-10 Micro-Start', 'Antigravity XP-10 Micro-Start', 'Antigravity XP-10 Micro-Start'),
(10608, 1, 'Ergobaby 360 All Carry Positions Award-Winning Cool Mesh Ergonomic Baby Carrier', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;360 BABY CARRIER ALL CARRY POSITIONS: COOL AIR MESH - CARBON GREY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nErgobaby\'s Award-Winning 360 Baby Carrier All Carry Positions with Cool Air Mesh offers every carry positions in a cool and breathable fabric to get out and about with baby, from summer hikes to leisurely strolls.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;MAXIMUM COMFORT FOR BABY- With its unique, structured bucket seat, the versatile Ergobaby 360 carrier keeps baby ergonomically seated in all carrying positions (front-outward, front- inward, hip and back carry). Always ensures your baby is seated in an ergonomic &quot;M&quot;; shape position with knees even to or above hips, and spine in curved &quot;C&quot;; position. The versatile extendable back panel can be folded in providing head support for your young baby or unfolded extending the back panel giving your toddler the back support they need&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;MAXIMUM COMFORT FOR YOU- The wide padded waistband ensures maximum comfort by providing you with the support you need to maintain a healthy posture preventing lower back pain&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;COOL &amp;amp; BREATHABLE- Our Cool Air Mesh collection carriers are made with wonderfully soft and durable mesh fabric that provides our renowned ergonomic support for baby while allowing for ultimate breathability and airflow.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHighest safety standard - At Ergobaby, we take safety seriously.&amp;nbsp; We hold all of our carriers to higher safety standards than those required by our industry&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;ADJUSTABLE- The 360 carrier is designed to fit all types of parents. It easily adjusts to fit multiple wearers from petite to larger body types (waistband adjusts 26-52&quot;; shoulder straps adjust from 28 3/4&quot; to 46 3/4&quot;). This way, all parents can share the joy of babywearing. The 360 carrier is also adjustable to your growing baby from 7lbs* to 33lbs (*with an infant insert sold separately).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;STRONG, DURABLE, LONG LASTING CARRIER-&amp;nbsp; Can be used for multiple years and multiple babies. No snagging &amp;amp; loosening. Carrier retains shape after wash for long-lasting use and comfort.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;BABY-SAFE MATERIALS- Oeko-tex; standard 100% certified fabrics&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;COMFORTABLE FOR YOU &amp;amp; YOUR BABY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEasy to adjust bucket seat supports your baby in an ergonomic natural \'M\' position in all carry positions from baby to toddler.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ALL THE CARRY POSITIONS YOU NEED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFace baby in or out. Wear on the hip or back as baby grows (~4-36 months/12-33lbs or start with newborn infant insert ~0-4Months/7-12lbs, sold separately).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LIGHTWEIGHT &amp;amp; BREATHABLE MESH&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCooler for you &amp;amp; baby with soft, lightweight &amp;amp; durable mesh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FITS YOU &amp;amp; YOUR PARTNER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEasily adjusts to fit multiple wearers from petite to larger body types (waistbelt adjusts 26-52&quot;, shoulder straps 28-46&quot;).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WE CONSIDERED EVERY DETAIL&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEasy breastfeeding &amp;amp; UPF 50+ tuckaway babyhood for sun &amp;amp; wind protection.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EASY TO CLEAN QUALITY MATERIALS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n100% Soft, Durable Quickdry Polyester.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Ergobaby 360 Baby Carrier All Carry Positions Cool Air Mesh - Carbon Grey, Ergobaby 360 All Carry Positions Award-Winning Cool Mesh Ergonomic Baby Carrier', 'Ergobaby 360 Baby Carrier All Carry Positions Cool Air Mesh - Carbon Grey, Ergobaby 360 All Carry Positions Award-Winning Cool Mesh Ergonomic Baby Carrier', 'Ergobaby 360 Baby Carrier All Carry Positions Cool Air Mesh - Carbon Grey, Ergobaby 360 All Carry Positions Award-Winning Cool Mesh Ergonomic Baby Carrier'),
(10609, 1, 'Ergobaby Omni 360 Baby Carrier All-In-One', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IMPORTANT: LIMIT 1 PER CUSTOMER! ORDERS THAT EXCEED LISTED AVAILABILITY WILL AUTOMATICALLY BE VOIDED WITHOUT NOTICE.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OMNI 360 BABY CARRIER ALL-IN-ONE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOur all-in-one, newborn ready Omni 360 has all the carry positions you need. The Omni 360 has an adjustable seat grows that grows with your baby, crossable shoulder straps, storage pouch, and a lumbar support waistbelt. You can have it all in this carrier! From Ergobaby, this carrier features:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;All carry positions including front outward facing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Newborn to toddler (7-45 lbs.), no infant insert needed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick &amp;amp; easy to switch baby to face in or out on the fly&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lumbar support waistbelt for long wearing comfort (adjusts 26&quot; – 55“)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Detachable storage pouch included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra-cushioned crossable shoulder straps (adjusts 28 ¾&quot; – 48 ¾&quot;)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easily adjusts to fit multiple users&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ergonomically holds baby in M-shape position at all carry positions, including facing out&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cushioned, adjustable head and neck support&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tuck-away baby hood for sun protection and privacy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Allows for easy and discrete breastfeeding&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cotton&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Machine washable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;1-year manufacturer\'s warranty&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Ergobaby Omni 360 Baby Carrier All-In-One Pure Black', 'Ergobaby Omni 360 Baby Carrier All-In-One Pure Black', 'Ergobaby Omni 360 Baby Carrier All-In-One Pure Black'),
(10610, 1, 'Jigsort 1500 Jigsaw Puzzle Case For Up To 1,500 Pieces From Jigthings', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JIGSORT 1500 - JIGSAW PUZZLE CASE FOR UP TO 1,500 PIECES FROM JIGTHINGS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Jigsort 1500 is the largest Jigsort in the range. The board within this puzzle carrier/case/holder measures 35.5 inches; x 25.5 inches; and it will accommodate almost all the puzzles you are likely to come across. For a complete list of puzzle types that fit please see the table at the bottom of this page.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Complete Puzzle system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Everything packs away&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Light removable board&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Separate sort trays&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy to transport&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This is the puzzle case most often used by dedicated puzzle enthusiasts and aficionados! The great majority of popular puzzles are made in the 1000 piece size and it could therefore be argued that a 1000 piece Jigsort would be adequate but even when doing 1000 piece jigsaws there is a case for using a Jigsort 1500.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;If you are a regular puzzle-doer you will know how it is when you pick up a puzzle piece that doesn\'t quite fit but you know you will have need of it soon! Well, the extra space around the outside of a 1000 piece puzzle that is sitting on a 1500 size board provides the ideal area to keep the piece safe for later use!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;As you have already learned, Jigsorts are made of the highest quality, durable materials and with the Jigsort 1500 this means they are a substantial weight - nearly 20lbs. For anyone under retirement age this is not likely to be a major problem but it is something to keep in mind if the product will be used by someone elderly.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE LISTS BELOW SHOW THE SIZES OF PUZZLE THAT CAN AND CANNOT BE ACCOMMODATED IN THE JIGSORT 1500:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://ankermart.com/image/data/JIGSORT-1500-Listing.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 600px; height: 899px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Jigsort 1500 Jigsaw Puzzle Case For Up To 1,500 Pieces From Jigthings', 'Jigsort 1500 Jigsaw Puzzle Case For Up To 1,500 Pieces From Jigthings', 'Jigsort 1500 Jigsaw Puzzle Case For Up To 1,500 Pieces From Jigthings'),
(10611, 1, 'Kettler Roma Folding Lounger in White Resin', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ROMA MULTI POSITION LOUNGER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Constructed of high impact resin&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Backrest reclines for four comfortable seating positions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Contoured back for added comfort&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folds for easy self standing storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Replaceable foot inserts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Drop down foot section and large wheels for easy maneuverability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unique Safety-Fold track&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Minimal wheel assembly required&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Item No:1638-000&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Description: ROMA MULTI POSITION LOUNGER&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Country of Origin: Germany&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Setup Length/Width/Height:72 x 31 x 42 inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Setup Weight:24 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Package Length/Width/Height:38 x 28 x 9 inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Package Weight:30 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Commercial Warranty:3 YEAR&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Residential Warranty:3 YEAR&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight Limit:265 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ships Assembled: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ship Via: FedEx&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Kettler Roma Folding Lounger in White Resin', 'Kettler Roma Folding Lounger in White Resin', 'Kettler Roma Folding Lounger in White Resin'),
(10612, 1, 'Fastcap 3HANDCPACK 3rd Hand Contractor Poles, 4-Pack', '&lt;p&gt;If you\'ve ever wished for a helping hand on one of your home improvement projects, the FastCap 3rd Hand Contractor Pack is your dream come true. Featuring heavy-duty telescopic poles, this contractor pack includes dust-barrier feet, universal feet, articulating feet, and a carrying bag. All the help you\'ve been looking for, the 3rd Hand Contractor Pack will help you brace, clamp, and support, so you can independently set up dust barriers, install crown molding, stabilize loads in your truck, secure flooring, put up shelves, and much, much more.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THIS CONVENIENT PACK FOR CONTRACTORS INCLUDES:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(4) 3rd Hands&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(8) Articulating Feet&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(4) Magnetic Dust Feet&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(4) Universal Feet&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(1) Ballistic nylon Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE FASTCAP 3RD HAND CONTRACTOR PACK: NEVER SHOWS UP LATE FOR WORK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe 3rd Hand HD is the help you have been looking for. It is rugged, built to last a lifetime, and it\'s never late for work! If you\'ve ever wishedyou had an extra hand, here it is. The 3rd Hand HD can brace, clamp, or provide support wherever and whenever you might need it.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE CONTRACTOR PACK PACKAGE DEAL: FIT EVERYTHING YOU NEED IN ONE BAG!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTo keep all of these handy tools organized, the 3rd Hand Contractor Pack comes with a ballistic nylon carrying bag. The bag carries all four 3rd Hand HD poles and all the accessories: four Mag Dust Barrier feet, four UniversalFOOT Feet (6x6 inch), eight Articulating Feet (3x3-inch).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FOUR TELESCOPING POLES GIVE YOU A HAND WHEREVER YOU NEED IT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIf you\'re a contractor or do-it-yourselfer who needs reliable support, 3rd Hand HD poles are the perfect assistant--and they\'re never late for work! With a rugged 150-pound load capacity, the heavy-gauge steel poles are as useful as an extra set of hands, and with a neoprene grip, they are incredibly comfortable to use.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDesigned for optimum versatility, 3rd Hand HD Poles telescope from 4.75 to 12.0 feet in length. This ample range means you can keep your poles on hand from job to job, whether you\'re working on high ceilings or in tight spaces&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;A dual adjustment system gives you two options for quickly choosing your length: use the tightening knob for smaller adjustments or lock in your desired height with the ball detents, which are spaced 12 inches apart along each pole.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Once a pole is in position, simply use the easy-pump handle to get maximum stability for clamping, bracing, and support. Use one or two poles for light-duty projects--such as hanging shelves--or all four poles for larger jobs--such as stabilizing ceilings (four Hand HD poles are included in the Contractor Pack).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;When the job is complete, the poles\' quick-release levers make disassembly a snap.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HANDY ACCESSORIES PROVIDE VERSATILITY ON THE JOB&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhen you\'re bracing a workpiece, such as a wooden cabinet, you want to be sure it\'s going to remain stable. That\'s why each FastCap 3rd Hand HD Poles is equipped with a 360-degree fully articulating head and food (eight included in kit). These 3x3-inch textured pads will solidly grip surfaces at virtually any angle, and they can be micro adjusted for the right fit.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;When you want a larger grip area at the base of your poles, swap in the 6x6-inch 3rd Hand Universal Feet (four included), which are ideal for just about any job. Or if you\'re planning to seal off your work area to minimize dust transfer, attach the magnetic Mag Dust Barrier feet (four included) for a 100% seal and 0% dust.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;To keep all of these handy feet organized, the 3rd Hand Contractor Pack comes with a ballistic nylon carrying bag. The bag carries all four 3rd Hand HD poles and all the accessories&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FASTCAP VIDEOS &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;table style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 5px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: top;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;video&quot; src=&quot;http://cdn.cshardware.com/media/images/downloads/types/video.png&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: top;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gNwje0EvLwQ&amp;amp;feature=youtu.be&quot; onclick=&quot;window.open(this.href, \'\', \'resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=no,dependent=no\'); return false;&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; transition: color 300ms ease-in-out, background-color 300ms ease-in-out; outline: none; font-weight: 600;&quot; title=&quot;3rd Hand&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&