ot; onclick=&quot;window.open(this.href, \'\', \'resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=no,dependent=no\'); return false;&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; transition: color 300ms ease-in-out, background-color 300ms ease-in-out; outline: none; font-weight: 600;&quot; title=&quot;3rd Hand Tripod&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;3rd Hand Tripod&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Fastcap 3HANDCPACK 3rd Hand Contractor Poles, 4-Pack', 'Fastcap 3HANDCPACK 3rd Hand Contractor Poles, 4-Pack', 'Fastcap 3HANDCPACK 3rd Hand Contractor Poles, 4-Pack'),
(10613, 1, 'JIGTABLE - Jigsaw Puzzle Table From Jigthings', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SMALL TABLES THAT ARE IDEAL FOR MANY HOBBIES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThese small tables are easily moveable within your living space and make it possible to enjoy many different hobbies within a restricted area. The tables are most often sold for constructing jigsaws and on the&amp;nbsp; puzzle table overview page you can read why they have been so widely adopted for this purpose. Continue reading here to find how this type of small table makes it easier to manage any number of different tasks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ONE SMALL TABLE - MANY DIFFERENT USES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHave you ever met anyone who has enough room in their house for everything they want to do? Probably not because the quantity of furniture in a home tends to expand to fill the available space and then grow just a little bit more!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The ultimate luxury!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sit back and relax&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable for comfort&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Like an artist\'s easel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Use for other purposes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;An area and a table reserved just for jigsaw puzzles (or for any other single purpose) is a luxury that few of us can ever afford and we are therefore pleased to report that our customers invariably find a multitude of other uses for our tables. You may have read on Main Puzzle Table page that you will need to purchase either a Jigboard or a Jigsort as a companion for your table (assuming that jigsaw puzzling is one of the things you intend to use it for) and once you have this you are set to go.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With the board on the table you can angle the surface for comfortable puzzling or drawing. Alternatively, level-off the table and you have the perfect surface for playing board games, dice and card games with the rest of the family.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Take the board off and you then have a small table that is ideal for sewing, reading, writing and serving meals. Adjust the angle of tilt to suit the job in hand.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;If the table is not going to be used for a while then the Jigboard can be safely stowed away in a cupboard. The table itself is small enough and portable enough to be easily pushed into a corner where it can reside until it is next required.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Here\'s a tip that almost all our customers employ: Make sure that your favorite chair points towards the TV and that your puzzle table can be pulled over its arms - that way you will be able to watch TV AND be involved with any one of a myriad other enjoyable tasks at the same time.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IS THE TABLE SUITABLE FOR YOUR NEEDS?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe purchase of one of these small tables is a sizeable investment and you might like to bear in mind the following statistics before buying:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The size of the table top is 31 inches x 22 inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The base area is 32 inches x 23 inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The table comes complete with 4 castors - one for each corner&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The height of the table is adjustable between 27 inches and 33 inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The table can span an armchair up to 29 inches wide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The table top is an attractive laminate beech effect and is easy to wipe clean&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ONE LAST WORD!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWe know we have said it before but don\'t forget that the table doesn\'t work for puzzles unless you have a Jigboard or a Jigsort to go with it.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=5&amp;amp;v=CeCQTDZ_0hY&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=5&amp;amp;v=CeCQTDZ_0hY&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'JIGTABLE - Jigsaw Puzzle Table From Jigthings', 'JIGTABLE - Jigsaw Puzzle Table From Jigthings', 'JIGTABLE - Jigsaw Puzzle Table From Jigthings'),
(10614, 1, 'Ruff Tough Single Door Dog Kennel', '&lt;p&gt;Man\'s best friend deserves a dog kennel that\'s a cut above the rest.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;1.Intermediate&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 20&quot;W x 31&quot;L x 23&quot;H.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 21 lb.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Large&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 22&quot;W x 35&quot;L x 26&quot;H.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 30 lb.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY WE LOVE IT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nA truly stackable dog crate that offers superior strength, durability and has been field-tested to hold the weight of a 350-pound man.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CONSTRUCTION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One-piece construction offers superior strength.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rugged composite door won\'t rust.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Roto-molded plastic is easy to clean.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ADDITIONAL FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Portable and stackable dog crate.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Upper and lower panels offer ventilation.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Made in the USA.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Ruff Tough Single Door Dog Kennel', 'Ruff Tough Single Door Dog Kennel', 'Ruff Tough Single Door Dog Kennel'),
(10615, 1, 'SportDOG 425S Training System with Dog Collar', '&lt;p&gt;The FieldTrainer is the perfect system for introducing your dog to in-the-field training, or for hunting with close-working dogs. This series is loaded with technical breakthroughs in the smallest package available in this price range. Features such as 3-dog capability and waterproof/submersible transmitters and receivers are among the most advanced features ever offered in a mid-range training system. With 400-500 yards of range, these palm-of-the-hand sized models and comfortable “soft-coat” transmitter finish makes these units a pleasure to use.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KEY BENEFITS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mid-range/introductory system for all dogs over 8 lbs with 500 yard range&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3-dog capability, DRYTEK waterproof and submersible to 25 feet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Expandable up to 3 dogs with additional collars and includes rechargeable batteries&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tone and vibration options with 7 instantly selectable stimulation levels with low/medium ranges&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Perfect system for introducing your dog to in-the-field training, or for hunting with close-working dogs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPORTDOG SD-425 COMES WITH&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Active SportDOG SD-425 collar&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SportDOG SD-425 transmitter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Short stimulation probes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Long stimulation probes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable black collar strap with square roller buckle and metal keeper which fits up to a 23&quot; neck&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;User replaceable, rechargeable batteries in the collar + transmitter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual lead battery charger -- save time because you can charge both collar and transmitter at the same time from one plug&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra mud plug for both the transmitter and collar&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lanyard for the transmitter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Test light&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SportDOG owner\'s manual / operating guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&quot;Basic training&quot; booklet by Charles Jurney with Rick Smith and Tom Dokken&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Basic training DVD featuring pro trainers Charles Jurney, Rick Smith, Tom Dokken, and Chris Akin&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Robin Macfarlane\'s Basic Obedience Ecollar Training DVD&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Long line / checkcord&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;SPORTDOG SD-425 TRANSMITTER (REMOTE)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;500 yard range&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy to upgrade to 2 or 3 dogs without loss of tone/vibration feature&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;DryTek waterproof design -- submersible to 25 ft.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2-hour quick charge Li-Ion batteries that are also user replaceable (3-5 year lifespan with proper care)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;40- to 60-hour run time on a full charge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LED battery charge indicator lets you know transmitter is finished charging&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Small enough to hang from the included lanyard&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weighs only 1.6 ounces&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measures 1.75&quot; wide by 5.25&quot; tall with antenna&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Transmitter MODES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The SportDOG 425 gives you the option of customizing the transmitter to fit YOUR needs. It also allows you the option of changing the stimulation setup as your needs change or if you want different options in different situations.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Modes include Continuous and Momentary with Tone or Vibration. Two or Three Dog Mode features one button per dog with either Tone (Mode 3) or Vibration (Mode 4). You also have the option of Continuous and Momentary with Tone and the ability to activate/deactivate the Locate Beeper (sold separately).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Change MODES in seconds by setting the transmitter dial to the mode you want. Next press the recessed button on the back of the transmitter. The transmitter light then flashes back the number of the mode you have selected. Modes can be changed as often as you like. Change them for different situations or training&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPORTDOG SD-425 COLLAR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Slim-profile collar design fits closer to your dog\'s neck&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3/4&quot; black collar strap&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Internal antenna system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Plastic molded case built to withstand all kinds of training and hunting conditions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Waterproof collar/receiver (perfect for retriever training)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rechargeable Li-Ion batteries are user-replaceable, heavy duty, and last 3-5 years with proper care&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in LED is a battery charge indicator and test light&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 2.4 oz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Receiver Dimensions: 1&quot; wide x 2 1/2&quot; long x 1&quot; thick&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Collar Strap Dimensions: 3/4&quot; x 28&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fits up to a 23&quot; neck&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collar MODES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Another feature in the 425 collar is the ability to change stimulation settings at the collar. The collar has a low and medium setting. This allows you the option of finding the correct range of stimulation for your dog. Lower the overall stimulation choices for more sensitive dogs and raise the levels for hard headed or stubborn ones.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;You can change the collar setting at any time. You can also have collars set up on different levels and work them from the same transmitter. This allows you the option of working sensitive and stubborn dogs from the same transmitter.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'SportDOG 425S Training System with Dog Collar', 'SportDOG 425S Training System with Dog Collar', 'SportDOG 425S Training System with Dog Collar'),
(10616, 1, 'Landmann USA 23192 Patio Lights Deer Tracks Fire Pit, Black', '&lt;p&gt;Bring your campfire with you wherever you go with this rugged wildlife-pattern fire pit and grill—and cook your favorites the old-fashioned way.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 29¼&quot;W x 23&quot;H x 23½&quot; Diameter.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 32 lb.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY WE LOVE IT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMade for safety with three stable legs, a rugged steel tub and wire mesh to contain sparks and ash, this wildlife-pattern fire pit and grill adds fun to any outdoor gathering. Easy to clean and simple to transport, it includes a rugged, easy-to-clean enamel grill for cooking.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CONSTRUCTION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes spark guard.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rugged steel walls contain fire.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steel mesh guard prevents sparks from escaping.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Nonstick enamel cooking grate.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Some assembly required.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ADDITIONAL FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Portable fire pit and grill.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ideal for campground, picnic area, beach or backyard.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Decorative wildlife cutouts create lively reflections when lit.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes nonstick enamel grill for cooking.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stable three-leg design.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Contains ashes to protect surroundings.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Imported.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Landmann USA 23192 Patio Lights Deer Tracks Fire Pit, Black', 'Landmann USA 23192 Patio Lights Deer Tracks Fire Pit, Black', 'Landmann USA 23192 Patio Lights Deer Tracks Fire Pit, Black');
