Rubber&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Foot Pads: Anti-slip, rubber&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery: 25.2V lithium-ion pack, rechargeable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes: Battery power indicator, balance level and mode indicator, and battery charger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Patent: U.S. Patent No. 8,738,278&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;RIDER TYPE:&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Age: 8+&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max Rider Weight: 176 lb (80 kg)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Razor was the first US brand to receive the UL 2272 listing for safety, and Hovertrax 1.5 meets or&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;exceeds the highest fire and electrical standards.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Our exclusive EverBalance technology automatically levels the Hovertrax 1.5 for an easier mount&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;and extremely smooth ride.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steel frame with shatter-resistant polymer body for maximum durability.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Silent, dual-hub motors with gyro-sensor technology deliver cruising speeds up to 6 mph (10 km/h) for up to 45 minutes of continuous use.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Anti-slip, rubber, traction pads keep you in perfect balance for foot-controlled, seamless&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;maneuvering.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Razor Hovertrax 1.5 Hoverboard Self-Balancing Smart Scooter, Black', 'Razor Hovertrax 1.5 Hoverboard Self-Balancing Smart Scooter, Black', 'Razor Hovertrax 1.5 Hoverboard Self-Balancing Smart Scooter, Black'),
(10640, 1, 'Razor E300 Electric Scooter, White', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RAZOR E300 ELECTRIC SCOOTER, WHITE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;MAX SPEED: 15 MPH&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BATTERY LIFE: UP TO 40 MINS&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AGES: 13 AND UP&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;MAX WEIGHT: 220 LBS&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FAST.&amp;nbsp; FUN.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe perfect ride for your sportier side.&amp;nbsp; The E300 is as excellent as its predecessors – only super-sized.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SAY…YAY!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith speeds up to 15mph, wider tires, and steely-gray profile, your ride just got way more interesting.&amp;nbsp; Yay for you.&amp;nbsp; Yay for electricity.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MAXIMUM OVERDRIVE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The thrill of power meets the latest technology and high-quality materials that Razor is known for – in the form of electric scooters. With larger deck, frame and tires for older teen and adult riders, the E300 electric scooter is Razor\'s speediest electric scooter - traveling up to 15 miles per hour. The rider friendly electric power engages a super quiet chain driven motor – applauded by neighbors everywhere.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Razor offers a range of electric scooters for ages eight to adult (E100, E200, E200S, E300 and E300S) – just match your age and weight to find your power ride.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Speeds up to 15 mph&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Up to 40 minutes of continuous use&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Super-sized deck and frame&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High torque, chain driven motor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Twist-grip acceleration control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hand operated rear brake&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra wide 10-inch pneumatic tires&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Retractable kickstand&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;24V (two 12V) sealed lead acid rechargeable battery system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Battery charger included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembled Product Dimensions: 41 x 17 x 42 inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Some assembly required&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RAZOR\'S SPEEDIEST ELECTRIC SCOOTER TO DATE!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With a larger deck, frame and tires for teens and adult riders, the E300 is one of Razor’s fastest electric scooters, traveling up to 15 miles-per-hour. Twist the throttle and feel the thrill of electric power. The E300 also has extra wide tires for superior comfort.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES&lt;br /&gt;\r\nExtra wide pneumatic tires&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOutfitted with extra wide 10-inch pneumatic tires for superior comfort and control.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Super-sized deck and frame&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSuper-sized deck and frame for riders of all ages!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Twist-grip acceleration control and hand operated &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;rear&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; brake&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTwist the throttle and feel the thrill of electric power.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Retractable kickstand&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nRetractable kickstand for rides on and off the go.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT RAZOR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;From day one, Razor has focused on providing the very best riding experience, combining cutting-edge technology, high-quality materials and innovation to deliver products designed to suit riders’ evolving lifestyles.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Founded in 2000, Razor quickly became an icon of American culture with the introduction of the now legendary A model kick scooter. The must-have item of the year, the A model continues to be an essential ride for anyone on the go.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Today, Razor offers a full line of award-winning products that inspire and excite riders around the globe. Influenced by our Southern California home, and rooted in popular action sports – from motocross and BMX, to snowboarding, skateboarding and surfing – Razor’s products embody the spirit of freedom and fun.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Razor E300 Electric Scooter, White', 'Razor E300 Electric Scooter, White', 'Razor E300 Electric Scooter, White'),
