ng&gt;Retractable kickstand&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nRetractable kickstand for rides on and off the go.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT RAZOR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;From day one, Razor has focused on providing the very best riding experience, combining cutting-edge technology, high-quality materials&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;innovation to deliver products designed to suit riders’ evolving lifestyles.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;Founded in 2000, Razor quickly became an icon of American culture with the introduction of the now legendary A model kick scooter. The must-have item of the year, the A model continues to be an essential ride for anyone on the go.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;Today, Razor offers a full line of award-winning products that inspire and excite riders around the globe. Influenced by our Southern California home, and rooted in popular action sports – from motocross and&amp;nbsp;BMX,&amp;nbsp;to snowboarding, skateboarding&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;surfing – Razor’s products embody the spirit of freedom and fun.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Razor E300 Electric Scooter, Blue', 'Razor E300 Electric Scooter, Blue', 'Razor E300 Electric Scooter, Blue'),
(10642, 1, 'Traeger Tailgater Pellet Grill, Bronze', '&lt;div&gt;From the truck to the game or the cabin without breakin’ a sweat, the Tailgater packs a full-size punch in a portable package. It weighs only 62 pounds and comes with EZ-Fold Legs for max portability. Infusing big, wood-fired taste in tight spaces, now you can grill, smoke, bake, roast, braise, and BBQ wherever and whenever you damn well please.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Never Use Gas or Charcoal Again: Cooking with wood just tastes better. Traeger created the original wood-pellet grill as the ultimate way to achieve wood-fired taste&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Versatile Barbecue Cooking: Hot and fast, or low and slow, the Traeger Tailgater pellet grill offers 6-in-1 versatility to grill, smoke, bake, roast, braise, and bbq food to juicy perfection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easily Transportable: Features EZ-fold legs that allow you to pack it up and grill on the go; Multi-Position Thermostat Control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Grilled to Perfection Every Time: Integrated Digital Elite Controller keeps temps within +/- 20 degrees F and makes setting the grill temperature as easy as turning a dial&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Great for Home, Camping, and Tailgating: Enjoy 300 sq. in. of portable grilling space that can accommodate up to 12 burgers, 2 whole chickens, or 3 racks of ribs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;300 sq. in. (20&quot; x 15&quot;) Grilling Area&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Digital Elite Controller&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EZ-Fold Legs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model: TFB30LZB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cooking capacity: 300 sq. in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pellet hopper capacity: 8 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 36 in. | Width: 37 in. | Depth: 18 in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 62 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;300 SQ. IN. GRILLING AREA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;Get big wood-fired flavor in one portable package. The Traeger Tailgater 20 grill can comfortably hold up to 12 burgers, 2 whole chickens, 18 hot dogs, or 3 racks of delicious Traeger-smoked ribs so you can grill out for a group.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DIGITAL ELITE CONTROLLER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;Setting your grill is now just as easy as setting your oven. The Digital Elite Controller maintains precise temperatures within +/- 20 degrees and allows you to cook low and slow on the \'Smoke\' setting to hot and fast at up to 450 degrees. The LED display makes getting a read on your grill temperature clear and easy.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FUELED BY 100% PURE HARDWOOD PELLETS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;Get amazing wood-fired taste that gas and charcoal grills just can\'t compete with. Traeger\'s hardwood pellets are made of pure, virgin hardwood with no fillers or binding agents, so you get amazing wood-fired flavor any nothing else.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ELECTRONIC AUTO-START IGNITION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;No more dealing with fire starters and charcoal chimneys, or having to light your propane grill with a match. With the simple flip of an on/off switch your Traeger is up, running, and ready to go.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EZ-FOLD LEGS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;Pack up your grill and head over to the parking lot for tailgating glory. The EZ-fold legs make this grill compact and ready to pack up for wood-fired grilling on-the-go.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EASY TO CLEAN PORCELAIN GRILL GRATES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;A non-stick surface makes these grill grates easy to clean after smoking a saucy rack of ribs or juicy burgers. Less time cleaning = more time enjoying your Traeger creations with family and friends.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VERSATILITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;Whether it\'s smoking a rack of ribs or grilling a wood-fired pizza, to even baking a homemade apple pie, do it all with Traeger\'s 6-in-1 versatility. No matter what you grill, smoke, bake, roast, braise, or BBQ, it all gets flavored with amazing Traeger wood-fired taste. Don\'t settle for a grill that can only grill or smoke when you can do it all with a Traeger.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://ankermart.com/image/guides/TFB30LZB-How-It-works.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 800px; height: 247px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TECHNICAL SPECIFICATION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;Download:&lt;a href=&quot;https://ankermart.com/image/guides/Technical-Specification-TFB30LZB.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt; User Manual&lt;/a&gt; [PDF ]&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Tailgater Pellet Grill, Bronze', 'Tailgater Pellet Grill, Bronze', 'Tailgater Pellet Grill, Bronze');
