(10660, 1, 'SimpliSafe Home Security System, The Oakstone - FREE CAMERA', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SIMPLISAFE HOME SECURITY SYSTEM, THE HAVEN PACKAGE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT OUR SPECIALISTS SAY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPerfect for homes with more windows—The Oakstone has eight entry sensors to cover your home.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S INCLUDED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Base Station (Cloud color)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Keypad&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;Cloud&lt;/span&gt; color)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Key Fob&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;8 Entry Sensors&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;colorbox-inline initColorboxInline-processed cboxElement&quot; href=&quot;https://simplisafe.com/home-security-system-oakstone?inline=true&amp;amp;width=1000&amp;amp;height=600#motion-sensor-cbox&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(43, 47, 53); text-decoration-line: none; font-family: Din, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; padding-left: 0px;&quot;&gt;Motion Sensor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;FREE CAMERA (excludes Doorbell Pro)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;24/7 PROFESSIONAL MONITORING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;It\'s like having a personal security guard in front of your house. Our specialists watch over your home day and night, ready to alert the authorities when you need help.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Central Station of the Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;$14.99/month&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No contracts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OPEN BOX. START PROTECTING.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;Anyone can set up SimpliSafe in just a few minutes. No drilling. No tools. Just plug in the Base Station, place your sensors, and start protecting your home.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BUILT FOR THE UNEXPECTED&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;Real home security prepares for the worst. So we built backups. And backups for those backups.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SmashSafe:&lt;/strong&gt; An intruder can damage the keypad. Doesn\'t matter. We still alert the police. Sorry, bad guys.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Twice Secured: &lt;/strong&gt;We doubled down. Took our built-in cellular connection. Put it on the strongest networks. Then reinforced it with Wi-Fi. So your home is always secure.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Disaster Ready:&lt;/strong&gt; We\'ve got 6 monitoring centers. They all protect your home. All the time. Overkill? It\'s not. It meansthere\'s no single point of failure. So a disaster can\'t take down your protection.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Power Outage Protection:&lt;/strong&gt; The power fails. We don’t. In a blackout, a back-up battery kicks in and protects you for a full 24 hours.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Confirmed Alerts&lt;/strong&gt;: Alert confirmation is big. It means that we send an alarm signal until the monitoring center confirms they got it. It’s how you can be absolutely sure help is there when you need it.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deep Encryption:&lt;/strong&gt; From sensor to Base Station to monitoring centers and back, your signals are encrypted.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LESS MARKUP. MORE SECURITY.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;A common misconception: the more you pay, the more you get. But the truth is you’re&amp;nbsp; paying for more markup. Not more security.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;You shouldn\'t have to pay more so we can do less. We cut out the middlemen, so you get award-winning protection at fair and honest prices.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LIGHTS UP WHEN THE SUN\'S DOWN&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;The all new touch-to-wake keypad. Lights up when you need to see it. Goes dark when you don\'t. It doesn\'t need power, just a good place to put it.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DETECTS INTRUDERS, NOT PETS.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;Alarms that cry wolf? No thanks. We precision-engineered our motion sensors to detect the unique heat signature of humans. Not pets&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'SimpliSafe Home Security System, The Oakstone', 'SimpliSafe Home Security System, The Oakstone', 'SimpliSafe Home Security System, The Oakstone'),
(10663, 1, 'Netatmo Smart Outdoor Security Camera with Integrated Floodlight', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRESENCE DOES OUTDOOR SECURITY BETTER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPresence, the smartest outdoor security camera, is able to distinguish people, cars and animals.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIt tells you exactly what it sees around your home and notifies you directly on your smartphone.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIt has an integrated smart floodlight which switches on only when needed, to help deter unwanted visitors, cars, animals or all three.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smart LED Floodlight&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Infrared night vision&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Free video storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;100° field of view&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1080p Full HD video&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4 MP video sensor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wi-Fi&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weatherproof: HZO protection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DETECT THE PRESENCE OF A PERSON, CAR OR ANIMAL. BE NOTIFIED WHEN IT MATTERS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPresence detects and reports in real-time if someone loiters around your home, a car enters your driveway or your pet is in the yard.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Each home is unique. With Presence you receive customized notifications that match your needs.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Alert-Zones feature allows you to select specific areas for alerts – you know instantly when someone enters a zone you selected.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PROTECTION DAY AND NIGHT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAt night, either watch discreetly with Presence\'s infra-red night vision or switch the camera\'s floodlight on.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe smart floodlight can be switched on manually in the app or set to switch on when it detects a person, car or animal - or for all three. It helps you find your way safely at night and deters any unwanted visitors.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SIMPLY INSTALLS AS AN OUTDOOR LIGHT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPresence simply replaces any existing outdoor light fixture.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIn just a few minutes you have a sophisticated security system with a powerful floodlight.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PREVENT BREAK-INS OR DAMAGE ON YOUR PROPERTY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nUltra-precise alerts let you know instantly about what happens outside your home.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nUse live stream to view your property in real-time.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ANY DEVICE. ANYWHERE. ANYTIME&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nAccess your videos and live stream through Presence’s app – anytime, anywhere, on any device.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FREE VIDEO STORAGE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFree and secure video storage: Storing your videos is free and secure on the included microSD card, with the option of using your FTP server or your Dropbox account as additional storage.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DATA PROTECTION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPresence uses bank-level, end-to-end encryption to guarantee the highest level of protection for your videos. Identification data and video footage is yours alone.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Netatmo Smart Outdoor Security Camera with Integrated Floodlight', 'Netatmo Smart Outdoor Security Camera with Integrated Floodlight', 'Netatmo Smart Outdoor Security Camera with Integrated Floodlight'),
(10664, 1, 'Netatmo Smart Indoor Security Camera', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RECEIVE HOME INTRUDER ALERTS DIRECT TO YOUR SMARTPHONE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWelcome is a new breed of smart security camera.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nInstead of the usual motion alerts which require you to waste time watching footage, Welcome sends a notification saying that an intruder has been detected in your home, complete with a picture of their face and a video of the intruder.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Full HD 1080p&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;130° field of view&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Infrared night vision&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;8x digital zoom into videos&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Video sensor 4MP&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wireless Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n (2.4G)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Data storage MicroSD card up to 32GB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Optional video backup on personal FTP server or Dropbox account&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EFFORTLESS SETUP IN A FEW MINUTES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWelcome’s setup is straightforward: place the camera indoors, facing your entrance, plug it in and download the App. Identify your loved ones with a simple click. That’s it!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ALARM DETECTION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe camera also features alarm detection to better protect your home. When it hears an alarm, such as a security or smoke alarm, it sends a notification to your smartphone and records a video.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LEAVE FAMILY OFF THE RECORD TO PROTECT THEIR PRIVACY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWelcome helps you keep watch over your home, without spying on the ones you love. With the option to disable video recording and notifications for familiar faces, your loved ones can relax in the privacy of your home, knowing they aren’t being watched or recorded.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VIDEO STORAGE IS FREE AND FLEXIBLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nStoring your videos is free and secure on the included microSD card, with the option of using your FTP server or your Dropbox account as additional storage.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SUPERIOR NIGHT VISION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nProtection day and night with infrared night vision for clear videos even in total darkness.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ANY DEVICE. ANYWHERE. ANYTIME.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nStay in touch from anywhere. Live video streaming, access to past events and a list of who\'s home are all at your fingertips, with the free, downloadable app.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Netatmo Smart Indoor Security Camera', 'Netatmo Smart Indoor Security Camera', 'Netatmo Smart Indoor Security Camera'),
(10589, 1, 'Netatmo Weather Station and Rain Gauge Pack', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NETATMO WEATHER STATION MONITORS:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Temp (indoor &amp;amp; outdoor)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Humidity (indoor &amp;amp; outdoor)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Barometric pressure&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CO2 levels (indoor)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sound levels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Even gives detailed 7-day forecast&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SO MUCH MORE THAN A PERSONAL WEATHER STATION.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Helps you monitor your home environment when you’re not there&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Great for keeping an eye on lake house or camp&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;CO2 monitor can alert you to dangerous conditions in your home&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sound meter can alert you to mechanical failures or presence of intruders&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Temperature alerts can alert you to heat system failure or conditions that cause freezing pipes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NETATMO LETS YOU MONITOR YOUR HOME ENVIRONMENT FROM ANYWHERE IN THE WORLD. IT INCLUDES INDOOR &amp;amp; OUTDOOR SENSORS AND WEATHER STATION APPS FOR IPHONE, IPAD OR ANDROID DEVICES.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBoth aluminum-bodied sensors use Wi-Fi to send data to your wireless router or Wi-Fi enabled smartphone or tablet. The outdoor sensor includes a mounting bracket for attaching to an exterior window, wall or deck area. Install the iOS or Android Weather Station App that’s right for your device, and instantly begin collecting weather and air-quality information for your local surroundings.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THESE NETATMO WEATHER STATIONS TRACK MORE THAN THE WEATHER.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIn addition to weather basics (temp, humidity and barometric pressure), Netatmo lets you monitor and analyze carbon dioxide concentration so you know when you need to ventilate your home. It also measures noise pollution, which can contribute to irritability and poor concentration.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KEEP AN EYE ON HOME, FROM ANYWHERE IN THE WORLD.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhen connected to your wireless router, Netatmo weather stations let you monitor home weather and air quality conditions anywhere you have access to the web or a wireless data network. With Netatmo and the weather station app, enjoy a free lifetime access to an online personal dashboard, no subscription needed.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IN THE PACK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One indoor station&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One outdoor module&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;USB cable for wall adapter or desktop set up: 1.5 m / 5 feet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;USB wall adapter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wall-mount kit for outdoor module&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 AAA batteries&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rain Gauge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HARDWARE REQUIREMENTS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWi-Fi router and internet access&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPublic hotspots not supported&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IPHONE &amp;amp; IPAD COMPATIBILITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;iPhone 4S, 5, 5S,6,6 Plus&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;iPhone 4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;iPhone 3GS - requires iOS 4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;iPhone 3G - requires iOS 4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;iPad (3rd and 4th generation), IPad Mini&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;iPad 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;iPad - requires iOS 4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;iPod touch (4th and 5th generation)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;iPod touch (3rd generation) - requires iOS 4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;iPod touch (2nd generation) - requires iOS 4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ANDROID™ COMPATIBILITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Android 4.0 or higher&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;WINDOWS PHONE 8.0&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DIMENSIONS&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Indoor station - 1.8&quot; Dia x 6&quot; H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Outdoor station - 1.8&quot; Dia x 4.1&quot; H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Netatmo Weather Station for Smartphone, Compatible with Amazon Alexa, Weather Station and Rain Gauge Pack', 'Netatmo Weather Station for Smartphone, Compatible with Amazon Alexa', 'Netatmo Weather Station for Smartphone, Compatible with Amazon Alexa'),
(10665, 1, 'YETI Hopper Flip 18 Cooler Tan Color, YHOP18T', '&lt;div&gt;The weekend is young, so pack up your new Hopper Flip 18 and head for the hills. The bigger build suits your larger hauls and longer expeditions. Set out with your lunch while you work for your dinner, and have a couple cold ones to kick back with after. Hopper Flip 18 is durable, leakproof and versatile with the HitchPoint™ Grid for tools and accessories. And like all YETI coolers, it’s equipped with superior insulation to keep the cold for days.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DRYHIDE SHELL&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;The Hopper’s high-density fabric is waterproof and resistant to mildew, punctures, and UV rays. The liner is made from an FDA-approved food-grade material.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;COLDCELL INSULATION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;Closed-cell rubber foam offers far superior cold-holding to ordinary soft coolers.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HYDROLOK ZIPPER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;The toughest, highest-performing waterproof and leakproof cooler zipper in the world.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HITCHPOINT GRID&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;Easily attach pretty much anything, including the MOLLE Zinger, MOLLE Bottle Opener and SideKick.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer warranty - general: 3 years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer warranty - parts: 3 years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufacturer warranty - labor: 3 years&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;OUTSIDE 10 3/4” × 13” × 16 1/4”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;INSIDE 8 1/2” × 10 1/4” × 14 1/4”&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EMPTY WEIGHT 5.1 LBS&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S IN THE BOX&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;YETI Hopper Flip 18 Cooler&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'YETI Hopper Flip 18 Cooler Tan Color, YHOP18T', 'YETI Hopper Flip 18 Cooler Tan Color, YHOP18T', 'YETI Hopper Flip 18 Cooler Tan Color, YHOP18T'),
(10666, 1, 'Airlift S3 Electric Height Adjustable Standing Desk Black, OFFK65818', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AIRLIFT S3 ELECTRIC HEIGHT ADJUSTABLE STANDING DESK, BLACK/BLACK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDiscover the benefits of getting active during your day with the AIRLIFT® S3 Electric Height-Adjustable Standing Desk. Upgrade with a desk that encourages a healthy lifestyle and by reducing unhealthy sedentary behavior. With a press of the AIRLIFT® buttons, dual electric motors smoothly and quietly adjust the height from a minimum of 25.6 inches high to a maximum height of 51.4 inches. Our desks feature steel construction for stability and durability through repeated uses and is compliant with the ANSI/BIFMA X5.5 Desk Products standard. Save up to four memory settings and adjust to the perfect height throughout the day with the digital height controller. An LED display lets you know how high the desk is as it rises and descends. Desk base is finished in black, with the top finished in black 3D laminate. Assembly is easy and can be done in minutes with the included tools. Use it as a home desk replacement, or as an instant upgrade to office spaces for large and small businesses.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DESCRIPTION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Powerful Dual Motors - Fast two-section legs adjust the desk top from 25.6 inches and rise to a height of 51.4 inches high&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ergonomic 54&quot; x 30&quot; Top - Curved side lets you stand closer to the desk for a more U-focused experience&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ANSI/BIFMA X5.5 COMPLIANT - Heavy-duty steel construction and adjustable leveling feet provide stability without sacrificing strength for a maximum weight capacity of 264 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Digital controller with LED screen stores up to four height settings for easy adjustment throughout the day&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Beveled Bottom Edges - Bottom of desk edges feature an inward slope&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight capacity: 264 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 120 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;7-Year Non-Electronic Component Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2-Year Electronic Component Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Live Well With AIRLIFT™&amp;nbsp; - Break the cycle of sedentary behavior and enjoy the health benefits of a sit-stand desk. Burn calories and stretch your legs and feet by standing and getting active while you work, study, and game. AIRLIFT™&amp;nbsp; can keep you moving wherever you choose to be.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;7-YEAR NON-ELECTRONIC COMPONENT WARRANTY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSeville Classics, Inc. warrants to the original retail purchaser that if this product proves to be defective in material or workmanship, we will replace the affected non-electronic part(s) for a period of seven years on Seville Classics Electric Height-Adjustable Standing Desks from the date of original purchase.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2-YEAR ELECTRONIC COMPONENT WARRANTY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSeville Classics, Inc. warrants to the original retail purchaser that if this product proves to be defective in material or workmanship we will replace the affected electronic part(s) for a period of two years on Seville Classics Electric Height-Adjustable Standing Desks from the date of original purchase.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: (45&quot; to 62.9&quot; W) x 23.63&quot; D x (25.6&quot; to 51.4&quot; H)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight capacity: 264 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 120 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Model no: OFFK65818&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT\'S IN THE BOX?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 ergo table top (54&quot; x 30&quot;)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 support beam&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 legs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 support bracket&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2 feet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 control box&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 controller&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4 bolt sleeve&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;12 washers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6 fasteners&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;8 zip ties&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;10 screws&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4 M8x25 bolt&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6 M6x16 bolt&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;8 M6x40 bolt&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;8 M6x6 bolt&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Allen wrench 3mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Allen wrench 5mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Allen wrench 6mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 screwdriver&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Airlift S3 Electric Height Adjustable Standing Desk Black, OFFK65818', 'Airlift S3 Electric Height Adjustable Standing Desk Black, S3-ADJUSTABLE', 'Airlift S3 Electric Height Adjustable Standing Desk Black, OFFK65818'),
