(10670, 1, 'Ring Floodlight Camera - Black, 8SF1P7-BEN0', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE EVOLUTION OF OUTDOOR SECURITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Replace your outdated security lights with Floodlight Cam, a motion-activated HD camera with two-way talk, lights and a siren. See, hear and speak to people on your property. Shine the lights on all your blindspots. And sound the siren on suspicious activity. All from your phone, tablet and PC.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Monitor your property in HD video, and check-in on your home at anytime with Live View on-demand video and audio.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Get alerts on your phone, tablet and PC when anyone presses your Doorbell or triggers the built-in motion sensors.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hear and speak to visitors from your mobile device using the built-in microphone and speakers with noise cancellation.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Activate the siren from your phone, tablet and PC to scare away any suspicious people caught on camera.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shine a light on suspicious activity with two motion-activated ultra-bright floodlights.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Customize your motion zones to focus on the most important areas of your yard.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Connects with select Alexa devices to launch on-demand video at the sound of your voice.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SAVE, REVIEW AND SHARE YOUR RING VIDEOS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEnjoy a free 30-day trial of Ring Protect Plus with your purchase! Ring Protect Plus lets you record, save and share all the videos captured by unlimited Ring Doorbells and Cameras at your home. Protect Plus members also get 24/7 professional monitoring with Ring Alarm, exclusive discounts and extended warranties. Activate Ring Protect Plus for only $10 a month, or get video recording and sharing for only $3 a month per each device with Ring Protect Basic.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WORKS WITH ALEXA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCombine Ring with Alexa for hands-free home monitoring. When anyone presses your Doorbell or triggers Ring\'s built-in motion sensors, your Echo device will illuminate and make an announcement, so you\'ll always know when someone\'s there. And if you have an Echo Show or Echo Spot, you can also see, hear and speak to anyone captured on camera.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Installation: Average install time: 15-25 minutes. Click here to download the manual.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Video: 1080p HD, Live View, Night Vision&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Field of View: 140° horizontal, 78° vertical&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Motion Detection: Advanced Motion Detection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Audio: Two-way talk with noise cancellation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Siren: Remote-activated alarm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lights: Two LED Floodlights, 1800 Lumens (Combined)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power: Hardwired to weatherproof electrical boxes (110-240 VAC).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Internet Requirements: Requires a minimum upload speed of 1Mbps, but 2 Mbps is recommended for optimal performance.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Connectivity: 802.11 b/g/n Wi-Fi connection @ 2.4GHz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Operating Conditions: -22°F to 120°F (-30°C to 48.5°C), Weather Resistant&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mounting Base: Integrated mounting base with adjustable light and cameras angles. Mounts on 4 inch round weatherproof electrical box (not included)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 11 in x 8.25 in x 7 in (28 cm x 21 cm x 17.8 cm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Setup Requierments: 4 inch round weatherproof electrical box with AC power wiring&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty and service: 1-year limited warranty and service included.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BOX INCLUDES:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFloodlight Cam, Mounting Bracket, Installation Tools and Screws, User Manual, Security Sticker&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Ring Floodlight Camera - Black, 8SF1P7-BEN0', 'Ring Floodlight Camera - Black, 8SF1P7-BEN0', 'Ring Floodlight Camera - Black, 8SF1P7-BEN0'),
(10671, 1, 'Costway Portable 3500W Digital Inverter Generator 4 Stroke 149cc, TL32873', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THIS DIGITAL INVERTER GENERATOR IS IDEAL FOR CREATING POWER FOR YOUR CONVENIENCE.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThis 3500-watt generator features a 149cc engine, providing sufficient power to your electronic devices. The oil alarm system is designed to prevent engine damage if the crankcase doesn\'t have any oil.&amp;nbsp; It has the safety output and overload indicator, in case the system overloads the current to the connected devices it will shut the system down. This digital inverter generator will power up your home and office devices up to 6 hours on a 100% load.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IF YOU ARE LOOKING FOR A GENERATOR, DON\'T HESITATE TO BUY IT NOW!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand new and high quality&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Professional and compact design that\'s lightweight and portable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in handle providing easy portability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Relatively quiet operation as low as 94 DB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low fuel consumption with high efficiency&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built-in circuit breaker to protect connected devices from a circuit overload&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Status lights on the control panel to indicate system status&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The oil alarm system is designed to prevent engine damage in the crankcase, in case there is not enough oil or none at all&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Forced air cooling system to prevent overheating&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Run time: 6 hours at 100% load&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall dimension: 22.8&quot; x 12.6&quot; x 20.1&quot; (L x W x H)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Net weight: Approx 73 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Type: 4-stroke, air-cooled, single-cylinder (4-stroke, OHV, 1-cylinder)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt