(10673, 1, 'Costway Portable Air Conditioner 10000BTU AC Unit and Dehumidifier, EP23475', '&lt;p&gt;OUR 10,000 BTU PORTABLE AIR CONDITIONER CAN COOL AND DEHUMIDIFY AREAS UP TO 200 SQUARE FEET.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIt can deliver optimum cooling, provide dehumidification and meanwhile it has fresh ventilation function and equipped with a four speed fan. The full-function remote control allows you to operate each feature from across the room. Unlike a fixed air conditioner unit, the portable air conditioner requires no permanent installation and the smooth-gliding caster wheels provide easy mobility from room to room. A special sleep mode setting allows you to control the temperature for comfort during the night.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SHOULD YOU LOOK FOR SUCH AN INTELLIGENT AIR CONDITIONER, JUST ADD IT TO YOUR CART.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Provides cooling, dehumidification, fan and sleep mode&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;10,000 BTU portable air conditioner can cool spaces up to 200 sq. ft.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Suitable for apartment, dormitory and office use.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dehumidified and filtered air cycle improve breathing environments effectively&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Four fan speed levels: Low, middle, high, auto&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;24 hour programmable timer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unique sleep control function&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Touch sensitive buttons with LCD digital screen for simple operation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Remote control for any settings increases convenience&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes a flexible exhaust hose and an easy-to-install window venting kit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Smooth-gliding caster wheels provide easy mobility from room to room&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Requires no permanent installation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: White&lt;/li&gt