(10674, 1, 'Costway Portable Electric Hydraulic Log Splitter Cutter, ET1173', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PORTABLE ELECTRIC HYDRAULIC LOG SPLITTER CUTTER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High quality and brand new&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fits for any home with wood-burning stove or fireplace&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Electric, convenient and clean&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Insulation class is class B, and it is very safe&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Waterproof Rate is IP 54, and it will not rust easily&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Working power is 1500W, and can work efficiently&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Portable and Easy to operate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Voltage: 120V-/60HZ&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Motor power: 1500W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max splitting force: 6Ton&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Motor no-load speed: 3450RPM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max cylinder travel:15.3&quot;(390mm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Diameter of cylinder: 2.3&quot;(60mm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Log capacity Diameter:1.9&quot;-9.8&quot;(50-250mm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Log length:14.5&quot;(370mm)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hydraulic oil capacity: 2.8 Liter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall size:37.0&quot;x12.2&quot;x18.1&quot;(LXWXH)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product weight: 102.1lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Package include: 1 x 1500w wood-log splitter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Costway Portable Electric Hydraulic Log Splitter Cutter, ET1173', 'Costway Portable Electric Hydraulic Log Splitter Cutter, ET1173', 'Costway Portable Electric Hydraulic Log Splitter Cutter, ET1173'),
(10675, 1, 'Costway 12 ft Trampoline Combo Safety, Spring Pad &amp; Ladder FREE Rain Cover, SP35279', '&lt;p&gt;Encourage your kids to be active outdoors with our trampoline! Its unique design and quality components reflect our commitment to safe, family outdoor fun.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The trampolines are made with galvanized steel frame for durability and are rust resistant. The frame is supported by a 4-leg U-shape design and patented double steel plated welding at the joints for added stability to ensure safety. The heavy duty PP jumping mat is better stitched, giving you a better experience during playing.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This net enclosure combo is designed for trampolines with no existing enclosure net, fits 12\' trampoline with 4 u-shaped legs. It comes with everything you need to setup the enclosure and more, including a sturdy net, foam sleeves for pole frames, and all the hardware. The enclosure combo is designed to attach at each spring, eliminating gaps between the mat and net, so you\'re guaranteed not to fall off. And the foam padded frame poles provide additional protection for you from being injured. The net has dual closure entry with zipper and buckles so that you will never worry about being injured.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;NOTE: ASSEMBLY IS REQUIRED ACCORDING TO THE INCLUDED INSTRUCTION. (ALL ACCESSORIES ARE INCLUDED.)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;STEEL FRAME&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4-leg U-shape design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy duty PP jumping mat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly information:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two adults in good physical condition are required for the following assembly. For your safety, you should wear proper shoes and clothing. Failure to follow these instructions and warnings may result in injury. You’d better assemble the trampoline according to the manual we provide.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NOTICE:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Always inspect the trampoline before each use.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Do not let unsupervised children near this product. Carry out the necessary safety&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Do not use when suffering from high blood pressure.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Jump with bare feet. Do not wear shoes. This will damage the jumping mat which is not covered by the warranty.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The trampoline must be set up only on a flat ground and non-slippery surfaces.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Protect the product against humidity and high temperatures.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Do not put cigarettes, pets, sharp objects, or any other foreign objects on the trampolines.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PACKAGE INCLUDES:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;12 ft trampoline&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;12 ft net enclosure&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Trampoline spring&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Spring cover&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rain cover&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ladder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Instruction manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Costway 12 ft Trampoline Combo Safety, Spring Pad &amp; Ladder FREE Rain Cover, SP35279', 'Costway 12 ft Trampoline Combo Safety, Spring Pad &amp; Ladder FREE Rain Cover, SP35279', 'Costway 12 ft Trampoline Combo Safety, Spring Pad &amp; Ladder FREE Rain Cover, SP35279'),
(10676, 1, 'Costway 800 W Folding Fitness Treadmill Running Machine, SP35309', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;800 W FOLDING FITNESS TREADMILL RUNNING MACHINE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThis foldable treadmill with low noise motor is a great choice for fitness and exercise.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIf you have little time to go the gym, go running, or are prevented from running due to bad weather, this is the solution. With this treadmill, your gymnasium can help you stay in shape much easier. The treadmill features a multi-functional display (heart rate / speed / distance / time / calories / scan) so you can track your progress. The treadmill can be folded manually for easy move.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;DON\'T HESITATE TO BUY IT!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy-duty construction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi-function LED display&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LED mode: Heart rate, scan, speed, distance, time and calories&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Handrails have speed +/-, start/stop and heart rate test functions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Safety guaranteed: Easy to reach emergency stop switch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Home exercise, portable and convenience&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;With ipad / mobile phone holder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folding design for easy storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extremely low noise motor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KEY FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy-duty Construction: Frame is made of high quality steel, has 220 lbs weight capacity, 38.2&quot;L x14&quot;W ruuning belt provides you more comfortable and more sturdy workout experience.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Space Save Design &amp;amp; IPAD/Mobile Phone Holder: The treadmill can be easy folded, with wheels it is easy for moving and storage.Put your mobile phone or Ipad on the holder,you can talk with your friends or watch movies when you work out on this treadmill.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Safety Guaranteed Design: Safety key connect you and the machine, emergency stop button on the handrail, which double protect you while working out.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi-function LED Display &amp;amp; Handrails LED Mode: Heart rate, scan, speed, distance, time and calories. Handrails have speed +/-, start/stop and heart rate test functions.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Frame Material: Heavy-duty steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Control pane lMaterial: ABS&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Running belt Material: PVC&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Black &amp;amp; Grey / Pink &amp;amp; White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rated power: 800 W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LED display screen: Heart rate / speed / distance / time / calories / scan&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Modes: P1 - P12&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rated voltage: 110 V&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rated frequency: 60 Hz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Speed: 0.5 - 6.5 mph&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Runway size: 38.2&quot; x 14&quot; (L x W)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall assembly size: 56&quot; x 24&quot; x 45.5&quot; (L x W x H)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folding size: 37.4&quot; x 57.9&quot; x 26.8&quot; (L x W x H)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 59 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight capacity: 220 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Plug type: Us standard&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Package includes: 1 x treadmill&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Costway 800 W Folding Fitness Treadmill Running Machine, SP35309', 'Costway 800 W Folding Fitness Treadmill Running Machine, SP35309', 'Costway 800 W Folding Fitness Treadmill Running Machine, SP35309'),
(10677, 1, 'Costway 2.25 HP Folding Electric Treadmill Motorized Power Running Machine, SP35498', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2.25 HP FOLDING ELECTRIC TREADMILL MOTORIZED POWER RUNNING MACHINE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Running can keep your fit and improve your overall health. The treadmill includes 12 programs and the incline could be adjusted in 3 levels to fit your needs. It features both side cushioning design and heavy-duty construction. Easy-folding mechanism and a soft-drop system are designed to help you fold and unfold your treadmill safely and easily. The 5&quot; blue-ray LCD display easily shows necessary information. The incremental speed settings can be adjusted from 0.5 MPH to a maximum of 7.5 MPH It also has 2 separate water bottle holders. What\'s more, it is easy to reach emergency stop switch.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;THIS TREADMILL IS THE PERFECT TOOL FOR LOSING WEIGHT OR INCREASING PERFORMANCE. DON\'T HESITATE TO BUY ONE!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High quality and heavy-duty construction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Powerful 2.25 horsepower continuous duty motor&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5&quot; multi-function blue-ray LCD display&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LCD mode: Modes, hand pulse, speed, distance, time and calories&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Handrails have speed +/-, start / stop and hand pulse test functions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Safety guaranteed: Easy to reach emergency stop switch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;P01 - P12 program available&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;With 2 separate water bottle holders&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3 levels incline adjustable to fit your needs (manual)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Both side cushioning design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;With easy-folding mechanism and a soft-drop system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The incremental speed settings can be adjusted from 0.5 MPH to a maximum of 7.5 MPH&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KEY FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2.25 HP Impulse Max Motor &amp;amp; Weight Capacity: 2.25 horsepower quite impulse motor deliver power for interval, speed, or endurance training. Don\'t worry it will make big noise, this treadmill is perfect for any room in your house. Weight capacity is 220LBs, as far as possible to meet your needs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Foldable &amp;amp; Adjustable Incline Design: Easy folding mechanism and a soft drop system to help you fold and unfold your treadmill safely and with ease. 3 levels incline change design help you burn more calories, tone more muscle, and build greater endurance.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;0.5-7.5 MPH Speed levels &amp;amp; P01-P12 Programs: With 0.5 to 7.5 MPH Speed levels available, you can select different speed base on your physical condition and exercise based. There are also 12 programs available for you to choose, these easy-to-use exercise programs help to improve your cardiovascular fitness, boost your health, and burn fat.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5&quot; Blue-Ray LCD Display &amp;amp; 16&quot; x 47&quot; Rubber Tread Belt: 5&quot; blue-ray LCD display screen and 16&quot; x 47&quot; big runing belt give you best workout experience. With Ipad/ mobile phone holder you can talk with your friend or watch wonderful video while you working out.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Safety Design and Cushioning Design: Safety Key connect you and the machine, emergency stop button on the handrail, which double protect you while working out. Cushioning design on both side of treadmill will reduce noise and descrese vibration to your floor, provide you best and quite workout experience.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Grey &amp;amp; blue&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Running belt: Rubber&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rated power: 2.25 HP&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LCD display screen: Hand pulse / speed / distance / time / calories / modes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Modes: P1 - P12&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rated voltage: 110 V&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Speed: 0.5 - 7.5 MPH&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall dimension: 62&quot; x 26.5&quot; x 49.5&quot; (L x W x H)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded dimension: 32.5&quot; x 26.5&quot; x 57&quot; (L x W x H)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Running belt dimension: 47&quot; x 15.5&quot; (L x W)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LCD size: 5&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unit weight: 96.5 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Capacity weight: 220 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PACKAGE INCLUDES:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x running machine&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x instruction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Costway 2.25 HP Folding Electric Treadmill Motorized Power Running Machine, SP35498', 'Costway 2.25 HP Folding Electric Treadmill Motorized Power Running Machine, SP35498', 'Costway 2.25 HP Folding Electric Treadmill Motorized Power Running Machine, SP35498'),
(10678, 1, 'Costway 1.5 HP LED Folding Exercise Fitness Running Treadmill with USB MP3, SP35897', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THIS HIGH-QUALITY, FOLDABLE AND EASILY OPERATED TREADMILL, LET YOUR HOME BE YOUR GYMNASIUM.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Safety clip will stop the treadmill as needed, thus you can avoid security concerns. This treadmill has 99 kinds of automatic systems and three different movement modes to choose for your comfortable sports experience indoors. Hi-Fi sound system will offer you relaxed atmosphere. What\'s more, you can connect treadmill to your phone through APP function and share your achievement with your friends.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;No time to go to the gym? Is the outdoor sports affected by the weather? Don\'t hesitate to take this running machine home!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand new and high quality&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Free-of-installation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;APP function for connecting treadmill and your phone&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LCD window console display &quot;Distance&quot;, &quot;Calories&quot;, &quot;Time&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi-patterns: Full manual movement mode, automatic program movement mode and the countdown mode motion mode&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;USB battery charge and Hi-Fi sound system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;99 kinds of optional Automatic systems modes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;MP3 playback by connecting the player and the board jack&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Foldable for easy storage and adjustable support feet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tweak the feet to fine-tune the slopes when you need&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Slow down or speed up depending on your heart rate automatically&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Convenient IPAD placement set to use or watch videos&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KEY FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand New And High Quality: frame is made of quality steel , max 220.5lbs weight capacity, speed range: 0.6-7.5mph.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi-function: lcd window console display that allows user to track progress in time, speed, distance, heart rate and calories burned. And the placement set of the ipad is convenient to use or watch videos.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Foldable &amp;amp; Portable: electric treadmill can be easy folded, with wheels it is easy for moving and storage and it both can be placed vertically for taking up smaller space. What\'s more the treadmill\'s feet can be tweaked to fine-tune the slopes when you need.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Multi-patterns: 99 kinds of optional automatic systems modes and it includes three different movement mode:Full manual movement mode, automatic program movement mode and the countdown mode motion mode.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;App Function: you can connect treadmill to your phone through app function and share your achievement with your friends. Hifi sound system: mp3 playback by connecting the player and the board jack through the spring connection line will offer you relaxed atmosphere. security monitoring: after setting up the system, the running opportunity will automatically slow down or speed up depending on your heart rate wirelessly.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: Black/Sliver Gray/Pink (Subject to the pictures)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rated voltage: 110 V&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Speed: 0.6-6.2 Mph&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall dimension: 46&quot; x 51&quot; x 22&quot; (L x W x H)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folding size: 16&quot; x 22&quot; x 52&quot; (L x W x H)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Runway size: 42&quot; x 16&quot; (L x W)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product weight: 77 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Max capacity: 220 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PACKAGE LIST:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Treadmill&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Accessory bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Instruction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ACCESSORY BAG INCLUDED:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Latch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Safety key&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x 30 ml silicone oil&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x MP3 cable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Allen wrench&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Screw driver10/13/14/17/19&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x USB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Heart rate belt&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Fixed knob&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Costway 1.5 HP LED Folding Exercise Fitness Running Treadmill with USB MP3, SP35897', 'Costway 1.5 HP LED Folding Exercise Fitness Running Treadmill with USB MP3, SP35897', 'Costway 1.5 HP LED Folding Exercise Fitness Running Treadmill with USB MP3, SP35897'),
(10679, 1, 'Costway 16 ft Trampoline Combo Safety Enclosure Net, Spring Pad &amp; Ladder, SP35282', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;16 FT TRAMPOLINE COMBO W/ SAFETY ENCLOSURE NET, SPRING PAD &amp;amp; LADDER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Six U-shaped Legs: Six legs are arranged averagely under the trampoline. U-shaped legs can also disperse much more gravity and enable the whole trampoline to be more stable. It is also more convenient to be assembled on the ground.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Safety Enclosure Net and Foam Sleeves: Safety enclosure netting are perfectly attached to the steel tubes through foam sleeves. It connects the enclosure net with the spring cover and also eliminates gaps between the mat and net to ensure your safety while jumping on the mat.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;All Accessories Included: Our trampoline includes steel frame, jumping mat, safety enclosure combo and ladder. It is also easy to assemble. All parts including hardware are listed and numbered in the instruction. The specific assembly steps are shown in picture form which is easy for you to understand.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Large Weight Capacity: Weight limit is 375 lbs. Heavy duty PP jumping mat is stitched perfectly well. It offers you a sense of secure feeling while you jump on the mat.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Solid Construction: The frame consists of galvanized rust resistant steel. They are durable and rust resistant and also provides longer service life for the trampoline. 108 springs are assembled for fixing the whole base part.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Encourage your kids to be active outdoors with our trampoline! Its unique design and quality components reflect our commitment to safe, family outdoor fun.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The trampolines are made with galvanized steel frame for durability and are rust resistant. The frame is supported by a 5-leg U-shape design and patented double steel plated welding at the joints for added stability to ensure safety. The heavy duty PP jumping mat is better stitched, giving you a better experience during playing.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This net enclosure combo is designed for trampolines with no existing enclosure net, fits 16\' trampoline with 5 u-shaped legs. It comes with everything you need to setup the enclosure and more, including a sturdy net, foam sleeves for pole frames, and all the hardware. The enclosure combo is designed to attach at each spring, eliminating gaps between the mat and net, so you\'re guaranteed not to fall off. And the foam padded frame poles provide additional protection for you from being injured. The net has dual closure entry with zipper and buckles so that you will never worry about being injured.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note: Assembly is required according to the included instruction. (All accessories are included.)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Steel frame&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5-leg U-shape design&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy duty PP jumping mat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Assembly information:&amp;nbsp;Two adults in good physical condition are required for the following assembly . For your safety, you should wear proper shoes and clothing. Failure to follow these instructions and warnings may result in injury. You’d better assemble the trampoline according to the manual we provide.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NOTICE:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Always inspect the trampoline before each use.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Do not let unsupervised children near this product. Carry out the necessary safety&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Do not use when suffering from high blood pressure.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Jump with bare feet. Do not wear shoes. This will damage the jumping mat which is not covered by the warranty.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The trampoline must be set up only on a flat ground and non-slippery surfaces.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Protect the product against humidity and high temperatures.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Do not put cigarettes, pets, sharp objects, or any other foreign objects on the trampolines.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PACKAGE INCLUDES:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;16 ft trampoline&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;16 ft net enclosure&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Trampoline spring&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Spring cover&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ladder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Instruction manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Costway 16 ft Trampoline Combo Safety Enclosure Net, Spring Pad &amp; Ladder, SP35282', 'Costway 16 ft Trampoline Combo Safety Enclosure Net, Spring Pad &amp; Ladder, SP35282', 'Costway 16 ft Trampoline Combo Safety Enclosure Net, Spring Pad &amp; Ladder, SP35282'),
(10680, 1, 'Costway GOPLUS 2.25HP Folding Treadmill Electric Motorized Running Machine, SP36091US', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GOPLUS 2.25HP FOLDING TREADMILL ELECTRIC MOTORIZED POWER RUNNING FITNESS MACHINE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThis is our brand new and high-quality folding Treadmill, which could make you get more results in less time.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Your home is your gymnasium. It helps you keep fit, prevent diseases, and decrease the stress of life or work as well. This folding Treadmill is ideal for everyday running workout fitness. It features easy-fold design for easy storage and heavy-duty steel frame. Once you own this treadmill and exercise with it every day, you will lead a healthier and happier life. The incline could be adjusted in 3 levels and will increase the intensity of your workout.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DON\'T HESITATE TO BUY ONE. THIS TREADMILL IS RIGHT FOR YOU!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy duty construction: Made from high-quality steel, this treadmill could hold people up to 220Lbs. You could securely run on it.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;LED display: Features with 5&quot; blue light LCD display, this treadmill provides better watching experience. It will show Time, Distance, Calories, Speed, Pulse, Incline and so on, so you could better understand your exercise condition&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Inclination adjustment: The inclination of this treadmill could be manually adjusted in 3 levels, you could choose different exercise intensity by adjusting the inclination.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Speed ddjustment: The speed could be adjusted from 0.5-7.5MPH. There are also 2/3/4/5/6/7MPH. You could choose different speed and inclination for different purposes.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Foldable design: This treadmill could be folded to save space when it is idle. It also features with 2 wheels for easy transportation. You could easily move it from room to room&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Main material: Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power: 2.25HP&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rated voltage: 110V&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Speed range: 0.5-7.5MPH&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight capacity: 220 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Runway size: 17&quot; x 47&quot; (W x L)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overall size: 61&quot; x 28&quot; x 52&quot; (L x W x H)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded size: 33&quot; x 28&quot; x 53&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PACKAGE INCLUDES:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Treadmill&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 x Instruction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Costway GOPLUS 2.25HP Folding Treadmill Electric Motorized Running Machine, SP36091US', 'Costway GOPLUS 2.25HP Folding Treadmill Electric Motorized Running Machine, SP36091US', 'Costway GOPLUS 2.25HP Folding Treadmill Electric Motorized Running Machine, SP36091US'),
(10681, 1, 'Costway 10000 BTU Portable Dehumidifier Air Conditioner with Window, EP23048', '&lt;p&gt;This 10000 BTU portable air conditioner is ideal for spot cooling small rooms up to 161 square feet.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;It is equipped with four casters that allow for easy movement to the spaces that need chilling, this portable ac unit also includes a remote control for easy temperature, fan speed and timer adjustments from across the room. A quick-install window kit is included for exhausting the unit through any horizontal or vertical opening window. This machine boasts two-way up/down air deflection that circulates air evenly to eliminate hot spots, providing ample airflow to cool spaces up to 161 sq. Ft. This portable air conditioner offers cooling, dehumidify, fan and sleep modes, ideal for home and office use. It is designed with various protection functions such as 24-hour programmable timer, super intelligent temperature sensor and water-full control and warning etc.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;100% new arrival and excellent quality&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Offers cooling, dehumidify, fan and sleep modes, ideal for home and office use&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two fan-speed level accessible by led display panel control and remote control&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dehumidification up to 50 pints per 24 hours&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Temperature setting range from 62℉ to 86 ℉&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Programmable 24-hour on/off timer cools on your schedule&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Easy roll caster wheels allow for easy movement across most floor surfaces&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Window kit and exhaust hoses included&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KEY FEATURES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rapid Cooling In Spacious Area: 10,000 BTU portable air conditioner could rapidly cool areas approximately 15㎡ x 20㎡.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;With Wheels And Handles: Safe dehumidifier includes built-in handles and wheels for easy transport.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable Fan Speed: Fan speed change by low - high - low loop manner, you could adjust the fan speed according to the change of season or indoor temperatur.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Two Control Methods: Panel control and remote control make control more convenient and easy, and the remote control features user-friendly memory design.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Much Energy-saving: This air conditioner is more energy-saving than normal air conditioner but is still well operation.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color: White&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cooling capacity: 10000 BTU&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Refrigerant / Charge: R410 A/16.9 Oz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Power supply: 110 V-120 V / 60 Hz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rated input: 970 W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rated current: 8.47 A&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Low side pres sure: 261psi&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High side pres sure: 580psi&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Air flow: 380m³/H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AC coverage area (Sq. Ft.): 400&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Noise: 56 dB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Temperature setting range: 62℉ To 86 ℉&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Filter type: Washable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exhaust hose: Single&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length of exhaust hose: 11&quot;- 5\'&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Remote control: Yes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimension: 12&quot; x 13&quot; x 30&quot;(W x D x H)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Product weight：49 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Package includes: 1 X Portable AC, 1 X Remote control,1 X Exhaust hose, 1 X Window seal-plate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Note: This item comes without drain hose.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Costway 10000 BTU Portable Dehumidifier Air Conditioner with Window, EP23048', 'Costway 10000 BTU Portable Dehumidifier Air Conditioner with Window, EP23048', 'Costway 10000 BTU Portable Dehumidifier Air Conditioner with Window, EP23048'),
