height)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Full: 53 inch (width) x 75 inch (length) x 10 inch (height)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Queen: 60 inch (width) x 80 inch (length) x 10 inch (height)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Snuggle-Pedic Mattress That Breathes Patented Airflow Transfer System, QUEEN', 'Snuggle-Pedic Mattress That Breathes Patented Airflow Transfer System, QUEEN', 'Snuggle-Pedic Mattress That Breathes Patented Airflow Transfer System, QUEEN'),
(10700, 1, 'Snuggle-Pedic Mattress That Breathes Patented Airflow Transfer System, TWIN-XL', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SNUGGLE-PEDIC MATTRESS THAT BREATHES - PATENTED AIRFLOW TRANSFER SYSTEM, KOOL-FLOW ULTRA-LUXURY BAMBOO COVER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Our Comfort and Support Layers The two-layer structure allows the softer Snuggle-Flex memory foam to give pressure relieving and conforming cushion for the shoulders and hips, while the firmer channeled base layer provides the spinal support needed for back and stomach sleepers. Even if you are on the heavier side, you won\'t have to worry about hammocking in our mattress, since it provides optimal orthopedic support for your spine. This universal comfort is allows the mattress to fit all sleeping positions and even means that it is fairly rare that a customer will need to us to customize their mattress to their personal preference, even though we are always happy to do so! KOOL-FLOW LUXURIOUS ZIPPER REMOVABLE VISCOSE OF BAMBOO COVER Our Kool-Flow Extra Breathable and soft Micro-Vented Natural Ivory Bamboo Cover allows maximum breathability, along with ultra-luxurious comfort for a cooler, more comfortable sleep. Our modular cover is designed to allow you easy access in case we need to exchange any of the layers within the mattress to alter the comfort and/or support of the mattress to suit your needs.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The PATENTED AIRFLOW TRANSFER SYSTEM works by creating 100 TIMES THE BREATHABILITY of other mattresses that only use ventilation holes or channels, but not both and do not connect the two like the ONLY THE SNUGGLE-PEDIC MATTRESS does!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Our Flex-Support Technology Gives The PRESSURE RELIEF of a Memory Foam/Gel Mattress, Only it is EASIER TO MOVE AROUND ON like a traditional mattress and MORE SUPPORTIVE. 100% MADE IN THE USA and CertiPUR-US Certified ECO-FRIENDLY and VERY LOW V.O.C. Please note that [2 TWIN XL MATTRESSES EQUAL A SPLIT KING SIZE, SO THEY ARE PERFECT FOR ADJUSTABLE BEDS!]&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;PRESSURE RELIEVING SURFACE WITH EXTRA SUPPORTIVE &amp;amp; FIRMER LOWER LAYER gives you the perfect balance and universal comfort. Compare to Tuft &amp;amp; Needle, Leesa, Sleep Innovations and Casper to see the difference for yourself!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ZIPPER REMOVABLE COVER SYSTEM ALLOWS FIRMNESS ADJUSTMENT LAYER EXCHANGES THAT WE OFFER COMPLETELY FREE IF YOU ARE NOT SATISFIED WITH THE SUPPORT OR COMFORT. Our Kool-Flow Extra Breathable Micro-Vented Cover Made In The U.S.A. with 43% viscose of bamboo, 56.4% polyester, .6% lycra KEEPS YOU COOL ALL NIGHT LONG! You do not need a special box spring, since they will work on any firm and level surface.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LOW TEMPERATURE SENSITIVITY &amp;amp; ULTRA-REACTIVE SLEEPING SURFACE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOur unique extra buoyant Flex-Support memory foam makes the mattress easier to move around on and react to your body in any temperature setting for immediate pressure relief, while still decreasing the motion transfer between partners in only the way memory foam can.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KOOL-FLOW LUXURIOUS ZIPPER REMOVABLE VISCOSE OF BAMBOO COVER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nOur Kool-Flow Extra Breathable and soft Micro-Vented Natural Ivory Bamboo Cover allows maximum breathability, along with ultra-luxurious comfort for a cooler, more comfortable sleep. Our modular cover is designed to allow you easy access in case we need to exchange any of the layers within the mattress to alter the comfort and/or support of the mattress to suit your needs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ALL OF OUR SNUGGLE-PEDIC MATTRESSES ARE MADE TO THE FOLLOWING SIZES:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Twin: 38 inch (width) x 75 inch (length) x 10 inch (height)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Twin XL: 38 inch (width) x 80 inch (length) x 10 inch (height)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Full: 53 inch (width) x 75 inch (length) x 10 inch (height)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Queen: 60 inch (width) x 80 inch (length) x 10 inch (height)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Snuggle-Pedic Mattress That Breathes Patented Airflow Transfer System, TWIN-XL', 'Snuggle-Pedic Mattress That Breathes Patented Airflow Transfer System, TWIN-XL', 'Snuggle-Pedic Mattress That Breathes Patented Airflow Transfer System, TWIN-XL'),
(10706, 1, 'Black Widow 9 Inch Long Aluminum 4-Beam Folding Arched 3-Piece Motorcycle Ramp', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;9\' LONG BLACK WIDOW ALUMINUM 4-BEAM FOLDING ARCHED 3-PIECE MOTORCYCLE RAMP&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSafely and easily transport your motorcycle, ATV or other power equipment by yourself with this reliable Black Widow ramp system. Featuring high-strength, lightweight aluminum construction, these versatile powersports ramps conveniently fold in half or break into three pieces when not in use to save precious storage space. With their innovative design these durable ramps can be assembled in a variety of ways to accommodate any loading situation. Whether you need a single runner ramp, dual runner or a wide full-width ramp, this Black Widow ramp can be configured for either of those applications.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Space out the motorcycle ramps or bolt them all together for maximum loading capacity. The side sections can be used independently as dual runners to load 4-wheeled equipment such as lawn mowers, garden tractors, ATVs, and more. These side section ramps each have a weight capacity of 600 lbs. each for a total of 1,200 lbs. when used conjointly or 1,500 lbs. when bolted together with the center section. US Patent # D595919&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from high-strength, lightweight aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Center ramp weight capacity 1,500 lbs., side ramp weight capacity up to 600 lbs. or 1,200 lbs. when used as a dual-runner&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measures 9\' L x 40&quot; W (total width)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Serrated rungs for excellent traction with an innovative 4-beam design for added strength&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folds in half and breaks down into three pieces for easy transport and storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Solid plate attaching lip&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes three safety straps to secure ramp to your vehicle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 9\'&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 40&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 1-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 89 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity:&amp;nbsp; 1,500&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Center Ramp: Capacity 1,500 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Side Ramps: Capacity 1,200 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded Length: 4\' 7-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded Height: 6-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight per Unit: 89 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: Black Widow&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 5 Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Black Widow 9 Inch Long Aluminum 4-Beam Folding Arched 3-Piece Motorcycle Ramp', 'Black Widow 9 Inch Long Aluminum 4-Beam Folding Arched 3-Piece Motorcycle Ramp', 'Black Widow 9 Inch Long Aluminum 4-Beam Folding Arched 3-Piece Motorcycle Ramp'),
(10707, 1, 'Black Widow Heavy Duty Steel Motorcycle Carrier 600 lb. Capacity', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BLACK WIDOW HEAVY DUTY STEEL MOTORCYCLE CARRIER – 600 LB. CAPACITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTake your motorcycle, dirt bike, or scooter everywhere with this heavy-duty steel motorcycle carrier from Black Widow. A built-in adjustable wheel chock features a customizable seven-position design and four integrated tie-down points ensure that you’ll keep your bike as secure as possible no matter what you are hauling.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This easy-to-assemble and easy -to-install steel motorcycle carrier with its huge 600 lb. capacity lets you haul all but the biggest bikes with you on your trips. The loading ramp easily attaches to the right side of the carrier for easy and safe loading away from traffic. Just roll your bike up the ramp, secure it in the adjustable wheel chock and with straps and wheel ties and you are ready. The ramp stores compactly on the carrier when not in use so it never will get lost.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from durable, powder-coated steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;600 lb. weight capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Designed for use with motorcycles, dirt bikes, and scooters with wheels up to 8” wide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Designed for Class III or IV 2&quot; hitch receivers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra long 71&quot; loading ramp can be stored on the carrier when not in use&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes a 5/8&quot; hitch pin, anti-rattle device, and built-in adjustable wheel chock&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Track Length: 79&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Track Width: 8&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ramp Length: 71&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ramp Width: 7-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 600 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 98 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hitch Class: III or IV&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hitch Size: 2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: Black Widow&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty 1 Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hitch Trailer Configurator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Black Widow Heavy Duty Steel Motorcycle Carrier 600 lb. Capacity', 'Black Widow Heavy Duty Steel Motorcycle Carrier 600 lb. Capacity', ''),
(10710, 1, 'Silver Spring Steel Deluxe Folding Scooter and Wheelchair Carrier', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SILVER SPRING STEEL DELUXE FOLDING SCOOTER AND WHEELCHAIR CARRIER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThis deluxe scooter, wheelchair, or power chair carrier has all the features you need for safe and efficient transportation of your mobility aid. Made from black powder-coated steel, this carrier holds up to 500 lbs. and is easy to handle. The surface of the carrier is a heavy duty steel mesh with 1&quot; square support tubes underneath that won\'t bend or flex from the weight of your mobility aid. This deluxe carrier features an extra-long 59” bi-fold ramp. The ramp releases for loading by pulling the carrier’s unique ergonomically designed T-shaped handles. The ramp easily stows either in its upright position or can be folded flat into the carrier for better visibility and compact storage when the carrier is not in use.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Silver Spring Deluxe Wheelchair and Scooter carrier has other great features that you won’t find elsewhere. When the carrier is not in use it can be conveniently folded up vertically against the back of the vehicle by releasing one pin on the This makes it safer to drive your vehicle and parking either outdoors or in your garage easier. The optional swing-away accessory allows for easy access to the rear of your vehicle or spare tire.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from durable, powder-coated steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Huge 500 lb. weight capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Designed for Class III or IV 2&quot; hitch receivers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Extra large platform measures 48&quot; L x 28&quot; W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Three position loading ramp measures 59-1/8&quot; L x 27-1/2&quot; W and folds flat into carrier when not in use to increase visibility and safety&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Carriers folds up against back of vehicle when not in using to make driving and parking easier&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes anti-rattle device, 5/8” hitch pin, and 10 tie-down points for maximum security for your scooter or power chair&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 48&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 28&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 4-1/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ramp Length: 59-1/8&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ramp Width: 27-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hitch Class: III or IV&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hitch Size: 2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Minimum Hitch Height: 11&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Hitch Height: 18&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 500 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 83 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: Silver Spring&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1 Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hitch Trailer Configurator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Silver Spring Steel Deluxe Folding Scooter and Wheelchair Carrier', 'Silver Spring Steel Deluxe Folding Scooter and Wheelchair Carrier', 'Silver Spring Steel Deluxe Folding Scooter and Wheelchair Carrier'),
(10711, 1, 'HD Ramps 6\' L x 15&quot; W Hook End Aluminum Car Trailer Ramps Knife Foot 4,000 lb', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6\' L X 15&quot; W HOOK END ALUMINUM CAR TRAILER RAMPS, KNIFE FOOT - 4,000-LB. PER AXLE CAPACITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nLoad cars, trucks, and other vehicles onto low-clearance trailers with our aluminum hook connecting end car trailer ramps. These ramps feature a knife foot for smooth transitions onto and off of the ramp. They are manufactured from high-strength, lightweight aluminum for strength and maneuverability. The serrated rungs provide excellent traction in all weather conditions, reducing the risk of injuries and vehicle damage.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from high-strength, lightweight aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measures 6\' L x 15&quot; W x 1-3/4&quot; H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4,000 lb. per axle weight capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wide serrated rungs for traction in all conditions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hook attaching end, no safety straps needed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Knife foot for smooth transition onto and off of ramps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sold in pairs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 6\'&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 15&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 1-3/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 28 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Minimum Height: 12&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Height: 15&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Foot: Type Knife&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Attaching End: Hook&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 4,000 lbs. per axle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: HD Ramps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Made in the USA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1 Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'HD Ramps 6\' L x 15&quot; W Hook End Aluminum Car Trailer Ramps Knife Foot 4,000 lb.', 'HD Ramps 6\' L x 15&quot; W Hook End Aluminum Car Trailer Ramps Knife Foot 4,000 lb.', 'HD Ramps 6\' L x 15&quot; W Hook End Aluminum Car Trailer Ramps Knife Foot 4,000 lb.'),
(10712, 1, 'HD Ramps 10\' L x 16&quot; W Hook End Aluminum Car Trailer Ramps, Knife Foot 4,000 lb', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6\' L X 15&quot; W HOOK END ALUMINUM CAR TRAILER RAMPS, KNIFE FOOT - 4,000-LB. PER AXLE CAPACITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nLoad cars, trucks, and other vehicles onto low-clearance trailers with our aluminum hook connecting end car trailer ramps. These ramps feature a knife foot for smooth transitions onto and off of the ramp. They are manufactured from high-strength, lightweight aluminum for strength and maneuverability. The serrated rungs provide excellent traction in all weather conditions, reducing the risk of injuries and vehicle damage.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from high-strength, lightweight aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measures 10\' L x 16&quot; W x 3&quot; H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4,000 lb. per axle weight capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wide serrated rungs for traction in all conditions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hook attaching end, no safety straps needed&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Knife foot for smooth transition onto and off of ramps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sold in pairs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 10\'&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 16&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 3&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 47 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Minimum Height: 12&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Height: 18&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Foot: Type Knife&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Attaching End: Hook&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 4,000 lbs. per axle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: HD Ramps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Made in the USA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1 Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'HD Ramps 10\' L x 16&quot; W Hook End Aluminum Car Trailer Ramps, Knife Foot 4,000 lb.', 'HD Ramps 10\' L x 16&quot; W Hook End Aluminum Car Trailer Ramps, Knife Foot 4,000 lb.', 'HD Ramps 10\' L x 16&quot; W Hook End Aluminum Car Trailer Ramps, Knife Foot 4,000 lb. 04-16-120-04-LOW'),
(10713, 1, 'Big Boy 9\' L x 19&quot; W Big Boy Aluminum 4-Beam Dual Runner Folding ATV Ramps', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;9\' L X 19&quot; W BIG BOY ALUMINUM 4-BEAM DUAL RUNNER FOLDING ATV RAMPS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Available only from DiscountRamps.com, the Big Boy loading ramp is simply the most versatile aluminum ramp system on the market. The 38&quot; wide ramp allows one person to load motorcycles, UTVs, ATVs and any other toys with ease. Manufactured from lightweight, high-strength aluminum, this dependable ramp will never rust. Each section includes two 19&quot; wide ramps safely held together with quick connect support brackets. Using a heavy duty hinge system, the ramps fold in half for storage in your vehicle or garage.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Driving your motorcycle up the ramp by yourself has never been easier thanks to the Big Boy\'s two 19&quot;-wide sections, while the 12 degree offset in the hinge acts the same as an arched ramp and provides additional ground clearance to eliminate bottoming when loading. From its unique two-piece design and military-grade aluminum construction to its innovative 3-3/4&quot; ramp end with solid flat plate/hook combo, the Big Boy II motorcycle ramp from DiscountRamps.com is the most versatile ramp on the market today. Thanks to the two quick-connecting support brackets that hold the two sections together safely and eliminate ramp flex, you can load a wide variety of motorcycles including cruisers, sport bikes, Harleys, the Boss Hoss, touring motorcycles, and other types of motorbikes into full-size pickup trucks, from stock or lifted 4x4 trucks, 2-wheel drive trucks and trailers to box trucks, loading docks and toy haulers.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;An extruded traction surface on the underside of the tapered foot at the base of the ramp creates a smooth loading approach surface at almost any angle, and its built-in radius on the bottom pivots on different vehicle heights making it safe to use on 10&quot; or higher trailers or trucks. The serrated cross-rung loading surfaces are spaced 3-5/8&quot; apart so your foot will not slide through while walking on the ramp and offer enhanced traction in the outdoor elements, while a pair of included heavy duty cam buckle safety straps connect the ramp to the vehicle to keep it from kicking out while loading. Add an additional level of security and save time by eliminating the need for tie down straps when you use the Alumi-Loc ramp attaching system (sold separately).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from high-strength, lightweight aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3,000 lb. weight capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Each ramp measures 9\' L x 19&quot; W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Serrated rungs spaced 3-5/8&quot; apart for maximum traction in mud, rain, or snow&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Arched design provides maximum clearance for lower ATVs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folds in half and breaks down into two pieces for easy transport and storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Combination plate and hook lip and two cam buckle safety straps to secure the ramp to your vehicle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 9\'&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 38&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 2-3/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 80 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 3,000 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded Length: 4\' 6-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded Height: 5-5/8&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight per Unit: 40 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: Big Boy&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Made in USA&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 5 Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Big Boy 9\' L x 19&quot; W Big Boy Aluminum 4-Beam Dual Runner Folding ATV Ramps', 'Big Boy 9\' L x 19&quot; W Big Boy Aluminum 4-Beam Dual Runner Folding ATV Ramps', 'Big Boy 9\' L x 19&quot; W Big Boy Aluminum 4-Beam Dual Runner Folding ATV Ramps'),
(10714, 1, 'EZ-ACCESS 8\' L TRAVERSE Aluminum Walk Ramp, TRAV308', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;8\' L EZ-ACCESS® TRAVERSE™ Aluminum Walk Ramp&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nQuickly load and unload equipment or products out of commercial-grade trucks with the EZ-Access Traverse Apron-End Aluminum Walk Ramp. Manufactured from lightweight aluminum, the ramp can easily be moved and set up by one or two people. The ramp features a serrated surface to provide superb traction in all weather conditions, helping to reduce labor costs, delivery damages, and workers\' compensation claims. An integrated safety attachment point allows the walk ramp to be secured to a vehicle through a safety strap, sold separately, which prevents the ramp from kicking out during loading. A pivoting foot plate provides a smooth transition from ramp to ground. This commercial grade-aluminum walk ramp is available in multiple lengths to accommodate rises 32&quot; high.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Easily move cargo up to raised landings, truck beds, and more using the EZ-ACCESS® TRAVERSE™ 8 foot Aluminim Walk Ramp . This durable ramp is manufactured from high-strength, lightweight aluminum that won\'t rust and features up to an impressive 1,200 lbs. weight capacity to accommodate heavy loads. A 6&quot; top lip provides superior stability when attached to an even surface and the 5.5&quot; bottom transition plate is flexible, creating a smooth transition to the ground. A textured, extruded aluminum surface and raised curbs increase safety while loading and unloading in any conditions while an integrated attachment point makes it easy to secure the ramp to a vehicle or surface using a strap or chain (not included).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from high-strength, lightweight aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1,200 lb. weight capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measures 8\' L x 30&quot; W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5-1/2&quot; long self-adjusting bottom transition plate provides a smooth transition&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Textured, extruded aluminum surface for increased traction&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Raised curbs ensure user is aware of edge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Integrated attachment point allows the ramp to be secured with a strap or chain (not included)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 8\'&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 31-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 3-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 60 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 1,200 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Usable Width: 30-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: EZ-Access&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Made in USA&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3 Year Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'EZ-ACCESS 8\' L TRAVERSE Aluminum Walk Ramp', 'EZ-ACCESS 8\' L TRAVERSE Aluminum Walk Ramp', 'EZ-ACCESS 8L TRAVERSE Aluminum Walk Ramp TRAV308'),
(10715, 1, 'Apex Piggyback Hitch Bike Rack - 4 Bike', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;APEX PIGGYBACK HITCH BIKE RACK - 4 BIKE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Piggyback bicycle rack from Apex uses an innovative extendable design to carry 2 or 4 bicycles using the same frame. Use this bike rack with 1 or 2 bikes only or to carry two more with the included 2 bike add on. Each individual rack is adjustable and fits bikes from 50&quot; to 76&quot; long. The Piggyback bike carrier has 4 rubber coated grabber bars that reach out and clamp onto each bike\'s frame to secure them to the carrier. When not in use the carrier rack easily swings down to gain access to SUVs or hatchbacks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hitch pin sold separately.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from durable, powder-coated steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Carry up to 4 bikes with easily attached extension&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Designed for use with Class III or IV 2&quot; hitch receivers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fits bicycles from 50&quot; to 76&quot; long&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes 8 velcro straps to secure tires to rack&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rubber coated grabber bars lock bikes to rack&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rack folds down for access to rear of vehicle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Bike Capacity: 4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 50&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 79&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 37&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 132 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 70 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hitch Class: III or IV&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hitch Size: 2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: Apex&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Year Warranty&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hitch Trailer Configurator&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Apex Piggyback Hitch Bike Rack - 4 Bike', 'Apex Piggyback Hitch Bike Rack - 4 Bike', 'Apex Piggyback Hitch Bike Rack - 4 Bike'),
(10716, 1, 'Apex Double Stroller and Bike Trailer, BT-502', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;APEX DOUBLE STROLLER AND BIKE TRAILER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This combination double jogger and kids bicycle trailer is a great way to take the family out for a walk, run, or ride. Two children - weighing no more than 88 lbs. combined - fit comfortably inside. Five point safety harnesses, side mounted wheel guards, attached reflectors and an included high visibility flag, help keep the occupants safe. Large, 20&quot; x 1-3/4&quot; rear tires and a 12-1/2&quot; x 2-3/4&quot; front tire, along with a wide, comfortable padded handle make the baby jogger easy to push. A built-in front wheel brake brings it to a quick stop. Available behind the seat is storage space able to hold a small diaper bag or purse. Pockets on each side of the interior are great for holding small items. Without the need for tools, the jogger easily converts to a kids bicycle trailer with a universal hitch, to pull behind nearly any 24&quot; to 28&quot; bicycle. The fabric sides include large vinyl windows to provide a great view, and keep out rain. A front mesh window allows airflow into the cabin on days when the weather is nice, and includes a rain flap for days that aren\'t. The kids bike trailer/jogger is made with a high quality steel frame, powder-coated to protect it from rust.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Holds up to two children, with a maximum capacity of 88 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dual five-point safety harnesses keep children in place&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Reflectors and bright safety flag included to make the kids bike trailer and stroller more visible to motorists&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Large 20&quot; x 1-3/4&quot; rear tires, and a 12-1/2&quot; x 2-3/4&quot; front tire make the double stroller easy to push&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Storage area behind seat provides room for a diaper bag or purse&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Interior pockets to hold small items&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Front Brake to help slow and stop loaded jogger&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 55-3/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 34-1/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 55-3/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 88 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 42 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: Apex&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1 Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Apex Double Stroller and Bike Trailer, BT-502', 'Apex Double Stroller and Bike Trailer, BT-502', 'Apex Double Stroller and Bike Trailer, BT-502'),
(10717, 1, 'HD Ramps 5\' L x 15&quot; W - EZ Traction Aluminum Hook End Car Trailer Ramps', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5\' L X 15&quot; W - EZ TRACTION ALUMINUM HOOK END CAR TRAILER RAMPS - 5,000 LB. PER AXLE CAPACITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEasily load and haul cars, trucks, and other equipment onto trailers with these tough, lightweight truck trailer ramps. Manufactured from high-strength, lightweight aluminum, these ramps feature a 5,000 lb. per axle weight capacity and are light enough to be lifted and maneuvered by one person. These ramps feature our exclusive EZ Traction punch plate surface, offering outstanding traction in all weather conditions. A stub foot provides extra flexibility in ramp load heights. Their hook-end design will hook over existing rub or round rails up to 1-5/16&quot; in diameter to prevent the ramps from kicking out while in use.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from high-strength, lightweight aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measures 5\' L x 15&quot; W x 1-3/4&quot; H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5,000 lb. per axle weight capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;EZ Traction punch plate surface offers excellent traction in all weather conditions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hook-style connecting end&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stub foot end for increased versatility in loading heights&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sold in pairs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 5\'&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 15&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 1-3/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 26 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Minimum Height: 4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;MaximumHeight: 27&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Foot: Type Stub&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Attaching End:Hook&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 5,000 lbs. per axle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Surface Type: Punch Plate&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: HD Ramps&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Made in USA&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Year Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'HD Ramps 5\' L x 15&quot; W - EZ Traction Aluminum Hook End Car Trailer Ramps', 'HD Ramps 5\' L x 15&quot; W - EZ Traction Aluminum Hook End Car Trailer Ramps', 'HD Ramps 5\' L x 15&quot; W - EZ Traction Aluminum Hook End Car Trailer Ramps'),
(10718, 1, 'HD Ramps 6\' L x 12&quot; W Hook &amp; Plate Hybrid End Aluminum Car Trailer Ramps', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6\' L X 12&quot; W HOOK &amp;amp; PLATE HYBRID END ALUMINUM CAR TRAILER RAMPS, STUB FOOT - 2,500-LB. PER AXLE CAPACITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nLoad cars, trucks, and other vehicles onto low-clearance trailers with our aluminum hook/plate hybrid connecting end car trailer ramps. These ramps feature a stub foot for increased versatility in loading heights. They are manufactured from high-strength, lightweight aluminum for strength and maneuverability. The serrated rungs provide excellent traction in all weather conditions, reducing the risk of injuries and vehicle damage. Two safety straps are included for securing the ramps to a trailer to prevent them from kicking out during loading.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from high-strength, lightweight aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measures 6\' L x 12&quot; W x 1-3/4&quot; H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2,500 lb. per axle weight capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Wide serrated rungs for traction in all conditions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hook/plate hybrid attaching end, includes two safety straps to prevent kickout&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stub foot for increased versatility in loading heights&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sold in pairs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 6\'&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 12&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 1-3/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 19 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;MinimumHeight: 4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Height: 16&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Foot Type: Stub&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Attaching End: Hook/Plate Hybrid&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 2,500 lbs. per axle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: HD Ramps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Made in USA&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Year Warrant&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'HD Ramps 6\' L x 12&quot; W Hook &amp; Plate Hybrid End Aluminum Car Trailer Ramps', 'HD Ramps 6\' L x 12&quot; W Hook &amp; Plate Hybrid End Aluminum Car Trailer Ramps', 'HD Ramps 6\' L x 12&quot; W Hook &amp; Plate Hybrid End Aluminum Car Trailer Ramps'),
(10719, 1, 'Black Widow 7\' 10&quot; L x 54&quot; W Aluminum Extra-Wide Punch Plate Tri-Fold ATV Ramp', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7\' 10&quot; L X 54&quot; W BLACK WIDOW ALUMINUM EXTRA-WIDE PUNCH PLATE TRI-FOLD ATV RAMP&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhether you\'re loading your pick-up with a lawn tractor for a landscape project across town, or you’re headed up north with the ATV to hit your favorite trail, this trifold loading ramp makes loading and unloading your equipment safe and easy to do. Each ramp features a 54&quot; wide solid surface with a punched hole design for maximum traction. These ramps secure to a pickup truck or trailer with six rubber coated ramp fingers and include two safety tie-down straps. An integrated strap attachment bar found on the underside of each ATV ramp provides an excellent way to attach safety straps to prevent ramp kick-outs during loading. Tri-Folding ATV loading ramps fold to 1/3rd the width and a 5-5/8&quot; height for convenient storage under or beside an ATV or other equipment.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from high-strength, lightweight aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1,500 lb. weight capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measures 7\' 10&quot; L x 54&quot; W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Punch plate surface for enhanced traction in mud, rain, or snow&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folds down to 1/3 of its size for easy transport and storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Rubber-coated finger-style attachment points support ramp on vehicle without scratching&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes two safety straps to secure the ramp to your vehicle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 7\' 10&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 54&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 1-7/8&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 62 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 1,500 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded Width: 18&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Folded Height: 5-5/8&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: Black Widow&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Year Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Black Widow 7\' 10&quot; L x 54&quot; W Aluminum Extra-Wide Punch Plate Tri-Fold ATV Ramp', 'Black Widow 7\' 10&quot; L x 54&quot; W Aluminum Extra-Wide Punch Plate Tri-Fold ATV Ramp', 'Black Widow 7\' 10&quot; L x 54&quot; W Aluminum Extra-Wide Punch Plate Tri-Fold ATV Ramp TFS-9454'),
(10720, 1, 'Apex Steel Universal Over-Cab Truck Rack, UPUT-RACK-V2', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;APEX STEEL UNIVERSAL OVER-CAB TRUCK RACK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCarry larger cargo items and free up your pickup bed by installing the Apex Universal Over-Cab Truck Rack. With an 800 lb. weight capacity, this adjustable rack is manufactured from durable, power-coated steel, and it can be installed on trucks with beds that measure 49&quot; to 64&quot; wide. By transporting cargo above your truck, ladders and similar large, unwieldy items will stay organized and can’t damage the bed of your truck. The removable rear bar is convenient for taller cargo as well, allowing it to rest in the truck bed and lean against the rack where it can be properly tied down. Four integrated tie-down cleats make it easy to secure your load, and 5&quot; guard rails keep horizontal cargo from slipping off the side. This roof rack ships ready for a quick and easy no-drill assembly, and it clamps on to the sides of your pickup bed.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Please note: This rack will not fit step-side beds. For a permanent solution, you can mount it to the bed rails by drilling into the truck and securing it with hardware (which must be purchased separately).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from durable, powder-coated steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;800 lb. Weight capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;49&quot;-64&quot; Adjustable width fits most pickup truck beds&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Over-cab design prevents cab damage from cargo&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;5&quot; guard rails and four integrated tie-down cleats for added security&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable rear bar allows for taller cargo&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick and easy no-drill, clamp-on installation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 132&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 57&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Minimum: Width 49&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum: Width 64&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 30-3/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Cab Height: 25&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 800 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 145 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: Apex&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Year Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Apex Steel Universal Over-Cab Truck Rack, UPUT-RACK-V2', 'Apex Steel Universal Over-Cab Truck Rack, UPUT-RACK-V2', 'Apex Steel Universal Over-Cab Truck Rack, UPUT-RACK-V2'),
(10721, 1, 'Race Ramps 8&quot; H Car Trailer Ramps 3,000 lb. Capacity', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;8&quot; H RACE RAMPS CAR TRAILER RAMPS - 3,000 LB. CAPACITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&quot;Hit the road&quot; takes on a whole new meaning when it\'s in reference to driving your high-performance sports car onto standard trailer ramps that are just too steep. Get the extra ground clearance you need to load your low profile car and keep from bottoming out with these specialized trailer ramps from Race Ramps. Notched edges on each ramp allow the trailer door to securely rest on the ramps, suspending the door 5&quot;, 4&quot; or 3&quot; off the ground for additional clearance.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from polystyrene material with a protected polyurethane case&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measures 4\' 6-3/4&quot; L x 16&quot; W x 8&quot; H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3,000 lb. weight capacity per pair&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Lightweight ramps only weigh 30 lbs or less combined&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Built in notched edge rests trailer door for additional ground clearance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Perfect for loading low profile cars into trailers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 4\' 6-3/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 16&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 8&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 30 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 3,000 lbs. per pair&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Brand: Race Ramps&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Made in USA&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Year Warranty&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;USAGE GUIDELINES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBefore using the ramps ensure other persons are clear of the vehicle and the ramps. Ensure that the ramps are free from damage or corrosion before use. Use only a single pair of wheel ramps at the front or rear, do not use two ramps on one side of the vehicle. Position the ramps in line with the wheels, with the steering wheel pointed straight and the incline against the tire tread. Carefully drive the vehicle onto the automotive ramps until it is in the correct position. Turn the engine off, apply the parking brake, get out of the vehicle and securely chock the remaining wheels on the ground. Before starting work, walk around the vehicle ensuring it is securely positioned. Always use jack stand if a person will be going under the vehicle. On completion of the work, check the parking brake is still firmly on and remove the chocks. It is important to drive very slowly when coming off the ramps to prevent the automotive bodywork from making contact with the car ramp. Exercise caution when using these car ramps with a trailer or three wheeled vehicle.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Race Ramps 8&quot; H Car Trailer Ramps 3,000 lb. Capacity', 'Race Ramps 8&quot; H Car Trailer Ramps 3,000 lb. Capacity', 'Race Ramps 8&quot; H Car Trailer Ramps 3,000 lb. Capacity'),
(10722, 1, 'Apex Aluminum Universal Over-Cab Truck Rack, UPUT-RACK-ALUM', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;APEX ALUMINUM UNIVERSAL OVER-CAB TRUCK RACK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIncrease your carrying capacity with the Apex universal aluminum truck rack. Designed for carrying long, bulky equipment like ladders, pipes, and lumber, this truck rack can hold up to 800 lbs. The fully adjustable crossbars fit most pickup truck models, and uses a no-drill clamp system for easy installation.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Manufactured from high-strength aluminum this truck rack weighs almost 50% less than comparable steel models without sacrificing load weight. This makes installation easy and the reduced weight of the truck rack helps to improve gas mileage. The truck rack securely attaches to bed rails using a patented clamp system which requires no drilling. With several anchor points for securing tie-down straps, you can safely haul cargo and equipment for work and play.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from high-strength, lightweight aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;800 lb. weight capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fully adjustable cross bars fit pickup trucks up to 66-1/2&quot; wide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Over cab design prevents damage to cab from cargo&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6-1/4&quot; guard rails for added security&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick and easy no-drill clamp-on installation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Several built-in anchor points for securing tie-down straps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 134&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 66-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 38&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Guard Rail Height: 6-1/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 800 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 78 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: Apex&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;Warranty:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;1 Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Apex Aluminum Universal Over-Cab Truck Rack, UPUT-RACK-ALUM', 'Apex Aluminum Universal Over-Cab Truck Rack, UPUT-RACK-ALUM', 'Apex Aluminum Universal Over-Cab Truck Rack, UPUT-RACK-ALUM');
