(10723, 1, 'Apex Aluminum Universal Heavy Duty Utility Rack, ATR-RACK', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;APEX ALUMINUM UNIVERSAL HEAVY DUTY UTILITY RACK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThis four post universal truck rack makes hauling large equipment both safe and simple. Its fully adjustable cross bars work in nearly any compact, mid, or full-size pickup truck. The innovative clamp system does not require any drilling into your pickup bed and the included ladder stoppers keep both your cargo and your truck safe while driving.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from high-strength, lightweight aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;800 lb. weight capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fully adjustable cross bars fit pickup trucks up to 66-1/2&quot; wide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sliding system creates a perfect fit for any full, mid-size, or compact truck&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick and easy no-drill clamp-on installation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes four ladder stops&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 12-5/8&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 66-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Width: 66-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 30&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 800 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 38 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: Apex&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1 Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Apex Aluminum Universal Heavy Duty Utility Rack, ATR-RACK', 'Apex Aluminum Universal Heavy Duty Utility Rack, ATR-RACK', 'Apex Aluminum Universal Heavy Duty Utility Rack, ATR-RACK'),
(10724, 1, 'Kill Shot 500 lb. Capacity Deluxe Hitch-Mounted Deer Hoist with Swivel &amp; Gambrel', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KILL SHOT 500 LB. CAPACITY DELUXE HITCH-MOUNTED DEER HOIST WITH SWIVEL &amp;amp; GAMBREL&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThis deluxe deer hoist has features you won’t find elsewhere - a 360-degree swivel, an adjustable support foot, and over 25-1/2&quot; of clearance from your truck for easy vehicle access. With a huge 500 lb. weight capacity, this hoist will be able to handle even your heaviest game. Perfect for effortlessly cleaning, skinning, or loading large game, this hoist is an essential piece of equipment for your hunting arsenal. This hoist simple to assemble and install and easily attaches to a 2&quot; Class III or IV hitch receiver. This hoist also comes with an integrated handle which make it easy to rotate the game hoist or for carrying it. This multi-use lift is not only perfect for cleaning, skinning, and loading large game, but also works great for cavity irrigation and deer aging in temperatures less than 45°F.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from durable, powder-coated steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;360 degree swivel with 4 position locking pin system&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes adjustable foot to support hoist in hitch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Heavy duty winch handles up to 500 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;25-1/2&quot; clearance from hitch for easy access to vehicle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes 24&quot; gambrel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height adjusts from 81&quot; to 95-3/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 37-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 27&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 43 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Minimum Height: 81&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Height: 95-3/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 500 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hitch Class: III or IV&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hitch Size:&amp;nbsp; 2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: Kill Shot&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1 Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Kill Shot 500 lb. Capacity Deluxe Hitch-Mounted Deer Hoist with Swivel &amp; Gambrel', 'Kill Shot 500 lb. Capacity Deluxe Hitch-Mounted Deer Hoist with Swivel &amp; Gambrel', 'Kill Shot 500 lb. Capacity Deluxe Hitch-Mounted Deer Hoist with Swivel &amp; Gambrel'),
(10725, 1, 'Apex 1,500 lb Capacity Universal Over-Cab Truck Rack, UPUT-RACK-HD', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1,500 LB CAPACITY UNIVERSAL OVER-CAB TRUCK RACK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe universal steel truck rack combines the convenience of a no-drill installation with a heavy duty 1,500 lb. capacity. Load up pipes, ladders, drywall, and other long cargo without damaging your truck cab. Siderails, tie-down points, and tie-down cleats make it easy to safely secure your load, while a removable rear crossbar provides additional room if needed.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from durable, powder-coated steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1,500 lb. weight capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adjustable width fits most pickup truck beds up to 75-3/4&quot;W&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Over cab design prevents damage to cab from cargo&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4.75&quot; guard rails and four integrated tie-down cleats for added security&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Quick and easy no-drill clamp-on installation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable rear bar allows for taller cargo&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 134-3/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Minimum Width: 61-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Width: 75-3/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 34-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Cab Height:&amp;nbsp; 25&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Bed Width: 67-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 1,500 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 190 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Steel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: Apex&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1 Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Apex 1,500 lb Capacity Universal Over-Cab Truck Rack, UPUT-RACK-HD', 'Apex 1,500 lb Capacity Universal Over-Cab Truck Rack, UPUT-RACK-HD', 'Apex 1,500 lb Capacity Universal Over-Cab Truck Rack, UPUT-RACK-HD'),
(10726, 1, 'Apex Aluminum Tray Premium Cargo Carrier with Ramp, ACC-500', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;APEX ALUMINUM TRAY PREMIUM CARGO CARRIER WITH RAMP&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThis Apex premium aluminum cargo carrier provides a versatile solution for all of your transportation needs, featuring lightweight aluminum construction that folds up against your vehicle for convenient and secure storage. A folding ramp allows for added mobility when you need it most, making it easy to transport scooters, lawnmowers, and wheeled equipment with ease.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from high-strength, lightweight aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;500 lb. weight capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tray measures 60 1/4&quot; L x 31 7/8&quot; W x 4&quot; H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ramp measures 58&quot; L x 29 1/2&quot; W and folds flat for easy storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Designed for Class III or IV 2” hitch receivers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;When not in use, carrier folds up against vehicle for easy storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes an anti-rattle threaded 5/8&quot; hitch pin&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 61-3/4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 31&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 4&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 76 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ramp Length: 58&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ramp Width: 29-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hitch Class: III or IV&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hitch: Size&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 500 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Aluminum&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: Apex&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty:1 Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;USAGE GUIDELINES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPlease note, hitch-mounted carriers are not recommended for use on tow-behind trailers including 5th wheel and camping trailers. Never exceed the maximum tongue rating of your trailer hitch and be aware that your hauling weight may be limited by your vehicle’s suspension. Some vehicles may require air shocks or heavier springs to stiffen up the suspension and prevent sagging. Carriers are not recommended for hitches less than 12” from the ground to the bottom of the hitch without the use of a riser adaptor.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Apex Aluminum Tray Premium Cargo Carrier with Ramp, ACC-500', 'Apex Aluminum Tray Premium Cargo Carrier with Ramp, ACC-500', 'Apex Aluminum Tray Premium Cargo Carrier with Ramp ACC-500'),
(10727, 1, 'Apex Roof Box - 18 Cubic Feet Capacity, RTB-18', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;APEX ROOF BOX - 18 CUBIC FEET CAPACITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCompatible with most existing and aftermarket crossbars, this 18 cubic foot Apex Roof Box is designed to withstand heavy use in all weather conditions. Featuring a UV inhibitor which resists fading and cracking, this cargo box is fully sealed during travel to keep your gear safe and protected – even in rain or snow. This carrier is designed with easy-access loading on three sides of the box for increased convenience and efficiency while packing up your vehicle. With easy no-tool “click-n-go” installation, you’ll be on your way to your destination without cluttering the interior space of your vehicle. The top and bottom pieces nest together for easy storage when not in use.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Manufactured from high-density polyethylene&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;110 lbs. weight capacity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Measures 57&quot; L x 39&quot; W x 19-1/2&quot; H&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;18 cu ft. of additional storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Compatible with OEM and aftermarket crossbars&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Included lock for extra security&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;No tool assembly – out of the box and onto your vehicle in 10 minutes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SPECIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Length: 57&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Width: 39&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Height: 19-1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Maximum Capacity: 110 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 36 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: Plastic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;BRAND: Apex&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Made in USA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1 Year&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Apex Roof Box - 18 Cubic Feet Capacity, RTB-18', 'Apex Roof Box - 18 Cubic Feet Capacity, RTB-18', 'Apex Roof Box - 18 Cubic Feet Capacity, RTB-18'),
(10728, 1, 'NRS Thrive Inflatable SUP Boards 9.10', '&lt;div&gt;A board for the do-it-all paddler, the Thrive series SUPs are equally adept at touring, fitness paddling and light river running with the stability to help any novice feel at ease. Make every weekend memorable with an inflatable SUP board that can handle any adventure.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Inflates to 20 psi (1.379 bar) for super rigid performance and folds compactly for easy storage and transport.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;With heavy-duty PVC drop-stitch construction and double sidewalls for increased durability, NRS SUPs can handle the abrasion and abuse of an adventurous lifestyle.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Proprietary Axis Technology™, an acrylic stiffening agent integrated in the deck, improves stiffness and performance without adding weight or making the board harder to fold and store.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable, interchangeable, nylon-reinforced plastic fins let you customize your setup and absorb impacts without breaking.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Four D-rings on the nose for custom rigging using the included bungee cord plus three additional D-rings for a water bottle, leash and tie-downs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Top-quality Leafield D7 inflation/deflation valve for unsurpassed reliability.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pressure relief valve prevents accidental over-inflation.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Three sturdy webbing handles in the center of the deck for hauling plus one handle on the end to aid in a swim.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes a high-pressure pump with pressure gauge, three Allwater fins, one Touring fin, carry bag and repair kit.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Three-year retail warranty, one-year commercial.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;APPLICATION:&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;All-around&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fitness&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flatwater&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adventure Touring&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Yoga&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TECH SPECS.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 9\'10&quot; L x 30&quot; W x 5&quot; T&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Paddler Size Range:&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;90-180 lbs&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Volume: 229 L&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 23 lbs&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: PVC Drop-Stitch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of D-rings: 7&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Handles: 4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Valve Type: Leafield - D7 and Pressure Relief&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 3 Years Retail, 1 Years Commercial&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;INCLUDES:&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;(3) Allwater Fins, (1) Touring Fin&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High-pressure pump&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pressure gauge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sup Travel Pack Bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Leafield valve adapter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Repair kit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES:&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Axis Technology™ acrylic stiffener&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Inflates to 20 psi (1.379 bar) for super rigid performance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'NRS Thrive Inflatable SUP Boards 9.10', 'NRS Thrive Inflatable SUP Boards 9.10', 'NRS Thrive Inflatable SUP Boards 9.10'),
