(10731, 1, 'NRS Escape 12\'6&quot; Inflatable SUP Board - Closeout', '&lt;div&gt;The longer length, and narrower width of the NRS Escape 12\'6&quot; Stand Up Paddle Board make this board our fastest and best option for racing or getting to your take-out point quickly. Inflatable boards are easy to travel with and store. Each board includes a backpack-style travel pack.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Inflates up to a rock-hard 20 psi for performance that rivals a hard board, then folds up compactly when deflated for easy transport and storage.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The Escape features our proprietary Axis Technology. Axis™, an acrylic stiffening agent integrated in the deck, improves stiffness and performance without adding weight or making the board harder to roll up.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable, interchangeable fins let you customize your setup and the ABS plastic fins absorb impacts without breaking.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Inflatable SUP boards add versatility to your adventures. So fold up the Escape, toss it in your rig and escape to your next paddling destination.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;With 329 liters of air volume, the 6-inch-thick Escape 12\'6&quot; provides optimal performance and stability for paddlers up to 250 pounds.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Double sidewall construction for increased durability and streamlined aesthetics. The heavy-duty PVC drop-stitch construction stands up to abrasion and abuse.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Top-quality Leafield D7 inflation/deflation valve for unsurpassed reliability.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;We added a sturdy webbing handle in the center of the board for easy carrying and a second handle on the front to aid you during an unexpected swim.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Hook the included shoulder strap to the two webbing loops on the board\'s sidewall to help carry your inflated SUP to the water over your shoulder.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;12 stainless D-rings maximize your options for attaching a leash, and enough gear for overnight trips.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes a high-pressure pump for easy inflation, a pressure gauge, travel pack and repair kit.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3 year retail warranty, 1 year commercial.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TECH SPECS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Application: Racing, Adventure Touring&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 12\' 6&quot; L x 30&quot; W x 6&quot; D&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Paddler Size Range: 100-250 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Volume: 329 liters&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 27 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: PVC Drop-Stitch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of D-rings: 12&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Handles: 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Valve Type: Leafield - D7&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty:&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;3 Years Retail, 1 Years Commercial&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;INCLUDES:&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One 5&quot; and one 9&quot; fins&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High-pressure pump&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Pressure gauge&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SUP Board Travel Pack&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Leafield valve adapter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Shoulder carry sling&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Repair kit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES:&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Axis Technology™ acrylic stiffener&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Inflates up to 20 psi (1.379 bar) for super rigid performance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'NRS Escape 12\'6&quot; Inflatable SUP Board - Closeout', 'NRS Escape 12\'6&quot; Inflatable SUP Board - Closeout\r\n', 'NRS Escape 12\'6&quot; Inflatable SUP Board - Closeout'),
(10732, 1, 'NRS STAR Phase Inflatable SUP Boards 10.8', '&lt;div&gt;From family fun to fitness paddling, from lakes to rivers, the fun and stable Phase Inflatable SUP Board is the perfect all-around SUP for paddlers who like to mix things up.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Available in three sizes to suit nearly any paddler, the Phase is equally capable for touring, fitness paddling, families and light river running.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Advanced materials and construction create a lightweight board that\'s easy to transport to and from the water.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;PVC-coated drop-stitch material inflates to a fully rigid 20 psi for superior paddling performance, then folds up for compact transport and storage.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Textured foam deck pad provides comfortable, no-slip footing as you paddle.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Top-quality Leafield D7 inflation/deflation valve for unsurpassed reliability.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sturdy webbing handle in the center of the board for easy carrying.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Four stainless D-rings on the nose give you options for attaching gear.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes one 9&quot; fin, travel bag, high-pressure pump and repair kit.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1-year limited retail warranty.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT TIPS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;When folding your deflated SUP board for transport or storage, it is very important to keep the fin plates flat. Folding the fin plates will deform them, making it impossible to insert your fins. Here on the product page, watch the video &quot;Quick Tips | How to Fold a SUP Board&quot; for a demonstration.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;APPLICATION:&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;All-around&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Fitness&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flatwater&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Adventure Touring&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Downriver&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TECH SPECS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 10\'8&quot; L x 35&quot; W x 6&quot; T&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Paddler Size Range: 150-250 lbs.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Volume: 350 L&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 19.8 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: PVC Drop-Stitch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of D-rings: 4&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Handles: 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Valve Type: Leafield - D7&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty: 1 year limited&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;INCLUDES:&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One 9&quot; fin&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;High-pressure pump&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SUP travel carry bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Repair kit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'NRS STAR Phase Inflatable SUP Boards 10.8', 'NRS STAR Phase Inflatable SUP Boards 10.8', 'NRS STAR Phase Inflatable SUP Boards 10.8'),
(10733, 1, 'NRS Whip 7\'8&quot; Inflatable SUP Board - Closeout', '&lt;div&gt;Pull up to your local play wave, pump up the NRS Whip SUP Board and start shredding. The Whip\'s rounder shape, shorter length and surf-style fin and tail configurations make it the ultimate park-and-play inflatable&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Inflates up to a rock-hard 20 psi for performance that rivals a hard board, then folds up compactly when deflated for easy transport and storage.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Removable, interchangeable fins let you customize your setup and the ABS plastic fins absorb impacts without breaking.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Inflatable SUP boards add versatility to your adventures. So fold up the Whip, toss it in your rig and flip a coin to decide your next paddling destination.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;With 189 liters of air volume, the 5-inch-thick Whip 7\'8&quot; provides optimal performance and stability for paddlers up to 160 pounds.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Double sidewall construction for increased durability and streamlined aesthetics. The heavy-duty PVC drop-stitch construction stands up to abrasion and abuse.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Top-quality Leafield D7 inflation/deflation valve for unsurpassed reliability.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;We added a sturdy webbing handle in the center of the board for easy carrying and two handles on the front to aid you during an unexpected swim.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;One stainless D-ring gives you a spot to attach your leash.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes a high-pressure pump for easy inflation, a pressure gauge, travel pack and repair kit.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;3 year retail warranty, 1 year commercial.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRODUCT TIPS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;When folding your deflated SUP board for transport or storage, it is very important to keep the fin plates flat. Folding the fin plates will deform them, making it impossible to insert your fins. Here on the product page, watch the video &quot;Quick Tips | How to Fold a SUP Board&quot; for a demonstration.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TECH SPECS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Application: Surfing, Park and play&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 7\' 8&quot; L x 33&quot; W x 5&quot; D&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Paddler Size Range:&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;90-160 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Volume: 189 liters&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Weight: 20 lbs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Material: PVC Drop-Stitch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of D-rings: 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Number of Handles: 3&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Valve Type: Leafield - D7&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty:&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;3 Years Retail, 1 Years Commercial&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FEATURES:&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:pre&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Axis Technology™ acrylic stiffener&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Inflates to 20 psi (1.379 bar) for super rigid performance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'NRS Whip 7\'8&quot; Inflatable SUP Board - Closeout', 'NRS Whip 7\'8&quot; Inflatable SUP Board - Closeout', 'NRS Whip 7\'8&quot; Inflatable SUP Board - Closeout');
