INSERT INTO `oc_review` (`review_id`, `product_id`, `customer_id`, `author`, `text`, `rating`, `status`, `date_added`, `date_modified`) VALUES
(1, 10002, 2, 'Matthew Haig', 'I love this highchair!! I put this together for my daughter (5 1/2 months old) and not only was it a cinch to put together, but she LOVES IT! She\'s comfortable, safe and is now part of our dining/cooking experience for every meal! It rolls great, we can get her in and out of it easily, clean up is a breeze and we love the 6 levels for adjusting the height. I also love the reclining feature, which I didn\'t think we\'d use, but after she eats her solid foods, we recline her and she enjoys some of her bottle! I have zero complaints about this chair and look forward to many years of use! My husband loves that he can \'roll\' her around the kitchen and dining room with ease! Thank you Graco for making such a great \'grow with me\' highchair!', 5, 1, '2014-06-12 22:27:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(2, 10002, 2, 'Mischa', 'It\'s been over 24 yrs since I, last purchased a highchair. I recently had a baby five moths ago, so I went in search of a versatile highchair that would grow with my daughter. She started sitting up at 4 mos. so I wanted her to sit with us at the table, so I, did an internet search and after looking at what was offered in my local stores I, tested them by placing her in the floor model, reading all that the chair could do and for the price comparison, I really loved the 4-in-1 and all that it did, and that it would grow as she did. And the price was very comfortable.', 5, 1, '2014-06-09 10:27:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(3, 10002, 2, 'Jason', 'Very sturdy and useful high chair. Our son likes it a lot.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-04-10 08:28:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(4, 10000, 2, 'Karis Zbaraschuk', 'This is well worth the money. We enjoyed our teas before but now that we have this breville one touch our tea is brewed perfectly. My wife and I did not realize what we were missing. Different teas have different temps and brew times and that is very very important!! Teavana tea + Breville one touch= perfection!!', 5, 1, '2014-05-23 05:34:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(5, 10000, 2, 'Ruth Lucca', 'I own the Breville BTM800XL Tea Maker as well as the 800 BLXL Blender, and both are extraordinarily well-designed, high-quality, and high-performing appliances. Further, Breville USA customer service is exceptional (for instance, I lost a part for my tea maker and they sent a replacement the same day). I feel as happy and passionate about my Breville appliances as I do about my Apple MacBook Pro and iPhone 4G (yep, I\'m a tech weenie) - exceptional design, function, and service. Bravo Breville.', 5, 1, '2014-04-23 05:44:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(6, 10022, 2, 'Mary Ellen', 'Great Vacuum-Great Price!\r\nThis vacuum cleans great and is self-propelled. The attachments are easy to use also. Given the price - it\'s a great bargain for anyone needing a new vacuum.', 5, 1, '2014-05-16 19:31:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7, 10022, 2, 'Jennifer', 'Excellent purchase!\r\nMy Eureka Boss SmartVac is everything you stated and I needed. Very powerful, easy to assemble, and use. A very smart purchase for me. Thanks.', 5, 1, '2014-04-24 11:21:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(8, 10000, 2, 'Paquette', 'Best price! This is the best tea maker on the market. I love the way it looks and it does exactly as advertised.\nI know people said the one drawback is that you cannot submerge the pot in water because of the heating element, but that is not a problem, would definitely purchase one again. I am a Breville FAN', 4, 1, '2014-06-14 16:01:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(9, 65, 2, 'Theresa', 'Fast shipping! Thank you so much!', 3, 1, '2014-05-29 08:20:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(10, 63, 2, 'Kim Klimezky', 'Great value for price! So far this Exercise bike has been working out very well for me. For the price I would recommend this product.', 4, 1, '2014-04-17 11:59:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(11, 54, 2, 'Lorraine Meyer', 'As advertised. A GREAT product for a GREAT price. Ordered on a Sunday, received it on a Wednesday. Only negative is the seat that comes with it is very poor and uncomfortable. You most likely will have to buy a better one.', 4, 1, '2014-06-04 12:43:22', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(13, 10019, 2, 'Jodi Howell - NC', 'Really Nice BBQ. This BBQ has much to offer. Spacious cooking area, vents well and cleans easy. The only down fall is that the rack can not adjust to go lower or higher. We have cooked fish, hamburgers, pork chops, ribs, vegetables and everything comes out tasting great. The charcoals heat quickly and the complete cooking area heats evenly. The BBQ looks great and does not take up much room. It is strong, durable and stable, it would take a lot to knock this over. I would feel safe with my grandchildren and pets around it', 4, 1, '2014-06-08 14:50:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(14, 63, 2, 'Diceguy', 'The makers went to some trouble to be sure this bike was easy to assemble. The parts were all well organized and nicely packaged and labelled. All bolts had blue loctite already applied to help assure that they stay tight under use. You\'ll just need a phillips screwdriver and an adjustable wrench; the required allen wrenches are supplied. Anybody that can tighten a bolt can assemble this.\nAfter assembly mine worked well, just as it should. The distance from the seat to the peddles is adjusted by loosening one knob and sliding the bottom frame sections apart. This looks harder than it is. In fact it does not require lifting the unit, and this adjustment is fairly easy.\nThe little fan directs a breeze at your face. It has two speeds but isn\'t adjustable for direction. I haven\'t tried the mp3 player yet, or any of the pre-programmed workouts.', 4, 1, '2014-05-08 04:30:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(15, 63, 2, 'Lorraine Meyer', 'Easy to assemble, sturdy, user friendly, comfortable seat, easy to adjust for various leg lengths, easy to read \"control panel\", great size, many various preprogramed workouts and the option to make-up your own workouts. Love it.', 4, 1, '2014-05-16 11:30:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(17, 63, 2, 'Glendajax - La Jara, CO', 'The bike was easy to assemble. I have been using it for 1 week and I love it. The panel gives me the time, speed, calories burned, distance, and heart rate.', 5, 1, '2014-05-22 01:33:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(18, 63, 2, 'Collies - Glide, OR', 'While the seat is much more comfortable than the other bike I was using, the pedals placement force my knees to go higher and makes it a more difficult workout and harder on my knee joints.', 2, 1, '2014-06-11 05:33:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(19, 65, 2, 'Hoogy Banyny\r\n', 'Great Product!!\r\nBought this for my 9 year old daughter for her birthday and she loves it!! We are actually purchasing another one for my son for his birthday!!!', 4, 1, '2014-06-19 08:29:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(16, 63, 2, 'Pamela', 'Easy to put together, so far working great and seems to be durable. Did not come with power cord, cord was pricey, but cheaper than batteries.', 5, 1, '2014-04-19 04:53:28', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(20, 65, 2, 'Butski', 'Exactly what I expected and wanted for my 12 year old. A really great gift.', 3, 1, '2014-06-02 08:42:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(21, 10000, 2, 'Almanimfa', 'This product is absolutely the BEST! It is well worth the money!!! Makes perfect tea every time. I recently went on a retreat weekend and did not have my tea maker. I had to revert to making tea the old fashioned way, with hot water and letting it brew in a basket in my cup. It just wasn\'t the same. If you love tea, give yourself a treat and buy a Breville One Touch Tea Maker!! You will be glad you did! mmmmm....my tea is brewing now....mmmmm', 5, 1, '2014-06-10 12:20:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(22, 10000, 2, 'Cathleen Cole', 'Not a coffee drinker~ have always loved tea~\r\nThe flavor of the loose leaf tea that this brings out is amazing!\r\nI love being able to set it and it be ready first thing in the morning~\r\nThis Tea Maker is so easy to use too~\r\nHere\'s to many mornings of waking up to the tea being ready at the same\r\ntime my husbands coffee is!\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-03 10:44:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(23, 10000, 2, 'Joli Howell', 'Fast shipping! Thank you for such an amazing product!!!\r\nMy husband purchased this tea maker for me as a gift just recently and I can not say enough great things about it. Being an avid lose leaf tea drinker this has been such a time saver. I usually make myself a thermos of tea every morning to bring to work with me so I can sip all day and this product has cut down my tea making time tremendously. This is by far one of the greatest gifts I have ever received.', 4, 1, '2014-06-19 06:23:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(24, 10022, 2, 'Charity K. Gikunda', 'This product is very good, it meets my expectations. It collects all the dirt and even sucks on wet carpet very well. I would recommend this product to someone.', 4, 1, '2014-05-14 09:40:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(25, 10022, 2, 'Addie', 'I bought this vacuum cleaner for myself. I\'m very satisfied with it. Easy to use everywhere. It\'s a good buy!\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-05-18 10:44:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(26, 10022, 2, 'Kimberly Bastian', 'I couldn\'t be happier with my purchase and just love this vacuum cleaner. I admit I had an unexpected surprise, the lever that stops the roller from moving use to be pretty hard to set but now its as easy as flipping a light switch. So thank you Eureka for making this an even better vacuum cleaner, thumbs up!!!', 5, 1, '2014-06-06 07:45:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(27, 10022, 2, 'Arizona Doug', 'Does a great job at a very good price. Works great on both rug and tile floors. I would recommend it as a great vac to my friends..\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-05 14:33:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(28, 10022, 2, 'M. R. Nelsen ', 'This vacuum is awesome. Even the kid loves it! Great for dog hair, even on crappy apartment carpet. It is basically self propelled, so the only effort you really need is pulling it back towards yourself.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-07 08:52:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(29, 10022, 2, 'Erin - Littleton, CO', 'I LOVE this vacuum. Sure, it\'s a bit unwieldy to use until you get used to it, it is quite heavy, and it is loud. But it makes up for all these things with its sucking power. We have a dog with an undercoat that leaves fur everywhere, and this vacuum is the only one I\'ve found that meets my meticulously-clean standards. When our old Boss broke, I immediately purchased the newer model. I highly recommend this vacuum!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-10 14:24:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(202, 10021, 0, 'Anna', 'I received this vacuum today, and tried it out right away - I love it! It\'s really light, but cleans great. The attachments all work well. Very easy to empty the canister, much easier than having to deal with bags! Overall, I\'m very satisfied with this vacuum, ESPECIALLY for the price!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-15 04:38:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(200, 10021, 0, 'Leigh Abraham', 'Powerful suction, really gets up the dog and cat hair!! Excellent little vacuum. We have a dog and 2 cats and 2 kids. It really keeps the house clean!!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-29 20:40:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(201, 10021, 0, 'D. Riordan (California)', 'What a deal. Looking for a bagless vacuum cleaner that was compact and it was everything I could hope for. Great price and great service.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-24 11:38:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(199, 10021, 0, 'Ruth M. (NY, USA)', 'Everything works as it should. I had a Eureka canister machine for decades and am very pleased with all the upgrades in filter technology.\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-26 10:45:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(197, 10021, 0, 'Denise Goodman ', 'So far this is a great vacuum. It pulls the carpet off the floor practically with its suction. Easy to maneuver.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-08 04:30:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(198, 10021, 0, 'Keith Simpson ', 'Works very good. Very light weight, good priced. I like the color.\nJust wish it had a better way to store the attachments.', 4, 1, '2014-07-01 04:46:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(196, 10021, 0, 'Jason Lawrence', 'I am very pleased with this machine. It has a lot of features, great suction and a number of attachments. I\'d definitely recommend it.\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-14 17:13:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(35, 10002, 2, 'Mel', 'I got this for my first grandson. His mother has nothing but praise for this highly versatile high chair. As my grandson is very young he has not tried all the functions yet, but I know the Graco name, and it is a good one.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-04-08 14:39:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(36, 10002, 2, 'Avioletsky', 'My son starting using this at 5-6 months and hasn\'t looked back. It is sturdy, and also looks nice in our kitchen. I really love how it has 3 trays, so if you don\'t get a chance to clean up after the previous meal, just take it off and there\'s another.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-06 07:24:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(37, 10002, 2, 'Moyer ', 'The versatility of this high chair is awesome! So many people who come to our house have commented on how much they like it. It is a great value for the money!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-07 03:10:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(38, 10002, 2, 'Racheal L. McCoy', 'I love this high chair and my babies seem to love it too. It is easy to clean and adjust. It rolls very nicely. I love all the different options with this chair. I have twins so I bought 2 of these and I love that we can use this chair for a long time instead of having to buy something else. I would buy it again and would recommend it to others.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-09 23:59:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(39, 10002, 2, 'Sonja Washington', 'This is a good investment. I love that high chair booster that comes of the chair great for restaurants. Will not be disappointed.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-05-08 05:40:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(40, 10002, 2, 'Michelle', 'Bought 2 for twins. Perfect from infant to toddler and the added booster seat is great for visiting and the next steps of sitting at the dinner table. Loved the recline feature for infants age and height adjustment for feeding.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-04-18 18:41:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(41, 10002, 2, 'Nicholas', 'My wife and I are extremely satisfied with the Graco blossom 4 in 1. It was a breeze to assemble and seems to be very sturdy. We would definitely recommend anyone to purchase this versatile high chair.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-04-16 06:53:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(42, 10002, 2, 'Lauren Hoff', 'I love that this can do multiple heights, as well as works with them from being super small to toddlers. The fact it comes with a booster seat too is a bonus because now I dont have to buy one if my son suddenly decides hes done with the chair. Also having 3 trays that are stacked to eat off of make it easy to go from dinner to dessert without having to clean up all the previous mess immediately.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-04-02 16:02:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(43, 10019, 2, 'Benjamin Lynch', 'This is the best item I have ever purchased. I switched from gas, and my meat has never tasted any better than is doesn now. I highly recomment this if you think you are a propane fan. This will blow it out of the water. 10 minutes the charcoal is ready, and Im cooking. Propane was ready in 5 minutes so either way its not much more time.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-11 12:37:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(44, 10019, 2, 'Karen J. Paige', 'Husband was very happy when he saw it said it was a great gift his old one was wearing out.. Came very fast would recommend to others.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-12 06:48:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(45, 10019, 2, 'Joaquin Pinnel', 'Excellent! This is my 3rd BBQ and my first Weber. I used to buy cheaper brands but now I understand why this is a little bit more expensive. It worth it. I could assemble in 15 minutes, consider that house tasks are not my best skill. So anyone could assemble this in a short while. \r\nSize of the grill is excellent. I would buy this same grill again!!! I really satisfied with my purchase!', 5, 1, '2014-06-03 08:40:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(46, 10019, 2, 'Ryan S. Kowlessar', 'This is a great grill. My family and I have been able to enjoy using it quite frequently here in South Texas. I have grilled the usual burgers, dogs, chicken and even a turkey with no hassle or problems. This grill keeps the heat contained and consistent. I have even been able to smoke with it. Works fantastic.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-09 12:51:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(47, 10019, 2, 'Jennifer Walters', 'I Bought this as an upgrade to the big Smokey Weber grill. The instructions for putting it together were easy, and it took probably around 1/2 hour (I was in no rush). There is an anchor for the lid so when you raise it, you don\'t have to find a place to put it down. Sturdy construction, easy maintenance and cleaning. I also bought the Weber cover for it and it fits well. I\'ve used it at least a dozen times since buying it, with different kinds of charcoal, and wood chips, and no problems at all. Cooks evenly, heats well, would definitely recommend.', 4, 1, '2014-05-08 05:29:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(48, 72, 2, 'Jeri Doty', 'I have been amazed at how much dirt and pet hair this little gadget picks up every day. I love to show it to my friends who then all want one.\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-04 11:31:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(49, 72, 2, 'Beverly Bellamy', 'Just love it. It is so much fun to watch it clean . My husband calls it my little buddy.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-05-10 04:45:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(50, 72, 2, 'Velma Robinson', 'We love the Neato. It does a fantastic job.\r\nRun it 3 or 4 times a week. Does a great job.', 4, 1, '2014-06-05 14:24:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(51, 72, 2, 'Carol C.', 'Love it,could not believe how much deep embedded dirt it pulled out of my carpet, and continues to do so. I am amazed every time I empty the dust bin. No wonder I couldn\'t keep up with the dusting. We have a sunken living room but vacuum senses it and does not drop over step which is great also. Bought one for each of my daughters and daughter in law. Other daughter in law has one, that is where I became acquainted with Neato, she has a large home with wood, tile and carpet, her floors always look so good. Would recommend it highly.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-14 14:24:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(52, 10008, 0, 'Candii', 'It is really heavy but most of them are. I LOVE it and my babies love it. Ages 10 months and 2 years\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-22 11:41:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(53, 10008, 0, 'Trymaine Kelley', 'Awesome stroller. It is smaller than a lot of other double strollers that are on the market today. It also has a basket at the bottom for storage. Easy to operate and great for the kids. I would definitely recommend.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-03 19:57:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(54, 10008, 0, 'Fredrik Pettersson', 'Just as we had in our mind when we searched for a new stroller. Suites us Perfect. Ankermart shipping was perfect as well! Will shop here again.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-06 17:26:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(55, 10008, 0, 'J. Molander \"Navy Wife\"', 'It\'s everything I wanted in a double stroller. It\'s smaller than a lot of doubles I\'ve tried, it\'s easily maneuverable when both kids are in it, and I love that it\'s interchangeable as the kids grow!! LOVE this stroller and the price!\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-05-10 04:14:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(56, 10008, 0, 'Velma Lester-Medeiros ', 'I am very pleased with this baby stroller that I purchased it again.. I will tell my friends that have new babies were to come to for there baby products . Thank you very much\r\nand on it.', 5, 1, '2014-06-14 08:39:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(57, 10008, 0, 'Shawna D. Smith', 'I love this stroller! I\'ve used several of the seating arrangements and have been happy with the ease and security of each one. The front wheels lock for navigating rougher terrain, which has been great! It folds up easily, though it\'s a tight fit in the trunk of my Honda Accord. Overall an excellent purchase and I get more excited about it every time I discover something new!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-20 18:59:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(58, 10006, 0, 'Shawuana Richardson', 'Great!This product is not only very stylish but it meets all of our expectations. We are very pleased with this purchase and recommend it to anyone with a newborn on the way.\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-06 12:09:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(59, 10006, 0, 'Bona L. Berg', 'I bought this for a baby shower gift. Its very nice for the family to take in the car and visit. I recommend every mother having one. Everything you need it right there! It\'s very well made and attractive looking. I was proud to give it as a gift.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-17 17:34:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(60, 10006, 0, 'Nora', 'Wonderful unit. Has everything one needs for new baby\'s comfort. Baby is comfortable and it is no problem moving her from bassinet to change table. She loves the nature sounds.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-14 20:50:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(61, 10006, 0, 'Douglas Ortega', 'Its really easy to assemble and disassemble. Its heavy once you have it packed but nothing out of this world. Perfect for trips and places out of the house were you need some kind of crib for your baby to sleep.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-04-09 04:33:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(62, 10006, 0, 'Chelden Kratz', 'Great product,very satisfied and fast shipping. Love the playard, very cute. Perfect for baby\'s naps or changing. Definitely a must have!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-05-15 16:15:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(63, 10006, 0, 'L. Mills', 'Showe gift and they loved it! Certain the baby will be very happy in the pack and play. Great idea!\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-20 12:31:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(64, 10006, 0, 'Heathur', 'Easy to put together and so pretty!! The optional vibrating rocker or bassinet is such a cool feature. The sounds and light are a great addition too.', 5, 1, '2014-06-05 12:41:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
