(66, 10006, 0, 'Ankermart Customer - West Virginia', 'This product will last the baby for many years to come. I consider it one of my best purchases because of the value for the number of years of use I will get from it. Quality is excellent and it is easy to assemble. It is very portable & easy to clean.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-05 17:11:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
