(157, 10003, 0, 'Mashed Tomato', 'Our family has a few of these since we have two vehicles. In the four years we\'ve had them, we haven\'t had any major issues with any of them (one of the buckles began to stick, but we received a replacement at no cost per the recall). The kids enjoy being able to have their cup next to them and little cubbies on the side to put their belongings. It is easy to adjust the straps when the child outgrows the current setting. I highly recommend this seat.', 5, 1, '2014-06-16 11:13:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(156, 10003, 0, 'Ryan Gavagni', 'Very nice material, like the sleekness of it. Easy to install and put together. We bought this car seat as an additional carseat so we do not have to keep switching the one we have out of our cars and this is worth the money! Plus, my son loves the cup holder and cubby holes in the seat for storing his snacks and toys !\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-19 02:54:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(154, 10003, 0, 'C. Sedita', 'It\'s very comfortable and extremely durable, the fabric is durable, and it looks easy to clean. I truly love this car seat, I have a good feeling this car seat will last a long time.', 5, 1, '2014-06-28 04:19:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(155, 10003, 0, 'Ashley New', 'Awesome carseat! Fits my 3-yr-old very well, and seems comfortable. I was nervous to order due to reviews warning of recalled button, but the buckle has been updated and works perfectly!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-19 02:54:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(73, 83, 0, 'Angry Scottsman', 'This grill is fantastic. It is rugged and huge! I love the lid holder, it makes it very easy to watch your grill when you have to. I am confident that this grill will last a looooong time!', 5, 1, '2014-06-20 03:48:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(74, 83, 0, 'BBQguy', 'Weber has outdone themselves. While only about four inches wider than their best-selling kettle, the new 26.75\" kettle has 40% more grill space. Charcoal baskets make indirect cooking a cinch, there is an excellent thermometer, they have added a heat baffle so you can open the lid safely bare handed, and there is a well designed holder to place the lid in effortlessly. I\'ve had it a week and cooked on it five nights', 5, 1, '2014-06-04 08:46:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(75, 83, 0, 'Mike', 'This grill is very large; keep this in mind. We needed one this size for parties and indirect grilling so it is perfect. Made in the US. Great weber quality.', 5, 1, '2014-05-15 07:50:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(76, 83, 0, 'Nicholas Sorg', 'No biggie though. Excellent in every way!!! I\'ve used this rig a few times now and one was in conjunction with a Smokenator 2600 to smoke a 25lb fresh ham. Kept temps amazingly well! Absolutely zero gripes!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-19 04:54:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(77, 83, 0, 'Sherriann Cox', 'My husband wanted this grill when our regular sized weber couldn\'t do the job, such as grilling home made pizzas, paella for a crowd, or large turkeys. It\'s what you would expect from Weber- quality, easy to assemble, well packaged.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-05-09 06:43:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(78, 10004, 0, 'Ashley New', 'Awesome carseat! Fits my 3-yr-old very well, and seems comfortable. I was nervous to order due to reviews warning of recalled button, but the buckle has been updated and works perfectly!\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-19 02:54:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(79, 10004, 0, 'Matthew Angel', 'We love this car seat. It installs very easily and all of the straps are take minimal effort to tighten. Our daughter loves the cubby holes and the cup holder.', 5, 1, '2014-06-11 15:26:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(80, 10004, 0, 'Praveen K. Gurram', 'This is one of the best car seats that you can get. It is awesome as not it not snugly fits the kid but has the right adjustments & recline.', 5, 1, '2014-06-05 12:14:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(81, 10004, 0, 'C. Sedita', 'It\'s very comfortable and extremely durable, the fabric is durable, and it looks easy to clean. I truly love this car seat, I have a good feeling this car seat will last a long time.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-28 13:06:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(82, 10004, 0, 'Vincent', 'I gave five stars for an excellent product.I purchased this car seat back in 2009 for my grand daughter. I\'m just getting around to reviewing it better late then never as they say.This is a very well made car seat my grand daughter loves it.I didn\'t mind paying more for a better car seat no skimpy on a child\'s safety .I like the fact that its a 3 in 1 car seat so as they grow and need a booster seat you have it no extra expense.I highly recommend this product.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-05-15 14:30:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(83, 10004, 0, 'Margret Goldsworthy ', 'We bought this as a second carseat for my husbands car and love it. The cupholder is a must have and i wish i had it on the seat that is in my car. The seat is so roomy and comfortable. It will easily become a booster seat as a high back with seat belt and then just the regular booster when the back comes off.', 5, 1, '2014-06-02 18:20:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(84, 10004, 0, 'Mashed Tomato', 'Our family has a few of these since we have two vehicles. In the four years we\'ve had them, we haven\'t had any major issues with any of them (one of the buckles began to stick, but we received a replacement at no cost per the recall). The kids enjoy being able to have their cup next to them and little cubbies on the side to put their belongings. It is easy to adjust the straps when the child outgrows the current setting. I highly recommend this seat.', 5, 1, '2014-06-16 11:13:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
