(86, 10017, 2, 'Patricia', 'Wonderful item this pot makes everything taste better!!!!! Worth every penny. The only drawback it is very heavy and a little hard to wash.', 5, 1, '2014-05-31 19:23:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(87, 10017, 0, ' Karl Kirchoff', 'I have very much enjoyed cooking with this oven. It\'s very high quality, and the food has turned out great!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-18 06:46:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(88, 10017, 0, 'Placebo', 'Excellent and versatile. What more could you ask for. Does require patience to keep from burning things. Cast iron takes a lot longer to heat up from a medium or less stove setting but it will eventually get there.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-12 04:49:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(89, 10017, 0, 'Susan - Taos, NM', 'I have a few Le Crueset pieces but hesitated in spending the money on this large piece. Big mistake. The other &quot;also ran&quot; brand stained and just didn\'t have the quality you get with Le Creuset. I LOVE this pan! Heavy duty, beautiful, and all that you expect from Le Creuset! Use it all the time and LOVE the fact I have purple cookware!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-26 13:41:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(90, 10017, 0, 'Nancy', 'Le Creuset is still the best for long, slow cooking. Their quality remains strong. This pan is a buy once and use for life.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-19 07:46:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(91, 10017, 0, 'By Kareem', 'Fantastic casserole, I use it every weekend for braising and making soups. It\'s non- stick if people use it correctly. Remember to start with low heat for 10 minutes before you put it on the stove, then go to medium heat, then put the oil or butter. Let it heat, then put whatever you\'re cooking. Braised and stewed meats and veggies for 2-3 hours are great and without sticking or cleaning trouble. I had my best results with putting it in the oven at 350 degrees for a 2-3 hours after the initial sautéing on the stove.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-01 13:35:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(92, 86, 0, ' Technut', 'This is a great slide. My kid started on at 8 months. We put a pillow for her to land on at the bottom of slide. And we backed it up to a wall just in case she fell back....she never did. Very durable and so cool looking we put it in our living room play yard! All the neighbor kids came over to play in her yard/slide!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-01 19:40:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(93, 86, 0, 'Grandmother', 'Great product - inviting design... best for kids who like to climb on things. it has gripping holes on the platform, so kids can pull up as they climb securely without falling. it has the right height for the platform - not too far from ground. platform has enough room to bring stuffed toys. indoors fun all through winter. now outside, still played on every day. at birthday party, kids and ages 18 months to 4 1/2 yrs. had fun for hours on it. primary colors look nice in yard. well worth money.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-27 19:01:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(94, 86, 0, 'Penelope D. Bratton', 'This was very easy to put together. It has proven to be very sturdy! My grandson LOVES it! We put it in the basement so he would have something to play on in the winter, so he is on it every day. Great value!!!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-18 05:49:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(95, 86, 0, ' W. Henneberger', 'For once a toy that works as advertised. Easy to assemble. Very durable. My 2 1/2 year old grand daughter would not get off of it, she loves it. Good inside or out.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-01 10:47:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(96, 91, 0, 'Heather Ducote', 'My very hands-on daughter LOVES her playhouse! It\'s so great that she can use her play hammer and screwdriver and build her very own picket fence, install her own flower garden, and pound away on some nails, while still being able to play &quot;house.&quot; It\'s not huge, but plenty big enough for my two toddlers to play together. My husband set it up while I was out, but he said it was easy enough with the right tools as long as you follow the instructions.\n\nThis has been a great purchase for our family. We have already had hours of fun play and look forward to many more for several years', 5, 1, '2014-07-03 15:22:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(97, 91, 0, 'Katie Latham', 'The perfect playhouse for any child! Our daughter loves playing in my herb garden and with daddy\'s tools; this playhouse allows her to have both in one place! Great quality & my husband was able to put together quickly!\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-07-01 18:11:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(98, 91, 0, 'Gary Magyar', 'What a great playhouse. Perfect for outdoor activities. Very durable and of great quality. My child enjoys this product very much.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-24 19:34:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(99, 91, 0, 'Noanie', 'Very nice product; the kids loved it. Allows for lots of imagination. Product was missing the piece that goes over tool holder.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-04 14:16:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(100, 91, 0, 'J. Geoghan', 'This is a great playhouse. My kids planted flowers and enjoy taking care of them. I love that all 3 of them can be playing at the same time w. out being in each other\'s way. They love being able to take the fence apart. All the neighbor kids like to come play. My family loves this house. Very easy to put together.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-16 06:38:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(101, 91, 0, 'Ashley Beckner', 'My daughter loves this thing. It didn\'t come in the girly colors like it shows, but it\'s not a big deal. The part where you plant flowers is plenty deep enough, about 3 1/2 inches and it isn\'t all that hard to put together. It\'s great for the price and is a decent size.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-20 14:12:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(102, 90, 0, 'Monica C Thompson', 'Very cute and quant. It is holding up very well. We have had it in and out of the sun, so I cant tell is it has faded or not. It is strong and big enough for a few kids to play in and around. We have had it almost one and a half years, and still looks great and works as good as new!\n', 4, 1, '2014-07-03 17:29:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(103, 90, 0, 'RJ', 'My granddaughter loves this playhouse, great size for the playroom. It was delivered within a couple of days. I cannot imagine a child not loving this playhouse.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-28 10:08:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(104, 90, 0, 'AMcVey - Wolfeboro, NH', 'I LOVE this playhouse! And so does my daughter :) I bought is becuase of the great deal and I am so happy I did. It did take some muscle to put together but everything snaps and clicks into place so there was no need for tools, which was nice. ', 4, 1, '2014-06-24 17:51:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(105, 90, 0, 'Corona, CA', 'Great Buy! I bought this for my 6 year old daughter. She is a tall girl, even though this playhouse favors smaller children, it didn\'t matter to us, she uses it as a doll house for her lalaloopsies. She spends hours playing! Very attractive toy!', 4, 1, '2014-07-04 17:51:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(106, 89, 0, 'Cynthia J. Baez', 'I purchased this playhouse for my granddaughter. She has really enjoyed playing with it. I would highly recommend this product.\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-02 14:43:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(107, 89, 0, 'Pirate Juniors Parents', 'I investigated for months before purchasing a playhouse for my son who was 2 1/2 when I purchased this one. My son just turned three and he loves playing in his play house! Hours of daily fun. Perfect size with lots of room to grow! Great choice!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-27 19:22:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(108, 89, 0, 'Jacks', 'This is a great product. It assembles easily and our granddaughter is enjoying is more that I ever dreamed she would. We have owned a similar one for about 12 years and it is still as good as when we bought it. I highly recommend them.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-16 19:22:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(109, 89, 0, 'Jacquelyn Pearlman', 'We purchased this playhouse for our grandson\'s 2nd birthday. He loves it! Because of all the rain we have been having, the playhouse was set up in the house. Sppencer moved right in and takes all of his toys in with him. I highly recommend this playhouse.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-02 05:42:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(110, 87, 0, 'Patricia', 'My son loves to play on this bed! Delivery was ahead of schedule and the company that was used to deliver the bed were awesome too. I think the delivery guy was almost as excited as my son was. Set up was easy, just make sure you have a power drill and a package of aa batteries.\n', 4, 1, '2014-07-01 04:37:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(111, 87, 0, 'Tasha Coulter', 'Perfect!! I am so happy with this purchase. This bed is amazing. My toddler (& his 5 year old brother) love this bed!! It\'s a bed by night and a really fun toy during the day. The lights are a great addition because my little guy is afraid of the dark. I even find it comfortable:) The fact that it has a built in toy box is even cooler. The shelves are pretty small but not a bad thing since my son has plenty of small stuff.', 5, 1, '2014-06-27 11:49:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(112, 87, 0, 'Darla J. Clapps', 'This bed is wonderful. It was easy to assemble, looks great in the pirate themed room, and my grandson loves it.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-18 17:27:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(113, 87, 0, 'Vermont Collector ', 'Bought this bed for a grandson. He loves it. In fact, I think his Dad loves it just as much. The bed is well made with lots of things that a little boy will love (from the cannon on front to the working lights on back of the ship). It\'s been a huge hit with everyone.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-22 13:21:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(114, 87, 0, 'Elizabeth Stingo', 'My grandson was overwhelmed when he saw his pirate bed. It was fairly easy to put together and has many practical features. The bookcase head board, the night lights and the storage under the cannon.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-28 07:45:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(115, 87, 0, 'Vincent N McCormick II ', 'This was easy to put together even with our toddler \"helping\". He absolutely loves it and spends time before and after bed playing in it.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-20 05:39:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(116, 87, 0, 'Shaun Bott', 'Great bed. My children love to play on it and my 2 year old does pretty good going to sleep in it. Would be better if the storage area was hinged. It keeps getting knocked off.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-16 05:44:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(117, 87, 0, 'Tad Manly ', 'I bought this bed for my 2 year old who recently learned how to climb out of his crib. He absolutely loves it! Naps are no longer a challenge as he can\'t wait to climb into his pirate ship. This bed definitely helped me gain a few \"awesome Dad\" points.', 4, 1, '2014-06-11 13:09:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(118, 87, 0, 'Ashish (San Francisco)', 'Great bed, its not too fancy but its a great bed, my son loves it , helped me move him from sleeping in our room to his own room. I cant be more happy with the purchase.', 5, 1, '2014-07-04 18:39:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(119, 87, 0, 'Sarah Kemp ', 'My son loves this! Very easy to put together (takes a little time though) and great quality. A little concerned that my dare devil will pull the mast and break it but otherwise seems very sturdy.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-22 20:13:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(120, 87, 0, 'Omar ', 'Excellent product arrived on time and very good quality 100% recommended . ..', 5, 1, '2014-06-25 12:24:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(121, 88, 2, 'D. Roach (CA)', 'Really fun! I would not say this is for big kids. This is definitely for toddlers and even so I wouldn\'t have more than 3 in at a time, but it\'s very handy and always fun for the kids. Very easy to set up and the bag is large enough that you have plenty of space to get it when the kids are done.\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-29 02:43:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(122, 88, 2, 'Whipple Newell ', 'Little tikes shady jump castle provides immediate and hours of fun!!! Easy to put up and stowe away. Our kids want to put in in our house it\'s so fun.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-21 17:42:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(123, 88, 2, 'D. Titus (Ohio) ', 'This was great! Kids loved playing in it, and when we needed to travel half across the country to visit the grandparents, we just set it up and waited for the first big gust of wind. Pays for itself on the first trip.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-07-02 10:24:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(124, 88, 2, 'Dominique', 'My 3 year old daughter and I love how convenient it is to put up and pack away. This is a great buy!!!!!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-28 18:16:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(125, 88, 2, 'Max Speyer ', 'This bouncer has been great - we have kept it inside the house and it is perfect for getting energy out on rainy or cold days. Just what we needed!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-03 04:46:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(126, 88, 2, 'Michael', 'This is an amazing gift for children ages 3 to 10. Kids love it and can even bounce inside the house. Inflates quickly and allows you to fold us and store easily.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-25 15:38:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(127, 92, 0, 'Kimrv', 'This is really a great toy. My 18 month old son really enjoys the slide and rock climber. The only problem I had was the instructions that was not so clear. The bolts did not include corresponding size so I had to figure out which one goes to the right hole. Definitely a 2-person job. I assembled it myself and it took about 4 hours including redoing the bolts. Other than the difficulty in the assembly, the toy is really nice. It satisfied the climber in my son.', 5, 1, '2014-06-11 12:31:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(128, 92, 0, 'Jamio', 'The product is exelent! Plenty of fun for my almost 18 months old son! Easy to put together, very sturdy, looks great and just the right size for our patio! Thank you Little tikes for great products and thank you Ankermart for good prices!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-05 10:49:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(129, 92, 0, 'Gramps', 'This was a gift for my grandson and within hours of it being assembled I was receiving pictures of him enjoying it very much. Thanks for a great product at a very reasonable price!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-18 06:41:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(130, 92, 0, 'Rais', 'Perfect for what we were looking for, great quality, and really great price from ankermart.com', 5, 1, '2014-06-30 03:39:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(131, 92, 0, 'Sunny Smile', 'We just put it together today. It is well built and well thought out. This should keep our two year old grandson busy for years. The price is good too!\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-07-01 06:36:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(132, 92, 0, 'Kristin - South Beach, OR', 'My daughter was climbing on everything. This gives the climbing space she needs without us worrying about height restrictions. She LOVES it!', 5, 1, '2014-06-28 16:10:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(133, 92, 0, 'Jessica', 'This is the perfect gift for my nephew. He loves being outdoors and he especially loves climbing things. I\'m very happy with this product. I highly recommend this to anyone who has a very young child that is a climber.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-04 02:50:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(134, 10009, 0, 'Grace', 'This has been the most wonderful carseat, the only one that we can put our son in an him not get upset because he is getting buckled in. His back doesn\'t get sweaty and hot like it was in the regular carrier. I will say its heavy and big, I am glad that I have a Ford Expedition that has enough room for it to be rear facing. But, I know that my son is safe and secure in it and that\'s what matters most. To buy it all over again, yes I would!\n\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-08 21:08:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(135, 10009, 0, 'Joann', 'This is a wonderful car seat. It is easy to install and the covers are easy to clean. We love the recline feature, the arm rests, and the cup holder. I especially love the fact that you don\'t have to rethread the straps to adjust them. To me that is one of the best features as well as the easy to install base and seat. The only con I can think of that people may not like is that it is a heavy car seat but I like that it is heavy because to me it feels safe. Also if you are not moving the car seat anywhere the weight won\'t be a problem and even better if you have 2 cars and you need to move the car seat all you will need to do it buy an extra base for your second car and will just have to move the seat part from car to car.\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-03 15:12:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(136, 10009, 0, 'Shannon', 'This carseat was purchased for my heart baby. I rear-faced her until she was 2 1/2 and she never complained. She is forward facing now and I love how it reclines to let her nap peacefully.\r\n\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-19 10:16:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(137, 10009, 0, 'Arfam', 'This car seat is very sturdy and safe. Right now we have our 19 month old in it, and he loves it too! If fits great in the bucket seat of our minivan. The base system with this seat makes it easier to install in the vehicle than our old toddler seat. This is a top of the line seat!\r\n\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-14 09:44:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(138, 10009, 0, 'Davis\r\n ', 'I really love this seat, I feel that my child is very safe. She loves the seat as well. my husband and I both love the stay in base, the fact that you can recline the seat while child is still in seat the side protection the seat give is great. It is well worth the money spent on it. I just wish you guys had it on the market when 7 year old was a baby.\r\n\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-10 10:10:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(139, 10009, 0, 'Wendy', 'I love this seat. I bought this when my daughter outgrew her infant seat and got this. This seat will hold her up til she weighs 100lbs. It is heavy but I feel like its a sturdy seat. We bought a extra base to put into another car and its easy to move in and into the other car. I would purchase it again.\r\n\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-27 19:37:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(140, 10009, 0, 'Anne\r\n ', 'Graco Products are extremely well made. Love the fact this car seat goes to 100 ilbs very universal. i am extermely happy with all Graco products they stand behine everything.\r\n\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-01 06:53:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(141, 10001, 0, 'Dyari', 'I got this for my baby and I love it!! The stroller is so light not heavy at all. I\'ve washed the carseat padding numerous times and still looks like new love it..\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-11 03:37:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(142, 10001, 0, 'Mama', 'This was the best travel system. So easy to use, able to open and close with one hand. So great I bought a second one for my second kid!!! My husband and I recommend this to everyone.\r\n\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-14 20:12:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(143, 10001, 0, 'Jame', 'We chose this system because of the pattern, easy of use and longevity. My son is 7.5 months, about 18 lbs and 26 inches. He still has room to grow in the car seat and although we are switching to a convertible for our main car, we will continue to use this as a backup seat in our second car and grandparent\'s cars until he outgrows it. The stroller is awesome and has never given us any trouble. I got all my Christmas shopping done with my little one sleeping in the car seat hooked into the stroller and now that the weather is nice we go for walks all the time with him strapped into the stroller. The stroller opens and collapses very easily with one hand. The car seat and base have been perfect in our car. I cannot say enough about this system and would highly recommend it to everyone!\r\n\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-09 11:12:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(144, 10001, 0, 'Carrie', 'FANTASTIC !!!!! Everything came in one simple box and was very easy to put together. I love at how i can load the stroller in the trunk of my car and go to walmart. If the baby is asleep in the car seat ..... NO PROBLEM!! I dont have to wake him up .... I just have to press the lever in the back of the car seat to release it from its base in the car and pop it onto the stroller .... easy as cake!!!! i believe this is a Must-Have for every mommy.\r\n\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-26 03:25:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(145, 10001, 0, 'Huda', 'Alano Travel System with SnugRide Infant Car Seat is the best travel system ever I used.\r\n\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-11 03:25:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
