(146, 10001, 0, 'Acarney\n\n', 'We love the Graco travel system. The print was exactly what I wanted and gender-neutral. The base system is easy to install and makes life so much easier. I love that the car seat fits right into the stroller. The stroller is super easy to open and close. It also rides very smoothly. Would definitely recommend.\r\n\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-09 03:25:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(256, 10027, 0, 'Luna', 'This booster! Car seat is exactly what we needed. Light weight and easy to install. The design is great for comfort and safety for my little one. I would recommend this car seat for any family that travel.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-09-07 16:27:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(158, 10003, 0, 'Matthew Angel', 'We love this car seat. It installs very easily and all of the straps are take minimal effort to tighten. Our daughter loves the cubby holes and the cup holder.', 5, 1, '2014-06-11 15:26:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(159, 10003, 0, 'Praveen K. Gurram', 'This is one of the best car seats that you can get. It is awesome as not it not snugly fits the kid but has the right adjustments & recline.', 5, 1, '2014-06-05 12:14:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(160, 10003, 0, 'Margret Goldsworthy ', 'We bought this as a second carseat for my husbands car and love it. The cupholder is a must have and i wish i had it on the seat that is in my car. The seat is so roomy and comfortable. It will easily become a booster seat as a high back with seat belt and then just the regular booster when the back comes off.', 5, 1, '2014-06-02 18:20:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(161, 10003, 0, 'Vincent', 'I gave five stars for an excellent product.I purchased this car seat back in 2009 for my grand daughter. I\'m just getting around to reviewing it better late then never as they say.This is a very well made car seat my grand daughter loves it.I didn\'t mind paying more for a better car seat no skimpy on a child\'s safety .I like the fact that its a 3 in 1 car seat so as they grow and need a booster seat you have it no extra expense.I highly recommend this product.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-05-15 14:30:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(162, 10005, 0, 'C. Sedita', 'It\'s very comfortable and extremely durable, the fabric is durable, and it looks easy to clean. I truly love this car seat, I have a good feeling this car seat will last a long time.', 5, 1, '2014-07-18 04:29:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(163, 10005, 0, 'Ashley New', 'Awesome carseat! Fits my 3-yr-old very well, and seems comfortable. I was nervous to order due to reviews warning of recalled button, but the buckle has been updated and works perfectly!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-19 02:54:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(164, 10005, 0, 'Ryan Gavagni', 'Very nice material, like the sleekness of it. Easy to install and put together. We bought this car seat as an additional carseat so we do not have to keep switching the one we have out of our cars and this is worth the money! Plus, my son loves the cup holder and cubby holes in the seat for storing his snacks and toys !\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-19 02:54:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(165, 10005, 0, 'Mashed Tomato', 'Our family has a few of these since we have two vehicles. In the four years we\'ve had them, we haven\'t had any major issues with any of them (one of the buckles began to stick, but we received a replacement at no cost per the recall). The kids enjoy being able to have their cup next to them and little cubbies on the side to put their belongings. It is easy to adjust the straps when the child outgrows the current setting. I highly recommend this seat.', 5, 1, '2014-06-16 11:13:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
