(177, 10007, 0, 'Shawuana Richardson', 'Great!This product is not only very stylish but it meets all of our expectations. We are very pleased with this purchase and recommend it to anyone with a newborn on the way.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-06 12:09:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(178, 10007, 0, 'Bona L. Berg', 'I bought this for a baby shower gift. Its very nice for the family to take in the car and visit. I recommend every mother having one. Everything you need it right there! It\'s very well made and attractive looking. I was proud to give it as a gift.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-17 17:34:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(179, 10007, 0, 'Douglas Ortega', 'Its really easy to assemble and disassemble. Its heavy once you have it packed but nothing out of this world. Perfect for trips and places out of the house were you need some kind of crib for your baby to sleep.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-04-09 04:33:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(180, 10007, 0, 'Nora', 'Wonderful unit. Has everything one needs for new baby\'s comfort. Baby is comfortable and it is no problem moving her from bassinet to change table. She loves the nature sounds.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-14 20:50:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(181, 10007, 0, 'Chelden Kratz', 'Great product,very satisfied and fast shipping. Love the playard, very cute. Perfect for baby\'s naps or changing. Definitely a must have!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-05-15 16:15:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(182, 10007, 0, 'L. Mills', 'Showe gift and they loved it! Certain the baby will be very happy in the pack and play. Great idea!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-20 12:31:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(183, 10007, 0, 'Heathur', 'Easy to put together and so pretty!! The optional vibrating rocker or bassinet is such a cool feature. The sounds and light are a great addition too.', 5, 1, '2014-06-05 12:41:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(184, 10007, 0, 'Rony', 'This is the most practical pack and play you can buy. I love everything about it. And the removable rocking chair is the best. I love the color too. I got so many complements on this piece I love it. Very much worth the price.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-18 08:48:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(185, 10007, 0, 'Ankermart Customer - West Virginia', 'This product will last the baby for many years to come. I consider it one of my best purchases because of the value for the number of years of use I will get from it. Quality is excellent and it is easy to assemble. It is very portable & easy to clean.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-05 17:11:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
