(189, 10012, 0, 'AllieVig', 'This car seat is highly recommended! It\'s very easy to secure your child into the seat. I love the ease of loosening and tightening the straps. The colors are beautiful and the fabric is soft. My child is very comfortable in this seat.\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-16 05:15:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(190, 10012, 0, 'Brandy\r\n ', 'We absolutely loved this carseat. We used this carseat until my son was 9 months old and finally had to move to a convertible carseat because of how tall he is. We didn\'t realize how lucky we were to have picked this carseat until we had to move on to a convertible. I still wish we could use this one. I would buy this 100x over again.\r\n\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-07-05 02:35:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(191, 10012, 0, 'Lucky ', 'Best car seat, for safety!! My child feels so safe in this car seat and my husband and I feel safe when our child is in in.\r\n\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-03 12:42:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(192, 10012, 0, 'Zemar\r\n ', 'I was so impressed that it was so easy to secure my child with this car seat. It was also super quick to remove the entire seat from the vehicle and transport into a store or the house.\r\n\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-30 18:39:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(193, 10012, 0, 'Kimmy\r\n ', 'I absoulutly love this seat i love graco its the best brand i would encourage ever mommy and daddy to rear face for as long as possible please and make sure the harness is at its appropriate level and tightness and to make sure the car seat is in properly.\r\n\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-25 17:45:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
