(195, 10012, 0, 'LadyDee\r\n \r\n ', 'We absolutely love this Car Seat, we purchased the Graco Stroller travel system and it came with the car seat. One thing I love the most is the weight and lenght recommendation, it\'s alot more then some other car seats. I also like the different comfort positions for baby from new born to 1 year. I would definately recommend this car seat. ', 5, 1, '2014-07-08 11:12:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(208, 50, 0, 'Tiffani', 'The suction is quite strong and seems to pick up dust and dirt that my old hoover missed. Additionally the brush dowel is very easy to remove and clean, which is not the case with many vacuums. This is a very well engineered device and I recommend it highly.\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-03 12:42:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(209, 50, 0, 'Nancy (West of Boston)', 'Dyson vacuum cleaners are the best. The suction is great and the on board tools make cleaning a snap. I have one and I\'m thinking about getting another to keep on the second floor.\r\n', 4, 1, '2014-06-19 12:42:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(210, 10013, 0, 'Jeffrey P. ', 'Love this blower. Works great with great power. I\'ve been a fan of this brand for a long time and they haven\'t disappointed. Highly recommended!\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-01 07:41:32', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
