(212, 10013, 0, 'Mandziuk (Chicago, Il, US)', 'Looks great, functions well, and as I expected it to be. Instructions were helpful as well and outlined the gas requirement well.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-07 17:17:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(213, 10013, 0, 'Onerka', 'Great little blower. Everyone out there that says the gas system falls apart, it\'s because they leave gas in it after they use it.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-02 12:17:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(214, 10013, 0, 'Harley Owner', 'Awesome leaf blower, starts in cold weather with no issues... highly recommended.... easy to prime, and not hard to pull or start.. its a must have product.\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-12 12:46:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
