(216, 10013, 0, 'Moe Grenier (Otisfield,Maine USA)', 'Needed a blower that would blow leaves up over a 5 foot rock wall , and this leaf blower that did very easily ! I would recommend it to anyone who needs a leaf blower with guts and power !\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-06 04:24:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
