(218, 10014, 0, 'Dale C.', 'The Husqvarna 125bvx 28cc 2-cyclegas powered 170 MPH Blower/Vac is GREAT!! It starts easy,runs great, and the vacum is good. I would really recommed this blower/vac\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-10 04:24:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(219, 10014, 0, '\"Rookie\" (NM)', 'Starts easy, prime it x3, usual starts on very first pull. Vacuum works good, mulches good. Would definitely recommend to anyone.\r\n\r\n\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-02 04:24:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(220, 10014, 0, 'Weasely (Missouri, USA)', 'Everything I expected. I took the warnings about wearing out the blower by processing sticks with the leaves, so I use just the blower, but it works very well.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-18 20:45:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(221, 10014, 0, 'Robert S Schmidt Jr ', 'Read the instructions.. mixed the gas and assembled the tubes.. followed the starting instructions and it fired right up!\r\nWorks very well , been blowing leaves daily since I received it!! Uses far less gasoline than my lawn tractor & leave vacuum!', 5, 1, '2014-06-27 20:29:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(222, 10014, 0, 'Great Blower!', 'Just got it yesterday, its just as described. Well made and easy to handle. Can\'t go wrong with Hasqvarna. Great deal.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-19 20:29:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(223, 10018, 0, 'Valerie Bishop', 'We love our Aros! I turn it on as soon as I get off the train so that it\'s on and up and running for about 10 minutes before I even walk in the door. We also have a timer set so that it turns itself off at 3am every night. Keeps the room cool while we sleep without forcing to run it all night or waking up freezing. I also love that it blows the air up at an angle instead of straigh across the room. Doesn\'t blow on anyone straight on or blow over anything sitting on a table. Very smart design. We can easily keep track of our spending which is important to us too. Not any louder than any other AC window unit I\'ve used but with way sleeker design. ', 5, 1, '2014-07-13 10:48:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(224, 10018, 0, 'So Convenient!', 'I love having the ability to adjust temps, turn off/on from bed. Was easily installed and light enough that I could do it myself, without help. Good looking, but unobtrusive. I could appreciate it being a tad quieter, but it is not overly loud. And, oh yeah, it cools!', 5, 1, '2014-07-03 18:28:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(225, 10018, 0, 'Daniel J Theiss', 'A great product works great. There customer service is great. Could not be happier.', 5, 1, '2014-06-30 05:53:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(226, 10016, 0, 'Thomas Fischel ', 'Fast shipping and works very well.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-16 15:26:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(227, 10016, 0, 'Carolina Transplant', 'This blower works extremely well. Starts easily and blows like a tornado. Quiet, light, and powerful - I love it!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-10 08:51:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(228, 10016, 0, 'Duke ', 'Everything I wanted in a leaf blower. Verry powerful. Moves wet, packed leaves with ease. Comfortable to carry. Starts easy and not to noisey.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-07 19:15:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(229, 10016, 0, 'Mike Jones ', 'I love this thing, it is like meditation for me, I can blow leafs and rocks wherever I want and nobody bugs me while I do it! Very powerful and no problems so far!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-03 10:39:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(230, 10016, 0, ' L. Kelton', 'We were looking for a new blower and this one had great recommendations. It\'s very powerful and just what we needed. Shipping was also very quick.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-18 03:48:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(231, 10016, 0, 'Donald G. Bull', 'This product is unbelieveable. I will never buy a different leaf blower. More than ample power and gets the job done in half the time. Just perfect...\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-21 17:25:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(232, 10016, 0, 'Orchid (Boston, MA) ', 'It helps cutting time in a half for cleaning. My husband is very pleased with the purchase. Highly recommended it.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-16 07:49:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
