(236, 10015, 0, 'Bryan D. Moszer ', 'I love this trimmer, it is light, fast/powerful, and easy to start. Reloading the spool with fresh line is easy and this thing is built to work.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-03 18:14:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(237, 10015, 0, 'Ci Chen', 'I have 2 of these Husqvarna, with all the various attachments you can buy for them. This is an excellent excellent weed wacker, so convenient with all the various attachments, it runs forever before it needs more fuel. It\'s powerful and so easy to use. You will be completely satisfied with it. I would pay more for it, worth every penny. 7 stars...\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-20 08:56:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
