(241, 10020, 0, 'F. North', 'I had heard good things about the Nest thermostat from my friends. When one of my original thermostats started to fail, I decided to go with the Nest. I went to my local Lowes and purchased two Nest thermostats.\nWhen I got home, I watch a youtube video on installing the Nest. It is now one week later and I am very happy with my decision. \nI like the ability to make adjustments from the internet and my smart phone. I will tell my friends to take a good look at the Nest thermostats.', 5, 1, '2014-08-01 14:45:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(242, 10020, 0, 'RobB - Roanoke, VA', 'I recently purchased a house that had an outdated manual thermostat. One of the first things on my to-do list was to upgrade to a thermostat that allowed schedules and preferably had wifi connectivity. After exhaustive research I settled on the NEST thermostat and couldn\'t be happier with my decision. Installation was very easy and NESTs customer service is superb. I took a picture of my current wiring with my smartphone, emailed it to NEST and within a day they responded with instruction on how to wire my new thermostat.\r\nGood design and great customer service goes a long way!', 5, 1, '2014-07-31 09:14:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(243, 10020, 0, 'Terrick - Atlanta', 'I was skeptical at first on how easy this is to use but now I do not know why I did not purchase sooner. Installation took all of 10 minutes and the Nest delivers. I have had it for a week so far and it has already cut down on energy use. This is a great product.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-29 03:56:08', '2014-08-12 00:00:00'),
(244, 10020, 0, 'Aspenshell', 'I bought this Nest for a second home.The Nest is amazing! My energy costs have dropped, and I love the monthly reports and the ability to control the thermostat from my phone, even when i am away.', 5, 1, '2014-07-24 16:27:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(245, 10020, 0, 'Jennifer', 'It\'s only been a week and it already knows what time I get out of bed in the morning! The house is toasty for my morning shower. I love the away feature. Also I can have the house warmed up before I get home from work by adjusting the temp on my smart phone when I leave work.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-17 03:35:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(246, 10020, 0, 'DoItYourself', 'Download the app and change the settings using your phone when you are at home in the other room. Have already noticed electricity usage since it was installed and it\'s only been one week. Can\'t wait to see the savings continue!!!\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-02 19:05:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(247, 10020, 0, 'Bassboy - Firebrick, KY', 'Had this a full month and I\'m already saving over $40 on my heating bill this month! Summer cooling should be a huge improvement. Well worth the initial cost to buy. Only took 5 minutes to install and set up. Love the iPhone app giving full control of unit from anywhere in the world.', 5, 1, '2014-08-05 17:24:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(248, 10020, 0, 'Darek', 'A great product and well designed. It was very easy to install, very easy to set up, and works as advertised! It works perfectly with my iPad.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-30 08:18:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(249, 10020, 0, 'Gopper', 'The nest is so easy to learn, and has incredible functionality. I would highly recommend this product to anyone looking to upgrade their thermostat at home.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-06-27 06:26:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(250, 10020, 0, 'Milorod', 'Excellent Thermostat with easy installation, and it\'s \"artificial intelligence\" is truly remarkable. Senses when you are in the room, and adjusts the temp accordingly.\r\n', 5, 1, '2014-07-02 20:17:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(251, 10026, 0, 'V. Stis ', 'Love this! It is fantastic! The sweetner in the soda is natural without all the adverse side effects as the aspertame and the taste is great! Prefer the dishwasher safe bottles. Love being able to pick how much fizz I want in my drinks!\n', 5, 1, '2014-09-01 08:27:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(252, 10026, 0, 'Eitan Shaked ', 'I had the old version of the Soda Stream , and this is much better.\r\nfirst - inserting the bottle to the machine is easier. Then comes the LCD screen and the touch panel - which are great.\r\nIn overall - I am recommending on this Soda Stream machine , smart buy.', 5, 1, '2014-08-30 16:10:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
