(320, 10647, 0, 'Bill in Prescott Az', 'I bought the grill on Sunday night.  It arrived in perfect condition yesterday.  The grill was easy to assemble as well.  I do have one complaint which is my luck...  The price shifted down again by 30.00!  I paid 579 on Sunday and now it is 549.  It looks great on my patio and very solid construction.', 5, 0, '2018-08-17 10:04:22', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(321, 10647, 0, 'Tyler', 'As a first time smoker, I have to say that this was super easy to setup and use. Great price for a great smoker. Ankermart delivered exactly as advertised.', 5, 0, '2018-08-17 13:10:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(322, 10642, 0, 'Carla', 'I just received this grill. Just as described. Delivery was speedy. Packaged well. Very pleased. Thank you.', 5, 0, '2018-08-17 17:17:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(323, 10642, 0, 'Carla', 'This grill is as described. The delivery was fast. Packaging was excellent.  I will definitely buy from here again.  Great quality , excellent service,  speedy delivery,  product just as described!! Excellent! !!!', 5, 0, '2018-08-17 17:20:22', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(324, 10642, 0, 'Tblackford', 'Amazing grill at a fraction of the price anywhere else online! Shipping was very fast and was very easy to assemble and I was grilling the same day. Can’t say how pleased I am with this grill and look forward to many years of use. ', 5, 0, '2018-09-12 19:57:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(325, 10628, 3500, 'LaSondra Stuckey', 'I am unable to purchase this item due to an Error Message about an unavailable payment method! Why? I read the payment methods accepted but I am not permitted to complete my order at check out! Why not? I need someone to contact me by email: lstuckey45@gmail.com. I already tried contacting their website email!', 1, 0, '2018-10-29 13:29:32', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(326, 10663, 0, 'roy escobar', 'this is a good security camera', 4, 0, '2019-02-13 00:44:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(327, 10663, 0, 'roy escobar', 'this is a great camera to have', 4, 0, '2019-02-13 00:45:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(328, 10673, 93, 'june', 'Tried to purchase 2 of these items and cannot because they are out of stock &amp; it shows in stock. The worst on line purchasing I have come across. I have to say you better not send me any emails if I could not purchase your items. If I receive any emails from you it will go right to spam', 1, 0, '2019-05-26 17:40:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
